NK091(ke)001:1: // yo ga s+au r+y+ya d+ai bi t+aa y+aa s+s+aa d+h+w+aa
NK091(ke)001:2: kh+y+aa ta pra b+haw+aa&a&a&a nu da yu pam shu n+aa
NK091(ke)001:3: ma sh+r+ai dz+aa ti s+au t+r+aa sha ya sam g+ha
NK091(ke)001:4: s+ya t+ai k+aa bi ha ra ti sma ////
NK091(ke)001:5: dpal spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa'i 'grel pa rnal
NK091(ke)001:6: 'byor nyi ma gsal bar byed pa'i legs bshad gzi
NK091(ke)001:7: ldan 'char kha'i 'od snang zhes bya ba glegs bam
NK091(ke)001:9: na mo gu ru d+har+m+aa s+aa r+aa ya /
NK091(ke)001:10: ji bzhin ye gnas che ba lnga ldan dbyings //
NK091(ke)001:11: rang bzhin lhun grub 'od gsal rig pa'i khams //
NK091(ke)001:12: dbyer med bde chen sras mchog byang chub sems //
NK091(ke)001:13: gnyug ma don gyi gshis la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:14: chos sku kun bzang rgyal tshab skyes bu dang //
NK091(ke)001:15: longs sku rigs lnga sprul sku thub pa'i dbang //
NK091(ke)001:16: rigs gsum sems dpa' gsang ba'i sku mchog ste //
NK091(ke)001:17: dgongs brgyud rgyal ba rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:18: rgyal sras gnyis kyis lha klu'i rig 'dzin dang //
NK091(ke)001:19: gsang ba'i bdag pos drag shul can gyi rtser //
NK091(ke)001:20: dam pa lnga la gsang ba'i mdzod bgros pa'i //
NK091(ke)001:21: rig brgyud rig 'dzin rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:22: sprul pa'i glegs bam dngos snang rgyal po dzah in+d+ra n+aa ga gu h+ya pu tri gsum //
NK091(ke)001:23: ku ku r+aa dza rig 'dzin sar gshegs pa'i //
NK091(ke)001:24: rna brgyud gang zag rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:25: ro langs bde ba rdo rje bzhad pa rtsal //
NK091(ke)001:26: pra b+ha hasti sh+aakya seng ge dang //
NK091(ke)001:27: sh+aakya mu tra sh+aakya pra b+ha gsum //
NK091(ke)001:28: bka' bab rtsal 'chang rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:29: d+aa na rak+shi h'u mdzad blo gros brtan //
NK091(ke)001:30: bde ba gsal mdzad d+harma b+ho d+hi dang //
NK091(ke)001:31: ba su d+ha ra mkhan chen chos rgyal skyong //
NK091(ke)001:32: 'phags bal pan grub rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:33: gangs ljongs mig gcig bee ro tsa na dang //
NK091(ke)001:34: dpal brtsegs klu yi rgyal mtshan che btsan skyes //
NK091(ke)001:35: mdo sgyu'i mnga' bdag gnubs chen mkhyen pa'i gter //
NK091(ke)001:36: sgra bsgyur lo ts+aa rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:37: yon tan rgya mtsho ye shes rgya mtsho dang //
NK091(ke)001:38: blo gros byang chub tho gar nam mkha' lde //
NK091(ke)001:39: dpal chen dngos snang zur chen sh+aakya 'byung //
NK091(ke)001:40: bstan pa'i mnga' bdag rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:41: bde gshegs zur chung pa dang ka ba bzhi //
NK091(ke)001:42: gsang bdag chen po mda' tsha hor po'i zhabs //
NK091(ke)001:43: lha rje smar dang gtsang pa 'gro ba'i mgon //
NK091(ke)001:44: gsang chen bstan 'dzin rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:45: 'jam dbyangs bla ma kun mkhyen kahthoga pa //
NK091(ke)001:46: phyag na pad+ma chos rje gtsang ston mchog /rdo rje 'dzin dngos byams pa 'bum pa'i zhabs //
NK091(ke)001:47: rgyal ba yab sras rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:48: nam mkha' rdo rje thugs rje ye shes dang //
NK091(ke)001:49: ston pa dbang 'byor dpal 'bar nam mkha'i mtshan //
NK091(ke)001:50: mgon po rgyal mtshan tshul khrims rgyal mtshan mchog /bstan pa'i mdzod 'dzin rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:51: bra bo chos 'bum ye shes rgyal mtshan pa //
NK091(ke)001:52: rdo rje bzang po nam mkha' rgya mtsho dang //
NK091(ke)001:53: nam mkha' dpal ba nam mkha' rgya mtsho'i sde //
NK091(ke)001:54: brgyud pa'i srol 'dzin rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:55: hor po chos dbang nam mkha' rdo rje dang //
NK091(ke)001:56: chos kyi 'byung gnas pad+ma bkra shis zhabs //
NK091(ke)001:57: rin chen rdo rje thugs mchog drag po rtsal //
NK091(ke)001:58: 'gran bral skyes chen rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:59: yang lung gi brgyud pa ltar na kha ba dkar po yan 'dra la de nas /
NK091(ke)001:60: bsod nams rgya mtsho bsod nams rdo rje dang //
NK091(ke)001:61: ston pa seng ge bkra shis rin chen zhabs //
NK091(ke)001:63: kun bzang rgya mtsho khyab gdal klong yangs dang //
NK091(ke)001:64: lhun grub rgya mtsho pad+ma nor bu dang //
NK091(ke)001:65: karma bkra shis pad+ma sbyin pa ste //
NK091(ke)001:66: smin grol mdzod 'dzin rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:67: karma lha dbang pad+ma bzod pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:68: mdo sngags bstan 'dzin chos kyi nyi ma mchog /rgyal mtshan 'od zer pad+ma rgyal mtshan te //
NK091(ke)001:69: bstan 'dzin skyes mchog rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:70: gzhan yang kun mkhyen rong klong rnam gnyis dang //
NK091(ke)001:71: 'gyur med rdo rje lo chen d+harma sh+r+ai //
NK091(ke)001:72: pad+ma phrin las rig 'dzin 'jigs bral gling //
NK091(ke)001:73: nges don gsal mdzad rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:74: 'jam mgon mkhyen brtse'i dbang dang mchog gyur gling //
NK091(ke)001:75: yon tan rgya mtsho chos kyi dbang po dang //
NK091(ke)001:76: smra ba'i nyi ma mi pham chos kyi rje //
NK091(ke)001:77: zla bral mkhas grub rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:78: khyad par dus 'dir dpags daka'i chos gter gyis //
NK091(ke)001:79: rgyal bstan spyi dang lung chen 'dus pa mdo'i //
NK091(ke)001:80: bstan pa'i sgo 'byed mkhas btsun grub pa'i dbang //
NK091(ke)001:81: chos kyi rgya mtsho'i sprin la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:82: 'gro 'dul rig 'dzin sna tshogs rang grol dang //
NK091(ke)001:83: chos kyi rdo rje mkhan chen dpal gyi mtshan //
NK091(ke)001:84: spobs pa'i gter mdzod pad+ma bi dza sogs //
NK091(ke)001:85: bka' drin mnyam med rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:86: las rab gling pa ngag dbang kun tu bzang //
NK091(ke)001:87: grub pa'i dbang mchog byams pa chos 'dzin rje //
NK091(ke)001:88: blo gros rgya mtsho rdo rje legs bshad rtsal //
NK091(ke)001:89: 'khor lo'i mgon po rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:90: de ltar bka' rgyud nor bu'i phreng ba la //
NK091(ke)001:91: sgo gsum gus pa'i phyag gis btud byas te //
NK091(ke)001:92: bka' rnams kun gyi dems gyur mdo chen po //
NK091(ke)001:93: rgyal kun dgongs pa'i mdzod 'di dgrol byed na //
NK091(ke)001:94: bla ma mchog dang rtsa gsum srung ma yis //
NK091(ke)001:95: sgrib med mkhyen pa'i spyan gyis rjes dgongs te //
NK091(ke)001:96: bdag rgyud dad pa'i me long dwangs pa la //
NK091(ke)001:97: ye shes thugs rje'i gzugs brnyan snang bar mdzod //
NK091(ke)001:98: ces mchod par brjod pa'i me tog gis mdun bsus te /
NK091(ke)001:99: rig 'dzin chen po dpal gyi seng ges rin po che'i rgyan las /
NK091(ke)001:100: rtsom rgyu shes rab snying rje ste //
NK091(ke)001:101: lung dang man ngag thob pas 'grub //
NK091(ke)001:102: gnas lugs mngon sum rtogs pa rab //
NK091(ke)001:103: yi dam mkha' 'gro bla ma las //
NK091(ke)001:104: lung bstan thob pa 'bring po yin //
NK091(ke)001:105: la shan bka' lung tshig la mkhas //
NK091(ke)001:106: bye brag phyed pa tha ma yin //
NK091(ke)001:107: zhes gsungs pa ltar mtshungs med bla ma rnams kyis
NK091(ke)001:108: bka' lung gser gyi cod pan spyi bor bcings shing
NK091(ke)001:110: spyir theg pa rim pa dgu'i bye brag ma 'dres par phyed cing /
NK091(ke)001:111: khyad par du skyabs rje thams cad mkhyen pa don
NK091(ke)001:112: gyi slad du mtshan nas smos te byams chen chos
NK091(ke)001:113: kyi rgya mtsho o rgyan bstan 'dzin chos kyi rgyal
NK091(ke)001:114: mtshan phyogs las rnam rgyal dpal bzang po'i bka' drin
NK091(ke)001:115: gyis 'dus pa mdo'i phyag dpe gsar du drangs pa
NK091(ke)001:116: rnams mjal ba'i skal bzang du gyur pas /
NK091(ke)001:117: slob dpon chen po d+harma b+ho d+his don bsdus las /
NK091(ke)001:118: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa kun 'dus las //
NK091(ke)001:119: mdo don chos kyi rnam grol sgo //
NK091(ke)001:120: de shes de 'jug bde sgrub phyir //
NK091(ke)001:121: mi 'gal tsam du bsdus te bshad //
NK091(ke)001:122: ces gsungs pa dang tshul mthun par legs bshad kun gyi bcud bsdus te /
NK091(ke)001:124: bka' don gtan tshigs rigs pa bzhis //
NK091(ke)001:126: zhes pa ltar rang gzhung la zlo zhing gzhan gyi
NK091(ke)001:127: grub mtha' shan 'byed pa'i bka' yi tshig la sgro
NK091(ke)001:128: skur med par snang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:130: gtan tshigs kyis rgyas shing rigs pas 'thad pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:131: la blo gros kyi 'jug pa cung zad thob pas
NK091(ke)001:132: / chos rje dam pa rin po ches /
NK091(ke)001:133: ston pa'i bstan pa rtogs sla'i phyir //
NK091(ke)001:134: tshig zur bcos phyir nges tshig 'grub //
NK091(ke)001:136: rang dang skal ba mnyam pa'i blo gros kyi rtsal
NK091(ke)001:137: zhan pa rnams la sman par 'dod pa'i lhag bsam
NK091(ke)001:138: dang ldan pa'i blos dman pa bdag kyang tshul 'di
NK091(ke)001:139: la gus pas zhugs pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:140: de la sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo /
NK091(ke)001:142: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse /
NK091(ke)001:143: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas /
NK091(ke)001:144: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po /
NK091(ke)001:146: man ngag thams cad kyi rtsa ba /
NK091(ke)001:147: don thams cad kyi mjug sdud /
NK091(ke)001:148: chos thams cad kyi me long /
NK091(ke)001:149: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs /
NK091(ke)001:150: 'bras bu thams cad kyi thug sa /
NK091(ke)001:151: rgyal ba thams cad kyi gshegs shul /
NK091(ke)001:152: ma 'ongs pa dang da ltar gyi rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam chen po /
NK091(ke)001:153: gsang ba bas kyang ches gsang ba /
NK091(ke)001:154: yang gsang rmad du byung ba'i bka' khyad par can /
NK091(ke)001:155: mdo rgyud chen po chos kyi me long 'di la don gsum gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:164: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta dz+ny+aa na gu h+ya ar+tha gar+b+ha b+y+au ha badz+ra tan+t+ra /
NK091(ke)001:165: sid+d+hii yo ga a ga ma sa m+aa dza sarba
NK091(ke)001:166: pir+y+aa s+au tra ma h+aa y+aa na a b+hi sa
NK091(ke)001:167: ma ya d+harma par+y+y+aa ya bi b+y+au ha n+aa ma
NK091(ke)001:168: s+au tram / bru sha'i skad du /
NK091(ke)001:176: mang kyang ku 'i dang rod ti /
NK091(ke)001:177: de gnyis bod skad du bsgyur na /
NK091(ke)001:178: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs /
NK091(ke)001:184: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:185: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba'i mdo /
NK091(ke)001:187: de ltar mtshan bstan pa 'di ni seng ge'i mchongs pa lta bu'i bshad pa'i dbang du /
NK091(ke)001:188: rnal 'byor bya ba med pa'i go lugs dang po bstan pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:191: don gyi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:195: bod kyi mtshan rnams shan sbyar te bstan pas go ba'i tshul ni ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:197: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta dang /
NK091(ke)001:201: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs /
NK091(ke)001:204: pi pu pi til ni gsang ba'i ye shes /
NK091(ke)001:211: sid+d+hi yo ga a g+aa ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:214: sa m+aa dza sarba bid+y+aa s+au tra dang /
NK091(ke)001:217: ma h+aa y+aa na a b+hi sa ma ya dang /
NK091(ke)001:218: pang ri zhe hal pi ni /
NK091(ke)001:219: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:220: d+harma par+y+y+aa ya bi byu ha n+aa ma s+au tram dang /
NK091(ke)001:221: mang kyang ku 'i dang rod ti ni /
NK091(ke)001:222: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba'i mdo /
NK091(ke)001:224: legs sbyar dang bstun na thad log tu bsgyur zhing /
NK091(ke)001:225: bru sha dang mthun par bsgyur ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:227: bru sha dang bod skad du bsgyur tshul bshad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:228: skabs su tshig gcig gis thad log tu'ang 'gyur te
NK091(ke)001:236: zhes pa la bru sha'i skad du /
NK091(ke)001:245: zhes shan sbyar ba thad log tu 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:246: 'dug sa bsnol dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:247: zhes gsungs pa ji ltar yin snyam na /
NK091(ke)001:248: de ni yig rnying phal mo che'i dbu na bzhugs pa ltar te /
NK091(ke)001:251: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta /
NK091(ke)001:255: b+h+yi d+ha t+ya tha b+h+yi d+ha su /
NK091(ke)001:261: bru sha gong dang mthun pas /
NK091(ke)001:263: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs /
NK091(ke)001:269: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:270: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba'i mdo /
NK091(ke)001:276: gzhan go rim bzhin yin kyang tshig gcig gis thad log tu gyur pa'i phyir de ltar gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:277: de la mtshan gyi skad gsum ni /
NK091(ke)001:278: pan+di ta d+harma b+ho d+hi dang /
NK091(ke)001:279: lo ts+aa ba che btsan skyes kyis rgya gar las bru sha'i skad du bsgyur zhing /
NK091(ke)001:280: slar pan+di ta d+aa na rak+shi ta dang che btsan skyes kyis bod skad du bsgyur bas na /
NK091(ke)001:281: tshul de'i lo rgyus smos pas yid ches par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:282: rang skad kyis 'jal bar bya ba'i phyir rim par bsgyur ba ltar gsum ka smos pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:283: des na mtshan gsum klad du byung ba'i dgos pa yang /
NK091(ke)001:285: khungs btsun pa'i phyir the tshom mi za bar yid ches par bya ba'i ched dang /
NK091(ke)001:287: lo ts+aa ba che btsan skyes kyis /
NK091(ke)001:288: rgya gar du byon nas gsang sngags mdo rgyud kyi don la sbyangs nas /
NK091(ke)001:289: bod yul du bsgyur bar bzhed pa na dus der
NK091(ke)001:290: rgyal po glang dar ma 'chal ba'i ring la dam
NK091(ke)001:291: pa'i chos bsnubs nas bsgyur dbang ma byung bas bru
NK091(ke)001:293: bru sha'i yul khrom du bod skad du bsgyur bas
NK091(ke)001:294: yul mi la drin la lan gyis blan pa'i ched
NK091(ke)001:295: du smos la / bod skad ni /
NK091(ke)001:296: brda 'jal bar bya ba'i phyir smos pas skad gsum 'byung ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:297: de la mtshan gyi 'bru nyid bod skad ltar mnan te /
NK091(ke)001:298: gnyis pa don bshad pas go ba'i tshul ni /
NK091(ke)001:299: dper na rta dkyus kyi sa bstan pa dang 'dra bar /
NK091(ke)001:300: tshig nyung ngu klad du smos pas dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad go bar ston te /
NK091(ke)001:301: de yang mtshan gyi tshig bdun gyi dngos don ni /
NK091(ke)001:302: ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid kyi rnam grangs
NK091(ke)001:303: yin pa'i phyir 'di'i don dkyil 'khor gsum po +amo
NK091(ke)001:304: h'u m+aum gyi don 'jal bas ril gyi don 'jal
NK091(ke)001:305: bar 'gyur ro // de la rnam grangs bdun ni /
NK091(ke)001:306: gzhi ji bzhin pa nyid du rtogs pa mthar son
NK091(ke)001:307: nas gdul bya la sku tha dad par snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:308: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:309: sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba de kho na
NK091(ke)001:310: nyid ji bzhin pa brtags na med la bsam na
NK091(ke)001:311: snang yang mtshan nyid yongs su ldan par ma zin
NK091(ke)001:312: pas lam pa'i blos reg par dka' ba'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:313: chen po las g.yo ba med pa 'di la 'dus
NK091(ke)001:314: shing lhun gyis rdzogs pas rgyal ba ril dgongs pa
NK091(ke)001:316: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs gsang ba'i ye shes zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:317: gnas lugs don gyi rtsa ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:318: dmigs pa'i spyod yul dang bral yang shes par bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:319: sgrub par bya ba ji snyed pa'i bdag nyid lta
NK091(ke)001:320: ba dang 'bras bu thams cad du rang shar zhing
NK091(ke)001:321: 'byung bas don gyi snying po zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:322: skad cig ma'i rgyun dang skye ba'i yul kun bral
NK091(ke)001:323: ba'i gnyis su med pa'i ye shes mi phyed pa
NK091(ke)001:324: chen pos sgrib pa'i phung po ji snyed pa ka
NK091(ke)001:325: nas dag par byed cing ji lta ngo bo la
NK091(ke)001:326: ji snyed pa'i ye shes thams cad lhun rdzogs su
NK091(ke)001:327: gsol zhing 'du 'bral med pas rdo rje bkod pa'i
NK091(ke)001:328: rgyud ces bya'o // gang don chen po la rnal
NK091(ke)001:329: du 'byor nas ji lta ba'i nges pa zab mo
NK091(ke)001:330: rnyed cing grub pa'i gdengs chen po thob pa na
NK091(ke)001:331: skyes bu dam par lung ston pa la sogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:332: phyir rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:333: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i theg mchog dam pa ni bka'
NK091(ke)001:334: kun gyi phyi mo dang 'phags pa thams cad kyi
NK091(ke)001:335: yul yin pas rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa kun gyi
NK091(ke)001:336: don 'dus shing / log pa'i lam yan chad ma
NK091(ke)001:337: bkol bar so so'i shan ma 'dres par rig kyang
NK091(ke)001:338: mdo don gyi che ba 'di nyid du gcig pas
NK091(ke)001:339: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:340: gang yang spangs pa dang dor ba med par rang gsal du rdzogs pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK091(ke)001:341: snang mi snang gi mtha' las grol ba'i gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:342: ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid de dngos theg pa chen
NK091(ke)001:344: de lta bu'i zab don de nyid dam pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:345: kyis rang rig pa'i mngon sum du yul las 'das
NK091(ke)001:346: par rtogs te ma mthong ba'i mthong ba chen por
NK091(ke)001:347: yang dag par 'char ba'i thabs dang don gnyis ka
NK091(ke)001:348: 'di nyid yin pas theg pa chen po mngon par
NK091(ke)001:350: mdo rgyud kyi rim pa kun dang /
NK091(ke)001:351: cha mthun gyi log lta la sogs pa kun ma
NK091(ke)001:352: 'dres par gsal te ngo bo ji bzhin pa la
NK091(ke)001:353: yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir rnam grangs kyi chos ji
NK091(ke)001:354: snyed pa'i rjod byed kyi yi ge dang bcas pa
NK091(ke)001:355: thams cad 'di nyid las 'phros te kun tu 'god
NK091(ke)001:356: pas na mdo'i chings chen po yin pas chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:357: rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba'i mdo
NK091(ke)001:358: / zhes pa'i mtshan du bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:359: de'i tshul rgyas par bkrol na bshad lugs te /
NK091(ke)001:360: rgyud lung man ngag gsum dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:361: che ba bdun dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:362: byung tshul bcu gnyis dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:363: le'u bdun cu rtsa lnga dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:364: mtshon pa dpe dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:365: snod bzhi la bstan pa bzhi ru gsungs pa dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:366: mtshan gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:368: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs /
NK091(ke)001:370: don gyi snying po rnams ni man ngag gi mtshan no //
NK091(ke)001:372: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo ni lung gi mtshan no //
NK091(ke)001:374: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:375: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa rnams rgyud kyi mtshan du bstan to //
NK091(ke)001:376: gnyis pa bstan pa gzhan las 'phags pa'i che ba
NK091(ke)001:377: bdun yang de kho na nyid kyi khyad par te
NK091(ke)001:378: / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs /
NK091(ke)001:379: gsang ba'i ye shes ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK091(ke)001:380: dgongs pa'i zhe phugs yin cing der skal dman gyi
NK091(ke)001:381: rim gyis bgrod la 'dir cig char du ston pas
NK091(ke)001:382: theg pa'i yang rtse yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:383: don gyi snying po ni de kho na nyid yin la /
NK091(ke)001:384: de nyid ji lta ba bzhin du ston pas man ngag gi rtsa ba yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:385: rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud ni rig pa'i bye brag
NK091(ke)001:386: thams cad kyi bdag nyid du gyur pas rgyud thams
NK091(ke)001:387: cad kyi rgyal po yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:389: lung don thams cad 'dis gtan la 'bebs pas na lung gi spyi 'a grel yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:391: bstan pa ril gyi don 'di la 'dus shing 'dis gcod pas /
NK091(ke)001:392: don gyi mjug sdud yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:393: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:394: gsang sngags ji bzhin pa'i don nyid rgyud 'dis ji lta bar mthong bar byed pas /
NK091(ke)001:395: chos kyi me long yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:396: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:397: bka' rgyud thams cad lhun gyis grub pa 'di las
NK091(ke)001:398: snang ba'i phyir bstan pa'i 'byung gnas yin pa'i che
NK091(ke)001:400: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs gsang ba'i ye shes /
NK091(ke)001:401: zhes pa rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:402: byin gyis rlabs kyi byung tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:404: zhes pa snying po byang chub tu nges pa'i byung tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:406: ces pa sgron ma yongs su bkod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:407: dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba'i byung tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:409: zhes pa gang gis nges pa rnyed pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:410: gdul bya'i skabs la bab pa'i byung tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:412: zhes pa brgyud pa thabs kyi grags pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:413: las rgyun yongs su gcod pa'i byung tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:414: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:415: zhes pa gang gi ched du mdzad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:416: lung chen nges par bstan pa'i byung tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:417: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa /
NK091(ke)001:418: zhes pa dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba'i byung tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:420: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs zhes par /
NK091(ke)001:421: le'u dang po dang bdun pa 'dus so //
NK091(ke)001:422: gsang ba'i ye shes zhes par /
NK091(ke)001:423: le'u gnyis pa nas drug pa'i bar dang brgyad pa dang dgu pa 'dus /
NK091(ke)001:424: don gyi snying po zhes par /
NK091(ke)001:426: rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud ces par /
NK091(ke)001:427: le'u bcu drug pa nas bcu dgu'i bar dang /
NK091(ke)001:428: so gnyis pa nas zhe gnyis pa'i bar 'dus /
NK091(ke)001:429: rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung zhes par /
NK091(ke)001:430: bcu pa nas bcu bzhi pa'i bar dang /
NK091(ke)001:431: nyi shu pa nas so gcig pa'i bar 'dus /
NK091(ke)001:432: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes par /
NK091(ke)001:433: re drug pa nas don lnga pa yan chad 'dus /
NK091(ke)001:434: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa zhes par /
NK091(ke)001:435: zhe bzhi pa dang zhe gsum pa 'dus /
NK091(ke)001:436: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes par /
NK091(ke)001:437: zhe lnga pa nas drug cu re lnga pa yan chad 'dus so //
NK091(ke)001:439: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs ni ngos
NK091(ke)001:440: bzung med cing bsam gyis mi khyab pas dper na
NK091(ke)001:442: gsang ba'i ye shes ni rang la yod kyang rtogs
NK091(ke)001:443: par dka' bas dbul po'i khyim gyi gter lta bu
NK091(ke)001:444: / don gyi snying po ni shes sgrub kyi bcud
NK091(ke)001:445: thams cad 'dus pas gzi ldan nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK091(ke)001:446: / lta bu / rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud ni
NK091(ke)001:447: rim pa dgu'i don thams cad mdzes par bkod pas
NK091(ke)001:448: gser mig la g.yus spras pa lta bu /
NK091(ke)001:449: rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung ni de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:450: ma bslad par ji bzhin du bstan te dngos grub
NK091(ke)001:451: thob pa la mnga' dbang bsgyur bas 'khor sgyur gyi
NK091(ke)001:452: bka' lung thob pa'i blon po lta bu /
NK091(ke)001:453: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo ni byung tshul bcu gnyis
NK091(ke)001:454: kyi don thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:455: par ston pas rgya mtsho la gza' skar shar ba
NK091(ke)001:456: lta bu / theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs
NK091(ke)001:457: pa ni theg pa mchog gi don gsal zhing mthas
NK091(ke)001:458: ma sgrib par mthong bas 'phrul gyi me long la
NK091(ke)001:459: gzugs brnyan gsal ba lta bu /
NK091(ke)001:460: 'di la seng ge'i dpe bkod pa ltar na /
NK091(ke)001:461: theg chen gsang sngags kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin par
NK091(ke)001:462: rtogs nas gzhan zil gyis gnon pas rtsal gyi rgyal
NK091(ke)001:463: po seng ge lta bu zhes sbyar /
NK091(ke)001:464: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa ni gsang
NK091(ke)001:465: sgo mtshon pa'i thabs kyi rnam pa thams cad ma
NK091(ke)001:466: 'dres par gsal bas pad+ma bkram pa lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:468: dang po zhen chags can la 'dod pa rang rkyen gyi tshig tu bshad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:469: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:470: yab yum gyi rtsa sa ya phrag bcu gsum gyi
NK091(ke)001:471: bcud yab yum gnyis kyi thig le'i bde ba rang
NK091(ke)001:472: bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes so //
NK091(ke)001:473: gsang ba'i ye shes zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:474: byis pa rnam gnyis dang ma ning la sogs pa'i spyod yul du ma gyur pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:475: don gyi snying po zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:476: yab yum gyi thig le rdo rje dang pad+ma'i rtser
NK091(ke)001:477: 'dus pa la bde ba thams cad kyi bcud 'dus
NK091(ke)001:478: pa'o // rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud ces pa /
NK091(ke)001:479: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes rdo rje lta bu
NK091(ke)001:480: la ye shes thams cad tshang 'brel du gnas pa'o
NK091(ke)001:481: // rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:482: chags pa thabs kyis zin pas 'bras bu grub par byed pa ste gsang ba'i sku'i gsung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:483: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:484: yab yum gyi thig le la bde ba kun 'dus pas don rig par byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:485: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:486: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes thabs kyis
NK091(ke)001:487: zin pas dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i bde bar
NK091(ke)001:488: gsal ba'o // chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba'i mdo zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:489: chags pa thabs kyis ma zin na 'khor ba'i chos thams cad 'byung la /
NK091(ke)001:490: thabs kyis zin na mya ngan las 'das pa'i lam dang 'bras bu'i chos thams cad 'byung ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:491: gnyis pa log sred can la bkri drang brgyud pa'i tshig tu bshad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:492: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:493: rtag par lta ba dang chad par lta ba gnyis rgyal ba'i thugs yin byas pas /
NK091(ke)001:494: tshig des brgyud nas ngo bo nyid mi 'gyur ba dang rang bzhin med pa rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:495: gsang ba'i ye shes zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:496: rtag chad kyi lta ba de kun gyi spyod yul ma yin pa'o byas pas /
NK091(ke)001:497: tshig des brgyud nas rang byung ye shes kun gyi spyod yul ma yin pa rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:498: don gyi snying po zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:499: lta ba rtag chad dang spyod pa phyin ci log
NK091(ke)001:500: la shes bya dang bsgrub bya thams cad kyi bcud
NK091(ke)001:501: 'dus byas pas / tshig des brgyud nas rang byung
NK091(ke)001:502: ye shes la shes sgrub kyi bcud 'dus pa rtogs
NK091(ke)001:503: 'dus byas pas / par byed pa'o // rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud ces pa /
NK091(ke)001:504: log par lta ba la ye shes thams cad tshang 'brel du gnas so byas pas /
NK091(ke)001:505: tshig des brgyud nas rang byung ye shes la ye
NK091(ke)001:506: shes thams cad tshang 'brel du gnas pa rtogs par
NK091(ke)001:507: byed pa'o // rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:508: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'bras bu
NK091(ke)001:509: grub pa ni lung ma nor ba yin byas pas
NK091(ke)001:510: / tshig des brgyud nas spyod yul dang bral ba'i
NK091(ke)001:511: dgongs pas 'bras bu grub par byed pa rtogs par
NK091(ke)001:512: / byed pa'o // kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:513: rtag chad gnyis su log lta thams cad 'dus pa des don rig par byed do byas pas /
NK091(ke)001:514: tshig des brgyud nas rang byung ye shes la chos thams cad 'dus pas /
NK091(ke)001:515: thams cad mkhyen pa'i lta ba rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:516: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:517: rtag par lta ba rtogs na mtho ris su 'degs par byed byas pas /
NK091(ke)001:518: tshig des brgyud nas rang byung ye shes gnyen po
NK091(ke)001:519: med par rtogs nas grol zhing thar pa rtogs par
NK091(ke)001:520: byed pa'o // chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:521: rtag chad gnyis las log pa'i lta ba sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa bkod par bstan pas /
NK091(ke)001:522: tshig des brgyud nas rang byung ye shes de kho
NK091(ke)001:523: na nyid la chos thams cad ma 'dres la yongs
NK091(ke)001:524: su rdzogs pa shes par byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:525: gsum pa rigs rgyud can ldem dgongs sbyor ba'i tshig tu bshad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:526: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:527: dam tshig ting 'dzin shes rab dang //
NK091(ke)001:528: byang chub sems dang snying rje lnga //
NK091(ke)001:529: bar mtshams med par rgyun mi gcad //
NK091(ke)001:530: 'di ni mtshams med dam tshig yin //
NK091(ke)001:531: zhes yang dag pa'i mtshams med lnga la dgongs nas /
NK091(ke)001:532: mtshams med pa lnga la spyod pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs yin zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:533: gsang ba'i ye shes zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:534: yang dag pa'i mtshams med lnga rtogs pa'am spyad dka'
NK091(ke)001:535: ba la dgongs nas log pa'i mtshams med lnga po
NK091(ke)001:536: de kun kyi spyod yul ma yin par ston pa'o
NK091(ke)001:537: // don gyi snying po zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:538: yang dag pa'i lta spyod la shes sgrub kyi bcud
NK091(ke)001:539: 'dus pa la dgongs nas mtshams med pa lnga dang
NK091(ke)001:540: sbyor sgrol rang ka ma la thams cad kyi bcud
NK091(ke)001:542: rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud ces pa /
NK091(ke)001:543: rang byung gi ye shes la ye shes thams cad tshang 'brel du gnas pa la dgongs nas /
NK091(ke)001:544: sems can gyi sems la rnam rtog thams cad tshang 'brel du gnas par ston pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:545: rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:546: sems kyi rang bzhin mi g.yo ba la dgongs nas /
NK091(ke)001:547: bying rgod kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis 'bras bu 'grub ces ston pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:548: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:549: chos thams cad byang chub kyi sems su gcig pa la dgongs nas /
NK091(ke)001:550: rtog bcas kyi sems la spros pa'i chos thams cad 'dus par ston pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:551: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:552: gsang sngags theg pa chen pos /
NK091(ke)001:553: chos thams cad sems nyid du rtogs pa la dgongs nas /
NK091(ke)001:554: mtshams med pa lnga la sogs pa log pa'i spyod pa nyid theg pa chen por ston pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:555: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:556: chos thams cad sems nyid la ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa la dgongs nas /
NK091(ke)001:557: rgyud 'di la mtshams med lnga dang mi dge bcu la sogs pa thams cad tshang bar ston pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:558: bzhi pa blo gros can la don dam nges pa'i tshig tu bshad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:559: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:560: sems can thams cad kyi sems 'khrul pa 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:561: dngos po la ma bcos ma bslad par dbyer med
NK091(ke)001:562: pa ni rgyal ba'i thugs te /
NK091(ke)001:564: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa 'di //
NK091(ke)001:565: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du gsal //
NK091(ke)001:566: ci phyir rdo rje gsang sngags dang //
NK091(ke)001:567: sangs rgyas sems can tha mi dad //
NK091(ke)001:569: gsang ba'i ye shes zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:570: sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes rtogs par dka' ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:571: dape'am tshad ma'am gtan tshigs sam //
NK091(ke)001:572: rjes su dpag pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK091(ke)001:573: rtogs par nus pa ma yin te //
NK091(ke)001:576: don gyi snying po zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:577: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer med pa'i don la shes
NK091(ke)001:578: bya dang bsgrub bya thams cad kyi bcud 'dus par
NK091(ke)001:580: thams cad de nyid der gcig pas //
NK091(ke)001:581: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK091(ke)001:582: skye 'gag med pa'i snying po yin //
NK091(ke)001:583: bya ba med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK091(ke)001:584: ye nas grub zin lhun gyis grub //
NK091(ke)001:586: rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud ces pa /
NK091(ke)001:587: ye shes thams cad kyi byed las dang ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:588: ni rdo rje lta bu ste de la rgyud kyi
NK091(ke)001:589: yan lag drug tshang bar nges te /
NK091(ke)001:590: bcas gzhi gtam rgyud las rgyud dang //
NK091(ke)001:591: rtog chen yan lag 'brel bcas rgyud //
NK091(ke)001:593: rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:594: rang bzhin gyi rnal 'byor ye nas grub pa'am /
NK091(ke)001:595: 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor grub par byed pa'i lung 'di nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:597: thig le gcig gis kun la khyab //
NK091(ke)001:598: thams cad lung chen nges par bstan //
NK091(ke)001:600: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:601: chos thams cad sems nyid du 'dus la nges don rig par byed pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:603: kun gyi rtsa ba 'di shes na //
NK091(ke)001:604: kun kyang ma bcos ji bzhin pa //
NK091(ke)001:605: de bzhin nyid de kun gyi mdo //
NK091(ke)001:607: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:608: rgyud 'dis gdul bya kun 'dren cing chos thams cad gsal bar ston pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:610: theg pa chen por brjod pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:611: ji snyed theg pa'i rnam grangs kun //
NK091(ke)001:612: de nyid chen po nyid mthong gsal //
NK091(ke)001:614: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa'i mdo zhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:615: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rig pa byang chub
NK091(ke)001:616: sems su ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa rgyud 'di
NK091(ke)001:619: bka' yi rab rgyud dam pa nyid //
NK091(ke)001:620: sde mdzod dam pa'i bka' lung rnams //
NK091(ke)001:624: gtan tshigs kyis rgyas thebs shing lung las snang bar bshad pa le'u re drug pa las /
NK091(ke)001:625: lang ka'i bdag po de la rnam grangs brgyad gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:626: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:627: don gyi snying po zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:628: rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyud ces kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:629: rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:630: kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:631: theg pa chen po mngon par rtogs pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:632: chos kyi rnam grangs rnam par bkod pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:633: theg pa chen po'i byung tshul bstan pa'i mdo zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:635: lang+ka'i bdag po gang la dgongs pa de nyid las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:636: gang gi spyod yul ma yin zhing med las thams cad 'byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:637: gang gi ye shes yongs su bkod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:638: 'di ltar gang nges pa rnal 'byor du lung ston pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:640: dam pa rnams kyi mngon par chud pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:641: gang la ma 'das par bkod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:642: gnas skabs bcu gnyis su nges par byung zhing 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:644: de ltar gtan tshigs dang sbrags mar brjod pas yid ches par 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:646: gzhi ji bzhin pa nyid du rtogs pa mthar son
NK091(ke)001:647: pas gdul bya la sku tha dad par snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:648: rgyal ba ril gyi dgongs pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:649: sems kyi dkyil 'khor rang gi rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba /
NK091(ke)001:650: de kho na nyid ji bzhin pa brtags na med
NK091(ke)001:651: la bsam na snang yang mtshan nyid yongs su ldan
NK091(ke)001:652: par ma zin pas lam pa'i bsam pas reg par
NK091(ke)001:653: dka' ba'i ye shes chen po las dus gsum du
NK091(ke)001:654: g.yo ba med pa 'di nyid yin la /
NK091(ke)001:655: de la dgongs pa ji snyed pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:656: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag thams cad lhun
NK091(ke)001:657: gyis rdzogs pas dgongs pa 'dus pa zhes kyang brjod
NK091(ke)001:658: de / rgyal ba ril dgongs pa de las mi 'da' ba'i phyir mtshan dang po'i don to //
NK091(ke)001:661: bsgrub par bya ba ji snyed pa'i bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:662: dmigs pa'i spyod yul dang bral bzhin du lta ba
NK091(ke)001:663: dang 'bras bu thams cad du rang shar zhing rang
NK091(ke)001:664: 'byung bas don gyi snying po'am rtsa bar gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:665: ni mtshan gnyis pa'i don to //
NK091(ke)001:666: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes chen po ni skad
NK091(ke)001:667: cig ma'i rgyun du skye ba'i yul thams cad dang
NK091(ke)001:668: bral bas sgrib pa'i phung po ji snyed pa ka
NK091(ke)001:669: nas dag par byed pa'i ji lta ba'i ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:670: la / ji snyed pa'i ye shes thams cad lhun
NK091(ke)001:671: gyis rdzogs pas rdo rje bkod pa'ang yin pas mtshan
NK091(ke)001:673: gang don chen po la rnal du 'byor nas gnas
NK091(ke)001:674: shing goms par byed pa rnams kyis mi ji lta
NK091(ke)001:675: ba'i don zab mo rnyed cing grub pa'i gdeng chen
NK091(ke)001:676: po thob pa na skyes bu dam par lung ston
NK091(ke)001:677: par byed de / rgyal tshab lnga lung bstan pa la sogs pa'i phyir mtshan bzhi pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:678: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i theg pa chen po ni bka'
NK091(ke)001:679: kun gyi phyi mo nyid yin pas 'phags pa ril
NK091(ke)001:680: gyi yum yin pa'i phyir rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa
NK091(ke)001:681: kun gyi don thams cad 'dus shing /
NK091(ke)001:682: log pa'i lam yan chad ma bkol bar so so'i
NK091(ke)001:683: shan ma 'dres par gsal zhing rig pa'i phyir mdo
NK091(ke)001:684: don gyi che ba 'dir gcig pas mtshan lnga pa
NK091(ke)001:685: 'grub bo // gang yang spangs pa dang dor ba med pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK091(ke)001:686: snang ba dang mi snang ba'i mtha' gnyis las grol
NK091(ke)001:687: te gsang sngags ji bzhin pa nyid de dngos theg
NK091(ke)001:688: pa chen po'o // de lta bu'i gsang ba zab
NK091(ke)001:689: mo'i don de nyid dam pa rnams kyis rang rig
NK091(ke)001:690: pa'i mngon sum du yul las 'das par rtogs te
NK091(ke)001:691: pa chen po'o // / mthong ba med pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:692: gyis mthong bar byed pa'i thabs dang don gnyis ka
NK091(ke)001:693: 'di nyid yin pas mtshan drug pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:695: cha mthun gyi log lta la sogs pa ril ma
NK091(ke)001:696: 'dres par gsal te ngo bo ji bzhin pa la
NK091(ke)001:697: rdzogs pa'i phyir chos kyi rnam grangs rjod byed kyi
NK091(ke)001:698: yi ge dang bcas pa rnam par bkod pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:699: ni mtshan bdun pa'i don to //
NK091(ke)001:700: de dag ni mtshan gyi rnam grangs bdun te dbu'i don no //
NK091(ke)001:701: brgyad kyi dbang du byas na /
NK091(ke)001:702: gnas skabs bcu gnyis su'ang thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK091(ke)001:703: don 'di nyid snang bas bya ba rdzogs par byed
NK091(ke)001:704: pa'i phyir byung tshul bstan pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:705: de ni byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi tshul ston pa'i
NK091(ke)001:706: le'u bdun cu rtsa lngas ji ltar bstan kyang rim
NK091(ke)001:707: gyis pa dang cig char ba gnyis kyis go zhing
NK091(ke)001:708: 'jug pas sgrub par bya rgyu ni /
NK091(ke)001:709: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid las gzhan mi snang la /
NK091(ke)001:710: des na mtshan gyi khyad par brgyad bdun du bsdus
NK091(ke)001:711: nas bstan pa de'i don tshul bzhin du rig pas
NK091(ke)001:712: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi don ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su
NK091(ke)001:714: 'o na spyir rgyud 'di la mtshan bzhir byung ba zlos sam snyam na mi zlos te /
NK091(ke)001:715: le'u dang po dang re drug pa'i mtshan ni /
NK091(ke)001:716: lung bstan brgyud pa'i rgyud kyi mtshan yin la /
NK091(ke)001:717: de yang le'u dang po'i mtshan ni lo ts+aa bas klad du bkod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:719: gsang bdag nyid kyis ma la yar gsungs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:721: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi thugs chen po //
NK091(ke)001:722: ye shes snying po don gyi mchog dang ldan //
NK091(ke)001:723: rnal 'byor theg chen rdo rje kun 'dus lung //
NK091(ke)001:724: 'dus pa'i tshogs la rgya cher bshad du gsol //
NK091(ke)001:733: rdo rje rnam par bsgyings pa'i gzhung rnams ni byin rlabs 'byung ba'i rgyud kyi mtshan te /
NK091(ke)001:734: gong ma ni zhus tshig dang /
NK091(ke)001:735: 'og ma ni lan gyi tshig ste ston pas gsung bar zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:737: zhes pa ni don gyi bam po dang tshig gi
NK091(ke)001:738: bam po gnyis las 'dir tshig gtso bor byas nas
NK091(ke)001:739: shwa lo ka gsum brgya ni bam po gcig ste
NK091(ke)001:740: / de nyid kyi grangs kyi thog mar zug par bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:742: bcom ldan 'das dpal sgrol byed thugs rje'i rgyal po
NK091(ke)001:743: shin tu rnam par grol ba nyid la phyag 'tshal
NK091(ke)001:745: byin rlabs 'byung ba'i rgyud ltar na /
NK091(ke)001:746: sdud pa po phyag na rdo rjes ston pa rigs
NK091(ke)001:747: kyi bdag po nyid la mchod par brjod pa ste
NK091(ke)001:748: / rnal 'byor lnga'i mthar son pa'i ye shes chen po ni /
NK091(ke)001:749: bya ba thams cad byas zin te /
NK091(ke)001:750: rang byung ye shes kyi ngo bo la chos thams
NK091(ke)001:751: cad rang snang du rdzogs pa'i dngos gzhir bzhugs te
NK091(ke)001:752: / spyod yul ka nas dag pas sdug bsngal gyi sa bon med pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK091(ke)001:753: de'i phyir lnga phung gi ngo bo mi snang bas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK091(ke)001:754: de la 'chi 'pho ba'i chos kyi 'pho 'gyur bral bas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK091(ke)001:755: de lta bu'i bdag nyid la bar chad ril ma
NK091(ke)001:756: dmigs pas lha yi bu'i bdud bcom pas bcom zhes
NK091(ke)001:757: bya zhing / legs pa'i yon tan drug dang ldana pa'i bdag nyid chen por bzhugs kyang /
NK091(ke)001:758: mtha' thams cad las 'das shing grol bas dngos gzhi
NK091(ke)001:759: bstan dka' ba ni chos kyi sku chen po nyid
NK091(ke)001:760: do // de ltar chos kyi skur bzhugs pa ni
NK091(ke)001:761: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi rang bzhin ji lta bar mngon
NK091(ke)001:762: du gyur pas rtogs pa bdag gi dpal yin la
NK091(ke)001:763: do // / de'i ngang las mi g.yo bar gdul
NK091(ke)001:764: bya gsum mdzad pa'i theg pa gsum gyi chu bo
NK091(ke)001:765: bzhi las mthar son par byed pas sgrol byed chen
NK091(ke)001:766: por gyur pa ni thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal te
NK091(ke)001:767: sprul pa'i sku'i bdag nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:768: de nyid kyi dgongs pa de bzhin nyid dus gsum du 'byung 'jug bral te /
NK091(ke)001:769: lhan ne lham me lhang nge bar rnal ma'i don
NK091(ke)001:770: bzhin du mdzad pa'i thugs rje'i byin rlabs rgyun mi
NK091(ke)001:771: 'chad pa'i ngo bor mnga' thang yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:772: sku'i rgyal po chen por bzhugs pa ni longs spyod
NK091(ke)001:774: de lta bu'i ngo bo shin tu rnam par grol
NK091(ke)001:775: ba'i bdag nyid ni ye nas 'ching ba thams cad
NK091(ke)001:776: dang bral zhing thabs dam pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pas
NK091(ke)001:778: ngo bo nyid dang gsang ba'i sku ste /
NK091(ke)001:779: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs pa'i ngo bo'i bdag nyid
NK091(ke)001:780: ni kun tu bzang po sangs rgyas he ru ka
NK091(ke)001:782: thun mong ma yin pa'i phyag gi yul lo //
NK091(ke)001:783: de nyid skyes bu nyid dang gcig dang du ma
NK091(ke)001:784: bral ba'i tshul du rig pa ni mchod cing 'dud
NK091(ke)001:785: pa'i mchog yin pas dman pas lus ngag gis mos
NK091(ke)001:786: pa lta bu ni min no //
NK091(ke)001:787: gzhan du lung bstan brgyud pa ltar na /
NK091(ke)001:788: sdud pa po blo gros thabs ldan gyis 'chad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:789: skyes bu ston pa gsang ba'i bdag po la sgo
NK091(ke)001:790: gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo zhes btud de mchod
NK091(ke)001:791: par mdzad pa'o // gnyis pa gzhung gi don la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:801: bye brag gi mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:805: rnam par bgro ba 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:806: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:807: byin rlabs 'byung ba'i dbang du na /
NK091(ke)001:808: 'di skad ces nye bar mtshon pa ni bstan pa ste rgyud 'di nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:809: gsal bar bgro ba ni ston pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:810: zhing khams dang gnas tha dad na ston pa rnams kyis bgro bar byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:811: bdag gis thos pa ni byung khungs gleng gzhi'i sdud
NK091(ke)001:812: pa phyag na rdo rje nyid kyis gsan pa ste
NK091(ke)001:813: / sku tha dad pa rigs lnga dang /
NK091(ke)001:814: gcig nyid kun tu bzang po dang /
NK091(ke)001:815: phyogs bcu'i bud+d+ha la'ang thos la /
NK091(ke)001:816: sku bzhi la'ang so sor thos pas rnam pa bzhi'i tshul du thos te /
NK091(ke)001:818: dus ni byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi tshe dang sku
NK091(ke)001:819: bzhis bstan pa'i dus bzhi ste tshe skabs kyi dus
NK091(ke)001:820: der thos pa'o zhes bgros pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:821: lung bstan brgyud pa'i dbang du na /
NK091(ke)001:822: ston pa phyag na rdo rjes zhing tha dad pa
NK091(ke)001:823: na rang gi ston pa la nyan nas nye 'khor
NK091(ke)001:824: la rgyud 'di skad ces bgro ba lang ka mgrin
NK091(ke)001:825: bcu bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na zhes sh+aakya
NK091(ke)001:826: thub pa 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi
NK091(ke)001:827: tshe mi yul 'dir thos te yi ger bris nas
NK091(ke)001:829: 'di la tha snyad drug ste 'di skad thos kyi
NK091(ke)001:830: ma phri ma bsnan no byas pas sgro skur gyi
NK091(ke)001:832: 'di skad bgro ba bdag gis thos kyi gzhan las
NK091(ke)001:833: ma brgyud do byas pas sdud pa po tshad ma'i
NK091(ke)001:834: zhal du bstan / bdag gis 'di skad thos /
NK091(ke)001:835: gzhan gyis gzhan skad thos byas pas bka' rgya ma chad par bstan /
NK091(ke)001:836: dus gcig kho nar thos kyi yang yang bldab kyin ma yin byas pas bka' 'byung dkon par bstan /
NK091(ke)001:838: gzhan du gzhan skad thos byas pas sdud pa po thos rgya che bar bstan /
NK091(ke)001:839: dus gcig tu 'di skad kyang thos la /
NK091(ke)001:840: gzhan du gzhan skad kyang thos byas pas sdud pa po blo rno bar bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:841: gleng gzhi rnam gnyis kyi ngo bo thun mong du bstan pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:842: de nas dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa mang
NK091(ke)001:843: po bsdus pa'i sgra thams cad kyi bdag nyid ni
NK091(ke)001:844: bcom ldan 'das rigs kyi gtso bo drug pa ste
NK091(ke)001:845: / mtshan gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:848: lung bstan brgyud pa'i dbang du de bzhin gshegs pa
NK091(ke)001:849: thams cad kyi bcom ldan 'das ni dngos gsang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:850: bdag po phyag na rdo rje nyid de dbang thob
NK091(ke)001:851: pas rgya gram 'khor lo lag na bsnams pas mtshan
NK091(ke)001:853: don ston pa las ji skad thos pa ltar du
NK091(ke)001:854: dman pa'i lus can la rnam par bgros te gsal
NK091(ke)001:855: bar ston pa'i 'chad pa'i skyes bu 'jigs shing zhum
NK091(ke)001:856: pa med par thams cad zil gyis gnon pas smra
NK091(ke)001:857: ba'i seng ge barla bkyal gyi spobs pa can de
NK091(ke)001:858: ston pa'i thugs kyi byin rlabs thob pas 'khor gyi
NK091(ke)001:859: nang du 'gying bgas kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang
NK091(ke)001:860: / seng ge rol pa'i ga zha mdzad pa'i phyir seng ger brjod pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:862: byung khungs kyi don 'di ltar gnas ni sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab pa na /
NK091(ke)001:863: ston pa phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba la sogs pa'i spyan sngar 'khod cing /
NK091(ke)001:864: de nas sems can gyi gnas ris tha dad pa
NK091(ke)001:865: na ji ltar 'dul ba'i skur bzhugs te mdzad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:866: phrin las kyis chos ston te gdul bya smin par
NK091(ke)001:867: mdzad pa yang / shin tu zab pas bsam gyis mi khyab cing /
NK091(ke)001:868: mtha' dang mu med pas bsam du med pa'i chos /
NK091(ke)001:869: grangs las 'das shing dpag tu med pa'i rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:870: kun gyis dgongs pa'i zhe phugs mthar thug tu basngagasa
NK091(ke)001:871: pa dus gsum du skad cig kyang mi 'bral bas
NK091(ke)001:872: 'du 'bral med par kun la khyab pa'i gzungs /
NK091(ke)001:873: chos thams cad chos kyi dbyings dang rig pa'i ye
NK091(ke)001:874: shes su ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par rang gsal
NK091(ke)001:875: bas rig pa / smrar med cing spyod yul du ma gyur pas gsang sngags /
NK091(ke)001:876: yon tan kun 'byung ba'i gnas kyi mtshan nyid bstan
NK091(ke)001:877: du yod la ngo bo dmigs su med pas bla
NK091(ke)001:878: dwags thams cad dang bral ba /
NK091(ke)001:879: chos so cog ji snyed pa'i de kho na nyid ma bcos ma bslad pas ji bzhin pa /
NK091(ke)001:880: gzhi dngos po gnyis kyi chos ril dang /
NK091(ke)001:881: lam rnal 'byor gsum po mtha' dag gsal bar ston
NK091(ke)001:882: pa'i thams cad snang la dngos gzhi med pas chos
NK091(ke)001:883: kyi me long nyid de bka' thams cad kyi rgyal
NK091(ke)001:884: po 'di las gzhan ma yin pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:885: der sdud pa po phyag na rdo rjes zhing khams
NK091(ke)001:886: so so'i rgyal ba la gus pas mi 'gal bar
NK091(ke)001:887: nyan cing dman pa'i lus can dag la ma nor
NK091(ke)001:888: bar ston pas 'chad pa po yang yin te /
NK091(ke)001:889: des rang gi 'khor la zhing khams tha dad na
NK091(ke)001:890: rnam par bgro zhing gsang ba dam pa 'chad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:891: tshul ni 'dii lta ste zhes nye bar bstan pa'o
NK091(ke)001:892: // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:893: gleng gzhi spyir bstan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:898: sprul sku'i gleng gzhi bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:901: de bzhin du chos kyi sku'i zhing khams sogs nas nges par 'grel to //
NK091(ke)001:902: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:903: rdo rje sems dpa'i chos sku'i bkod pa de kho
NK091(ke)001:904: na nyid ji lta ba bzhin du gdal khyab chen
NK091(ke)001:905: po dbus mtha' dang bral ba chos kyi sku'i zhing
NK091(ke)001:906: khams 'og min chen po chos thams cad kyi de
NK091(ke)001:907: bzhin nyid mngon du gyur pas byang chub snying po
NK091(ke)001:909: 'khor rigs lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:910: gsang ba po yang sku lnga pa rgyal tshab skyes
NK091(ke)001:911: bu zhes bya bar gyur te gcig dang du ma
NK091(ke)001:912: bral ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs nas /
NK091(ke)001:913: byang chub sems dpa' rtsal chen rdzogs pa rgyal tshab
NK091(ke)001:914: skyes bu bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'khor dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:915: te sems kyi rang bzhin ye ji bzhin pa gdod
NK091(ke)001:916: nas lhun gyis grub pas sangs rgyas par gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:917: / gnyis su med pas gsang sngags kyi ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:918: de nyid ji lta ba bzhin la tshig tu ma
NK091(ke)001:919: byung bar dgongs pa chos nyid kyi nam mkha' la
NK091(ke)001:920: / / ye shes kyi nyi ma rang gsal te nges par 'grel to //
NK091(ke)001:921: de lta bas na chos kyi sku las kyang thos so //
NK091(ke)001:922: gnyis pa longs sku'i gleng gzhi la rigs lnga ste /
NK091(ke)001:923: dang po rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs kyi 'od zer
NK091(ke)001:924: snang ba'i zhing khams kyi bkod pa bstan pa ni
NK091(ke)001:925: / sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa'i zhing khams /
NK091(ke)001:928: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:929: spangs rtogs mthar phyin pas sangs rgyas /
NK091(ke)001:930: mtha' yi rtog pas mi bskyod pa'i ston pa longs
NK091(ke)001:931: spyod rdzogs pa de'i zhing khams ni bzhugs pa dang
NK091(ke)001:932: 'dul ba gnyis te gnas dang gdul bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:933: rgyal ba mi bskyod pa de dang po de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:934: gshegs pa rdo rje 'chang chen po la byang chub
NK091(ke)001:935: mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i dus su zhing khams 'dir
NK091(ke)001:936: mtshan de skad ces bya bar 'gyur ba'i lung bstan
NK091(ke)001:937: thob pa'i phyir mngon par dga' ba zhes bya ba'o
NK091(ke)001:938: // gnas de ni yangs shing mnyam pa la rin po che'i gcal bkram pa /
NK091(ke)001:939: chu yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa /
NK091(ke)001:940: shing yal ga phyogs bzhir gyes pa /
NK091(ke)001:941: dus bzhi'i dgra las skyob pa /
NK091(ke)001:943: der skyes pa thams cad sems mngon par dga' bar byed pas na mtshan nges pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:944: zhes spyir bstan pa yin la /
NK091(ke)001:945: zhing de'i bye brag gi yon tan ni /
NK091(ke)001:946: ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gsal ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:947: rdo rje d+r+wa ba'i 'od zer gyis rnam par brgyan pa dang ldan pa na /
NK091(ke)001:949: kun mkhyen dam pa rin po che'i phyag mtshan na /
NK091(ke)001:950: 'di rgyal tshab rgyud kyi ston pa'i gnas 'dra ste
NK091(ke)001:951: 'grel pa dang man ngag gang na'ang gsal ba med
NK091(ke)001:952: gsung / 'di la legs par dpyad na gnad chen po mang zhig go rgyu yod par mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:953: ri de la sa phyogs gang nas bltas kyang rdo rje'i phung po spungs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:954: rdo rje'i rtse mo'i dbyibs su snang bas rdo rje'i phung po'i ri bo la /
NK091(ke)001:955: de kho na nyid dang ston pa'i lung dang /
NK091(ke)001:956: 'khor gyi bsam pa gsum dang mthun par lung bstan
NK091(ke)001:957: pas 'chad pa'i skyes bu chen po gnyis med kyi
NK091(ke)001:958: don las mi phyed pas sems dpa' rdo rje zhes
NK091(ke)001:959: bya bar gyur pa de ni gleng gzhi gnyis kyi
NK091(ke)001:960: don gyis zhing khams 'dir mi bskyod pa dang phyag
NK091(ke)001:961: na rdo rje gnyis ka'i mtshan du sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:962: rdo rje'i rigs kyi byang chub sems dpa' lam lnga
NK091(ke)001:963: dang rnal 'byor lnga la gnas pa bye ba phrag
NK091(ke)001:964: sa ya'i grangs kyi 'khor phun sum tshogs pa dang
NK091(ke)001:966: byang chub kyi sems lhun gyis rdzogs pas sems kyi
NK091(ke)001:967: dkyiil 'khor spros pa gang dang yang lhan cig mi
NK091(ke)001:968: gnas pas sgrib byed ngang gis med par 'od gsal
NK091(ke)001:969: ba / yongs su gzung bar dka' bas gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:970: kyi ngo bo de nyid ni dngos su rgyud 'di
NK091(ke)001:971: ba / nyid do // de sdud pa po phyag
NK091(ke)001:972: na rdo rjes rang gi ston pa mi bskyod pa
NK091(ke)001:973: la nyan cing 'chad pa'i skyes bur snang bas rang
NK091(ke)001:974: gi nye 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpa' rnams la
NK091(ke)001:976: spyir chos sku'i zhing khams kyi khongs na longs sku'i zhing khams du ma yod la /
NK091(ke)001:977: longs sku'i zhing khams kyi khongs na sprul sku'i zhing khams du ma yod pas /
NK091(ke)001:978: de bzhin gshegs pa de'i sprul pa'i sku yongs su mya ngan las 'das nas kyang /
NK091(ke)001:979: zhing der chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid ji
NK091(ke)001:980: bzhin pa de kho na nyid du don dang mthun
NK091(ke)001:981: par bsnyad pa'i sgo nas dman pa'i lus can gyi
NK091(ke)001:982: 'khor la de ltar rnam par bgro bar byed do
NK091(ke)001:983: // 'o na zhing khams gcig tu ston pa gnyis mi srid pas chos dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:984: zhing de'i ston pa ni mi bskyod pa nyid yin la /
NK091(ke)001:985: phyag na rdo rje ni de tsam na 'khor gyi
NK091(ke)001:986: gtso bo byang chub sems dpa'i cha byad du snang
NK091(ke)001:987: ba'i phyir rgyal ba nyid ma yin pas 'gal ba
NK091(ke)001:988: med do // de yang yongs su 'das nas kyang /
NK091(ke)001:989: zhes pa ston pa'i bshad pa 'das pa yin na
NK091(ke)001:990: rigs lnga dang dag pa'i zhing na bzhugs pa'i sangs
NK091(ke)001:991: rgyas la chos nyan pa'i dus na 'das nas kyang
NK091(ke)001:992: bya ba 'dug la chos sku dang ma dag pa'i
NK091(ke)001:993: zhing na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang thub pa'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:994: po la nyan pa'i skabs na 'das nas kyang bya
NK091(ke)001:995: ba med pas / de rnams dus gcig tu so sgril te 'chad dgos pa'i skyon 'ong la /
NK091(ke)001:996: yang longs sku mya ngan las 'das pa yin na
NK091(ke)001:997: longs sku'i 'khor 'das pas 'dul ba med pas mi
NK091(ke)001:998: 'thad do // yang longs sku'i cha byad kyi rigs
NK091(ke)001:999: lnga sprul sku yin pas sku 'das zer na 'o
NK091(ke)001:1000: na sprul sku la rigs lnga dang dag pa'i zhing
NK091(ke)001:1001: 'thad do // na bzhugs pa / ma dag pa'i zhing na bzhugs pa /
NK091(ke)001:1002: thub pa'i dbang po nyid dang gleng gzhi cha brgyad byung la /
NK091(ke)001:1003: longs sku'i gleng gzhi med pa'i skyon 'ong ngo //
NK091(ke)001:1004: des na nges par gang la bzhag na bshad ma
NK091(ke)001:1005: thag pa ltar rigs gzhan bzhi la'ang shes par bya'o
NK091(ke)001:1006: // gnyis pa rdo rje sems dpa'i yon tan gyi
NK091(ke)001:1007: che ba yongs su bkod pa'i zhing khams bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:1011: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1012: sangs rgyas rin chen dbang gi rgyal po ltar 'dod
NK091(ke)001:1013: pa 'byung ba'i zhing khams gdul bya'i longs spyod ji
NK091(ke)001:1014: ltar 'dod pa ltar 'byung zhing tshe dang bsod nams
NK091(ke)001:1015: mchog tu gyur pas dpal dang ldan pa zhes bya
NK091(ke)001:1016: ba rin po che sna tshogs kyi phung po zhing
NK091(ke)001:1017: de la bkod pas rin po che'i phung po rnam
NK091(ke)001:1019: nor bu bee d+aur+ya'i ri shin tu 'od 'bar zhing
NK091(ke)001:1020: rtse mo mtho ba dang ldan pa zhes bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:1021: ri bo la skyes bu chen po gnyis med rtogs
NK091(ke)001:1022: pa'i yon tan dang ldan pas rdo rje rin chen
NK091(ke)001:1023: zhes bya bar / rin chen rigs kyi byang chub
NK091(ke)001:1024: sems dpa' bye ba phrag sa ya'i 'khor dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:1025: te bstan pa sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba
NK091(ke)001:1026: gasnga sngags kyi ngo bo de nyid rang gi ston
NK091(ke)001:1027: pa rin chen 'byung ba la nyan cing /
NK091(ke)001:1028: rang gi nye 'khor la de bzhin du ston te /
NK091(ke)001:1029: sprul pa'i sku yongs su 'das nas kyang rnal ma
NK091(ke)001:1030: ma bslad pa ji bzhin par bsnyad pa'i sgo nas
NK091(ke)001:1031: de rnam par bgro bar byed do //
NK091(ke)001:1032: gsum pa rdo rje sems dpa'i gsung gi sgra dbyangs
NK091(ke)001:1033: kyi snang ba yongs su bkod pa'i zhing khams bstan
NK091(ke)001:1034: pa ni / sangs rgyas 'od dpag /ces pa nas /
NK091(ke)001:1036: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1037: sangs rgyas thugs rje dang mkhyen pa tshad med pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1038: phyir 'od dpag med kyi zhing khams sems can chen
NK091(ke)001:1039: po thams cad pad+mo las bardzusa te skye zhing bde
NK091(ke)001:1040: ba dang ldan pas bar ma dor 'chi ba dang
NK091(ke)001:1041: 'thab rtsod dang zas skom dang khur dang sdug bsngal
NK091(ke)001:1042: du bya ba med pa'i phyir bde ba can zhes
NK091(ke)001:1043: bya ba / zhing de la pad+mo sna tshogs kyis mdzes pas pad+mosa mdzes par bkod pa na /
NK091(ke)001:1044: ri'i dbyibs pad+ma brtsegs pa lta bur snang bas /
NK091(ke)001:1045: pad+ma'i phung po'i ri bo la skyes bu chen po
NK091(ke)001:1046: gdul bya la chos kyi char 'bebs pas chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:1047: sprin zhes bya bar pad+ma rigs kyi byang chub sems
NK091(ke)001:1048: dpa' bye ba phrag sa ya'i 'khor dang bcas te
NK091(ke)001:1049: bstan pa sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba gsang
NK091(ke)001:1050: sngags kyi ngo bo de nyid rang gi ston pa
NK091(ke)001:1051: 'od dpag med la nyan cing rang gi nye 'khor
NK091(ke)001:1052: la de bzhin du ston te /
NK091(ke)001:1053: sprul sku yongs su 'das nas kyang /
NK091(ke)001:1054: ji bzhin pa rang gsal bar bsnyad pa'i sgo nas de rnam par bgro bar byed do //
NK091(ke)001:1055: bzhi pa rdo rje sems dpa'i phrin las rgya mtsho'i
NK091(ke)001:1056: snang ba yongs su bkod pa'i zhing khams bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:1057: ni / sangs rgyas gdon mi za /
NK091(ke)001:1060: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1061: sangs rgyas bdag gzhan gyi bya ba ma lus par
NK091(ke)001:1062: gdon mi za bar grub pa'i zhing khams zhing der
NK091(ke)001:1063: las dag pa'i sems can rnams skye ste ngan pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1064: las lam mi spyod pa sha stag tu nges pas
NK091(ke)001:1065: shin tu dag pa'i las lam spyod pa la mos
NK091(ke)001:1066: pa'i phyir rnam par dag pa zhes bya ba /
NK091(ke)001:1067: de la rin po che in+d+ra n+ai la shin tu
NK091(ke)001:1068: mdzes pa'i brgyan pas in+da n+ai la'i d+r+wa bas brgyan
NK091(ke)001:1069: pa na / rin po che sna tshogs kyi phra
NK091(ke)001:1070: bkod pa'i nye bar mdzes pas rin po che sna
NK091(ke)001:1071: tshogs bkod pa'i spo zhes bya ba'i ri bo la
NK091(ke)001:1072: skyes bu chen po phrin las phun sum tshogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1073: gzhan don byed pas rdo rje las zhes bya bar
NK091(ke)001:1074: pa na / / las kyi rigs kyi byang chub
NK091(ke)001:1075: sems dpa' bye ba phrag sa ya'i 'khor dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:1076: pa na / / te / bstan pa sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba /
NK091(ke)001:1077: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de nyid rang gi ston
NK091(ke)001:1078: pa gdon mi za bar grub pa la nyan cing
NK091(ke)001:1079: rang gi nye 'khor la de bzhin du ston te
NK091(ke)001:1080: / sprul sku yongs su 'das nas kyang ma nora
NK091(ke)001:1081: bar tha snyad btags pa'i sgo nas de rnam par
NK091(ke)001:1083: lnga pa rdo rje sems dpa'i sku'i cho 'phrul gyi
NK091(ke)001:1084: snang ba yongs su bkod pa'i zhing khams bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:1085: ni / sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad /
NK091(ke)001:1088: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1089: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das 'khor gyi sems kyi dkyil
NK091(ke)001:1090: 'khor rnam par snang bar mdzad pa nyid kyi zhing
NK091(ke)001:1091: khams zhing de'i 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpa' thams
NK091(ke)001:1092: cad byang chub kyi sa non cing lung bstan thob
NK091(ke)001:1093: pa sha stag tu nges pas byang chub kyi snying
NK091(ke)001:1095: gdul bya'i bsam pa rnam par dag cing ting nge
NK091(ke)001:1096: 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag mang po rdzogs pas sems
NK091(ke)001:1097: sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa na /
NK091(ke)001:1098: zag pa med pa'i 'bras bu dang dgongs pa mi
NK091(ke)001:1099: g.yo ba khyad par chen pos 'phags pas chos kyis
NK091(ke)001:1100: mtho ba zhes bya ba'i ri bo 'og min gyi
NK091(ke)001:1101: gnas de la / skyes bu chen po gnyis med
NK091(ke)001:1102: kyi don rtogs nas mi gtong bas rdo rje 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:1104: de bzhin rigs kyi byang chub sems dpa' bye ba
NK091(ke)001:1105: phrag sa ya'i 'khor dang bcas te bstan pa sems
NK091(ke)001:1106: kyi rang bzhin 'oda gsal ba gsang sngags kyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:1107: bo de nyid / rang gi ston pa rnam snang la nyan cing /
NK091(ke)001:1108: rang gi nye 'khor la de bzhin du ston te /
NK091(ke)001:1109: sprul sku yongs su 'das nas kyang /
NK091(ke)001:1110: sems kyi de kho na nyid du ma nor mi
NK091(ke)001:1111: bslu bar nges pa'i sgo nas de rnam par bgro
NK091(ke)001:1112: bar byed do // gsum pa sprul sku'i gleng gzhi la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:1114: dag pa'i zhing na bzhugs pa'i gleng gzhi /
NK091(ke)001:1115: ma dag pa'i zhing na bzhugs pa'i gleng gazhi'o //
NK091(ke)001:1117: sangs rgyas thub pa'i dbang po'i zhing /
NK091(ke)001:1119: nye 'khor la de bzhin ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1120: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1121: 'dis ni rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa spyir thub
NK091(ke)001:1122: pa drug dang bye brag thub pa'i dbang po bye
NK091(ke)001:1123: ba sa ya snang ba'i zhing khams yongs su bkod
NK091(ke)001:1124: pa nyid de / sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku 'khor
NK091(ke)001:1125: ba'i dpung bcom zhing rigs drug la dbang bsgyur bas
NK091(ke)001:1126: thub pa'i dbang po'i zhing khams /
NK091(ke)001:1127: zhing der mos pa spyod pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK091(ke)001:1128: mang zhing 'khor rnams mos brtson dang ldan pa sha
NK091(ke)001:1129: stag tu gnas pas mos pa can 'dod chags zhe
NK091(ke)001:1130: sdang gti mug la sogs pa las sems mi mjed
NK091(ke)001:1131: pas mi mjeda kyi 'jig rten phyogs cha drug gi
NK091(ke)001:1132: gnas drug re re la'ang phyogs bcu dang ldan pa
NK091(ke)001:1133: zhes bya ba rdo rje'i gdan dpag tshad brgyad cu
NK091(ke)001:1134: gser las grub cing sra ba ste 'og rdo rje'i
NK091(ke)001:1135: brag tu snang ba nyid kyis rnam par brgyan pa
NK091(ke)001:1136: na / bya rgod phung po'i ri bo zhes bya bar /
NK091(ke)001:1137: 'chad pa'i skyes bu phyag na rdo rje bzhugs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1138: gnod sbyin gyi gnas lcang lo can gyi pho brang
NK091(ke)001:1139: na / dam pa'i mdzod gsum la mnga' dbang mdzad
NK091(ke)001:1140: par dbang bskur bas skyes bu chen po gsang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:1142: gnod 'dul nyid dang rigs mthun pas gsang sngags la
NK091(ke)001:1143: mos pa'i byang chub sems dpa' bye ba sa ya'i
NK091(ke)001:1144: gnod sbyin gyi rigs can manga po'i 'khor dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:1145: te bstan pa sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba
NK091(ke)001:1146: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo nyid rang gi ston pa
NK091(ke)001:1147: sh+aakya thub pa la brjod pa tshig gi sgo nas
NK091(ke)001:1148: nyan cing rang gi nye 'khor dman pa'i lus can
NK091(ke)001:1149: rnams la de bzhin du ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1150: 'o na sh+aakya thub pa zhal bzhugs pa'i dus su gsang sngags gsungs sam ma gsungs /
NK091(ke)001:1152: nges pa'i theg chen yong ma gsungs //
NK091(ke)001:1154: le'u zhe gsum pa nas gsang sngags phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa dang 'gal la /
NK091(ke)001:1156: gleng gzhi 'di dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:1157: thub pa'i dbang po'i rgyu'i byang chub sems dpa' dang
NK091(ke)001:1158: lha mi skal ba can la sogs pa la rgyu'i
NK091(ke)001:1160: 'dus pa phal mo che'i 'khor rnams gsang sngags kyis
NK091(ke)001:1161: 'dul ba'i dus la ma bab pas phyis 'byung bar
NK091(ke)001:1162: lung bstan pa yin pas le'u gnyis pa dang mi
NK091(ke)001:1163: 'gal la / 'bras bu'i byang chub sems dpa' dang
NK091(ke)001:1164: rig 'dzin khyad par can rnams la gzhan gyi yid
NK091(ke)001:1165: tshod ma yin par gsang sngags ji bzhin du bstan
NK091(ke)001:1167: der ma zad sprul sku'i zhing khams bye brag pa
NK091(ke)001:1168: 'di'i lung bstan brgyud pa'i dbang du na rtsa ba'i
NK091(ke)001:1169: rgyud kyang ston pa'i zhal nas gsungs pas shin tu
NK091(ke)001:1171: de bzhin du sangs rgyas bsam gyis mi khyab //
NK091(ke)001:1173: rnam par bgro bar byed do //
NK091(ke)001:1174: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1175: 'dis ni rdo rje sems dpa'i mdzad pa mtha' yas
NK091(ke)001:1176: par snang ba'i zhing khams bkod par bstan pa ste
NK091(ke)001:1177: / de bzhin du sprul pa'i sku'i sangs rgyas bsam
NK091(ke)001:1178: gyis mi khyab pa bzhugs pa'i dag pa'i zhing khams
NK091(ke)001:1180: gsang ba'i bdag po'i mtshan grangs med par so sor
NK091(ke)001:1181: grags pa'i skyes bu chen po zhes bya bar snang
NK091(ke)001:1182: nas / byang chub sems dpa' bye ba sa ya
NK091(ke)001:1183: dang rdo rje rnon po dang rdo rje myur ba
NK091(ke)001:1184: la sogs pa brjod kyis mi lang ba'i 'khor dang
NK091(ke)001:1185: bcas te bstan pa sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal
NK091(ke)001:1186: ba gsang sngags kyi ngo bo mtha' yas pa de
NK091(ke)001:1187: nyid rang rang gi ston pa dag la dngos su
NK091(ke)001:1188: nas / nyan cing / rang rang gi nye 'khor dag la de bzhin du ston te /
NK091(ke)001:1189: sprul pa'i sku de dag yongs su 'das nas kyang
NK091(ke)001:1190: zhes sprul sku bstan pa sna tshogs 'byung ba dag
NK091(ke)001:1191: zhal bzhugs pa'i dus su thun mong gi 'khor la
NK091(ke)001:1192: gsang sngags yongs su grags par mi gsungs pas /
NK091(ke)001:1194: 'chad pa'i skyes bus gsang sngags kyi snod nges par
NK091(ke)001:1195: brtags pa'i sgo nas gsang ba'i don de rnam par
NK091(ke)001:1198: de bzhin du sems can gyi ris /
NK091(ke)001:1200: nye 'khor la de bzhin du ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1201: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1202: 'dis rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin gyis zhing khams
NK091(ke)001:1203: bkod de sprul pa'i sprin yongs su spro bar ston
NK091(ke)001:1204: pa ste / de bzhin du sems can gyi ris
NK091(ke)001:1205: sna tshogs su snang ba bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK091(ke)001:1206: gyur pa ji snyed pa'i gnas kyi khyad par /
NK091(ke)001:1207: tshangs pa dang brgya byin la sogs pa'i lha'i ris dang /
NK091(ke)001:1208: thag bzang ris la sogs pa lha ma yin gyi ris dang /
NK091(ke)001:1209: 'jog po la sogs pa klu'i ris dang /
NK091(ke)001:1210: li tsa byi dri med grags pa la sogs mi'i ris dang /
NK091(ke)001:1211: skar mda' gdong la sogs pa gnod sbyin gyi ris dang /
NK091(ke)001:1212: lang ka mgrin bcu la sogs pa srin po'i ris dang /
NK091(ke)001:1213: seng ge yi dam brtan pa sogs byol song gi ris dang /
NK091(ke)001:1214: kha 'bar ma sogs yi dwags kyi ris dang /
NK091(ke)001:1215: gshin po'i rje la sogs pa dmyal ba'i ris te /
NK091(ke)001:1216: de la sogs pa 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu tha dad pa kun na /
NK091(ke)001:1217: ston pa'i sku ji ltar mos shing 'dul ba ltar
NK091(ke)001:1218: thub pa drug la sogs par snang bas cha mthun
NK091(ke)001:1219: pa'i 'khor la so so'i skad du chos ston te
NK091(ke)001:1220: / phyag na rdo rje nyid ded dpon tha dad
NK091(ke)001:1221: pa'i skyes bu gzugs tha dad par rnam par snang
NK091(ke)001:1222: zhing mtshan mi 'dra bar grags pa dag rang rang
NK091(ke)001:1223: gi lus can kyi 'khor tha dad pa dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:1224: te bstan pa sems kyi me long 'od gsal ba
NK091(ke)001:1225: / / gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de nyid rang rang gi thub pa'i dbang po rnams la /
NK091(ke)001:1226: 'gro ba rigs drug rang rang gi skad dang /
NK091(ke)001:1228: theg pa gang la mos pa dang mthun par thabs
NK091(ke)001:1229: sna tshogs kyis ji ltar 'dul ba rnams so sor
NK091(ke)001:1230: nyan cing / ston pa de dag 'das nas kyang
NK091(ke)001:1231: 'chad pa'i skyes bu ston pa gsang ba'i bdag po
NK091(ke)001:1232: mtshan tha dad par byung ba rnams kyis skad sna
NK091(ke)001:1233: tshogs kyis rang rang dang mthun par don gyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:1234: bo brda sprod pas ming dang don gyi khyad par
NK091(ke)001:1235: ston pa'i tshig gis mtshan mar btags pa'i sgo nas
NK091(ke)001:1236: nyan cing / / rang rang gi nye 'khor rnams la de bzhin du ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1237: des na gnas de rnams su rang rang gi blo
NK091(ke)001:1238: dang mthun par rang rang gi skad du chos ston
NK091(ke)001:1239: pas ngan 'gro'i gnas kyi skal pa can dag la
NK091(ke)001:1240: so so'i thub par snang bas sdug bsngal de dag
NK091(ke)001:1242: 'o na ngan song gsum gyi gnas na dam pa'i chos yod dam med /
NK091(ke)001:1243: yod na mi khoms pa'i gnas su mi 'gro la /
NK091(ke)001:1244: chos med na le'u 'di dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:1245: rnam par grol ba'i chos lta ba dang sgom pa
NK091(ke)001:1246: dang spyod pa la sogs pa med pas mi khoms
NK091(ke)001:1248: dmyal ba la tshe snga phyi dran pa tsam /
NK091(ke)001:1249: yi dwags la bsngosa pas tshim pa tsam /
NK091(ke)001:1250: byol song la rig pa phra mo'i chos tsam ston pas thub pa'i dbang po la nyan ces bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:1251: des na bshad rgyud mdo bcu las /
NK091(ke)001:1252: gti mug byol song gnas ris su //
NK091(ke)001:1253: rig pa shes pa'i chos kyang bstan //
NK091(ke)001:1254: ser sna yi dwags gnas ris su //
NK091(ke)001:1255: ma chags tshim pa'i chos kyang bstan //
NK091(ke)001:1256: sdug bsngal dmyal ba'i gnas ris su //
NK091(ke)001:1257: snga phyi dran pas zhen pa bzlog /ces so //
NK091(ke)001:1258: der ma zad mtho ris gnas gsum du'ang skal dman la blo dang mthun par ston te /
NK091(ke)001:1260: lha dang lha min gnas ris su //
NK091(ke)001:1261: che ba nga rgyal 'joms par bstan //
NK091(ke)001:1262: shes pa mi yi gnas ris su //
NK091(ke)001:1263: dge sdig rgyu 'bras sde snod bshad //
NK091(ke)001:1265: 'o na chos tshul phra mo de gsang sngags kyi bstan par mi 'agro'o zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:1266: de ni blo chung la gsang sngags brgyud nas bstan pa na rim gyis bstan pa yin la /
NK091(ke)001:1267: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor la ni cig char du ston pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:1269: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de phyin ci ma log par rim gyis dang cig char ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1271: 'on kyang sems kyi me long 'od gsal ba //
NK091(ke)001:1272: zhes gsungs pas 'gal lo zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:1273: de ni sems kyi dkyil 'khor gzhir bzhag pa yin te /
NK091(ke)001:1276: de yis gtan la 'bebs pas so //
NK091(ke)001:1277: gnyis pas 'khor bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:1281: de lta bu'i byang chub sems dpa' /
NK091(ke)001:1283: byang chub chen po dag go //
NK091(ke)001:1284: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1285: de lta bu'i 'khor gyi byang chub sems dpa' de
NK091(ke)001:1286: dag kyang sa mtho dman dang skal pa che chung
NK091(ke)001:1287: yod pa'i phyir lnga phrag bcu gsum gyis rnam par
NK091(ke)001:1289: 'di dag thams cad lam la gnas pa sha stag yin la /
NK091(ke)001:1290: de yang thun mong gi lam dang khyad par gyi
NK091(ke)001:1291: lam gnyis 'dir thun mong du bstan kyang don gyis
NK091(ke)001:1292: thun mong ma yin pa'i lam du 'jal bar bya
NK091(ke)001:1293: ste gsang sngags nyan pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:1294: la la zhes dgar ba'i tshig brjod pa ni nang
NK091(ke)001:1295: ris so sor 'byed pa ste 'dun par byed pas
NK091(ke)001:1296: brgyud nas nges par 'byung ba dang ldan pas byang
NK091(ke)001:1297: chub kyi rigs can dag go //
NK091(ke)001:1298: 'di rnams tshogs lam 'dun pa sems pa'i rnal 'byor la gnas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1299: la la ni bslab pas don khong du chud de
NK091(ke)001:1300: goms rtogs rnyed nas mthong lam rag pas byang chub
NK091(ke)001:1301: pa dag go // 'di rnams sbyor lam rigs chen 'byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1302: la la ni sngar ma mthong ba'i don ji lta
NK091(ke)001:1303: bar mngon sum du mthong bas don dang shes rab
NK091(ke)001:1304: mi phyed pas byang chub sems dpa' dag go //
NK091(ke)001:1305: 'di rnams mthong lam dbugs chen 'byin pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1306: la la ni rtogs pa'i don la ting nge 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:1307: gyis yang yang goms pas bdag don du mi g.yo
NK091(ke)001:1308: ba thob nas gzhan don du sprul pa mang pos
NK091(ke)001:1309: gdul bar mdzad pas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa'
NK091(ke)001:1311: 'di rnams sgom lam lung chen thob pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1312: la la ni goms pa mthar phyin nas ltos pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1313: bya ba yongs su rdzogs pas lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1314: byang chub kyi sems shar ba byang chub chen po
NK091(ke)001:1315: dag go // 'di rnams mthar lam pa rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor thob pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1316: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:1317: de bzhin du skal ba rang thad du mnyam pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1318: gzhi lam lnga las btags pa mtshan gyi rnam pa
NK091(ke)001:1319: tha dad du grags pa rnams ni 'di lta ste
NK091(ke)001:1320: zhes so sor bshad pa la rnam grangs bcu gnyis
NK091(ke)001:1321: te / lam gyi yon tan gyi sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1322: dus kyi sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1324: sems bskyed lugs kyi sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1325: slob rim gyi sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1326: rgyud du 'byung lugs kyi sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1327: rigs kyi sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1328: lam rang gi ngo bo'i sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1329: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1330: rtogs tshul gyi sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1331: don gyi sgo nas btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:1332: rig 'dzin gyi sgo nas btags pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1336: lung bstan thob pa dag dang /
NK091(ke)001:1337: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1338: 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor du gnas pas rtogs pa'i mthu
NK091(ke)001:1339: khyad par can du ma gyur kyang gsang sngags thun
NK091(ke)001:1340: mong ma yin pa'i don la rjes su yi rang
NK091(ke)001:1341: bas rtsol bas sgrub pa rjes su yi rang ba
NK091(ke)001:1342: dag dang / mnyam pa chen po'i ngo bo gang
NK091(ke)001:1343: du'ang mi zin pa'i don bstan pa la mi skrag
NK091(ke)001:1344: cing mi sngangs par gyur pas ma skyes pa'i chos
NK091(ke)001:1345: la bzoda pa thob pa dag dang /
NK091(ke)001:1346: ji bzhin pa mthong ba'i shes rab kyi spyan dang
NK091(ke)001:1347: ldan pas lta ngan dang sgrib pa dang nyon mongs
NK091(ke)001:1348: pa'i rdul dang dri ma dag pas chos la chos
NK091(ke)001:1349: kyi mig rdul med cing dri ma dang bral ba
NK091(ke)001:1350: rnam par dag pa dag dang /
NK091(ke)001:1351: yang nas yang du goms pas mtshan ma la sogs
NK091(ke)001:1352: par slar mi ldog pas mi g.yo ba thob pa
NK091(ke)001:1353: / phyir mi ldog pa'i sa la gnas pa dag dang /
NK091(ke)001:1354: bslab pa mthar phyin pas sangs rgyas kyi mtshan dang
NK091(ke)001:1355: zhing khams kyi lung bstan thob pas lung bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:1360: srid pa tha ma dag dang /
NK091(ke)001:1361: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1362: yang gzhi rnal 'byor lnga las tha dad du snang ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:1363: bla ma dang gsang sngags la 'dun pa'i rgyus yang
NK091(ke)001:1364: dag pa'i don la phyogs pas rnal 'byor dang po
NK091(ke)001:1365: pa 'dun pas phyogs pa dag dang /
NK091(ke)001:1366: theg pa chen po la zhugs nas mi 'gyur ba'i
NK091(ke)001:1367: dad pas don rang rig mtshan nyid la mos shing
NK091(ke)001:1368: rtsal sbyong bas dad pas mos pa dag dang /
NK091(ke)001:1369: chos ji lta bar mthong bas dbugs phyin nas ngal
NK091(ke)001:1370: sos pas bsti gnas thob pa yongs su bsti gnas
NK091(ke)001:1371: pa dag dang / skye ba phyi ma la mdzad
NK091(ke)001:1372: pa mthar phyung nas 'tshang rgya ba rje btsun byams
NK091(ke)001:1373: pa lta bu skye ba gcig gis thogs pa dag
NK091(ke)001:1374: pa dag dang / dang / skye ba 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:1375: kyis mdzad pa mthar dbyung nas 'tshang rgya ba rgyal
NK091(ke)001:1376: bu don grub lta bu srid pa tha ma pa
NK091(ke)001:1377: pa dag dang / dang / dag dang lnga'o // gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:1381: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1382: kun gzhi'i skabs lnga las gzhi nyid rgyu'i kun gzhi'i
NK091(ke)001:1383: stobs kyis sems rgyu gnyis dang rkyen bzhi ste drug
NK091(ke)001:1384: gis lam dam pa la 'jug pas lam du 'jug
NK091(ke)001:1385: pa dag dang / sbyor ba 'dun pa'i kun gzhi'i
NK091(ke)001:1386: stobs kyis bslab pa la zhugs nas gong ma la
NK091(ke)001:1387: sbyor zhing skyed du 'gro bas 'gro ba dag dang
NK091(ke)001:1388: pa dag dang / / snang ba don gyi kun
NK091(ke)001:1389: gzhi'i stobs kyis ji bzhin pa nyid du rig cing
NK091(ke)001:1390: 'jal bas ngal sos te 'dzin pa dang bral nas
NK091(ke)001:1391: 'jigs pa med par gyur pa phyin pa pa dag
NK091(ke)001:1392: pa dag dang / / dang / 'gyur ba med
NK091(ke)001:1393: pa'i kun gzhi'i stobs kyis dgongs pa las mi g.yo
NK091(ke)001:1394: bar phyir 'gro don la sprul pa'i lus kyis skye
NK091(ke)001:1395: ba tha dad pa rang dbang du bzhes pas phyir
NK091(ke)001:1397: btsal med gnas pa'i kun gzhi'i stobs kyis bya ba
NK091(ke)001:1398: med par gnas pas gnas pa dag dang lnga ste
NK091(ke)001:1403: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1404: byang chub 'dod pa shes pa'i phyir bla ma la
NK091(ke)001:1405: dad cing gsang sngags kyi don rtogs par smon pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1406: sems skyes pas smon pa dag dang /
NK091(ke)001:1407: chos kyi rnam pa shes pa'i phyir de la mi
NK091(ke)001:1408: gnas par dad pa dang rtsol bas langs te don
NK091(ke)001:1409: rang gi mtshan nyid la sbyor bar sems pas ldang
NK091(ke)001:1410: ba pa dang / lta bas don thams cad shes
NK091(ke)001:1411: pa'i phyir don la rig pa gnyis med du 'jug
NK091(ke)001:1412: pa'i sems kyis mi phyed par nges pas 'jug pa
NK091(ke)001:1413: ba pa dang / pa dang / lam yongs su
NK091(ke)001:1414: shes pa'i phyir de bzhin nyid las mi g.yo ba'i
NK091(ke)001:1415: gnyis med kyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i sems
NK091(ke)001:1417: shes pa chen po mthar thug pa'i ye shes mnga'
NK091(ke)001:1418: ba'i phyir bslab pa rdzogs te mthar phyin pa'i sems
NK091(ke)001:1419: kyis rdzogs pa pa dang lnga ste sems lnga'i rim
NK091(ke)001:1423: mngon du gyur pa ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:1424: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1425: las sbyong ba'i bsti gnas tshogs gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1426: bslab pa la sgo gsum gyis rtsol bas rtsol ba
NK091(ke)001:1427: pa dang / bslab pa sbyong ba'i bsti gnas bslab
NK091(ke)001:1428: pa'i mtha' bcu la mi 'bral bar slob pas slob
NK091(ke)001:1429: pa dang / pa pa dang / mtshan ma'i rgyud
NK091(ke)001:1430: sbyong ba'i bsti gnas bden pa mthong ba'i phyir zag
NK091(ke)001:1431: bcas la mi slob pas mi slob pa pa dang
NK091(ke)001:1432: pa dang / pa pa dang / / sgyu mas
NK091(ke)001:1433: sbyong ba'i bsti gnas bslab pa rnams snang la rang
NK091(ke)001:1434: bzhin med par rtogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin yang nas
NK091(ke)001:1435: yang du sgom pa'i phyir goms pa pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1436: ye shes rtsal gyi bsti gnas rdo rje lta bu'i gnyis med kyi don chub pa'am /
NK091(ke)001:1437: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo rang rig pas
NK091(ke)001:1438: mngon du gyur ba pa dang lnga ste bsti gnas
NK091(ke)001:1443: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1444: g.yo ba'i sems kyis bslab pa la 'bad pas sems
NK091(ke)001:1445: bskyed pa'i rigs can yin pa'i phyir rgyud du 'byung
NK091(ke)001:1446: ba pa dang / nan tan dang don la yid
NK091(ke)001:1447: ches pas byang chub pa'i rigs su nges pa yin
NK091(ke)001:1448: pa'i phyir rigs su nges pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1449: bden don mthong bas byang chub sems dpa' yin pa'i phyir chos su shes pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1450: byang chub rnam gnyis la gnas te mnyam par bzhag
NK091(ke)001:1451: ste bsgoms pas sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po yin
NK091(ke)001:1452: pa'i phyir chos lugs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1453: sku bzhi'am lnga'i 'khor du gyur pa'i byang chub chen
NK091(ke)001:1454: po yin pas nye 'khor la chos ston nus pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1455: phyir rgyal tshab pa dang lnga ste byang chub lnga'o
NK091(ke)001:1459: rigs gsum pa bzhi pa lnga pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1460: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1461: 'gyur dbang ma nges pa'i sa pa sa bon nam
NK091(ke)001:1462: ras bal dang 'dra bar don la nges pa ma
NK091(ke)001:1463: rnyed pas gang du'ang 'gyur du btub pa'i phyir rigs
NK091(ke)001:1465: myu gu'am snam bu dang 'dra bar don la nges
NK091(ke)001:1466: par zhugs pas ngan song du mi 'chor ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:1468: 'dab ma'am bkru bcag lta bur sbyangs pas don mthong
NK091(ke)001:1469: bas 'khor bar mi ldog pa'i nges pa thob pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1471: me tog gam 'jen tshur ltar goms pas 'bras bur
NK091(ke)001:1472: byed pa'i don mthong dka' ba'i phyir gsang sngags pa
NK091(ke)001:1473: dang / 'bras bu dang chos kyi kha dog tu 'gyur ba dang 'dra ste /
NK091(ke)001:1474: kri ya'i rigs gsum pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1475: u pas rigs bzhi pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1476: rnal 'byor dang nang pas rigs lnga pa'i yon tan
NK091(ke)001:1477: mang po ldan pa'i phyir ram yang na rigs 'di
NK091(ke)001:1478: dag gi rgyal tshab byed pas rigsa gsum pa bzhi
NK091(ke)001:1479: pa lnga pa dang lnga ste sa lnga'o //
NK091(ke)001:1484: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1485: 'bad rtsol gyis lam mthar phyin par byed pa'i phyir tshogs pa pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1486: bslab pa mthar phyin nas mthong lam la sbyor ba'i phyir sbyor ba pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1487: zag med kyi bden pa mthong ba mthar phyin pa'i phyir mthong ba pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1488: ting nge 'dzin gyis de bzhin nyid la goms pa mthar phyin pa'i phyir bsgom pa ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:1489: lam gzhan la bgrod du med pas grub pa mthar
NK091(ke)001:1490: phyin pa'i phyir mthar phyin pa pa dang lnga ste
