NK091(ke)001:1495: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1496: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1497: yid la byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:1498: lta ba chos nyid la 'dun par gnas pa 'dun
NK091(ke)001:1500: 'phro 'du gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob pas yang
NK091(ke)001:1501: dag pa'i rigs su 'gro ba'i phyir rigs chen 'byed
NK091(ke)001:1503: yongs su mi ldog pa'i ting nge 'dzin thob pas
NK091(ke)001:1504: dbugs dang po phyin pa dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal
NK091(ke)001:1505: 'byor pa dang / de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge
NK091(ke)001:1506: 'dzin thob pas rgyal ba'i bka' lung thob pa lung
NK091(ke)001:1507: chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1508: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin thob pas bdag
NK091(ke)001:1509: gzhan gyi bya ba rdzogs par byed pas rtsal chen
NK091(ke)001:1510: rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa dang lnga ni ting nge
NK091(ke)001:1514: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo nyid la 'jug go //
NK091(ke)001:1515: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1516: bslab bya yul du byas nas tshig dang sgra la slob pa'i phyir tshig gi tshogs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1517: don la mi 'gyur bar rtogs nas yi ge 'phro
NK091(ke)001:1518: 'du la gnas pa'i phyir yi ge'i tshogs pa dang
NK091(ke)001:1519: / btags pa tsam du rtogs pas thams cad ming
NK091(ke)001:1520: tsam las ngo bo med par shes pa'i phyir ming
NK091(ke)001:1522: brda dang ting nge 'dzin gyis grol ba'i phyir brda'i tshogs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1523: dbyings dang ye shes tha snyad tsam las ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:1524: gnyis med thugs su chud pas byang chub sems kyi
NK091(ke)001:1525: don du 'jal ba'i phyir tha snyad kyi tshogs pa
NK091(ke)001:1526: la sogs pa she dag go //
NK091(ke)001:1527: de dag las spyod yul gyi gzhi gsum pa mthong
NK091(ke)001:1528: lam ni gsang sngags kyi ngo bo nyid la 'jug
NK091(ke)001:1530: mthong ba mthar phyin pa bden pa mthong ba'i skabs
NK091(ke)001:1531: las btags kyi dbugs mtha' mar phyin pa ni ma
NK091(ke)001:1532: yin no // de rnams ni tshogs pa lnga'o //
NK091(ke)001:1537: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1538: tshogs la gnas pas lus ngag gi spyod pa gtso bor byed pa'i phyir spyod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1539: mos pas shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i phyir gansa pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1540: des rang don du rang rig pa'i mngon sum du mthong ba'am thos pa'i phyir thob pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1541: gzhan don du byang chub kyi thabs spro bar sems pa'i phyir phyir lta ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:1542: bslab pa mthar phyin par rdzogs pa'i phyir yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1543: de rnams ni don gyi chos lnga'o //
NK091(ke)001:1545: de kun tu sgra la gnas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1547: lhun gyis grub par gyur pa 'ba' zhig go //
NK091(ke)001:1548: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1549: de ltar rnal 'byor lnga'i lam la gnas pa'i skabs kun tu rig pa 'dzin pa lngar 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:1550: mtshan ma tshig gi rnal 'byor pa don yid la
NK091(ke)001:1551: byed pa tsam ste sar chud pa pa tshig gi
NK091(ke)001:1552: tshogs pas sgra la gnas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1553: rigs su nges pas rnal 'byor gnyis la rtsol zhing
NK091(ke)001:1554: gnas pas sa la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin thob pa
NK091(ke)001:1556: don rtogs pas 'jigs pa lnga spang ba'i phyir tshe
NK091(ke)001:1557: la dbang thob pas tshe'i rig 'dzin ni tshe la
NK091(ke)001:1558: gnas pa dang / lung nges par thob ste rnal
NK091(ke)001:1559: 'byor la gnas pas mtshan dang dpe byad kyi sku
NK091(ke)001:1560: mchog mngon du snang ba'i phyir phyag rgya chen po
NK091(ke)001:1561: gnas pa dang / dang / bslab pa mthar phyin
NK091(ke)001:1562: te skad cig snga phyir rag las pa tsam las
NK091(ke)001:1563: rtsol ba med pa'i phyir mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK091(ke)001:1564: 'khor lo ci mnga' ba thob ste lhun gyis grub
NK091(ke)001:1566: de ltar 'khor lnga phrag bcu gsum po de rtsa
NK091(ke)001:1567: ba lam lnga ru 'dus la mtshon tshul tha dad
NK091(ke)001:1570: zhwa'i ngos nas thang zhu can lnga zhes bya /
NK091(ke)001:1571: gos kyi ngos nas ras phrug can lnga zhes bya /
NK091(ke)001:1572: yul gyi ngos nas gtsang pa lnga /
NK091(ke)001:1573: chos nyan pa'i ngos nas grwa pa lnga zhes pa lta bu dang 'dra'o //
NK091(ke)001:1574: 'dir gzhi lnga las nang ris de dag tu phye
NK091(ke)001:1575: zhing bstan ci dgos lnga phrag gcig gis chog mod
NK091(ke)001:1576: ce na / de ni mdo sngags kyi grags lugs
NK091(ke)001:1577: dang sangs rgyas kyi zhing tha dad pa'i phyir don
NK091(ke)001:1578: gcig la sgra tha dad par shes par bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:1579: ce na / phyir bkod pa'o // 'on kyang 'di
NK091(ke)001:1580: rnams ni rgyud 'di nyid kyi lam la gnas pa
NK091(ke)001:1581: rnams la mtshan tha dad du bstan par 'jal te
NK091(ke)001:1582: lam pa de dag la gsang sngags de kho na
NK091(ke)001:1583: nyid kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bas sa nas
NK091(ke)001:1584: sar 'phar bar byed pa'i khyad par gyi bstan pas
NK091(ke)001:1585: ce na / phyir bkod pa'o // so // de rnams sku gsum dang sbyar na /
NK091(ke)001:1586: tshogs sbyor mthong lam pa gsum ni sprul sku'i 'khor ro //
NK091(ke)001:1587: sgom lam pa ni longs sku'i 'khor ro //
NK091(ke)001:1588: mthar lam pa ni chos sku'i 'khor te /
NK091(ke)001:1589: de yang phal che ba'i dbang du smos kyi rgya chad pa med par shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:1590: gsum pa bye brag gi mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:1591: de ltar na 'jig rten gyi khams /
NK091(ke)001:1593: yongs su grags shing rnam par snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:1594: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1595: de ltar na 'jig rten gyi khams tha dad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1596: gnas ris ji snyed pa bsam gyisa mi khyab pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1597: 'dzam bu'i gling tha dad pa bye ba bsam gyis
NK091(ke)001:1598: mi khyab pa'i 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu dang
NK091(ke)001:1599: bcas pa mtha' yas par snang ba rnams su 'jig
NK091(ke)001:1600: rtena gyi sgron ma ston pa thub pa'i dbang po
NK091(ke)001:1601: 'chad pa'i skyes bu dang bcas pa de snyed du
NK091(ke)001:1602: byung nas bye ba mtha' yas par shar ba de
NK091(ke)001:1603: dag kyang 'khor ba thog ma dang tha ma med
NK091(ke)001:1604: par brjod kyis mi lang ba'i zhing khams rnams su
NK091(ke)001:1605: / bskal pa thog ma dang tha ma med pa
NK091(ke)001:1606: brjod kyis mi long ba'i skabs don la med bzhin
NK091(ke)001:1607: du snang ba de dag la rtag par rgyun gyi
NK091(ke)001:1608: 'khor mor yang nas yang du rgyun mi 'chad par
NK091(ke)001:1609: / 'byung zhing / bstan pa chos kyi 'khor lo
NK091(ke)001:1610: bskor nas sgron ma'i bya ba byas pas lha mi'i
NK091(ke)001:1611: 'jig rten gyi gdul bya'i gtso bo rnams kyi rgyud
NK091(ke)001:1612: la sgrib pa'i ma rig pa'i ling tog gi mun
NK091(ke)001:1613: pa mtha' dag bsal nas rim dang cig char gyis
NK091(ke)001:1614: sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba rtogs para byas
NK091(ke)001:1615: te sku dngos kyi mdzad pa thams cad rdzogs pa
NK091(ke)001:1616: na dngos po la nub pa med kyang gdul bya'i
NK091(ke)001:1617: ngo bo sprul pa'i sku de dag nyi zla'i dkyil
NK091(ke)001:1618: 'khor nub pa ltar sku yongs su mya ngan las
NK091(ke)001:1619: 'ad'o zhes dus snga phyir zhing de dag tu thams
NK091(ke)001:1620: cad nas thams cad du yongs su grags shing gdul
NK091(ke)001:1621: bya'i ngo la'ang rnam par snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:1622: de lta bas na zhing 'dir thub pa'i dbang po
NK091(ke)001:1623: mya ngan las 'da' ba'i sgra dang 'das pa ltar
NK091(ke)001:1624: snang ba'ang dus 'khor mor 'byung ba'i skabs gcig bzung
NK091(ke)001:1625: ba yin no // le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK091(ke)001:1626: sangs rgyas kun gya dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen
NK091(ke)001:1627: po las theg pa che chung dang gsang sngags thun
NK091(ke)001:1628: mong gi bcas gzhir gyur pa'i byin rlabs 'byung ba
NK091(ke)001:1629: dang lung bstan brgyud pa'i gtan tshigs byung khungs bstan
NK091(ke)001:1630: pas gnyis ka'i gleng gzhi'i skabs bshad pa'i le'u ste
NK091(ke)001:1631: dang po'o // zhes dper na gos dang 'dra bar
NK091(ke)001:1632: don gyi tshoms rnams so sor ma 'dres par ston
NK091(ke)001:1633: pa'i phyir le'u ste de'i thog ma'i grangs kyi don
NK091(ke)001:1635: mdo'i ka ba lha rje yang khyed bla mas sku lnga'i gleng gzhi dang sbyar bar gsungs pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:1636: byin rlabs 'byung ba'i dngos don te gleng gzhi 'ga'
NK091(ke)001:1637: zhig 'og nas 'byung ba ni rgyud dkrug pa yin
NK091(ke)001:1638: la lung bstan brgyud pa'i gtan tshigs byung khungs kyi
NK091(ke)001:1639: gleng gzhir nges pas bye brag gi gleng slong dang
NK091(ke)001:1640: rtsa rgyud le'u gnyis pas ston pas shin tu gnad
NK091(ke)001:1641: che'o ////gnyis pa rkyen gleng bslang ba la gnyis te
NK091(ke)001:1642: / ston pas mdun bsus te gleng bslang ba /
NK091(ke)001:1643: 'khor gyis gus pas dris te gleng bslang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:1645: ston pas 'khor sdus shig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:1647: ston pas the tshom chod cig par gdams pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1652: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1653: le'u 'dis spyir drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston la /
NK091(ke)001:1654: blo chung la drang don shas che zhing blo che ba la nges don shas che'o //
NK091(ke)001:1655: de nas thun mong phyogs gcig gi lung bstan brgyud
NK091(ke)001:1656: pa'i bstan pa bshad rgyud kyis gsal bar ston cing
NK091(ke)001:1657: yongs su grags par 'gyur ba'i gleng gzhi'i rgyu'i rgyu
NK091(ke)001:1658: yang shes par bya ba'i phyir rtsa ba'i rgyud gdams
NK091(ke)001:1659: ngag zhal chems kyi tshul du bka' stsal te sku
NK091(ke)001:1660: mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul 'chad de gleng gzhi
NK091(ke)001:1661: bstan pa de nas sprul pa'i sku la don la
NK091(ke)001:1662: 'char nub med kyang gdul bya'i ngo la 'char nub
NK091(ke)001:1663: ltar snang ba nyi zla'i dpes ji ltar byung ba'i
NK091(ke)001:1664: tshul bstan pa'i snga ma'i lo rgyus de ltar cha
NK091(ke)001:1665: gcig bzung ste nye bar ston par 'byung ba 'di
NK091(ke)001:1666: ltar dug gsum las sems mi 'phro bas mi mjed
NK091(ke)001:1667: ces bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams sgron ma'i zhing
NK091(ke)001:1668: 'di na bzhugs pa'i ston pa rdo rje ltar sku
NK091(ke)001:1669: shin tu sra zhing bdud kyi dpung bcom pas thub
NK091(ke)001:1670: pa'i dbang po sh+aakya seng ge de nyid nyi zla'i
NK091(ke)001:1671: dkyil 'khor shar ba ltar skye rgu'i bye brag mi
NK091(ke)001:1672: rnams kyi tshe lo brgya pa 'di la sprul pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1673: skur byung ste yun ha cang yang mi ring ba
NK091(ke)001:1674: lo brgyad cu rtsa gnyis kyi grangs tshad zhig tu
NK091(ke)001:1675: gdul bya dang mthun par bzhugs te /
NK091(ke)001:1676: le lo can brtson 'grus la bskul ba dang rtag
NK091(ke)001:1677: par re ba sun dbyung ba'i phyir rdo rje lta
NK091(ke)001:1678: bu'i sku mchog nyi zla nub pa ltar 'jig rten
NK091(ke)001:1679: du mi snang bar yongs su mya ngan las 'ad'a
NK091(ke)001:1680: bar dgongs nas / rgya gar gyi yul li tsa
NK091(ke)001:1681: byi gyad yin pas sku gdung bgos na bar chad
NK091(ke)001:1682: mi 'ong bas grong khyer yangs pa can zhes bya
NK091(ke)001:1683: bar 'khor rnam pa bzhi la sogs pa mang po
NK091(ke)001:1684: dang thabs gcig tu bzhugs par /
NK091(ke)001:1685: dbyar gyi ngo bo zla ba gsum 'das nas ston
NK091(ke)001:1686: zla ra ba'i nya la yongs su 'da' bas 'jig
NK091(ke)001:1687: rten gyi slob ma la bstan pa gdams ngag gsum
NK091(ke)001:1688: zhal chems su bzhag pa'i slad du thun mong gi
NK091(ke)001:1689: 'khor 'dus pa nyan thos rnams kyi nang nas khyad
NK091(ke)001:1690: par gyi 'khor rdzu 'phrul cher spyod pa mo'u gal
NK091(ke)001:1691: gyi bu chen po la 'khor bsdu bar bka' stsal
NK091(ke)001:1692: pa / rdzu 'phrul can khyod deng ba'am song la 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na /
NK091(ke)001:1693: nga'i slob ma gang dag 'khod pa sangs rgyas pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1694: grub mtha' 'di par phyogs shing nga'i bka' la mos
NK091(ke)001:1695: pa daga gang ji snyed zhig yod pa rnams bsdus
NK091(ke)001:1696: shig /spyan sngar 'dus pa'i blo la nges par bzhag
NK091(ke)001:1697: par bya ba gdams ngag dag yod do //
NK091(ke)001:1698: zhes gsungs te zhal chems bor bar bka' stsal pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:1703: gzhan thams cad 'dus par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:1704: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1706: yung dkar bskor ba'i yun tsam gyis chos kyi skad
NK091(ke)001:1707: cig gis kun gyis go bar nus pa'i ngag gi
NK091(ke)001:1708: rdzu 'phrul gyis tshig bzhi bsgrags nas thams cad bsdus
NK091(ke)001:1710: rgyal ba'i gdul zhing du gyur pa'i rigs drug gi
NK091(ke)001:1711: gnas na gdul bar bya ba gang su dag chos
NK091(ke)001:1712: 'di par nges shing don rtogs pa la mos pas
NK091(ke)001:1713: phyogs pa kun gyis nyon cig /denga 'dir rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:1714: thub pa'i dbang pos zhi gnas dang lhag mthong dang
NK091(ke)001:1715: zung du 'brel ba'i bdud rtsi gsum zhal chems su
NK091(ke)001:1716: 'jog gis / zhi gnas kyis zhe sdang /
NK091(ke)001:1717: lhag mthong gis gti mug /las kyi mthas 'dod chags
NK091(ke)001:1718: te dug gsum 'joms par 'dod pa kun 'dus par
NK091(ke)001:1719: gyis shig /de skad ces bsgrags pas /
NK091(ke)001:1720: dama pa'i rigs can rnam pa lnga 'du ba la ma gtogs pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:1721: chos nyid zab mo bsgoms pas sngags kyi bsam gtan
NK091(ke)001:1722: chen po'i nang du yang dag par mnyam par 'jog
NK091(ke)001:1723: pa theg pa chen por rigs nges pas bskul ba
NK091(ke)001:1724: chen po lang ka'i mnga' bdag blo gros thabs ldan
NK091(ke)001:1725: dang / la sogs pa zhes klu'i rgyal po gtsug
NK091(ke)001:1726: na rin chen yod pas 'jog po ste blo gros
NK091(ke)001:1727: dang / rgya mtsho dang / tshangs pa dung gi gtsug phud can blo gros mtha' yas dang /
NK091(ke)001:1728: gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong blo gros dad sel dang /
NK091(ke)001:1729: dge bsnyen dri ma med par grags pa blo gros
NK091(ke)001:1730: rab zhi dang lnga ni ston pa la skye 'jig
NK091(ke)001:1731: med par mkhyen pas spyan sngar ma 'dus te /
NK091(ke)001:1732: de lnga las gzhan pa'i 'khor thun mong ba thams
NK091(ke)001:1733: cad rgyal ba 'da' ba'i zhal chems 'byung bar go
NK091(ke)001:1739: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1740: de nas 'dus pa de dag la ston pas bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:1741: kye zhes bos nas zhal bskyungs pa dang rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:1742: la dgongs te grogs po dag shes par gyis shig
NK091(ke)001:1743: / 'khor ba'i chos thams cad ni byas pa'i phyir mi rtag pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1744: 'byor pa thams cad ni mthar rgud pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1745: rgyu rkyen las skyes pa'i dngos po thams cad ni nges par 'jig pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1746: gdul bya gang zag gi srog gi dbang po la
NK091(ke)001:1747: skye shi yod pa'i phyir gdul bya'i snang ba dang
NK091(ke)001:1748: mthun par thub pa nga yang yongs su mya ngan
NK091(ke)001:1749: las 'da' bas 'khor su dag rang rang gi the
NK091(ke)001:1750: tshom ma chod pa rnams 'dir dri bar byos la
NK091(ke)001:1751: the tshom chod par gyis shig /de skad ces bka'
NK091(ke)001:1760: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1761: de nas 'khor dera 'dus par gyur pa rig 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:1762: gyi rgyal po drang srong kuny+dza ra zhes bya ba
NK091(ke)001:1763: thun mong ltar na kun dga' bo dang /
NK091(ke)001:1764: thun min ltar na phyag na rdo rje yin la /
NK091(ke)001:1765: de nyid rang gi stan las langs te /
NK091(ke)001:1769: bag dang ldan pa bzhi'i sgo nas seng ge'i lta
NK091(ke)001:1770: stangs kyi tshul gyis ston pa'i zhal du bltas nas
NK091(ke)001:1774: sngar mdo las gsang sngags ma gsungs pas phyis ji ltar 'byung tshul don gyis zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:1776: rnam thar gyi theg pa bsdu lugs zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:1777: ston pa 'das nas sgron mar gang 'os zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:1778: log lta tshar gang gis gcod zhus pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:1780: khyod ni nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK091(ke)001:1782: nges pa'i theg chen yong ma gsungs //
NK091(ke)001:1783: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1784: ston pa khyod kyi ngo bo ni nam mkha'i rang
NK091(ke)001:1785: bzhin ltar te 'dus ma byas chos kyi skur bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:1786: pas 'da' ba dang mi 'ad'a ba'i spros pa med
NK091(ke)001:1787: cing / de las ma g.yos par gdul bya rgyud
NK091(ke)001:1788: dag pa la longs spyod rdzogs skur snang bas yongs
NK091(ke)001:1789: su 'da' ba mi mnga' yang gdul bya 'jig rten
NK091(ke)001:1790: pa rnams la mthun 'jug gi tshul du sprul pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1791: sku mya ngan las 'da' ba'i mdzad pa bstan nas
NK091(ke)001:1792: yongs su 'dul ba'i thabs kyis don bya bar dgongs
NK091(ke)001:1793: pa yin no zhes rang bzhin mi 'gyur yang mthun
NK091(ke)001:1794: 'jug gi thabs kyis gdul ba la basngagasa shing thub
NK091(ke)001:1795: pa khyod ni 'jig rten gyi khams 'di'i gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:1796: rnams kyi ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i sgron
NK091(ke)001:1797: mar shar bas lha mi'i 'jig rten thams cad kyi
NK091(ke)001:1798: ma rig pa'i mun pa'i dkyila 'khor rgya che la
NK091(ke)001:1800: las nyon shes bya'i sgrib pa thams cad bsal nas
NK091(ke)001:1801: sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal zhing rang bzhin gyis
NK091(ke)001:1802: rnam par dag pa gsal bar mdzad de zhes dpe'i
NK091(ke)001:1803: sgo nas mdzad pa'i byed las la basngagasa pa sngon
NK091(ke)001:1804: du btang nas dri ba dngos ni /
NK091(ke)001:1805: sa bcu dang rnam par thar pa bzhi'am brgyad la
NK091(ke)001:1806: spyad pas 'bras bu byang chub gsum gyi go 'phang
NK091(ke)001:1807: thob par gyur pa yi kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg
NK091(ke)001:1808: pa rnam pa gsum la nyan rang byang chub sems
NK091(ke)001:1809: dpa'i rigs can gyi gdul bya gang dag rim par
NK091(ke)001:1810: bkod de nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa'
NK091(ke)001:1811: gsum gyi sa la gnas pa'i bya ba yongs su
NK091(ke)001:1812: rdzogs par mdzad lagas na yang /
NK091(ke)001:1813: lta ba mnyam nyid chen po ji bzhin par rtogs nas spyod pa blang dor med par spyod cing /
NK091(ke)001:1814: 'bras bu byang chub chen po sems kyi chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:1815: las gzhan nas mi tshol bas 'chi ba'i dug gi
NK091(ke)001:1816: nad 'joms pa'i lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i thabs mchoga khyad
NK091(ke)001:1817: par can / thabs mang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:1823: myur ba'i sgo nas thabs kyi khyad par dpag gisa
NK091(ke)001:1824: mi lang ba'i don ston pas nges pa'i theg chen
NK091(ke)001:1825: gsang sngags kyi sde snod phul du byung ba nyid
NK091(ke)001:1826: sngar thun mong gi 'khor la yong ye ma gsungs
NK091(ke)001:1827: pas de nyid gsungs par 'tshal zhes zhu ba dang
NK091(ke)001:1828: po phul ba'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:1829: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa tshig gsum po //
NK091(ke)001:1831: nges pa'i blo gros gang la bzhag /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1832: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa zab mo zhi gnas lhag mthong
NK091(ke)001:1833: las mtha' gsum gyi don ston pas tshig gi rjod
NK091(ke)001:1834: byed gsum po / gdams ngag gi yi ger lung du bstan te sngar ma bzhag na /
NK091(ke)001:1835: phyi rabs kyi blo chung mun pas rmongs par gyur
NK091(ke)001:1836: pa rnams kyis ngesa pa'i don gyi blo gros ganga
NK091(ke)001:1837: la bzhag /ces zhu ba gnyis pa phul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:1839: rnam par thar pa'i theg pa gsum //
NK091(ke)001:1840: gar bsdu gang la gang gis bsdu //
NK091(ke)001:1842: 'khor ba dang mtha' gnyis las rnam par thar pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1843: theg pa sde snod rin po che rnam pa gsum
NK091(ke)001:1844: don gyi ngo bo gar bsdu /
NK091(ke)001:1846: byed pa po ganga gisa bsdu bar 'gyur zhes zhu ba gsum pa phul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:1848: 'jig rten gsal ba'i nyi nub na //
NK091(ke)001:1849: sgron ma gang gis mdzad par 'gyur //
NK091(ke)001:1851: 'jiga rten gasla bar byed pa'i nya ma nub ste ston pa 'das par gyur na /
NK091(ke)001:1852: phyis don ji bzhin du ston pas sgron ma rgyal tshab ganga gisa madzada para 'gyur /
NK091(ke)001:1853: zhes zhu ba bzhi pa phul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:1855: bstan pa 'jig pa'i log sde pa'i //
NK091(ke)001:1856: rgol ba gang gis tshar gcod 'gyur //
NK091(ke)001:1858: ston pa mi bzhugs na bstan pa 'jiga par byed
NK091(ke)001:1859: pa'i loga par lta ba'i sde par gyur pa'i bdud
NK091(ke)001:1860: dang mu stegs la sogs pa phyi nang gi rgol
NK091(ke)001:1861: ba rnams skyes bu gang gisa tshara gcod pa'i gnyen
NK091(ke)001:1863: zhes zhu ba lnga pa phul nas de skad ces gsol pa lasa /
NK091(ke)001:1865: gsum pa rgyud kyi don dngos la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:1866: legs par byin te nye bar bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:1867: rgyud don rgyas pa dngos so //
NK091(ke)001:1869: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:1872: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1873: de nas bcoma ldana 'adsa kyis bka'a stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:1874: riga pa 'dzina pa chena po kuny+dza ra khyod kyis
NK091(ke)001:1875: legs par zhu ba de ni bdag don du legsa
NK091(ke)001:1876: so // khyod kyis dri ba lnga dris pa ni gzhan don du shin tu legsa so //
NK091(ke)001:1877: des na lan kyang 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:1880: dri ba dang po'i lan sngags byung tshul bcu gnyis su 'byung ba /
NK091(ke)001:1881: dri ba gnyis pa'i lan gdams ngag gsum bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:1882: dri ba gsum pa'i lan rnam thar gyi theg pa'i bsdu lugs /
NK091(ke)001:1883: dri ba bzhi pa dang lnga pa'i lan thun mong
NK091(ke)001:1884: du dam pa'i rigs can gyis byed par bstan pa'o
NK091(ke)001:1886: de kho na nyid nges pa'i /
NK091(ke)001:1888: dri ba dang po'i rtog pa yongs su chad do //
NK091(ke)001:1889: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:1890: de kho na nyid ngesa pa'i gsang sngags theg pa
NK091(ke)001:1891: chen po de blo che chung gi dus dang bstan
NK091(ke)001:1892: pa gnyis kar 'gyur bas gnas skabsa gnyis dang bacur
NK091(ke)001:1893: 'byung ba ste de las gzhan du mi srid do
NK091(ke)001:1894: // des na bcu gnyis po ni dus kyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:1895: bo ste de rnams la gang 'byung ba ni rgyud
NK091(ke)001:1896: gcig po 'di yi don kho na ste gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:1897: kyi theg pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:1898: de'i phyir zhing 'dir yang ston pa sh+aakya thub pas
NK091(ke)001:1899: dus 'di dag tu 'byung bar spyi'i lo rgyus kyi
NK091(ke)001:1900: tshul du bshad gzhir gsungs pas phyis so sor bshad
NK091(ke)001:1901: de don gsal bar 'byung bar lung ston par smos
NK091(ke)001:1902: te / ma la ya'i rtse la gang rmongsa pa
NK091(ke)001:1903: dman pa'i lus can rnams kyis gdung ba nyi shu
NK091(ke)001:1904: rtsa gsum bton pa de dag gsang ba pas sel
NK091(ke)001:1905: ba'am bsal ba'i dus kyi tshe na yanga gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:1906: te / 'byung ngo // de'i don le'u drug pa yan chad kyis ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1907: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa'i zhing khams so sor
NK091(ke)001:1908: ganga 'dul gyis 'jiga rten gyi sgron ma yongs su
NK091(ke)001:1909: bkoda de chos ston pa'i sprul pa rnams mya ngan
NK091(ke)001:1910: las 'das pa'i rjes thog gi dus na yang gsang
NK091(ke)001:1911: sngags 'byung ngo // de'i don le'u bdun pa dang brgyad pas ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1912: dam pa'i khye'u lnga la sogs pa ganga gisa gsang
NK091(ke)001:1913: sngags kyi don la ngesa pa rnyed de tha ma'i
NK091(ke)001:1914: dbugs chen po phyin pa na yanga 'byung ba ni
NK091(ke)001:1915: bskal pa mngon dag'i dus te /
NK091(ke)001:1916: de'i don le'u dgu pa nas bcu bzhi pa'i bar gyis bstan to //
NK091(ke)001:1917: skyes bu dam pa thub dka' gzhon nu la sogs
NK091(ke)001:1918: pa snying po byang chub nyid du son te ngesa
NK091(ke)001:1919: pa rnyed pa'i dus na yang 'byung ste de ni
NK091(ke)001:1920: le'u bco lnga pa nyid kyis ston te ru tra
NK091(ke)001:1921: snang ba'i bskal ba dang gcig go //
NK091(ke)001:1922: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dgongsa pa snying
NK091(ke)001:1923: po byang chub kyi don skye ba bzhis nges par
NK091(ke)001:1924: 'grel pa gang gi dus na yang 'byung ste /
NK091(ke)001:1925: le'u bcu drug pa nas bcu dgu pa'i bar gyis ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1926: dge slong thar pa nag po ru trar gyur te
NK091(ke)001:1927: rtsal chen pas gdula bya'i yul de thabs kyis gdul
NK091(ke)001:1928: ba'i skabs la baba pa'i dgos ched khyad par can
NK091(ke)001:1929: du gyur pa'i dus na yang gsang sngags 'byung ste
NK091(ke)001:1930: / le'u nyi shu pa nas so gcig pa'i bar gyis bstan to //
NK091(ke)001:1931: sku gsung thugs dang spyod pa'i byin gyis brlabs lasa
NK091(ke)001:1932: 'bras bu mngon par snang ba de'i tshe na yang
NK091(ke)001:1933: 'byung ste / so gcig pa nas so lnga pa'i bar gyis bstan to //
NK091(ke)001:1934: gsang ba'i bdag pos dgongs pa dang tshig gis brgyud
NK091(ke)001:1935: pa thabsa la mkhas pa'i khyad par gyis sngags spyod
NK091(ke)001:1936: pa'i lo rgyus kyi sgo nas lha mi'i 'jig rten
NK091(ke)001:1937: du yongs su gragsa pa nyid kyi dus na yang
NK091(ke)001:1938: 'byung ste / le'u so drug pa nas so brgyad pa'i bar gyis gsal bar ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1939: grong khyer gsum gang gi ched du yul dang mthun
NK091(ke)001:1940: par mdzad pa bzhi snang zhing don mdzad pa'i tshe
NK091(ke)001:1942: so dgu pa nas zhe gnyis pa'i bar gyis ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1943: rgyal ba rnams kyis nyid kyi bstan pa re la
NK091(ke)001:1944: gsang sngags phyis 'byung bar lung chen ngesa par bstan
NK091(ke)001:1945: pa gang gi tshe na yang 'byung ste /
NK091(ke)001:1946: le'u zhe gsum pas gsal bar ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1947: theg pa gsum gyis gdul bya gsum gyi lasa gsum
NK091(ke)001:1948: gyi rgyud gdul thabs gsum gyis yongsa su gcoda pa
NK091(ke)001:1950: le'u zhe bzhi pas gsal bar ston to //
NK091(ke)001:1951: ma la yar gsang ba'i bdag pos rgyal ba kun
NK091(ke)001:1952: gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po rnam par
NK091(ke)001:1953: bgro zhing gsungs pa gang gi tshe na yang gsang
NK091(ke)001:1954: sngags 'byung ste / de'i don le'u zhe lnga pa
NK091(ke)001:1955: nas don lnga pa'i bar gyis gsal bar ston to
NK091(ke)001:1956: sngags 'byung ste / // de dag ni sngar 'das pa'i dus thamsa cad kyi tshe dang /
NK091(ke)001:1957: da ltar gyi dus thams cad nas ma 'ongs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:1958: dus thamsa cad du zhing kun tu gdul bya rnams
NK091(ke)001:1961: da lta snang bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:1962: ma 'ongs pa na snang bar 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:1963: de lta bas na dus gsum kar byung tshul bcu
NK091(ke)001:1964: gnyis tshang ba'i dbang gis gsang sngags kyi theg pa
NK091(ke)001:1966: da ltar gyi dus 'dir yang byung tshul bcu gnyis
NK091(ke)001:1967: kyi tshul mdzes pa las bstan pa dam pa 'di
NK091(ke)001:1970: byung tshul dang po'ang bskal pa 'di nyid la ma la ya'i rtser gdung ba gsal lo //
NK091(ke)001:1971: gnyis pa'i sgron ma'ang zhing 'dir thub pa'i dbang pos
NK091(ke)001:1972: bkod de theg chen gsang sngags kyi byung tshul dang
NK091(ke)001:1973: 'brel dgos pas rtsa rgyud zhal nas gsungs pa'ang gsal
NK091(ke)001:1974: lo // gsum pa khye'u lnga sangs rgyas te nges
NK091(ke)001:1975: pa chen po rnyed pa'ang bskal pa 'di nyid de
NK091(ke)001:1976: lo // / snying po'i gleng gzhi ltar gcig dang
NK091(ke)001:1977: du ma bral bas gnad kyis shes par bya ste
NK091(ke)001:1978: gzhung gi dgongs par yang gsal lo //
NK091(ke)001:1979: bzhi pa khye'u lngas snying po byang chub tu nges pas 'gro ba'i gnyen por gyur pa'ang dus 'adi'o //
NK091(ke)001:1980: lnga pa khye'u lnga'am skyes bu dam pa nyid du
NK091(ke)001:1981: nges pa dag dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa'ang dus
NK091(ke)001:1982: 'di la gong dang mtshungs par bcu drug pa'i stod
NK091(ke)001:1983: na gsal lo // drug pa ru tra ma la ya'i rtse la dus 'di nyid la'ang bab bo //
NK091(ke)001:1984: bdun pa byin rlabs kyang ru tra la sogs pa
NK091(ke)001:1985: 'bras bu thob pa'i phyir thub daka'i byin rlabs snang
NK091(ke)001:1986: bar bstan pa'ang gcig dang du ma bral ba'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:1988: brgyad pa'ang snying po byang chub nas dgongs pas brgyud
NK091(ke)001:1989: pa'i rgyal tshab skyes bus 'jig rten du grags pa'ang
NK091(ke)001:1991: dgu pa grong khyer gsum gyi ched du mdzad pa bzhi bskal pa 'di la'ang mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:1992: bcu pa rgyal ba thub pa'i dbang pos lung bstan pa'ang 'di nyid las gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:1993: bcu gcig pa mdzad pa gsum gyis las rgyud bskal pa 'di la'ang bcad pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:1994: bcu gnyis pa tha ma so so'i dgongs pa zhing
NK091(ke)001:1995: so so nas bgro ba yang ri ma la ya'i
NK091(ke)001:1997: lang kas bskul bas gsang ba pas sku bzhi las
NK091(ke)001:1998: thos pa'i don bgros pa'ang bskal pa 'di nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:1999: phyir ro // de lta bas na bskal pa gcig la'ang byung tshul bcu gnyis tshang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:2000: 'o na bskal pa gcig la byung tshul bcu gnyis smos ci dgos /
NK091(ke)001:2001: gcig gis chog mod ces dri na /
NK091(ke)001:2002: dgos pa so sor nges pa'i phyir bstan pa gcig la'ang de ltar 'byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:2003: de dag gi gtan tshigs ni so so'i le'u rnams
NK091(ke)001:2004: kyi tshoms bsdus pa las shin tu gsal bar 'chad
NK091(ke)001:2005: par 'gyur ro // 'on kyang bye brag gi dbang du dus gcig gam tha dad zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:2006: ston pas gsungs pa'i dus gcig la /
NK091(ke)001:2007: tshul tha dad yin zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2008: de bas na byung tshul rang gi ngo bo la yang la la dus gcig pa'ang yod cing /
NK091(ke)001:2009: la la tha dad pa'ang yod ces bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2010: des na gsang sngags theg pa chen po nyid phyis
NK091(ke)001:2011: bskal pa 'di nyid la ston pa'i rjes thog tu
NK091(ke)001:2012: 'byung bar le'u bdun pa las sngar ston pas bka'
NK091(ke)001:2013: stsal ba'i byung tshul lung bstan du gsal bas de'i
NK091(ke)001:2014: bshad rgyud du nges pa'i phyir the tshom dang po
NK091(ke)001:2015: chod do // ston pa gcig mya ngan las 'das
NK091(ke)001:2016: ma thag par 'byung ba las byung tshul ril smos
NK091(ke)001:2017: chod do // pas kyang / dus gsum kar 'byung ba 'di la'ang tshang bar mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:2018: zhes ston pas de lta bu'i tshul gyis lan dang po bka'a stsal pas /
NK091(ke)001:2019: dri ba dang po gsang sngags mi 'byung ngam snyam
NK091(ke)001:2020: pa'i rtog pa yongs su chad de the tshom dang
NK091(ke)001:2021: bral nas nges pa rnyed do //
NK091(ke)001:2022: des na 'di nyid rtsa rgyud du byed pa'i skabs su /
NK091(ke)001:2023: 'khor phal pa blo chung rnams la sngags byung tshul gyi dus su phyis 'byung bar bstan la /
NK091(ke)001:2024: 'khor rig 'dzin la sogs pa blo che ba la
NK091(ke)001:2025: byung tshul bcu gnyis po de nyid rgyud don du
NK091(ke)001:2026: bka' stsal pa'o // de yang byung tshul bcu gnyis la /
NK091(ke)001:2027: byung tshul bsdus pa las gsungs pa ltar /
NK091(ke)001:2028: mtshon tshul lnga ru shes par bya ste /
NK091(ke)001:2029: snying po byang chub kyi byung tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:2030: gdams ngag dpog pa'i byung tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:2031: dbang bskur thabs kyi byung tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:2032: khyad par rtsal 'phang gi byung tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:2033: rgyud gnas lugs kyi byung tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:2035: snying po byang chub kyi gnas lugs la byung tshul bcu gnyis tshul gyi rtsi ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:2036: snying po byang chub kyi rtogs tshul la sbyor ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:2038: slob ma las dang skal bar 'dzom pa gcig la
NK091(ke)001:2039: bla ma dam pas gdams ngag dpog pa la byung
NK091(ke)001:2040: tshul bcu gnyis tshul gyi rtsi ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:2042: bla ma dam pas slob ma snod ldan la dbang
NK091(ke)001:2043: bskur ba la byung tshul bcu gnyis kyi tshul du
NK091(ke)001:2046: lam la byung tshul drug ste /
NK091(ke)001:2048: sgron ma bkod pa gnyis tshogs lam yin te /
NK091(ke)001:2049: rmongs pa gdung sel ni tshogs pa'i sngon du sems bskyed pa yin pas /
NK091(ke)001:2051: rmongs pa gsang phyir sems bskyed de //
NK091(ke)001:2052: ngo mtshar tshig gis 'du shes bsgyur //
NK091(ke)001:2055: le'u bdun pa bsod nams kyi tshogs gsog /brgyad pa ye shes kyi tshogs gsog pas lam dngos so //
NK091(ke)001:2056: gang gi nges pa rnyed pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2057: rgyal tshab skyes bu khye'u lnga blo chos nyid du 'byor bas sbyor lam mo //
NK091(ke)001:2058: snying po byang chub tu nges pa ni stod mthong lam /
NK091(ke)001:2059: smad sgom lam gyi bdag don te /
NK091(ke)001:2061: dgongs pa chos nyid kyi nam mkha' la //
NK091(ke)001:2062: 'grel pa ye shes kyi nyi ma gdal //
NK091(ke)001:2064: dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2066: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa cho 'phrul bzhir bkral ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:2067: gdul bya skabs la bab pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2068: gnyen po rdo rje lta bus bdud btul ba mthar lam mo //
NK091(ke)001:2069: 'bras bu la byung tshul drug ste /
NK091(ke)001:2070: byin gyis brlabs kyi snang ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:2071: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ste bdag don grub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2072: gzhan don mdzad pa la lnga ste /
NK091(ke)001:2073: brgyud pa thabs kyi grags pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2074: thabs la mkhas pa'i mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2075: gang gi ched du mdzad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2076: yul dang mthun pa'i mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2077: lung chen nges par bstan pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2078: rmad byung che ba'i mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2079: las rgyud yongs su gcod pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2080: las rgyun gcod pa'i mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2081: dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:2084: dkyus ji lta ba bzhin te /
NK091(ke)001:2086: rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2087: ma rig mun sel gyi lta ba ma dang bu 'phrad pa lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2088: a nu'i lung gi rtsa ba dgongs pa gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK091(ke)001:2089: 'gro gang gdung sel byung ba'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:2090: ma rig mun sel lta ba ni //
NK091(ke)001:2091: dper na ma bu 'phrad pa bzhin //
NK091(ke)001:2093: rgyal po dzahs byung tshul gsal byed las /
NK091(ke)001:2094: rmongs pa gdung sel byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2095: ma rig mun sel lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2096: ma bu 'phrad pa ltar bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2098: sgron ma bkod pa'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2099: ye shes rang gsal gyi lta ba nyi ma'i snying po lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2101: sgron ma bkod pa byung ba'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:2102: ye shes rang gsal lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2103: dper na nyi ma'i snying po bzhin //
NK091(ke)001:2106: sgron ma yongs su bkod pa ni //
NK091(ke)001:2107: ye shes rang snang lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2108: nyi ma'i snying po ltar bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2110: gang gi nges pa rnyed pa'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2111: ma nor don rnyed kyi lta ba dbul mos gter rnyed pa lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2113: nges pa rnyed pa byung ba ni //
NK091(ke)001:2114: ma nor don gyi lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2115: dbul mo dag gis gter rnyed bzhin //
NK091(ke)001:2118: gang nges rnyed pa'i byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2119: ma nor nges rnyed kyi lta ba /
NK091(ke)001:2120: dbul mos gter rnyed ltar bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2122: snying po byang chub tu nges pa'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2123: de kho na nyid kyi lta ba nam mkha'i dkyil lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2125: snying po byang chub dag tu nges //
NK091(ke)001:2126: de nyid don gyi lta ba ni //
NK091(ke)001:2127: nam mkha' lta bur bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2130: snying po byang chub nyid nges tshul //
NK091(ke)001:2131: dngos po kho na nyid kyi lta //
NK091(ke)001:2132: nam mkha'i dkyil ltar bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2134: dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2135: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi lta ba rgya mtsho'i gzugs brnyan lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2137: sangs rgyas dgongs pa rnam par bkrol //
NK091(ke)001:2138: ma 'dres pa la yongs su rdzogs //
NK091(ke)001:2139: dper na rgya mtsho'i gzugs brnyan 'dra //
NK091(ke)001:2142: dgongs pa nges 'grel byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2143: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2144: chu yi zla ba ltar bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2146: gdul bya skabs la bab pa'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2147: mtshan ma rang zhi'i lta ba dpa' bos dgra thul ba lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2149: skabs la bab pa gdul bya'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:2150: mtshan ma'i rtog pa rang zhi'i lta //
NK091(ke)001:2151: dpa' bos gdul dka' thul ba ltar //
NK091(ke)001:2154: gdul bya skabs bab byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2155: mtshan ma rang zhi'i lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2156: dpa' dgra thub pa ltar bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2158: byin gyis brlabs kyi snang ba'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2159: byin rlabs 'byung ba'i lta ba nam mkha'i ngang las cho 'phrul 'byung ba'am /
NK091(ke)001:2160: rgya mtsho la gza' skar shar ba lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2162: rgyal ba'i byin rlabs snang ba'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:2163: gang yang mi 'gog snang ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2164: gza' skar rgya mtshor shar lta bu //
NK091(ke)001:2167: byin rlabs snang ba'i byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2168: byin rlabs mi 'gag lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2169: rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs ltar bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2171: brgyud pa thabs kyi grags pa'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2172: mi mthun skyon sel gyi lta ba stag mos tshang skyon sel ba'am /
NK091(ke)001:2173: ldum ra'i dug sel ba lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2175: brgyud pa thabs kyi grags pa'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:2176: mi mthun pa yi skyon rnams sel //
NK091(ke)001:2177: dper na tshang ngam de skyon sel //
NK091(ke)001:2180: brgyud thabs grags pa'i byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2181: mi mthun skyon sel lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2182: stag mo tshang sel lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:2184: gang gi ched du mdzad pa'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2185: grol ba don mthun gyi lta ba sman pa mkhas pas nad gso ba lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2187: gdul bya gang gi ched mdzad pa //
NK091(ke)001:2188: grol ba don mthun lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2189: mkhas pas nad rnams gso mdzad bzhin //
NK091(ke)001:2192: gang ched mdzad pa'i byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2193: grol ba don mthun lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2194: sman pas nad gso ltar bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2196: lung chen nges par bstan pa'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2197: nges pa'i phyis 'byung gi lta ba blon po rig pa can gyi kha chems lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2199: bde gshegs lung gis nges par bstan //
NK091(ke)001:2200: gsang sngags phyis 'byung lta ba ni //
NK091(ke)001:2201: ji ltar rig pa'i gtam bzhin te //
NK091(ke)001:2204: lung chen nges bstan byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2205: nges pa phyis 'byung gi lta ba //
NK091(ke)001:2206: blon po rigs rgyud zhal chems 'dra //
NK091(ke)001:2208: las rgyud yongs su gcod pa'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2209: bag chags rang dag gi lta ba'am /
NK091(ke)001:2210: srid pa spyi blugs kyi lta ba khrus mkhan mkhas pas khrus byas pa lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:2212: las ngan myur du rgyun gcod pa //
NK091(ke)001:2213: srid pa spyi blugs lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2214: dper na khrus mkhan khrus byed bzhin //
NK091(ke)001:2217: las rgyud yongs gcod byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2218: srid pa spyi blugs lta ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:2219: khrus mkhan khrus byed pa ltar bshad //
NK091(ke)001:2221: dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba'i byung tshul /
NK091(ke)001:2222: don gtan la 'bebs pa'i lta ba bla blon tshogs
NK091(ke)001:2223: nas rgyal po'i chab srid 'dzin pa lta bu ste
NK091(ke)001:2224: / dgongs pa gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK091(ke)001:2225: sangs rgyas dgongs pa bgro ba ni //
NK091(ke)001:2226: nges par gtan la 'bebs par byed //
NK091(ke)001:2227: rgyal po'i chab srid 'dzin pa bzhin //
NK091(ke)001:2230: dgongs pa bgro ba'i byung tshul ni //
NK091(ke)001:2231: nges don gtan la 'bebs pa'i lta //
NK091(ke)001:2232: bla blon tshogs nas gros byed 'dra //
NK091(ke)001:2234: de ltar le'u gnyis pa rtsa rgyud du byed pa la skyon gzhan mi rnyed kyang /
NK091(ke)001:2236: mdo la sogs pa sngags nang pa thun mong min pa'i gzhung gis sprul skus mtshan nyid gsungs /
NK091(ke)001:2237: longs skus kri yog /chos skus nang pa gsum gsungs par bzhed pas /
NK091(ke)001:2238: le'u gnyis pa sprul skus gsungs pas sngags kyi rgyud min pa'i skyon 'ong zer na /
NK091(ke)001:2239: sprul skus mtshan nyid gsungs pa la sogs pa de phyogs re tsam nas mtshon pa yin gyi /
NK091(ke)001:2240: don la rgya chad pa med pas sprul skus gsang sngags gsungs yang mi sto ste /
NK091(ke)001:2241: sku gsum dbyer med du bzhugs pas der sku nyid
NK091(ke)001:2242: chos sku ru snang nas bskyed rdzogs gsum gsungs te
NK091(ke)001:2244: mi bskyod rdo rje thugs mchog kyang //
NK091(ke)001:2245: thugs rje sprul pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK091(ke)001:2246: 'jig rten khams ni dpag med du //
NK091(ke)001:2247: mun snang rang byung rang zhi yin //
NK091(ke)001:2249: sprul sku'i yang gsungs par don bsdus las /
NK091(ke)001:2250: byin rlabs sku bzhi'i bstan pa dag /ces 'byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:2251: shin tu spros pas chog go //
NK091(ke)001:2252: spyir mdo'i lugs la rtsa bshad la bzhed tshul gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:2253: lung bstan gyi chos skor gyi lugs kyi rgyud 'di nyid la rtsa ba'i rgyud dang /
NK091(ke)001:2255: phyi ma'i phyi ma gsum du bzhed de /
NK091(ke)001:2256: le'u gnyis pa gdams ngag nges par bzhag pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2258: gsum pa man chad rgyud phyi ma dang phyi ma'i phyi ma ni bshad pa'i rgyud de /
NK091(ke)001:2260: gdams ngag lung bstan rtsa ba'i rgyud //
NK091(ke)001:2263: gsum pa nas byung drug cu rtsa lnga'i bar //
NK091(ke)001:2264: gnyis pa'i rtsa ba legs par bshad pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:2266: de'ang le'u gsum pa nas drug cu rtsa lnga yan chad rgyud phyi ma ste /
NK091(ke)001:2268: dang po'i don las byung bas phyi ma ste //
NK091(ke)001:2269: snga ma'i don de gsal bas phyis 'chad cing //
NK091(ke)001:2270: 'brel zhing the tshom gcod dang don 'chad pas //
NK091(ke)001:2271: 'di ni rgyud kyi phyi mar bstan pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:2273: le'u drug cu re drug pa nas bdun cu don
NK091(ke)001:2274: lnga pa yan chad bslab pa'i mtha' bcu ni rgyud
NK091(ke)001:2277: rnal 'byor legs par sgrub cing nges par gnas pa las //
NK091(ke)001:2278: bslab pa'i mtha' bcus don ni rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK091(ke)001:2279: 'di ni phyi ma'i phyi mar bstan pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:2281: 'grel chen mun pa'i go cha la sogs pa'i lugs kyis /
NK091(ke)001:2283: dgongs 'dus bshad pa'i rgyud du bzhed de /
NK091(ke)001:2284: le'u dang po ni gtan tshigs byung khungs kyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK091(ke)001:2285: gnyis par gdams ngag bzhag nas ston pa 'das pa ni lung bstan brgyud pa'i gleng gzhi'i rgyu'i rgyu'o //
NK091(ke)001:2286: le'u gsum pa gdung ba bton pa ni rgyu dngos so //
NK091(ke)001:2287: le'u bzhi par gdung ba sol zhig par bskul nas
NK091(ke)001:2288: bsal bar zhal gyis bzhes pa ni gleng gzhi'i rkyen
NK091(ke)001:2289: no // le'u lnga pa'i stod ni gleng gzhi rang gi ngo bo'o //
NK091(ke)001:2290: lnga pa'i smad ni rkyen gleng bslang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:2291: drug pa man chad rgyud kyi don byung tshul bcu gnyis so //
NK091(ke)001:2292: zur lugs kyi bla ma dam pa rnams kyang de ltar bzhed do //
NK091(ke)001:2293: 'di la kun mkhyen kahthoga pa chen pos /
NK091(ke)001:2294: mdo sngags gzhan gyi lto dang sbyar na /
NK091(ke)001:2295: dgongs 'dus nyid la rtsa rgyud bshad rgyud du 'thad par go ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:2297: dur khrod rmad byung gi rgyud las /
NK091(ke)001:2298: thog mar gsungs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud //
NK091(ke)001:2299: phyis nas gsungs pa bshad pa'i rgyud //
NK091(ke)001:2300: mdo tsam brjod pa rtsa ba la //
NK091(ke)001:2301: gsal bar byed pa bshad pa'i rgyud //
NK091(ke)001:2302: ces sogs bka' lung mang po dang mthun zhing byung
NK091(ke)001:2303: tshul bcu gnyis kyi don kho na dri ba dang
NK091(ke)001:2304: lan gyis gsal bar bshad pa'i phyir 'chad tshul bla
NK091(ke)001:2305: na med pa'o // 'on kyang de gnyis mthar thug gi don la dgongs gnad gcig tu 'bab ste /
NK091(ke)001:2306: dus 'dir lung bstan brgyud pa'i bstan pa dbang btsan
NK091(ke)001:2307: par bya ba'i phyir bshad ma thag pa ltar nges
NK091(ke)001:2308: kyang / byin rlabs 'byung ba'i bstan pa'i rang skabs dang /
NK091(ke)001:2309: le'u zhe gsum pa lung chen nges par bstan pa'i rang dus sogs dang sbyar na /
NK091(ke)001:2310: kun 'dus rtsa rgyud du bzhed pa'ang gzhung gi dgongs
NK091(ke)001:2311: par gsal ba'i phyir 'grel chen las de ltar gsungs
NK091(ke)001:2312: pa'ang de yi gnad kyis yin no //
NK091(ke)001:2320: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2321: de nas yang ston pasa dri ba gnyis pa la lan bka'a stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:2322: riga pa 'dzina pa chen po zhes bos nas /
NK091(ke)001:2323: 'khor rnams la spyi'i gdams ngag gsum gyi don bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2324: bslab par bya ba rnams la spyod pas zhi gnas dang shes rab kyi blo dang ldana par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2325: de nas shes rab 'byongs te rno myur zab yangs zhib par gyur pas /
NK091(ke)001:2326: skye ba med par ji bzhin par mthong ba'i gdeng rnyed de /
NK091(ke)001:2327: lhag mthong gi gros kyis thag chod para bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2328: de ltar thag chod pa la blo mi g.yo bar
NK091(ke)001:2329: 'jog pas zung du 'brel ba'i spyod lam mam las
NK091(ke)001:2330: kyi mtha' rnam par dag pa'i thabsa kyis zin par
NK091(ke)001:2332: rnam pa gzhan du na shes rab kyi gdams ngag tu'ang mi 'thad pa ma yin no //
NK091(ke)001:2340: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2341: 'di gsum ni sdom pa spyod pa'i gdams ngag gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:2343: sgo gsum g.yo sgyu med pas sems kyi bsam pa
NK091(ke)001:2344: rang bzhin dang rnam pa gnyis ka daga para bya'o
NK091(ke)001:2345: // sgro skur med cing bsam pa ji bzhin du smra bas ngag gi brjod pa drang pora bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2346: bdag gzhan gyi don du 'gyur ba ma yin pa
NK091(ke)001:2347: rnam par gnon pas lus kyi spyod pa legas par
NK091(ke)001:2349: thun mong ma yin pa dang sbyar na /
NK091(ke)001:2350: dran rtog thams cad don dam par de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:2351: rang byung gi ye shes su shar bas log par
NK091(ke)001:2352: mi dmigs pa bsam pa dag pa /
NK091(ke)001:2353: don dam par brjod pa dang bral ba rgyal ba'i
NK091(ke)001:2354: gsung la skyon bzhi ma spangs bral bar rtogs pas
NK091(ke)001:2356: don dam par ril rgyal ba'i mdzad pa la legs nyes bral ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:2357: spyod pa legs par spyad pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:2358: de dag la spyod pa mi 'gog cing 'ching bar spyad pa med pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2360: sems la shes rab bskyed pa'i gdams ngag /ngag la
NK091(ke)001:2361: brjod pa drang po'i gdams ngag /bya ba byed pa
NK091(ke)001:2367: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2368: de yang shes rab lta ba'i gdams ngag gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:2369: thos pa'i shes rab kyis ji bzhin pa de kho
NK091(ke)001:2370: na nyid kyi don thabs khyad par can gyi gtan
NK091(ke)001:2371: tshigs la brten nas batsala ba la 'bad par bya'o
NK091(ke)001:2372: // bsam pa'i shes rab kyis de la dgosa ched
NK091(ke)001:2373: ci yod pa thams cad shes par byas te don
NK091(ke)001:2374: la nges par brtagsa par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2375: sgom pa'i shes rab kyis de ltar btsal bas gnad
NK091(ke)001:2376: tshud de gdeng la desa pa rnyed pas don mthong
NK091(ke)001:2382: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2383: ngag gi gdams ngag gsum ni spyod par 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:2384: don rjes tshig gis 'tshob pas brjod pa ci la'ang rdzun pa spangs te bden par smra bar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2385: tshig rjes tshig gis 'tshob ste ngag gi brjod pa
NK091(ke)001:2386: bzhin phyis rjes su snyog pas tshig mi 'gyur bar
NK091(ke)001:2387: bya'o // tshig rjes don gyis 'tshob pas ngag gis
NK091(ke)001:2388: ji skad smras pa bzhin du sgo gsum gyis spyod
NK091(ke)001:2389: bya'o // par bya ba'o // gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2392: yongs su rtog pa chad do //
NK091(ke)001:2393: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2394: bya ba byed pa mdo sngags thun mong gi spyod pa'i gdams ngag gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:2395: gang la bslab pa shes par bya ba'i phyir dka' thub sdom pa'i sgo spyod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:2396: rtogs pa shes rab kyi sgo lta ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:2397: goms pa ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo sgom pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2398: gol sa shes par bya ba'i phyir rtsol bas 'jug pa'i sgo dang /
NK091(ke)001:2399: grub pa thabs kyi sgo dang /
NK091(ke)001:2401: spyir shes par bya ba'i phyir stong pa nyid kyi rnam par thar pa'i sgo dang /
NK091(ke)001:2402: mtshan ma med pa'i sgo dang /
NK091(ke)001:2403: smon pa med pa'i sgo mo ste de ltar sgo gsum la mkhas par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2404: sngags kyi sde snod gsum phyis 'byung ba la slob par gyis shig pa'am /
NK091(ke)001:2405: gnas skabs bcu gnyis su 'byung ba'i gsang sngags de
NK091(ke)001:2406: kho na nyid ji bzhin pa'i ngo bo la gsum
NK091(ke)001:2407: gyi ming gi rnam grangs ni /
NK091(ke)001:2408: yi ge +amo m+aum h'u gi don gsum ste rang
NK091(ke)001:2409: bzhin lhun gyis grub pa bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK091(ke)001:2410: po nyid dang / ye ji bzhin pa ril dang ngo bo mi phyed pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:2411: rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems spyod yul dang bral ba blos reg dka' ba de nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:2412: de dag ni sngags gsum ste de la cir yang mi bsam mi dpyad g.yo ba med de /
NK091(ke)001:2413: mi bsgom pa'i sgom pa la bslab pa med pa'i bslab par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2414: yang na phyis 'byung ba'i rig sngags gsang sngags gzungs sngags gsum la slob par gyis shig pa'am /
NK091(ke)001:2415: mdo nyid las grags pa'i rig sngags rang bzhin lhun grub /
NK091(ke)001:2416: gzungs sngags ye ji bzhin pa //
NK091(ke)001:2417: gsang sngags rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor te de ltar sngags gsum la bslab par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2418: de ltar sgom pas gol sa sgrib pa ni grong khyer gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:2419: rgyud tha dad pas 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med khams gsum dang /
NK091(ke)001:2420: rgyud gcig pas lus snang ba 'dod khams /
NK091(ke)001:2422: yid mi snang ba gzugs med kyi khams gsum dang /
NK091(ke)001:2423: shes pa rtog pa'i rgyud tshogs drug rang yul rnams 'dod pas 'dod khams /
NK091(ke)001:2424: nyon yid nga'am bdag gi bar rloms sems pas gzugs khams /
NK091(ke)001:2425: kun gzhi bltar dngos su med pas gzugs med khams te de ltar grong khyer gsum bshig par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2426: 'o na 'dir gsum tsho lnga yod pas gdams ngag gsum du 'jog btub bam zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:2427: de ni bco lngar snang yang rtsa ba'i dbang gis
NK091(ke)001:2428: gsum zhes pa mi 'gal te dper na rims nyin
NK091(ke)001:2429: bzhi pa'am / sbrul gom pa bdun pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:2430: shing 'dab ma bdun pa lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:2431: de dag kyang blo chung ba'i ngor rgyu'i theg pa'i nges par bzhag pa gsum yin kyang /
NK091(ke)001:2434: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa tshig gsum po //
NK091(ke)001:2435: 'phrul gyi blo dang gros mchog ste //
NK091(ke)001:2436: yul gyi don srid chen po pas //
NK091(ke)001:2437: blo gros dam pa'i yul du snang //
NK091(ke)001:2439: le'u lnga bcu nga drug pa las /
NK091(ke)001:2440: kun nas 'dus pa'i dgongs pa tshig gsum po //
NK091(ke)001:2441: yid ches nges pas blo yi gdengs su bya //
NK091(ke)001:2442: tshig gsum don la nges rnyed mngon gyur na //
NK091(ke)001:2443: nges pa'i don ni rang rig kho nar zad //
NK091(ke)001:2445: gsang sngags theg pa mchog gi ngo bo rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi dngos gzhi ste /
NK091(ke)001:2447: zhes de skad ston pas bka' stsal pas /
NK091(ke)001:2448: dri ba gnyis pa'i yongs su rtog pa chad do //
NK091(ke)001:2452: yongs su rtog pa chad do //
NK091(ke)001:2453: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2454: de nas yang ston pasa dri ba gsum pa la lan bka'a stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:2455: riga pa 'dzin pa chen po zhes bos nas /
NK091(ke)001:2457: ston pa thub pa'i dbang po nga yis yi ge'i
NK091(ke)001:2458: sgron ma bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa gsum du
NK091(ke)001:2459: gang bzhag pa de ni snod kyi rim pa rab
NK091(ke)001:2460: 'bring tha ma gsum dag la rang rang gi mos
NK091(ke)001:2461: pa ltar du snang ba ste de'i phyir spyi'i ngo
NK091(ke)001:2462: bo ni sde snod rin po che rnam pa gsum
NK091(ke)001:2463: du bsdu'o // de'i don gyi bsdu lugs ni zhi gnas lhag mthong lasa mtha' gsum du bsdu'o //
NK091(ke)001:2464: de yang 'dul ba'i dbang gis dang po shes pa'i
NK091(ke)001:2465: rgyud gsum sgo gsum mam thos bsam sgom gsum gyi
NK091(ke)001:2467: rnam pa gzhan du gang zag gcig gi kun gzhi nyon yid yid de shes pa gsum la'ang bsdu'o //
NK091(ke)001:2468: 'jug pa'i skal ba chung bas yi ge la ma
NK091(ke)001:2469: brten par mi go ba'i phyir de nasa yi ge'i
NK091(ke)001:2470: tshogsa te sde snod kyi glegs bam nyid la'ang bsdu'o
NK091(ke)001:2471: // gang gis bsdu na gang zag la che chung
NK091(ke)001:2472: gi rim pa'i blo yi khyad par yod pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:2473: na de gnyis kyi ched du theg pa'i rim pa'ang
NK091(ke)001:2474: de bzhin du mtho dman gnyis su byas te /
NK091(ke)001:2475: bsdu ba'ang blo chung 'bring gi ngor snang ba theg
NK091(ke)001:2476: pa chung ngu nyan thos kyi lugs su 'od srung
NK091(ke)001:2477: la sogs pas bsdu ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:2478: blo chen po'i ngor snang ba theg pa chen po
NK091(ke)001:2479: dbu ma'i lugs su kun dga' bo'am phyag na rdo
NK091(ke)001:2480: rje la sogs pa so so'i sdud pa pos che
NK091(ke)001:2481: chung gi rim pa gnyis kyis bsdu bas so //
NK091(ke)001:2482: gzhi gang la bsdu na de ltar blo che chung
NK091(ke)001:2483: rnam pa gnyis kyi khyad par las blo yis 'jug
NK091(ke)001:2484: pa'i yul theg pa'i chos kyi rim pa yang lta
NK091(ke)001:2485: spyod la sogs pa mtho dman gyi khyad par /
NK091(ke)001:2486: de kho na bzhin du bkal stsal pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2487: des na gdul bya rang rang gang la mos pa
NK091(ke)001:2488: de nyid dang mthun par 'dul bar 'gyur bas che
NK091(ke)001:2489: chung gnyis nyid du bsdu bar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:2491: dri ba gsum pa'i yongas su rtog pa chad do //
NK091(ke)001:2495: mya ngan las 'das par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:2496: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2497: de nas yanga ston pasa dri ba bzhi pa dang
NK091(ke)001:2498: lnga pa gnyis kyi lan tshig le'u gcig pa bka'
NK091(ke)001:2499: stsal pa ni / lan gzhan yang dri ba tha
NK091(ke)001:2500: ma gnyis kyi lan tshig gcig gis yongs su chod
NK091(ke)001:2501: stsal pa ni / par bya ste / bde gshegs
NK091(ke)001:2502: snying pos bsdus pa'i chos kyi sbun du byas pa
NK091(ke)001:2503: stsal pa ni / par bya ste / yi /
NK091(ke)001:2504: rig pa 'dzin pa kuny+dzara khyod nyon cig ces bos
NK091(ke)001:2505: stsal pa ni / par bya ste / yi /
NK091(ke)001:2506: nas gdams te / ston pa sku mya ngan las
NK091(ke)001:2507: 'das pa'i 'og tu ston pa'i rgyal tshab kyi sgron
NK091(ke)001:2508: ma byed cing gsang sngags yongs su grags par gsung
NK091(ke)001:2510: sku ma 'das pa'i sngon du byung ba'i rgyal po
NK091(ke)001:2511: dzahl phyis gsang sngags 'byung bar lung bstan pa'i dus
NK091(ke)001:2513: 'gro ba dman pa'i lus kyi sems dpa' chen po
NK091(ke)001:2514: dam pa'i rigs can lnga la sogs pa dag byung
NK091(ke)001:2515: nas drag shul can gyi rtser gsol ba btab pas
NK091(ke)001:2516: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje dngos su
NK091(ke)001:2517: byon te de dag la gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg
NK091(ke)001:2518: pa nyid ji bzhin par ston cing de dag gis
NK091(ke)001:2519: kyang so sor rang rang gi mthun pa'i gnas ris
NK091(ke)001:2520: su ston par mdzad cing spros nas gsal bar byed
NK091(ke)001:2521: pa dang / log pa'i sde pa'ang sun 'byin zhing tshar gcod par byed do //
NK091(ke)001:2522: 'di'i shugs kyis pad+ma la sogs pa yang mtshon par chos rje'i phyag mchan las gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:2523: de skad ces bka' stsal pas dri ba bzhi pa
NK091(ke)001:2524: dang lnga pa'i yongs su rtog pa chad de ston
NK091(ke)001:2525: zlar ba'i nya la sku yongs su mya ngan las
NK091(ke)001:2528: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongas pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen
NK091(ke)001:2529: po las ji skad gsungs pa'i lan lnga dang gdams
NK091(ke)001:2530: ngag gsum nges par bzhag pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa
NK091(ke)001:2531: gsal bar bshad pa'o ////e ma rgyud lung man ngag
NK091(ke)001:2532: kun gyi mdzod // bstan pa'i dbyig mchog lung chen 'dus pa mdo'i //
NK091(ke)001:2533: bka' yi nges gsang rtsa ba'i rgyud chen gyi //
NK091(ke)001:2534: dgongs don man ngag tshad mas deng 'dir gsal //
NK091(ke)001:2535: zla 'od zer gyis kun+da'i ge sar bkra //
NK091(ke)001:2536: 'od stong ldan pas pad dkar 'dab brgya grol //
NK091(ke)001:2537: lung rigs gsal bas chos kyi me long 'grel //
NK091(ke)001:2538: blo mchog zab don bzhed rnams dga' bas longs //
NK091(ke)001:2540: gnyis pa bshad pa'i rgyud la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:2547: gleng gzhi rang gi ngo bo'o //
NK091(ke)001:2549: 'khor gdung ba yod med kyi bye brag /ston pa 'das pa'i nyes dmigs /
NK091(ke)001:2550: gdung ba bton pa dngos so //
NK091(ke)001:2555: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2557: bshad tshul rjes su mthun par bstan pa'i gleng gzhi'i rgyu bshad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2558: gdams ngag bzhag nas sku 'das pa de'i tshe de'i
NK091(ke)001:2559: dus na skyes bu gang dag don la shed bye
NK091(ke)001:2560: ba'i bsod nams dang rtogs pa che bas mi chen
NK091(ke)001:2561: po dam pa'i rigs can lnga la sogs pa sems
NK091(ke)001:2562: dpa' chen po dang rig pa 'dzin pa rnams ni
NK091(ke)001:2563: / ston pa'i sku la 'da' ba dang mi 'da'
NK091(ke)001:2564: med cing sems la skye shi med par shes pa'i
NK091(ke)001:2565: dbang gis yongs su gdung ba med par nanga du
NK091(ke)001:2566: mi g.yo ba'i bsam gtan la yang dag par mnyam
NK091(ke)001:2567: / par 'jog go // don chen po la shed
NK091(ke)001:2568: ma bye ba'i nyan thos dang 'jig rten pa la
NK091(ke)001:2569: sogs pa'i byis pa gzugs sku skye 'jig tu mthong
NK091(ke)001:2570: ba'i lta ba can rnams ni ston pa sku 'das
NK091(ke)001:2571: par mthong nas sems mya ngan gyis yongs su gdung
NK091(ke)001:2572: / par 'jog go // bar gyur te / blo
NK091(ke)001:2573: 'jigs shing skyi bung bas ya ya bor gyur cing
NK091(ke)001:2574: dran pa nyams pas shin tu blong nas rtag par
NK091(ke)001:2575: smre sngags 'don te rab tu ngu'o //
NK091(ke)001:2577: lo ka pa dang sangs rgyas pa gdung bas zin pa /
NK091(ke)001:2578: gzhan gyi sde pa bcas ka'i tshig sgrogs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2583: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2584: 'jiga rten pa phal par gyur pa la la ni
NK091(ke)001:2585: shin tu gdung bas shi ba la thug para gyur
NK091(ke)001:2586: / la la ni smra zhing 'gyel bas bargyal zhing
NK091(ke)001:2587: la la ni mi smra bar 'gyel bas 'boga par
NK091(ke)001:2588: / gyur / la la na sems kyi khams stor
NK091(ke)001:2589: nasa lus kyi mdangs nyams te ro bam pa bzhin
NK091(ke)001:2590: / gyur / du gyur to // de bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:2591: 'khor gyi nyan thos thamsa cad kyang gu ljo ste
NK091(ke)001:2592: byis pa mang po pha shi ba bzhin du ngag
NK091(ke)001:2593: nas kyi hud kyi hud ces sdug bsngal gyis gdung
NK091(ke)001:2595: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten yang snod rnams ni rtsi shing skams pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:2596: rlung dang kha char la sogs pa byung nas yid du mi 'ong bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:2597: bcud kyi sems can rnams kyang ston pa la mos
NK091(ke)001:2598: pa rnams ni sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'thibs te mi
NK091(ke)001:2599: gsal bas mog mog por gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:2600: sangs rgyas pa'i chos 'di par phyogs pa rnams ni mi dga' bas mdangsa nag pora gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:2605: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2606: sku 'das pa la dga' ba bye ba dung phyur
NK091(ke)001:2607: la sogs pa bdud kyi cha 'dzin cing gzhan gyi
NK091(ke)001:2608: sde pa mu stegs byed rnams ni /
NK091(ke)001:2609: sems dga' nas bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dkar por gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:2610: kun kyang go ta ma'i rdo rje'i sku 'das nas
NK091(ke)001:2611: bstan pa ni me shi ba'i dud pa ltar du
NK091(ke)001:2612: gyur to // zhes log par lta bas mi snyan
NK091(ke)001:2613: pa brjod de bcas ka'am ya ka'i tshig sgrogs par
NK091(ke)001:2614: gyur to // gyur to // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:2621: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2622: de nas lo brgyad dang bcu tshan gnyis 'das pa na /
NK091(ke)001:2623: dam pa'i rigs can lang ka'i bdag po la sogs
NK091(ke)001:2624: pa sems dpa' chen po dag /nang du yang dag
NK091(ke)001:2625: par 'jog pa dgongs pa'i ting nge 'dzin las langsa
NK091(ke)001:2626: pa dang / 'jig rten gyi ston pa nub par gyur pa mthong bas ston pa med pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:2628: gdul bya'i bya ba sgrub tshul la sems te gzhan
NK091(ke)001:2629: don du yul so so nas rma ga chad pa
NK091(ke)001:2630: ste phal che bar ngus nas /
NK091(ke)001:2631: de nas rig pa 'dzin pa kun kyang gdung ba
NK091(ke)001:2632: 'don pa dang bgro ba'i phyir rang rang gi mngon
NK091(ke)001:2633: par shes pas / lang ka'i yul gyi grong rdal
NK091(ke)001:2634: gyi mtsho gling yon tan mang pos mngon par mtho
NK091(ke)001:2635: ba'i ri ma la ya gnam lcagsa yoda pa'i rtse
NK091(ke)001:2636: par shes pas / la / phyag na rdo rjes gsang sngags ston par mthong nas /
NK091(ke)001:2637: sa la 'dzul zhing mkha' la 'gro ba'i rdzu 'phrul gyi bya basa mngon par raba tu 'dus so //
NK091(ke)001:2638: yongsa su 'dus par gyur nas 'dusa pa de dag kun kyang /
NK091(ke)001:2639: sems bskyed dang ngag mthun pas mgrin gcig tu shin tu nyam thag pa'i nga ros /
NK091(ke)001:2640: rgyal ba rnams yid la byas te /
NK091(ke)001:2641: smre sngags kyi gdung ba nyi shu rtsa gsum bton pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:2643: gnyis pa la nyi shu rtsa gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:2644: sgron ma nub pas mun pa gang gis sel gdung zhing dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:2645: tshad ma'i zhal med pas gtan la phebs sam zhes gdung ba /
NK091(ke)001:2646: ye shes kyi spyan zum pas log stobs mi 'phel lam zhes gdung ba /
NK091(ke)001:2647: nyi zla nub pas mun par mi 'khyams sam zhes gdung ba /
NK091(ke)001:2648: gdug pa sus 'dul zhes zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2649: bstan pa gsal bar sus byed zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2650: bslab pa sus 'dzin par zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2651: slob ma la lung bstan ji ltar 'byung ba zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2652: rtsod pa mi 'phel lam zhes gdung ba /
NK091(ke)001:2653: bka' bslad cing mi 'chos sam zhes gdung ba /
NK091(ke)001:2654: chos dang nor mi barje'am zhes zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2655: bstan pa la dgra dar bar mi 'gyur ram zhes zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2656: bstan pa gnas pa'i yun dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:2657: dus ji ltar 'gyur ba zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2658: bstan pa'i mtha' ji ltar 'gyur zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2659: slob ma'i mtha' ji ltar 'gyur zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2660: 'di nas gang du gshegs shing gang na bzhugs zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2661: da 'jig rten gyi mgon du gang 'ong ba zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2662: blo gros gang nas btsal zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2663: nges don gang la bzung zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2664: sku gdung ji ltar 'byung zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2665: slad kyis mchod gnas gang la bya ba zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2666: ston pa'i gdung 'tshob 'byung ngam zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2671: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2672: 'di dag rgyu dang rkyen thun mong du'ang 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:2673: byang chub sems pa' de dag la mngon shes yod
NK091(ke)001:2674: pas snying po byang chub kyi rgyal ba la don
NK091(ke)001:2675: gyis bskul bar yang 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:2676: bdag don du sdug bsngal gyi sgra e ma'o kyi hud ces dang /
NK091(ke)001:2677: gzhan don du dran pa nyams pas e ma'o blong zhes gdung ba'i smre sngags phyung ste /
NK091(ke)001:2678: ston pa thub pa'i dbang po'i sgron ma'i 'od kyi snang ba nub par gyur na /
NK091(ke)001:2679: phyi nas 'jig rten gyi ma rig pa'i mun pa
NK091(ke)001:2680: bstan pa dang ston pa gang gisa sel bar 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:2681: zhes zhus pa'o // spyir ston pa la bzhi ste
NK091(ke)001:2682: rgyal tshab rgyud kyi ston pa mi pham byams pa
NK091(ke)001:2684: byin rlabs sprul pa'i ston pa thub pa drug /
NK091(ke)001:2685: 'dren pa rang byung gi ston pa sh+aakya thub pa /
NK091(ke)001:2686: bsod nams rten gyi ston pa la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:2687: sku dang thugs kyi gzugs brnyan gyi rnam pa /
NK091(ke)001:2688: gsung gi glegs bam zab mo /
NK091(ke)001:2689: don la lhag chad med par ston pa'i gang zag chos kyi mig can rnams las 'dir gsum pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2694: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2695: bden zhing mi bslu bas tshad ma'i zhal de mi bzhugs pasa /
NK091(ke)001:2696: nyid kyi tshad mas gsungs pa'i bstan pa rin po
NK091(ke)001:2697: che la yang dag par 'jug par 'atshala ba'am 'dod
NK091(ke)001:2698: pa'i 'gro ba rnams lta ba ji lta bar rtogs
NK091(ke)001:2699: mi nus par phyin ci log par 'jug ste gol
NK091(ke)001:2701: tshad mar dam bcas pa'i slob ma gang zag chos
NK091(ke)001:2702: kyi mig can dag gis nges pa ma rnyed pa'i
NK091(ke)001:2703: gang zag slob bu gzhan la phan gdags par bya
NK091(ke)001:2704: ba'i phyir ston pa'i bka' yi don bkrol ba na
NK091(ke)001:2705: / ji bzhin du gtan la phebs nus par 'gyur zhig gu /
NK091(ke)001:2711: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2712: ston pa legsa nyes kyi khyad par ci bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:2713: 'byed pa'i ye shes kyi spyan can zum ste mi
NK091(ke)001:2714: bzhugs pas / mu stegs sogs sam log pa'i nga
NK091(ke)001:2715: rgyal skyes nas bka' nyid khyad du gsod pa yi
NK091(ke)001:2716: log par lta bas skyon gyi spyi gtsug mthar phyin
NK091(ke)001:2717: pas mgo rting log pa lta bur gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:2718: log stobs 'phel bar mi 'gyur ram zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2723: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2724: ston pa tshad ma'i skyes bu mi bzhugs na /
NK091(ke)001:2725: thar lam las phyin ci log tu gyur pa'i bstan
NK091(ke)001:2726: pa ngan pa'i sprin 'khrigs pa lta bus khebs pas
NK091(ke)001:2727: / bstan pa'i don bden pa gnyis kyi nyi zla
NK091(ke)001:2728: lta bu nub par gyur te 'gro ba gang zhig
NK091(ke)001:2729: yang dag pa'i lam tshol ba rnams kyang ma rig
NK091(ke)001:2730: pas non te muna par 'khyams par mi 'gyur ram
NK091(ke)001:2736: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2737: ston pa mi 'jigs bzhi'i bdag nyid mya ngan las
NK091(ke)001:2738: 'das pa'i 'og tu bstan pa la 'tshe ba'i phyi
NK091(ke)001:2739: nang gi bdud dang srin po dang mu stegs byed
NK091(ke)001:2740: dang / gnod sbyin dang 'byung po dang mi ma
NK091(ke)001:2741: yin gyi rigs ma rung ba'i gdug pa can rnams
NK091(ke)001:2742: phyis su stobs kyi mnga' bdag sus 'dul bar 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:2748: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2749: rang bzhin gyis dag cing 'khrul pa'i gnyen por gyur
NK091(ke)001:2750: pas dri ma med pa bstana pa'i bdud rtsi chen
NK091(ke)001:2751: po 'di nyid gal te nub par gyur na shin
NK091(ke)001:2752: tu ma rung bar nges na /
NK091(ke)001:2753: shes rab kyi rtsala dang ldan pa su zhig gis /
NK091(ke)001:2754: gsal bar 'bar zhing kun tu snang bar byed par 'gyur zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2759: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2760: shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin dang tshul khrims kyi
NK091(ke)001:2761: bslab pa dam pa rin po che rnam pa gsum
NK091(ke)001:2762: po dang bral bar gyur na shin tu ma rung
NK091(ke)001:2763: bar nges na / phyis su skyes bu dam pa
NK091(ke)001:2764: gang zhig gis bslab pa'i tshul rnams ji bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:2765: 'dzin par byeda par 'gyur zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o
NK091(ke)001:2766: bar nges na / // brgyad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2769: gang du zhig /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2770: ston pa thugs rje'i mnga' bdag mi bzhugs pa de yi rjes na /
NK091(ke)001:2771: ston pa'i slob ma gang ji snyeda pa rnams kyi la la sa non pas 'phagsa pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:2772: la la zag pa dang bcas pas gang zag tha
NK091(ke)001:2773: dad pa rnams la rang rang dang mthun par lung
NK091(ke)001:2774: bstan gsal bar 'byung ba gnas skabs gang du su
NK091(ke)001:2775: zhig gis ston par 'gyur zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o
NK091(ke)001:2780: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2781: bstan pa rin po che ni phyogs ris med pa nam mkha' dang 'dra ba yin pa la /
NK091(ke)001:2782: rang rang gi mos pa tha dad pa ltar phyogs ris su bzung nas /
NK091(ke)001:2783: rang gi lugs yin pa dang gzhan gyi ltar ma
NK091(ke)001:2784: yina pas dgag sgrub kyi cha so sor 'dzina cing
NK091(ke)001:2785: rtsod pa 'phel zhing kun tu 'khrugs par mi 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:2786: rama zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2791: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2792: bstan pa'i de kho na nyid nges par theg pa
NK091(ke)001:2793: chen po gsang sngags su rigsa gcig par gnas pa
NK091(ke)001:2794: la / mi shes pa rnams kyis lugsa mi mthun
NK091(ke)001:2795: par bzung nas tha dad du spyod pas rigs gcig
NK091(ke)001:2796: tha snyad tha dad du bzhag ste rigs sna tshogs
NK091(ke)001:2797: rnams su mu stegs pa la sogs pas bslad cing
NK091(ke)001:2798: bcos para mi 'gyur rama zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o
NK091(ke)001:2803: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2804: rin thang tshad med pa'i dam pa'i chos rin po che nyid /
NK091(ke)001:2805: mi mkhas bzhin du slob dpon gyi go sa thob pa'i gang zag tha dad du gyur pas /
NK091(ke)001:2806: rang rgyud nyon mongs dang 'dod pas gzir zhing khrid
NK091(ke)001:2807: pa'i dbang gis nor rdzas kyi dngos po rnam smin
NK091(ke)001:2808: dbal tsha bas dug dang 'dra ba la barje bar
NK091(ke)001:2809: mi 'gyur ram zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2814: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2815: chos kyi rgyal po ston pa stobs bcu'i dbang phyug
NK091(ke)001:2816: de nyid dus 'di yi sngon phan chad du zhal
NK091(ke)001:2817: bzhugs te dngos su chos ston pa'i skabs na'ang bdud
NK091(ke)001:2818: dang mu stegs la sogs pas ma rung ba rnams
NK091(ke)001:2819: kyis bstan pa la 'tshe bar bgyid na /
NK091(ke)001:2820: ston pa mi bzhugs na bstan pa la phyi'i dgra
NK091(ke)001:2821: gdug cing mi srun pa dar bar mi 'gyur ram
NK091(ke)001:2827: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2828: da lta'i dus gang 'dir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:2829: rin po che 'byung ba 'di nyid gnas pa'i yun
NK091(ke)001:2830: ci srid cig tu gnas par 'gyur zhes gdung zhing
NK091(ke)001:2831: dris pa'o // bcu bzhi pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2835: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2836: da lta'i dus gang 'dira bstan pa rin po che
NK091(ke)001:2837: 'byung ba'ang sngar byung ba 'das pa'i dus su ji
NK091(ke)001:2838: ltar byung / da lta gong sngar byung zin pa 'di'i don ji ltar 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:2839: phyis ma 'ongs pa na bstan pa 'di nub nas
NK091(ke)001:2840: gzhan byung ba'i dus su 'di nyid ji ltar 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:2846: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2847: ston pa'i bstan pa 'di nyid dus tha ma'i tshe na /
NK091(ke)001:2848: nges par nub pa'am mi nub pa ji ltar du 'gyur zhig gu zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2853: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2854: bslab pa gsum dang bcu po rnams 'dzin pa'i slob ma rnams /
NK091(ke)001:2855: dus kyi tha ma la ji ltar 'gyur zhig gu zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2860: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2861: ston pa de nyid 'di nas mya ngan las 'adsa
NK091(ke)001:2862: pa'i 'og tu tshul gang ltar gdul bya su yi
NK091(ke)001:2864: zhing khams kyi phyogs ni gang zhig na bzhugs nas
NK091(ke)001:2865: zhing de na bstan pa dam pa ji lta bu
NK091(ke)001:2866: zhig sgrogsa par mdzad pa lags zhes gdung zhing dris
NK091(ke)001:2871: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2872: ston pa mi bzhugs kyang da yong 'jig rten 'dir
NK091(ke)001:2873: mgon skyabs med pa rnams kyi mgon dang skyabs su
NK091(ke)001:2874: rgyal tshab skyes bu gang zhig 'byung bar 'gyur zhes
NK091(ke)001:2879: gang nas btsal zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2880: rin chen 'phrul gyi me long lta bu'i man ngag
NK091(ke)001:2881: gi rtsa ba zhi bar gnas pas blo dang lhag
NK091(ke)001:2882: ger mthong bas gros dam pa stor nas ma rnyed
NK091(ke)001:2883: na / kun la phan pa'i blo dang gros ni
NK091(ke)001:2884: gang nas btsal bar bya zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o
NK091(ke)001:2889: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2890: man ngag gis rtogs par bya ba nges pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:2891: gyi snying po gsang ba dam pa 'di nyid ma
NK091(ke)001:2892: dad pa dang yid gnyis dang le lo'i dbang gis
NK091(ke)001:2894: da yong nges don zab mo gang la gzung bar bgyi zhes gdung zhing dris pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2899: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2900: mchod pa'i gnas dang yid mos pa'i rten du gyur
NK091(ke)001:2901: pa ston pa 'gro ba'i mgon po nyid mi bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:2902: na / bsod nams kyi gnas sku gdung ring bsrel
NK091(ke)001:2903: 'byung ngam mi 'byung ji ltar 'gyur zhig gu zhes
NK091(ke)001:2906: slad kyis mchod gnas ci la bgyi //
NK091(ke)001:2908: gal te ring bsrel ma byung na slad kyis gus
NK091(ke)001:2909: pas mchod gnas ci la bgyi zhes gdung zhing dris
NK091(ke)001:2914: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2915: da ltar zhing 'dir ston pa 'das pa'i 'og tu
NK091(ke)001:2916: ston pa'i gdung 'tshob nus pa'i rgyal tshab kyi skyes
NK091(ke)001:2917: bu dam pa 'byung bar 'gyur ram zhes dris shing
NK091(ke)001:2918: zhus te / e ma'o kyi hud e ma'o blong /
NK091(ke)001:2919: zhes yongs su gdung ba bton to //
NK091(ke)001:2921: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:2922: gsang sngags yongs grags su ma byung ba'i thog mar
NK091(ke)001:2923: bshad pa'i rgyud kyi gleng gzhi'i rgyur gyur pa dman
NK091(ke)001:2924: pas mi spobs pas dam pasa gdung ba bton pa'i
NK091(ke)001:2925: le'u ste gsum pa rnam par bshad pa'o ////gnyis pa
NK091(ke)001:2926: la gnyis te / rgyal ba rnams kyis gsang bdag la bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:2927: gsang bdag gis zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:2929: gdung ba gsan nas lcang lo can du 'dus pa /
NK091(ke)001:2930: sngon dam bcas pa'i sgo nas gdung ba sol zhig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:2931: mthun pa'i 'du shes bsgyur la sngags la khod cig par bskul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:2936: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2938: de ltar gdung ba gsan pas de nyid sel bar
NK091(ke)001:2939: bgro ba mdzad nas ston pa phyag na rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:2940: la bskul ba'i rkyen du gyur pa'i don bstan pa'i
NK091(ke)001:2941: phyir de skad smras te gdung ba bton pa las
NK091(ke)001:2942: srid pa gsum gyi 'gro ba ma lus pa la
NK091(ke)001:2943: phan 'dogs pa'i gnyen gcig pa lta bur gyur pa'i
NK091(ke)001:2944: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba grangs mang la mi dpogs pas
NK091(ke)001:2945: rgya mtsho lta bu rnams kyis gsan nas snying rje
NK091(ke)001:2946: gsum dbyer med pa'i rang gi ngo bo mngon du
NK091(ke)001:2947: gyur pas snying rje'i bdag po de dag kun kyang
NK091(ke)001:2950: de las lcang lo can gyi gnas //
NK091(ke)001:2951: kun gzigs rnam par snang mdzad kyis //
NK091(ke)001:2952: 'di nyid gzung bas rigs lngar smin //
NK091(ke)001:2953: zhes gsungs pa ltar nges kyang /
NK091(ke)001:2955: nyan thos med cing gnod sbyin gos sngon can rnams
NK091(ke)001:2956: gdul bas lcang lo can gyi pho brang nyid du
NK091(ke)001:2957: gshegs te gsang ba'i bdag po'i bzhugs gnas su 'dus
NK091(ke)001:2958: par gyur to // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:2962: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2963: de nas phyogs bcu'i rgyal bas gsang bdag la bskul ba chen po 'di skad ces gsungs te /
NK091(ke)001:2964: gsang ba pa yi bdag po khyod kyis dang po
NK091(ke)001:2965: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i dus na 'gro
NK091(ke)001:2966: ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar dam bcas pas sngon gyi
NK091(ke)001:2967: go cha bsgos pa yal lam ci de bas na
NK091(ke)001:2968: 'jig rten gyi sdug bsngal rnams brtson pa dang dam
NK091(ke)001:2969: bcas kyi go cha gyon pa khyod kyis mi shes
NK091(ke)001:2970: sama zhes thugs dam gnad nas bskul te thugs snying
NK091(ke)001:2971: rje'i mnga' bdag khyod nyid 'dzam bu'i gling gi mi
NK091(ke)001:2972: yul gyi sa ri ma la ya la babs nas
NK091(ke)001:2973: kyang / gsang sngags bgros te 'jig rten dang dam
NK091(ke)001:2974: pa'i rigs can rnams kyi gdung ba bsal ba'i rigsa
NK091(ke)001:2980: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:2981: bdud dang mu stegs log pa'i tshogs btul ba la
NK091(ke)001:2982: gdul bya so so'i rigas kyi cha dang mthun par
NK091(ke)001:2983: bzung nas rdo rje'i rigs kyis dri za /
NK091(ke)001:2984: rin chen rigs kyis gshin rje 'dul ba la sogs
NK091(ke)001:2985: pa ma rungsa pa dag kun thabs 'dzud bsre ba
NK091(ke)001:2986: dang cha mthun sbyor bas btul te /
NK091(ke)001:2988: 'dod pa rang rkyen dang bkri drang brgyud pa'i sgo
NK091(ke)001:2989: nas rang rang gi 'dod tshul dang mthun par khrid
NK091(ke)001:2990: nas don dam nges pa'i thabas su gsung gi sgron
NK091(ke)001:2991: ma tshig gi gsang ba rnams kyis mtshon zhing /
NK091(ke)001:2992: thabs 'dzud bsre ba'i las kyi cha dang mthun 'jug gi spyod pa dang tshul mthun par sbyar te /
NK091(ke)001:2993: gdul bya'i rgyud kyi 'du shes yang dag par bsgyur ba byas nas ni /
NK091(ke)001:2994: gsang sngags theg pa mchog gi bka' yi bgro ba
NK091(ke)001:2995: bstan pa dam pa de nyid bshad de tshul bzhin
NK091(ke)001:2996: du don go ba la sbyar bar byas nas yang
NK091(ke)001:2997: dag pa'i don gsang sngags kyi lam dang 'bras bu
NK091(ke)001:2998: la dgoda par byed pa'i thabs mchog mdzad par rigas
NK091(ke)001:2999: so // zhes de skad rgyal ba rnams kyis rnam par bskul ba las /
NK091(ke)001:3002: sprul pas lung bstan pa ltar gsung bar zhal gyis bzhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:3003: ri ma la yar sngar gyi rgyal ba ltar bskul ba'i tshe zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3008: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3009: mdor bstan pa'i tshul gyis dpa' bo rdo rje 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:3010: rgyal po zhes gsungs pa nyid tshig gsum gyis rgyas
NK091(ke)001:3011: par bshad de / bdud la sogs pa gdul bar
NK091(ke)001:3012: daka'a ba rnams 'dus ba'i thabs la mkhas shing log
NK091(ke)001:3013: pa'i dpung tshogs ma lus pa bcom pa'i mthu mnga'
NK091(ke)001:3015: 'khor ba'i dgra dpung bsnyil bar mdzad pas 'jig rten
NK091(ke)001:3016: kun gyi nyon mongs bag chags dang bcas pa las
NK091(ke)001:3017: rgyal ba'i mchog tu gyur pa /
NK091(ke)001:3018: rgyal ba kun gyis gsang ba'i bdag por dbang bskur
NK091(ke)001:3019: ba'i rtags su rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin pas rdo
NK091(ke)001:3020: rje can nam rdo rje 'dzin pa zhes su grags
NK091(ke)001:3021: pa de nyid / bdag don gyi dgongs pa mthar
NK091(ke)001:3022: phyin nas thugs rjes gzhan don la bskul bas dgyes
NK091(ke)001:3023: pa de nyid / shing / don gyi gdan dgongs
NK091(ke)001:3024: pa mi g.yo ba'am rtags kyi gdan las bzhengs nas
NK091(ke)001:3025: pa de nyid / shing / ni / stobs bcu
NK091(ke)001:3026: mnga' ba'i rtags su phyogs bzhir gom pa bcu bcu
NK091(ke)001:3027: dor bas sa g.yo ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:3029: 'od kyis snang ba dag par byas shing thams cad snod du rung bar byas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3030: 'od thams cad tshur bsdus pa la sogs pa cho
NK091(ke)001:3031: 'phrul chen po kun tu bstan nas byin rlabs snang
NK091(ke)001:3032: bar mdzad de / srin po dang klu la sogs
NK091(ke)001:3033: pa 'jig rten log pa'i gtso bo dam pa'i rigs
NK091(ke)001:3034: bar mdzad de / can rnams / sngags kyi skal
NK091(ke)001:3035: ba dang ldan par sprul pas lung bstan pa bzhin
NK091(ke)001:3036: du tshogs bsags pas las dag pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3037: rgyud sbyangs pas skal ba phun sum tshogs par rab tu ldan pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:3038: rgyal ba rnam 'dren dam pas gsang sngags phyis 'byung
NK091(ke)001:3039: bar lung bstan pa'i tshul dang mthun par sngags kyi
NK091(ke)001:3040: don la longs spyod pas bsod nams chen po dang
NK091(ke)001:3041: skal ba chen po nges par ldan pa'i 'khor rnams
NK091(ke)001:3043: thub pa sprul pa'i sku yis byung tshul bcu gnyis
NK091(ke)001:3044: dang gdams ngag gsum bka' stsal pas rtsa rgyud gsungs
NK091(ke)001:3045: te / de dag gi don gsal bar phyis su
NK091(ke)001:3046: bshad rgyud kyis bstan par ji ltar lung bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:3047: bzhin du da lta'i dus deng 'dir nges par bab
NK091(ke)001:3048: te / kyis / gsang sngags kyis brjod bya don
NK091(ke)001:3049: gyi mtshan nyid 'khor ba nyid ma spang bar chos
NK091(ke)001:3050: nyid kyi snying por ye nas gnas par lung bstan
NK091(ke)001:3051: te / kyis / pa'i phyir / cho 'phrul bzhi'i
NK091(ke)001:3052: mnga' bdag phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams kyi byin rlabs
NK091(ke)001:3053: kyis bshad pa ltar spyir gsang sngags thams cad dang
NK091(ke)001:3054: khyad par du sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus
NK091(ke)001:3055: pas bstan pa'i snying po dam pa rmad du byung
NK091(ke)001:3056: ba zhig sngar phyag na rdo rje bdag gis rgyal
NK091(ke)001:3057: ba kun las thos pa bzhi'i tshul du thos nas
NK091(ke)001:3058: ji ltar bshad cing bstan pa de nyid da ltar
NK091(ke)001:3059: yang lung bstan pa bzhin du /
NK091(ke)001:3060: skal ldan rigs can lnga la sogs pa la bgro bar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:3063: ma brgyud bdag gis mngon sum du //
NK091(ke)001:3064: thos tsam tshad mar mi rung bas //
NK091(ke)001:3065: nges par bshad de bstan pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:3066: sdud pa dgongs pa cig chod yin //
NK091(ke)001:3068: yang na sngar gyi sprul pa'i sku rnams kyis ji
NK091(ke)001:3069: ltar bshad cing gsang sngags phyis 'byung bar lung bstan
NK091(ke)001:3070: pa bzhin du zhes sbyar bar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:3075: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3078: gcan gzan sna tshogs kyi 'khra sa /
NK091(ke)001:3079: rtse la gnam lcags kyi thog yod pas re zhig
NK091(ke)001:3080: rten can gyi mtshan rten la btags te mtshan la
NK091(ke)001:3081: drag shul can zhes bya bar grags pa'i ri /
NK091(ke)001:3082: tha mal gyis bgrod dka' bas dgon pa chen po'i gnas shin tu dben pa 'di ni /
NK091(ke)001:3083: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa ye shes kyi
NK091(ke)001:3084: snying po can rnams kyi theg pa chen po gsang
