NK091(ke)001:3085: ba de nyid 'byung ba'i gnas su thog ma dang
NK091(ke)001:3086: tha ma'i dus med par rgyal ba dam pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:3087: kyis ri'i yon tan basngagasa pa yin te rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:3088: gdan dang 'dra bar mi 'jig par gsang sngags nas
NK091(ke)001:3090: de ltar thog ma dang tha ma med pa yi
NK091(ke)001:3091: rgyal ba dpag tu med pa'i bstan pa la gsang
NK091(ke)001:3092: sngags 'byung ba'ang 'di lta bu'i gnas su ston par
NK091(ke)001:3093: gsungs pas / sa 'dzin dben pa dam pa'i dgon gnas chen po der bstan par bya la /
NK091(ke)001:3094: ston pa po yang thog mtha' ril du rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:3095: ji snyed pas so so'i zhing khams kyi gnas su
NK091(ke)001:3096: sems kyi dkyil 'khor rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba
NK091(ke)001:3097: nyid me long gi gzugs brnyan bzhin du ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:3098: yongs rdzogs su ston pa'i gsang sngags theg pa'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:3099: po sprul pa de dag 'das pa'i rjes su 'byung
NK091(ke)001:3100: bar lung bstan pa de ltar rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK091(ke)001:3101: bdag gisa kyang dus 'di ru ma zad thog ma
NK091(ke)001:3102: dang tha ma med pa ru bskul ba'i dus ni
NK091(ke)001:3103: gang byung bar yang cho 'phrul gyis gsang sngags bstan
NK091(ke)001:3105: da lta'i dus 'dir yang bskul ba po byung bas
NK091(ke)001:3106: bdag kyang sngar gyi bkod pa de bzhin du cho
NK091(ke)001:3107: 'phrul dang bcas te snang bar mdzad de ston par
NK091(ke)001:3108: byed do // zhes bgros te bka' stsal par zhal gyis 'ches so //
NK091(ke)001:3109: tshig 'di dag gis gsang bdag sangs rgyas nyid du gsal bar mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:3111: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:3112: dman pa'i lus can dam pa gang dag gi gdung
NK091(ke)001:3113: ba de dag rgyal ba ril dang gsang ba pos
NK091(ke)001:3114: sel bar bka' bgros pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3115: bskul bas zhal gyis 'ches pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa gsal bar bshad pa'o ////gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:3117: ston pa'i dris lan bye brag tu bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3120: byin rlabs rgyal po dzahl rmi ltas su shar ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:3125: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3127: gong du snyegs pas de nas 'dren pa'i zhal gyis
NK091(ke)001:3128: bzhes pa de tshe dus dang gnas de nyid du
NK091(ke)001:3129: / ston pa gnod 'dul rgyal pos de ltar gsungs nas /
NK091(ke)001:3130: gnas phun sum tshogs pa mi yi yul gyi gnas kyi 'jig rten gyi khams /
NK091(ke)001:3131: gling bzhi pa ji snyed pa las khyad par gyi
NK091(ke)001:3132: gnas mchog 'dzam bu'i gling gi bye brag drag shul
NK091(ke)001:3133: can zhes bya ba'i ri bo ma la yar grags
NK091(ke)001:3134: pa de ni / spyir gnod sbyin rnams 'du zhing
NK091(ke)001:3135: khyad par du ston pa gsang ba'i bdag po gnod
NK091(ke)001:3136: 'dul nyid byon te gsang sngags ston pa'i sa 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:3137: pa de ni / yin te / de lta bu'i
NK091(ke)001:3138: gsang sngags kyi chos 'dzin zhing rigsa kyi grub pa
NK091(ke)001:3139: brnyes pa'i chos kyi gnas dam pa phal pas mi
NK091(ke)001:3140: bgrod cing byin che la bkra shis shing nyams dga'
NK091(ke)001:3141: ba'i bsti gnas su thugs rje chen po'i shugs kyis
NK091(ke)001:3142: 'gro ba mang po gsang sngags kyis 'dul bas 'khor
NK091(ke)001:3143: ba'i gnas kyi sa de la mngon par sprul te
NK091(ke)001:3144: gshegs pas sku gdul bya'i ngor snang bar gyur to
NK091(ke)001:3145: pa de ni / yin te / // de'i byin
NK091(ke)001:3146: rlabs kyis phyi ltar sa dngos su g.yos shing nang
NK091(ke)001:3147: gi sa rnams 'og nas gong du 'phar bas yongs
NK091(ke)001:3149: 'og tu gleng bslang nas 'byung ba ltar rmad du
NK091(ke)001:3150: byung ba'i cho 'phrul rnams kyis phyi zhing khams rnam
NK091(ke)001:3151: par dag par byas shing nang du ting nge 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:3152: bskyed de gdul bya'i rtog sgrib thamsa cad sbyangs te
NK091(ke)001:3153: don gsang mchog bde ba chen por gsal bar snang
NK091(ke)001:3154: bar gyur to // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:3158: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3159: sngon thub pa'i dbang po nyid sku ma 'das par bzhugs pa'i dus nyid du /
NK091(ke)001:3160: gsang sngags theg pa chen po rgyal po 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:3161: la snang bar 'gyur ba'i lung bstan thob pas skal
NK091(ke)001:3162: ba mchog dang ldan pa can /
NK091(ke)001:3163: lus 'gro ba dman pa'i mi lus 'dzin kyang sems
NK091(ke)001:3164: gsang sngags rtogs pas dam pa'i rigsa su nges pa
NK091(ke)001:3165: / mi rigs bzhi las mchog tu gyur pa rgyal
NK091(ke)001:3166: po'i rigsa can ya rab kyi ngang tshul khrel bag
NK091(ke)001:3167: dang ldan pas d+r+wa ma che ba'am chen po /
NK091(ke)001:3168: rgyal bu dzahzhesa bya ba de la rgyal bas lung
NK091(ke)001:3169: bstan dang gsang sngags kyi gleng gzhi 'tshogs pa'i byin
NK091(ke)001:3170: rlabs kyis sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa sogs bdun
NK091(ke)001:3171: po rnams rmi lam gyi ltas su shar te snang
NK091(ke)001:3172: ngo // rgyal po 'di la brgya byin bu zhes kyang bya gsung /
NK091(ke)001:3180: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3181: gsang sngags 'byung ba'i gleng gzhi 'tshogs nas ston pa
NK091(ke)001:3182: mthong ba de yi tshe lang ka la sogs pa
NK091(ke)001:3184: gdung tshig gi don yod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3186: gsang sngags 'byung bar shes nas sems dga' ba dang
NK091(ke)001:3187: bcas te ston pa yin min gyi the tshom skyes
NK091(ke)001:3188: te / ston pa gang yin ngo shes par bya
NK091(ke)001:3189: ba'i phyir spobs pa chen po'i dri ba drug dris
NK091(ke)001:3190: te / te / dam pa'i tshul gyis e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad re che ste /
NK091(ke)001:3191: skyes bu chen po khyod kyi ngo bo su zhig yin /
NK091(ke)001:3193: nyid kyi lam gang ltar las byung ba lags /
NK091(ke)001:3194: rten ganga la brten nas byon sa gang du byon pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3195: don gyi ched ka ci yi phyir du byon zhes dri ba dris so //
NK091(ke)001:3197: drug po'i lan so sor sbyar te 'khrugs sdeb kyis gsal bar bshad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3198: go rim bzhin du ston pas mdun bsus te gleng
NK091(ke)001:3199: slang ba yan chad don bcu bdun gyi lo rgyus
NK091(ke)001:3200: zhib tu brjod de khri 'ur du lan gdab tshul
NK091(ke)001:3201: gnyis las / dang po la drug ste /
NK091(ke)001:3202: su yin gyi lan rdo rje sems dpa' srid gsum gyi gnyen po yin pa /
NK091(ke)001:3203: gang nas byon gyi lan stong pa chen po 'khor 'das dbyer med nas byon pa /
NK091(ke)001:3204: gang ltar byung ba'i lan nyid dang shul gnyis kyi sgo nas gdab pa /
NK091(ke)001:3205: gang la brten gyi lan bla ma dang theg chen la brten nas 'ong ba /
NK091(ke)001:3206: gang du byon gyi lan dge sdig 'dres mar spyod pa'i 'dod khams su byon pa /
NK091(ke)001:3207: don ched kyi lan 'khor gyi sems nyid btsal ba'i ched du byon pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3212: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3213: cho 'phrul gyi bdag nyid gsang bdag chen pos 'di skad ces lan du brjod de /
NK091(ke)001:3214: bdag don gyi ngo bo nga ni mtha' yi rtog pa cis kyang mi bskyod de /
NK091(ke)001:3215: dpal nyon mongs pas mi 'khrugs pa rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ba yin la /
NK091(ke)001:3216: gzhan don mdzad pa'i ngo bo thugs snying rjes g.yo
NK091(ke)001:3217: zhing bskyod pas na srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gcig
NK091(ke)001:3218: dang skyabs mgon chen po yin no //
NK091(ke)001:3220: stong pa chen po nga yi yul //
NK091(ke)001:3223: mun snang gnyis kyi khams nas 'ongs //
NK091(ke)001:3224: zhes pa'i rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3225: don gyi 'og min rnam pa kun gyi mchog dang
NK091(ke)001:3226: ldan pa'i stong pa chen po ni nga yi yul
NK091(ke)001:3227: yin te / mun pa 'khor ba dang snang ba
NK091(ke)001:3228: myang 'das gnyis su dbye ba med pa'i chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:3229: dbyings kyi zhing khams nas 'dir 'ongs pa yin no
NK091(ke)001:3230: yin te / // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:3231: nyid rang gang ltar byung na rdo rje'i rigs thabs dang shes rab gnyis med las byung ba /
NK091(ke)001:3237: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3238: gnyis su med pas mi phyed pa rdo rje rigs chen dam pa ni nga yi gdung yin la /
NK091(ke)001:3239: pha ni rig pa'i ye shes ma 'gag pas thabs mchog dpag tu med pa yin zhing /
NK091(ke)001:3240: ma ni dbyings kyi chos nyid ma skyes pas shes rab brjod pa las 'das pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:3242: nyid kyis chos nyid ma rtogs pa'i lo rgyus /
NK091(ke)001:3243: nyid kyi bla mas tshol cig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:3244: ji ltar btsal ba'i thabs zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:3245: thabs kyi mchog gi lam bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:3246: bstan pa bzhin bgrod pas gzhan nas ma byung bar rang las rnyed par bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3251: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3252: bskal pa kun dga' lta bu thog ma med pa'i dus kyii tshe /
NK091(ke)001:3253: nga yi rgyun du mi 'bral bar 'chang ba'i yid
NK091(ke)001:3254: bzhin gyi nor bu byang chub kyi sems stor te
NK091(ke)001:3255: / ma rtogs kyang dgos pa 'byung bas nor bu
NK091(ke)001:3256: rin chen rtogs na nyon mongs 'joms pas bdud rtsi
NK091(ke)001:3257: de nyid rang la yod par ma shes kyang stor
NK091(ke)001:3258: bar tshor ba de yi tshe byang sems kyi che
NK091(ke)001:3259: ba'i yon tan med pas kun nas dbul zhing ltogs
NK091(ke)001:3260: / pa dang / 'khor ba las thar ba med
NK091(ke)001:3261: par sdug bsngal gyi nad dang nyon mongs rnams kyis
NK091(ke)001:3263: nyi ma dang 'dra ba'i gsang sngags rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi dben pas mun pa /
NK091(ke)001:3264: zla ba dang 'dra bar theg pa chen po'i shes
NK091(ke)001:3265: rab kyi dben pas mun nag /skar ma dang 'dra
NK091(ke)001:3266: ba'i theg dman gyi shes rab kyi dben pas smag
NK091(ke)001:3268: thar pa'i lam du bgrod par bya ba'i lam yang stor te /
NK091(ke)001:3269: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyis gdung bar gyur kyang de nyid ji ltar yin pa ni ma shes so //
NK091(ke)001:3274: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3275: dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu lta bu /
NK091(ke)001:3276: de yi tshe nga yi bshes gnyen mchog tu gyur
NK091(ke)001:3277: pa rdo rje sems dpa' zhes su grags pa'i byams
NK091(ke)001:3278: mgon dam pa zhig gisa 'di skad bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3279: e ma'o khyod kyis ci zhig nor bu rin po che rang la yod par mi shes sam /
NK091(ke)001:3280: mthong ba tshe 'di dang phyi ma phan chad yun
NK091(ke)001:3281: gyi dus kun tu bde ba mchog nyid ster ba
NK091(ke)001:3282: yi ngo bo rtogs na 'bras bu rgya che zhing
NK091(ke)001:3283: myur du phan pas don srid chen po zhar byung
NK091(ke)001:3284: du 'byung bar 'gyur ba' nor bu rin chen byang
NK091(ke)001:3285: chub kyi sems de ma brlag gama /
NK091(ke)001:3286: 'on te rang la chos nyid du yod par mi shes sam /
NK091(ke)001:3287: 'di ci zhig rigs chad pa yin par 'dug gam ci ste /
NK091(ke)001:3288: des na ma 'dug par tshol zhig pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3289: de skad bshes gnyen mchog des bdag la sbran no //
NK091(ke)001:3293: lung ston cig /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3294: de yi tshe gsang bdag nga yisa slar lan sbran
NK091(ke)001:3295: pa don srid chen po 'byung bar gyur pa de
NK091(ke)001:3296: nyid rang la yod par ma shes kyang stor bar
NK091(ke)001:3298: 'di nyid dang 'phrad par bya ba'i thabsa kun gyi
NK091(ke)001:3299: mchog tu gyur pa zhig ston pa bshes gnyen khyod
NK091(ke)001:3300: kyis lung ston par mdzod cig ces zhus so //
NK091(ke)001:3305: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3306: de nas ston pa dam pa de yisa rang la
NK091(ke)001:3307: yod pa mngon par 'byung ba'i shes rab kyi dmigs
NK091(ke)001:3308: bu bstan pa / de dang myur du 'phrad par 'dod pa nyid na /
NK091(ke)001:3309: btsal bar bya ba'i thabs la shes rab gsum gyis brtson par bya dgos te /
NK091(ke)001:3310: ston pa'am bshes gnyen lta bu sa mkhan dam pasa
NK091(ke)001:3311: shes rab zab mo'i dmigsa rkyen rgyal ba'i dgongs pa
NK091(ke)001:3312: gsal bar ston zhing sems kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin
NK091(ke)001:3313: pa mtshon pas lung la brten te /
NK091(ke)001:3314: mun pa 'khor ba dang snang ba 'das pa'i khams
NK091(ke)001:3315: dang byang chub sems dpa'i zag med kyi rigs sa
NK091(ke)001:3316: khams nyid dang / theg pa sna tshogs kyi lam
NK091(ke)001:3317: rnams bgrod par byas nas btsal bar byas kyang gzhan
NK091(ke)001:3318: gang nas kyang mi rnyed de /
NK091(ke)001:3319: rang gi rigs kyi sa khams sems nyid rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:3320: gyis 'od gsal bar rang gis rig nas rang las
NK091(ke)001:3321: 'byung bar 'gyur te rang snang nyid du grol bas
NK091(ke)001:3322: so // de ltar rnyed pa ni sems kyi rin
NK091(ke)001:3323: chen rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid ji bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:3324: sngar rnyed par gyur pa'i 'das pa'i sangs rgyas dam
NK091(ke)001:3325: pa rnams kyi chos nyid dbyings kyi khyim yin te
NK091(ke)001:3326: so // / de nyid ni sngar rnyed par gyur
NK091(ke)001:3327: pa yi rnyed pa zin pa ji snyed pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:3328: kyi rnyed pa'i gnas rang gi sems nyid kho na
NK091(ke)001:3331: de skad thos nas de tshe ngas //
NK091(ke)001:3337: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3338: de skad ston pas bka' stsal pa thos nas de tshe gsang ba'i bdag po ngas /
NK091(ke)001:3339: 'khor ba'i gcan 'phrang skye rga na 'chi bzhi'am /
NK091(ke)001:3343: sdug bsngal gyi chu bo bzhi brgal te /
NK091(ke)001:3344: theg pa sna tshogs kyi lam rnams bgrod cing kun tu btsal nas /
NK091(ke)001:3345: 'dren pa dam pa sangs rgyas rnams kyi lam du zhugs shing /
NK091(ke)001:3346: sa bcu dang rnam par thar pa bzhi'am brgyad kyi lam bgrod de /
NK091(ke)001:3347: mya ngan las 'das pa'i grong khyer bsnyags te nor
NK091(ke)001:3348: bu rin chen byang chub kyi sems de nyid ji
NK091(ke)001:3349: ltar rnyed pa'i thabs la 'bad de rtsad bcad par
NK091(ke)001:3350: byas so // de ltar thabs sna tshogs la brtson pas sgo kun nas bsdur te btsal kyang /
NK091(ke)001:3351: lung chen rgyud kyi rgyal po'i dgongs don ltar gzhan
NK091(ke)001:3352: las ma byung zhing yul nas ma rnyed par rang
NK091(ke)001:3353: nyid kyi sems kyi chos nyid ye nas 'dus ma
NK091(ke)001:3354: byas pas che ba lnga dang ldan pa'i dbyings kyi
NK091(ke)001:3355: khyim nas rnyed de che ba'i yon tan rnams lhun
NK091(ke)001:3356: gyis grub bo // de ltar rnyed pa nyid na
NK091(ke)001:3357: yang dngos po ngos bzung can du rnyed pa med
NK091(ke)001:3358: gyis grub bo // de / stor ba nyid na'ang
NK091(ke)001:3359: gting nas gzhan du stor bral du gyur pa med
NK091(ke)001:3360: gyis grub bo // de / do // 'o na
NK091(ke)001:3361: stor rnyed du brjod pa ji lta bu zhe na
NK091(ke)001:3362: gyis grub bo // de / do // / ngo
NK091(ke)001:3363: bo ye ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid gang du'ang ma
NK091(ke)001:3364: grub pas yod pa min zhing /
NK091(ke)001:3365: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub par kun tu 'od gsal
NK091(ke)001:3366: bas med pa min la rtsa ba gnyis su med
NK091(ke)001:3367: pas byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la stor rnyed
NK091(ke)001:3368: gnyis su yod pa mina kyang /
NK091(ke)001:3369: gzhan nas ma byung bar rang las byung bar ngo shes pa la rnyed ces btags shing /
NK091(ke)001:3370: ngo ma shes pa la stor zhes pa'i tha snyad btags par zad do //
NK091(ke)001:3371: des na dang po yod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3373: tha ma rnyed pa'i dus gsum gyi rang bzhin mthong
NK091(ke)001:3374: tshe gzhi rtsa dang bral bas thog ma med pa'i
NK091(ke)001:3375: dus nas so // zhes gsungs te /
NK091(ke)001:3376: a nu'i rang lugs mdo chen po'i dgongs pa thun mong min pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:3377: 'di dag gi spyi rgya gcod na /
NK091(ke)001:3378: ye ji bzhin pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' chos rnams
NK091(ke)001:3379: kyi chos nyid de bzhin nyid ma nor ma bcos
NK091(ke)001:3380: ma bslad pa snying po byang chub tu ye nas
NK091(ke)001:3381: gnas pa la btags pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3382: rgyud dag pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' sems can kun
NK091(ke)001:3383: gyi sems kyi chos nyid ji bzhin du mthong ba'i
NK091(ke)001:3384: skabs la btags pa'i tshul gyis gong 'og kun dang
NK091(ke)001:3390: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3391: ston pa'am bla ma dam pa de la lam gyi
NK091(ke)001:3392: gzhir re ltos bcas te brten zhing rang gis zhi
NK091(ke)001:3393: gnas dang lhag mthong gi blo gros dam pas nges
NK091(ke)001:3394: par the tshom rnams bcad de lta ba rtogs par
NK091(ke)001:3395: bya nas / theg chen gsang mchog rgyal po'i cang
NK091(ke)001:3396: shes kyi rta de la don nyams su len pas
NK091(ke)001:3397: zhon cing brten te 'dir 'ong ba yin no //
NK091(ke)001:3402: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3403: de ltar chos nyid bsam brjod las 'das shing spros pa med pa de'i ngang las /
NK091(ke)001:3404: sprul pa thub pa'i dbang po snang nas 'das pa'i dus 'dir ni /
NK091(ke)001:3405: sdig pa spyod pas mun pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3406: dge ba spyod pas snang ba gnyis 'dres mar spyod
NK091(ke)001:3407: pas 'dod pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams ma la ya
NK091(ke)001:3410: gang tshe btsal ba'i ched phyir du //
NK091(ke)001:3412: dus gang gi tshe 'khor rnams kyis sems nyid stor
NK091(ke)001:3413: ba de btsal ba la zhugs pa na thabs dam
NK091(ke)001:3414: pas mtshon te rnyed par 'gyur ba'i dgos ched khyad
NK091(ke)001:3415: par can gyi phyir du 'ongs pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:3416: de ltar bshad pa ni 'grel pa lung bstan ma'i lugs so //
NK091(ke)001:3417: gnyis pa rkyen gleng bslang ba la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:3418: ston pas mdun bsus te gleng bslang ba /
NK091(ke)001:3419: 'khor gyis gus pas dris te gleng bslang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:3421: thabs bcu gcig gi sgo nas don byed pas nyid la 'dun zhig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:3423: dang po la bcu gcig ste /
NK091(ke)001:3433: lde mig /bka' yi 'grel pa'i sgo nas don byed pas nyid la 'dun zhig par bskul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:3437: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3438: 'di dag re re la'ang zhal bzhes dang gdams ngag gsum gsum du sbyar te /
NK091(ke)001:3439: ston pa nga ni thabs kyi bdag po mnyan pa'am gru makhana te /
NK091(ke)001:3440: gang zhig 'khor ba'i skye rga na 'chi ba'i bzhi'i chu bo mtha' med pa las /
NK091(ke)001:3441: srid gsum gyi sems can rnams phrin las kyis bsgral bar dam bcas kyis /
NK091(ke)001:3442: thar pa dang grol bar 'dod pa rnams gdams ngag gi lam 'dir shog cig /gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:3445: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3446: nga ni thabs kyi dbang phyug mig 'byed makhana te
NK091(ke)001:3447: 'jig rten gyi shes rab dang bral bas long ba
NK091(ke)001:3448: dpag tu med pa rnams kyi ma rig pa'i ling
NK091(ke)001:3449: tog basla bar dam bcas kyis /
NK091(ke)001:3450: gang zhig ma bcos pa'i don mthong bar 'doda pa rnams lam 'dir shog cig /gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:3453: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3454: nga ni thabs kyi mnga' bdag sman pa mchog ste /
NK091(ke)001:3455: khams gsum mam grong khyer gsum gyi dug gsum gyis mnar ba'i nada pa rnams /
NK091(ke)001:3456: thog ma med pa'i rnam rtog gi gcong rnying sbyang bar dam bcas kyis /
NK091(ke)001:3457: gang zhig nad med bde bar 'dod pa rnams lam 'dir shog cig /bzhi pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:3460: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3461: nga ni thabs kyi 'dren pa sa lam mkhan te /
NK091(ke)001:3462: 'gro ba lam phyin ci log tu gol nas yang dag pa'i lam stor ba rnams /
NK091(ke)001:3463: ma nor ba'i lam du khrid par dam bcas kyisa /
NK091(ke)001:3464: gsang ba sngags kyi yang dag pa'i nye lam 'dod pa rnams lam 'dir shog cig /lnga pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:3467: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3468: nga ni thugs rje chen po'i spyan ras kyi gzigs pas so pa mkhan te /
NK091(ke)001:3469: 'khor ba'i dgra dpung bdag 'dzin las nyon gyi 'jigsa pa las /
NK091(ke)001:3470: gdul bya thams cad bskyab par dam bcas kyis /
NK091(ke)001:3471: srid pa'i 'jigsa pa dang bral bar 'dod pa rnams lam 'dira shog cig /drug pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:3474: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3475: nga ni theg pa'i rgyal po'i rdo rje'i rdzong mkhar chen po ste /
NK091(ke)001:3476: 'khor ba'i g.yul chen byings chags pa'i damga dpung lasa
NK091(ke)001:3477: 'gro ba'i 'jigs pas mi tshugs pa'i thabs kyi 'khra
NK091(ke)001:3479: gang zhig snying po byang chub kyi mkhar rdzong 'dod pa rnams lam 'dir shog cig /bdun pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:3482: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3483: nga ni thabs kyi mdzod 'dzin tshong dpon chen po ste /
NK091(ke)001:3484: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la ji ltar spyod kyang 'dod pa rgya mtshos mi ngoms pa rnams la /
NK091(ke)001:3485: chos kyi gtera chen gcig gis 'dod rgu thams cad sbyin par dam bcas kyis /
NK091(ke)001:3486: gang zhig rang gnas sems kyi gter la spyod par
NK091(ke)001:3487: 'dod pa rnams lam 'dir shog cig /brgyad pa ni
NK091(ke)001:3490: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3491: nga ni thabs kyi gsal byed sgron ma dam pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:3492: 'khor ba'i gnas su lhan cig skyes pa'i mun nag
NK091(ke)001:3493: dang kun tu brtags pa'i smag tu 'phyan nas las
NK091(ke)001:3495: kun tu rmongs pa'i mun nag bsal bar dam bcas kyis /
NK091(ke)001:3496: gang zhig rang rig ye shes kyi snang ba 'dod pa rnams lam 'dir shog cig /dgu pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:3499: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3500: nga ni gang 'dod 'byung ba'i yida bzhin gyi nor bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:3501: gang dag byang chub sems kyi yid bzhin gyi nor bu rnyed par 'dod pa rnams kyi /
NK091(ke)001:3502: yid bzhin du 'dod pa bskang ste lung gis ston par dam bcas kyis /
NK091(ke)001:3503: yon tan lhun gyis grub par 'dod pa rnams lam 'dir shog cig /bcu pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:3506: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3507: nga ni bka'a yi gsang sgo 'byed pa'i 'phrul gyi lde'u mig ste /
NK091(ke)001:3508: bka' yi mdzod sgrom rnams kyi sgo lcags lta bu'i
NK091(ke)001:3509: lung gi tha ram gasnga ba rnams ma nor bar
NK091(ke)001:3510: rnam par 'byed par dam bcas kyis /
NK091(ke)001:3511: gang zhig dka' gnad khrol nas rgyud grol bar 'doda
NK091(ke)001:3512: pa rnams lam 'dira shog cig /bcu gcig pa ni
NK091(ke)001:3515: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3516: ston pa nga ni bka' yi nges don gsal ba'i 'grel pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:3517: thub pa'i gsung gi glegs bam zaba mo rgyud lung gi po ti rnams /
NK091(ke)001:3518: ji bzhin du nges par dgrol bar dam bcas kyis /
NK091(ke)001:3519: gang dag ma nor bar shes par 'dod pa rnams lam 'dir shog cig /gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:3520: lam la brtson par gdams pa /
NK091(ke)001:3521: bka' grags par 'gyur bar gdams pa /
NK091(ke)001:3522: gdung ba ma bskyed cig par gdams pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3526: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3527: khams gsum chos nyid du dag pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3528: gzung 'dzin gnyis med du dag pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3529: lam gyis rtsol ba thams cad theg pa 'dir dag pas /
NK091(ke)001:3530: rnam pa tha dad pa kun chos dbyings gsang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:3531: ngo bor dag pas lam chen 'di la gnas pa
NK091(ke)001:3532: kun gzhi lam gyi nyes pa las nges par sgrol
NK091(ke)001:3533: bas rgyud lung man ngag gi gsang mdzod chen po
NK091(ke)001:3534: 'dira skal ldan gang zhig su yang rung ba zhugs
NK091(ke)001:3535: par gyur pa rnams la byang chub kyi sems nor
NK091(ke)001:3536: bu rin chen 'od 'bar ba de nyid nges par
NK091(ke)001:3537: rang sems las 'char bar 'gyur gyis 'di la brtson
NK091(ke)001:3539: de ltar rang rig byang chub kyi sems 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:3540: ni sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:3541: kyi ngo bo chos thams cad kyi me long yin
NK091(ke)001:3542: pas ji bzhin du mthong ste mngon gsum du gasla
NK091(ke)001:3543: bar rtogs pa de ma thag nas dman pa 'gro
NK091(ke)001:3544: ba'i lus la sems sangs rgyas su gyur pa yin
NK091(ke)001:3546: rtogs pa'i blo dang gang ldan pa //
NK091(ke)001:3547: bud med bu yang rgyal ba'i sras //
NK091(ke)001:3548: ko ba'i stan yang seng ge'i khri //
NK091(ke)001:3549: 'gro ba'i lus la sangs rgyas yin //
NK091(ke)001:3555: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3556: lung thams cad kyi spyi 'grel rdo rje gasnga ba
NK091(ke)001:3557: chen po rgyud kun gyi rgyal po gasnga ba bka'
NK091(ke)001:3558: yi gzhi ma man ngag thams cad kyi rtsa ba
NK091(ke)001:3559: nges don dam pa'i mdzoda mchog gsum po rnams dus
NK091(ke)001:3560: 'dir rdo rje 'dzin pa bdag gis gdul bya rnams
NK091(ke)001:3561: la bgros te gsal bar bshad de lung chen theg
NK091(ke)001:3562: pa'i gsang mdzod la sbyar bas /
NK091(ke)001:3563: rgyal ba rnams la dgongs pas brgyud pa nyid /
NK091(ke)001:3564: lha tshangs pa gtsug phud dang mi dri med grags
NK091(ke)001:3565: pa la sogs pa yi rig 'dzin rnams la rig
NK091(ke)001:3566: pas brgyud nas rim par gang zag rnams la rna
NK091(ke)001:3567: bar brgyud de lha mi'i yul kun tu yongs su
NK091(ke)001:3573: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3574: lha dang mi'i 'jig rten na gdul bya thams cad
NK091(ke)001:3575: kyi rgyud la yod pas ma rig pa gnyis kyi
NK091(ke)001:3576: mun pa dang nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba ma lus
NK091(ke)001:3577: pa kun bsal bar byas nas sems kyi dkyil 'khor
NK091(ke)001:3578: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba rtogs par 'gyur bas
NK091(ke)001:3579: na khyed cag ci yi phyir gdung ba'i mun par
NK091(ke)001:3580: zhugs pa yin te gdung ba'i gzhi dang bral bas
NK091(ke)001:3581: so // gal te thub pa mya ngan las 'das pa la gdung ba yin no zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:3582: thub pa de ni rdo rje lta bu nam mkha'i
NK091(ke)001:3583: sku mnga' ba yin pas 'ad'a ba dang mi 'ad'a
NK091(ke)001:3584: ba'i spros pa mi mang'a ste chos kyi sku 'pho
NK091(ke)001:3585: 'gyur med pas nama mkha' bzhin yin na gdung ba
NK091(ke)001:3586: skyed pa rigs pa ma yin no //
NK091(ke)001:3587: de skad ces sprul pa'i zhal nas gsang ba'i sgra
NK091(ke)001:3588: byung ste ston pas mdun bsu ba'i gleng slong nyid
NK091(ke)001:3589: bka' stsal to // gnyis pa 'grel chen gyi dgongs
NK091(ke)001:3590: pa ltar ston pas don bcu bdun gyi lo rgyus
NK091(ke)001:3591: zhib tu brjod de lan khri'ura du gdab pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:3595: zhes pa'i bar ni dri ba dang po yin gyi lan te /
NK091(ke)001:3596: ston pa cho 'phrul gyi bdag nyid gsang bdag chen pos lan du /
NK091(ke)001:3598: nga ni cis kyang sogs rkang pa gnyis ni mtshan ci yin pa gsungs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3600: snying rjes sogs rkang pa gnyis ni thugs rje skyabs kyi bdag po yin pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3602: stong pa sogs rkang pa gcig ni bzhugs yul dang /
NK091(ke)001:3604: rdo rje sogs rkang gcig ni gdung ci yin pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3606: pha ni sogs rkang pa gcig gis yab bstan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3608: ma ni sogs rkang pa gcig gis yum bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3609: de nas bdun pa nas bcu gcig gi bar ni /
NK091(ke)001:3610: dri ba gsum pa gang ltar byung gi lan te /
NK091(ke)001:3615: zhes pa'i bar ni don ma rig pa'i lo rgyus dang /
NK091(ke)001:3620: zhes pa'i bar ni sems kyi don ma rtogs par mkhyen nas sdug bsngal brgyud par bstan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3622: bgrod par bya ba'i sogs rkang pa gnyis ni lam
NK091(ke)001:3623: brtsal bas ma rnyed pa'i lo rgyus gsungs pa dang
NK091(ke)001:3628: zhes pa'i bar ni dus der ston pa rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:3629: sems dpas bstan pa'i tshig gis sems kyi nor bu
NK091(ke)001:3630: rang la yod par mi shes na yal bar ma
NK091(ke)001:3631: 'dug cig bar bskul ba'i lo rgyus bkal stsal pa
NK091(ke)001:3636: zhes pa'i bar ni gsang ba po nyid kyis sems ji bzhin par rtogs pa'i thabs zhus pa na /
NK091(ke)001:3637: ston pas rang nyid las tshol zhig par gsungs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:3638: lo rgyus brjod pa ste shul gang ltar byung gi
NK091(ke)001:3640: bcu gnyis pa yis dri ba gsum gyi lan bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3641: dang po de skad thos nas /
NK091(ke)001:3644: zhes pa'i bar gyis dri ba bzhi pa gang la brten nas byon gyi lan gdab ste /
NK091(ke)001:3645: bka' gsang bdag nyid kyis thos pas ston pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:3646: la brten nas theg pa chen po'i sgor zhugs te
NK091(ke)001:3647: bgrod pas 'khor ba'i skye rga na 'chi bsgral zhing
NK091(ke)001:3648: / sgo kun nas bsdur te theg pa chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:3649: yang chen por zhugs nas bgrod de btsal bas byang
NK091(ke)001:3650: chub rang rig pa nyid las ma rnyed par rnyed
NK091(ke)001:3651: / de / ji lta ba'i 'bras bu thob pa med par thob nas byon pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:3652: zhes bla ma dang theg mchog rgyal por brten nas
NK091(ke)001:3653: snying po byang chub nyid mngon du byas pa gang
NK091(ke)001:3655: gnyis pa de ltar zhes rkang pa gcig gis dri
NK091(ke)001:3656: ba gnyis pa yul gang nas byon gyi lan bstan
NK091(ke)001:3657: te / ye ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid gang du'ang
NK091(ke)001:3658: ma grub pa nyid mngon du gyur te rang snang
NK091(ke)001:3659: lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang las byon pa yin no
NK091(ke)001:3660: te / // gsum pa sprul pa sogs /
NK091(ke)001:3661: rkang pa gnyis kyis dri ba lnga pa gang du byon gyi lan bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3662: thub pa'i dbang po sprul pa snang ba'i dus 'dir
NK091(ke)001:3663: dge sdig spyod pa'i gnas 'dir 'gro 'ong med par
NK091(ke)001:3666: nga ni thabs kyi zhes pa nas /
NK091(ke)001:3667: lam 'dir shog /ces pa'i bar gyis dri ba drug
NK091(ke)001:3668: pa don gyi ched ka ci la byon gyi lan
NK091(ke)001:3669: bstan te / 'gro ba bsgral ba'i ched du yon
NK091(ke)001:3670: tan bcu gcig dang ldan pa'i mdzad thabs bcu gcig
NK091(ke)001:3671: gis gdul bya thar bar bya ba'i phyir byon no
NK091(ke)001:3672: zhes lan gdab ste 'di nas bzung 'khor gyis ma
NK091(ke)001:3673: zhus par ston pas sbran nas gleng bslang ba'i don
NK091(ke)001:3674: gnyis las ston pas mdun bsu bar yang sbyar ro
NK091(ke)001:3679: zhes pa'i bar 'adi'ang dri ba tha ma'i lan te /
NK091(ke)001:3680: theg pa chen po 'dir su zhugs pa 'bras bu
NK091(ke)001:3681: rang la 'char te brtson pas rtogs pa nyid sangs
NK091(ke)001:3682: rgyas yin pas 'bad cig par gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:3687: zhes pa'i bar ni ngo bo ji bzhin pa dngos
NK091(ke)001:3688: po rnams kyi de kho na nyid mi phyed mi
NK091(ke)001:3689: 'gyur rgyu rkyen bral ba'i don nyid mthong dka' ba
NK091(ke)001:3690: ni rdo rje gsang sngags te /
NK091(ke)001:3691: rgyud lung man ngag gi mdzod rgyal ba ril gyi
NK091(ke)001:3692: yum du gyur pa'i theg pa dag 'dir bshad pas
NK091(ke)001:3693: tshangs pa gtsug phud dang dri ma med par grags
NK091(ke)001:3694: pa la sogs pa rnams las snga phyir brgyud de
NK091(ke)001:3695: lha mi'i yul du rgyas shing snang bar gsungs pa
NK091(ke)001:3696: ste 'adi'ang gsum pa dang lnga pa'i lan no //
NK091(ke)001:3701: zhes pa'i bar ni gdul bya de dag gi ma
NK091(ke)001:3702: rig pa gnyis dang gdung ba rtsa gsum la sogs
NK091(ke)001:3703: pa bsal nas rang rig pa rang gi rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:3704: gyi 'od gsal ba rtogs par 'gyur bar gsungs pa'o
NK091(ke)001:3709: zhes pa'i bar ni dam pa'i rigs can khyod rnams
NK091(ke)001:3710: dgos pa gang gi ched du gdung ba nyi shu
NK091(ke)001:3711: rtsa gsum gyis gzhan du tshol ba'i mya ngan gyi
NK091(ke)001:3712: mun par zhugs pa yin zhes dris nas ston pa
NK091(ke)001:3713: 'das pa la mya ngan bya bar rigs pa min
NK091(ke)001:3714: te / de ni chos kyi sku'i bdag nyid sku
NK091(ke)001:3715: lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa rdo rje'i sku brnyes te
NK091(ke)001:3716: te / / 'das ma 'das med pas ma gdung zhig pa'i lan bka' stsal pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:3717: 'di gnyis kyang tha ma'i lan no //
NK091(ke)001:3726: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3727: de nas thub pa'i dbang po ma 'das pa'i sngon du byung ba'i dam pa'i rigas can rnams /
NK091(ke)001:3728: ston pa gsang bdag chen pos gsang sngags theg pa'i
NK091(ke)001:3729: rgyal po thabs chen lung gi dgongs mdzod dam pa
NK091(ke)001:3730: gsung bar zhal gyis bzhes te gleng bslang ba'i don
NK091(ke)001:3731: la mchog tu dga' ba ches cher skyes te ston
NK091(ke)001:3732: pa ngo shes pas sems dga' zhing yid mgu na
NK091(ke)001:3733: yi rangsa pa'i bsam pa yis lus btud de sgo
NK091(ke)001:3734: gsum shin tu gus pa la sbyar nas spyan sngar
NK091(ke)001:3735: 'dug ste spobs pa chen pos zhu ba 'di skad
NK091(ke)001:3736: ces gsol to // gnyis pa 'di la'ang /
NK091(ke)001:3737: 'khrugs su byas nas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las la bstod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3738: 'khrugs med du nor bu lugs su bstod par 'grel pa'i lugs gnyis las /
NK091(ke)001:3739: dang po ltar na lnga ste /
NK091(ke)001:3740: sku gsal ba'i nyi ma la sogs par bstod pa /
NK091(ke)001:3742: thugs gsang ba'i bdag por bstod pa /
NK091(ke)001:3743: yon ta na sman pa'i rgyal por bstod pa /
NK091(ke)001:3744: phrin las bdud kyi yang bdud du bstod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3747: sku gsum bye brag tu phye ste bstod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3752: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3753: bdag cag rigs can lnga la sogs pa'i gdul bya'i sems kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad la /
NK091(ke)001:3755: lta sgom spyod pa'am lta spyod dam tshig gi gsang ba'i nyi ma shar bas /
NK091(ke)001:3756: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:3758: rang byung de kho na nyid la sgrib pas shes bya'i mun pa kun dang nyon mongs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3759: las kyi sgrib pa dang bcas pa ma lus pa
NK091(ke)001:3760: dus gcig la bsal bar mdzad pa'i phyir ston pa
NK091(ke)001:3761: khyod ni gsal ba'i nyi mara kun tu grags so
NK091(ke)001:3762: // 'di ni chos rje dam pa rin po ches
NK091(ke)001:3763: thabs kyi sgron ma la bstod par gsungs shing bzhed
NK091(ke)001:3766: chos sku gsal ba'i me long du bstod pa /
NK091(ke)001:3767: longs sku gdung ba sel bar bstod pa /
NK091(ke)001:3768: sprul sku yid bzhin nor bur bstod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3773: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3774: chos rnams kyi chos nyid de bzhin nyid ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:3775: dmigs pa med cing stong pa nyid sems kyi rang
NK091(ke)001:3776: bzhin rang rig pa'i ye shes 'od gsal ba nyid
NK091(ke)001:3777: dang gnyis su med pas 'gag pa med par chos
NK091(ke)001:3778: kun gyi gzugs brnyan snang la rang bzhin med par
NK091(ke)001:3780: ston pa khyod la chos kyi me long zhes kyang grags so //
NK091(ke)001:3781: 'di nyid dam pa rin po ches thabs kyi mig mkhan la bstod par bzhed pa /
NK091(ke)001:3782: gzhan mig mkhan dang sa mkhan gnyis la bstod pa bzhed pa'ang yod do //
NK091(ke)001:3787: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3788: chung 'bring che gsum mam sems dga' zhing yid mgu la bsam pa rangs par mdzad pas na /
NK091(ke)001:3789: ston pa khyod ni gdul bya kun gyi gdung ba sel bar grags so //
NK091(ke)001:3790: chos rjes mnyan pa dang spyan ras mkhan gnyis la bstod par bzhed cing /
NK091(ke)001:3791: gzhan gdams ngag gsum bstan pa la bstod par bzhed pa'ang yod do //
NK091(ke)001:3796: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3797: 'gro ba kun gyi gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi
NK091(ke)001:3798: 'dod pa thams cad yid bzhin du skong bar mdzad
NK091(ke)001:3799: pas na / ston pa khyod ni yid bzhin gyi nor bura yongs su grags so //
NK091(ke)001:3800: dam pa rin po ches tshong dpon dang nor bu
NK091(ke)001:3801: gnyis la bstod par bzhed la gzhan yang mthun no
NK091(ke)001:3806: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3807: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang mdzod zab mo'i bka' rnams bgro bar khyod la basngagasa par mdzad pas na /
NK091(ke)001:3808: ston pa khyod ni bka' yi dgongs pa 'grel pa'i gsal byed chen pora grags so //
NK091(ke)001:3809: chos rjes lde mig dang 'grel pa gnyis la bstod par bzhed cing gzhan yang mthun no //
NK091(ke)001:3814: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3815: dper na mtshan mo mun nag gi sprin rum nas /
NK091(ke)001:3816: glog gsal bar 'gyus pas bar du snang ba rnams mthong bar ston pa lta bus /
NK091(ke)001:3817: don gyi gnas lugs thog ma dang tha ma med
NK091(ke)001:3818: pa yi chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid
NK091(ke)001:3819: las / gsang chen sngags kyi dgongs pa thabs mchog
NK091(ke)001:3820: rnam par dag pa'i nye lam chen po de nyid
NK091(ke)001:3821: mthar phyin nas rang don du rtogs pa'i don las
NK091(ke)001:3822: mi g.yo bar gzhan don du mngon par byung ba'i
NK091(ke)001:3823: skyes bu chen po don gnyis grub pa khyod nyid
NK091(ke)001:3824: las / / 'dren pa dam pa sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin cing /
NK091(ke)001:3825: gsang ba ma lus pa yi bdag po chen por grags so //
NK091(ke)001:3826: dam pa rin po ches sa mkhan la bstod par
NK091(ke)001:3827: bzhed la gzhan mnyan pa mkhan la bstod par bzhed
NK091(ke)001:3828: pa'ang yod de rgya mtsho las nor bu len pa
NK091(ke)001:3834: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3835: nyon mongs pa'i dug rnams 'jomsa pa'i thabs sna tshogs
NK091(ke)001:3836: dang ldan pas sman gyi dkyil 'khor gsang ba'i theg
NK091(ke)001:3837: pa nyid kyis nyon mongs pa'i tshogs kyi rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:3838: shes pas nyid kyis nyid grol te zug rngu 'byin
NK091(ke)001:3839: pa bla na med par nges pas /
NK091(ke)001:3840: phyi nang gi nad do cog gi dgrar gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:3841: yi ston pa khyod ni sman gyi rgyal pora grags
NK091(ke)001:3842: so // 'di nyid chos rjes sman pa la bstod par bzhed de gzhan yang mthun no //
NK091(ke)001:3847: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3849: nang nyon mongs pa sogs gdul dka' ma lus pa kun 'dul zhing /
NK091(ke)001:3850: bdud bzhi dang log sde kun gyi yang bdud du
NK091(ke)001:3851: gyur pa rdo rje 'chang he ru ka ste bdud
NK091(ke)001:3852: kyi dpung tshogs ma lus pa rnams 'jomsa shing ru
NK091(ke)001:3853: tra la sogs pa 'jigsa pa'i tshogs kyang phrin las
NK091(ke)001:3854: sna tshogs kyis 'jomsa par byed pas ston pa khyod
NK091(ke)001:3855: ni bdud kyi'nga bdud du grags so //
NK091(ke)001:3856: dam pa rin po ches rdo rje'i rdzong chen la
NK091(ke)001:3857: bstod par bzhed cing gzhan rdzong chen dang spyan ras
NK091(ke)001:3858: mkhan gnyis la bstod par bzhed pa'ang yod do //
NK091(ke)001:3860: rigs can rnams kyis rgyud don zhu ba'i phyir ston
NK091(ke)001:3861: pa skyes bu'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs las bstod pa
NK091(ke)001:3867: zhes pa'i bar gyis khyod gsang ba'i don gyi bdag
NK091(ke)001:3868: po sku shin tu bkod pa'ang rgyal ba ril gyi
NK091(ke)001:3869: dgongs pa'i mnga' bdag yin no bar bstod pa ni
NK091(ke)001:3870: thabs bcu bzhi pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod
NK091(ke)001:3875: zhes pa'i bar gyis bka' thams cad kyi dgongs pa
NK091(ke)001:3876: 'grel pa por bstod pa ni thabs bcu pa dang
NK091(ke)001:3877: / bcu gcig pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3882: zhes pa'i bar gyis gdul bya'i bsam pa ril la
NK091(ke)001:3883: gsang ba gsum gyi don shar bar mdzad nas sgrib
NK091(ke)001:3884: pa'i mun pa sel ba'i nyi ma yin no bar
NK091(ke)001:3885: bstod pa ni thabs brgyad pa'i yon tan gyi sgo
NK091(ke)001:3890: zhes pa'i bar gyis log lta dang log lta can
NK091(ke)001:3891: ril gyis mi tshugs shing 'joms pas bdud kyi yang
NK091(ke)001:3892: bdud khyod yin no bar bstod pa ni thabs drug
NK091(ke)001:3893: pa'i yon tan la bstod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3898: zhes pa'i bar gyis chos ril ma 'dres la yongs
NK091(ke)001:3899: su rdzogs par gsal bar mdzad pas chos kyi me
NK091(ke)001:3900: long khyod yin no bar bstod pa ni thabs gnyis
NK091(ke)001:3901: pa'i yon tan gyis bstod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3906: zhes pa'i bar gyis gdul bya'i nang gi gcong rnying
NK091(ke)001:3907: 'byin pa'i sman pa'i rgyal po khyod yin no bar
NK091(ke)001:3908: bstod pa ni thabs gsum pa'i sgo nas bstod pa'o
NK091(ke)001:3913: zhes pa'i bar gyis gdul bya ril gyi bsam pa
NK091(ke)001:3914: dang mthun par don mdzad pas sgo gsum gyi gdung
NK091(ke)001:3915: ba sel ba la bshes gnyen mgon yin no bar
NK091(ke)001:3916: bstod pa ni / mdzad pa dang po dang bzhi pa dang lnga pa'i sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3921: zhes pa'i bar gyis gdul bya'i bsam pa'i re 'dod
NK091(ke)001:3922: ril skong bas nor bur rin po che khyod yin
NK091(ke)001:3924: thabs bdun pa dang dgu pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3925: gsum pa zhus pa dngos ni /
NK091(ke)001:3929: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3930: de ltar mnyes pa'i rgyu sngon du btang nas zhu ba dngos ni /
NK091(ke)001:3931: sngar gyi ston pa dam pa rnams dang dgongs pa dang mdzad pa mthun par mdzod la /
NK091(ke)001:3932: bdag cag dman pa'i lus can gyi 'khor lang ka la sogs pa riga pa 'dzin pa rnams la /
NK091(ke)001:3933: dam pa'i sprul pa thub pa'i dbang po nyid gang
NK091(ke)001:3934: ltar nub ste mya ngan las 'das par zhus te
NK091(ke)001:3935: / 'di nyid lha rje yang khyed bla mas rmongs
NK091(ke)001:3936: pa gdung ba sel ba'i byung tshul zhus par bzhed
NK091(ke)001:3937: / la / zhing khams so sor dam pa'i sgron ma ji ltar bkod pa zhus te /
NK091(ke)001:3941: dgongs pa 'grel ba gsum dris par bzhed cing /
NK091(ke)001:3942: gsang sngags theg pa chen po dam pa'i gsang lung ji ltar byung ba zhus te /
NK091(ke)001:3944: gdul bya'i skabs la bab pa /
NK091(ke)001:3945: brgyud pa thabs kyi grags pa /
NK091(ke)001:3946: lung chen nges par bstan pa gsum zhus par bzhed de /
NK091(ke)001:3947: de ltar gsum zhus nas gsang ba chen po sngags
NK091(ke)001:3948: kyi theg pa rgyud kyi rgyal po bgro ba'am bshad
NK091(ke)001:3949: par mdzod cig ces gsol ba gdab ste /
NK091(ke)001:3952: dgongs pa bgro ba gnyis zhus par bzhed cing /
NK091(ke)001:3953: nges don dgongs pa'i dris tshig gsum po bgro bar mdzod cig ces gsol ba gdab ste /
NK091(ke)001:3955: gang gi ched du mdzad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:3956: las rgyud gcod pa gnyis dris par bzhed la /
NK091(ke)001:3957: ye ji bzhin pa nam mkha'i rdo rje nges pa'i
NK091(ke)001:3958: gsang ba mchog gi don nyid bgro ba'am ston par
NK091(ke)001:3959: mdzod cig ces gsol ba gdab ste /
NK091(ke)001:3961: snying po byang chub tu nges pa'i byung tshul zhus par bzhed do //
NK091(ke)001:3962: de ltar bskul zhing gus pas gsol ba gsum btab bo //
NK091(ke)001:3964: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:3965: bshad ma thag pa ltar lung dam pa bgro bar
NK091(ke)001:3966: gsol ba btab pa'i le'u ste lnga pa rnam par
NK091(ke)001:3967: bshad pa'o ////gsum pa rgyud kyi don dngos la gnyis
NK091(ke)001:3968: te / bshad par dam bcas te nyon cig par gdams pa /
NK091(ke)001:3969: rgyud kyi don dngos rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:3974: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:3975: gong du bstan ma thag pa de skad ces gsol ba btab pa las /
NK091(ke)001:3976: ston pa gsang ba pa'i bdag posa bshad par zhal gyis bzhes te bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:3977: ston pa ma 'das pa'i sngon du byung nas byung
NK091(ke)001:3978: tshul bcu gnyis kyi tshul gyis gsang sngags thabs kyi
NK091(ke)001:3979: theg pa khyed rnams la bgro bar thub pas lung
NK091(ke)001:3980: bstan mdzad pa'i / 'gro ba lus kyi dam tshig
NK091(ke)001:3981: gi sems dpa' rnams kyis gdung sngags nyer gsum dang
NK091(ke)001:3982: dri ba drug dang bcas pa'i zhu ba phul ba
NK091(ke)001:3983: rnams ni sgyu ma'i rtoga pa yin pas dgrol dgos
NK091(ke)001:3984: la dgrol yang nus pas na /
NK091(ke)001:3985: rgyal ba rnams kyi bka' lung bzhin du gsal bar
NK091(ke)001:3986: bgros te dgrol bar byed kyis legs par nyon la
NK091(ke)001:3988: gnyis pa la byung tshul bcu gnyis kyis bstan pa las /
NK091(ke)001:3989: dang po rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba la lnga ste /
NK091(ke)001:3990: gdung ba nyi shu rtsa gsum bsal ba'i lan /
NK091(ke)001:3991: gdung ba skye ba'i rgyu med pas ma skyed cig par gdams pa /
NK091(ke)001:3992: gdung ba sel ba'i yon tan /
NK091(ke)001:3994: gdung ba yod med kyi khyad par ro //
NK091(ke)001:3995: dang po la nyi shu rtsa gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:3996: sgron ma mi nub par mun pa rang bzhin gyis sel ba /
NK091(ke)001:3997: shes bya nyid tshad mar gyur pas gtan la phebs pa /
NK091(ke)001:3998: spyan la zum pa med pas log stobs mi 'phel ba /
NK091(ke)001:3999: nyi zla ma nub pas mun par mi 'gyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:4000: ston pa mi 'da' zhing gdug pa bdag med pas 'dul ba /
NK091(ke)001:4001: bstan pa shes rab rtsal can gyis gsal bar byed pa /
NK091(ke)001:4002: bslab pa sa non pa phyis 'byung bas 'dzin pa /
NK091(ke)001:4003: snying po byang chub tu gnas pas btsal du med par lung bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:4004: mi mkhas pas rtsod cing mkhas pas mi rtsod pa /
NK091(ke)001:4005: ma rtogs pas tha dad du bslad cing 'chos pa /
NK091(ke)001:4006: rmongs pas chos dang nor barje bas gnyis ka sreg pa /
NK091(ke)001:4007: ston pa sems nyid la 'pho 'gyur med pas bstan pa la dgra mi 'ong ba /
NK091(ke)001:4008: bstan pa'i yun byang chub snying po dang mnyam par gnas pa /
NK091(ke)001:4009: dus gsum mnyam pas snga phyi med de mi 'gyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:4010: bstan pa'i mtha' brjod pa dang bral bar 'gyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:4011: slob ma'i mtha' de bzhin nyid las mi 'gyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:4012: 'di nas de bzhin nyid du gshegs shing me tog bkod par snang ba /
NK091(ke)001:4013: 'gro ba'i mgon du bde gshegs snying po 'ong ba /
NK091(ke)001:4014: blo gros dgongs pa tshig gsum la btsal ba /
NK091(ke)001:4015: nges don ji bzhin pa blo la bzhag la gzung ba /
NK091(ke)001:4016: sku gdung dngos po med kyang gdul bya la 'byung ba /
NK091(ke)001:4017: mchod gnas mkhas pa dang sku gsung thugs kyi gzugs brnyan la bya ba /
NK091(ke)001:4018: gdung 'tshob skyes bu sems can la 'byung bar bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:4023: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4024: spyir le'u 'dis nges don ston la /
NK091(ke)001:4025: dam pa'i sprul pa gang ltar nub kyi lan te /
NK091(ke)001:4026: khyad par rtsal 'phangs las tshogs lam sems bskyed pa /
NK091(ke)001:4027: rgyud gnas lugs las rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba'i
NK091(ke)001:4028: byung tshul ma rig mun sel gyi lta ba ma
NK091(ke)001:4029: dang bu 'phrad pa lta bu nyid rgyas par ston
NK091(ke)001:4030: no // sems kyi dkyil 'khor rang bzhin gyi 'od
NK091(ke)001:4031: gsal ba'i ngo bo chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:4032: dbyings de nyid ston pa yin pas don la ston
NK091(ke)001:4033: pa rdo rje'i sku mnga' ba de ni 'dus ma
NK091(ke)001:4034: byas nam mkha' bzhin du nub pa med de gsang
NK091(ke)001:4035: sngags kyi rang bzhin ye nas 'od gsal ba ji
NK091(ke)001:4036: bzhin pa'i don du shar bas /
NK091(ke)001:4037: de la ganga gis sgrib ste 'gro ba'i mun pa
NK091(ke)001:4038: ma spang bar zhi bas gdul bya'i rgyud kyi mun
NK091(ke)001:4039: pa de yang sems nyid rang snang du rtogs pa
NK091(ke)001:4040: nyid kyis sel te me dang shing bal lta bu'o
NK091(ke)001:4041: zhes lan btab pas dri ba dang po'i gdung ba
NK091(ke)001:4046: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4047: thub pa'i dbang po dang gsang sngags kyi ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:4048: ni gcig dang du ma las grol ba'i phyir phyis
NK091(ke)001:4049: gsang sngags thun mong ma yin pa'i thabs la mngon
NK091(ke)001:4050: sum dang rjes dpag gnyis su byung zhing gnyis po
NK091(ke)001:4051: la'ang lung dang man ngag gi tshad ma gnyis kyis
NK091(ke)001:4052: gang shar yang byang chub kyi sems dkyil 'khor gsum
NK091(ke)001:4053: gyi bdag nyid du gzhal byar byas pa na de
NK091(ke)001:4054: ltar rtogs pa'i gang zag gis kyang don gtan la
NK091(ke)001:4055: phebs pas / shes bya dngos po sna tshogs pa kun kyang gsang sngags kyi ngo bor gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:4056: me rang nyid tsha zhing gzhan sreg pa ltar shes
NK091(ke)001:4057: bya de yang rang bzhin gyi snang bar shar nas
NK091(ke)001:4058: rang gi ngo bos tshad mar 'gyur bas log par
NK091(ke)001:4059: mi 'gyur ro zhes lan gsungs pas gdung ba gnyis
NK091(ke)001:4060: pa sangs so // gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:4064: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4065: ston pa 'das kyang legs nyesa sam nor ba dang
NK091(ke)001:4066: ma nor ba'i rtsa ba ni ma rig pa yin
NK091(ke)001:4067: la de yi ngo bo'ang sems nyid ye ji bzhin
NK091(ke)001:4069: de ltar gtan la 'bebs pa'i gzhi tshad ma gnyis
NK091(ke)001:4070: kyis bstan pa la zhugs nas de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:4071: yang dag par rtogs pa de la 'gyur ba med
NK091(ke)001:4072: cing ye shes kyi spyan la zum pa med pas
NK091(ke)001:4073: rgol ba tshar gcod de log stobs 'phel bar mi
NK091(ke)001:4074: 'gyur ro // zhes lan btab pas gdung ba gsum pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4078: gnag pa'i mun pa sel ba med //
NK091(ke)001:4079: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4080: gsang sngags de kho na nyid kyi lugs kyis kun
NK091(ke)001:4081: gzhi dgu pa sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba
NK091(ke)001:4082: nyid ye nas bden pa gnyis su med par rang
NK091(ke)001:4083: shar bas na mthas ma sgrib par gdod nas dkar
NK091(ke)001:4084: bas gnyen po dang bral ba la 'phral du lam
NK091(ke)001:4085: pas tha dad dang gcig par dkar bar byed pa'i
NK091(ke)001:4086: glo bur ba'i nyi zla yang med pas /
NK091(ke)001:4087: gnag pa'i mun pa gol sa yang ma dmigs pa
NK091(ke)001:4088: la gzhan gyis sela ba'nga meda de spang gnyen las
NK091(ke)001:4089: grol ba'i phyir bstan pa log pa'i sprin 'khrigs nas
NK091(ke)001:4091: zhes lan mdzad pas gdung ba bzhi pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4092: 'di la sde spar dang phyag dpe gzhan kun na rkang pa gnyis las mi bzhugs kyang /
NK091(ke)001:4093: chos rje rin po che'i phyag mchan bzhugs pa'i dpe
NK091(ke)001:4094: dang phyag dpe gzhan gcig la'ang gsum snang bas 'grel
NK091(ke)001:4095: chen gyi sgros la brtags na chad par mngon no
NK091(ke)001:4100: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4101: bshad pa bzhin du 'pho 'gyur mi mnga' bas sangs
NK091(ke)001:4102: rgyas rdo rje'i sku mya ngana las yongs su mi
NK091(ke)001:4103: 'da' la / de'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i dam pa'i
NK091(ke)001:4104: chos kyang ji srid 'khor ba gnas kyi bar du
NK091(ke)001:4106: lhun gyis grub pa'i bstan pa la shar nub med pas so //
NK091(ke)001:4107: de lta bas na sems can gang dag le lo
NK091(ke)001:4108: can la phan gadgas pa'i phyir sprul pa rnams ni
NK091(ke)001:4109: mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul ston te de yis
NK091(ke)001:4110: 'dul bas so // don la mi 'da' ba'i tshad ji ltar nam mkha' nyid zhig par gyur nas /
NK091(ke)001:4111: de tshe sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo nyid kyang mya
NK091(ke)001:4112: ngan las 'ad'a bar 'gyur te skye shi med par
NK091(ke)001:4113: 'dra bas so // gang dag phyi nang gi gdug
NK091(ke)001:4114: pa ma rungs pa log sred can dang nyon mongs
NK091(ke)001:4115: pa la sogs pa rnams ni bdag med gnyis kyi
NK091(ke)001:4116: rang bzhin mtha' bral stong pa chen po gnyis su
NK091(ke)001:4117: med pa'i gshis kyi yin lugs rtogs nas ngang las
NK091(ke)001:4118: mi 'da' bas lta sgom gyi stobs kyis 'dul zhing
NK091(ke)001:4120: dper na thab kyi me bsad na rtsig mig gi du ba 'chad pa bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:4121: zhes lan bka' stsal pas gdung ba lnga pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4126: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4127: rgyu rkyen med par rang bzhina gyis 'od gsal ba'i
NK091(ke)001:4128: ye shes ni snang ba dang stong pa dang gnyis
NK091(ke)001:4129: su med pa'i spros pa gsum ma spang bar bral
NK091(ke)001:4130: ba'i mi g.yo ba chen po ste gsung lnga'i ngo
NK091(ke)001:4131: bo bstan pa rgya mtsho'ang de nyid yin pas /
NK091(ke)001:4132: rang byung gi ye shes de'i don ji lta bar
NK091(ke)001:4133: son pa'i 'gying bag gis chos ston pas smra ba'i
NK091(ke)001:4134: seng ge rtsal chen po rdzogs pas gsang bdag rdo
NK091(ke)001:4135: rje 'dzin pa nyid dang lang ka la sogs pa
NK091(ke)001:4136: rnams kyis bstan pa khyad par can kun tu 'bar
NK091(ke)001:4137: zhing snang bar byed de rgyas shing 'phel bar mdzad
NK091(ke)001:4138: pa'o // zhes lan gsungs pas gdung ba drug pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4143: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4144: lhag pa'i bslab pa rin po che'ang theg pa chen
NK091(ke)001:4145: po rang rig pas lhag pa'i sems nyid yin pas
NK091(ke)001:4146: don du gnyer ba'i sgrub pa kun gyi mchog gsang
NK091(ke)001:4147: ba sngags kyi bslab pa 'di ni /
NK091(ke)001:4148: rig pa 'dzin pas sa mchog rab tu gsang ba
NK091(ke)001:4149: de nyid snang zhing non pa bka' lung dam pa
NK091(ke)001:4150: 'di nyid bgros pas mthu las phyis su 'byung bar
NK091(ke)001:4151: 'gyur ba'i 'gro ba lusa kyi sems dpa' chen po
NK091(ke)001:4152: dam pa'i rigs can lang ka la sogs pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:4154: zhes lan btab pas gdung ba bdun pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4158: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4159: 'khor ba thog ma dang tha ma'i mtha' la thug
NK091(ke)001:4160: pa med pa'i 'gro ba sems can rnams rtsa ba
NK091(ke)001:4161: byang chub kyi snying pora ye nas gnas pa yin
NK091(ke)001:4162: pas / rigs mi 'gyur bar de bzhin nyid du rgyud gcig par nges pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:4163: rmad du byung ba'i theg pa 'dis kun kyang mi
NK091(ke)001:4164: slob pa de nyid du bya ba med pa'i sangs
NK091(ke)001:4165: rgyas su lung ston par byed do //
NK091(ke)001:4166: zhes lan gsungs pas gdung ba brgyad pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4171: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4172: sems 'di nyid yang dag par yod pa dang don
NK091(ke)001:4173: la grub pa med do zhes thun mong ma yin
NK091(ke)001:4174: pa gnyis su med pa'i don la shed ma bye
NK091(ke)001:4175: ba'i dbu ma pa la sogs pa byis pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:4176: ni mtha' yod med la rtsod par byed kyang /
NK091(ke)001:4177: don chen po la shed bye ba'i 'bras bu gsang
NK091(ke)001:4178: sngags la mkhas pas dam pa dag ni ye nas
NK091(ke)001:4179: mtha' dang bral ba la de nyid du'ang 'dzin cing
NK091(ke)001:4180: rtog pa med pa'i phyir rtsod pa dang bral zhing
NK091(ke)001:4181: yod med la sogs par gnyis su rtog pa'i tshig
NK091(ke)001:4183: ces lan mdzad pas gdung ba dgu pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4188: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4189: ston pa nga yi gsang sngags nges pa'i gsang don
NK091(ke)001:4190: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid lhun gyis
NK091(ke)001:4192: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs thugs kyi
NK091(ke)001:4193: gsang ba yin pa'i phyir shin tu brtags par dka'
NK091(ke)001:4194: bas / gang blos mthong ba'i skal ba med pa
NK091(ke)001:4195: dag gis sngags kyi dgongs don zab mo ji lta
NK091(ke)001:4196: bar mi dpogsa shing rtogs par mi nus pas gzhan
NK091(ke)001:4197: thun mong gi tshad ma gnyis kyis tshol zhing dpogsa
NK091(ke)001:4199: de ltar brtags pas mthong ba tha dad kyi phyir /
NK091(ke)001:4200: nges pa'i gsang bar sgra gcig kyang don tha dad
NK091(ke)001:4201: du 'phel zhing lta bas phyogs ris su 'dzin pa
NK091(ke)001:4202: 'byung yang gsang don ji bzhin du mthong ste /
NK091(ke)001:4206: thog tu drod tshad kyis dbab pa rnams ni bka'
NK091(ke)001:4207: yi don la tshul bzhin du gnas par 'gyur ro
NK091(ke)001:4208: // zhes lan bka' stsal pas gdung ba bcu pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4213: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4214: rmad du byung ba'i bka' sgro skur dang bral zhing
NK091(ke)001:4215: sangs rgyas dang rig 'dzin dam pa rnams kyi bya
NK091(ke)001:4216: bral rdzogs pa'i gsang lung 'di nyid kyi don 'khrul
NK091(ke)001:4217: pa'i gang zag gang dag gis ji bzhin du mi
NK091(ke)001:4218: shes shing ma rnyed pa'i dbang gis sems rmongs te
NK091(ke)001:4219: yid 'dod pas g.yem zhing 'phyar bas 'phyon ma'i sems
NK091(ke)001:4220: lta bus / don med pa'i snyan ngag gi chos
NK091(ke)001:4221: dang zang zing gi nor rdzas dug lta bu dang
NK091(ke)001:4222: khyad par lhag pa'i bka' zab mo'i dam pa'i chos
NK091(ke)001:4223: kyi bdud rtsi gnyis barje bar byed pa 'byung ste
NK091(ke)001:4224: lta bus / / de rnams ni 'di phyi kun
NK091(ke)001:4225: tu phung bar byed cing gtsub shing gtsub stan ltar
NK091(ke)001:4226: gnyis ka sreg par 'gyur bas bag yod par bya'o
NK091(ke)001:4227: lta bus / / // zhes lan gsungs pas gdung ba bcu gcig pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4232: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4233: sems nyid bde ba chen po'i ye klong yangs pa
NK091(ke)001:4234: ni dngos po gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos kun ma
NK091(ke)001:4235: bkol bar ye shes bde ba chen por rang gsal
NK091(ke)001:4236: bas me long 'od po che de nyid theg mchog
NK091(ke)001:4237: rgyal po 'dis gcig dang tha dad las grol ba'i
NK091(ke)001:4238: phyir ma 'dresa yongs rdzogs su ston pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:4239: / de lta bu'i klong la thub pa'i dbang po'ang
NK091(ke)001:4240: dpe nam mkha' ltar 'pho 'gyur med par bzhugs pa'o
NK091(ke)001:4241: / // de bas na ma rungs pa'i 'tshe bar
NK091(ke)001:4242: byed pa'ang lhun grub kyi klong la snang yang mi
NK091(ke)001:4243: dmigs te ngo bo mi zin pas dper na glog
NK091(ke)001:4244: 'gyu ba na sprin gyi mun pa rang dag tu
NK091(ke)001:4245: gsal ba bzhin du gnod par mi nus pa'am /
NK091(ke)001:4246: yang na sprin med na glog kyang med pa ltar
NK091(ke)001:4247: ma rig pa med na ye shes kyang med pas
NK091(ke)001:4248: / 'tshe bar byed pa'ang rtogs pa'i bogs 'don du gyur te skabs tshol bar med pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:4249: zhes lan mdzad pas gdung ba bcu gnyis pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4254: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4255: ji srid byang chub kyi snying po de kho na
NK091(ke)001:4256: nyid ji tsam du gnas shing yod kyi bar de
NK091(ke)001:4257: srid du de dang tha ni dad pa'i phyir mtshon
NK091(ke)001:4258: bya don gyi bstan pa yang gnas par 'gyur ba
NK091(ke)001:4259: yin no // zhes lan btab pas gdung ba bcu gsum pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4264: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4265: bstan pa rin po che ni dus ril du shar
NK091(ke)001:4266: te sngar byung ngo da lta 'byung ngo ma 'ongs
NK091(ke)001:4268: de yang don gyi dbang du na ye thog ma
NK091(ke)001:4269: dang tha ma brjod du med pa na rang shar
NK091(ke)001:4270: du byung bas dus gsum mnyam pa nyid la snga
NK091(ke)001:4271: phyi yod pa ma yin te /
NK091(ke)001:4272: dus gsum gyi rgyud las grol bas ngo bo ji
NK091(ke)001:4273: bzhin pa la dgongs te lan mdzad pas gdung ba
NK091(ke)001:4279: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4280: bstan pa dam pa dang po snang ba'i tshe na'ang
NK091(ke)001:4281: gzhi dngos po med pa ji bzhin pa'i ngang las
NK091(ke)001:4282: 'gro 'ong med par rang byung bar brjod pasa tha
NK091(ke)001:4283: ma'ang tshig dang yi ges brjod pa dang bral te
NK091(ke)001:4284: dmigs pa med pa rang bzhin gyis stong par 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:4285: te gzhi ji bzhin pa las gzhan du ma yin
NK091(ke)001:4286: pa'i phyir ro // zhes lan bka' stsal pas gdung ba bco lnga pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4291: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4292: bstan pa'i gdung 'dzin pa'i rigs can dag kyang thog
NK091(ke)001:4293: ma'ang ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:4294: yin pa'i phyir / tha ma'ang de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:4295: las gzhan du mi 'gyur te tha snyad du 'pho
NK091(ke)001:4297: zhes lan gsungs pas gdung ba bcu drug pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4302: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4303: don la chos thams cad de bzhin nyid du rang
NK091(ke)001:4304: gsal ba la 'gro 'ong ma dmigs kyang gdul bya'i
NK091(ke)001:4306: mi mjed 'di nas de bzhin nyid chos kyi dbyings 'dir gshegs te /
NK091(ke)001:4307: ye nas ma bcos pa gdal khyab chen po'i zhing
NK091(ke)001:4308: na chos kyi sku snang ba med par bzhugs la
NK091(ke)001:4309: / de'ang ngo bo ji lta bur bzhugs na /
NK091(ke)001:4310: rang don du sems kyi chos nyid rig pa'i klong
NK091(ke)001:4311: mtha' dbus med pas dkyil 'khor rang bzhin gyis 'od
NK091(ke)001:4312: gsal ba nyid du bzhugs te /
NK091(ke)001:4313: chos thams cad rang byung gi ye shes de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:4314: nyid kyi ngo bo ye ji bzhin pa nyid du
NK091(ke)001:4315: rnam par snang ste rang gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:4316: de ltar 'das nas don brda ma go ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:4317: gzhan don du mos pa spyod pa'i sa pa la
NK091(ke)001:4318: sogs pa byis pa'i gdul bya rnams kyi ched du
NK091(ke)001:4319: skus 'dul bas sprul pa'i cho 'phrul zhig /me tog
NK091(ke)001:4320: bkod pa'i 'jig rten zhes bya ba na /
NK091(ke)001:4321: mtshan nges par gcig tu ma grags pa zhes bya ba bsam gyis mi khyab par snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:4322: 'o na de kho na ltar 'byung 'jug tu snang ba yod dam zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:4323: de ltar snang ba nyid na'ang snang ba med de /
NK091(ke)001:4324: snang stong gi mtha' las grol bas so //
NK091(ke)001:4325: thub pa'i dbang po'i tshul dang bkod pa de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:4326: du zhing khamas tha dad pa gang dag tu sprul
NK091(ke)001:4327: pa'i sangsa rgyas ji snyed cig snang bar mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:4328: kun kyang dper na sgyu ma'i mkhan pos rdzas las
NK091(ke)001:4329: rta glang sogs su sprul pa ji lta ba bzhina
NK091(ke)001:4330: du zhi nga la lar sku 'das nas mi snang
NK091(ke)001:4331: la / 'on kyang zhing gzhan du snga ma'i mtshan
NK091(ke)001:4332: dang sku ma yin par ji ltar 'dul ba ltar
NK091(ke)001:4334: gang gis sprul pa yin na /
NK091(ke)001:4335: ston pa mi bskyod pa rdo rje sems dpa' de
NK091(ke)001:4336: kho na nyid kyi thugs mchog mnga' ba nyid kyang
NK091(ke)001:4337: / snang ba'i rgyu thugs rje sprul pa'i byin rlabs kyis mthu las /
NK091(ke)001:4338: 'jig rten gyi khams ni dpag tu med pa'i zhing
NK091(ke)001:4339: ji snyed du mya ngan las 'das nas nub ste
NK091(ke)001:4341: sku snang nas sgron mar bkod pa ji ltar du
NK091(ke)001:4342: mdzad kyang gcig dang du ma las sprul pa ril
NK091(ke)001:4343: grol ba'i phyir / sku gsum dbyer med mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:4344: lhun grub chen po'i ngang las rang byung zhing slar
NK091(ke)001:4345: yang de nyid du rang zhi ba yin te /
NK091(ke)001:4346: ston pa'i rgyud gcig la 'byung 'jug can gyi chos ni ma dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:4347: zhes lan mdzad pas gdung ba bcu bdun pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4348: phyag dpe la lar nub snang zhes 'byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:4353: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4354: ngo bo gang du'ang mi zin pas skye ba med
NK091(ke)001:4355: cing sgrib byed dang bral bas rang byung gi ye
NK091(ke)001:4356: shes chos sku de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings de ni
NK091(ke)001:4357: gdoda ma nas sems nyid bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK091(ke)001:4358: po yin la / de ltar ma rtogs pa'i dbang las /
NK091(ke)001:4359: sems can rnams kyi rnam rtog glo bur bas kun
NK091(ke)001:4360: nas bslang ba'i las kyis bsgribs pas mig gis mig
NK091(ke)001:4361: ma mthong ba bzhin du gyur kyang /
NK091(ke)001:4362: ril de'i bdag nyid du gyur pas mgon skyabs dam pa'ang de las gzhan na med pas /
NK091(ke)001:4363: rang gi snying po byang chub kyi sems de kho
NK091(ke)001:4364: na nyid gang de 'gro ba rnams kyi mgon dang
NK091(ke)001:4366: zhes lan btab pas gdung ba bco brgyad pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4371: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4372: thub mchog rgyal ba'i dbang pos dgongs pa tshig gsum
NK091(ke)001:4373: ni mgo bya tsha ba ston pas mdun bsu ba'i
NK091(ke)001:4374: gdams ngag gsum du bzhed skad kyang /
NK091(ke)001:4375: 'dir ni 'grel chen las dkyil 'khor gsum dang sngags
NK091(ke)001:4376: gsum gyi don du gsungs shing so ye shes dbang
NK091(ke)001:4377: phyug gis dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med pa'i don du
NK091(ke)001:4378: bzhed pa dang / gsang bdag chen po sgro phug
NK091(ke)001:4379: pas mda' glan yang khyed gsum gyi gsung sgros dang
NK091(ke)001:4380: bzhed pa dang / mthun par / zhi lhag zung 'jug /dkyil 'khor gsum /
NK091(ke)001:4381: sngags gsum du bzhed pa ltar te /
NK091(ke)001:4382: de gsum gyi don gyi ngo bo ji bzhin pa
NK091(ke)001:4383: ni theg rim dgu po kun gyis rtogs par bya
NK091(ke)001:4384: ba'i de kho na nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su
NK091(ke)001:4385: 'char bar byed pa'i man ngag 'phrul gyi gsang sgo
NK091(ke)001:4386: la brten nas le'u zhe lnga pa las rtsa ba
NK091(ke)001:4387: gsum du gsung pa'i don la sogs pa bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:4388: blo dang gros dang thabs kyi mchog ste yun gyi
NK091(ke)001:4389: don srid chen po dang gsum gyis rtogs par nges
NK091(ke)001:4390: pasa / lam pa'i ngor ting nge 'dzin dang shes rab dang de gnyis su med pa gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:4391: de ni le'u nga drug pa las gsungs pa ltar /
NK091(ke)001:4392: rnal 'byor mchog gi blo gros dam pa'i spyod yul
NK091(ke)001:4393: du snang ba kho na yin pa'i phyir rang las
NK091(ke)001:4395: zhes lan bka' stsal pas gdung ba bcu dgu pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4400: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4401: rgyal ba kun gyi thugs kyi gsang ba rnam par
NK091(ke)001:4402: mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyis dngos po thams cad
NK091(ke)001:4403: kyi chos nyid gnas lugs kyi don la yul dang
NK091(ke)001:4404: yul can med par 'jug pa ni rang byung gi
NK091(ke)001:4405: ye shes de bzhin nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:4406: de la 'byung 'jug gi dus bral ba'i phyir bsam
NK091(ke)001:4407: du med pa'i chos nyid ji bzhin pa yi de
NK091(ke)001:4408: kho na nyid du rtogs goms mthar phyin pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:4409: gyis yang dag par nges pa'i ngo bo nyid la
NK091(ke)001:4410: / cir yang mi bsam par blo bzhag pa de
NK091(ke)001:4411: nyid ngesa pa don gyi lta sgom phul du byung
NK091(ke)001:4412: / ba yin no // zhes lan mdzad pas gdung ba nyi shu pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4417: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4418: chos so cog kun gyi mtshan nyid snang la ma
NK091(ke)001:4419: grub pa dang med la zad mi shes pa dang
NK091(ke)001:4420: stong la thams cad 'byung bas nam mkha'i mtshan nyid
NK091(ke)001:4421: dang mthun par ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:4422: kyi phyir mtha' kun dang bral ba'i ye shes kyi
NK091(ke)001:4423: sku can rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK091(ke)001:4424: chos nyid kyi sku la gdos bcas dang dngos po
NK091(ke)001:4425: gnyis dang bral te snang ba med par dkyil 'khor
NK091(ke)001:4426: gsum gyi ngo bo nyid la don du 'byung mi
NK091(ke)001:4427: 'byung mi mnga' bas sku gdung ringa bsrel ji ltar
NK091(ke)001:4428: 'byung zhes gdung ba rigs pa ma yin no //
NK091(ke)001:4429: 'on kyang drang don du snang ba mi 'gog pas /
NK091(ke)001:4430: gdul bya'i sems can sku gdung la mos pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:4431: la mchod yul du snang nas phan gdags pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:4432: du / dngos po med cing gang yang rdzogs pa
NK091(ke)001:4433: nyid kyi byin rlabs lasa sprul pa yi sgyu ma'i
NK091(ke)001:4434: ring bsrel yungs 'bru tsam la sogs pa 'chad 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:4435: gyi tshad ltar thugs rje chen pos 'dul thabs kyis
NK091(ke)001:4436: bzhag tshul bstan par mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:4437: 'o na de btsal bas 'byung zhing rnyed dam zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:4438: ngesa par ring bsrel ni 'dod pa med pa'i byin
NK091(ke)001:4439: rlabs yin pas gang 'doda pa tha dad kyis btsal
NK091(ke)001:4440: bas mi rnyed pa ni dper na bye ma dag
NK091(ke)001:4441: la mar 'dod nas btsal ba dang 'dra'o //
NK091(ke)001:4442: des na nges pa'i don du mi 'byung ba'i dpe /
NK091(ke)001:4443: dus gang gi tshe na sa bon la 'bras btab
NK091(ke)001:4444: pas 'bras bu til 'brur smin pa de yi tshe
NK091(ke)001:4446: zhes lan gsungs pas gdung ba nyer gcig pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4451: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4452: sku gdul bya'i gang zag gi ngo la 'gro ba'i
NK091(ke)001:4453: gzugs su snang zhing gsung theg chen mdo sngags kyi
NK091(ke)001:4454: zab don lung rigs man ngag dang mthun par sgrogs
NK091(ke)001:4455: pas chos kyi mig mnga' ba thugs lo rgyus la
NK091(ke)001:4456: mkhas pas yid ches kyi tsha da ma dang 'brel
NK091(ke)001:4457: te man ngag gi don la nges pa'i gdeng rnyed
NK091(ke)001:4458: pas snying po can ni rdo rje gsum gyi bdag
NK091(ke)001:4459: nyid bla ma slob dpon dam pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:4460: rgyal ba ril gyi yang ston pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:4461: yab yum yin pa'i phyir ram /
NK091(ke)001:4464: thugs rten rdo rje la sogs pa gsum ni mchod pa'i gnas yid rten dam pa yin zhes /
NK091(ke)001:4465: ston pa 'gro ba'i mgon po rdo rje sems dpas bashada do //
NK091(ke)001:4466: zhes lan btab pas gdung ba nyer gnyis pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4471: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4472: sprul pa dang longs spyod dpag tu med pa'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:4473: ba sku gsum gyi bdag nyid ji snyed pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:4474: kyang 'khor ba'i sems can gyi rgyud dag pa las
NK091(ke)001:4475: byung ba'i phyir gzhi la sangs rgyas dang sems can
NK091(ke)001:4476: dbyer med pas rang bzhin dang rgyu 'bras dbang btsan
NK091(ke)001:4477: par byas nas 'khor ba'i sems can gyi rgyun bcad
NK091(ke)001:4478: par gyur na de'i ngo bo'am de la ltos pas
NK091(ke)001:4479: sangs rgyas kyi rgyun yang chad pa yin pas gdung
NK091(ke)001:4480: 'tsho ba ni 'gro ba skal ba can gyi rigs
NK091(ke)001:4481: las byung ba'i skyes bu dam pa rnams kyis 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:4483: de lta bas na 'khor ba med na rgyal ba'ang
NK091(ke)001:4484: mi 'byung na'ang de yod pas de 'byung ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:4485: ro // zhes lan bka' stsal pas gdung ba nyer gsum pa sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4490: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4491: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa mya ngan las 'das pa ni ngo bo nyid med pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:4492: dper na nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon bzhin te de nyid dang po gzhan nas 'ongs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:4493: tha ma gzhan du song ba med par nam mkha'
NK091(ke)001:4494: de nyid las rang byung zhing rang zhi ba ltar
NK091(ke)001:4495: du / don la rgyal ba'i sprul pa thub pa'i
NK091(ke)001:4496: dbang po'i sku yang chos nyid las rang byung nas
NK091(ke)001:4497: slar yang chos nyid du rang zhi bas /
NK091(ke)001:4498: rgyal ba de nyid chos nyid de yi ngang la nub pa med de /
NK091(ke)001:4499: sku mya ngan las 'das par gyur kyang chos nyid dang ma bral bas tha dad pa min la /
NK091(ke)001:4500: sku ma 'das par bzhugs pa na'ang chos nyid dang
NK091(ke)001:4501: bral te tha dad pa min kyang gdul bya rnams
NK091(ke)001:4502: la mtshan nya da sna tshogs kyi bkod pa ston
NK091(ke)001:4504: des na 'da' ba dang mi 'da' ba las 'das
NK091(ke)001:4505: pas na bral dang ma bral gyi tha snyad ga
NK091(ke)001:4507: rgyu mtshan des na de lta bu'i don gang la
NK091(ke)001:4508: 'khor khyed rnams ci yi phyir gdung bar byed de
NK091(ke)001:4509: / gdung ba'i gzhi med cing rgyu dang dgos pa ma dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:4510: sprul pa 'das par mthong nas gdung ba ni ji
NK091(ke)001:4511: bzhin pa la rmongs nas ma rig pas 'khrul pa
NK091(ke)001:4513: de ltar mya ngan byar med pa la gdung bar
NK091(ke)001:4514: byed pa ni e ma'o ngo mtshar che ba ji
NK091(ke)001:4516: 'di go ji ltar yang blo nor ba'i nyes pas 'khrul zhig gu zhes so //
NK091(ke)001:4521: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4522: zhes gang gis na ston pa gsang ba pa'i bdag po des /
NK091(ke)001:4523: tshul ji ltar na skyes bu sku 'gying bag gi
NK091(ke)001:4524: seng ge rnam par lta ba'i lta stangs kyi tshul
NK091(ke)001:4525: gyis gzigs te / bru sha'i skad kyi khrel ba'i
NK091(ke)001:4526: gad mo ste bod skad du'ang grags par ltar ga
NK091(ke)001:4527: zhasa btab ste bzhad mo mdzad pas /
NK091(ke)001:4528: gang la na 'khor rmongsa pas gdung ba rnams sems dga' yid mgu bsam pa rangsa par gyur nas /
NK091(ke)001:4529: mya ngan dang bral bas gdung ba yongs su sangs te /
NK091(ke)001:4530: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin rang snang lhun grub
NK091(ke)001:4531: kyi dkyil 'khor ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su mthong ste
NK091(ke)001:4532: / skye shi med pa'i don rtogs pas /
NK091(ke)001:4533: sems ma bcos par gnas te bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK091(ke)001:4534: thams cad mdangs dang ldan pas 'od gsal bar gyur
NK091(ke)001:4535: to // de dag ni dri ba drug gi gsum pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:4536: gsol gdab drug gi dang po dang /
NK091(ke)001:4537: gdung ba nyer gsum gyi lan dus gcig tu smos
NK091(ke)001:4538: pa ste so so'i rang ngo dang sbyar te shes
NK091(ke)001:4543: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4544: de nas lang ka'i bdag posa gsang ba pa'i bdag po la gsol pa /
NK091(ke)001:4545: gsang ba pa'i bdag po chen po /
NK091(ke)001:4546: 'jig rten gyi khams kun dang dus ril gyi gdung ba thams cad sel tam /
NK091(ke)001:4547: 'on te mi mjed kyi 'jig rten 'di'i da ltar gyi gdung ba 'ba' zhig sel ba lags /
NK091(ke)001:4548: gsang ba pa'i bdag posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:4549: lang ka'i bdag po kho bo ni gdung ba thams cad sel ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:4551: bskul ba'i dus ni gang byung bar //
NK091(ke)001:4552: bdag kyang de bzhin cho 'phrul snang //
NK091(ke)001:4554: 'das pa'i dus kyi gdung ba ji snyed pa yang sngar bsal to //
NK091(ke)001:4555: da lta mi mjed kyi 'jig rten gyi khams 'di'i
NK091(ke)001:4556: gdung ba yang bsal zhing 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan
NK091(ke)001:4557: rdul snyed kyi gdung ba yang de bzhin du basla
NK091(ke)001:4558: la / ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi 'jig rten gyi
NK091(ke)001:4559: khams kun gyi gdung ba ji snyed pa yang sel
NK091(ke)001:4560: la / bar 'gyur ro // lnga pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:4564: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4565: 'o na gdung ba gang la yod zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:4566: de lta bas na gang dag yongs su gdung ba rnams ni /
NK091(ke)001:4567: don skye 'gag med pa'i gnas lugs mi shes pa /
NK091(ke)001:4568: blo ma bcos pa'i rig pa la rmongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:4569: shed ma bye ba kho na yin gyi /
NK091(ke)001:4570: don dang blo shes pas ji bzhin pa la ma rmongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:4571: mkhas pa sheda bye ba rnams ni de kho na
NK091(ke)001:4572: nyid kyi ngang du blo ma bcos par gnas pas
NK091(ke)001:4573: gang du yang gdung ba med pa gdung ba dang
NK091(ke)001:4575: zhes thos pas lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:4576: 'gro ba lus kyi sems dpa' rnams yongs su gdung ba las grol te mya ngan sangs so //
NK091(ke)001:4578: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:4579: bshad zin pa ltar rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba
NK091(ke)001:4580: zhes bya ba'i le'u ste drug pa gsal bar bshad
NK091(ke)001:4581: pa'o // de dag gis theg pa chen po nges
NK091(ke)001:4582: par 'byung ba'i tshul las gang rmongs pa gdung ba
NK091(ke)001:4583: sel ba'i gtam rgyud brjod pa /
NK091(ke)001:4584: chos kyi phyag rgya'i ye shes rnam par bgros pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:4585: byung tshul bstan pa dang po rnam par bshad de
NK091(ke)001:4586: don rgyas par bkrol ba'o ////gnyis pa sgron ma bkod
NK091(ke)001:4587: pa'i byung tshul la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:4588: byung tshul gyi dris lan spyir bstan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:4589: byung tshul gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:4597: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4598: spyir byung tshul 'di nyid dam pa'i sgron ma ji ltar bkod kyi lan te /
NK091(ke)001:4599: khyad par rtsal 'phangs las tshogs lam /
NK091(ke)001:4600: rgyud gnas lugs las sgron ma bkod pa'i byung tshul
NK091(ke)001:4601: ye shes rang gsal gyi lta ba nyi ma'i snying
NK091(ke)001:4602: po lta bu rgyas par ston no //
NK091(ke)001:4603: de nasa langa ka'i badga posa /
NK091(ke)001:4604: sngon thub pa'i dbang po sh+aakya seng ge de nyid
NK091(ke)001:4605: 'jig rten du bzhugs pa na zhal nas dngos su
NK091(ke)001:4606: lung bstan pa gnang ba'i tshig drug gnyis sam bcu
NK091(ke)001:4608: ganga du sgron ma yongsa su bkoda pa na yanga
NK091(ke)001:4609: 'byung zhes lung bstan pa skabs las 'phros te yongsa
NK091(ke)001:4611: gasnga ba pa'i badga po la gsola ba /
NK091(ke)001:4612: gasnga ba pa'i badga po sngon badga gisa dam pa rnams las phyin ci ma loga para thosa pa /
NK091(ke)001:4613: ganga don la shed ma bye ba'i rmongsa pa rnams kyi /
NK091(ke)001:4614: 'jig rten pa ma rig pas sdug bsngal gyis gdung zhing /
NK091(ke)001:4615: lam la gnas pa rnams lam ring ba dang rtsol
NK091(ke)001:4616: ba dang yul du byas pas gdung ba rnams sela
NK091(ke)001:4617: bar byed cing / 'khrul pa yongs su gcod pa'i khyad par /
NK091(ke)001:4618: semsa cana rnams kyi semsa kyi dkyil 'khora ji bzhin
NK091(ke)001:4619: du gasla bar byed pa gnas lugs rang gsal du
NK091(ke)001:4621: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chena po rnams kyi
NK091(ke)001:4622: blo gros dam pa'i mdzod du gyur pas thabs kyi
NK091(ke)001:4623: gsang ba kun rdzogs pa'i khyad par /
NK091(ke)001:4624: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi dgongs pa de kho
NK091(ke)001:4625: na nyid gsang ba dam pa yin pas rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:4626: kun gyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs su gyur pa'i khyad
NK091(ke)001:4627: par te / phyin ci ma log pa yang dag
NK091(ke)001:4628: pa'i lta ba khyad par bzhi dang ldan pas sangs
NK091(ke)001:4630: theg pa chen po gsang sngags lung gi yang bcud chos kyi me long de nyid /
NK091(ke)001:4631: 'degs pa'i yul sprul pa'i skyes bu tshad ma thub
NK091(ke)001:4632: pa'i dbang po 'das nas nub par gyur phan chad
NK091(ke)001:4633: du lha mi phal pa la 'byung bar 'gyur zhig
NK091(ke)001:4639: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4640: gsang ba pa'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:4641: lang ka'i bdag po ji ga 'di ci snyam du sems /
NK091(ke)001:4643: yul tshad ma thub pa nyid kyi ma 'das pa'i dus su bka' stsal gyis /
NK091(ke)001:4644: rig 'dzin gyi rgyal po kun+dza ra zhes bya ba chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:4645: ston pa'i spun yin pas 'khor che ba skyed cing /
NK091(ke)001:4646: gdul bya spro ba bskyed pa'i phyir kho bo cag
NK091(ke)001:4647: gi chos kyi spun du gyur pa la dngos su
NK091(ke)001:4649: rig pa 'dzin pa khyod kyisa dri ba 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:4650: de kho na nyid gsang ba dam pa de ni skabs gnyis dang bcur 'byung ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:4651: gang rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4652: gang 'jig rten gyi sgron ma yongas su bkod pa na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4653: gang gis nges pa rnyed pa na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4654: snying po byang chub nyid du nges pa na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4655: dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4656: gdul bya skabs la bab pa'i ched na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4657: byin gyis rlabs kyis snang ba na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4658: brgyud pa thabsa kyis grags pa na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4659: gang gi ched du mdzad pa na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4660: lung chen nges par bstan pa na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4661: las rgyud yongs su gcod pa na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:4662: dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba na yang 'byung ste /
NK091(ke)001:4663: de dag ni thams cad kyi thams cad nas thams cad du yongs su rnam par snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:4666: zhes mchog gi sprul sku sh+aakya thub pas lung bstan
NK091(ke)001:4667: pa gang de zhing 'di nyid du gragsa par gsungs
NK091(ke)001:4668: pa khyod kyis mi shes sama zhes smras te bka'
NK091(ke)001:4670: de'i don lang ka nang du yang dag par 'jog
NK091(ke)001:4671: pas thub pa'i dbang po las tshul bcu gnyis ma
NK091(ke)001:4672: thos pa'i phyir dris par 'jal to //
NK091(ke)001:4673: tshig 'dis ni phyis kyi lung bstan tsam las dngos
NK091(ke)001:4674: su bka' stsal ba ma yin pa'i phyir yang thub
NK091(ke)001:4675: pa'i dbang po ni rgyud 'di'i ston pa ma yin
NK091(ke)001:4676: par yid ches te kun 'dus rtsa rgyud du bzhed
NK091(ke)001:4677: pa'ang lam klong du gyur pa yon tan gyi gzhir
NK091(ke)001:4678: bstan pa sogs dang bstun na gzhung gi dka' gnad
NK091(ke)001:4679: mang po ma 'dres par gsal ba'i 'chad tshul ngo
NK091(ke)001:4681: 'on kyang lang ka'i bdag pos skabs 'byed pa'i tshig gis mdun bsus te dris pas /
NK091(ke)001:4682: gsang bdag chen pos sngar thub pas bka' stsal pa'i byung tshul bcu gnyis gsungs te /
NK091(ke)001:4683: zhing 'dir grags par lung bstan pa'i lan mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:4684: na dang po'i don rtogs zin pas gnyis pa nas
NK091(ke)001:4685: dri ba dang lan gyis gsal bar bshad pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:4686: rgyud chen po rang nyid la rtsa bshad du bzhag
NK091(ke)001:4687: pa'ang byin rlabs 'byung ba'i bstan pa'i khungs dang 'brel
NK091(ke)001:4688: bar da lta'i sgron ma ston mchog sh+aakya thub pas
NK091(ke)001:4689: lung bstan brgyud pa'i bstan pa rin po che gsang
NK091(ke)001:4690: chen lung gi mdzod khang mdo chen po'i gzhung don
NK091(ke)001:4691: mtha' dag yongs su rdzogs par gsal ba'i 'chad tshul
NK091(ke)001:4692: ngo mtshar bla na med pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:4693: des na de gnyis po mthar thug gi don la
NK091(ke)001:4694: dgongs gnad gcig tu 'bab pa'i tshul la blo gros
NK091(ke)001:4695: kyi 'jug pa thob ste mdo rgyud chen po'i zab
NK091(ke)001:4696: don dngos bstan ji snyed pa thams cad ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:4697: yongs rdzogs su mthong nas gsang ba'i spyi rgya gcod
NK091(ke)001:4698: pa la mkhas par gyur na che ba bdun dang
NK091(ke)001:4699: ldan pa'i bka' dam pa rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs
NK091(ke)001:4700: pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po 'di'i dkyus don ma
NK091(ke)001:4701: lus pa ji bzhin du khrol nas chos kyi mig
NK091(ke)001:4702: dang ldan te rgyud lung man ngag kun gyi dgongs
NK091(ke)001:4703: pa'i mthil rnyed de don gyi nor bu snang ba
NK091(ke)001:4705: e ma mdo rgyud chos kyi me long 'di //
NK091(ke)001:4706: bka' rnams kun gyi dems su nges pa'i phyir //
NK091(ke)001:4707: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sku lnga'i ston mchog dang //
NK091(ke)001:4708: zhing 'di'i sgron ma bu ram shing pa'i bka' //gsang
NK091(ke)001:4709: chen gsang ba zab mo'i mdzod kyi bdag /rgyal tshab
NK091(ke)001:4710: rgyud kyi ston pa rdo rje can //
NK091(ke)001:4711: gang gis rigs can sprul pa'i rgyal sras la //
NK091(ke)001:4712: legs par bgros pa'i nges don snying po'i dpyid //
NK091(ke)001:4713: sngon dus chos rgyal lung bstan rdo rje la //
NK091(ke)001:4714: thub pa'i lung bzhin snang nas gsal bar bshad //
NK091(ke)001:4715: ljongs 'dir gnubs chen yang dbang gter nyid kyis //
NK091(ke)001:4716: rgyas par spel te rdo rje'i tha ram bkrol //
NK091(ke)001:4717: mtshungs med zung dang 'phags bod mkhas grub kyi //
NK091(ke)001:4718: bka' srol bzhin du kun mkhyen kahthoga pas //
NK091(ke)001:4719: khams kyi yul grur chos kyi thang mar brdal //
NK091(ke)001:4720: zag bral 'ja' sku'i rig 'dzin brgyud mar byon //
