NK091(ke)001:4721: 'on kyang re zhig gdul bya'i skal ba yis //
NK091(ke)001:4722: 'degs par ma nus 'grel ba'i dpe yang yib //
NK091(ke)001:4723: de tshe pan chen chos kyi rgya mtsho yis //
NK091(ke)001:4724: dpe gter bzhes te gsang ba'i mdzod sgo phyes //
NK091(ke)001:4725: gang de rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa yi //
NK091(ke)001:4726: gzhung don ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs tshul du //
NK091(ke)001:4727: lung rigs man ngag tshad mas 'dir spros pas //
NK091(ke)001:4728: tshul bzhin blo gros mig gis legs mthong na //
NK091(ke)001:4729: grong khyer gsum gyi gnas na bzhugs pa'i mgon //
NK091(ke)001:4730: khye'u snang ba dam pa dngos mjal te //
NK091(ke)001:4731: dbyings kyi khyim du thabs shes yab yum dang //
NK091(ke)001:4732: 'phrad nas bde chen dpal la spyod par nges //
NK091(ke)001:4733: zhes bya ba ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:4734: 'o na 'di nyid le'u gnyis pa dang bldab bo zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:4736: le'u gnyis par zhu ba po ni rig 'dzin gyi rgyal po kuny+dza ra yin la /
NK091(ke)001:4737: lan 'debs pa po ni ston pa sh+aakya thub pa nyid sku ma 'das pa'i dus su'o //
NK091(ke)001:4739: zhu ba po lang ka'i bdag po yin la /
NK091(ke)001:4740: lan 'debs pa po ni gsang ba'i bdag pos dus
NK091(ke)001:4741: ston pa 'das nas lo brgyad dang bcu gnyis na
NK091(ke)001:4742: lan btab pa yin te sngon gyi lo rgyus gsungs
NK091(ke)001:4743: pa'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:4744: rdo rje sems dpa'i cho 'phrul bkod pa /
NK091(ke)001:4745: de'i gzhi gsang sngags rang gi ngo bo'o //
NK091(ke)001:4753: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4754: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK091(ke)001:4755: yang langa ka'i badga posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:4758: thub pa'i dbang po las ma thos kyang gsang bdag
NK091(ke)001:4759: nyid las thos pa de ni badga gisa thosa pa
NK091(ke)001:4760: dama pa phyin ci ma log par thosa so //
NK091(ke)001:4761: zab par khong du chud pas thosa pa'i mchoga thosa so //
NK091(ke)001:4763: tshul dang po'i the tshom chod pas /
NK091(ke)001:4764: yongas su rmongsa pa gdunga ba ni sangas pa lta na /
NK091(ke)001:4765: gnyis pa'i tshul sgron ma yongas su bkoda pa na yanga 'byung bar /
NK091(ke)001:4766: ji lta ba zhiga tu yongas su gragsa pa lagas /
NK091(ke)001:4767: mi mjed kyi 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir /
NK091(ke)001:4769: sgron ma bkod pa zhes bya bar 'gyur ram /
NK091(ke)001:4771: mi mjeda kyi 'jig rten gyi zhing khams 'di 'bar
NK091(ke)001:4772: zhig gi sgron ma sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das
NK091(ke)001:4773: sam / 'on te 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' dag na /
NK091(ke)001:4774: zhing khams ji snyed pa'i sgron ma bkod pa'i sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das par gyur /
NK091(ke)001:4775: zhes dri ba gsum dris pa las /
NK091(ke)001:4781: zhing khams gang gi sprul pa yin pa /
NK091(ke)001:4782: sangs rgyas gang gi sprul pa yin pa /
NK091(ke)001:4783: thub pa'i nges tshig /sprul pa'i dbye ba bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:4788: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4789: gsang ba pa'i bdag posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:4790: dri ba dang po'i lan du lang ka'i bdag po 'di ji snyam du sems /
NK091(ke)001:4791: thub pa'i dbang po 'das pa 'di yang sgron ma
NK091(ke)001:4792: zhes bya ste sprul pa gcig gis 'dul thabs yin
NK091(ke)001:4793: pas so // dri ba gnyis pa'i lan du /
NK091(ke)001:4794: da ltar ston pa 'das pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:4795: zhing khams mtha' dag gi sangs rgyas lta zhog /
NK091(ke)001:4796: 'dzam bu gling bye ba phrag sa ya'i sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:4797: lta yang zhog /gzhan dag las bye ba phrag brgya
NK091(ke)001:4798: zer yang 'dir ni 'dzam bu'i gling gcig gi sangs
NK091(ke)001:4799: rgyas gcig yongs su mya ngan las 'das par zungs
NK091(ke)001:4801: mi mjed kyi zhing khams 'di ni /
NK091(ke)001:4802: sprul pa'i sku sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa nyag gcig gi zhing khams yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:4803: dri ba gsum pa'i lan du /
NK091(ke)001:4804: de bzhin du stong chen gyi mi mjed kyi 'dzam bu'i gling gi sgron ma sh+aaka thub yin pas /
NK091(ke)001:4805: bsam gyisa mi khyab pa'i sangs rgyas ji snyed pa /
NK091(ke)001:4806: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhal du med pa na sgron ma'i bya ba mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:4807: zhing 'dir ston pa sh+aaka thub 'das nas gzhan du
NK091(ke)001:4808: sgron ma mdzad pa de dag ji lta ba de
NK091(ke)001:4809: ltar sprul pa'i sangs rgyas rdul snyed kyang /
NK091(ke)001:4810: zhing so so na 'da' ba dang sgron ma mdzad tshul de bzhin du blta bar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:4811: 'o na sh+aaka thub kyi zhing khams stong gsum gyi
NK091(ke)001:4812: stong chen po gcig yin nam 'dzam bu'i gling gcig
NK091(ke)001:4814: zhing khams mtha' dag gi sangs rgyas lta zhog /
NK091(ke)001:4815: 'dzam gling bye ba phrag sa ya'i sangs rgyas lta yang zhog /
NK091(ke)001:4816: 'dzam bu gling gcig gi sangs rgyas nyag gcig mya
NK091(ke)001:4817: ngan las 'das par zungs shig /ces pa dang 'gal
NK091(ke)001:4819: stong gsum gyi stong chen po mi mjed zhes bya ba 'di na /
NK091(ke)001:4820: sangs rgyas thub pa'i dbang po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:4821: zhes pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:4822: de ni 'di ltar shes par bya ste /
NK091(ke)001:4823: stong gsum gyi stong chen po gcig na /
NK091(ke)001:4824: sprul pa'i gzhi ma sh+aakya thub pa gcig bzhugs pa de la /
NK091(ke)001:4825: gdul bya'i mthong stangs kyis 'dzam bu'i gling re na
NK091(ke)001:4826: sprul pa'i sku re re bzhugs pa'am 'das par mthong
NK091(ke)001:4828: dper na nam mkha' la nyi ma gcig las med
NK091(ke)001:4829: pa la chu tha dad pa'i nang na nyi ma'i
NK091(ke)001:4830: gzugs brnyan tha dad par snang ba bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:4832: ci ltar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi gzugs gzhal med
NK091(ke)001:4833: khang las ma g.yos bzhin du chu tha dad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:4834: nang du gzugs brnyan snang ba bzhin du sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:4835: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid las ma g.yos bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:4836: / zhing khams dpag tu med par sangs rgyas mtha' yas par snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:4841: zungs shig /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4842: de nas lang ka'i mnga' bdag byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:4844: mi mjed kyi 'jig rten gyi zhing khams 'dzam bu
NK091(ke)001:4845: gling gcig gi sprul pa'i sangs rgyas nyag gcig mya
NK091(ke)001:4846: ngan las 'das pa 'di sangs rgyas gang gi sprul
NK091(ke)001:4847: par yongs su gzung bar bgyi /
NK091(ke)001:4848: gsang ba pa'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:4850: 'di ni rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa bsam gyis
NK091(ke)001:4851: mi khyab pa las sprul pa cha gcig 'ba' zhig
NK091(ke)001:4852: kho nar zungs shig /gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:4856: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4859: zhing khams 'dir sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya bar grags na /
NK091(ke)001:4860: 'di ci ltar yongs su gzung bar bgyis /
NK091(ke)001:4863: de rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa'i bla dwags 'ba' zhig go //
NK091(ke)001:4866: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa ji snyed pas /
NK091(ke)001:4867: bdag gzhan gyi 'khor ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK091(ke)001:4868: dpung gtan du bcom pa'i phyir mtshan thub pa chen
NK091(ke)001:4869: po zhes tha snyad du yongs su grags so //
NK091(ke)001:4874: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4875: de'ang ji ltar 'dul ba'i dbang gis 'jig rten drug gi gnas re re'i phyogs bcur yang /
NK091(ke)001:4876: mtshan mthun par thub pa chen po zhes bya bar yang gragsa pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:4878: lha yi gnas su thub pa chen po brgya byin
NK091(ke)001:4879: lha yi rgyal srid la mnga' dbang sgyur ba'am chos
NK091(ke)001:4880: kyi srid 'dzin pas srid thub 'dzin ces bya bar
NK091(ke)001:4881: grags so // lha ma yin gyi gnas su thub
NK091(ke)001:4882: pa chen po thag bzang ris sam mtha'i g.yul las
NK091(ke)001:4883: rnam para rgyal ba zhes bya bar grags so //
NK091(ke)001:4884: mi yi gnas su thub pa chen po sh+aakya'i rigs
NK091(ke)001:4885: las mi 'jigs par chos ston pas sh+aakya seng ge
NK091(ke)001:4887: byol song gi gnas su thub pa chen po seng
NK091(ke)001:4888: ge yi dam brtan pa'am stobs kyis rnam par gnon
NK091(ke)001:4889: pa zhes bya bar grags so //
NK091(ke)001:4890: yi dwags kyi gnas su thub pa chen po kha
NK091(ke)001:4891: 'bar de ba'am yid bzhin rnam par snang byed ces
NK091(ke)001:4893: dmyal ba'i gnas su thub pa chen po gshin rje
NK091(ke)001:4894: bu'am chos kyi rgyal po zhes bya bar grags so
NK091(ke)001:4899: cha lugs so sor bstan pa'i dgos ched /
NK091(ke)001:4902: tshe dang longs spyod kyi tshad do //
NK091(ke)001:4910: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4911: kye lang ka'i bdag po zhing 'di'i 'jig rten drug
NK091(ke)001:4912: gi thub pa drug po der yang ma zad de
NK091(ke)001:4913: / de ji lta ba de ltar de bzhina du
NK091(ke)001:4914: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i mi mjed kyi 'jig
NK091(ke)001:4915: rten drug gi phyogs bcu na thub pa drug gi
NK091(ke)001:4916: sgron ma yongs su snang ba de lta de ltar
NK091(ke)001:4917: / / rdul snyed kyi 'jig rten gyi khams bsam
NK091(ke)001:4918: gyisa mi khyab pa'i 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu
NK091(ke)001:4920: rdul snyed kyi thub pa drug gi sgron ma mtha' yas para snang ba yang 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:4922: phyogs mtshams kyi zhing khams brgyad du snang zhing grags pa /
NK091(ke)001:4923: rnam par snang ba la sogs pa'i zhing khams zhe gcig tu snang zhing grags /
NK091(ke)001:4924: mi mjed kyi stong gsum du thub pa'i dbang por snang zhing grags pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:4929: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:4930: de ltar zhing bsam gyis mi khyab pa na bzhugs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:4931: mi mjed 'di na snang ba'i tshul gyis khyad par
NK091(ke)001:4932: gyi zhing khams bcu phrag lnga bstan te 'di dag
NK091(ke)001:4933: gi rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa ni le'u tha
NK091(ke)001:4934: ma'i dgongs mdor gsungs pa dag kyang rim pa bzhin
NK091(ke)001:4936: slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyi ti ka bzhin zhes gsungs pa ltar sbyar te bshad na /
NK091(ke)001:4937: phyogs mtshams brgyad las dang po mi mjed kyi 'jig
NK091(ke)001:4938: rten stong gsum po 'di'i pha mtha' nas phar bgrangs
NK091(ke)001:4939: pas shar phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khamsa gling bzhi
NK091(ke)001:4940: ri rab dang bcas pa 'di lta bu'i grangs stong
NK091(ke)001:4941: phrag bcu gnyis 'das pa yi pha rol na /
NK091(ke)001:4942: 'jig rten gyi khamsa der skyes pa'i sems can rnams
NK091(ke)001:4943: gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i ye shes la rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:4944: gyis nyon mongs pa dang nag po'i las la mi
NK091(ke)001:4945: spyod pas mtshan dri ma med pa zhes bya ba
NK091(ke)001:4946: zhing khams de thams cad rgyu rin po che sna
NK091(ke)001:4948: de na gnas pa'ii 'gro ba rnams tshe dang longs
NK091(ke)001:4949: spyod thams cad sum cu rtsa gsum dang mnyam pa
NK091(ke)001:4950: / bar ma dor 'chi ba med cing /
NK091(ke)001:4951: bardzusa nas skye ba sha stag kyang /
NK091(ke)001:4952: 'dod pa thams cad bsam pas 'grub ste /
NK091(ke)001:4953: de na sbyin pa yang med /
NK091(ke)001:4955: len pa dang slong ba po yang med de /
NK091(ke)001:4956: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan dag na gtong slong yod pa dag gi gtam thos pa na /
NK091(ke)001:4957: de dag la tshogs gsog pa'i sgo yod do zhes yongs su smon pa yin te /
NK091(ke)001:4958: zhing de na sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa thub pa'i dbang po de /
NK091(ke)001:4959: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa dri med sgra zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:4960: yod mthong snang grags chos so cog /tha dad sna tshogs mtha' yas kyang //
NK091(ke)001:4961: rang bzhin ma bcos de bzhin nyid //
NK091(ke)001:4962: ma bsgribs 'od gsal rnam dag zhing //
NK091(ke)001:4963: zhes pa'i dgongs pa rnam par bshad de /
NK091(ke)001:4964: theg pa chen po'i chos sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od
NK091(ke)001:4965: gsal ba gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de nyid skal
NK091(ke)001:4966: ldan la ston pas sgron ma chen po yongs su
NK091(ke)001:4967: snang ngo // shar phyogs kyi zhing de nyid kyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na yang /
NK091(ke)001:4968: thub pa drug gi sgron ma snang bas 'gro ba
NK091(ke)001:4969: drug gi sems kyi dkyil 'khor yongs su gsal bar
NK091(ke)001:4970: byed do // 'o na dri med sgra nyid thub pa drug gi cha'am bdun du 'gyur zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:4971: mi las grags pa gtsor byas pa'i dbang yin pas
NK091(ke)001:4972: bdun du mi 'gyur te 'chad pa ril la de
NK091(ke)001:4974: zhing khams dang mtshan ni thub pa so so'i dgongs pa las dpogs shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:4975: gnyis pa yang thub pa'i dbang po de /
NK091(ke)001:4976: lho phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khamsa stong phrag brgya brgyad yang snang /
NK091(ke)001:4979: 'jig rten gyi khams yon tan 'byung ba zhes bya
NK091(ke)001:4980: ba na ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub
NK091(ke)001:4981: pa dkon mchog sprin zhes bya bar sprul nas /
NK091(ke)001:4982: kun tu snang ba'i ye shes 'di //
NK091(ke)001:4983: sus kyang ma byas rang byung ste //
NK091(ke)001:4984: thams cad 'byung ba'i rtsa bas na //
NK091(ke)001:4985: rang las byung ba'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK091(ke)001:4986: zhes pa'i dgongs pa ltar bstan pa sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba /
NK091(ke)001:4987: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de nyid rim dang cig char gyis yongs su snang bar byed do //
NK091(ke)001:4988: de nyid kyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na yang /
NK091(ke)001:4989: thub pa chen po drug gi sgron ma snang bas
NK091(ke)001:4990: 'gro ba drug gi sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal
NK091(ke)001:4991: bar byed do // gsum pa yang thub pa'ii dbang po de /
NK091(ke)001:4992: nub phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag nyi shu 'das pa na /
NK091(ke)001:4993: 'jig rten gyi khams me tog gis rgyan sna tshogs shin tu bkrama pa zhes bya ba na /
NK091(ke)001:4994: gang zag bardzusa nas skye ba sha stag ste /
NK091(ke)001:4995: tshe lo brgyad khri bzhi stong gnas pa'i zhing khams
NK091(ke)001:4996: de na de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa yon
NK091(ke)001:4997: tan 'byung gnas zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:4998: ye nas ma bcos ji bzhin pa //
NK091(ke)001:4999: chos so cog gi snying po ste //
NK091(ke)001:5000: med pa las byung sna tshogs snang //
NK091(ke)001:5001: snang med de bzhin dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK091(ke)001:5002: zhes pa'i dgongs pa ltar sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od
NK091(ke)001:5003: gsal ba gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de nyid ston
NK091(ke)001:5004: to // de nyid kyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na yang /
NK091(ke)001:5005: thub pa drug gi sgron ma snang bas sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal bar byed do //
NK091(ke)001:5006: bzhi pa yang thub pa'i dbang po de /
NK091(ke)001:5007: byang phyogs kyi 'jig rten gyi khams stong khrag suma cu 'das pa na /
NK091(ke)001:5008: 'jiga rten gyi khamsa mnyam nyid rtogs pas bag tsha ba med pa zhes bya ba na /
NK091(ke)001:5009: de bzhin gshegsa pa sh+aakya thub pa seng ge'i sgra zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5010: rang byung rig pa'i sems nyid kyis //
NK091(ke)001:5011: ma bcos chos nyid dbyings kyi don //
NK091(ke)001:5012: lhun grub thabs dang shes rab las //
NK091(ke)001:5013: yang dag rang bzhin dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK091(ke)001:5014: zhes pa'i dgongs pas sems kyi dkyila 'khor 'od gsal ba /
NK091(ke)001:5015: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de nyid ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5016: de nyid kyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na yang thub pa drug gi sgron ma snang bas /
NK091(ke)001:5017: 'gro ba drug gi sems kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar byed do //
NK091(ke)001:5018: lnga pa de bzhin du thub pa'i dbang po de nyid /
NK091(ke)001:5019: shar lho'i 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag brgyad cu brgyad yang snang /
NK091(ke)001:5021: 'jig rten gyi khamsa rin po che la sogs pas rnam par mdzes pa zhes bya ba na /
NK091(ke)001:5022: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa mdzes pa'i tog ces bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5024: bde dang mi bde'i rnam pa kun //
NK091(ke)001:5025: de bzhin nyid du ro gcig pas //
NK091(ke)001:5026: tshor ba bde sdug gang yang med //
NK091(ke)001:5027: ces pa'i dgongs pas gong ma bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5028: drug pa lho nuba kyi mtshams kyi 'jig rten gyi khams stonga phrag bdun cu 'das pa na /
NK091(ke)001:5029: 'jig rten gyi khams rtogs pa gsal bas rab tu snang ba zhes bya ba na /
NK091(ke)001:5030: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa de nyid gzi brjid rgyan zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5031: de bzhin nyid kyis don bstan du //
NK091(ke)001:5032: de bzhin nyid du kun gcig pas //
NK091(ke)001:5033: gang gis gang la gang zhig bstan //
NK091(ke)001:5034: nyid la nyid gleng kho nar zad //
NK091(ke)001:5035: ces gong ma bzhin du chos stona to //
NK091(ke)001:5036: bdun pa nub byang gi mtshams kyi 'jig rten gyi khams stong phrag lnga bcu 'das pa na /
NK091(ke)001:5037: 'jig rtena gyi khams yid rab tu dang ba can zhes bya ba na /
NK091(ke)001:5038: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa tsan dan dri mchog dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5039: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid la //
NK091(ke)001:5040: dus gsum dus bzhir mi dmigs te //
NK091(ke)001:5041: ye shes rig pa'i khyad par las //
NK091(ke)001:5042: skad cig bskal pa de gcig tshul //
NK091(ke)001:5043: zhes gong ma bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5044: brgyad pa byang shar gyi mtshamsa kyi 'jig rten gyi
NK091(ke)001:5045: khams stong phrag bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi 'das pa na
NK091(ke)001:5046: / 'jig rten gyi khams chos kyi sgras gdung ba sel ba zhes bya ba na /
NK091(ke)001:5047: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa de snying rje'i rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5049: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid du //
NK091(ke)001:5050: ye nas mya ngan 'das pas na //
NK091(ke)001:5051: rang bzhin lhun grub tshogs gnyis rdzogs //
NK091(ke)001:5052: zhes gong ma bzhin du chosa ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5057: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5058: de la zhing khams bzhi bcu zhe gcig las /
NK091(ke)001:5060: de bzhin du rnam par snang ba zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5061: sangs rgyas myur du 'dzin pa zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5062: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings 'di la //
NK091(ke)001:5063: 'khor dang mya ngan 'das dang rtag /ye nas rnam par dag pas na //
NK091(ke)001:5064: rang snang lhun grub tshogs chen rdzogs //
NK091(ke)001:5065: zhes ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5067: yang rin chen sna tshogs bkod pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5068: sangs rgyas dga' ba'i spyan zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5069: chos so cog gi rang bzhin ni //
NK091(ke)001:5070: ma skyes pa las thams cad skyes //
NK091(ke)001:5071: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK091(ke)001:5072: rig mchog rdo rje skye gnas dam //
NK091(ke)001:5073: zhes ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5075: yang rin po che gcal du bkram pas rnam par
NK091(ke)001:5076: bkrama pa zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams nas
NK091(ke)001:5077: / de bzhin gshegsa pa yongs su dgongs pa'i rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5078: de bzhin nyid du kun rig na //
NK091(ke)001:5079: des khyab gar gnas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK091(ke)001:5080: yon tan rin chen sprin bkod pa //
NK091(ke)001:5081: bgrod par bya ba ci yang med //
NK091(ke)001:5082: ces ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5084: yang mdog sngo bas bee d+aur+ya'i snying po zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5085: sangs rgyas gser gyi 'od zer zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5086: dpag tu med pa'i rgyal ba rnams //
NK091(ke)001:5087: ji bzhin de bzhin nyid la bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:5088: de bzhin nyid dang thams cad kyang //
NK091(ke)001:5089: gnyis med de bzhin de nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:5090: zhes ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5092: yang 'od rang chas su yod pas 'od dam pa zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5093: de bzhin gshegs pa 'od kyi dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5095: so sor snang ba ma yin te //
NK091(ke)001:5096: ji bzhin de bzhin nyid nges na //
NK091(ke)001:5097: de la 'khor ba'i rang bzhin med //
NK091(ke)001:5098: ces ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5100: yang sems can rnams sems zhi bas rnam par zhi ba zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khamsa nas /
NK091(ke)001:5101: de bzhin gshegs pa zhi ba'i dbang po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5102: de bzhin nyid kyi de nyid ni //
NK091(ke)001:5103: dpag med gzhal bar mtha' yas pas //
NK091(ke)001:5104: dpag med rgyal ba'i pho brang yin //
NK091(ke)001:5105: de na kun bkod der gcig nas //
NK091(ke)001:5106: zhes ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5108: yang thugs rje char rgyun lta bus sprin rnam par
NK091(ke)001:5109: bkod par zhes bya ba'i 'jig rten gyi khams na
NK091(ke)001:5110: / de bzhin gshegs pa sprin gyi dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5112: cir yang 'gyur ba'i ye shes te //
NK091(ke)001:5113: gdos par gyur pa'i chos med pas //
NK091(ke)001:5114: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'byung //
NK091(ke)001:5115: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhina du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5117: yang ngo bo nyid kyis yid mngon par dga' ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5118: sangs rgyas yid du 'ong ba'i dbyangs zhes bya bar bstan nasa /
NK091(ke)001:5120: ma rig ngo bo de bzhin pas //
NK091(ke)001:5121: gzhi rtsa med pa'i skad cig ma //
NK091(ke)001:5122: de nyid rig na bde chen gnas //
NK091(ke)001:5123: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5125: yanga sa gzhi thams cad la gzugs brnyan 'char bas
NK091(ke)001:5126: me long gi dkyil 'khor shin tu sbyangs pa zhes
NK091(ke)001:5128: sangs rgyas me long gi 'od snang ba zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5129: nyon mongs ye shes lngar rtog pa //
NK091(ke)001:5130: ji bzhin de la gnyis kas sgrib //
NK091(ke)001:5131: rtog dang mi rtog gnyis med de //
NK091(ke)001:5132: rtog pa de nyid yang dag lam //
NK091(ke)001:5133: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5135: yang sa gzhi la zla ba lta bu'i 'od mang
NK091(ke)001:5136: bas zla bas brgyan pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams
NK091(ke)001:5137: na / sangs rgyas zla 'od dpal zhes bya bar bstan nasa /
NK091(ke)001:5138: theg pa dpag med bstan pa yang //
NK091(ke)001:5139: ji ltar mos pa tha dad pa //
NK091(ke)001:5140: khrid par bya ba'i thabs su zad //
NK091(ke)001:5141: rdo rje theg pa nyid las med //
NK091(ke)001:5142: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5144: 'di yang sa gzhi la nyi ma lta bu'i 'od
NK091(ke)001:5145: mang bas nyi ma'i 'od zer brgyan pa zhes bya
NK091(ke)001:5147: de bzhin gshegs pa nyi ma'i snying po'i dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5148: gang gis de ltar mthong ma thag /mi shes chod pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod //
NK091(ke)001:5149: khyung dang seng ge ji bzhin du //
NK091(ke)001:5150: mngal ltar lus kyi mngal gyis bsgribs //
NK091(ke)001:5151: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5153: yang zhing la spos ngad ldang bas spos dri ngad ldang zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5154: sangs rgyas spos kyi rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5155: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi ye shes kyis //
NK091(ke)001:5156: sgyu ma'i chos la dbang thob pas //
NK091(ke)001:5157: mun la snang 'byung ji bzhin du //
NK091(ke)001:5158: thams cad dbang bsgyur rang rig yin //
NK091(ke)001:5159: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5161: yang longs spyod chos dang mthun pas rnam par spros pa'i rgyan zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5162: sangs rgyas rnam par spros pa'i rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5163: rnam dag ye shes sgyu ma dang //
NK091(ke)001:5164: log rtog mtshan ma'i sgyu ma gnyis //
NK091(ke)001:5165: de bzhin de nyid gcig pas na //
NK091(ke)001:5166: gnyis su shes pa nyid tshogs rdzogs //
NK091(ke)001:5167: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5169: yang rin po che sna tshogs kyis spras pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5170: sangs rgyas rin chen rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5171: bsam gyis mi khyab chos 'di rnams //
NK091(ke)001:5172: de bzhin nyid du gcig pas na //
NK091(ke)001:5173: gang gis de bzhin de shes na //
NK091(ke)001:5174: kun la dbang bsgyur thob pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:5175: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5177: yang rang bzhin gyis zhing la 'od 'khrigs pas 'od zer 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5178: sangs rgyas 'od zer dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5179: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa 'di //
NK091(ke)001:5180: shes nas de la gang gnas pa //
NK091(ke)001:5181: rang rig nyid la dbang thob pa'i //
NK091(ke)001:5182: de bzhin rigs chen 'dzin pa nyid //
NK091(ke)001:5183: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5185: yang bya dka' ba la sgrubs pas rnam par spyod pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5186: sangs rgyas dka' thub rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5187: de nyid ji bzhin mngon gyur na //
NK091(ke)001:5188: med la mi zad 'byung ba yi //
NK091(ke)001:5189: che ba'i yon tan rgyun mi 'chad //
NK091(ke)001:5190: cir snang kun 'byung rin chen gter //
NK091(ke)001:5191: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5193: yang theg pa'i rtse mo ston pas gtsuga tor bkod pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5194: sangs rgyas gtsug tor snying po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5195: ji bzhin ma bcos de nyid la //
NK091(ke)001:5196: de bzhin pa yi blo bzhag pa //
NK091(ke)001:5197: de bzhin de nyid ma yin pa'i //
NK091(ke)001:5198: sgrub dang bsgrub pa ga la yod //
NK091(ke)001:5199: ces yang dag pa ja lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5201: yang thams cad rigs theg chen du nges pas nges pa can zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5202: sangs rgyas nges par gshegs pa zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5203: mkha' la glo bur sprin 'thibs ltar //
NK091(ke)001:5204: de bzhin glo bur rtog pas sgribs //
NK091(ke)001:5205: mkha' dag nang du sprin sangs ltar //
NK091(ke)001:5206: rnam rtog stong pas ngang gis sangs //
NK091(ke)001:5207: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5209: yang 'bras bu la sbyor bas nges par 'phags pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5210: sangs rgyas nges par gsung ba zhes bya bar bstan nasa /
NK091(ke)001:5211: ji snyed dag pa'i gsung brjod kyang //
NK091(ke)001:5212: rdo rje'i gsung la spros pa med //
NK091(ke)001:5213: spros med gsung nyid kun gsal khyab //
NK091(ke)001:5214: ma gsung ba nyid rgya cher bshad //
NK091(ke)001:5215: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5217: yang gsang ba mchog gi thabs kyi bdag nyid bde spyod zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5218: sangs rgyas bde ba chen po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5219: thams cad yul la 'jug pa yi //
NK091(ke)001:5220: thogs med ma chags de bzhin blos //
NK091(ke)001:5221: ji snyed de bzhin nyid du bsgyur //
NK091(ke)001:5222: zad med gter ldan rin chen 'byung //
NK091(ke)001:5223: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5225: yang dngos su me tog sna tshogs bkra bas me tog bkram pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5226: sangs rgyas me tog dbang po'i dbyangs zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5227: ji bzhin nyid la bzhugs pas na //
NK091(ke)001:5228: 'di zhes tshig tu ma gsungs kyang //
NK091(ke)001:5229: khyab pas gcig pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK091(ke)001:5231: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5233: yang 'jig rten thams cad du yongs su gragsa pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5234: sangs rgyas gragsa pa'i dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5235: sangs rgyas sems can la sogs pa //
NK091(ke)001:5236: thams cad ma lus lus pa med //
NK091(ke)001:5237: rang rig ma rig rtog pa nyid //
NK091(ke)001:5238: kun kyang rang byung ye shes nyid //
NK091(ke)001:5239: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5241: yang cho 'phrul gyis rnam par 'phrul pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5242: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5243: yi ge phyag rgya ye shes kyang //
NK091(ke)001:5244: tshig lam 'byung ba'i gzhi yin te //
NK091(ke)001:5245: de nyid dag pas thams cad dag /gsung la gsung nyid mi gnas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5246: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5248: yang zhing dag par thams cad ngag snyan pas rnam par sbyangs pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khamsa na /
NK091(ke)001:5249: sangs rgyas sgra dbyangs mi zad pa zhes bya bar bstan nasa /
NK091(ke)001:5250: de bzhin nyid kyi rang bzhin du //
NK091(ke)001:5251: lnga phung nyon mongs rnam par dag /rnam rtog rdul bral skye 'gag med //
NK091(ke)001:5252: thams cad ngo bo nyid du bcom //
NK091(ke)001:5253: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5255: yang nyon mongs pas gdung ba thabs kyis zhi bas
NK091(ke)001:5256: sman gyis brgyan pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na
NK091(ke)001:5257: / sangs rgyas sman gyi rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nasa /
NK091(ke)001:5258: dpag med 'jig rten rdul rnyed na //
NK091(ke)001:5259: 'gro ba rdul phran bsam yas la //
NK091(ke)001:5260: khyad par de bzhin nyid snang bas //
NK091(ke)001:5261: til 'bru mar gyis khyab ltar gnas //
NK091(ke)001:5262: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5264: yang dngos su gser 'od ldan pas gser gyi 'od snang ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5265: sangs rgyas gser gyi 'od 'phro zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5266: rdul phran gcig tsam gang zag la //
NK091(ke)001:5267: dgongs te mdun du gsung brjod pa //
NK091(ke)001:5268: dpag med mtha' yas rdul snyed tsam //
NK091(ke)001:5269: de snyed kun thos rnam par grol //
NK091(ke)001:5270: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5272: yang 'od zer sna tshogs bkod pa lta bu zhes bya ba'i zhing khamas na /
NK091(ke)001:5273: sangs rgyas bkod pa'i rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5274: gsung gcig mi zad mtha' yas gsung //
NK091(ke)001:5275: mtha' dang dbus med kun tu khyab //
NK091(ke)001:5276: khyab dang khyab med rdo rje'i gsung //
NK091(ke)001:5277: sna tshogs dngos med de bzhin nyid //
NK091(ke)001:5278: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5280: yang dngos su gser 'byung bas gser gyi 'byung gnas zhes bya ba'i zhing khamsa na /
NK091(ke)001:5281: sangs rgyas gser gyi gzu ba zhes bya ba bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5282: gang yang ma bcos de nyid la //
NK091(ke)001:5283: phyogs dang snga phyi dus med de //
NK091(ke)001:5284: thams cad de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings //
NK091(ke)001:5285: de nyid rang byung de nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:5286: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5288: yang mchog gi bsgrub pa dam pas dpal gyi 'byung gnas zhes bya ba'i zhing khamsa na /
NK091(ke)001:5289: sangs rgyas dpal gyi rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5290: de nyid de snyed rang bzhin te //
NK091(ke)001:5291: de snyed de nyid yin pa la //
NK091(ke)001:5292: byis pa rnams kyis gnyis su bzung //
NK091(ke)001:5293: de la gnyis su dbye byar med //
NK091(ke)001:5294: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5296: yang dbyer med ston pas snang ba dam pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5297: sangs rgyas snang ba brtsegs pa'i dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5298: stong nyid nam mkha'i rang bzhin du //
NK091(ke)001:5299: mi mthun pa dang gnyen po gnyis //
NK091(ke)001:5300: ye nas dbyer med gcig pas na //
NK091(ke)001:5301: gnod pas 'jigs pa ga la yod //
NK091(ke)001:5302: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5304: yang bden pa mthong bas mya ngan med pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5305: sangs rgyas mya ngan med pa'i dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5306: mi 'gyur nam mkha'i rang bzhin te //
NK091(ke)001:5307: dag pa dag la dag pa nyid //
NK091(ke)001:5308: rtog pa dag la rtog par snang //
NK091(ke)001:5309: cis 'dul der snang ci yang med //
NK091(ke)001:5310: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5312: yang don khong du chud pas dga' ba'i mdangs zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5313: sangs rgyas dga' mchog dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5314: rang bzhin ngang gis ma bcos pa //
NK091(ke)001:5315: yongs kyis 'od gsal de bzhin nyid //
NK091(ke)001:5316: kun gyi snying po de nyid pas //
NK091(ke)001:5317: cis kyang ma bsgribs nam mkha' che //
NK091(ke)001:5318: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5320: yang sems can rnams mtshan dpe dang ldan pas gaza brjid 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5321: sangsa rgyas gzi brjid dpal zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5322: ji bzhin pa nyid sa mchog ste //
NK091(ke)001:5323: de rig ye shes bla ma'i sa //
NK091(ke)001:5324: ye nas de bzhin nyid la gnas //
NK091(ke)001:5325: da gdod bgrod du ga la yod //
NK091(ke)001:5326: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5328: yang dngos su rgyal ba rnams 'du bas sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:5329: mang po 'du ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khamsa na
NK091(ke)001:5330: / sangsa rgyas kun gyi dge ba'i bshesa gnyen zhesa bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5331: stong pa nyid kyi snying po la //
NK091(ke)001:5332: sna tshogs snang ba'i 'khor gyis bskor //
NK091(ke)001:5333: sus kyang ma byas rang byung ba //
NK091(ke)001:5334: ji bzhin pa yi dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK091(ke)001:5335: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhina du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5337: yanga las kyi sgrib pa sbyong bas yongsa su sbyong ba zhesa bya ba'i zhing khamas na /
NK091(ke)001:5338: sangs rgyas ngan song thams cad sbyong ba zhes bya bar bstan nasa /
NK091(ke)001:5339: zag med ye shes dngos grub ni //
NK091(ke)001:5340: de bzhin nyid du dngos grub pas //
NK091(ke)001:5341: zad pa med cing 'phel ba med //
NK091(ke)001:5342: da gdod bsgrub tu ga la yod //
NK091(ke)001:5343: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5345: yang mos pa sna tshogs pas tha dad spyod pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5346: sangs rgyas 'jiga rten kun gyi slob dpona zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5347: chos kun rang bzhin med pa nyid //
NK091(ke)001:5348: mya ngan 'das zhes de la bya //
NK091(ke)001:5349: stong nyid rang bzhin rnam dag pa //
NK091(ke)001:5350: de nyid mi gnas byang chub sems //
NK091(ke)001:5351: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5353: yang rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo dpung rgyan zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5354: sangs rgyas rnam par rgyal ba zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5355: rnam rtog chu bo'i rka mgo de //
NK091(ke)001:5356: stong nyid zhing du ma bsgyur na //
NK091(ke)001:5358: de mi shes la de ltar snang //
NK091(ke)001:5359: zhes yang dag pa ji bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5361: yang dngos su ge sar me ta zhes bya bas
NK091(ke)001:5362: brgyan pas me tog mdzes pa'i rgyan zhes bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:5363: zhing khams na / sangs rgyas me tog bkod pa'i rgyal po zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5364: ji bzhin pa yi de bzhin nyid //
NK091(ke)001:5365: thams cad 'byung ba'i ma yin pas //
NK091(ke)001:5366: kun bzang shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK091(ke)001:5367: sems can sangs rgyas kun gyi gnas //
NK091(ke)001:5368: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5370: yang spyod yul thams cad mdzes par snang ba zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5371: sangsa rgyas thams cad snang ba zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5372: stug po bkod pa'i sangs rgyas dang //
NK091(ke)001:5373: sems can rnam pa thams cad dag /dngos po brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK091(ke)001:5374: de nyid las byung dngos med sku //
NK091(ke)001:5375: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5377: yanga tsan dan bkoda pa zhes bya ba'i zhing khams na /
NK091(ke)001:5378: sangsa rgyas tsan dan dri zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5379: rang byung ye shes rtsa ba ni //
NK091(ke)001:5380: byang chub sems nyid yin pas na //
NK091(ke)001:5381: de yi rtsa ba snying rje ste //
NK091(ke)001:5382: pha rol phyin par thabs kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5383: zhes yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5385: yang seng ge 'byung gnas zhes bya ba'i zhing khamsa na /
NK091(ke)001:5386: sangsa rgyas seng ge 'bum gzugs zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5387: ji snyed ji bzhin nyid kyi don //
NK091(ke)001:5388: yi ge ming tshig sgras mtshon pa //
NK091(ke)001:5389: ming tshig sgra la ma brten pa //
NK091(ke)001:5390: nyams drod blo yis rig pa med //
NK091(ke)001:5391: ces yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5396: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5397: yang stong gsum gyi stong chen po mi mjed kyi zhing khams zhes bya ba 'di na /
NK091(ke)001:5398: sprul pa'i sku mchog da ltar gyi ston pa sangs
NK091(ke)001:5399: rgyas thub pa'i dbang po sh+aakya seng ge don kun
NK091(ke)001:5400: grub pa zhes bya bar bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5401: chos kun chos kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK091(ke)001:5402: de bzhin nyid las mi gzhan pas //
NK091(ke)001:5403: de nyid byang chub lam nyid de //
NK091(ke)001:5404: lam de stug po bkod pa'i gnas //
NK091(ke)001:5405: zhes de bzhin nyid kyi dgongs pa zab mo las
NK091(ke)001:5406: brtsams te yang dag pa ji lta ba de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:5408: de ltar dgongs mdo rnams bde ba gsal mdzad kyi
NK091(ke)001:5409: ti ka ma mjal zhing dam pa rin po che'i
NK091(ke)001:5410: phyag mchan na mi gsal yang /
NK091(ke)001:5411: kun mkhyen rong zom chen po'i zhal slob ru yong rin chen 'bar las /
NK091(ke)001:5412: mkhas pa 'brom ston gyis zhus te phyag dpe gsar
NK091(ke)001:5413: bzhengs mdzad pa'i mchan rnying dang bstun na sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:5414: myur du 'dzin pa ma gtogs rang gzhung dang 'grigs
NK091(ke)001:5415: pas / bka' lung la snang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:5416: don dang mi 'gal bar rigs pas 'thad pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:5417: la yid ches kyis nges pa rnyed na'ang mchan la
NK091(ke)001:5418: la na cung zad 'dra min 'dug go //
NK091(ke)001:5423: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5424: de dag tu ma zad de de bzhin du 'jig
NK091(ke)001:5425: rten gyi khams bye ba sa yar rdo rje sems
NK091(ke)001:5426: dpa'i sku dang mtshan bye ba sa yara bstan nas
NK091(ke)001:5427: / chos yang dag pa ji lta ba bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:5428: snang bar mdzad de ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin don
NK091(ke)001:5429: mdzad pa'ang 'gro 'ong med par snang bas chu la
NK091(ke)001:5431: de dag la dus gcig tu chos ston pa ni ma yin te /
NK091(ke)001:5432: 'khor mor rgyun ma chad pa'i phyir la lara ni
NK091(ke)001:5433: 'og min dang de nyid du mngona para rdzogas para
NK091(ke)001:5434: sangsa rgyas / gnas dang dus la lara ni da dung yum gyi lhumsa na bzhugs /
NK091(ke)001:5435: la lara ni dag'a ldana gyi gansa na bzhugs /
NK091(ke)001:5436: la lara ni thub ba lta bu sku yongsa su mya ngan las 'das so //
NK091(ke)001:5437: la lar ni 'ad'a ba'i tshul bstan nas /
NK091(ke)001:5438: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan nas gzhan gyi sgron mara snang ste chos ston par mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5439: de'ang sprul pa la so sor ngos bzung ba 'thad pa min te /
NK091(ke)001:5440: gdul bya'i mthong stangs ltar tshul brtsi ba mi 'gal bas so //
NK091(ke)001:5445: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5446: 'dir yang sprul pa tha dad sems can bzang ngan
NK091(ke)001:5447: gyi cha lugs kyis kyang chos ston te la lar
NK091(ke)001:5448: ni / rin chen bdun dang dpung tshogs bzhi ldan
NK091(ke)001:5449: zhing longs spyod btsun mo dang bcas te 'khor los
NK091(ke)001:5450: sgyur ba'i cha lugs kyis theg pa chen po'i chos
NK091(ke)001:5451: gsang ba dam pa ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5452: la lar ni nyan thos kyi cha byad kyis theg pa chung ngu'i chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5453: la lar ni rang sangs rgyas kyi cha byad kyisa rdzu 'phrul gyisa chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5454: la lar ni snying po byang chub brnyes nas shing drung na dgongs pa mdzad de bzhugs /
NK091(ke)001:5455: la lar ni bskul ba'i sa la gzhes te 'og
NK091(ke)001:5456: min chen po dang de nyid du chos kyi 'khor
NK091(ke)001:5457: lo bskor / la lar ni khyim med par rab tu byung ste thar pa'i cha lugs kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5458: la lar ni lus kyi cha byad khyim pa'i cha lugs kyis sa //
NK091(ke)001:5459: la lar ni lha yi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5460: la lar ni klu yi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5461: la lar ni lha ma yin gyi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5462: la lar ni bar chod byed pa bdud kyi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5463: la lar ni gnod sbyin gyi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5464: la lar ni srin po'i cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5465: la lar ni 'byung po'i cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5466: la lar ni nam mkha' lding gser mig gi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5467: la lar ni mgo lus mi 'tshams pa'am mu stegs
NK091(ke)001:5468: gcer bu pa lta bu ya mtshan can gyi cha
NK091(ke)001:5469: byad kyis so // la lar ni byol song gi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5470: la lar ni yi dwags kyi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5471: la lar ni dmyal ba lta bu bzod ldan gyi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5472: la lar ni srog gcod pas shan pa'i cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5473: la lar ni lus kyis 'dod pa tshol bas smad 'tshong ma'i cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5474: la lar ni chags pa la sems par na chung gi cha byad kyis so //
NK091(ke)001:5475: la lar ni sku gdung sha ri ram mam mdun
NK091(ke)001:5476: na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas lta bur yang snang ngo
NK091(ke)001:5477: // la lar ni rus pa'i sku'i ring srel lam chos kyi ring bsrel lta bur yang snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5478: sprul sku rigs lnga'i cha lugs can la lar ni rdo rje sems dpa' nyid du snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5479: la lar ni rnam par snang mdzad lta bur snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5480: la lar ni rin chen 'byung ldan lta bur snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5481: la lar ni snang ba mtha' yas lta bur snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5482: la lar ni don yod grub pa lta bur snang ste /
NK091(ke)001:5483: de dag kun kyang yang dag pa ji bzhin du chos ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5488: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5489: gzhan yang skye ba tha dad pa'i gzugs 'di dag
NK091(ke)001:5490: la rang rgyud pa dang sprul pa gnyis gnyis yod
NK091(ke)001:5491: de rang rgyud pa skal ba can rnams de dang
NK091(ke)001:5492: mthun pa'i sprul pas gdul ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:5493: gti mug gi rgyal po grol bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:5494: gdul bya dang 'dra bar zil gyis gnon pas tshangs pa'i gzugs lta bur snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5495: zhe sdang gi rgyal po dgrol bar bya ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:5496: 'khor lo nag po can khyab 'jug gi gzugs lta
NK091(ke)001:5497: bur snang ngo // 'dod chags kyi rgyal po dgrol bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:5498: ma h+aa de ba drag po'i gzugs lta bur snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5499: nga rgyal gyi rgyal po dgrol bar bya ba'i phyir dregs pa tshogs bdag lta bur snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5500: phrag dog gi bdag po dgrol bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:5501: brgya byin lha yi dbang po lta bura snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5502: 'di sa bzhi pa yan chad la'ang 'byung gsung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5503: de bzhin du rgyud tha dad pa'i skye ba thams cad kyi gzugs su snang ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:5505: ra hu la sred med de 'di gnyis gza' dang /
NK091(ke)001:5515: srin bu me khyer ram lham bu chu gsher dang /
NK091(ke)001:5516: sroga chagsa ldem bu ste phye ma leb dang /
NK091(ke)001:5517: gang zin pa de dang de'i gzugs su sprul pa snang bar mdzad cing /
NK091(ke)001:5518: de'i cha byad kyis gang dag ji ltar mos pa rnams la de bzhin du snang ste /
NK091(ke)001:5519: ji ltar nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor gyi gzugs gzhal med khang las ma g.yos par /
NK091(ke)001:5520: chu tha dad pa'i nang du gzugs brnyan chu'i grangs ltar tha dad par snang ba bzhin du /
NK091(ke)001:5521: don sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa' nyid las ma
NK091(ke)001:5522: g.yosa bzhin du zhing khams dpag tu med par sangs
NK091(ke)001:5523: rgyas mtha' yas par snang ste dgos ched bsam gyis
NK091(ke)001:5524: mi khyab pa dang 'brel bar 'byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5526: mtshan mtha' yas par bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:5527: mtshan thos pa'i yon tan no //
NK091(ke)001:5532: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5533: de ltar na gang ming sna tshogs su btags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:5534: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams mtha' yas pa na 'khod
NK091(ke)001:5535: pa'i sems can rnams kyisa sangs rgyas rdo rje sems
NK091(ke)001:5536: dpa' ni ye ji bzhin pa dang rgyud dag pa
NK091(ke)001:5537: gnyis ka yin na'ang rgyud dag pa'i rdo rje sems
NK091(ke)001:5538: dpa'i mtshan kho na sna tshogsa par shes pa ni
NK091(ke)001:5539: brjod kyis mi lang ba'i bskal par smras kyang shar
NK091(ke)001:5540: phyogs gcig pu'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing na bzhugs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:5541: mtshan gyi mtha' yang mi rdzogs so //
NK091(ke)001:5542: de bzhin du phyogs thamsa cad kyi sangs rgyas kyi zhing na 'khod pa'i sems can rnams kyis /
NK091(ke)001:5543: brjod kyis mi lang ba'i bskal par smras kyang mtshan gyi mtha' ni mi rdzogsa so //
NK091(ke)001:5544: ji ltar sems can mos pa chung ngu rnams kyis
NK091(ke)001:5545: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhing khams tshad med pa dang
NK091(ke)001:5546: mtshan mtha'a yas pa thos na blo la mi shong
NK091(ke)001:5547: bas 'jig mi nus par blo ga chad pa dang
NK091(ke)001:5548: dran pa nyams te myos par 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:5551: sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa'i /
NK091(ke)001:5554: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5555: sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan gang gisa thos pa desa yon tan 'di dag 'dzin te /
NK091(ke)001:5556: rgyal ba thams cad kyi dngos gzhi yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:5557: lam pa'i dbang du na don gzhan la dgongs te
NK091(ke)001:5558: rgyal ba mang po la sngon du bya ba byas
NK091(ke)001:5559: pa yin no // snying po byang chub las mi
NK091(ke)001:5560: 'gyur bar nges pa'am phyis snang ba'i skal ba nges
NK091(ke)001:5561: pa can yin pa'i phyir rdo rje sems dpa'i zhing
NK091(ke)001:5562: khams nyid du nges para 'byung ba yin no //
NK091(ke)001:5563: bde gshegs mang pos sngar byin gyis brlabs te bdag
NK091(ke)001:5564: nyid byin rlabs kyi bdag po yin pa'i phyir sgron
NK091(ke)001:5565: ma bkod pa'i rgyal ba rnams kyis byin gyis brlabs
NK091(ke)001:5566: pa yin no // theg pa chen po gsang ba mchog gis nges par 'byung ba yin no //
NK091(ke)001:5567: mngon par shes pa dag dang ldan pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:5568: sangs rgyas kyi thugs kyi sras su nges pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:5569: lhag mthong gi mig dang ldan pa dag yin no //
NK091(ke)001:5570: zhes dbang po mchog dang ldan pa la yon tan de dag ril thob pa yin kyang /
NK091(ke)001:5571: dbang po dman pa'i dbang du na /
NK091(ke)001:5572: gnyis pa'i zur phyi ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:5573: bzhi pa nas mar lnga ka thams cad dus gzhan la dgongs pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:5578: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5579: ji ltar rdo rje sems dpa'i zhing khams de dag
NK091(ke)001:5580: gi sprul pa'i dbang du phan tshun smos pa las
NK091(ke)001:5581: yan man gsal bar ma bstan kyang /
NK091(ke)001:5582: 'dir phyogs bcu kar 'jal bar bya ste bye bas
NK091(ke)001:5583: yar snang ba'i phyir de ltar zhing de rnams thamsa
NK091(ke)001:5584: cada na / semsa kyi dkyil 'khora 'od gsal ba
NK091(ke)001:5585: gsang sngagsa kyi ngo bo de nyid 'ab'a zhig yanga
NK091(ke)001:5586: dag pa ji lta ba bzhina du /
NK091(ke)001:5588: rgyu'i theg pas rim gyis dang sngags kyi theg pas cig char bar ston to //
NK091(ke)001:5589: 'o na chos ston lugs gnyis kho nar smos pa ji zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:5592: rdo rje semsa dpa'i zhing khamsa na 'akhada pa'i 'gro ba semsa cana rnams ni /
NK091(ke)001:5593: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi skal ba dang
NK091(ke)001:5594: ldan pa'i phyir chena po zhes khyad par gyi sgrar
NK091(ke)001:5595: brjod de de daga ni chos can semsa kyi rang
NK091(ke)001:5596: bzhina yid kyi shes pa dang nyon mongs can gyi
NK091(ke)001:5597: yid la sogs pa kun gzhi'i rgyud la khams sna
NK091(ke)001:5598: tshagas pa'i khyad par yod pa'i phyira /
NK091(ke)001:5599: de nyid la shes rab ji bzhin pa mthong ba'i
NK091(ke)001:5600: mthu can rgya mtsho lta bu blo shina tu zaba
NK091(ke)001:5601: pa dang / de kho na nyid kyi mu mtha'
NK091(ke)001:5602: tshol ba ldeng ka'am khron pa lta bu blo mi
NK091(ke)001:5603: pa dang / zab pa dang / gang la yang
NK091(ke)001:5604: mi skrag cing theg pas lung don ji bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:5605: shong ba bar snang lta bu blo yangsa pa dang
NK091(ke)001:5606: pa dang / zab pa dang / / de ltar
NK091(ke)001:5607: don zab mo mi shong ba ri brag lta bu
NK091(ke)001:5608: pa dang / zab pa dang / / dog pa
NK091(ke)001:5609: dang / nges pa ji bzhin par rnyed de nam
NK091(ke)001:5610: yang mi 'gyur ba ri rab lta bu blo brtan
NK091(ke)001:5611: pa dang / zab pa dang / / dog pa
NK091(ke)001:5612: dang / pa dang / de ltar ma nges pa'i
NK091(ke)001:5613: blo can chu bo lta bu kun 'gyur ba dang
NK091(ke)001:5614: pa dang / zab pa dang / / dog pa
NK091(ke)001:5615: dang / pa dang / / don ji lta bar
NK091(ke)001:5616: thag chod pa ral gri lta bu blo shin tu
NK091(ke)001:5617: pa dang / zab pa dang / / dog pa
NK091(ke)001:5618: dang / pa dang / / rno ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:5619: de ltar don thag mi chod pa byang gri ste
NK091(ke)001:5620: khrab byang gi gri lta bu rtul ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:5621: lan mang du thebs shing yul don la de ma
NK091(ke)001:5622: thag par 'jug pa glog lta bu blo myur ba
NK091(ke)001:5623: dang / lan don thogs pa dang bcas pa bu
NK091(ke)001:5624: chung lta bu bul ba ste sna tshogs pa dang
NK091(ke)001:5625: gcig pa sha stag pas gsang sngags kyi ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:5626: nyid kyi gtam der yang blo dman rnams ni rim
NK091(ke)001:5627: dang / gyis pa dang / blo bzang rnams ni cig char bar nges pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:5628: de ltar cha gnyis las gzhan pa bkag pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5629: de lta bur blo dman pa dang mchog gis rim
NK091(ke)001:5630: pa bzhin gsang sngags la 'jug lugs gnyis su thos
NK091(ke)001:5631: nas kyang ye nas dbang po gcig chod dam dman
NK091(ke)001:5632: pas sbyangs pa las gyur pa'ang rung ste rigs can
NK091(ke)001:5633: du gyur pa de dag gang la'ang mi skrag mi
NK091(ke)001:5634: dngang gi / chos la bzod pa thob nas dga' zhing mgu ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:5635: rangsa par 'gyur ba'i phyir blo dang chos sna tshogs su snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5640: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5641: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhing khams de na gnas pa'i
NK091(ke)001:5642: 'gro ba rnams ni las dang bsod nams tha dad
NK091(ke)001:5643: pas tshe'i tshad kyang gcig tu ma nges te thung
NK091(ke)001:5646: zhing 'dir da ltar gyi sprul pa nyag gcig gi dbang gis brgya pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:5647: brgyad khri bzhi stong thub pas sna tshogs pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:5648: rgyu des na longs spyod kyang ni /
NK091(ke)001:5649: ji ltar bsam pa bzhin du 'byung ba yang yod /
NK091(ke)001:5650: so nams dang khe spogs sogs dka' bas 'byongsa pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:5652: de dag kun kyang ril snying po byang chub kyi
NK091(ke)001:5653: ngo bo nyid kyis bsnums pa'i phyir rang bzhin mnyam
NK091(ke)001:5654: pa nyid la dgongs pa'am mtha' 'khob kyi mi dang
NK091(ke)001:5655: 'bu cor sde la sogs pa re zhig skal ba
NK091(ke)001:5656: med pa'ang ngo bo nyid gsang sngags su ma gyur
NK091(ke)001:5657: pa med pa la mdongs pa dang phal che ba'i
NK091(ke)001:5658: phyir dus gzhan la dgongs te gsang sngags la spyod
NK091(ke)001:5659: par lung bstan pa thob pa sha stag go //
NK091(ke)001:5664: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5666: rgyas par brjod pa gtan tshigs su gyur pa de'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:5667: 'dzam bu'i gling gcig gis sangs rgyas nyag gcig 'di mya ngan las 'das pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:5668: de lta bas na de bzhin du rdo rje sems
NK091(ke)001:5669: dpa'i sprul pa sangs rgyas de snyed mtha' dag la
NK091(ke)001:5670: / thub pa lta bu mya ngan las 'das pa yang yod /
NK091(ke)001:5671: gzhan dag na ma 'das par bzhugs pa yang yod do //
NK091(ke)001:5673: dman pa'i lus kyi sems dpa' de dag zhing 'dir
NK091(ke)001:5674: sprul pa gcig 'dul dbang gis 'das par bstan kyang
NK091(ke)001:5675: thub pa'i dbang po'i sprul pa'i sgron ma ngos zin
NK091(ke)001:5676: nas the tshom chod de yid mgu zhing yongs su
NK091(ke)001:5679: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:5680: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa'i sku'i sgron ma'i cho
NK091(ke)001:5681: 'phrul 'jig rten gyi khams dam par yongs su bkod
NK091(ke)001:5682: pa'i le'u ste bdun pa gsal bar bshad pa'o ////gnyis
NK091(ke)001:5683: pa sgron ma'i gzhi gsang sngags rang gi ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:5684: la gsum ste / mdor bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:5691: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5693: de'ang sgron ma bkod pa'i dus su sprul pa thams
NK091(ke)001:5694: cad rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam 'phrul du bas na
NK091(ke)001:5695: de'i ngo bo rang gang yin dris pa las /
NK091(ke)001:5696: de ni rnal 'byor dang po'i don te sprul pa'i
NK091(ke)001:5697: sgron ma 'byung ba'i gzhi'i ngo bor bstan pa ste
NK091(ke)001:5698: / de nas yang lang ka'i bdag pos dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:5700: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes dngos de nyid gang la bgyi zhes dris pa las /
NK091(ke)001:5701: gsang ba pa'i bdag posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:5703: rdo rje sems dpa' ni rang gi byang chub sems
NK091(ke)001:5704: kyi dkyil 'khor ril len cing sdud pas snying por
NK091(ke)001:5705: gyur pa la sgrib byed ngang gis bral bas 'od
NK091(ke)001:5706: gsal ba / thun mong ma yin pas gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:5707: kyi ngo bo ma bcos pas ji bzhin pa ma
NK091(ke)001:5708: bslad pas de bzhin pa ma nor bas de kho
NK091(ke)001:5709: na nyid la bya'o zhes gzhan phyogs bcad pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:5712: rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bo /
NK091(ke)001:5715: ming gi gzhi ma grub pa /
NK091(ke)001:5716: de stong pa nyid du gnas pa /
NK091(ke)001:5717: de byams pa dang snying rje la gnas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5722: 'og gi tshigs bcad rnams mdor bstan du byas te sbyar dgos pas /
NK091(ke)001:5723: lang ka'i bdag po de lta bas na 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:5728: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5729: de yang tshig shad kyi tshul gyis sngags kyi mdo zhes pa ming 'grub ste /
NK091(ke)001:5730: don lhag pa min kyang lhug pa dang tshig shad
NK091(ke)001:5731: gnyis mdo rgyas su 'byung ba'i phyir te cha mthun
NK091(ke)001:5733: des na lang ka'i bdag po zhes sdud pa po la bos nas /
NK091(ke)001:5734: gzhung gi go rim ltar na /
NK091(ke)001:5735: sngar rgyas par bstan pa'i tshul de lta bas na zhes par 'gyur yang /
NK091(ke)001:5738: rgyas bshad cha mthun du sbyar te ston pa de lta bas na mdor brjod pa 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:5739: gang de bzhin nyid stong la zad mi shes pa
NK091(ke)001:5740: med la thams cad 'byung zhing khyab par snang la
NK091(ke)001:5741: mi 'gag pa chos nyid kyi gnas lugs ni dper
NK091(ke)001:5742: na nam mkha'i dkyil yangs shing dwangs pa lta bu
NK091(ke)001:5743: ste gzhi chos kyi sku yin la /
NK091(ke)001:5744: de la mtha' ma dmigs pas bla dwags tsam du
NK091(ke)001:5745: ma chung pa med par de nyid kyi ngang nasa
NK091(ke)001:5746: rang byung gi ye shes ril gyi dngos gzhi 'byung
NK091(ke)001:5747: ba'i gnas su rang shar ba ni dper na nyi
NK091(ke)001:5748: ma'i dkyil 'khor bkrag dang ldan pa lta bu longs
NK091(ke)001:5749: spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ru gsal la /
NK091(ke)001:5750: de lta bu'i bdag po'i rkyen byas pas thugs rje
NK091(ke)001:5751: chen po'i bdag nyid gang la gang 'dul du spro
NK091(ke)001:5752: ba ni dper na kun gsal sgron ma nyi ma'i
NK091(ke)001:5753: 'od zer ram me 'od dang 'dra bar sprul pa'i
NK091(ke)001:5754: sku nyid kyis gdul bya'i rgyud kyi gti mug gam
NK091(ke)001:5755: ma rig pa gnyis kyi mun pa thams cad ka
NK091(ke)001:5756: nas bsal ba'am sbyangs pas ril spyod yul dag pa
NK091(ke)001:5757: nyid du rnam par snang zhing ye shes su gsal
NK091(ke)001:5758: lo // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:5760: bye brag tu sems kyi dris lan no //
NK091(ke)001:5765: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5766: yang lang ka'i bdag posa dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:5767: nges par rtogs shing khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir bzhi po re re nas dris te /
NK091(ke)001:5768: kye gsang ba pa'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:5769: sems kyi dkyil 'khor zhes bgyi ba ni gang /
NK091(ke)001:5770: de bzhin du 'od gsal ba zhes bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:5771: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo zhes bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:5772: ji bzhin pa de bzhin pa de kho na nyid ces gang la bgyi /
NK091(ke)001:5774: gsang ba pa'i bdag posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:5776: gang rgyu rkyen 'dus pa las 'phral du ma grub
NK091(ke)001:5777: pa'i ye shes la sems zhes bya ba ste de
NK091(ke)001:5778: nyid ni ngo bo la byed pa po ka nas
NK091(ke)001:5780: mtshan nyid rgyu rkyen la rag ma las pas ma bcos pa /
NK091(ke)001:5781: rol pa ji snyed pa'i chos su ma 'gags par rang shar bas sna tshogs su 'byung ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:5783: brtags na med la bzhag na sna tshogs 'byung ba'i legs pa che /
NK091(ke)001:5784: dngos po med par chags pa'i cha lugs kun la ston /
NK091(ke)001:5786: bde ba chen po ji bzhin pa'i klong la mtha' dbus med pas dkyil 'khor zhes bya ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:5787: ril gyi dngos gzhi bas theg rim dgu'i tha snyad
NK091(ke)001:5788: gzhan thams cad 'dus la ma dmigs pa'i phyir thig
NK091(ke)001:5789: le gang yin pa dper na 'bras kyi phung po
NK091(ke)001:5790: bzhin du mar snang yang gdal khyab mnyam pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:5791: do // de dag ni rtsa ba bzhi'i dang po'i lan no //
NK091(ke)001:5792: 'oda ces bya ba ni gang du'ang snang ma myong
NK091(ke)001:5793: yang ngo bo dang dri ma bral bas phyogs med
NK091(ke)001:5795: gsal ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:5796: gang ma rig pa'am mi shes pa las gzhan gang
NK091(ke)001:5797: gisa kyang ma bsgribsa pas ngo bos de nyid kyang
NK091(ke)001:5798: ye shes chen po'i don du nges pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5800: gsang ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:5801: ji skad brjod pa mthar gyur pas bstan du mi
NK091(ke)001:5802: btub pas smrar med pa dang yul las grol zhing
NK091(ke)001:5803: brtags par dka' bas spyod yul du ma gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:5804: la bya'o // sngags zhes bya ba ni byin rlabs
NK091(ke)001:5805: kyi gzhir gyur pa'i phyir rgyal ba thams cad dang
NK091(ke)001:5806: la bya'o // nye / sgrib pa thams cad 'joms /
NK091(ke)001:5807: 'bras bu thams cad 'thob pas yon tan gyi 'byung gnas su brjod pa la bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:5808: ngo bo nyid ces bya ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:5809: ngo bo yongs su mi zin pas dngos po meda
NK091(ke)001:5810: pa gza' gtad dang bral bas mi dmigs pa dngos
NK091(ke)001:5811: po gnyis pa'i chos rnams kyi rtsa bar gyur pas
NK091(ke)001:5814: ji bzhin pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:5815: min pa la yin par 'phral du lam pas gtan
NK091(ke)001:5816: tshigs kyis ma bsgyur bas ma bcos rtsol ba dang
NK091(ke)001:5817: bsam dpyod kyis sel ma zhugs pas ma bslad pa
NK091(ke)001:5818: la bya'o // de bzhin pa zhes bya ba ni
NK091(ke)001:5819: ye nas de nyid pas glo bur du rgyu rkyen
NK091(ke)001:5820: gzhan gyis ngo bo bsgrubs pa min pas ma byasa
NK091(ke)001:5821: pa ming gi tha snyad ma bkol bar sgro ma
NK091(ke)001:5822: btags pas rang bral ba'i don dam pa la bya'o
NK091(ke)001:5823: la bya'o // // de kho na ces bya ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:5824: de nyid la gol sa med pas ma nor /
NK091(ke)001:5825: gnyen pos bya ba med pas mi 'gyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:5826: 'gre ldog spyi'u tshugs gar 'gros kyang snying po byang
NK091(ke)001:5827: chub nyid pa'i phyir ngo bo nges par grub pa
NK091(ke)001:5828: la bya'o // zhes bzhi pa'i lan no //
NK091(ke)001:5833: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5834: yang lang ka'i bdag posa dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:5836: ma byas ma bcos pa zhes bya ba ni gang /
NK091(ke)001:5837: sna tshogs 'byung ba zhes bya ba ni ji lta
NK091(ke)001:5838: bu zhes dri ba gnyis dris te snga ma'i sems
NK091(ke)001:5839: kyi dri ba'o // gsang ba pa'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:5841: ma lus pa'i chos thig le chen por rgyas thebs pa la /
NK091(ke)001:5842: byed pa po mkhan po med la /
NK091(ke)001:5843: de'i las su bya basa btsal du med pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:5844: gnyis kar yang ma dmigs pas des ngo bo zhig
NK091(ke)001:5845: bsgrub tu'ang mi btub pa'i phyir ma byas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5846: gzhi phyi mo'i chos nyid ci bzhin pa'i phyir gang du'ang ma g.yos pas ma bcos pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5847: gang rang gi ngo bo bstan du med pa las
NK091(ke)001:5848: rang bzhin thams cad pa'i phyir rgyun du 'byung zhing
NK091(ke)001:5849: dus gsum ril du mtshan ma tha dad thams cad
NK091(ke)001:5850: la zhen pas ma bsgos par khyab gdal du 'gro
NK091(ke)001:5851: ba legs pa dge ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:5852: nyes pa sdig pa dang gnyis ka ma yin pa
NK091(ke)001:5853: lung du ma bstan pa ste dngos po gzhi gsum
NK091(ke)001:5854: gyi bsdus pas tha dad sna tshogs par rang byung
NK091(ke)001:5855: ba'am snang ba'i phyir rang bzhin kun tu gsal ba'i
NK091(ke)001:5856: dbyings te rnam shes dgu pa gang de nya da
NK091(ke)001:5857: ni dpe nam mkha'a lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:5858: de'i rgyun nam sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi ni
NK091(ke)001:5859: de nyid dus gsum gyi rgyun du snang bas nam
NK091(ke)001:5860: mkha' las cho 'phrul 'byung ba lta bu ste glo
NK091(ke)001:5862: de las so sor snang ba nyon yid sprin lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:5863: yid shes khu rlangs lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:5864: sgo lnga 'ja' tshon la sogs pa lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:5865: phyi ma 'di la 'ja' rlan yang snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5870: ngo bo dang mthun pa las tshig gzhan med kyang /
NK091(ke)001:5871: chos nyid sku gsum dbyer med 'dus ma byas pa'i
NK091(ke)001:5872: ngo bo ye shes su gsal bas ma rig pa
NK091(ke)001:5873: gnyis po bag chags dang bcas pa zil gyis gnon
NK091(ke)001:5874: pas nges tshig gi don blang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:5879: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5880: nges tshig dri ba'i phyir yang dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:5881: gsang ba pa'i bdag po de la ci'i phyir rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bgyi /
NK091(ke)001:5883: lang ka'i bdag po de kho na nyid ci bzhin
NK091(ke)001:5884: pa de ni gtan tshigs bdun gyis rdo rje sems
NK091(ke)001:5886: rdo rje sems dpa' ma bslad pa'i de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:5887: chen po ni dus snga phyi thams cad nas thams
NK091(ke)001:5888: cad du de bshig pa pos gnyen po med pa
NK091(ke)001:5889: dang / bdag gzhan gyi spros pa dang bral bas 'pho 'gyur meda pa /
NK091(ke)001:5890: rgyu rkyen las 'das pas skye 'gag med pa /
NK091(ke)001:5891: ma nor mi 'gyur bas de kho na nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:5892: mi g.yo zhing ma bsgribs par gsal bas sems rang rig pa /
NK091(ke)001:5893: don chen po ji lta bar ye mngon du byas
NK091(ke)001:5894: pa'i ngo bor gyur pas dgongs pa nges para 'grel
NK091(ke)001:5895: ba las / cho 'phrul sna tshogs 'byung ba'i mtshan
NK091(ke)001:5896: gzhi cir yang snang ba ril mnyam pa chen por
NK091(ke)001:5897: ma bkag la ma dmigs par gtan nas sbyangs pa'am
NK091(ke)001:5898: dngos po med pa nyid du bcom pa'i phyir rdo
NK091(ke)001:5899: rje sems dpa' zhes bya ba'i mtshan nges par bstan
NK091(ke)001:5900: ba las / pa'o // dang po nas gsum pa'i bar ni mtshan dang po'i don dang /
NK091(ke)001:5901: bzhi pa nas drug pa'i bar ni bar pa'i don dang /
NK091(ke)001:5902: tha ma ni tha ma'i don to //
NK091(ke)001:5910: zhes pa'i bar rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5911: mtha' yas pa'i ming du btags te zhen yul du
NK091(ke)001:5912: snang ba yi dngos po bzang ngan gyi yul drug
NK091(ke)001:5913: la sogs pa yod mthonga snang grags kyi chos rnams
NK091(ke)001:5914: kun kyang gnyis med kyi ngo bo las ma bkol
NK091(ke)001:5915: bas ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5920: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5921: rdo rje sems dpa'i mtshan sgra du mar snang ba'i rtsa ba bcu gcig bstan pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:5923: rdo rje sems dpa'i de kho na nyid de la
NK091(ke)001:5924: ni che ba ril gyi bdag nyid pas bla na
NK091(ke)001:5925: med pa / zla med cing dri ma ma spangs la dag pas byang /
NK091(ke)001:5926: yon tan rang snang du lhun gyis grub pas chub /
NK091(ke)001:5927: gnyis med kyi ngo bo gsal la mi g.yo bas sems zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:5928: bshad ma thag pa ltar chos bzhis bsdus pa ril
NK091(ke)001:5929: gyi ngo bo phyogs ris dang bral bas chos rnams
NK091(ke)001:5930: kyi chos nyid ma bcos pa chen po'i phyir de
NK091(ke)001:5932: ngo bo ma spangs la ma grub pa'i phyir sems kyi stong pa nyid ces kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:5933: tshig gis brjod du mi btub cing gang la'ang mi gnas pas mtha' las 'das pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:5934: mtha' mi spong zhing dbus yul du mi byed pas
NK091(ke)001:5935: de nyid du'ang 'dzin pa dang bral bas dbu mar
NK091(ke)001:5936: mi dmigs pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:5937: nor bu rin po che ltar rgyal ba ril gyi
NK091(ke)001:5938: ngo bor bzhugs te gang mos su snang bas sangs
NK091(ke)001:5939: rgyas kun gyi dngos gzhi zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:5940: 'gro 'ong med par ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin rang
NK091(ke)001:5941: snang bas sprul pa kun gyi 'byung gnas zhes kyang
NK091(ke)001:5942: bya'o // sangs rgyas kun 'dis grol bar byed pas
NK091(ke)001:5943: sangs rgyas kun gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen zhes kyang
NK091(ke)001:5944: bya'o // bya'o // rtogs na mun pa sel zhing
NK091(ke)001:5945: sprul pa thams cad pa yin pas zhing khams kun
NK091(ke)001:5946: gyi sgron ma zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:5947: byin rlabs mi 'gog par cir yang 'char la rang
NK091(ke)001:5948: snang ye shes chen pos zin pas thugs rje thabsa
NK091(ke)001:5951: sems ni gzugs bral gzugs kyang rdzogs //
NK091(ke)001:5953: ril ma 'dres pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir chos
NK091(ke)001:5954: thams cad kyi gzugs brnyana snang ba zhes kyang bya'o
NK091(ke)001:5957: bla dwags glo bur ba yin pa /
NK091(ke)001:5958: des na ming ma grub par bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5963: bla dwags tsam du btags par zad //
NK091(ke)001:5965: 'khor 'das kyi chos ril ci'ang ma yin pa las
NK091(ke)001:5966: bla dwags tsam du cir yang btags pa ltar snang
NK091(ke)001:5967: bar zad de ngo bo mi zin pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:5972: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5974: mtshan de dag bstan pa'i dgos ched kyang mos pa
NK091(ke)001:5975: can dang gang gi don du rigs tha dad nas
NK091(ke)001:5976: bya ba'i sgor de ltar btags kyi /
NK091(ke)001:5977: de kho na nyid kyi ngo bo la ni ming du btags pa med do //
NK091(ke)001:5978: des na glo bur ba dang lhag par 'byung ba
NK091(ke)001:5979: de dag ni bla dwags nyid du rig cing rtogs
NK091(ke)001:5982: de'i phyir na sangsa rgyas su btags pa ni bla dwags so //
NK091(ke)001:5984: byang chub kyang bla dwags so //
NK091(ke)001:5985: de bzhin du dbyings dang ye shes dang chos kyi sku dang sku tha dad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:5986: khams gsum gyi sems can dang /
NK091(ke)001:5987: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa ming tha dad
NK091(ke)001:5988: du btags pa ltar chags par snang ba ji snyed
NK091(ke)001:5989: pa dag tha snyad kyi bla dwags 'ba' zhig tu
NK091(ke)001:5990: rig par bya'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:5997: zhes pa'i bar rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:5998: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems ni mtha' gang du'ang
NK091(ke)001:5999: snang ma myong bas mi snang ba las thams cad
NK091(ke)001:6000: kun gyi dngos gzhi bas zhen pas ji ltar bsam
NK091(ke)001:6001: pa ltar snang ba la 'khor ba thams cad dang
NK091(ke)001:6002: myang 'das thams cad de bzang ngan ril bshad pa
NK091(ke)001:6003: ltar ltos pa'i glo bur du snang ba kho na'o
NK091(ke)001:6007: bla dwags su rig par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:6008: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6009: bla dwags kyi mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir lang ka'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:6010: bla dwags gang yin pa ni glo bura du btags
NK091(ke)001:6011: te de bzhin nyid la rtog kyang dngos po gnyis
NK091(ke)001:6012: ye thog ma nas ldan pa can ni ma yin
NK091(ke)001:6013: no // bla dwags kyi mtshan nyid de las gzhan zhig ldan pa'i skyon ni /
NK091(ke)001:6014: lang ka'i bdag po gal te bla dwags nyid ye
NK091(ke)001:6015: nas ldan pa de bzhin nyid dang mtshungs te glo
NK091(ke)001:6016: bur ba ma yin pa zhig na ni /
NK091(ke)001:6017: gang glo bura ba 'khor 'das dang dge sdig la
NK091(ke)001:6018: sogs pa dngos po gnyis pa'i chos thams cad mi
NK091(ke)001:6019: 'byung bar snang ba go 'gag pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:6020: sgrib pa sbyangs kyang dag par mi nus pa'i skyon du 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:6022: glo bur gyi mtshan nyid ni dper na sprin bzhin te /
NK091(ke)001:6023: ther zug tu gnas pa ma yin /
NK091(ke)001:6024: ya nas ldan pa ma yin /
NK091(ke)001:6025: brtags bzod pa ma yin pa'i gtan tshigs gsum gyis nges pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:6027: de ltar glo bur gyi ngo bo yin pa de'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:6028: ming gis btags pa'i chos rnams dang /
NK091(ke)001:6029: brda yis mtshon te zhe na blos phyi rol du snang ba'i mthu can dag dang /
NK091(ke)001:6030: ming tsam pa de'i sgra'i spyi tshig gi tha snyad dang /
NK091(ke)001:6031: 'du shes kyis mtshan ma sna tshogs su gdung ba don gyi spyi dang /
NK091(ke)001:6032: sgra rang gi mtshan nyid blos ngang gis brtags te rjod byed du btags pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:6034: bsod nams ma yin pa dang mi g.yo ba'i las gsum dang /
NK091(ke)001:6035: las kyi rnam para smin pa khams gsum la sogs
NK091(ke)001:6036: pa thams cad ni ngo bo glo bur ba ste
NK091(ke)001:6037: / de'i mtshan nyid zhen pa po la rgyu rkyen las 'byung bar snang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:6038: zhen pas 'dog pa de nyid dag pas sangsa par gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:6039: don mthong du mi ster bas sgrib pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:6040: mtshan ma de nyid 'byongs pas sgrib pa rnams rang
NK091(ke)001:6041: sar dang para rig par bya ste glo bur gyi
NK091(ke)001:6043: 'o na gong gi dkon mchog gsum la sogs pa
NK091(ke)001:6044: ni bsgrub bya nyid pas glo bur du mi 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:6045: ro zhe na / de dag ni ngo bo nyid ma spangs bral ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:6046: lam pas der 'dod na ched du byas pa'i zhen pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:6047: chu bo brgal ba'i gru bzhin de dag tu 'dzin pa nyid kyang 'dor bar rigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:6048: glo bur min na skyon gsum bshad pa de'i ngo
NK091(ke)001:6049: bo bstan pa'i phyir lang ka'i bdag po gal te
NK091(ke)001:6050: rgyu las dang 'bras bu las kyi rnam par smin
NK091(ke)001:6051: pa la sogs pa chos de rnams glo bur du
NK091(ke)001:6052: ma btags par gyur na ni de bzhin nyid dam
NK091(ke)001:6053: de kho na nyid kyang dri ma can pas mtshan
NK091(ke)001:6054: nyid gong du bshad pa de ltar gnas lugs su
NK091(ke)001:6055: mi rung ba zhig tu 'gyur na yang /
NK091(ke)001:6057: de bzhin nyid de ni phyi mo'i chos nyid gang
NK091(ke)001:6058: gi dbang du yang mi 'gyur ba'i bla dwags su
NK091(ke)001:6059: rig par bya'o // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:6066: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6067: gsang sngags de kho na nyid la ni ye nas rnam pa ma dmigs pas sangs rgyas dang /
NK091(ke)001:6068: byang chub dang chos nyid la sogs pa'i sgo nas
NK091(ke)001:6069: tha dad du btags pa'i ming gi bla dwags 'di
NK091(ke)001:6070: rnams ming gi tha snyad tsam du'ang grub pa med
NK091(ke)001:6071: pas de ltar tshig tu brjod de smra ba'nga don
NK091(ke)001:6072: la med do // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:6076: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6078: bshad pa bzhin gtan tshigs kyis grub pa de'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:6079: chos thams cada kyi dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs
NK091(ke)001:6080: ni ye ji bzhin pa'i ngang nyid de ming gi
NK091(ke)001:6081: rnam pas btags pa med la /
NK091(ke)001:6082: sgra nyid ma dmigs pas tshig gi mtshon par byed
NK091(ke)001:6083: pa med cing ngo bo gang du'ang ldan pa med
NK091(ke)001:6084: pa la tshig gis brjod de bstan du med pas
NK091(ke)001:6085: ngo bo nyid ni gang gis kyang mtshon par mi
NK091(ke)001:6086: nus par tshig lam chad de bsam brjod dang bral
NK091(ke)001:6087: ba'o // lnga pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:6088: gzhi'i don tsam du'ang ma grub pa /
NK091(ke)001:6089: tha snyad sna tshogs de kho na nyid la med kyang blo chung ba'i dbang du bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:6094: de la dngos gzhi ga la yod //
NK091(ke)001:6096: ngo bo de la dngos gzhi rang rgyud du grub
NK091(ke)001:6097: pa ga la yod de gzhi'i don tsam du'ang ma
NK091(ke)001:6098: grub pas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:6102: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6103: lang kas ji bzhin pa nyid du la blos gzung du yod med dris pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:6104: smras pa gsang ba pa'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:6105: gang ming du btags pa' gzhi ci bzhin pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:6106: la btags pa bral ba'i gzhi'i don tsam du yang
NK091(ke)001:6109: smras pa lang ka'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:6110: gzhi ci bzhin pa'i ngang la rtog bya rtog byed
NK091(ke)001:6111: la dmigs pas gzhi'i don tsam nyid du rtog na
NK091(ke)001:6112: yang nad yin pa'i phyir mi rtog bye brag tu
NK091(ke)001:6115: de las gzhan pa'i gtan tshigs kyis de'i ngo bo ldan par mi rnyed pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:6116: gzhi'i don tsam zhig ni 'di lta bu zhes sangs
NK091(ke)001:6117: rgyas nyid kyis btsal yang mi brnyes te ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:6118: la gnyis su med cing ngos gzung dang bral bas
NK091(ke)001:6127: zhes pa'i bar rkang pa gsum dang /
NK091(ke)001:6131: zhes pa'i ming bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6132: 'o na gang med pa las snang na ri bong
NK091(ke)001:6133: gi rwa dang nam mkha'i me tog kyang 'byung bar
NK091(ke)001:6135: de kho na nyid gang la snang ba tha dad
NK091(ke)001:6136: ltar ming du ma sna tshogs su btags pa'i gzhi
NK091(ke)001:6137: ni / mtshan nyid thams cad pa la mtshan nyid med pa /
NK091(ke)001:6138: rnam pa kun ldan rnam pa bral ba /
NK091(ke)001:6139: brjod pa kun 'byung brjod pa med pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:6140: gang yang ma bkol bas rnam pa'i phyogs bral ba'i
NK091(ke)001:6141: phyir ngo bo dngos por med cing lhun gyis grub
NK091(ke)001:6142: pa'i rgyu las ji ltar btags shing bsnyad pa ltar
NK091(ke)001:6143: chagsa la bsgrub pa ltar 'grub cing /
NK091(ke)001:6144: bsam pas gang du bltas par snang ste kun tu
NK091(ke)001:6145: btags pa'i ngor mtshan ma ltar yod pa yin pas
NK091(ke)001:6146: ri bong gi rwa dang mi mtshungs te /
NK091(ke)001:6148: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges pas //
NK091(ke)001:6149: ji ltar bltas pa de ltar snang //
NK091(ke)001:6152: mdor na ji ltar btags bsam bzhin //
NK091(ke)001:6153: 'gyur bas thams cad ngo bor snang //
NK091(ke)001:6155: des na gzhi nyid gang yang lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK091(ke)001:6156: phyir rnam pa'i chos sangs rgyas la sogs pa gang
NK091(ke)001:6157: du'ang med pa las sangs rgyas dang byang chub dang
NK091(ke)001:6158: chos nyid la sogs pa'i tha dad kyi ming gi
NK091(ke)001:6159: bla dwags bzang phyogs su btags pa rnams ni don
NK091(ke)001:6160: mi shes par rmongs pa rnams la bstan pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:6162: brgyud nas drang ba'i dgos pa yod pas so //
NK091(ke)001:6167: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6168: gong du bshad pa de lta bas na don gyis
NK091(ke)001:6169: glo bur gyi rtog pa kun tu 'khrul pa ngan
NK091(ke)001:6170: pa dang / de ltar mi rtog pa bzang por
NK091(ke)001:6171: gyur pa las sangs rgyas dang sems can zhes gnyis
NK091(ke)001:6172: su btags pas zhen pa gnyis kyis de ltar mthong
NK091(ke)001:6173: pa dang / bar zad kyi / de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:6174: ni ngo bo de la ni sangs rgyas dang semsa
NK091(ke)001:6175: can tha dad du gdags pa cung zad kyang med
NK091(ke)001:6176: pa dang / bar zad kyi / do // 'on
NK091(ke)001:6177: kyang don chen po ma rig pa'i byis pa rgyu'i
NK091(ke)001:6178: theg pa rnams ni glo bura ba'i rtog pa dag
NK091(ke)001:6179: gi sprin gyisa yang dag pa'i don la bsgribs pas
NK091(ke)001:6180: don ji bzhin pa mthong du mi ster ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:6181: pa dang / bar zad kyi / do // /
NK091(ke)001:6182: glo bura gyi chos kun rdzob pa de dag la
NK091(ke)001:6183: slar yang don du gnyer te ched du byed cing
NK091(ke)001:6184: rgyu 'bras la sogs par 'dzin pas 'khrul nas rgyu
NK091(ke)001:6185: 'khor ba dang 'bras bu byang chub gnyis su rtog
NK091(ke)001:6186: pa dang / bar zad kyi / do // /
NK091(ke)001:6187: par byed do // de bzhin du ma dag pa
NK091(ke)001:6188: sems can dang dag pa sangs rgyas gnyis su yang
NK091(ke)001:6197: ces rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6198: de yang btags pa ltar chags shing bsgrub pa ltar
NK091(ke)001:6199: 'grub pa'i snang ba nyid kyang don la dngos por
NK091(ke)001:6200: med pa'i snying po de kho na nyid du rang
NK091(ke)001:6201: gsal ba ste de las gzhan pa med pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:6202: ril yod med sogs mtha' gnyis su'ang dmigs pa med
NK091(ke)001:6208: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6209: de dag gi rang bzhin rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:6212: 'o na sems can dang sangs rgyas 'di gnyis ji ltar shes par bya /
NK091(ke)001:6215: rang rig pa 'od gsal ba'i ngo bo sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:6216: dang sems can gyi ngo bo ma dmigs pas stong
NK091(ke)001:6217: pa nyid du shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:6220: stong pa nyid ci la gnas /
NK091(ke)001:6223: stong pa nyid ni chos so cog gi mtshan nyid yin pas /
NK091(ke)001:6224: ril la khyab ste chos thams cada la gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:6227: chos thams cad ci la gnas /
NK091(ke)001:6230: chos thams cad ni stong pa kho na'i phyir spyod
NK091(ke)001:6231: yul rten dang rten can las grol bas gang la'ang
NK091(ke)001:6232: rten mi 'cha' bas mtha' thams cad dang bral te
NK091(ke)001:6238: des na byas med byas pa zin //
NK091(ke)001:6240: stong pa nyid kyi gtan tshigs des na ched du
NK091(ke)001:6241: byas pa med par phrin las kyis don ye nas
NK091(ke)001:6242: byas te mdzad pa rdzogs zin pas ril lhun gyis
NK091(ke)001:6243: grub pa'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:6244: byams pa dang snying rje la gnas pa dngos dang /
NK091(ke)001:6250: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6253: stong pa nyid la gnas pa ji la gnas pa lags /
NK091(ke)001:6256: gzhan don bya byed med par rtogs tshul bstan pa'i
NK091(ke)001:6257: phyir stong pa nyid la gnas pa ni byed pa
NK091(ke)001:6258: med la bya ba rdzogs pas byams pa dang snying
NK091(ke)001:6259: rje chen po la gnas pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:6260: gang stong pa nyid des kun la khyab zin pas
NK091(ke)001:6261: sems can gyi don kun byed pa med par bya
NK091(ke)001:6262: ba yongs su rdzogs te byams dang snying rje'i dmigs
NK091(ke)001:6263: yul dang bral bar gnas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:6265: don byed pa po'i sangs rgyas dang bya ba'i yul
NK091(ke)001:6266: sems can thams cad la stong pa nyid lasa lhag
NK091(ke)001:6267: pa'i don byed pa dang bya ba ci yang med
NK091(ke)001:6268: par rgyas thebs pas gzhan nas mi rnyed pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:6273: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:6276: sangs rgyas dang sems can kun stong pa nyid yin na /
NK091(ke)001:6277: sangs rgyas gang gi thugs rje chen pos /
NK091(ke)001:6278: gdul bya sems can gang la don ji ltar mdzad de nam mkha' dang 'dra bas so //
NK091(ke)001:6279: thugs rje chen po zhes su grags pa de yang gang gi tshig bla dwags lagas /
NK091(ke)001:6280: zhes dri ba gnyis dris pa las /
NK091(ke)001:6283: dngos po gnyis pa'i chos thams cad mtha' dang bral
NK091(ke)001:6284: ba'i stong pa nyid chen po la rang bzhin gyis
NK091(ke)001:6285: gnas pas na / de'i ngo bor ma bgrod par
NK091(ke)001:6286: rgyas btab ste sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis su
NK091(ke)001:6287: ma mthong bas snying rje'i yul sems can gud na
NK091(ke)001:6288: med par don gyi gnas lugs ci'ang ma mthong zhing
NK091(ke)001:6289: ma rig pa'i tshul gyis mthong zhing rig par gyur
NK091(ke)001:6290: pa ni 'gro don ma byas par rdzogs te thams
NK091(ke)001:6291: cad snying po byang chub tu yo bsgral ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:6292: dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje chen po yin la
NK091(ke)001:6293: gnas pas na / / de lta bu'i nges don
NK091(ke)001:6294: zab mo ma rnyed par theg pa dman pas byis
NK091(ke)001:6296: gang stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i sems can thams cad kyi srog bton te bskyab pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:6297: gang thar par bton te mya ngan las 'das pa
NK091(ke)001:6298: la bkod pa de ni gnyis su bzung bas snying
NK091(ke)001:6299: rje chung ngur rig par bya ste /
NK091(ke)001:6300: dmigs pas bya ba'i las su gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:6301: 'jig rten mtha' med la ltos nas ba spu'i cha'i don tsam yang med pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:6302: slar yang 'chi ba yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:6303: de dag gi rtsa ba yang snying rje chen po yin pa'i phyir na'o //
NK091(ke)001:6305: de bas na snying rje chen po la dmigs pas
NK091(ke)001:6306: gnas par mi 'dod pa'i tshul gyis rgyun du gnas
NK091(ke)001:6307: pa dang mi 'bral ba'i ngang la mi gnas pas
NK091(ke)001:6308: gnas par bslab ste lta bar bya'o //
