NK091(ke)001:7778: gtsang ma'i ris rnams kyis bskal pa bzang po zhes
NK091(ke)001:7779: brjod pas de ltar grags la /
NK091(ke)001:7780: de'ang rgyal ba stong gi re re sangs rgyas pa
NK091(ke)001:7781: na seng khri pad ma can stong stong 'byung ba
NK091(ke)001:7782: la rang gar bab pa'i sa na bzhugs pas gzhan
NK091(ke)001:7783: ma rnams 'phur te mi snang bar 'gyur la /
NK091(ke)001:7784: de ltar bskal pa bzang po 'di nyid la sangs rgyas stong rtsa gnyis 'byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7785: 'di nas gyen du 'das pa brtsis na /
NK091(ke)001:7786: bskal pa bzang po 'di'i sngon du /
NK091(ke)001:7787: mun pa'i bskala pa bargya byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7788: de'i sngon du yon tan rdzogs pas bskal pa rdzogs ldan zhes bya ba la /
NK091(ke)001:7789: sangs rgyas bye ba phrag bargya byon te tha ma dkon mchog dpal byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7790: de 'das pa'i sngon rol du mtha' 'khob kyi bskal pa bargya byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7791: de 'das pa'i sngon du gdul bya rnams skal pa
NK091(ke)001:7792: bzang bas bskal pa bzang rgyan zhes bya ba la
NK091(ke)001:7793: / sangs rgyas bye ba phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi byon te tha mar bzang rgyan dpal byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7794: de 'das pa'i sngon du mun pa'i bskal pa lnga bargya byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7795: de 'das pa'i sngon du dge bcu la spyod pas bskal pa mthong dga' zhes bya ba la /
NK091(ke)001:7796: sangs rgyas bye ba phrag bcu byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7797: de 'das pa'i sngon du mun pa'i bskal pa bdun bargya byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7798: de 'das pa'i sngon du mi rnams yid dga' bas bskal pa dga' ba zhes bya ba la /
NK091(ke)001:7799: sangs rgyas stong phrag drug cu byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7800: de la sogs pa 'das pa'i dus dang ma 'ongs
NK091(ke)001:7801: pa'i dus mtha' yas par mun pa dang sgron ma'i
NK091(ke)001:7802: bskal pa 'dren mar thog ma dang tha ma med
NK091(ke)001:7804: gang sgron ma sangs rgyas ji snyed pa sngar byung zhing phyis 'byung ba rnams kyang /
NK091(ke)001:7805: gsang sngags kyi nges pa de kho na nyid ma
NK091(ke)001:7806: rnyed kyi bar du dpag tu med pa'i dka' ba
NK091(ke)001:7807: spyad kyang rnam pa thams cad ma mkhyen /
NK091(ke)001:7814: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:7815: de bas na rgyal ba ril gyi lam 'dir gcig
NK091(ke)001:7816: pas gang gsang sngags kyi nges pa de kho na
NK091(ke)001:7817: nyid de dus sam lam gyi skabs nam du rnyed
NK091(ke)001:7818: ma thag par sngar yang 'bras bu ye shes thob
NK091(ke)001:7819: pas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen to //
NK091(ke)001:7820: da ltar yang 'bras bu ye shes brnyes te rnam pa thams cad mkhyen no //
NK091(ke)001:7821: phyi dus su yang 'bras bu ye shes thob nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen para 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:7822: de'ang tshogs lam nas nges pa rnyed pa'ang yod la /
NK091(ke)001:7824: mthong lam nas sa bcu rim pa bzhin du'ang rnyed pa yod cing /
NK091(ke)001:7825: sa bcu mthar phyin pa ni gsang sngags so //
NK091(ke)001:7827: lam lnga phrag gnyis su bgrod pa /
NK091(ke)001:7828: bgrod kyang nges pa ma rnyed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:7830: bdag don du thun mong gi lam nas bgrod pa /
NK091(ke)001:7831: gzhan don du mdo khyad par gyi lam nas bgrod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:7833: lam pa'i gang zag 'byung ba'i dus /
NK091(ke)001:7834: ngo bo lam bgrod tshul dngos so //
NK091(ke)001:7839: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:7840: de lta bas na de las cha gcig nges par
NK091(ke)001:7841: gzung bar bstan pas yid ches par bya ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:7842: de bzhin du rigs lngas gsang sngags ma rtogs pa
NK091(ke)001:7843: dang rtogs pas 'bras bu brnyes pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:7844: dang po sems bskyed pa nas mthar thug gi bar ston te /
NK091(ke)001:7845: de yang dus kyi dbang du sngon gyi bskal pa
NK091(ke)001:7846: grangs med pa las kyang grangs med par 'das pa
NK091(ke)001:7847: mang po tshad med pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK091(ke)001:7848: na / bskal pa chen po mngon par dga' ba zhes bya ba la /
NK091(ke)001:7849: sangs rgyas sum khri sum stong ngam khri sum stong yang gsungs te de ltar byung ba'i dus na /
NK091(ke)001:7850: bstan pa dang slob dpon gyi dbang du phyi ma
NK091(ke)001:7851: ltar na khri nyis stong brgyad brgya dgu bcu go
NK091(ke)001:7852: dgu song ba'i tha ma'ii sangs rgyas kun tu bzang
NK091(ke)001:7853: po zhes bya ba'i bstan pa la /
NK091(ke)001:7854: thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang la 'jug par 'dod
NK091(ke)001:7855: pa'i gang zag lnga ste rigs kyi sgo nas rgyal
NK091(ke)001:7856: rigs dang / bram ze'i rigsa dang /
NK091(ke)001:7859: gdol pa'i rigsa dang lnga byung bas dge 'dun rigs kyi sgo nas kyang dkon la /
NK091(ke)001:7860: ngo bo'i dbang du mchog chen po lnga byung ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:7862: las dang po pa'i mtshan khye'u bde skyob ces bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:7863: khye'u tra li ta zhes bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:7864: khye'u dpas byin zhes bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:7865: khye'u las sbyin zhes bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:7866: khye'u dum bur zhes bya ba byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7867: dang po'i khye'u lnga da ltar gyi rgyal ba rigs lngar ngos bzung ba /
NK091(ke)001:7868: bstan pa shar ba de'i tshe mchog chen po lnga byung ba de'i dus na /
NK091(ke)001:7869: sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa' ni khye'u bde skyob ces bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:7870: de'i tshe de'i dus na sangs rgyas tshe mtha' yas pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:7871: khye'u tra li ta zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:7872: de'i tshe de'i dus nas sangs rgyas rin chen 'byung ldan ni /
NK091(ke)001:7874: de'i tshe de'i dus na sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad ni /
NK091(ke)001:7876: de'i tshe de'i dus na sangs rgyas dona yod grub pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:7877: khye'u dum bu ra zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:7878: ci'i phyir lnga ru bshad na /
NK091(ke)001:7880: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NK091(ke)001:7881: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan dang //
NK091(ke)001:7882: mdzad pa'i phrin las nyid dang lnga //
NK091(ke)001:7883: de las byung zhing der 'dus pas //
NK091(ke)001:7884: lnga zhes nges par bstan pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:7896: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:7897: de'ang sems bskyed pa nas rim par bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:7898: ston pa dang khye'u lnga'i dbang gis de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK091(ke)001:7899: khye'u de rnams kyis sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po
NK091(ke)001:7900: de la rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa rgyu dang
NK091(ke)001:7901: / lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen yon tan mthong thos
NK091(ke)001:7902: dang byin rlabs thabs kyi 'grel pa 'dzom pa las
NK091(ke)001:7903: rnal 'byor mchog tu sems bskyed de dper na mun
NK091(ke)001:7904: pa'i zer ram r+ts+wa me ltar g.yo ba'i sems skye
NK091(ke)001:7905: ba'i dus dang po grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba
NK091(ke)001:7906: 'jig rten gyi sa la gnas pa'i skabs na /
NK091(ke)001:7907: phal pa'i sems brgyad bskyed cing 'jig rten pa'i lam brgyad nas bgrod de 'jug pa'i tshul ni /
NK091(ke)001:7908: lam dang sems ngo bo thun mong ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:7909: gsang bdag dga' rab dpa' bos mdzad pa'i bsgom thabs sgron ma las /
NK091(ke)001:7910: bsnyung bar gnas pa'i sems dang sa bon ltar //
NK091(ke)001:7911: bcos ma'i snying rje'i gnas gtong song lta bu //
NK091(ke)001:7912: phra men dge sbyong la gtong lo ma ltar //
NK091(ke)001:7913: tshul 'dzin lhug par gtong sems me tog ltar //
NK091(ke)001:7914: mos pas khrims srung sems bskyed gsos su 'gyur //
NK091(ke)001:7915: dge bar 'dun pa lha mchod 'jig rten lam //
NK091(ke)001:7917: so so'i skye bo phyugs dang 'dra ba las /
NK091(ke)001:7918: brgya lam re na chos kyi 'du shes 'byung ba
NK091(ke)001:7919: ni bsnyung bar gnas pa'i sems te sa bon lta
NK091(ke)001:7920: bu dang / pha ma dang nye du lta bu
NK091(ke)001:7921: la sbyin pa byed de myu gu lta bu dang
NK091(ke)001:7922: bu dang / / sbyin gnas ji snyed pa dag la gtong ste sdong bu lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:7923: bram ze dang dge slong dag la'ang gtong ba lo ma lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:7924: bla ma dang rol mo mkhan la sogs pa la lhug par gtong ba me tog lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:7925: gang dang gang 'dod pa gtong bas yid dga' bar
NK091(ke)001:7926: byed pa 'bras bu lta bu ste sbyin pa'i bslab
NK091(ke)001:7927: pa drug dang / sbyin pa des rgyu byas nas
NK091(ke)001:7928: tshul khrims la mos pa skye ste bsrung ba gsos
NK091(ke)001:7929: su gyur pa lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:7930: de bas 'jig rten pa'i lha chen po la mchod
NK091(ke)001:7931: pa phul ba shes stobs can du 'gyur snyam nas
NK091(ke)001:7932: tshangs pa la sogs pa mchod pa ni stobs su
NK091(ke)001:7934: zhes rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i tan+t+ra las byung ba ltar ro //
NK091(ke)001:7935: de ltar rim par bskyed pa'ang 'di ltar rnal 'byor lnga'i rim par gnas pas spyad de /
NK091(ke)001:7936: 'dun pa sems pa'i rnal 'byor gyi skabs la /
NK091(ke)001:7937: gsang sngags yid la byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin tsam
NK091(ke)001:7938: bsgom ste ras bal lam sa bon dang 'dra ste
NK091(ke)001:7939: gang du'ang 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur pas rkyen la rag
NK091(ke)001:7940: las te nges pa med pa'i phyir sa dang po
NK091(ke)001:7941: 'gyur dbang ma nges pa'i sa par gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:7942: de'i tshe sangs rgyas sum khri sum stong la the
NK091(ke)001:7943: tshom bcad kyang gsang sngags la ngesa pa ma rnyed
NK091(ke)001:7944: do // 'di dang 'og ma'i bud+d+ha'i grangs rnams bskal
NK091(ke)001:7945: pa yun ring ba la bsnyen pa yin te yun
NK091(ke)001:7946: thung ba la gshib pa min gsung /
NK091(ke)001:7947: tshoms su bcad pa ni lam lnga'i grangs kyi ngos nas so //
NK091(ke)001:7948: 'di dag ni skabs kyis kyang thun mong gi lam du sbyar la /
NK091(ke)001:7949: spyir na gzhi dang po dang skabs kyi dang po gnyis las /
NK091(ke)001:7950: 'dir gzhi ste sngar ma sbyang pa'i las dam pa
NK091(ke)001:7951: gsang sngags kyi bslab pa thog mar rtsom pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:7952: ro // de ltar las dang po pa'i skabs bka' sdod las kyi rnal 'byor gyi dus na /
NK091(ke)001:7954: bslab pa sbyong ba'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK091(ke)001:7955: nges pa'i rnal 'byor gyi sems gsum bskyed cing zag
NK091(ke)001:7956: bcas kyi bslab pa'i mtha' bcu chub pas 'grub par
NK091(ke)001:7957: khong du chud nas sems gsum dang bslab pa bcu
NK091(ke)001:7958: dang / gsang sngags la sogs pa thun mong gi sems g.yo ba /
NK091(ke)001:7960: mos pa gsum la brten pas nges par 'byung ba'i
NK091(ke)001:7961: phyir bag chags dang po dag nas dge ba'i chos
NK091(ke)001:7962: thams cad kyi rten gzhir gyur pas sa gnyis pa
NK091(ke)001:7963: rten pa gzhi'i sa par gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:7965: sangs rgyas bzhi khri bzhi stong la the tshom bcad kyang nges pa ma rnyed do //
NK091(ke)001:7966: yang na 'di rnams sprul pa'i slob dpon yin kyang rung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:7971: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:7972: yang rigsa chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor gyi skabs su 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:7973: theg pa che chung gi rigs so sor nges par gyur nas rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK091(ke)001:7974: gsang sgo lung gi rnal 'byor dang /
NK091(ke)001:7975: spyod pa rgyun gyi rnal 'byor dang /
NK091(ke)001:7976: mtshan ma rtags kyi rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin dang sems bzhi rdzogs te /
NK091(ke)001:7977: zag bcas kyi bslab pa'i mtha' bcu khong du chub
NK091(ke)001:7978: nasa don chen po longs spyod pa zad pa med
NK091(ke)001:7980: gsum pa gal chen sbyong ba'i sa dang /
NK091(ke)001:7981: bzhi pa bslab pa rgyun gyi sa dang /
NK091(ke)001:7982: sa lnga pa nges pas bsod nams bsags te zag
NK091(ke)001:7983: pa med pa la sbyor bas mi zad pa'i gter
NK091(ke)001:7984: gyi yon tan dang ldan pa'i sa par gyur to
NK091(ke)001:7986: gong gi thun mong gi sems gsum gcig tu brtsis pa'i steng rang gi lta ba /
NK091(ke)001:7988: sbyor ba gsum sa gsum dang sbyar ba la bzhed pa'ang yod do //
NK091(ke)001:7989: dee'i tshe sangs rgyas lnga khri lnga stong la the tshom bcad kyang nges pa ma rnyed do //
NK091(ke)001:7994: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:7995: yang chos nyid rang gi mtshan nyid ji lta ba
NK091(ke)001:7996: bzhin du rtogs pas dang po ngal sos te 'khor
NK091(ke)001:7997: ba las dbugs chen po 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor gyi
NK091(ke)001:7998: skabs su / chos nyid ma skyes par rtogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:7999: bsam gtan 'ba' zhig dang ldan pas dga' ba byang
NK091(ke)001:8000: chub kyi sems gcig la nyes pa zad /
NK091(ke)001:8003: zag pa dang bral ba'i khyad par bzhi rdzogs ste /
NK091(ke)001:8004: zag pa med pa'i bslab pa'i mtha' bcu legs par chub cing rtogs nas /
NK091(ke)001:8006: 'tsho ba med dang mi basngagasa 'khor ba med //
NK091(ke)001:8007: 'khor gyis 'jig bral 'ching ba'i bag tsha rnam par spangs /
NK091(ke)001:8008: zhes pa ltar 'jigsa pa lnga las 'das te /
NK091(ke)001:8009: ji lta ba'i don mthong ba la brten nas sgom
NK091(ke)001:8010: pas 'bras bu khyad par can du 'gro bas sa
NK091(ke)001:8011: drug par gnas te chos nyid kun tu 'gro ba'i
NK091(ke)001:8013: dus de'i tshe sangsa rgyas drug khri drug stong la
NK091(ke)001:8014: the tshom bcad pasa rgyal ba la ltos na gnyis
NK091(ke)001:8015: su med pa'i don phyogs tsam shes te sa dang
NK091(ke)001:8016: por dbugs phyin par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:8017: de nas 'gro don byed pa'i tshul yang 'di ltar /
NK091(ke)001:8018: thams cad ye shes sgyu mar mthong bas sgyu mar
NK091(ke)001:8019: lta bu'i lus kyis dngos po dang mtshan ma'i rgyud
NK091(ke)001:8020: sbyong ba'i skyes bu de yis gzhan don la rtsol
NK091(ke)001:8021: ba de yang mi basngagasa pa med pa thob pas
NK091(ke)001:8022: mtshan dang dpe byad ldan pa'i lha mi'i rgyal po'i
NK091(ke)001:8023: sku 'khor los bsgyur ba'i cha byad can du sprul
NK091(ke)001:8024: nas / blon po dang btsun mo la sogs rin
NK091(ke)001:8025: chen sna bdun dang dpung gi tshogs bzhi po rnams
NK091(ke)001:8026: kyis cha rkyen dang ldan par rang gi 'dod pa
NK091(ke)001:8027: gser dngul zangs lcags gang yin pa'i 'khor los dbang
NK091(ke)001:8028: bskur bas gling bzhi sogs la mnga' dbang bsgyur te
NK091(ke)001:8029: gdul bya rnams la tshig tsam du thabas kyi rgyal
NK091(ke)001:8030: po theg pa chen po'i lam yang ston cing don
NK091(ke)001:8031: dge ba bcu la legs par 'god de rin chen
NK091(ke)001:8032: bdun gyi dbang thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:8037: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8038: yang sangs rgyas rnams kyis lung bstan pa chen po
NK091(ke)001:8039: thob pa'i skabs su rgyu'i sgom lam sa dgur lung
NK091(ke)001:8040: bstan pa dngos su 'byung zhing thob pa dang lta
NK091(ke)001:8041: ba mtshungs pa min kyang rnam par thun mong du
NK091(ke)001:8042: gyur pa ltar shes par bya ste /
NK091(ke)001:8043: de'ang sa drug pa la rnal 'byor bdun dang bdun
NK091(ke)001:8044: pa la gsum du gsungs pa mtshan nyid kyi 'phags
NK091(ke)001:8045: pa'i sa bcu dang sbyar te tha ma la phyi
NK091(ke)001:8046: rgyud gsum gyi don yang gnas par mdo chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:8047: rang lugs su bshad pa ltar te /
NK091(ke)001:8049: drug pa la bdun dbugs chen 'byin pa ni //
NK091(ke)001:8050: bdag gnyis med rtogs mthong lam sa rab daga'o //
NK091(ke)001:8051: rigs chen 'dzin pas gnyis pa dri ma bral //
NK091(ke)001:8052: mnyam rdzogs bden pa gnyis mnyam gsum pa byed //
NK091(ke)001:8053: nges spyod thugs chud don mdzad bzhi pa 'phro //
NK091(ke)001:8054: rtsal sbyong dbyer med sbyong bas sa lnga pa //
NK091(ke)001:8055: rig pas chos nyid yul la 'jug pas drug /rig par sbyor bas nyon mongs dag pas bdun //
NK091(ke)001:8056: bdun pa la gsum grub pa'i rnal 'byor ni //
NK091(ke)001:8057: mtshan ma las grol mi g.yor gnas pas brgyad //
NK091(ke)001:8058: legs pa cher ldan rnal 'byor chen po dgu //
NK091(ke)001:8059: nges 'byung gzhir gnas chos kyi sprin chen te //
NK091(ke)001:8060: dam tshig ye shes 'byed pas phyi rgyud gsum //
NK091(ke)001:8061: zhes gsungs pa ltar dbugs chen 'byin pa ni rgyu'i
NK091(ke)001:8062: rab tu dga' ba rnal 'byor gsum pa dang sbyor
NK091(ke)001:8063: la / de nas sa gnyis pa nas brgyad pa
NK091(ke)001:8064: man chad kyi rigs chen 'dzin pa'i rnal 'byor mi
NK091(ke)001:8067: nges par 'byin pa'am spyod pa'i rnal 'byor /
NK091(ke)001:8070: rig par sbyong ba'am sbyor ba'i rnal 'byor /
NK091(ke)001:8071: sa bdun pa rang gi grub pa'i rnal 'byor gyi bar sems bdun rdzogs te /
NK091(ke)001:8072: lhan cig gnas pa g.yo ba'i dri ma shes bya rags pa dag nas /
NK091(ke)001:8073: rtog pa'i ri bo dgu bcu'am 'dzin pa'i cha mtha'
NK091(ke)001:8074: dag las brgal te don la ting nge 'dzin du
NK091(ke)001:8075: byas pas rnal 'byor chen po dang nges par 'byung
NK091(ke)001:8076: ba'i rnal 'byor kyang ngang la gnas pa dang mthar
NK091(ke)001:8077: lam la sbyor ba'i rtsal du rdzogs nas ting nge
NK091(ke)001:8078: 'dzin la dmigsa pas 'brasa bu skye ba'i sa bdun
NK091(ke)001:8079: par gnas so // de'i tshe sangs rgyas bdun khri
NK091(ke)001:8080: bdun stong gi lung thob ste the tshom bcad pas
NK091(ke)001:8081: thun mong ltar kri yog rnam gsum la gnas te
NK091(ke)001:8082: lha yi skur yang gsal ba'i phyir yang dag pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8083: rtog chen rig 'dzin gyi sa la gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:8084: de yang sgom lam gyi gzhan don byed tshul 'di ltar /
NK091(ke)001:8085: lam la goms pa de tshe skyes bu dam pa
NK091(ke)001:8086: de yis rang don du 'bras bu nyid la lam
NK091(ke)001:8087: du shes pas theg pa mchog gi don mthong bas
NK091(ke)001:8088: rang gi rig pa la 'bras bu'i lam gyi yan
NK091(ke)001:8089: lag thams cad shin tu bde bar rdzogs te nyam
NK091(ke)001:8090: nga ba med pa la gzhan don du gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:8091: dag smin par bya ba'i phyir ji ltar 'dod pa
NK091(ke)001:8092: ltar rngon pa dang smad 'tshong la sogs pa ji
NK091(ke)001:8093: ltar 'dul ba'i cha lugs kyis 'dul te thabs chen
NK091(ke)001:8094: mchog gi sbyor bas ci ltar spyad kyang mi gos
NK091(ke)001:8095: pa'i tshul gyis don rdzogs par mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:8100: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8101: yang mthar lam gyi rtsal chen dang po rdzogs pa'i skabs su /
NK091(ke)001:8102: rmad byung rol pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK091(ke)001:8104: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor gsum sgom ste sems
NK091(ke)001:8105: gsum bskyed cing bslab pa'i mtha' yas nas bgrangs pa
NK091(ke)001:8106: drug gi don rtogs shing chub ste mthar phyin nas
NK091(ke)001:8107: don gyi ngo bo gnas pa mi 'gyur ba'i sa
NK091(ke)001:8110: bslab pa bcu yi sgra gcig la //
NK091(ke)001:8111: zag bcas bzhi dang bar chad med //
NK091(ke)001:8112: zag med lam lnga'i bslab pa dag /slob pa'i lugs dang lobs pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:8113: nus mthu dang ni ngo bo dag /bslab pa'i yul gyi khyad par 'gyur //
NK091(ke)001:8115: de'i tshe sangs rgyas brgyad khri brgyad stong las lung
NK091(ke)001:8116: bstan pa mngon sum du thob nas the tshom bcad
NK091(ke)001:8117: pas tha ma'i don nges pa'i ting nge 'dzin la
NK091(ke)001:8118: nyam mi nga bar gdenga chen po rnyed de rtogs
NK091(ke)001:8119: pa mthar phyin pa nyid du gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:8120: de ni mtshan nyid ltar na sa bcu rgyun gyi tha ma ste /
NK091(ke)001:8122: longs spyod rdzogs pa chen po'i 'khor du nges pa
NK091(ke)001:8123: desa na ston pa'i rgyal tshab 'chad pa'i skyes bu
NK091(ke)001:8124: nyid du gyur pa de yis chos kyi rgyal po
NK091(ke)001:8125: ston pa chen po mya ngan las 'das nas mthar
NK091(ke)001:8126: lam pa gang de yi gzhan don gyi spyod pas
NK091(ke)001:8127: ston pa'i gdung 'tshob ste rigs 'dzin cing da lta
NK091(ke)001:8128: dga' ldan lha yi gnas na 'khor rnams la dad
NK091(ke)001:8129: pa skye ba'i theg pa chen po ston te byams
NK091(ke)001:8130: pa lta bu dang mi yi gnas tshe lo bcu
NK091(ke)001:8131: pa'i dus yan chad du de'i mdzad pa 'byung ste
NK091(ke)001:8132: tshig dang bstan pa la sogs pa cho 'phrul kun
NK091(ke)001:8133: tu snang ngo // sangs rgyas kyi grangs mang nyung
NK091(ke)001:8134: ni sa non cing sgrib pa dag pas spobs pa
NK091(ke)001:8135: dang stobs khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir grangs cha
NK091(ke)001:8136: tu snang ngo // res 'phags so // brdal ba
NK091(ke)001:8137: chos nyid kyi sa dang rdzogs pa spyir chibs kyi
NK091(ke)001:8138: sa ni da dung ma non te lam tha ma'i
NK091(ke)001:8140: lam bgrod tshul 'di dag ni rjes su 'jug pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8141: dbang du na theg pa dgu nyid rgyud gcig gi
NK091(ke)001:8142: dbang du gyur pa ste bskal pa mang pos snga
NK091(ke)001:8144: grub pa nas grub par thug pa med par 'jug pa lta bu ni ma yin gyi /
NK091(ke)001:8145: so so'i rgyu'i lta spyod ting nge 'dzin las bogs su gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:8149: lam rnal 'byor lngar bgrod tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:8154: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8155: lang ka'i bdag po de ltar na gzhi'i las dang po pa'i rigs kyi bu de dag ni /
NK091(ke)001:8156: mi bu rigs lngar skye ba blangsa pa de nas kyang /
NK091(ke)001:8159: sa la snyegs pas rigs so so nges pa nas
NK091(ke)001:8160: phyis bskal pa grangs med pa dpag tu med pa
NK091(ke)001:8161: brjod pa las 'das para snga phyir 'byung ba'i thog
NK091(ke)001:8162: ma dang tha ma med pa'i dus na /
NK091(ke)001:8163: dang po gsang ba mchog gi sems bskyed pa'ang sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang chen po dang /
NK091(ke)001:8166: chos kyi dbang phyug rgyal po dang /
NK091(ke)001:8167: las sna tshogs dang lnga la rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK091(ke)001:8171: don yod grub pa dang lngas dngos po'i gnas lugs
NK091(ke)001:8172: dang mthun par byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas
NK091(ke)001:8177: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8178: de ltar sems bskyed nas 'khor losa sgyur ba'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:8179: po rnam par snang byed kyi bu lngar skyes te
NK091(ke)001:8180: rgyal bu spun lngar gyur pa ni 'di lta ste
NK091(ke)001:8181: / sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa' ni mdzes pa'i me tog dang /
NK091(ke)001:8182: sangs rgyas rnam par snang mdzad ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dpal dang /
NK091(ke)001:8183: sangs rgyas rin chen 'byung ldan ni nor sbyin 'dzin dang /
NK091(ke)001:8184: sangs rgyas 'od dpag med ni zla mdzes dpal dang /
NK091(ke)001:8185: sangs rgyas don yod grub pa ni kun la mdzes pa'i 'od ces bya ba dang lngar gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:8189: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8190: de ltar rigs lnga khye'u lngar gyur pa de dag
NK091(ke)001:8191: chos thams cad bdag nyid chen por lhun gyis grub
NK091(ke)001:8192: pa'i gsang chen mchog gi las kyi dang po gsang
NK091(ke)001:8193: sngags theg pa chen po gnyis su med pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:8194: la mos shing 'dun bas sems pa'i rnal 'byor par
NK091(ke)001:8195: gyur pa nyid la gsang sngags spyi'i mtshan nyid la
NK091(ke)001:8196: sgra'i rjes su 'brangs pas nges pa rnyed de tshig
NK091(ke)001:8197: gi rjes su don yid la byed pa zhes bya
NK091(ke)001:8198: ba'i lta ba dang de ltar mos pas sgom pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8200: des las kyi sgrib pa dag nas sems 'phar te
NK091(ke)001:8201: sa nas sar 'byung ba'i skal ba can du gyur
NK091(ke)001:8202: pas chos dbyings kyi nam mkha' la 'gro ba'i rmi
NK091(ke)001:8203: ltas dag mthong bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:8204: de'i tshe tshogs gsog pa bya ba las kyi spyod pa la gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:8205: de nas gnyis pa ltung ba dang mi ltung ba'am
NK091(ke)001:8206: lam dang 'bras bu'i rigs chen po 'byed pa'i rnal
NK091(ke)001:8208: de kho na nyid mthong ma rag pas bar chad med pa'i lta ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:8209: sems phyir 'phro ba dang nang du 'du ba yi
NK091(ke)001:8210: ge dang phyag rgya gnyis la byed de gang yul
NK091(ke)001:8211: du gtad pa'i mtshan ma la sems rtse gcig tu
NK091(ke)001:8212: gyur pas chos ma 'gags pa dang mi dmigs pa
NK091(ke)001:8213: dbyer med pa'i ting nge 'dzin las gzhan du mi
NK091(ke)001:8215: desa yi ge'i gzungs thob pa'i phyir bdag nyid yi
NK091(ke)001:8216: ge' phreng bar snang ba'i rmi ltas mthong bar gyur
NK091(ke)001:8217: to // de'i dus su spyod pa ni brtson 'grus kyis phyogs gcig la gnas par byed do //
NK091(ke)001:8218: de nas gsum pa bden pa rnam gnyis dbyer med
NK091(ke)001:8219: pa'i don mngon sum du mthong bas dang por dbugsa
NK091(ke)001:8220: chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor par snang ba nyid la
NK091(ke)001:8221: / ji bzhin pa mngon sum du rtogs pa'i lta
NK091(ke)001:8222: bas 'jigs pa lnga dang bral zhing chu srin gyi
NK091(ke)001:8223: phyag rgya lta bur gyur pas 'khor ba'i gnas dang
NK091(ke)001:8224: / / theg pa dman pa dang lta spyod dman
NK091(ke)001:8225: par yongsa su mi ldog pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK091(ke)001:8227: des spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i phyir snang ba thams cad yid bzhin lha yi sku'am /
NK091(ke)001:8228: 'jig rten gyi khams nor bu rin po ches gang bar spyod pa'i rmi ltas mthong bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:8229: de ni 'khor los sgyur ba'i cha byad kyis chos ston pa'i yang rtags so //
NK091(ke)001:8230: de'i tshe shes rab dang mthun par mi dmigs pa'i spyod pa la gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:8231: de nas bzhi pa rgyal ba rnams las lung chen
NK091(ke)001:8232: po thob nas 'bras bu lhun gyis grub pa'i rnal
NK091(ke)001:8234: chos thams cad chos kyi dbyings su lhun gyis grub pas mtshan mas mi g.yo ba'i lta ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:8235: ril gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin las ma g.yo bar 'thob bo //
NK091(ke)001:8236: des mtshan ma la sogs pa ldang mi nus pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8237: phyir seng ge dag la zhon te thams cad zil
NK091(ke)001:8238: gyis gnon pa'i rmi ltas mthong bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:8239: de ni rnam rtog zil gyis gnon cing mi 'jigs bzhi rjes mthun pa thob pa'i yang ltas so //
NK091(ke)001:8240: de'i tshe rngon pa dang smad 'tshong lta bu yan
NK091(ke)001:8241: chad kyis don mdzad pas thabs kyi spyod pa la
NK091(ke)001:8242: gnas so // de nas lnga pa bgrod pa la
NK091(ke)001:8243: ltos nas 'bras bu'i chos kyi rtsal chen po dang
NK091(ke)001:8244: por rdzogs te mthar phyin pa'ii rnal 'byor du snang
NK091(ke)001:8245: gnas so // ba nyid la / ltos nas mthar thug pa'i lta ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:8246: ril rig pa'i ye shes yang dag pa'i thugs rjes
NK091(ke)001:8247: zin pa'i don gsal la khyab pas kun tu snang
NK091(ke)001:8248: gi ting nge 'dzin 'thob ste thugs rje dang ye
NK091(ke)001:8249: shes dang cho 'phrul gyis yongs su khyab par mdzad
NK091(ke)001:8250: do // desa ston pa'i rgyal tshab nus pa'i ye
NK091(ke)001:8251: shes dang thugs rje chen pos 'og ma ltar btsal
NK091(ke)001:8252: bar don rdzogs pas nyi zla'i 'khor lo bskor bas
NK091(ke)001:8253: thams cad 'od kyis gsal bar byed pa'i rmi ltas
NK091(ke)001:8255: 'di nyid mthar lam dang po yin la des mthar
NK091(ke)001:8256: lam bar par rang byung ye shes 'od gsal ba'i
NK091(ke)001:8258: de'i tshe bya ba med pa'am btsal ba med pa'i spyod pa la gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:8260: sa bcu la ting nge 'dzin gyi rnal 'byor bcu dang /
NK091(ke)001:8261: rnal 'byor so bzhi gsungs pa rnams sbyar te so
NK091(ke)001:8262: so'i sems bskyed dang sa lam gyi ngo bo rgyas
NK091(ke)001:8263: par bshad na gal che bar mngon yang yi ges
NK091(ke)001:8264: 'jigs pas blo gsal rnams kyis le'u re gcig pa
NK091(ke)001:8265: sa'i sgron ma las rnal 'byor so bzhi'am bzhi bcu
NK091(ke)001:8266: 'byung ba ltar sbyar te chos rje dam pa rin
NK091(ke)001:8267: po che'i gsung sgros sogs gnad mang po yod pa
NK091(ke)001:8269: 'o na 'dir rigs lngas sems bskyed pa ni ldab par gyur pa'i dgos pa ji zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:8270: mdo sngags kyi lugs rnam pa gnyis kyi dbang du bskyed par bstan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:8274: thun mong gi dbang du bskal pa snga phyir skye
NK091(ke)001:8275: ba'i rim pas phyi ma la rgyu nas bgrod de
NK091(ke)001:8276: mjug tu sngags su sems bskyed par brgyud pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:8277: te / rigs lngar skye ba blangs pa de nas kyang zhes sngar bstan pas mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:8278: de ltar khye'u lngas lam bgrod pa de sngon byung sprul pa'i lam yin te /
NK091(ke)001:8279: rgyal ba rigs lnga khye'u lngar sprul pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:8280: lam lnga phrag gnyis su lan gnyis bgrod pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:8281: snga ma ni thun mong gi lam chen po nas bgrod pa yin la /
NK091(ke)001:8282: phyi ma ni a nu yo ga'i rang lam thun mong min pa nas bgrod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:8283: yang snga ma ni bdag don du bgrod la /
NK091(ke)001:8284: phyi ma ni gzhan don du bgrod par gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:8285: lam lnga phyi'i bar na bskal pa dpag tu med pa brjod pa las 'das pa /
NK091(ke)001:8286: zhes bskal pa mang pos bar chod pa de mi 'thad ce na /
NK091(ke)001:8287: zur snga rabs pa rnams de ni lam snga ma
NK091(ke)001:8288: bgrod nas mthar lam du sleb nas mthar lam gyi
NK091(ke)001:8289: dgongs pa'i yun bskal pa tshad med pa yin te
NK091(ke)001:8291: bskal pa tshad med pas so //
NK091(ke)001:8293: 'di la kun mkhyen kahthoga pa chen pos /
NK091(ke)001:8294: kho bo ni lam snga ma rgyal ba rigs lngas
NK091(ke)001:8295: khye'u lngar skye ba blangs nas 'jig rten phal pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8297: phyi ma ni rang gi lam nas bgrod de de
NK091(ke)001:8298: ltar thun mong gi lam bgrod nas mthar lam gyi
NK091(ke)001:8299: bar du bskal pa mang po thogs par 'thad de
NK091(ke)001:8301: las dang po pa'i rigs kyi bu de dag ni
NK091(ke)001:8302: rigs lngar skye ba blangs pa de nas kyang bskal
NK091(ke)001:8303: pa dpag tu med pa brjod pa las 'das pa
NK091(ke)001:8304: thog ma dang tha ma med pa'i dus na zhes
NK091(ke)001:8305: pas mngon no // des na lam lnga phrag gnyis
NK091(ke)001:8306: bdag don gzhan don a cang che ste snga ma
NK091(ke)001:8307: ni mdo chen po'i lugs kyi rgyu 'bras thun mong
NK091(ke)001:8309: phyi ma ni mdo chen po'i rang lugs thun min
NK091(ke)001:8310: gyi sgo nas bgrod de gnyis ka 'bras bu'i lam
NK091(ke)001:8311: la ltos na lam thun mong pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:8312: 'bras bu'i lam dngos ni rtogs bya mthar thug gi ngo bo gsang sngags yin pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:8313: dbang bskur dgos pa rang gis mthar lam bar pa
NK091(ke)001:8314: nas gsang sngags ci bzhin pa'i lam du bgrangs te
NK091(ke)001:8315: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de kho na nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:8316: nges pa rnyed pa de nas 'byung bar gsungs pas
NK091(ke)001:8317: so // spyir sngags la 'jug pa la nges pa med de /
NK091(ke)001:8318: lam mtho dman gang nas kyang rung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:8319: zhes bka' stsal te gzhung don ji lta ba bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:8327: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8329: de ltar rtsol ba dang bcas pa'i lam thob tu
NK091(ke)001:8330: zin kyang sa tha ma gnyis ma non pas gsang
NK091(ke)001:8331: sngags kyi ngo bo ji bzhin pa de kho na
NK091(ke)001:8332: nyid kyi nges pa rnyed pa ni ma yin te
NK091(ke)001:8333: da dung yul du byed pa yod pas so //
NK091(ke)001:8334: zhes gsang sngags rtsol med kyi lam la drang ba
NK091(ke)001:8335: dang rgyal ba'i dgongs pa la ltos nas yin no
NK091(ke)001:8340: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8341: de'i gtan tshigs brjod pa de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:8343: gang lasa dang po pa'i rigsa kyi bu de dag
NK091(ke)001:8344: mthar lam dang po thob ste bar pa'i ltas mthong
NK091(ke)001:8345: nas rgyal tshab skyes bura gyur pa na mdzes pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8346: me tog la skyes bu dam pa rdo rje sems
NK091(ke)001:8347: dapa'a dang / nor sbyin 'dzin la skyes bu dam pa'i rdo rje rin chen dang /
NK091(ke)001:8348: zla mdzes dpal la skyes bu dam pa rdo rje chos dang /
NK091(ke)001:8349: kun la mdzes pa'i 'od la skyes bu dam pa las kyi rdo rje dang /
NK091(ke)001:8350: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dpal la skyes bu dam
NK091(ke)001:8351: pa rdo rje dbyings zhes bya bar phyogs thug pa
NK091(ke)001:8352: med pa'i zhing khams thams cad du grags so //
NK091(ke)001:8353: de la zhing khams la lara ni sku lnga'am rigs
NK091(ke)001:8354: lnga'i rgyal tshab skyes bu zhes bya bar brjod cing
NK091(ke)001:8356: la lara ni 'khor los sgyur ba'i skye ba lta
NK091(ke)001:8357: bur bzhes nas rten des byang chub chen po brnyes
NK091(ke)001:8358: pas srid pa tha ma pa zhes bya bar brjod
NK091(ke)001:8360: la lara ni lhun grub rig 'dzin sa chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:8361: sangs rgyasa zhes bya bar brjod cing rgyud dag pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8363: gsang sngags de kho na nyid spyod yul dang bral
NK091(ke)001:8364: bas 'byung 'jug med pa'i sangsa rgyas kyi dgongs pa
NK091(ke)001:8365: gasnga ba dam pa da dung ji bzhin du nyams
NK091(ke)001:8367: gsang sngags yul du byed pa'i mnyam bzhag la sgom
NK091(ke)001:8368: ldang yod pas nges pa'i gnad ma chud de gzhag
NK091(ke)001:8369: tu med pa la yul du bzung nas mnyam pa
NK091(ke)001:8372: nges pa ma rnyed pa ci nyes zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:8373: blo gros ma chub pas nyes pas chub par gdams pa /
NK091(ke)001:8374: blo gros chub pa'i thabs zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:8380: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8381: de'ang ye ji bzhin pa'i rgyal ba'i dgongs pa ma rtogs pa'i gtan tshigs de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:8382: skyes bu dam pa de dag gis nam mnyam pa la ma bzhag gi bar du /
NK091(ke)001:8383: dus phyad pa chen po sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa
NK091(ke)001:8384: nyams su myong nas ting nge 'dzin gyi the tshom
NK091(ke)001:8385: gcod pa'i phyir gsang sngags yul du byed pa'i bsam
NK091(ke)001:8386: pa yang dag pa'i rtog pas ye phyi ma'i ston
NK091(ke)001:8387: pa dang po'i sangs rgyas rdo rje sems dpa' sangs
NK091(ke)001:8388: rgyas kun gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen la gsol pa
NK091(ke)001:8390: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'adsa rnams la ni mnyam para
NK091(ke)001:8391: bzhag pa dang ma bzhag pa mi mnga' bar rnam
NK091(ke)001:8392: pa thams cad mkhyen pa yin na /
NK091(ke)001:8393: skyes bu lnga po bdag cag gisa bskal pa dpag
NK091(ke)001:8394: tu med par thun mong rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8395: dka' ba dpag tu med par bgyi ba thams cad
NK091(ke)001:8396: yongs su rdzogs par bgyisa kyang /
NK091(ke)001:8397: mnyam par ma bzhag gi bar du sangs rgyas kyi
NK091(ke)001:8398: dgongs pa nyams su myong bar ma 'gyur pa 'di
NK091(ke)001:8400: bde bar gshegs pa ngo mtshar che lags so //
NK091(ke)001:8401: zhes ya mtshan shin tu che bas lan gnyis brjod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:8402: de skad ces gsol pa las /
NK091(ke)001:8404: spyir sa dang po man chad sprul sku'i 'khor //
NK091(ke)001:8406: mthar lam pa chos sku'i 'khor te kun tu bzang po'i rgyal tshab byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:8407: de'i phyir sangs rgyas kun gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen kyang spyir na chos sku yin la /
NK091(ke)001:8408: gdul bya'i ched du bstan pa mi 'gags pas go
NK091(ke)001:8409: phye ba'i 'khor gyi dbang du longs sku'ang mi 'gal
NK091(ke)001:8414: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8415: bcom ldan 'adsa sems dpa' rdo rje snying po des bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:8416: kye skyes bu dam pa rnams /
NK091(ke)001:8417: gang de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du lhun gyis grub
NK091(ke)001:8418: par 'dod pa rnams kyis sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos
NK091(ke)001:8419: dus snga phyi thams cad nasa thams cad du rang
NK091(ke)001:8420: dang spyi'i mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8421: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes chags thogs
NK091(ke)001:8422: dang bral bar bya ba dam pa'i mdzod gsum du
NK091(ke)001:8423: nges pa las / khyed rnams kyis gang bya ba spyod pa yongs su rdzogs para byas shing /
NK091(ke)001:8424: bsrung ba dam tshig yongs su dag para byas su zin kyang /
NK091(ke)001:8425: da dung blo gros dam pa'i lta bas nges pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8426: gdengs chen po ma rnyed pas kun tu chub par
NK091(ke)001:8427: ma byas so // de lta bas na gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:8428: phyi mo'i chos nyid gdod ma nasa dam pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:8429: kyi de kho na nyid dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med
NK091(ke)001:8430: pa'i don la blo gros kun tu chub par mdzod
NK091(ke)001:8431: la rtogs par gyis shig dang /
NK091(ke)001:8432: de yongs su chub pa bzhin du dam pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:8433: kyi dgongs pa ji bzhin pa myong nas mngon par
NK091(ke)001:8434: rdzogs par sangs rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:8435: de skad ces gdams shing bka' stsal pa las /
NK091(ke)001:8440: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8441: skyes bu dam pa rnams kyis gsol pa /
NK091(ke)001:8443: zhes ngo mtshar ba'i tshig gis drangs te /
NK091(ke)001:8444: ston pa bcom ldana 'das zhes bos nas /
NK091(ke)001:8445: bcom ldan 'das kyis ni bdag cag rnams la gsang
NK091(ke)001:8446: ba ya mtshan lnga'i 'byung gnas mchog tu gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:8447: snang la rang bzhin med pas shin tu ngo mtshar
NK091(ke)001:8448: che zhing gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pas rmad
NK091(ke)001:8449: du byung ba / don zab la mu mtha' yas pas dapagas par dka' ba /
NK091(ke)001:8450: phyogs gcig tu ma nges pas the tshom skye ste nges par rnyed dka' ba /
NK091(ke)001:8451: don 'di ma yin pa zhig kyang yod dam snyam
NK091(ke)001:8452: pas soma nyi 'tshal bar gyur pa la don 'di
NK091(ke)001:8453: rtogs shing chub par gyis shig pa'i tshig gsungs te
NK091(ke)001:8455: lta bas blo gros kun tu chub par bgyid pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8456: gdal khyab chen po'i ye shes sangs rgyas dam pa
NK091(ke)001:8457: rnams kyi rang bzhin ji lta ba de kho na
NK091(ke)001:8458: nyid ces bgyi ba de gang lagas /
NK091(ke)001:8459: bdag don du bshad du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:8460: gzhan don du bde bar gshegs pa bshad du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:8466: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8467: rgyal ba ril gyi the tshom gcod pa'i phyir sangs rgyas kun gyi bcom ldan 'das /
NK091(ke)001:8468: gsang sngags kyi de kho na nyid bstan pa dang
NK091(ke)001:8469: ston pa tha mi dad pa'i dbang gis ye ji
NK091(ke)001:8470: bzhin pa des bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:8471: kye skyes bu dam pa rnams kyi de kho na nyid 'di ni /
NK091(ke)001:8473: nyon mongs pa lam du bde bas thabs che la /
NK091(ke)001:8474: dngos po gang yang bsal spangs med par thabs kun shong bas sgo yangas pa /
NK091(ke)001:8475: rtsol ba'i tshi chad pa med par 'bras bu lam du byed pas tshegs chung la /
NK091(ke)001:8476: khams gsum ye shes bla ma'i sar grub nas mthar thug gi 'bras bu 'byung bas don che ba /
NK091(ke)001:8477: dus la rag ma las par rtogs ma thag pas
NK091(ke)001:8478: chog cing rang la rdzogs te bgrod mi dgos pas
NK091(ke)001:8479: thag nye la / ngo bo la blos yongs su
NK091(ke)001:8480: lhan te reg pa med par don spyod yul dang
NK091(ke)001:8482: ma rtogs par sgra bzhin dpyad na sgo dgu sogs
NK091(ke)001:8483: ltung ba'i sa mang la gol sa che ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:8484: nyen che la / zhen pas ngo bo de las mi g.yo bar bya dka' zhing /
NK091(ke)001:8485: rtsa ba dang yan lag las 'das na brlag par 'gyur bas bsrung dka' ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:8486: snod dkon la go dka' ba'i dbang gis sam /
NK091(ke)001:8487: yang na shes brjod dang bral bas mtshon dka' /
NK091(ke)001:8488: dmigs yul las 'das pas go dka' bas na ngas
NK091(ke)001:8489: kyang khyed la 'di yin no zhes ci 'dra bar
NK091(ke)001:8490: phyin ci ma log par bstan par rab tu daka'o
NK091(ke)001:8491: // de ltar gsal bar ston mi spyod pa ltar byas nas thabs kyis dngos su mtshon pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:8492: de skad ces bka' stsal pa las /
NK091(ke)001:8493: skyes bu dam pa de rnams ston pas gsang ba
NK091(ke)001:8494: ston mi spyod pa'i gnad chud de don go dka'
NK091(ke)001:8495: zhing bstan dka' ba la dmigs te rma ga chad
NK091(ke)001:8496: par rang don du ngus so //
NK091(ke)001:8497: gzhan don du shin tu rab tu ngus nas gsang
NK091(ke)001:8498: ba'i sngags kyi sgo bye bar gyur te gsang don
NK091(ke)001:8499: rig pa la shar bas 'khor ba rang sar grol
NK091(ke)001:8500: nas de kho na nyid bde ba chen po rtogs
NK091(ke)001:8501: pas mthar lam bar pa la zin te brdal ba
NK091(ke)001:8502: chos nyid kyi sa non pas chos thams cad bshad
NK091(ke)001:8503: ma thag pa'i gsang sngags kyi dngos po brgyad du
NK091(ke)001:8504: gnas pa'i mtshan nyid yongs su shes par gyur to
NK091(ke)001:8506: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:8507: rgyud dag pa'i rgyal tshab lnga'i skad cig ma'i rgyun
NK091(ke)001:8508: las sa lam 'phags pa'i skye rgyud bstan pa'i le'u
NK091(ke)001:8509: ste bcu gcig pa rnam par bshad pa'o ////bzhi pa
NK091(ke)001:8510: dbugs dbyung zhing nges pa rnyed pa dngos la gsum
NK091(ke)001:8511: ste / gdams pa nye bar bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:8518: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8519: le'u 'dis nges don mdor bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:8520: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa gzugs sku thams cad
NK091(ke)001:8521: kyi bdag nyid sku gsum dbyer med pa'i bcom ldan
NK091(ke)001:8522: 'das sangs rgyas dam pa rnams kyi rang bzhin nam
NK091(ke)001:8523: ngo bo de kho na nyid rdo rje sems dpa'
NK091(ke)001:8524: des / skyes bu dam pa lnga po de dag la 'di skad ces bka'a stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:8525: kye skyes bu dam pa rnams ma ngu zhig /
NK091(ke)001:8526: 'bras bu la re zhing rtsol bas sdug bsngal gyi
NK091(ke)001:8527: gdung ba ma bskyed cig /khyed rnams rang chas su
NK091(ke)001:8528: yod bzhin du cii'i phyir ngu ba yin zhes mi
NK091(ke)001:8529: ngu ba'i thabs bka' stsal to //
NK091(ke)001:8530: spyir mthar lam tha ma la rnal 'byor gsum du
NK091(ke)001:8531: gsungs pas klong yangs chub pa'i rnal 'byor gyi skabs
NK091(ke)001:8532: su gza' gtad med pa'i lta ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:8533: snang gsal ye 'phyo'i ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin pa na ngo bo nyid sku'i 'khor yin pas /
NK091(ke)001:8534: de'i tshul rgyas par rdzogs pa chen po'i kun grol
NK091(ke)001:8535: gyi rgyud las 'byung ba ltar shes dgos kyang mdor
NK091(ke)001:8536: bsdus pa tsam le'u nga drug pa snang ba dag
NK091(ke)001:8537: pa'i spyod yul bstan pa'i dus su 'chad par spros
NK091(ke)001:8538: / de'i dbang gis mdo chen po'i gleng gzhi sku lnga dang sbyor ba'ang /
NK091(ke)001:8539: sku gsum gyi steng du gsang ba'i sku dang ngo
NK091(ke)001:8540: bo nyid sku la 'jog pa yin te go rim
NK091(ke)001:8541: la nges pa med pa ni dus 'dir lung bstan
NK091(ke)001:8542: brgyud pa'i bstan pa dbang btsan pa'i don to //
NK091(ke)001:8544: dbugs ji ltar dbyung zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:8545: chos nyid ma rtogs pa'i dpe yod bas sdug bsngal ma skyed cig par gdams pa /
NK091(ke)001:8546: de la mos te rdo rje sems dpa' la zhu ba the tshom bcad pa /
NK091(ke)001:8547: de kho na nyid zhus pa dngos /
NK091(ke)001:8548: de'i lan du de kho na nyid bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:8549: de ltar rtogs pa'i yon tan no //
NK091(ke)001:8554: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8555: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi bcom ldan 'das /
NK091(ke)001:8556: rdo rje sems dpa' de kho na nyid la skyes
NK091(ke)001:8557: bu dam pa de rnams kyis 'di skad ces gsol
NK091(ke)001:8558: to // bcom ldan 'das yong ji ltar thabs gang gis mi ngu bar bgyi /
NK091(ke)001:8559: bdag cag gis rgyu'i sgo nas 'bras bu bsgrub pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8560: btsal ba ji snyed pa rnams tshi chad de ngal
NK091(ke)001:8561: ba don med par nyon mongs shing thang chad du
NK091(ke)001:8562: byas te gyong bskur bar ma gyur tam /
NK091(ke)001:8563: bcom ldan 'das bdag cag gi blo gros kyis don ji ltar rtogs par bgyi /
NK091(ke)001:8564: bdag cag rnams kyi bshes gnyen dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:8565: bdag cag gis bskal pa dpag tu meda pa ji
NK091(ke)001:8566: snyed zhig tu rgyu'i sgo nas dka' ba dpag tu
NK091(ke)001:8567: med pa spyad nas 'bras bu yongs su chub par
NK091(ke)001:8568: 'dod na yang da dung du gsang sngags kyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:8569: bo de kho na nyid phyin ci ma log par
NK091(ke)001:8570: bstan par daka'o zhes sangs rgyas la ltos na ming
NK091(ke)001:8571: tsam thos pa'i skal ba yanga ma mchis pas thabs
NK091(ke)001:8572: zad pa lta bur gyur na /
NK091(ke)001:8573: da yong ji ltar bya ba'i thabs ma nor ba gang la 'jug par bgyi lagas /
NK091(ke)001:8574: de skada ces gsol pa las /
NK091(ke)001:8579: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8580: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bcom ldan 'das /
NK091(ke)001:8581: rdo rje sems dpa' de kho na nyid desa bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:8582: skyes bu dam pa lnga rnams de skada ma zer cig ces gdams nas /
NK091(ke)001:8583: gsang sngags ni nyan rang dang byang sems la bcu pa sogs kun gyi thun mong ma yin te /
NK091(ke)001:8585: thabs che dpags dka' rtog dpyod 'das //
NK091(ke)001:8586: dman pa'i yul du ma gyur dang //
NK091(ke)001:8587: mchog gi yul gyur mchog bral dang //
NK091(ke)001:8588: thun mong ma gyur bla na med //
NK091(ke)001:8590: don de kho na nyid kyi mtshan nyid ni sangs
NK091(ke)001:8591: rgyas rdo rje sems dpa' nyag gcig gi spyod yul
NK091(ke)001:8592: du gyur pa'i dgongs pa dam pa /
NK091(ke)001:8593: ngo bo med la brjod gzhi dang bral bas smrar med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8594: yul dang bral zhing mtshan nyid med pas lam pa
NK091(ke)001:8595: mtha' dag gi rtog dpyod thams cad dang bral ba
NK091(ke)001:8596: / nges par 'di kho na'o zhes dape'am tshig gis mtshon du med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8597: blos dngos por gzhal te don btsal du med pas brtags par dka' zhing /
NK091(ke)001:8598: dpe dang bral bas tshig gis nye bar bstan par dka' la /
NK091(ke)001:8599: ci yang yin phyir gang du'ang ma nges par tshig
NK091(ke)001:8600: lam dang bral bas brjod pa'i tha snyad rnams dang
NK091(ke)001:8601: bral ba / byang chub sems dang rnam pa thams
NK091(ke)001:8602: cad du phyogs kun nas mtshungs pa med pas dpe
NK091(ke)001:8603: bral ba / dang bral ba / 'o na nam mkhas mi mtshon nam zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:8605: rig med stong pa'i khyad par gyis nam mkha'i khongs
NK091(ke)001:8606: su gsang ba ma 'dus pas nam mkha' dpes kyang
NK091(ke)001:8607: phyogs thams cad nas bskrun du yod pa ma yin
NK091(ke)001:8608: pa / dngos po dang bral bas tshad med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8609: mu mtha' med pas tshad dang bral ba /
NK091(ke)001:8610: chos nyid la nges pa gzung ba med pas thun
NK091(ke)001:8611: mong gi mngon sum dang rjes su dpags pa'i tshad
NK091(ke)001:8613: rten cing 'brel 'byung la sogs pa'i gtan tshigs sama /
NK091(ke)001:8614: rang gi don dang gzhan gyi don du rgyu lkog
NK091(ke)001:8615: tu gyur pa dang rang bzhin lkog tu gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:8616: la rjes su dpagsa pa rnams kyis gzhal bas mi
NK091(ke)001:8617: dpogsa shing mi rig pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:8618: de'i phyir skyes bu lnga po khyed kyisa yul ma
NK091(ke)001:8619: yin pas ji ltar ma shes shing ma thos pa
NK091(ke)001:8620: dee ltar gang rgyud yongs su dag pa'i sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:8621: kun tu 'od la bzhugs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:8622: sa bcu pa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK091(ke)001:8623: rnams kyis sngar bskal pa grangs med mang po nas
NK091(ke)001:8624: sbyangs kyang da dung spyod yul du med pa'i gsang
NK091(ke)001:8625: sngags kyi ngo bo de kho na nyid kyi 'bras
NK091(ke)001:8627: de'i don shes rab kyis mngon par ma rtogsa /
NK091(ke)001:8628: de bas na ji bzhin nyid du ma son te mngon par rdzogs para sangsa rgyas so //
NK091(ke)001:8630: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de kho na nyid mtha'
NK091(ke)001:8631: yod med dang rnam pa bral ma bral thams cad
NK091(ke)001:8632: dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med pa'i ye ji bzhin par
NK091(ke)001:8633: yongs su dag pa de ni tha snyad ril ngang
NK091(ke)001:8634: gis ma spangs la bral ba'i phyir bshad pa bzhin
NK091(ke)001:8635: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' zhes ming gi
NK091(ke)001:8636: bla dwags tsam las ngo bo la rang rgyud pa
NK091(ke)001:8637: mi dmigs shinga de'i phyir don du gnyer te btsal
NK091(ke)001:8639: rgyu'i sa bcu la gnas pa'i skyes bu dam pa rnams kyis ni /
NK091(ke)001:8640: de bzhin gshegsa pa'i snying po gsang sngags kyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:8641: bo de kho na nyid gsang ba dam pa de
NK091(ke)001:8642: lhan cig skyes pa'i mun pas bsgribs pa'i dbang gis
NK091(ke)001:8643: mdzub mo'i rtse mo ltar rang gis rang la reg
NK091(ke)001:8644: par ma nus pas rang la yod para ma shes
NK091(ke)001:8645: te dka' bas gzhan du tshol nas chos nyid la
NK091(ke)001:8646: ched du 'jog cing yul du byed pa'i blo yis
NK091(ke)001:8647: dpyod pa lta ba'i rtog sgrib dang ma bral ba
NK091(ke)001:8648: de'i phyir da dung ma rtogs shing mthob bo //
NK091(ke)001:8649: kun tu 'od la bzhugs pa'i rgyud dag pa'i sangsa
NK091(ke)001:8650: rgyas rnams ni shes bya'i tshul ye snying po byang
NK091(ke)001:8651: chub la shes byed kyi tshul byang chub snying po
NK091(ke)001:8652: nyid du'ang 'du shes kyis mi rtog pa'i ngang du
NK091(ke)001:8653: mi g.yo bar dgongs pa la gnas te rig pa
NK091(ke)001:8654: spyod yul dang bral bar mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8655: mthar dbyung dgos pa'i phyir da dung mngon par rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:8656: par 'tshang mi rgya bar gnas na khyed rnams ci'i
NK091(ke)001:8658: de skada ces bka' stsal pas /
NK091(ke)001:8663: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8664: de ltar gsungs pas 'khor skyes bu dam pa rigs
NK091(ke)001:8665: lnga rnams dga' mgu rangs pas yid bde ba skyes
NK091(ke)001:8666: te dbugs phyin nasa bdag cag kho nas ma rtogs
NK091(ke)001:8667: pa min par thos pas 'di snyam du sems so
NK091(ke)001:8668: // ji ltar bdag cag gi sngon du sems bskyed
NK091(ke)001:8669: de gshegsa pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'adsa dang byang
NK091(ke)001:8670: chub sems dpa' chen po rnams kyis kyang da dung
NK091(ke)001:8671: gsang sngags kyi ngo bo de kho na nyid mngon
NK091(ke)001:8672: du ma gyur par rtsol ba la gnas na /
NK091(ke)001:8673: bdag cag la sogs pa mthar lam du zhugs pas mi rtogs pa lta ci smos te /
NK091(ke)001:8674: nges par yang ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' de
NK091(ke)001:8675: kho na nyid 'di ni sangs rgyas kun gyi the
NK091(ke)001:8676: tshom gcod pas dge ba'i bshes gnyen dam pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:8677: kho na bas bdag cag gi blo gros 'dii la
NK091(ke)001:8678: chub ste gros kyis chod pas mi 'gyur ba thob
NK091(ke)001:8679: par gor ma chag snyam mo //
NK091(ke)001:8683: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8684: de nas skyes bu dam pa rnams kyis bcom ldan
NK091(ke)001:8685: 'das de kho na nyid la 'di skad cesa gsol
NK091(ke)001:8686: to // bcom ldan 'das gsang sngags dam pa de kho na nyid de ni /
NK091(ke)001:8687: bstan pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas gang yongs su brjod pa las 'das te /
NK091(ke)001:8688: gsung bar mi mnga' la brjod par mi nus par bstan cing /
NK091(ke)001:8689: brtags par rab tu dka' ba lagsa zhe na yang /
NK091(ke)001:8690: ston pa'i yon tan gyi sgo nas bcom ldan 'das
NK091(ke)001:8691: nyid ni gdul bya blo gros chen po mthar lam
NK091(ke)001:8692: pa rnams kyis bsten pa'i spyod yul du nges shing
NK091(ke)001:8693: / the tshom thams cad gcod par mdzad pa /
NK091(ke)001:8694: sangs rgyas dam pa rnams kyisa yang rje btsun dam pa nyid du lagas pas na /
NK091(ke)001:8695: bdag cag gi blo gros nges par chub pa gsang
NK091(ke)001:8696: sngags rtogs bya dam pa rang gi ngo bo phyogs
NK091(ke)001:8697: ris las grol pas ji bzhin pa'i phyogs /
NK091(ke)001:8698: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa dam pa mnyam pa
NK091(ke)001:8699: nyid gang yin pa de nyid legs par bstan du
NK091(ke)001:8700: gsol / zhes gsol ba btab pa las /
NK091(ke)001:8705: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8706: de nas bcom ldan 'das de kho na nyid des bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:8707: skyes bu dam pa rnams legs so //
NK091(ke)001:8709: zhes zhu ba byas pa la gnang ba stsal nas
NK091(ke)001:8710: don nye bar bstan pa ni 'di lta ste smrar
NK091(ke)001:8711: med cing yul du ma gyur pa'i don mchog ma
NK091(ke)001:8712: nor ba gsang sngags dam pa de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:8713: de ni 'di ltar tha snyad lnga bcu las grol
NK091(ke)001:8715: ye grub zin pa la yul dang yul can med
NK091(ke)001:8716: pa'i phyir nyan rang tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mthar lam
NK091(ke)001:8717: rnams kyis so sor rtog cing dpyod pa thams cad
NK091(ke)001:8720: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK091(ke)001:8721: ngang la rtog dang rtog bya med //
NK091(ke)001:8723: ngo bo ma grub la cir yang snang bas yod
NK091(ke)001:8724: med med la dbu mar tha snyad med pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:8725: mtha' dang dbus mi dmigs pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:8727: yod la ltos pas med pa'ang med de med pa'i med pa'ang med //
NK091(ke)001:8728: mtha' rnams med phyir dbus med la'ang gnas par mi byed do //
NK091(ke)001:8730: ye dngos po'i gnas lugs kyi chos ji bzhin pa
NK091(ke)001:8731: ni rtag chad las grol bas sgro skur med pa
NK091(ke)001:8732: / ril bde ba chen po mnyam pa'i klong la bzang ngan ma dmigs pas blang dor med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8733: ye nas byang chub snying po sangs rgyas dang sems
NK091(ke)001:8734: can gnyis su med pa la bskyed bya skyed byed
NK091(ke)001:8735: las grol bas rgyu 'bras las 'das pa /
NK091(ke)001:8736: sdug bsngal chos nyid kyi longs spyod /
NK091(ke)001:8737: nyon mongs pa bde ba chen po /
NK091(ke)001:8738: phyin ci log byang chub kyi lam mchog /sgrib pa
NK091(ke)001:8739: ye shes kyi ngo bo la sbyang bar bya rgyu
NK091(ke)001:8740: glo bur ba med pas ye nasa dag pa /
NK091(ke)001:8741: stong gsum ji snyed sangs rgyas kyi sa la gdod ma nas bkod pas ye nasa grub zin pa /
NK091(ke)001:8742: 'bras bu dang phrin las dbang bsgrub pa ril byas zin pas bya ba med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8743: de ltar zin pa'i phyir 'phral du thob par bya
NK091(ke)001:8744: ba med pas 'bad rtsol gyis brtsal ba med pa
NK091(ke)001:8745: / sems las logs na 'bras bu brtsal te don
NK091(ke)001:8746: du gnyer bya ma dmigs pas bsgrub tu med pa
NK091(ke)001:8747: / / don du gnyer ba med pa'i phyir 'phral du bya ba med pas brtsal du med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8748: rang rig pa las bsgrub bya zhig gzhan na med pas 'bras bu gzhan nas mi 'byung ba /
NK091(ke)001:8749: mi mthun pa dang bral ba'i phyir zla med cing mi 'jig pas gnyen po med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8750: ye nas grub zin pa'i phyir rang las gzhan pa'i bsgrub pa med pas byed pa po meda pa /
NK091(ke)001:8751: bya bas btsal du mi rnyed cing rgyu rkyen med pas ma byas pa /
NK091(ke)001:8752: tshig gis mi phebs shing ngo bo 'di 'drar med pas ma btags pa /
NK091(ke)001:8753: dngos gzhi ma nges pa dang yul sems gnyis med
NK091(ke)001:8754: la chos dang gang zag ma grub pas bdag med
NK091(ke)001:8755: pa / ye legs pa chen por bzhugs pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:8756: nang dang bral zhing ji bzhin pas ma bcos pa
NK091(ke)001:8757: pa / / ye nyid dag pa chen por bzhugs pa'i phyir sel med pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:8758: glo bur ba ma yin pas log rtog gis ma bslad pa /
NK091(ke)001:8759: ngo bo ma nor ba'i phyir gzhan du ma dmigs pas de yina pa /
NK091(ke)001:8760: 'gyur ba med cing bslu ba'i phyir rdzun pa spangs bas yang dag par nges pa /
NK091(ke)001:8761: log 'khrul med cing ji lta bar ngo bo ma 'khrul bar byung bas ma nora ba /
NK091(ke)001:8762: ma bcos ma bslad pa'i rnal ma phyi mo nyid las ma g.yos pas ji bzhin pa /
NK091(ke)001:8763: sgrib byed med cing 'od gsal ba la cir yang
NK091(ke)001:8764: go mi 'gog pas sna tshogs su 'char te ma
NK091(ke)001:8765: 'aggas pa / rgyu rkyen las ma byas par ngo
NK091(ke)001:8766: bo med pa'i phyir 'phral du ma byung bas ma
NK091(ke)001:8767: 'aggas pa / skyes pa / nyin mtshan dang bral
NK091(ke)001:8768: zhing gnyen po med pa'i phyir ye nas gdal khyab
NK091(ke)001:8769: chen po la rkyen gyis mi shigs pas mi nub
NK091(ke)001:8770: 'aggas pa / skyes pa / pa / ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:8771: dus gsum du 'pho 'gyur med par snying po nyid
NK091(ke)001:8772: du nges pas mi brlag pa /
NK091(ke)001:8773: mtha' gang du'ang ma byung zhing ngo bos med pas mi snang ba /
NK091(ke)001:8774: phyogs gcig pa gang du'ang mi snang la dngos po ma spangs par bral bas ma byung ba /
NK091(ke)001:8775: kun la khyab zin cing yul med pa dang rgyud
NK091(ke)001:8776: gcig pa ma yin pas yul la mi 'gro ba
NK091(ke)001:8777: / gdod nas sangs rgyas dang sems can gang bas
NK091(ke)001:8778: kyang snga la glo bur ba ma yin par dus
NK091(ke)001:8779: gsum du rgyun ma chad pas ye nas gnas pa
NK091(ke)001:8780: / / thams cad yin cing ril des bsnums pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:8781: de las gzhan du 'da' ba med pas bgos pa med par chos kun la khyab pa /
NK091(ke)001:8782: dbyibs dang kha dog ril ma spangs la rnam pa'i cha med pas btags pa'i ming med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8783: mtshan ma thams cad pa'i mtshan med gang la rnam
NK091(ke)001:8784: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir gang du'ang gzugs
NK091(ke)001:8785: snang med pas gzugs med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8786: ji snyed pa ma spangs bral ba la grangs las grol bas 'du shes kyi mtshan ma med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8787: dmigs bya dmigs byed med pas bla dwags su gdags pa'i tha snyad med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8788: yul gyi rnam pa'i phyogs ris las grol bas bltar med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8789: ngo bo nyid gang du'ang mi gnas pas gzung du med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8790: de dang 'dra ba med pas dape'am tshig gis mtshon du meda pa /
NK091(ke)001:8791: nye bar sbyor ba po ma dmigs pas 'dra bar bskrun pa'i dpe med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8792: mu mtha' yas pas 'adi'o zhes tshad gzung du med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8793: bshad pa ltar blos reg dka' bas brtag tu med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8794: spyod yul du ma grub pas rtog ge las 'das pa /
NK091(ke)001:8795: blos gting mtha' mi rnyed pas dpag tu med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8796: yid la bya ba med pas bsam du med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8797: phyogs su 'dzin pa'i bsam pas mi chub par kun tu shar bas bsam gyisa mi khyab pa /
NK091(ke)001:8798: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa ril gyi gzhir gyur pas kun gyi 'byung gnas /
NK091(ke)001:8799: dus thog mthar rgyun ma g.yos ma nyams pas thams
NK091(ke)001:8800: cad nas thams cad du btang snyomsa chen po ste
NK091(ke)001:8802: sems nyid ma bcos bde ba che //
NK091(ke)001:8803: mtshon par mi nus 'bral mi nus //
NK091(ke)001:8804: phyogs ris mi mnga' btang snyoms che //
NK091(ke)001:8805: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa nyid rig pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:8807: dngos por med cing ngo bo gang du'ang ma grub
NK091(ke)001:8808: pas stong pa nyid gsal ba nyid rgyu rkyen dang
NK091(ke)001:8809: byed pa po med par ma bslad ma bcos par
NK091(ke)001:8810: ye che btsan gcig pur byung bas rig pa rang
NK091(ke)001:8811: byung ba de kho na nyid kyi don nges par
NK091(ke)001:8812: gzung ba'o // de skad ces bka' stsal pas /
NK091(ke)001:8814: blang dor gyi the tshom pa'i yon tan /
NK091(ke)001:8815: yang dag pa'i nges pa rnyed pa'i yon tan /
NK091(ke)001:8816: tha ma'i dbugs 'byin pa'i yon tan /
NK091(ke)001:8817: byin rlabs gzhan la snang ba'i yon tan no //
NK091(ke)001:8822: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8823: de nas skyes bu dam pa de rnams ston pas
NK091(ke)001:8824: gsang ba'i mtshan nyid brjod pas 'khor ba dang mya
NK091(ke)001:8825: ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad blang dor med
NK091(ke)001:8826: par ji bzhin pa nyid rtogs shing thugs su chud
NK091(ke)001:8827: de / ngo bos gnyis su med pa'i gsang ba zab mo la shin tu ngo mtshar skyes nas /
NK091(ke)001:8828: sngar gyi rgyal ba'i bka' stsal dang ma mthun pas the tshom du gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:8831: bdag cag gis dam pa rnams las sngon du thos pa ltar na /
NK091(ke)001:8832: sngon gyi rgyal ba dam pa rnams ni /
NK091(ke)001:8835: de ni blo gros yongs su chub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:8837: skyes bu chen po rdo rje sems dpa' 'di ni
NK091(ke)001:8838: nyon mongs pa dang byang chub la gnyis su med
NK091(ke)001:8839: pas blang dor med do zhes gsungs pa ngo mtshar
NK091(ke)001:8840: to // snyam du cang mi smra bar gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:8841: de nas ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' de kho
NK091(ke)001:8842: na nyid des skyes bu dam pa de rnams kyi
NK091(ke)001:8843: yongs su rtoga pa bsam pa'i the tshom bsal ba'i
NK091(ke)001:8845: kye skyes bu dam pa rnams gang the tshom yongs
NK091(ke)001:8846: su za ba na dngos po lo rgyus kyi gtan
NK091(ke)001:8847: tshigs nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin gang yin gang las
NK091(ke)001:8848: byung / byang chub kyi rang bzhin gang yin gang las byung /
NK091(ke)001:8849: nges par rtogsa par gyis shig dang /
NK091(ke)001:8850: gang chos nyid yongs su mthong ba nyid na the tshom chad par 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:8856: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8857: de nas skyes bu dam pa de rnams kyis /
NK091(ke)001:8858: kun nas nyon mongs pa 'khor ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:8859: mya ngan las 'das pa byang chub gnyis kyi rang
NK091(ke)001:8860: bzhin gang yin gang las byung ba nges par brtags
NK091(ke)001:8861: pa na / mtha' gsum gang du'ang ma grub pas rang bzhin stong par mthong /
NK091(ke)001:8862: nyon mongs dang byang chub gnyis ka rtsa ba rang rig nyid yin pas semsa las byung bar mthong /
NK091(ke)001:8863: sems nyid rgyu las ma byung /
NK091(ke)001:8865: ngo bo ye nas skye ba med pa /
NK091(ke)001:8866: sgro skur med pas ye ji bzhin pa dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK091(ke)001:8867: rang bzhin 'gags pa med pas lhun gyis grub pa 'od gsal rig pa'i dkyil 'khor /
NK091(ke)001:8868: skye 'gag gnyis su med pas rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK091(ke)001:8869: dam pa gsum dbyer med pa'i chos nyid de kho na nyid du nges par chud de /
NK091(ke)001:8870: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dam pa'i ngo bor ma rtogs par rtogs /
NK091(ke)001:8872: ma myong bar nyams su myong ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:8873: sems rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad dang sems lasa
NK091(ke)001:8874: byung ba tshor 'du 'du byed rnams dang snang ba
NK091(ke)001:8875: thams cad mtha' dbus med pa nam mkha' lta bur
NK091(ke)001:8876: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs te rang rig rang
NK091(ke)001:8877: gsal chen po las mi g.yo bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:8878: spyod yul med pa'i dgongs pa la mnyam par bzhag
NK091(ke)001:8879: pa dang ma bzhag pa'i sgom pa dang mi bsgom
NK091(ke)001:8880: pa'i ting nge 'dzin las 'das te bzhengs bzhugs mi
NK091(ke)001:8881: mnga' bar mthar lam tha ma'i dbugs chen po phyin
NK091(ke)001:8882: nas bcu pa rdzogs pa spyir chib kyi sa mthar
NK091(ke)001:8883: phyin te lta ba'i sgrib pa dag pas gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:8884: ji bzhin pa nyid du son te yang dag pa'i
NK091(ke)001:8885: nges pa rtsol ba dang bral ba'i gdeng chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:8886: g.yo ba yongs su rnyed do //
NK091(ke)001:8887: rnyed pa thob par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:8888: thob pa kun tu brtan par rab tu rnyed nas /
NK091(ke)001:8889: de nyid dus byed pa chen po nyams bral med pa'i klong du gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:8890: yang skyes bu dam pa de rnams sngon du sbyangs
NK091(ke)001:8891: pa dang 'dir ngal sos pas dga' ches te thabs
NK091(ke)001:8892: la ngam zhing gzhan don du dgongs nas rma ga
NK091(ke)001:8893: chad par rab tu ngus so //
NK091(ke)001:8898: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8899: yang rdo rje sems dpa' de kho na nyid des mkhyen bzhin du /
NK091(ke)001:8900: skyes bu dam pa de rnams la bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:8901: kye skyes bu dam pa khyed cag ci'i phyir ngu /
NK091(ke)001:8903: bshes gnyen dam pa 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:8904: tshe 'di la 'grub cing rtogs pa tsam gyis chog
NK091(ke)001:8905: pas btsal mi dgos pa'i lam gyi nang na nye
NK091(ke)001:8907: nyon mongs pa ma spangs par sangs rgya bas thabs
NK091(ke)001:8908: kyi nang na thabs dam pa rtsol ba med pa
NK091(ke)001:8909: nyid kyis thob par byed pa 'di nyid sngon du
NK091(ke)001:8910: rgyu'i theg pa sogs la gnas pa'i tshe ma thos
NK091(ke)001:8911: pa de las 'phro dang skal ba chung snyam nas
NK091(ke)001:8912: ngu ba lags / e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad du
NK091(ke)001:8913: byung ba nges pa don gyi chos gsang ba zab
NK091(ke)001:8914: mo mthar thug gi bde ba la gnas pa'i yun
NK091(ke)001:8915: gyi don srid chen po'i 'di lta bu /
NK091(ke)001:8916: sems nyid las thabs dang ngo bo logs su btsal
NK091(ke)001:8917: mi dgos pas don rtogs pa dang grol ba dus
NK091(ke)001:8918: mnyam pas raga gzhan la ma las par rang la
NK091(ke)001:8919: rdzogs pa'i rgyu 'bras gnyis med 'di nyid ma rtogs
NK091(ke)001:8920: pas bskal pa de snyed du lam la zhugs nas
NK091(ke)001:8921: rgyal ba de snyed la the tshom gcod cing gzhan
NK091(ke)001:8922: la re rtsol gyis tshol ba ni e ma'o nor
NK091(ke)001:8923: zhing 'khrul snyam nas ngu ba lags /
NK091(ke)001:8924: de ltar rgyu'i theg pa la sogs pas rtsol sgrub
NK091(ke)001:8925: dang dka' thub sna tshogs pas bya ba'i thabs kyi
NK091(ke)001:8926: las la sgo gsum sha thang chad par 'bad kyang
NK091(ke)001:8927: mtshan ma'i tshig gi rjesa su bsam pa 'phros te
NK091(ke)001:8928: rnam par g.yeng ba la spyod de ngal zhing chad
NK091(ke)001:8929: par byas pas don ji bzhin pa mthong ba med
NK091(ke)001:8930: par tshig mtha' yas pa'i rjes su 'brangs pas bya
NK091(ke)001:8931: ba ma zin nas rnam grangs so sor bzung ba
NK091(ke)001:8932: chos nyid thig le nyag gcig tu bsdu zhing ji
NK091(ke)001:8933: bzhin par chub pas rtogs par ma 'dus te bdag
NK091(ke)001:8934: gzhan gyi don kun ma rdzogs pas dona re chung
NK091(ke)001:8935: snyam nas ngu ste sngon chad bsgyangs pas so //
NK091(ke)001:8936: da lta ston pa bshes gnyen dam pa gsang bdag
NK091(ke)001:8937: rdo rje sems dpa' khyed las ji bzhin pa 'di
NK091(ke)001:8938: nyid thos pa lasa gsang ba'i gdeng dam pa thob
NK091(ke)001:8939: ste nges pa rnyed nas bya ba'i las dang bral
NK091(ke)001:8940: te nga la sos pas dbugs chen po phyina pa
NK091(ke)001:8941: na yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis
NK091(ke)001:8942: mchog blang dor med pa dang mnyam pas mthar phyin
NK091(ke)001:8943: pa'i lam dang ma bcos bla ma'i sa chen ma
NK091(ke)001:8944: bgrod par non te bcings pa thams cad dbyings su
NK091(ke)001:8945: grol bas ma brtsal bar de kho na nyid chen
NK091(ke)001:8946: por lhun gyis grub pas ches dga' ba rnyed de
NK091(ke)001:8947: ngu ba lags / de'i phyir mchi ma zag pa
NK091(ke)001:8948: ni snga ma'i bya ba la kho thag chod pa
NK091(ke)001:8949: ngu ba lags / dang / rang ngo ma shes
NK091(ke)001:8950: pas rgyu gsum dang shes pas rgyu gcig ste bzhi
NK091(ke)001:8951: ngu ba lags / dang / la ngam pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:8952: zhes gsol te rgyal ba'i dgongs pa lhun gyis grub
NK091(ke)001:8953: ngu ba lags / dang / la ngam pa'o // bo // bzhi pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:8957: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:8958: de dag ma nor bar mngon par rtogs pas sangs rgyas pa'i byin rlabs dang ltas ni /
NK091(ke)001:8959: de ltar ngo mtshar gyi rtogs pa chen po thob
NK091(ke)001:8960: pa med par thob pas dgyes shing dga' ba chen
NK091(ke)001:8961: po kun nas rgyas pa'i byin rlabs las ye shes
NK091(ke)001:8962: kyi 'od zer nyi ma 'bum phrag lta bu gdul
NK091(ke)001:8964: 'di ni ston pa nyid kyi sku'i 'od zer las
NK091(ke)001:8965: bde gshegs 'khor bcas spro ba dang yang sbyar la
NK091(ke)001:8966: rang bzhin gyi 'od dang yang sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:8967: de ltar byung bas dngos po gang dag byang chub
NK091(ke)001:8968: sems dpa' dang rig pa 'dzin pa sa pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:8969: ni shes rab kyi rtsal rnyed pas rig pa'i rtsal
NK091(ke)001:8970: sbyangs / lta ba'i gdeng 'phang bstod pas don gyi che ba phyung /
NK091(ke)001:8971: sa pa'i rig pa ril gong du 'phar ba'i byin rlabs mthong ste sa rnams kun tu g.yos pas /
NK091(ke)001:8972: sngar gyi dam pa dag ji lta bar yongs su
NK091(ke)001:8973: bya ba gcig ma rnyed par gnyis la gnas pas
NK091(ke)001:8974: rtsol ba la spyod pa'i rnal 'byor ba dam pa
NK091(ke)001:8975: ji snyed pa dag gis ngo mtshar bar gyur te
NK091(ke)001:8976: / rang rang gi ston pa rnams la gsol pa /
NK091(ke)001:8977: 'di lta bu'i ltas ya mtshan can 'di ci lta bu zhig lagsa /
NK091(ke)001:8979: rang rang so so'i ston pa dpag tu med pas
NK091(ke)001:8980: so so'i 'khor dpag tu med pa la bka' stsal
NK091(ke)001:8981: pa / rigs kyi bu dag ltas chen po 'di ni /
NK091(ke)001:8982: zhing 'dis thams cad la khyab kyang rang rang gi
NK091(ke)001:8983: rigs kyi las kyis bskal pas ma mthong yang don
NK091(ke)001:8984: la gdal khyab chen po zhes bya ba'i zhing khamas
NK091(ke)001:8985: na / sangs rgyas kun gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen
NK091(ke)001:8986: rdo rje sems dpa' de kho na nyid ces bya
NK091(ke)001:8987: na / ba / theg pa chen poo gasnga sngags
NK091(ke)001:8988: kyi de kho na nyid nges pa zhes bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:8989: na / ba / chos ston to // sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:8990: de ni the tshom thams cad gcod cing kun tu
NK091(ke)001:8991: 'od la bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang sa bcu'i byang
NK091(ke)001:8992: chub sems dpa' thams cad nges para sangs rgyas par
NK091(ke)001:8993: lung bstan pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen dam par gyur
NK091(ke)001:8994: na / ba / chos ston to // pas /
NK091(ke)001:8995: skyes bu dam pa lnga gang gsang sngags kyi ngesa
NK091(ke)001:8996: pa ma rnyed pas yongs su mngon par rdzogs par
NK091(ke)001:8998: de dag nges pa'i the tshom bcad de /
NK091(ke)001:8999: tha ma'i lung ston pasa de dag gi ltas yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9005: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9007: de ltar na skyes bu dam pa de dag ni
NK091(ke)001:9008: de kho na nyid kyi nyams rnyed ma thag tu
NK091(ke)001:9009: rgyal tshab gnyis las 'dir tha ma'i dbugs phyin pa
NK091(ke)001:9010: de dag gsang sngags ston pa'i dbang phyug chen po
NK091(ke)001:9013: gsang ba'i chos la longs spyod pas mnga' thang yongs
NK091(ke)001:9014: su rdzogs pa'i chos kyi rgyal po'i ston mchog rigs
NK091(ke)001:9015: lnga'am sku lnga'i rgyal tshab chen po skyes bu dam
NK091(ke)001:9016: pa zhes bya bar nges par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:9018: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:9019: rtsol ba dang bral ba'i don rtogs pas skyes bu
NK091(ke)001:9020: dam pa lnga dbugs chen po yongs su phyin te
NK091(ke)001:9021: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i don dang /
NK091(ke)001:9022: rjes su 'jug pa'ang de bzhin du nges par bstan
NK091(ke)001:9023: pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa gsal bar bshad pa'o
NK091(ke)001:9024: ////lnga pa lam gyi cha rkyen dbang bskur ba la
NK091(ke)001:9031: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9032: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK091(ke)001:9033: de nas langa ka'i bdag po byang chub sems dpa' chen po des /
NK091(ke)001:9034: 'di skad ces dri ba yongs su dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:9036: skyes bu dam pa de dag dam pa rnams kyi
NK091(ke)001:9037: zhing du ji ltar gragsa pa lagsa zhes rgyu mtshan
NK091(ke)001:9038: dris pa'o // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:9046: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9047: gsang ba pa'i bdag posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:9049: skyes bu dama pa de dag ni dam pa sangs
NK091(ke)001:9050: rgyas rnams kyi zhing du gang chos kyi rgyal po'i
NK091(ke)001:9051: rgyal tshab tu gyur pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:9052: rgyal tshab skyes bu zhes bya bar yongs su grags par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:9053: de'ang gtan tshigs kyis yid ches par bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9054: rjes su 'jug pa po rim pas rdzogs par bya ba'i don bstan pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:9058: dper na gang d+r+wa ma chen poo kun gyi spyi
NK091(ke)001:9059: bor gyur pa 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dag
NK091(ke)001:9060: gi phrug gu chos lnga dang ldan pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:9061: rgyal po rgyal rigsa chen po'i rigs kyi gdung 'dzin pa'i rgyud du gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9062: thun mong gi mtshan dpe dang ldan la rgyal yar shis pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9063: rgyal po'i chos lugs shes pas mkhas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9064: phyi nang gi 'khor 'bangs dang ldan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9065: rin chen sna bdun la sogs pa rgyal po'i mnga' dbang thob pa'i skal ba dang ldan na /
NK091(ke)001:9066: gling bzhi'i mi la sogs pa mgo nag mang pos
NK091(ke)001:9067: spyi bos len cing bkur ba thob nas nges par
NK091(ke)001:9068: 'dzin pa ni rgyal bu dam par mtshon pa de
NK091(ke)001:9069: bzhin du / don gyi dbang du /
NK091(ke)001:9070: skyes bu dam pa lnga po de dag kyang /
NK091(ke)001:9071: rgyal ba kun gyi rigs sam gdung rgyud du byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9072: thun mong dang thun mong min pa'i yon tan mtshan
NK091(ke)001:9073: dang dpe byad kyi rtags brgya dang bcu gnyis ldan
NK091(ke)001:9074: pa dang / theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi
NK091(ke)001:9075: chos ji bzhin pa bzhin pa shes shing rtogs pa
NK091(ke)001:9077: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin par bsdu ba'i 'khor dang ldan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9078: tshe dang yo byad la sogs pa dbang bcu po thob par gyur pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:9079: chos lnga po de dag dang ldan pas na /
NK091(ke)001:9080: de'i phyir rgyal tshab skyes bu zhes bya bar zhing khams thams cad du rab tu grags so //
NK091(ke)001:9081: zhes dpe don gnyis kyi sgo nas bsdus te bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9090: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9091: de'ang 'grel pa lung bstan ma las /
NK091(ke)001:9092: ji ltar rgyal sras bcas pa la //
NK091(ke)001:9093: mdzes pa'i yon tan rdzogs pa yis //
NK091(ke)001:9094: dbang bskur khongs su yid ches nas //
NK091(ke)001:9095: dam pa brgyud pa'i man ngag gis //
NK091(ke)001:9096: rjes 'jug tu yang shes par bya //
NK091(ke)001:9098: sngon byung rgyal ba'i mdzad spyod kyi sgo nas gdul bya spro ba bskyed pa'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:9099: rjes 'jug gi gang zag nyams su len thabs kyi
NK091(ke)001:9100: sgo nas gdul bya chud mi za bar bskur thabs
NK091(ke)001:9101: kyi don rnam grangs kyis ston te /
NK091(ke)001:9102: lang ka'i bdag po dbang gi don gyi lus 'di
NK091(ke)001:9103: ltar yang yid gcig tu bsdus te ma yengs par
NK091(ke)001:9104: shes par gyis shig /gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:9106: rgyal tshab tu grags pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9107: rgyun ma chad pas chu bo bzhi dang /
NK091(ke)001:9111: rdzas la brten te bskur thabs dang /
NK091(ke)001:9112: gang du bskur ba'i gnas dang /
NK091(ke)001:9115: sdom du bsdus pa 'di yis yongs su rdzogs pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9116: zhes don bcu'i sgo nas bstan pa 'di nyid so
NK091(ke)001:9117: sor rgyas par bshad pas sngon byung gi dbang dang
NK091(ke)001:9118: tha mas thun mong du tshig zin gyi dngos su
NK091(ke)001:9119: bstan cing des rjes 'ajugagi dbang kyang shugs kyis 'phangs
NK091(ke)001:9121: ji ltar sngon du de bzhin gshegs pa de nyid
NK091(ke)001:9122: ji lta ba'i thabs med na gdul bya la phan
NK091(ke)001:9126: khungs rgyal bas dbang bskur ba /
NK091(ke)001:9128: rgyun ma chad pa chu bo /
NK091(ke)001:9132: rdzas la brten te bskur thabs /
NK091(ke)001:9140: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9142: de yang khungs nges par bstan pa 'di ltar te /
NK091(ke)001:9143: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po la sras du ma mnga' yang /
NK091(ke)001:9144: rigs kyi rgyud du gang nges par byung nas dbang thob par gyur na /
NK091(ke)001:9145: de la rgyal srid thams cad 'bangsa rnams kyis gang der bstabs shing phul bas /
NK091(ke)001:9146: rgyal po'i bka' lung gi tshig btsan zhing gling bzhi
NK091(ke)001:9147: sogs rang yul la dbang bsgyur ba'i bdag por gyur
NK091(ke)001:9148: te mgo nag kun gyis bkur gnas kyi spyi bor
NK091(ke)001:9149: gyur nas rgyal po chen por 'gyur ba'i dpe ji
NK091(ke)001:9151: rgyal tshab skyes bu rnams kyis chos lnga dang bya
NK091(ke)001:9152: ba gzhan thams cad yongs su rdzogs par gyur te
NK091(ke)001:9153: mthar lam du nges pa na /
NK091(ke)001:9154: gdul bar bya ba lha dang mir bcas pa'i 'jig
NK091(ke)001:9155: rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i 'khor rnams kyis
NK091(ke)001:9156: gus par 'dud pas ston pa chos kyi rgyal pora
NK091(ke)001:9157: mnga' thang bstabs te phul bar byas pas rgyal tshab
NK091(ke)001:9158: tu grags pa de nas mdzad pa mthar phyungs te
NK091(ke)001:9159: / byang chub mchog tu mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:9160: de ltar lo rgyus bsnyad pas yid ches par byas te lang ka'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:9161: gang la bskur na da ltar chos lnga dang ldan
NK091(ke)001:9162: pa'i skyes bu dam pa rgyal ba'i rigs rgyud du
NK091(ke)001:9163: nges pa lnga po de dag ni bskur ba'i dus
NK091(ke)001:9164: kyi rgyu'o // gang du bskur ba'i gnas ni /
NK091(ke)001:9165: rtsal chen rdzogs pas dbugs chen po yongs su phyin
NK091(ke)001:9166: pa'i gnas 'og min chen po ga na ba der
NK091(ke)001:9167: / gang gis bskur ba'i slob dpon ni dam pa
NK091(ke)001:9168: sangs rgyas rnams kyi zhing khams mtha' thug pa med
NK091(ke)001:9169: pa nas dbang gi dgongs pa mdzad pa'i gzugs sku'i
NK091(ke)001:9170: rgyal ba dpag tu med pa kun gyi bshes gnyen
NK091(ke)001:9171: dam pa dag /dpe ji ltar na nam mkha' la
NK091(ke)001:9172: dbyar gyi sprin dpung bzhin du yongsa su 'du bar
NK091(ke)001:9173: / 'dus nas / ji ltar bskur ba'i thabs ni /
NK091(ke)001:9174: gong du bshad pa'i mtshungs pa bzhi mnga' ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:9175: de dag kun kyang sku gsum dbyer med rang snang
NK091(ke)001:9176: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par gsungs pa mgrin
NK091(ke)001:9177: gcig tu bskur bar mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:9178: zhes rgyal bas ji ltar bskur ba'i khungs bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9186: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9187: spyir ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ci rigs thob
NK091(ke)001:9188: pa'i slob dpon gyis lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK091(ke)001:9189: 'khor du skal ldan gyi slob ma la dbang bskur
NK091(ke)001:9190: bas mos slob tsam gyi nus pa skye rung du
NK091(ke)001:9191: smin pa dang / lam lnga gong ma gong ma thob pa'i slob dpon gyis /
NK091(ke)001:9192: sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor du 'og ma 'og mar gnas pa'i slob bu la bskur bas /
NK091(ke)001:9193: rang lam gong mar smin pa sogs dkyil 'khor gsum
NK091(ke)001:9194: du slob dpon gsum gyis rgyal sras gsum la dbang
NK091(ke)001:9195: bskur ba ni phyi nang gi bka' du ma las
NK091(ke)001:9196: gsungs te / des na de dag las 'dir ni
NK091(ke)001:9197: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:9198: skus rim pa tha mas bya ba bzhi rdzogs par
NK091(ke)001:9199: 'byung ba la dbang bskur bas byang chub rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:9200: brnyes te zhing kun tu grags par 'gyur ba'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:9201: gsungs te / du ste / rjes su 'jug pa'i yang don gyis gsal lo //
NK091(ke)001:9202: de la rgyal tshab lnga'i mtshan gyi grags pa rang gi ngo bo mdor bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9203: rgyal tshab skyes bu dam pa chos kyi rgyal po
NK091(ke)001:9204: zhes bya ba'i ming du grags pa'i dbang gisa rgyal
NK091(ke)001:9205: tshab skyes bu lnga la dbang bskur ro //
NK091(ke)001:9207: rgyal tshab skyes bu chos lnga dang ldan par grags pa la bskur ba /
NK091(ke)001:9208: rgyal tshab skyes ba nyid du grags pa la bskur ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:9212: thugs mkhyen pa'i chos dang ldan pa /
NK091(ke)001:9214: dbang bcu thob par grags pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9219: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9220: de rnams so sor grags pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:9221: rgyal tshab rgyud kyi ston pa rgyal ba rigs lngar grags pa'i dbang ste /
NK091(ke)001:9222: 'das pa la snyegs pa de ltar ngo bo bstan pa 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:9223: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba ji snyed pa thams cad de
NK091(ke)001:9224: bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i skur ma 'dres par so
NK091(ke)001:9225: sor snang bar gyur pa'i ston pa rdo rje'i rigs
NK091(ke)001:9226: mchog la las rdo rje'i rigs 'tshob cing rgyud du
NK091(ke)001:9227: 'byung ba de'i lung bstan thob pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:9228: bkar ba'i sgras dam pa lnga las rdo rje sems
NK091(ke)001:9229: dpa' ste skal ba de bzhin du ldan pas thugs
NK091(ke)001:9230: rdo rje'i rigs kyi gtso bo gdung dang /
NK091(ke)001:9231: de'i rigs kyi 'khor rnams sde'i rgyud du nges par
NK091(ke)001:9232: gyur pa'i ming dang rigs kyi dbang gis dbang byin
NK091(ke)001:9233: cing bskur bas rigs de'i byang chub rdo rje'i de
NK091(ke)001:9234: bzhin gshegs par sangs rgyas te thob pa'i rtags su
NK091(ke)001:9235: zhing khams kun tu'ang de ltar yongs su grags pa
NK091(ke)001:9236: yin no // rigs gzhan bzhi'ang de dang rjes su mthun par /
NK091(ke)001:9238: rin po che'i rigs 'tshob cing rgyud du 'byung ba
NK091(ke)001:9239: de'i lung bstan thob pa ni rin chen rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:9240: ste skal pa de bzhin du ldan pas yon tan
NK091(ke)001:9241: rin po che'i rigs kyi gdung dang sde'i rgyud du
NK091(ke)001:9242: nges pa'i ming dang rigs kyi dbang gi dbang byin
NK091(ke)001:9243: pas byang chub rdo rjer sangs rgyas te de ltar
NK091(ke)001:9246: pad+ma'i rigs 'tshob cing rgyud du 'byung ba de'i lung
NK091(ke)001:9247: bstan thob pa ni rdo rje chos te skal pa
NK091(ke)001:9248: de bzhin du ldan pas gsung pad+mo'i rigs kyi gdung
NK091(ke)001:9249: dang sde'i rgyud du nges pa'i ming dang rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:9250: dabnga gis dbang byin pas byang chub rdo rjer sangs
NK091(ke)001:9251: rgyas te yongs su grags pa'ang yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9252: phrin las kyi rigs mchog la lasa las kyi rigs
NK091(ke)001:9253: 'tshob cing rgyud du 'byung ba de'i lung bstan thob
NK091(ke)001:9254: pa ni las kyi rdo rje ste skal pa de
NK091(ke)001:9255: bzhin du ldan pas phrin las las kyi rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:9256: gzhona nu'i gdung dang sde'i rgyud du nges pa'i ming
NK091(ke)001:9257: dang rigs kyi dabnga gis dbang byin pas byang chub
NK091(ke)001:9258: rdo rjer sangs rgyas te de ltar grags pa'ang yin
NK091(ke)001:9259: no // de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs mchog la lasa
NK091(ke)001:9260: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs 'tshob cing rgyud du 'byung
NK091(ke)001:9261: ba de'i lung bstan thob pa ni rdo rje dbyings
NK091(ke)001:9262: te skal ba de bzhin du ldan pas sku de
NK091(ke)001:9263: bzhin gshegs pa glang po'i gdung dang sde'i rgyud du
NK091(ke)001:9264: nges pa'i ming dang rigs kyi dabnga gis dbang byin
NK091(ke)001:9265: pas byang chub rdo rjer sangs rgyas te zhing kun
NK091(ke)001:9266: tu de ltar grags pa'ang yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9267: spyir rigs de dag la thabs gsum gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:9268: dang po rgyal tshab lnga po rang rang gi rigs dang mthun pa'i ston pas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9269: de nas phyogs bcu'i rgyal bas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9270: de nas phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rigs de dang der bstan nas dbang bskur ba dang gsum mo //
NK091(ke)001:9271: de bzhin du lam pa rjes 'jug gi ming gi dbang du'ang sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:9276: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9277: 'di dag dam pa lnga dang 'chad pa'i bzhi thun mong du yin la /
