NK091(ke)001:9278: gsung gis bskur ba'i rjes su sku yis bskur te
NK091(ke)001:9279: sku'i rgyan dang ldan par grags pa ste la lasa
NK091(ke)001:9280: zhes bkar ba ni rgyal ba ji snyed pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:9281: so sor dbang bskur ba ma 'dres pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9282: de'ang ston pa'i mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi gtsug
NK091(ke)001:9283: tor lta bu la sogs pa nas 'od zer bye
NK091(ke)001:9284: ba khrag khrig brgya stong drug cu drug cu byung
NK091(ke)001:9286: tshur 'dus pas rgyal tshab kyi gnas de dang der
NK091(ke)001:9287: thim pas byin gyis brlabs kyi dbang gisa dbang byin
NK091(ke)001:9288: te bskur pas mtshan gyi yon tan rnams yongs su
NK091(ke)001:9290: ston pa la lasa ni dpe byad bzang po brgyad
NK091(ke)001:9291: cu'i gnas rnams kyi 'od zer bkye nas slar 'dus
NK091(ke)001:9292: pa rgyal tshab kyi gnas de dang der thim pas
NK091(ke)001:9293: byin rlabs kyi dbang gisa dbang byin pas dpe byad
NK091(ke)001:9294: bzang po yongs su rdzogs pa dang ldan no //
NK091(ke)001:9295: la lasa ni dbu rgyan la sogs pa byang chub kyi yan lag bdun /
NK091(ke)001:9297: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i rtags dang
NK091(ke)001:9298: ldan pa'i rgyan gyi gnas las byung ba'i 'od zer
NK091(ke)001:9299: gyi byin gyis brlabs pas dbang gis dbang byin no
NK091(ke)001:9300: // la lasa ni ye shes drug gi rtags sngon
NK091(ke)001:9301: po rdo rje'i rigs dang ser por rat+na'i rigs sogs
NK091(ke)001:9302: kha dog drug gi gnas las byung ba'i 'od zer
NK091(ke)001:9303: gyi dbang gis rigs lnga'i sku mdog dang 'od sna
NK091(ke)001:9304: tshogs kyi dbang byin pas mthun pa dang mi mthun
NK091(ke)001:9305: pa gnyis ka'i yon tan yongs su rdzogs pa dang
NK091(ke)001:9310: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9311: gsung dang thugs kyis bskur pa thun mong du bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9312: mkhyen pa'i thugs dang ldan par grags pa'i dbang ste /
NK091(ke)001:9313: la las ni rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi chos ma
NK091(ke)001:9314: 'dres pa bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang gisa
NK091(ke)001:9316: la las ni mkhyen pa chags thogs med pas stobs bcu'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9317: la lasa ni mi 'jigsa pa bzhi'i dbang gis mchog byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9318: la lasa ni thun mong min pas so so yang
NK091(ke)001:9319: dag par rig pa bzhi'i dbang gis dbang byin te
NK091(ke)001:9320: de dag gi don brda 'jal zhing thob par byas
NK091(ke)001:9321: pa yin no // 'di dag thugs ka'i 'od kyis kyang bskur zhing thob pa yin la /
NK091(ke)001:9322: phyi ma gsum glang po che dang /
NK091(ke)001:9324: shang shang te'u'i khri yi rtags dang yang sbyar te gzhan gnyis kyang mtshon no //
NK091(ke)001:9329: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9330: spyod pa dang phrin las 'dren mar grags pa'i bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhis dbang bskur ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:9331: la lasa ni gdul bya dang chos lugs don mthun
NK091(ke)001:9332: par gyur pas 'khor rnams bsdu ba'i dbang gisa dbang
NK091(ke)001:9333: byin no // la lasa ni snyan par smra bas
NK091(ke)001:9334: phyogs med cing ris mi 'byed par bsdu ba'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:9336: la lasa ni phyii nang gi dngos po gang la'ang
NK091(ke)001:9337: ma chags par gtong ba'i sbyin pasa bsdu ba'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:9339: la lasa ni bdag nyid don dang mthun par spyod pas 'khor bsdu ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9340: la lasa ni lus ngag gi mdzad spyod gdul bya'i
NK091(ke)001:9341: bsam pa dang cha mthun pas dad cing 'khor dang
NK091(ke)001:9342: longs spyod skyon med par dbang du sdud pa'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:9344: la lasa ni snyan par smra ba dang gdams ngag
NK091(ke)001:9345: nan tan gyi lung lta bu thabs kyis 'dren par
NK091(ke)001:9346: mdzad pas bsdu ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9347: la lasa ni phrin las bzhi'i dbang gis mnga' dbang
NK091(ke)001:9348: du rang dbang med par bsdu bar byed pa'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:9350: la lasa ni blang dor ris mi 'byed par mnyam
NK091(ke)001:9351: pa'i ngang la bzang ngan du mi 'dzin pas bsdu
NK091(ke)001:9352: ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9353: de yang don spyod pa dang mthun pa'i rim pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9354: la lasa ni 'bras bu dang yon tan gyi bdag
NK091(ke)001:9355: nyid chen pos che ba kun dang ldan kyang gzhan
NK091(ke)001:9356: gyi thugs rje dang rtogs pa la rag las par
NK091(ke)001:9357: gyur pas bsdu ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9358: la lasa ni mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i don bstan te rgyus bsdu ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9359: la lasa ni gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:9360: bstan te 'bras bus bsdu ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin
NK091(ke)001:9361: no // de gnyis ni sbyin dang snyan par smra ba dang don spyod pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9362: 'o na bsdu ba bzhi la bcu gcig tu brjod pa ci zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:9363: spyir rgyal ba tha dad re res bskur ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:9364: dang rtsa ba bzhi'ang bsdu ba'i yon tan gyi sgo
NK091(ke)001:9365: nas spyod pa dang phrin las tha dad kyis 'khor
NK091(ke)001:9366: dang gdul bya sdud pa'i bye brag tha dad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9367: phyir te phyogs gcig tu 'grul bar bstan daka'o //
NK091(ke)001:9372: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9373: rgyal ba de snyed pas dbang bcu'i dbang bskur bas dbang bcu thob par grags pa'i dbang ste /
NK091(ke)001:9374: la lasa ni bdag nyid gnas gang du ci tsam
NK091(ke)001:9375: gnas par 'dod pa'i bar du bzhugs kyang skyon gyis
NK091(ke)001:9376: mi gos par gnas pas tshe la dbang ba'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:9378: la lasa ni shes bya rnam par shes shing 'gro
NK091(ke)001:9379: ba kun gyi sems rgyud rig pas blo gros dang
NK091(ke)001:9380: nyon mongs che chung mkhyen pa sems la dbang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:9382: la lasa ni rang nyid gang du skye ba la
NK091(ke)001:9383: dga' ba der skye ba bzhir bstan te gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:9385: skye bas ma gos pas skye ba la rang dbang du gyur pa'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9386: la lasa ni 'dod yon lnga la ji ltar 'dod
NK091(ke)001:9387: par spyod pa yongs su bkod de bdag gzhan gyi
NK091(ke)001:9388: don rdzogs par sbyor zhing 'byin nus pas rgyu rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:9389: pa yo byad la dbang ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin
NK091(ke)001:9390: no // la lasa ni theg pa'i sgo kun la
NK091(ke)001:9391: rab tu 'jug pa gsung rab rgya mtsho dang chos
NK091(ke)001:9392: kyi phung po dpag tu med pa la mnga' brnyes
NK091(ke)001:9393: pas chos la dbang ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin no
NK091(ke)001:9394: no // // la lasa ni sku gsung thugs kyi
NK091(ke)001:9395: sprul pas skad cig gis bya ba byed nus pas
NK091(ke)001:9396: kun tu myur ba rdzu 'phrul la dbang ba'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:9398: la lasa ni gdul bya'i bsam pa ji ltar gnas
NK091(ke)001:9399: pa'i mos pa dang mthun par sku gsung thugs kyi
NK091(ke)001:9400: snang ba sna tshogs ston pa la mnga' bsgyur bas
NK091(ke)001:9401: mos pa la dbang ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin no
NK091(ke)001:9402: // la lasa ni bdag gzhan gyi don ji lta
NK091(ke)001:9403: ba bzhin du dga' mgur spyod pa'i phrin las bzhi
NK091(ke)001:9404: la mnga' brnyes pas las la dbang ba'i dbang gisa
NK091(ke)001:9405: // dbang byin no // khye'u lnga ni re re la'ang bzhi ka dang ldan par dbang bskur ro //
NK091(ke)001:9406: la lasa ni sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:9407: skye 'gag med pa ji bzhin par mthong nas ji
NK091(ke)001:9408: snyed pa'i chos ma 'dres par mkhyen pas ye shes
NK091(ke)001:9409: la dbang ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9410: la lasa ni thugs rje'i dbang gis cir yang snang
NK091(ke)001:9411: ba 'dod pa tha dad grub pas smon lam la
NK091(ke)001:9412: dbang ba'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9413: de'ang dgar ba'i sgras de rnams kyi yon tan mnga'
NK091(ke)001:9414: ba'i rgyal ba re res bskur te dbyar gyi sprin
NK091(ke)001:9415: phung ji snyed la ngos gzung bar daka'o //
NK091(ke)001:9416: 'di dag skyes bu lnga la ni thun mong bar shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:9417: dam pa tog dkar po dang /
NK091(ke)001:9420: phyag na rdo rje bzhi la ni phal che ba'i
NK091(ke)001:9421: dbang nas so sor mang nyung bstan par yangs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9422: rim pas phye ba'i skal bas bstan du'ang rung na
NK091(ke)001:9423: de dag kyang thun mong du smra'o //
NK091(ke)001:9428: zhes par bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9429: de'ang rgyal tshab nyid du grags pa bzhi'i dbang 'di
NK091(ke)001:9430: nyid skyes bu lnga'i dbang du thun mong du shes
NK091(ke)001:9431: par bya la / bka' spyi gzhung gi skyes bu
NK091(ke)001:9432: bzhi po dag gi dbang du tshig don gyi grangs
NK091(ke)001:9433: kyang rjes su mthun par 'byung bas so sor shes
NK091(ke)001:9434: par bya la / par bya ste / la lasa
NK091(ke)001:9435: ni dam pa lnga la sprul pa'i rgyal tshab kyi
NK091(ke)001:9436: skyes bu'i dbang gisa dbang byin pas zhing kun tu
NK091(ke)001:9437: sprul sku'i rgyal tshab tu grags pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9438: tshul bstan gyi dbang du dang por byang chub sems
NK091(ke)001:9439: dpa' dam pa tog dkar po zhes bya ba de
NK091(ke)001:9440: ni chos kyi rgyal sar 'byung ba'i dus la bab
NK091(ke)001:9441: pa'i phyir dga' ldan gyi gnas su phyogs bcu'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:9442: bas chos kyi rgyal po lta bur bstan nas rin
NK091(ke)001:9443: po che 'od stong 'bar ba'i rdzas la brten te
NK091(ke)001:9444: chos kyi rgyal po'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:9445: ston pa'i rigs 'tshob pas rgyud kyi chu bo'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:9446: rgyal tshab skyes bu'i dbang byin te thob pas chos
NK091(ke)001:9447: kyi rgyal tshab nyid du gyur pa'i rtags mngon du
NK091(ke)001:9449: de ni rgyal tshab kyi dbang ste don bdun ni 'chad pa rnams la'ang sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:9450: la lasa ni mngon par byang chub pa lngas byin
NK091(ke)001:9451: gyi rlabs kyis longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lngar sangs
NK091(ke)001:9452: rgyas pa'i dbang gisa dbang byin pas longs sku'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:9453: tshab tu grags pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9454: tshul bstan gyi dbang du mi yul du rgyal bu
NK091(ke)001:9455: don grub tu mtshan grags pa de longs spyod rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:9456: pa'i sku rnam par snang mdzad gnyis par 'tshang rgya
NK091(ke)001:9457: ba'i dus la bab pa'i phyir 'og min khang bu
NK091(ke)001:9459: rgyal ba ril rigs lnga'i skur snang bas nee rany+dza
NK091(ke)001:9460: nar dka' thub byed pa la bskul te ye shes
NK091(ke)001:9461: kyi lus 'og min du gshegs pa las nyi zla
NK091(ke)001:9462: rdo rje 'bar ba'i rdzas la brten nas mngon par
NK091(ke)001:9463: byang chub pa lngas bstabs te /
NK091(ke)001:9464: longs spyod rdzogs par byin gyis brlabs nas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:9465: longs spyod rdzogs par 'byung ba'i chu bo dang /
NK091(ke)001:9466: thabs lngas snang mdzad du byin gyis brlabs pas rtags ni longs spyod rdzogs pa nyid du gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:9467: des sgron ma'i rgyal tshab sh+aakya thub pa nyid sprul nus pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9468: la lasa ni rigs lnga'i rgyal bar lung bstan pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9469: dbang gisa dbang byin pas zhing rnams kyi sgron ma'i
NK091(ke)001:9470: rgyal tshab tu grags pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9472: bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya bar mtshan
NK091(ke)001:9473: grags pa de chos kyi sgron mar lung mngon du
NK091(ke)001:9474: thob pa'i phyir snying po byang chub 'og min chen
NK091(ke)001:9475: por phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba mang pos 'khor lo la
NK091(ke)001:9476: sogs pa'i rigs kyi phyag rgya mang po'i rdzas la
NK091(ke)001:9477: brten nas chos kyi sgron ma'i bya ba byed pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9478: dbang dang / zhing khams kun tu thub pa'i dbang por grags pa'i chu bo dang /
NK091(ke)001:9479: chos kyi sgron mar lung ston pa'i dbang byin pas
NK091(ke)001:9480: rtags chos kyi mnga' dbang nyid du gyur nas 'khor
NK091(ke)001:9481: lo bskor ro // la lasa ni gsang ba dam
NK091(ke)001:9482: pa 'chad cing 'dzin pa'i rtsal chen nus pa'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:9483: gisa dbang byin pas gsang ba dam pa'i bdag por
NK091(ke)001:9484: zhing rnams su grags pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9486: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje de gsang sngags rdo
NK091(ke)001:9487: rje theg pa'i mdzod zab mo mtha' dag 'dzin pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9488: dus la bab pa'i phyir dbang bsgyur gyi khang bzang
NK091(ke)001:9489: dang / gyad yul du longs spyod rdzogs pa dang
NK091(ke)001:9490: sprul pa'i skus rdo rje pha lam lta bu'i rdzas
NK091(ke)001:9491: la brten nas gsang ba'i mdzod kyi bdag po byed
NK091(ke)001:9492: dang / pa dang / don zab mo mthar rdzogs pa'i chu bo dang /
NK091(ke)001:9493: mthu stobs khyad par can du gyur pas gsang ba
NK091(ke)001:9494: 'dzin cing ston pas log sde tshar gcod pa'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:9495: byin pas gsang bdag nyid du mngon du gyur pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9497: 'o na dam pa tog dkar sprul pa'i rgyal tshab
NK091(ke)001:9498: tu dbang bskur ba dang sh+aaka thub sgron ma'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:9499: tshab tu dbang bskur ba la khyad par ci yod
NK091(ke)001:9500: zhe na / skye ba gcig gis thogs pa'i byang
NK091(ke)001:9501: chub sems dpa'i tshul gyis skye ba sprul pa'i skur
NK091(ke)001:9502: dbang bskur ba dang byang chub chen po sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:9503: nyid du dbang bskur ba'i khyad par ro //
NK091(ke)001:9504: rjes 'jug gi dbang gi chu bo bzhi ni /
NK091(ke)001:9506: byang chub sems kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:9508: bde ba chen por bsnyad do //
NK091(ke)001:9509: 'di dag a nu'i rang lam du bla ma dam
NK091(ke)001:9510: pas slob ma skyes bu bzhi byin gyis brlabs pa
NK091(ke)001:9516: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9517: de'ang rgyal tshab skyes bu lnga la thun mong du bskur ba yin la /
NK091(ke)001:9518: tshul bstan gyi dbang du dam pa bzhi la phal
NK091(ke)001:9519: cher skal ba che chung gis bskur bas thun mong
NK091(ke)001:9521: de rnams bshad pas snga ma rnams kyang mthar lam
NK091(ke)001:9522: gsum rdzogs pa'i tshul gyis chos kyi rgyal po dam
NK091(ke)001:9523: par zhing kun tu yongs su grags par rtogs nus
NK091(ke)001:9524: par bya'o // la lasa ni dam pa tog dkar
NK091(ke)001:9525: po nyid sprul pa'i rgyal ba mthar thug pa med
NK091(ke)001:9526: par rgyun du 'byung bas rnam 'dren stong gi rgyud
NK091(ke)001:9527: du byung ba dpe chu bo dang 'dra bar rgyud
NK091(ke)001:9528: kyi chu bo'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9529: la lasa ni don kun grub pa nyid chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:9530: rgyal po longs spyod rdzogs pa chen po zhing dag
NK091(ke)001:9531: pa dang 'khor smin pa rgya mtsho bar ma chad
NK091(ke)001:9532: par 'byung ba'i chu bo'i dbang gisa dbang byin no
NK091(ke)001:9533: // la lasa ni sh+aakya thub pa nyid stong gsum
NK091(ke)001:9534: gyi stong chen po re rer sprul pa re res
NK091(ke)001:9535: zhing khams kyi sgron mar rgyun du grags pas zhing
NK091(ke)001:9536: khams tha dad du sgron mar gyur pa'am grags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9537: chu bo'i dbang gisa dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9538: la lasa ni phyag na rdo rje nyid rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:9539: kun gyi gsang ba gsum gyi rtsal rdzogs pas gsang
NK091(ke)001:9540: ba'i mdzod kyi bdag por byin gyis brlabs te gsang
NK091(ke)001:9541: ba mchog gi don kun rdzogs pa'ii chu boo'i dabnga
NK091(ke)001:9545: srid pa gsum gyis phyag byas pa'i //
NK091(ke)001:9546: bla ma'i sa la gnas pa yi //
NK091(ke)001:9547: dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug yin //
NK091(ke)001:9548: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK091(ke)001:9549: sgrub pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK091(ke)001:9550: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK091(ke)001:9551: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK091(ke)001:9553: bshad rgyud rngam glog las kyang /
NK091(ke)001:9554: dang po phyi yi dbang bcu bskur //
NK091(ke)001:9555: de nas nang dbang bcu dang gcig /de nas sgrub dbang bcu dang gsum //
NK091(ke)001:9556: tha mar gsang ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK091(ke)001:9557: bcu phrag gsum dang drug dag gis //
NK091(ke)001:9558: dbang mchog dam pa bskur ba yin //
NK091(ke)001:9559: zhes gsungs pa ltar dpal ldan 'dus pa mdo'i chu
NK091(ke)001:9560: bo chen po bzhi'i dbang ste spyir dbang la rgyu
NK091(ke)001:9561: lam 'bras bu'i dbang gsum las 'dir 'bras dus kyi
NK091(ke)001:9562: dbang gi rigs su 'du ba yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9567: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9568: de'ang dbang gang la bskur zhing thob par bya ba'i yul rnams te /
NK091(ke)001:9570: skyes bu dam pa de dag kyang /
NK091(ke)001:9571: la la zhes dgar ba'i sgras dam pa tog dkar
NK091(ke)001:9572: po la na sprul pa'i rgyal tshab dga' ldan lha
NK091(ke)001:9573: yi chos kyi rgyal pora dabnga byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9574: la la zhes don grub la ni rgyal ba kun
NK091(ke)001:9575: gyi mngon par byang chub pa lngas byin gyis brlabs
NK091(ke)001:9576: kyi longs sku'i dbang phyug tu dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9577: la la zhes sh+aaka thub la ni zhing tha dad
NK091(ke)001:9578: du 'dzam gling kun gyi sgron ma byed pa'i bya
NK091(ke)001:9580: la la zhes phyag na rdo rje la ni gsang
NK091(ke)001:9581: ba kun gyi mdzod gsum la dbang rdzogs shing des
NK091(ke)001:9582: gzhan la phan 'dogs pas gsang ba dam pa 'dzina
NK091(ke)001:9588: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9589: gang gis bskur ba'i dbang po rnams te /
NK091(ke)001:9590: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba la la ni 'od srung dang
NK091(ke)001:9591: mar me mdzad sogs chos kyi rgyal po nyid lta
NK091(ke)001:9592: bura bstan nas dam pa tog la sprul pa'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:9594: de yis sh+aaka thub kyis mi pham mgon la bskur ba'ang mtshon no //
NK091(ke)001:9595: rgyal ba la la ni rigs kyi sangsa rgyas lnga
NK091(ke)001:9596: lta bur bstan nas don grub la longs sku'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:9598: sangs rgyas la la ni gzugs sku'i rgyal ba dpag
NK091(ke)001:9599: tu meda pa nyid du bstan nas sh+aakya thub pa
NK091(ke)001:9600: la sgron ma'i rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur ro //
NK091(ke)001:9601: rgyal ba la la ni 'og min du rnam par
NK091(ke)001:9602: snang mdzad dang 'dir sh+aaka thub la sogs pa gzugs
NK091(ke)001:9603: sku gnyis lta bur bstan nas gsang ba'i bdag po
NK091(ke)001:9604: la sngags phyi nang gi ston pa dang sdud pa
NK091(ke)001:9610: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9611: la la zhes dam pa tog la ni sprul pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9612: rgyal tshab kyi rgyal sar byung ba'i dus la bab
NK091(ke)001:9613: pa'i phyir sprul sku'i rgyud du dbang bskur /
NK091(ke)001:9614: la la zhes don grub la ni longs spyod rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:9615: pa'i gzugs su sangs rgyas pa'i dus la bab pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9616: phyir sa tha ma'i 'gro ba sgrol bar bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:9617: dbang bskur // la la zhes sh+aakya thub pa la
NK091(ke)001:9618: ni zhing khams kyi sgron ma gyis shig par lung
NK091(ke)001:9619: ngesa par thob pa'i dus la bab pa'i phyir snying
NK091(ke)001:9620: po byang chub kyi sgron mar dbang bskur /
NK091(ke)001:9621: la la zhes phyag na rdo rje la ni gsang bas 'dul ba la phan gdags pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9622: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i gsang ba mi nub par bya
NK091(ke)001:9623: bas gsang ba'i snying pora nges pa'i dus la bab
NK091(ke)001:9624: pa'i phyir gsang ba chen po'i mdzod 'dzin par dbang
NK091(ke)001:9629: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9630: la la zhes dam pa tog la ni thabs kyi
NK091(ke)001:9631: rdzas rin po che yi dbu rgyan tog dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:9632: pa lta bu'i chos kyi cod pan gyi dbang gis
NK091(ke)001:9633: dbang byin no // la la zhes don grub la
NK091(ke)001:9634: ni thabs shes rdor dril dang gsang ba nyi zla'i
NK091(ke)001:9635: rtags kyis nyi zla rdo rje 'bar ba gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:9636: nang pa'i dbang gis dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9637: 'di nyid don grub btsun mo'i nang na bzhugs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9638: tshe thabs shes nyi zla'i dbang ngam yang na phyogs
NK091(ke)001:9639: bcu'i rgyal bas nyi ma spyi bor bstim /
NK091(ke)001:9642: la la zhes sh+aaka thub la ni rigsa kyi phyag
NK091(ke)001:9643: rgya lnga lta bu'i rdzas kyis rdo rje gdan gyi
NK091(ke)001:9644: byang chub snying por dbang gis mdzad pas bdud bzhi
NK091(ke)001:9645: btul ba'i dbang gis dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9646: la la zhes phyag rdor la ni rdo rje pha
NK091(ke)001:9647: lam lta bu'i rdzas gsang bdag chen po'i rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:9648: rgya gram mu khyud can de nyid /
NK091(ke)001:9649: gyad yul du phyogs bcu'i sprul skus rdo rje phyag
NK091(ke)001:9650: la grim byas te gsang mdzod 'dzin pa'i dbang gis
NK091(ke)001:9651: dbang byin no // brgyad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:9655: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9656: la la zhes dam pa tog la ni sgron ma'i
NK091(ke)001:9657: zhing khams na grangs mang ba la ltos te dga'
NK091(ke)001:9658: ldan lta bu sha stag tu dbang byina no //
NK091(ke)001:9659: la la zhes don grub la ni bkod pa sna
NK091(ke)001:9660: tshogs dang bstun pa'i 'og min chen po lta bu
NK091(ke)001:9661: sha stag tu dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9662: la la zhes sh+aakya thub pa la ni snying po byang chub kyi gnas dam pa /
NK091(ke)001:9664: sh+aakya thub pa rdo rje gdan //
NK091(ke)001:9665: 'dir ni de bzhin nyid bder gshegs //
NK091(ke)001:9666: gdal khyab chen po'i zhing na bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:9668: de bzhin nyid du rnam par snang //
NK091(ke)001:9670: 'og min bla na med pa byang chub kyi shing drung ga na bar dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9671: lung 'di nyid sngar dang mthun par 'brom ston gyis
NK091(ke)001:9672: phyag mchan na bzhugs pas rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul
NK091(ke)001:9673: pa'i bkod pa bye brag pa stong chen po'i sgron
NK091(ke)001:9674: mar ji ltar spros pa'i tshul gyis mdo chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:9675: gleng gzhi dang 'brel bar dbang don gyi zab gnad
NK091(ke)001:9676: slong nus pas nges pa ster ba 'di 'dra pan
NK091(ke)001:9677: grub snga ma la ma grags shing kun mkhyen rong
NK091(ke)001:9678: zom chen po'i gsung sgros yin par gor ma chag
NK091(ke)001:9679: snyam mo // la la zhes phyag na rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:9680: la ni 'og min de nyid rnam mdzes sam dbang
NK091(ke)001:9682: la sogs pa zhes lho phyogs theg pa gyad kyi yul lta bur dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9687: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9688: la la zhes dam pa tog dkar ni sprul pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9689: chos kyi rgyal tshab tu gyur pa lta bu rtags
NK091(ke)001:9690: mngon du snang ba'i dbang byin /
NK091(ke)001:9691: la la zhes don grub ni rdzogs pa'i longs spyod
NK091(ke)001:9692: lta bu longs spyod rdzogs sku'i rtags mngon du snang
NK091(ke)001:9693: ba'i dbang byin / la la zhes sh+aakya thub pa
NK091(ke)001:9694: ni sgron ma'i bya ba mdzad pas chos kyi mnga'
NK091(ke)001:9695: bdag nyid du gyur pa lta bu thob pa'i rtags
NK091(ke)001:9696: mngon du snang ba'i dbang byin /
NK091(ke)001:9697: la la zhes phyag na rdo rje ni gsang ba
NK091(ke)001:9698: 'chad pa'i ston pa mdzod gsum 'dzin pa'i bdag po
NK091(ke)001:9699: nyid du gyur pa lta bu thob pa'i rtags mngon
NK091(ke)001:9700: par snang ba'i dbang byin no //
NK091(ke)001:9708: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9709: tha ma'i don la rjes su 'jug pa dang thun mong pa'i dbang du phye ba gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:9710: lang ka'i bdag po de yang 'di ltar dbang gi don la /
NK091(ke)001:9713: mi thob pa'i gegs dang sngon byung du rgyal ba lta bu thob pa'i yul dang /
NK091(ke)001:9714: snod du gyur pa slob ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:9716: mngon du gyur pa rtags te bdun gyis dbang 'di'i don bsdus pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9717: zhes grangs kyi ngo bo bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9725: mngon du snang ba'i rtags so //
NK091(ke)001:9730: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9731: lang ka'i bdag po de la rgyu ni rnal 'byor chen po lnga ste /
NK091(ke)001:9732: gsang ba'i don zab mo la sems skyes te zhugs
NK091(ke)001:9733: pas mos pa'i sgo nas yid la byed pa 'duna
NK091(ke)001:9734: pa sems pa'i rnal 'byor tshogs lam dang /
NK091(ke)001:9735: theg pa chen po'i sgor 'jug ldog dang ltung mi
NK091(ke)001:9736: ltung rigs 'byed pas rigsa chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor
NK091(ke)001:9737: sbyor lam dang / gnyis med kyi don dang por
NK091(ke)001:9738: mthong bas dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor mthong lam
NK091(ke)001:9739: sbyor lam dang / dang / mngon sum du lung
NK091(ke)001:9740: thob pas lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor sgom las
NK091(ke)001:9741: sbyor lam dang / dang / dang / rig pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9742: rtsal rdzogs pas rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor mthar
NK091(ke)001:9743: lam pa chen po pa ste 'di dag kyang sngon
NK091(ke)001:9744: goms pa'i tshad ma bcos pa'i don snang zhing bsam
NK091(ke)001:9746: rig pa dus kyi tshad chos nyid rig pa /
NK091(ke)001:9747: shes rab la zlo ba'i tshad grub pa thob pas gzungs mang po thob pa /
NK091(ke)001:9748: man ngag lung gi tshad bla ma dam pa'i lung snod du lon pa /
NK091(ke)001:9749: yon tan rdzogs pa'i tshad yon tan gyi chos mthar
NK091(ke)001:9750: phyin pa lnga dang ldan pa rnams su rig par
NK091(ke)001:9755: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9756: lang ka'i bdag po chu bo bzhi'i dbang bskur bas
NK091(ke)001:9757: thob pa'i tshad dang ldan pa ni 'di lta lte
NK091(ke)001:9758: / lam rnal 'byor lnga dang rim par sbyar na /
NK091(ke)001:9759: gang zag bcas kyi bslab pa yongs su chub pa dang po gnyis mthar phyin pa'i tshad dang /
NK091(ke)001:9760: de kho na nyid bden pa mthong ba'i tshad dang ldan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9761: shesa bya gang ci la'ang nyam ma nga bar shes pa'i tshad mnga' ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9762: gang gi the tshom la sogs pa'i 'jigsa pa dang bral ba'i tshad du phyin na /
NK091(ke)001:9763: las kyi dbang dang bsnyen bsgrub sgom pa'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:9764: rdo rje rgyal po rab 'byams kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:9765: 'chad pa'i dbang bskur du rung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:9766: yang na glegs bam bcu gnyis dang /
NK091(ke)001:9767: nyi zla gnyis sbyin pa la sogs pa'i 'chad pa dag go //
NK091(ke)001:9768: 'di dag tshad du phyin pas bskur ba'i dus la bab par 'gyur gyi /
NK091(ke)001:9769: 'chad pa'i mi 'thob pa'i zla la ltos pas kyang thob zin pa'i tshad ni ma yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9770: rnal 'byor gyi dbang du dang po gnyis gcig tu brtsis te dbang bzhi dang rim pa bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:9771: rang bzhin gyi dbang du 'bras bu dang sbyar na
NK091(ke)001:9772: dam pa tog dkar po bslab pa bcu mthar phyin
NK091(ke)001:9773: par yongs su chub ste nyam nga med pa dang
NK091(ke)001:9774: / don grub gsang ba ji lta ba'i de kho
NK091(ke)001:9775: na nyid mthong ste mnga' dbang chen po thob pa
NK091(ke)001:9776: / dang / sh+aakya thub pa shes bya gang yang
NK091(ke)001:9777: mi mkhyen pa med la ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo
NK091(ke)001:9778: 'bum phrag du ma rdzogs te nyam mi nga ba'i
NK091(ke)001:9780: phyag na rdo rje 'khor ba ye shes su rtogs
NK091(ke)001:9781: nas gang gi 'jigs pa dang bral te gsang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:9787: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9788: gang mi 'thob pa ni chu bo bzhi'i dbang gi rim pa dang sbyar te /
NK091(ke)001:9789: gang bslab pa'i don chud par grags pa'i tshul gyis
NK091(ke)001:9790: rang gi yon tan la nga rgyal rlom sems su
NK091(ke)001:9791: byed pa dang / gang dag don nges par ma
NK091(ke)001:9792: rtogs te bsam sbyor dang theg pa'i rigs ma nges
NK091(ke)001:9793: byed pa dang / ba dang / gang bsgom pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9794: don dang shes bya la dam par dmigs te lta
NK091(ke)001:9795: bas mnyam par ma rtogs pas ched byas la 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:9796: byed pa dang / ba dang / pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9797: sgrib pas chod de skyon tshang ba gang du ye
NK091(ke)001:9798: shes dang yon tan gyi rtsal gang yang mi 'byung
NK091(ke)001:9800: 'chad pa'i don bzhi bzhir snang ba'ang rjes su mthun no //
NK091(ke)001:9805: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9806: lang ka'i bdag po dbang gang las len pa'i yul ni /
NK091(ke)001:9807: lam gyi dbang du bla ma ste ngo mtshar gyi
NK091(ke)001:9808: rdzas rnyed cing kun gyis mchod pa'i rten gnas su
NK091(ke)001:9809: gyur pa'i byin stobs can bden pa'i don mthong ba
NK091(ke)001:9810: dang / dngos su sgra snyan gyis lung bstan pa thob pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9811: rtsal chen rdzogs pas blo gros nges pa'i tshad ma can bde gshegs kyi zhal mthong ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9812: yang dag pa'i ched du nges pa rnyed zin pa'i rgyal ba nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:9813: sa lnga po gang snga rol pa'i slob ma la
NK091(ke)001:9814: phyi rol pas bskur ba'i phyir sa de nyid kyis
NK091(ke)001:9815: de nyid la bskur ba ni byin rlabs snang bar
NK091(ke)001:9818: dam pa tog dkar gyis blang ba'i yul chos kyi rgyal po nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:9819: don grub kyis rigs lnga dang /
NK091(ke)001:9820: sh+aakya thub pas phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9821: phyag na rdo rjes gzugs sku gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:9822: ril gyi bdag po chen po mchod pa'i rten du nges pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:9823: mngon par byang chub pa lnga'i sgra snyan par 'byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:9824: sku gsung thugs mi bslu bar bden pas tshad ma mthar phyin pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:9825: gsang sngags nges pa don gyi mdzod dam pa ster ba'i phyir rim par bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9830: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9832: ganga chu bo bzhi'i snod du gyur pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:9833: gang yid la byed pa dang 'phro 'du gcig pa
NK091(ke)001:9834: la sbyangs nas rgyal ba'i gdung 'dzin pa'i rgyud du
NK091(ke)001:9835: byung ba dang / gang don rtogs te rtsal rdzogs pa'i phyir 'jigs pa lnga dang bral ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9836: gang lung thob cing gdeng dang ldan pas thugs rje chen pos gzhan don du phyis 'byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9837: gang rtsal chen rdzogs pas gzhan ril dbang du gyur pa la sbyin par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:9838: rang bzhin sngon byung gi dbang du ni /
NK091(ke)001:9839: gang dam pa tog dkar po ni chos kyi rgyal
NK091(ke)001:9840: tshab byed pa'i phyir sprul pa'i rgyud du byung ba
NK091(ke)001:9841: dang / don kun grub pa ni 'og min du rtsal rdzogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9842: sh+aakya thub pa sprul pa'i skus 'gro ba gzhan sgrol ba'i phyir thugs rje 'byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9843: phyag na rdo rje log sde 'dul stobs can gyi
NK091(ke)001:9844: phyir drag shul gyi thabs kyis kun tu bsgyur nas
NK091(ke)001:9845: gzhan kun dbang du bsdus kyang dul ba dang ldan
NK091(ke)001:9846: par gyur pa'o // drug pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:9850: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9852: dbang gi khyad par gyi grangs ni 'di ltar gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:9854: rig pa rtsal gyis thob pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9855: rim gyis pa'i dbang du bskur bas thoba pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9857: lam pa cig char bas rtsal gyis thob pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:9859: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsang ba'i thugs dkyil 'khor gsum
NK091(ke)001:9860: dbyer med pa'i gsang sngags ji lta ba'i don phul
NK091(ke)001:9862: tshig tsam min par shes rab kyi rtsal gyis thob
NK091(ke)001:9863: ste yang dag par rtogsa shing mthong bas rang don
NK091(ke)001:9864: rdzogs nasa gzhan gang la don dang mthun par ji
NK091(ke)001:9865: lta ba bzhin du gsal bar ston pa'i rtsal dang
NK091(ke)001:9866: nus pa rdzogs pas kun tu sgrol bar byed pa
NK091(ke)001:9867: ni dbang rnams kun gyi mchog tu gyur pa thob
NK091(ke)001:9868: pa yin te / slob dpon chen po 'jal dpal bshes gnyen gyis /
NK091(ke)001:9869: zab pa don gyi dbang mchog ni //
NK091(ke)001:9870: rig pa'i rtsal dbang thob pa ste //
NK091(ke)001:9871: chos nyid rtogs pas dbang zhes bya //
NK091(ke)001:9872: ye shes dbang bskur cod pan can //
NK091(ke)001:9874: des na chos kyi rgyal po'i rigs 'tshob pa'i phyir sde brgyad dang /
NK091(ke)001:9876: lam pa ril gyis dam pa de nyid la bdag
NK091(ke)001:9877: po chen por dbang bskur zhing 'dren pa'i dbang por
NK091(ke)001:9878: bstab ste bka' la gus pas nyan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9880: gang lam pa rim gyis par bskur basa thob pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:9881: bsod nams kyi sa bon du gyur pas /
NK091(ke)001:9882: sa bon ngan pa spong bas gang phyi ma la phan pa tsam dang /
NK091(ke)001:9883: gang gisa sgo gsum gyi rtsal gyis bdag gzhan gyi don nus pa tsam du shes par bya ste /
NK091(ke)001:9884: de'ang bum pa'i dbang la sogs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9890: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:9892: mngon du gyur pa'i rtags ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:9893: rang bzhin sngon byung gi dbang du dam pa tog
NK091(ke)001:9894: dkar po kun gyis bskur bas dbu la gtsug tor
NK091(ke)001:9895: ltar mi mngon pas dam pa 'byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:9896: don kun grub pa mnyam pa nyid rdo rje lta
NK091(ke)001:9897: bu'i ting nge 'dzin gang la mnyam par ma bzhag
NK091(ke)001:9898: par rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes lhan ne
NK091(ke)001:9899: ba las mi g.yo ba thob pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9900: sh+aakya thub pa 'bad rtsol med par 'bras bu'i chos
NK091(ke)001:9901: kyi yon tan ji snyed pa lhun gyis yongs su
NK091(ke)001:9903: phyag na rdo rje theg pa chen po gsang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:9904: thugs rje kun la khyab pa thob pas 'od zer
NK091(ke)001:9905: dang rdzu 'phrul mtha' yas pa kun nas rgyas par
NK091(ke)001:9906: gyur pa'o // zhes skyes bu dam pa bzhi rim pa bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:9907: rjes 'jug gi dbang du na rnal 'byor dang po
NK091(ke)001:9908: gnyis sam nges pa las gyen du 'phags te mthong
NK091(ke)001:9909: lam phyir mi ldog pa thob cing phal pa'i skye
NK091(ke)001:9910: bo kun gyis spyi bor bkur ba'i phyir gtsug tor
NK091(ke)001:9912: dbugs chen pas mthong ba'i don las bsgom pa'i lam
NK091(ke)001:9913: gyi ting nge 'dzin gang la ma bzhag lhan ne
NK091(ke)001:9914: ba'i ye shes mi rtog pa las mi g.yo ba
NK091(ke)001:9915: thob pa dang / lung chen pas lung dam pa
NK091(ke)001:9916: thob nas rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i sa mchog lhun gyis
NK091(ke)001:9917: yongs su grub par gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:9918: rtsal chen pas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sa chen
NK091(ke)001:9919: po thob ste rang lus la 'od zer dang rdzu
NK091(ke)001:9920: 'phrul mtha' yas par rgyas pa mngon par grub pa'o
NK091(ke)001:9923: tshogs sbyor gnyis so sor phyi nas chu bo bzhi
NK091(ke)001:9924: dang sbyar zhing mthar lam pa dbang gi 'bras bur
NK091(ke)001:9926: dbang 'di dag kyang rnal 'byor pa'i dbang du ste /
NK091(ke)001:9927: 'dun pa'i rnal 'byor pa la ni phyi'i dbang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:9928: rigs chen 'byed pa la ni nang gi dbang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:9929: dbugs chen 'byin pa la ni sgrub pa'i dbang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:9930: lung chen thob pa la ni gsang ba'i dbang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:9931: rtsal chen rdzogs pa ni dbang gi 'bras bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:9933: rgyu'i dbang sngon du song nas gong du bshad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:9934: lam dbang dang sbyar te mthar lam pa 'bras bur
NK091(ke)001:9935: bzhag pa la sngon byung gi dbang bskur ba'i nges
NK091(ke)001:9936: pa dang bstun na mdo chen po'i rang lugs kyi
NK091(ke)001:9937: chu bo bzhi'i dbang gi spyi 'gros kyi dka' gnad
NK091(ke)001:9938: mang po khrol bar mthong ngo //
NK091(ke)001:9939: de ltar sngon byung gi mdzad spyod kyis gdul bya spro ba bskyed de /
NK091(ke)001:9940: des ni rjes 'jug nyams len gyi sgo nas gdul
NK091(ke)001:9941: bya chud mi gsan par bskur thabs shugs la 'phang
NK091(ke)001:9942: bas don gyi gnad zin par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:9943: 'di la kun mkhyen dam pa rin po ches /
NK091(ke)001:9944: dbang 'di rnams khungs dang grags pa la sogs pa don dgu po ni /
NK091(ke)001:9945: sngon byung du dam pa tog dkar po dang /
NK091(ke)001:9948: phyag na rdo rje dang bzhi la dbang bskur zhing /
NK091(ke)001:9949: de bzhin du rgyal tshab skyes bu khye'u lnga la dbang bskur ba yin no //
NK091(ke)001:9950: khungs dang grags pa la sogs pa'i don bcu'i tha
NK091(ke)001:9951: ma dbang gi don la bdun du bstan pa de
NK091(ke)001:9952: sngon byung rjes 'jug gnyis char du gsungs na /
NK091(ke)001:9953: kho bo ni khungs dang grags pa la sogs pa
NK091(ke)001:9954: don dgu po ni sngon byung gi dbang yin la
NK091(ke)001:9955: don bcu'i tha ma dbang gi don ni rjes 'jug
NK091(ke)001:9958: rnal 'byor lnga la dbang bskur ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:9960: rgyu rnal 'byor lngas mtshon te don bdun po rjes
NK091(ke)001:9961: 'jug lam pa'i dbang dngos bstan du gyur pa la
NK091(ke)001:9962: dgongs pas gzhung don ji lta ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:9963: thob pa'i tshad la sogs pa sngon byung dang yang
NK091(ke)001:9964: sbyar ba rnams lam mthar phyin pa na bye brag
NK091(ke)001:9965: don mthun du 'gyur ba'i phyir gnad gcig ste spros
NK091(ke)001:9966: pas chog go // de lta na'ang slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyis /
NK091(ke)001:9967: khungs sogs dang po gsum btang snyoms su mdzad nas /
NK091(ke)001:9968: de phyin yul sogs drug gis sngon byung dang /
NK091(ke)001:9969: bcu pa don la nang gses kyi bdun du phye
NK091(ke)001:9970: bas rjes 'jug lam pa'i dbang bstan pa shas che
NK091(ke)001:9972: sngon byung dang rjes 'jug lam pa'i dbang gnyis sngom gyi don bcus dngos su bsdus par bkral zhing /
NK091(ke)001:9973: des dpags te rjes 'jug las dang po pa ma
NK091(ke)001:9974: smin pa smin par byed pa'i dbang gi rim pa
NK091(ke)001:9975: gtso bor bstan pa chu bo bzhis bsdus pa'ang shugs
NK091(ke)001:9978: sems can rnams kyi don chen du //
NK091(ke)001:9979: dbang gi don rnams bsdu bar bya //
NK091(ke)001:9980: chu bo chen po bzhi rnams la //
NK091(ke)001:9981: sngon byung dang ni rjes su 'jug /sngon byung chu bo rnam bzhi la //
NK091(ke)001:9982: yul dang dbang po dgos ched dang //
NK091(ke)001:9983: thabs dang rtags dang gnas dang drug /rjes 'jug lam pa dang po gnyis //
NK091(ke)001:9984: lam pa chu bo rnam bzhi la //
NK091(ke)001:9985: rgyud dang thob dang mi thob dang //
NK091(ke)001:9986: yul dang snod dang khyad par brtags //
NK091(ke)001:9987: bdun gyis 'di yi don bsdus pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:9988: rjes 'jug las kyi dang po la //
NK091(ke)001:9989: chu bo bzhi yi dbang bskur ba //
NK091(ke)001:9990: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK091(ke)001:9991: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK091(ke)001:9992: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la //
NK091(ke)001:9993: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bos bya //
NK091(ke)001:9994: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK091(ke)001:9995: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bos bya //
NK091(ke)001:9996: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga la //
NK091(ke)001:9997: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bos bya //
NK091(ke)001:9998: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK091(ke)001:9999: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10000: sum cu rtsa drug legs dbang bskur //
NK091(ke)001:10001: zhes sdoms su bstan pa de nyid dbang don rnam
NK091(ke)001:10002: par 'byed pa las so sor bkral te gsungs pa
NK091(ke)001:10003: ltar shes dgos kyang 'dir sngon byung dang rjes 'jug
NK091(ke)001:10004: lam pa'i dbang sngar bshad pa rnams dang sbyar la
NK091(ke)001:10005: / rjes 'jug las dang po pa'i dbang la /
NK091(ke)001:10006: dang po rgyal po bka' rtags dbang //
NK091(ke)001:10007: zhes sogs kyis bstan par bya ba rtsa rgyud kun
NK091(ke)001:10008: 'dus rig pa las dngos su gsungs pa'i dbang chog
NK091(ke)001:10009: so drug gi grangs tsam 'chad de /
NK091(ke)001:10010: de nas yang sems dpa' rdo rje des yongs su rdzogs pa dbang gi le'u 'di gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:10013: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK091(ke)001:10014: zhes pa'i bar gyis mdor bstan nas //
NK091(ke)001:10015: de'i don rgyas par bshad pa la //
NK091(ke)001:10017: dang po phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo ni //
NK091(ke)001:10019: de la dang por sbyin pa'i dbang ni 'di yin te /
NK091(ke)001:10021: kun gyis 'da' bar dka' ba yi //
NK091(ke)001:10022: tshig btsan yul la dbang bsgyur ba //
NK091(ke)001:10023: rgyal po bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK091(ke)001:10024: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK091(ke)001:10026: 'jig rten kun la kha lo bsgyur ba yi //
NK091(ke)001:10027: dbang mchog rgyal po 'di yang sbyin par bya //
NK091(ke)001:10028: zhes pa'i bar gyis bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10029: rtags kyi mtshan ma'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10030: shes rab gzungs kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10031: bkra shis bum pa'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10032: bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10033: rin chen sna bdun gyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10034: khyad par gdan khri'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10035: rgyan cha rtags kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10036: rdo rje ming gi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10037: rin chen 'khor lo'i dbang ste phan dbang ngam phyi dbang bcu bskur tshul bshad do //
NK091(ke)001:10038: gnyis pa nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo ni /
NK091(ke)001:10039: phyi 'khor skyong ba'i rgyal por gyur phan chad //
NK091(ke)001:10040: bla med mchog gi rtogs dang ldan 'gyur pas //
NK091(ke)001:10041: gsang sgo phye nas nang du gzhug par bya //
NK091(ke)001:10042: shin tu gsang ba'i rdzas dang ldan gyur nas //
NK091(ke)001:10043: gsang sgo gang las 'dod pa'i don rnams zhu //
NK091(ke)001:10044: gnang ba chen po'i rtags su byin gyis brlabs //
NK091(ke)001:10045: zhes pas phyi dbang thob nas snod rung du byas
NK091(ke)001:10046: pa de nang gi dkyil 'khor du gzhug cing rang
NK091(ke)001:10047: blo dang theg tshad kyi dbang bskur tshul mdor bstan
NK091(ke)001:10049: bskur thabs rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:10050: gsang ba'i don la nyan cing slob pa'i dbang //
NK091(ke)001:10051: dbang thob skal can de la sbyin par bya //
NK091(ke)001:10053: rtsal gyi thig le rdo rje byin //
NK091(ke)001:10054: zhes pa'i bar gyis gsang ba nyan cing klog pa'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10055: rnam bzhi las kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10057: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10058: zil gnon gdan gyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10059: khyad par rin chen sna bdun gyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10060: phyag rgya gzugs brnyan gyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10061: ye shes thugs kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10062: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10063: bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10064: gsang ba ming gi dbang ste nang nus pa'i dbang bcu gcig bskur tshul bshad do //
NK091(ke)001:10065: gsum pa sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo ni /
NK091(ke)001:10066: nang du 'jug pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK091(ke)001:10067: de dag kun la spyod sgrub pa'i //
NK091(ke)001:10068: dbang mchog dam pa spyin par bya //
NK091(ke)001:10070: de dag gi don khyad par can sgrub pa'i thabs
NK091(ke)001:10071: spyod pa'i dbang sbyin tshul mdor bstan pas mtshams sbyar
NK091(ke)001:10072: nas bskur thabs rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:10073: skye med chos kyi dbyings nyid la //
NK091(ke)001:10074: sems kyis dbang bskur thob pa yi //
NK091(ke)001:10075: shes rab chen po rig pa'i dbang //
NK091(ke)001:10076: sems lon don gyi gtan tshigs sbyin //
NK091(ke)001:10078: rdo rje ming ni sbyin par bya //
NK091(ke)001:10079: zhes pa'i bar gyis shes rab rig pa'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10080: snying rje rtags kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10082: dug gsum gting nas sprugs pa'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10083: srid gsum sgrol ba'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10084: skyon gyis ma gos pa'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10085: las rnams rdzogs pa'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10087: gsang ba sbyor ba'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10088: 'dod yon longs spyod kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10089: sgrub pa'i rgyal po'i dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10090: sgrub rdzas thams cad kyi dbang dang /
NK091(ke)001:10091: gnyis med ming gi dbang ste sgrub dbang bcu gsum bskur tshul bshad de /
NK091(ke)001:10092: chu bo bzhi po phan nus zab mo'i dbang gsum
NK091(ke)001:10093: du bsdu ba'i tshe 'di ni nus dbang gi nang
NK091(ke)001:10094: tshan no // bzhi pa gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo ni /
NK091(ke)001:10095: sgrub pa'i dbang mchog thob pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:10096: gsang ba'i bdag po yin pas na //
NK091(ke)001:10097: gsang ba'i dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK091(ke)001:10099: dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK091(ke)001:10100: kun tu tshim par byed pa yi //
NK091(ke)001:10101: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK091(ke)001:10102: dbang thob de yi lce la bzhag /brtsal med byang chub sems chen po //
NK091(ke)001:10103: shes rab chen po'i rtsal gyis ni //
NK091(ke)001:10104: chos kun sgyu mar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK091(ke)001:10105: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i dbang yin pas //
NK091(ke)001:10106: rdzas dang tshig dang gang zag dang //
NK091(ke)001:10107: kun rdzob dbang de ma thob kyang //
NK091(ke)001:10108: chos la sems kyi dbang thob na //
NK091(ke)001:10109: rgyal ba rig 'dzin thams cad dang //
NK091(ke)001:10110: srid gsum dbang can thams cad kun //
NK091(ke)001:10111: de la dbang mchog bskur bar 'gyur //
NK091(ke)001:10112: zhes gsungs pa ltar kun rdzob byang sems kyi dbang lus dang /
NK091(ke)001:10113: don dam byang sems kyi dbang sems la bskur tshul bshad do //
NK091(ke)001:10114: de bzhin du bshad rgyud rngam glog las kyang dbang so drug gi rkang grangs gsal bar bstan no //
NK091(ke)001:10115: de las yan lag gi dbye ba dbang don rgya cher 'byed pa las /
NK091(ke)001:10116: chu bo bzhi yi dbang gi rim pa las //
NK091(ke)001:10117: dang po rgyud kyi chu bo rnam grangs bcu //
NK091(ke)001:10118: dang po rgyal po bka' rtags nyi shu dang //
NK091(ke)001:10120: dang po rgyal po bka' rtags nyi shu ni //
NK091(ke)001:10121: cod pan lha mo seng ge glang po che //
NK091(ke)001:10122: zhes sogs kyis rgyas par bshad de mdo dbang rtsa
NK091(ke)001:10123: ba so drug las yan lag rags pa brgyad brgya
NK091(ke)001:10124: so gcig tu phye nas bskur tshul ni slob dpon
NK091(ke)001:10125: chen po bde ba gsal mdzad kyis las tho'i dgongs
NK091(ke)001:10126: pa yin pas man ngag gi lugs zhes bya ste
NK091(ke)001:10127: / 'dir chos rje dam pa rin po ches phyag
NK091(ke)001:10128: mchan las zag bcas las dang po par chu bo
NK091(ke)001:10129: bzhir bskur lugs 'dir bsdebs zhes gsungs pas rgyud dang
NK091(ke)001:10130: man ngag gi lugs kyi rkang grangs mdo tsam bshad
NK091(ke)001:10131: par zad kyi rgyas par dbang chog rnams las shes
NK091(ke)001:10136: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10137: lang ka'i bdag po zhes sdud pa po la bos
NK091(ke)001:10138: nas de ltar na de'i phyir zhes dbang bskur ba'i
NK091(ke)001:10139: don rgyas pa la snyegs pa'i tshul ni /
NK091(ke)001:10140: skyes bu dgu po las skyes bu dam pa lnga
NK091(ke)001:10141: gtsor byas te de dag ni dbang thob pas chos
NK091(ke)001:10142: kyi rgyal po dam pa zhes bya bar /
NK091(ke)001:10143: rgyal ba dam pa rnams kyi zhing du yongs su grags so //
NK091(ke)001:10144: 'o na skyes bu dam pa dag tha ma'i dbugs
NK091(ke)001:10145: phyin nas gzod dbang thob pas grags sam zhe na
NK091(ke)001:10146: / mtshon pa'i tshig gis gral tsam du dbang thob pas tha ma'i dbugs phyin pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:10147: dbang snga rol du sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:10149: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:10150: skyes bu dam pa lnga bzhi gtso bor bstan pa 'bras bu la gnas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10151: rgyu'i skyes bu lngas dbang thob pa'i don bstan pa'i
NK091(ke)001:10152: le'u ste bcu gsum pa gsal bar bshad pa'o ////drug
NK091(ke)001:10153: pa nges pa rnyed pa'i yon tan sangs rgyas su
NK091(ke)001:10155: skyes bu dam pa de rnams zhing khams lngar sangs rgyas par lung bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:10157: rig 'dzin kun gtan tshigs kyis rigs lngar bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:10158: don gsang bar nges pas nges pa rnyed par dkon pa /
NK091(ke)001:10159: don la brtsad pa'i skyon spang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:10164: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10165: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK091(ke)001:10166: rim pa yongs su rdzogs pa na /
NK091(ke)001:10167: 'bras bu mthar phyin par lung ston pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10168: skabs kyi 'brel bas de nas rdo rje sems dpa' de kho na nyid des /
NK091(ke)001:10169: skyes bu dam pa lnga po de dag /zhing khams dang /
NK091(ke)001:10171: dbang gi chu bo yongs su rdzogs par gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:10172: na zhing khams lngar yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK091(ke)001:10173: rgyas rigs lnga'i byang chub chen po'i 'bras bur mngon
NK091(ke)001:10174: du lung bstana ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:10175: skyes bu dam pa de dag dang 'khor 'dus pa
NK091(ke)001:10176: phal mo che khyed ni zhes pa'i tshig 'dis khye'u
NK091(ke)001:10177: lnga lam pa 'dra ba'i sprul par gsungs par ltar
NK091(ke)001:10178: 'khor de rnams kyang mtshungs pas dam pa'i rigs can
NK091(ke)001:10179: rnams kyang mtshon pa yin la /
NK091(ke)001:10180: yang na rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10181: zhes 'byung kyang gzhung don snga ma'o //
NK091(ke)001:10183: mngon sum du lung bstan pa sgom lam lung chen thob pa lta bu /
NK091(ke)001:10184: shugs las lung bstan pa 'od gsal bde ba chen
NK091(ke)001:10185: po'i lung thob pa mthong lam yin pa lta bu
NK091(ke)001:10186: / zhar la lung bstan pa zab don rtogs shing
NK091(ke)001:10187: smra ba de sras dam pa yin par lung thob
NK091(ke)001:10188: pa gsang snying le'u tha ma nas bstan pa lta
NK091(ke)001:10189: / bu / dus kyi tha mar skad cig gis
NK091(ke)001:10190: lung bstan pa rgyal tshab chos kyi rgyal por longs
NK091(ke)001:10191: sku rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su lung thob pa lta
NK091(ke)001:10193: de'ang rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngo bo ye
NK091(ke)001:10194: ji bzhin pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' thog ma dang
NK091(ke)001:10195: tha ma med pa'i dus nasa ye sangs rgyas pa
NK091(ke)001:10196: de nyid ji bzhin par rtogs pa mthar phyin nas
NK091(ke)001:10197: mngon par rdzogs para sangs rgyas pas rgyud dag pa'i
NK091(ke)001:10198: rdo rje sems dpa' dag pa gnyis dang ldan pa
NK091(ke)001:10200: skyes bu dam pa sems dpa' rdo rje zhes bya ba de ni /
NK091(ke)001:10201: 'jig rten gyi khams shar phyogs mngon par dga' ba zhes bya bar /
NK091(ke)001:10202: sangs rgyas mi 'khrugsa pa zhes bya bar 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:10203: skyes bu dam pa rdo rje rin chen zhes bya ba de ni /
NK091(ke)001:10204: 'jig rten gyi khams lho phyogs dapala dang ldan pa zhes bya bar /
NK091(ke)001:10205: sangs rgyas rin chen 'byung ba zhes bya bar 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:10206: skyes bu dam pa rdo rje chos zhes bya ba de ni /
NK091(ke)001:10207: 'jig rten gyi khams nub phyogs bde ba can zhes bya bar /
NK091(ke)001:10208: sangs rgyas 'oda snang mtha' yas zhes bya bar 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:10209: skyes bu dam pa rdo rje dbyings zhes bya ba de ni /
NK091(ke)001:10210: 'jig rten gyi khamsa dbus phyogs byang chub kyis brgyan pa zhes bya bar /
NK091(ke)001:10211: sangs rgyas rnam para snang mdzad ces bya bar 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:10212: skyes bu dam pa rdo rje sna tshogsa zhes bya ba de ni /
NK091(ke)001:10213: 'jig rten gyi khams byang phyogs rnam par dag pa zhes bya bar /
NK091(ke)001:10214: sangs rgyas gdon mi za bar don yod grub pa
NK091(ke)001:10215: zhes bya bar 'byung bar 'gyur ro zhes lung bstan
NK091(ke)001:10216: te le'u dang po dang sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:10221: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10222: zhing khams de dag kun gyi yon tan ni /
NK091(ke)001:10223: zag pa med pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:10224: yongs su brjod par bya ba'i dpe las 'das te
NK091(ke)001:10225: / thub pa'i zhing gis bskrun mi nus pas dpe
NK091(ke)001:10226: med pa'i phyir tshad dang bral bas longs sku'i zhing
NK091(ke)001:10227: gi bkod pa thams cad brjod kyisa mi lang ngo
NK091(ke)001:10228: / // ston pa rigs lnga'i sku tshe'i tshad ni
NK091(ke)001:10229: mya ngan las 'das pa mi mnga' bas dpag tu
NK091(ke)001:10231: 'dul ba'i zhing ni bzhugs pa'i zhing na gnas te
NK091(ke)001:10232: zhing khams der 'khod pa'i sems can rnams ni sa
NK091(ke)001:10233: non pas rgyal sar bsnyen pa rig 'dzin chen po
NK091(ke)001:10234: 'ba' zhig go // 'dir chos rje'i phyag mchan na /
NK091(ke)001:10235: phyag rgya chen po yang gsung la lhun grub kyang zhes bzhugs pas /
NK091(ke)001:10236: dngos su phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la /
NK091(ke)001:10237: sgyu 'phrul man chad kyi lhun grub rig 'dzin kyang yin te zur gyi bka' srol ltar gzung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:10238: 'khor de rnams kyi tshe'i tshad kyang tshe la dbang
NK091(ke)001:10239: thob pas ston pa de nyid kyi rigsa 'dzin pa'i
NK091(ke)001:10240: tshe tshad dang ldan te rang don du dpag tu
NK091(ke)001:10241: med la gzhan don du cir yang snang bas ma
NK091(ke)001:10243: sprul pa'i zhing gi 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan dag
NK091(ke)001:10244: nas smin pa'i rigsa 'dzin mtha' thug pa med pa
NK091(ke)001:10245: rnamas kyang zhing khams de dag tu rnam par snang
NK091(ke)001:10247: zhing de dag na chos nyan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10249: rnam par bgro ba na ting nge 'dzin gyi dgongs
NK091(ke)001:10250: pa 'ba' zhig gis ston cing rtogs pa sha stag
NK091(ke)001:10251: go // bstan pa dam pa'i chos kyang gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:10252: ji bzhin pa bya ba med pa'i chos de kho
NK091(ke)001:10253: na nyid gsang ba dam pa 'ba' zhig las gzhan
NK091(ke)001:10254: gyis sel med pas sgras rgyu'i theg pa bkag go
NK091(ke)001:10255: go // // ston pa dang 'khor kun gyi longs
NK091(ke)001:10256: spyod kyang thun mong du chos nyid zab mo 'ba'
NK091(ke)001:10258: tshig 'di dag gis longs spyod rdzogs pa'i zhing du
NK091(ke)001:10259: gsal bas le'u dang po'i rgyal ba rigs lnga longs
NK091(ke)001:10263: gtan tshigs kyis rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10268: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10269: rigs dang zhing khams kyi bye brag gi rigsa 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:10270: pa de dag kun kyang rgyu dang 'bras bu gnyis
NK091(ke)001:10271: ka'i sgo nas sems can dang rgyal ba ril yang
NK091(ke)001:10274: de dag thams cad kyang rgyu nyon mongs pa rigsa lnga las byung zhing /
NK091(ke)001:10276: de las bskal pa bogs su gyur pa'i mi bu rigs lngar smin pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:10277: lam lnga'am ye shes lnga las gyur pas rigs kyi sangs rgyas lngar nges pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:10279: zhes gtan tshigs kyi mdo bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10284: zhes pa'i par gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10285: log pa dang ma log pa'i nyon mongs lnga thun mong du sbyar te /
NK091(ke)001:10286: gang zhe sdang gi rigsa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10291: mi bzad pa'i sdug bsngal can bzod ldan gyi rigsa dmyal ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:10292: shin tu yid gdung bas kun gdung gi rigsa yi dwags dang /
NK091(ke)001:10293: rkang gcig rkang gnyis rkang bzhi /
NK091(ke)001:10294: rkang drug rkang mang rkang med de nang rigs gcig la drug tu 'byung ba'am /
NK091(ke)001:10295: rigs drug ka'i gnas su 'byung bas drug 'byung gi rigs byol song dang /
NK091(ke)001:10296: byang chub kyi bsam rgyud can mang bas rgyud ldan gyi rigs mi dang /
NK091(ke)001:10297: gnas khyad par mtho ba'i bde ba can gnas ldan gyi rigs lha dang 'gro ba lnga ste /
NK091(ke)001:10298: lha min ni shing rta chen po thogs med kyis
NK091(ke)001:10299: stod rigs lha dang smad rigs dud 'gror bsdus la
NK091(ke)001:10300: / kun tu bzang po klong drug pa'i 'grel pa
NK091(ke)001:10301: dang yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod du rigs bzhi'am
NK091(ke)001:10302: lngar gsungs kyang lha dang dud 'gro yi dwags gsum
NK091(ke)001:10304: 'dir 'grel chen du stod rigs lha dang smad rigs yi dwags su bsdus pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:10305: 'tsho thabs kyi mi bu lnga ni /
NK091(ke)001:10312: lam pa 'di dag ni theg pa so so bar
NK091(ke)001:10313: gyur na ting nge 'dzin gyis chos nyan pa'i skal
NK091(ke)001:10314: ba can du mi rigs pa'i phyir mi sbyar te
NK091(ke)001:10315: / 'dir thun mong ma yin pa'i las dang po pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10320: rigs kyi dbang du de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su 'byung ba la ma rag pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10321: de bzhin du rdo rje'i rigs dang /
NK091(ke)001:10324: rin po che'i rigs kyi rigs 'dzin du gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:10325: dngos so zhes gzhan dag 'dod na khro bo ni
NK091(ke)001:10326: ye shes lngar smra ste ye shes lnga las rigs
NK091(ke)001:10329: chos rje dam pa rin po che'i phyag mchan sogs kyang de ltar bzhugs pas /
NK091(ke)001:10330: kun snang gi rigsa me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK091(ke)001:10331: rigs gcig pa'i rigsa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK091(ke)001:10332: tha dad pa'i rigs so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK091(ke)001:10333: bya ba byed pa'ii rigsa bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes dang /
NK091(ke)001:10334: thams cad 'byung ba'i rigsa chos dbyings ye shes sam stong pa nyid kyi ye shes rnams te /
NK091(ke)001:10335: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi dang /
NK091(ke)001:10339: ye don gyi kun gzhi rnams kyi phyin ci ma log pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:10340: rigs lnga'i rgyud 'dzin cing 'tshob pa'i phyir rigs lnga dngos thob pa'i nges pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:10341: rdo rje'i rigs kyi gtso bo gdung dang 'khor rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK091(ke)001:10344: legs pa rnams sde'i rigs dang /
NK091(ke)001:10345: rin po che'am nor bu'i rigs kyi gtso bo gdung dang /
NK091(ke)001:10349: bzhad pa rnams sde'i rigsa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10350: pad+mo'i rigs kyi gtso bo gdung dang /
NK091(ke)001:10354: smra ba rnams sde'i rigs dang /
NK091(ke)001:10355: las kyi'am gzhon nu'i rigs kyi gtso bo gdung dang /
NK091(ke)001:10359: khu tshur te 'khor rnams sde'i rigs dang /
NK091(ke)001:10360: de bzhin gshegs pa'am glang po'i rigs kyi gtso bo gdung dang /
NK091(ke)001:10364: las rdo rje rnams ni sde'i rigsa te 'ba' zhig go //
NK091(ke)001:10365: zhes sel med pa ni der ma 'dus pa med pa'i don to //
NK091(ke)001:10366: lngar nges pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:10367: de bzhin du dus thams cada nas gnas skabs thams
NK091(ke)001:10368: cad du snang ba'i thog mtha' med pa'i sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:10369: ril dang / byang chub semsa dpa' mtha' thug pa med pa rnams kyang /
NK091(ke)001:10370: rgyal ba rnams kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi mdzad pa'i las dang /
NK091(ke)001:10371: sems dpa' rnams kyi 'jug pa'i sgo nges pa'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:10372: gisa rigs lnga 'ba' zhig go zhes so so'i skal
NK091(ke)001:10373: ba'i khyad par gyis grangs lngar nges pa kho na
NK091(ke)001:10374: ste / gzhi la de ltar ril lngar yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:10375: bshad pa'i byung snang smin pa ltar gyi rgyu nas
NK091(ke)001:10376: mthar thug rigs so sor 'byung zhing 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:10378: de ni rgyal ba gcig la 'khor lnga ni ma yin te /
NK091(ke)001:10379: rigs btsan pos so sor nges pa'i phyir sgra de dag kyang zhing so sor grags pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10380: 'on kyang mthar phyin nas tha dad du lta ba ni ma yin no //
NK091(ke)001:10383: gtan tshigs kyis rnyed par dka' bar bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10388: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10389: de ltar lngar nges par bstan pa'ang lam pa'i ngo btsan tsam las /
NK091(ke)001:10390: ye ji bzhin pa'i phyi mo'i chos nyid ma bcos pa ni mtha' las grol ba'i dbang gisa na /
NK091(ke)001:10391: sngar gyi dus su thams cad nas phyis kyi gnas
NK091(ke)001:10392: skabs thams cad kyi thog mtha' ril du rigs lnga
NK091(ke)001:10393: tha dad kyi mtshan ma med pas gzung cha gnyis
NK091(ke)001:10394: su ma 'dres par rang rgyud du gzung ba dang
NK091(ke)001:10396: gang gi nyon mongs lnga nas rigs lnga'i bar gyi mtshan ma med tshul rgyas par gsung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:10397: de bzhin du btags pa'i ming gi tha snyad med do //
NK091(ke)001:10398: gdags gzhi ngo bo ma 'dres pa'i rnam pa can du med do //
NK091(ke)001:10399: 'jug pa'i yula lam yang med do //
NK091(ke)001:10401: grub pa mthar phyin ma phyin ma dmigs pas sangs rgyas pa med do //
NK091(ke)001:10402: bshad pa'i 'byung mtha' lnga grol te /
NK091(ke)001:10403: de'i phyir phyis gang du 'gyur bar lung bstan pa med do //
NK091(ke)001:10404: don la ngesa pa rnyed de grub pa mi 'gyur ba'i tha snyad kyang med do //
NK091(ke)001:10405: de ltar med do zhes bkol ba'ang med do //
NK091(ke)001:10406: 'o na ji bzhin pa de'i mtshan nyid ji lta bu zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:10407: bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir te /
NK091(ke)001:10408: snga phyi'i chos so cog gi mtha' ma spangs bral
NK091(ke)001:10409: zhing lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir thams cada nas thams
NK091(ke)001:10410: cad du dbyer med pas byang chub pa nyid do
NK091(ke)001:10411: // 'bras bu'i rtsi bcud yin pa'i phyir snying po nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10412: don ma nor nges par gzung ba nyid yin pa'i phyir de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10413: phyin ci ma log pa lam du shar ba nyid kyi phyir yang dag pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10414: don mthar thug pa nyid yin pa'i phyir nges pa dam pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10415: bya rtsol gyis mi rnyed pa'i phyir gzhan ma yin pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10416: rten dang grogs med pas dngos gzhi mi zin pa'i phyir skye ba med pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10417: mtshan nyid ma nges pas cir yang snang ba'i phyir 'gag pa med pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10418: ye ji bzhin pa bcos bslad med pa'i phyir de bzhin nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10419: 'khrul gzhi ka nas dag pa'i phyir ma nor ba nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10420: mtha' med cing mi g.yo ba'i phyir spros pa dang bral ba'i chos nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10421: mu mtha' las 'das pa'i phyir chos kyi dbyings nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10422: rtog ge bas brtag dpyad las grol ba'i phyir bsam
NK091(ke)001:10423: gyis mi khyab pas rgya che zhing zab pas bsam
NK091(ke)001:10425: dgongs pa don gyi zhe phugs su gyur pa'i phyir yang dag pa'i mtha' nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10426: zhes gsungs te lung bstan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10431: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10432: de ltar de kho na nyid gsang ba dam pa'i
NK091(ke)001:10433: sgra ston pa dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:10434: de kho na nyid stong pa chen por ye nas
NK091(ke)001:10435: mnyam pa nyid du bzhugs pa las grags pas 'khor
NK091(ke)001:10436: skyes bu dam pa de rnams thamsa cad nas thams
NK091(ke)001:10437: cad du rigs chen po lngar dus ril du byang
NK091(ke)001:10438: chub kyi snying po nyid du lhun gyis grub par
NK091(ke)001:10439: mngon du gyur te nges pa dam pa rnyed do
NK091(ke)001:10440: // kye lang ka'i bdag po zhes gsang bdag gis sdud pa po la bos te /
NK091(ke)001:10441: byang chub kyi sems de kho nyid gsang sngags gsang ba dam pa ji bzhin pa de ni /
NK091(ke)001:10442: 'di ltar 'jig rten pas ma shes pas shing brtags par dka' ba /
NK091(ke)001:10443: 'di ltar 'das pas ma shes pas gting dpag dka' la zaba pa /
NK091(ke)001:10444: 'di ltar ngo bo mu mtha' med cing khyab pas rgya che ba /
NK091(ke)001:10445: 'di ltar ngos gzung med cing spyod yul dang bral bas bsam du med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10446: yul du yid la dmigs pas ma khyab pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:10447: gang gisa rtogs shing grub nas nges pa rnyed par daka'a ba ni de lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:10451: de las 'phros te rgyas pa'i dris lan /
NK091(ke)001:10452: de las 'phros te shin tu rgyas pa'i dris lan no //
NK091(ke)001:10457: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10458: le'u drug gis gtan la dbab pa'i gsang ba mchog
NK091(ke)001:10459: gi ngo bo la gtar ka gegs sel gyi tshul
NK091(ke)001:10460: du / de nas yang lang ka'i bdag poos dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:10461: kye gsang ba pa'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:10462: byang chub kyi sems de kho na nyid gsang sngags kyi ngo bo gsang ba dam pa 'di nyid /
NK091(ke)001:10463: skad cig ma'i rgyun dang bcas pa zhig gam /
NK091(ke)001:10464: 'on te rgyun chad de med pa zhig yin /
NK091(ke)001:10465: gal te skad cig gi rgyun dang bacasa pa zhig yin na na /
NK091(ke)001:10466: ye shes chen po skye 'gag dang bcas pa'i skyon du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK091(ke)001:10467: 'on te rgyun chad pa zhig na ni /
NK091(ke)001:10468: lam pa'i ye shes dang sangs rgyas kyi ye shes kyi khyad par dang /
NK091(ke)001:10469: lam gong ma gong ma'i dgongs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10470: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i go 'phang gi khyad par med par 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:10471: zhes de skad ces dris pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10472: gsang ba pa'i bdag posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:10474: byang chub kyi sems de kho na nyid gsang ba
NK091(ke)001:10475: dama pa de ni rgyu rkyen bzhi dang bral bas
NK091(ke)001:10476: ngo bo ma grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:10477: ye shes chen po gang yang snang ba mi 'gog
NK091(ke)001:10478: pa'i phyir yongs rdzogs la skye 'gag gi mtha' gnyis
NK091(ke)001:10479: dag pas skad cig ma meda par ma 'dres pa
NK091(ke)001:10480: la rang bzhin rgyun dang bacasa pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10485: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10486: yang lang ka'i bdag pos dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:10488: gang gi rgyun dang bcas pa lagas /
NK091(ke)001:10489: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:10491: 'gro ba dang 'ong ba med par ye shes rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10492: snying rje rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10493: phrin las rgyun dang bcas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10494: yon tan rgyun dang bacasa pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10495: byin rlabsa rgyun dang bacasa pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10496: smon lam rgyun dang bcas pa'i phyir drug po gdul bya la 'byung bas rgyun ma chad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10497: de ltar skad cig ma'i mi rtag pa dag pas rgyu'i theg pa las 'phags par gsal lo //
NK091(ke)001:10498: de nas nges tshig dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:10500: de dag la cii'i phyir rgyun zhes bya /
NK091(ke)001:10503: dus dang skad cig ma gnyis las /
NK091(ke)001:10504: 'dir sems kyi chos nyid byang chub kyi sems de
NK091(ke)001:10505: dus gsum du rgya ma chad par rgyun gyi rang
NK091(ke)001:10506: bzhin drug tu 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:10507: zhes rgyun gyi ming gi nges tshig grub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10508: 'di rnams rgyas par yongs rdzogs la dkyil 'khor gsum du dbyer med kyang /
NK091(ke)001:10509: ma 'dres pa'i skabs don le'u dgu pa nas bcu
NK091(ke)001:10510: bzhi pa'i bar gyi so so'i nges gsang la brten
NK091(ke)001:10516: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10518: rgyun gyi rang bzhin gang lags /
NK091(ke)001:10521: gang ngo bo 'di ltar mi zin pas dngos po med pa nyid rgyun gyi rang bzhin yin te /
NK091(ke)001:10525: ngo bo ma grub me shel 'dra //
NK091(ke)001:10526: dngos med ye shes mthong bas grol //
NK091(ke)001:10527: gzugs sogs snang ba btags pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:10531: dus gsum du rgya chad phyogs lhung med par drug
NK091(ke)001:10532: nyid bar ma chad pa dang ldan pas rgyun dang
NK091(ke)001:10533: bcas pa'ii chos nyid kyi dbyings byang chub kyi sems
NK091(ke)001:10534: ni / rang bzhin thams cad pa'i phyir ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:10535: med pa nyid thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyu yin pas
NK091(ke)001:10536: de nyid las rnam par rtogs pas gang ltar btags
NK091(ke)001:10537: pa ltar chagsa shing rig pa la phyogs med pas
NK091(ke)001:10538: gang du bltas te bsam par byas pa ltar snang
NK091(ke)001:10539: ni / ba yin kyang / skye bo dang lam
NK091(ke)001:10540: pa dag gis snang ba de nyid yang dag par
NK091(ke)001:10541: 'dod cing yul gyi dngos por 'dzin zhen byed na
NK091(ke)001:10542: don gyi gnas lugs mthong du mi ster bas gcong
NK091(ke)001:10543: rnying sdug bsngal chen po'i nad kyis gdung bar 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:10544: ni / ba yin kyang / la / de nyid
NK091(ke)001:10545: rol pa rang snang du rtogs na che ba'i yon
NK091(ke)001:10546: tan rgyun mi 'achada pa'i snang ba yin te /
NK091(ke)001:10547: zag pa med pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:10548: de 'khor la bstan pa'i tshul ni /
NK091(ke)001:10549: ma rtogs na'ang dgos pa skong bas chos nyid kun
NK091(ke)001:10550: tu rgyun dang bacasa pa yi gsang sngags don gyi
NK091(ke)001:10551: gnas lugs thun mong gi sa pa dang rgyud dag
NK091(ke)001:10552: pas kyang ji bzhin du ma rtogs pas gsang ba
NK091(ke)001:10553: dam pa yin don ma nor ba'i de kho na
NK091(ke)001:10554: nyid gang de / rdo rje sems dpa'i sgron ma
NK091(ke)001:10555: bkod pa'i rgyal ba dam pa gang dag gis gsang
NK091(ke)001:10556: ba'i bdag po sogs skyes bu dam pa gang dag
NK091(ke)001:10557: la gsang mchog de kho na nyid chen por rtogs
NK091(ke)001:10558: pa mthar phyin te de bzhin nyid du brgyud pa
NK091(ke)001:10559: ni chu dwangs pa dang nyi zla'i tshul du ston
NK091(ke)001:10560: pa'i dgongs pa zab mo blo che ba la rang
NK091(ke)001:10561: gsal du snang ba ma gtogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:10562: tshig tu brjod pas ji lta bar bstan du yod pa ma yin te /
NK091(ke)001:10563: dngos po med pa nyid chos thams cad kyi rgyu
NK091(ke)001:10564: ru gyur kyang ngo bo phyogs gcig pa'i snang ba
NK091(ke)001:10565: gang yang med pa'i chos nyid bsam gyis mi khyab
NK091(ke)001:10566: pa dbyings dang 'du 'bral med pa'i ye shes ma
NK091(ke)001:10567: bcos pa de nyid skal ldan gang gis ma nor
NK091(ke)001:10568: bar rtogs pa ni mdor na thun mong min pa'i
NK091(ke)001:10569: bden pa mthong ba nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:10570: 'di la zhib mor dbye na rgyal ba la dgongs brgyud /
NK091(ke)001:10572: gang zag la rna bar brgyud pa'i tshul gyis don dang sbyor shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:10574: gsang bdag dga' rab dpa' bos dam tshig gi klong las /
NK091(ke)001:10575: byang chub sems nyid rnam par dag /ye nas lhun gyis rdzogs pas na //
NK091(ke)001:10576: ngang la gnas pa'ang rnam par dag /de lta min na dri mar bcas //
NK091(ke)001:10578: byang chub kyi sems dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med pa'i
NK091(ke)001:10579: ngo bor ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don la blo
NK091(ke)001:10580: bya rtsol kyi 'du shes btang la ma bcos ji
NK091(ke)001:10581: bzhin pa'i ngang du gnas te brtan pa thob na
NK091(ke)001:10582: snying po byang chub nyid du nges pa rnyed nas
NK091(ke)001:10583: dgongs pa de kho na nyid du rnam par dag
NK091(ke)001:10584: pa yin te / de ltar min na gzhi dbyings rang bzhin rnam dag min par 'gyur la /
NK091(ke)001:10585: de lta bu'i gnas lugs de bzhin nyid la yul
NK091(ke)001:10586: dang ngo bo med pas mtha' gang cir yang mi
NK091(ke)001:10587: snang bar rtog dpyod thams cad dang bral te blos
NK091(ke)001:10588: cir yang bsam du med cing dmigs pa'i yul las
NK091(ke)001:10589: 'das pas 'du shes gang yang ma g.yos na sgom
NK091(ke)001:10590: du med pa bsgom pa'i mchog dam pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10591: gsum pa mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:10595: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10597: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa dam pa gsang ba'i snying po 'di la /
NK091(ke)001:10598: zhes le'u dgu pa sdud la /
NK091(ke)001:10599: mi gnas pas theg pa 'og ma ltar min par
NK091(ke)001:10600: gsang sngags pa ltar thams cad nas thams cad du
NK091(ke)001:10601: gnas par bya'o // zhes le'u bcu pa sdud de de ltar bsgom par gdams pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10603: gang lasa kyi chos kyisa bsgyangs pa rtsol bas ring du song ba rgyu'i theg pa ba rnams kyis /
NK091(ke)001:10604: rnyed dang ma rnyed kyi rim pas bye ba snyed
NK091(ke)001:10605: kyi bskal para las dka' ba dpag tu med pas
NK091(ke)001:10606: 'bad cing brtsal bar byas kyang dam pa ma thob
NK091(ke)001:10608: zhes le'u bcu gcig pa sdud cing /
NK091(ke)001:10609: gsang sngags bya ba med pa'i don gyisa thang cig
NK091(ke)001:10610: yud tsam du'ang dam pa gsang ba 'di la gnyis
NK091(ke)001:10611: su med par mos pa tsam gyis dbugs phyin te
NK091(ke)001:10612: zhes le'u bcu gnyis pa sdud la /
NK091(ke)001:10613: gdon mi za bar dbang dam pa thob ste zhes
NK091(ke)001:10614: le'u bcu gsum pa sdud de lung ston par 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:10615: ro // zhes le'u bcu bzhi pa bsdus pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10616: de'i phyir lang ka'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:10617: ma brtsal na de nyid mthong ma thag tu grub pas gsang ba 'di la gnas par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:10618: dus kun tu 'di lasa mi 'da' bar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:10621: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa rnams /
NK091(ke)001:10622: lan gyi sgo nas blo gros dam pa'i nges pa rnyed par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:10624: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongsa pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:10625: rgyal tshab skyes bu dam pa lnga rigs lnga'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:10626: bar lung bstan pa'ii le'u ste bcu bzhi pa rnam
NK091(ke)001:10627: par bshad pa'o // de dag gis theg pa chen po nges par 'byung ba'i tshul las /
NK091(ke)001:10628: gang gis nges pa rnyed pa'i gtam rgyud brjod pa /
NK091(ke)001:10629: chos kyi phyag rgya'i ye shes rnam par bgros ba
NK091(ke)001:10630: ste byung tshul bstan pa gsum pa'i don gsal bar
NK091(ke)001:10631: bshad de rgyas par bkrol ba'o ////bzhi pa snying po
NK091(ke)001:10632: byang chub tu nges pa'i byung tshul la gsum ste
NK091(ke)001:10640: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10641: spyir le'u 'dis nges don ston la /
NK091(ke)001:10642: nam mkha' rdo rje bgro bar mdzod kyi lan te /
NK091(ke)001:10643: khyad par rtsal 'phangs las stod mthong lam smad sgom lam bdag don /
NK091(ke)001:10644: rgyud gnas lugs las snying po byang chub kyi byung
NK091(ke)001:10645: tshul de kho na nyid kyi lta ba nam mkha'
NK091(ke)001:10646: lta bu nyid rgyas par ston no //
NK091(ke)001:10647: de nas yang sdud pa po lang ka'i bdag posa /
NK091(ke)001:10648: ston pa gsang ba pa'i bdag po la /
NK091(ke)001:10649: sngon du byung ba'ii tshig bcu gnyis pa'i bzhi pa /
NK091(ke)001:10650: snying po byang chub tu nges pa na yang 'byung
NK091(ke)001:10651: zhes lung bstan pa yongs su dri ba dris pa
NK091(ke)001:10652: / kye gsang ba pa'i badga po nyid kyi theg
NK091(ke)001:10653: pa chen po gsang ba dam pa byung ba'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:10654: gtam du brjod pa'i skabs su /
NK091(ke)001:10655: snying po byang chub nyid du nges pa na yang 'byung zhes bkod pa de /
NK091(ke)001:10656: ji lta bu zhig tu nges te byung ba lagas /
NK091(ke)001:10657: lan mdor smras te bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:10659: gang mthar thug gi rgyal ba dam pa dag la
NK091(ke)001:10660: 'jig rten pa'i dus thams cad nas 'jig rten las
NK091(ke)001:10661: 'das pa'i dus thamsa cad du snying po byang chub
NK091(ke)001:10662: kyi ngo bo 'byung 'jug med pa nyid mi snang
NK091(ke)001:10663: bar thams cad du rang snang bar nges pas mnyam
NK091(ke)001:10664: par bzhag ma bzhag mi mnga' ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:10666: snying po byang chub kyi ngo bo bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:10667: gnas tshad dang mtshan nyid dang rang bzhin bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:10668: dris lan mang po'i sgo nas bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:10670: ming gi rnam grangs bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:10671: chos thams cad kyi gzhir bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:10672: snying po byang chub tu nges pa na gdul bya skabs la bab tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:10680: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10681: yang lang ka'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:10683: skyes bu dam pa rigs lnga la sogs pa gang
NK091(ke)001:10684: dag yongs su nges pa rnyed de snying po byang
NK091(ke)001:10686: snga ma'i dus thams cad nas phyi ma'i dus thams
NK091(ke)001:10687: cad du dgongs pa dam pa de nyid ji ltar
NK091(ke)001:10688: snang ste / gang yul du snang ba zhig yin na ni /
NK091(ke)001:10689: ma byung ma skyes par mi rung ba zhig la /
NK091(ke)001:10690: 'on te mi snang ba zhig na ni /
NK091(ke)001:10692: rgyuna gyi snying rje 'byung bar mi rung ba zhig na /
NK091(ke)001:10693: 'di ji ltar yongs su shes par bgyi /
NK091(ke)001:10694: de skad ces dris pa lasa /
NK091(ke)001:10695: gsang ba pa'i bdag posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:10698: snying po byang chub ni chos nyid ji lta ba nyid la /
NK091(ke)001:10699: skyes bu dam pa ni sems nyid de bzhin du rtogs pa de nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:10700: des na chos nyid dang sems nyid tha mi dad
NK091(ke)001:10701: pas snying po byang chub gang yina pa de ni
NK091(ke)001:10702: skyes bu dam pa de nyid la /
NK091(ke)001:10703: skyes bu dam pa gang yin pa de ni snying
NK091(ke)001:10704: po byang chub nyid de ngo bo dbyer med du
NK091(ke)001:10705: bzhugs pas spyod yul dang bral bar nges te skyes
NK091(ke)001:10706: bu dam pa zhes ni dmigs byed du ma mthong
NK091(ke)001:10707: la / snying po byang chub zhes ni yul du
NK091(ke)001:10708: ma dmigs par snang mi snang las grol bas so
NK091(ke)001:10714: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10716: gang spyod yul dang bral te 'dzin cha gang yang
NK091(ke)001:10717: ma mthong la gzung yul cir yang ma dmigsa na
NK091(ke)001:10718: ni / le'u dgu pa dang bcu gcig pa sogs las dam pa rnams kyis gsungs pa ltar na /
NK091(ke)001:10719: gang sems kyi de nyid mthong ba des chos thams cad mthong ngo //
NK091(ke)001:10720: chos thams cad mthong ba des snying po byang chub mthong ngo //
NK091(ke)001:10722: gang de kho na nyid la nges pa rnyed pa
NK091(ke)001:10723: desa sems kyi chos nyid rtogs nas nges pa rnyed
NK091(ke)001:10724: do // zhes gsungs pa rnams las dngos su 'gal bar gyur na /
NK091(ke)001:10725: 'di nyid ji ltar yongs su shes par bgyi /
NK091(ke)001:10726: de skad ces dris pa las /
NK091(ke)001:10728: kye lang ka'i bdag po 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:10729: mig gis gzugsa kyi yul snang gcod pa ltar gang
NK091(ke)001:10730: yang dag pa'i bden don mthong ba ni rdzas kyi
NK091(ke)001:10731: rnam par logs nas rnyed de rtogs shing thob pa
NK091(ke)001:10732: min te / de ni cir yang ma nges pas
NK091(ke)001:10733: gang du'ang mthong byar med pa'i ma mthong ba'i don
NK091(ke)001:10734: de nyid rang gsal du mthonga ba na de kho
NK091(ke)001:10735: na nyid nges pa yin la /
NK091(ke)001:10736: de bas na brjod du med pa'i don dang mthun
NK091(ke)001:10737: par rang rig lhun grub chen po'i dgongs nyamsa rnyed
NK091(ke)001:10738: pa la / bden don mthong ba dang nges pa
NK091(ke)001:10739: rnyed do zhes bla dwags kyi tha snyad tsam du
NK091(ke)001:10740: brjod pa las ngo bo nyid kyis yul dang yul
NK091(ke)001:10741: can du mthong ba med par la bzla ste /
NK091(ke)001:10743: chos can mi mthong chos nyid kyang //
NK091(ke)001:10744: mi mthong sems can sems mi mthong //
NK091(ke)001:10745: sangs rgyas mi mthong gang mthong ba //
NK091(ke)001:10746: des ni yang dag bden pa mthong //
NK091(ke)001:10748: de'i tshul ji lta bu zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:10749: mtha' kun ma spangs par sel bas rnam par dag
NK091(ke)001:10750: pa'i nye lam chen po de kho na nyid dam
NK091(ke)001:10751: pa theg pa'i rgyal po'i gsang sgo rmad du byung
NK091(ke)001:10752: ba gang de nges par snang ba'i skyes bu dam
NK091(ke)001:10753: pa rigs lnga la sogs pa de dag gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:10754: bya ba med pa'i don chen po rab tu nges
NK091(ke)001:10755: pa'i gdeng rnyed de mtha' gang du'ang mi dmigsa pa
NK091(ke)001:10756: yi rig pa gnyis su med pa'i ngang nyid du
NK091(ke)001:10757: gsal ba la yul gyis mi g.yo zhing blo yis
NK091(ke)001:10758: kun tu mi rtog pa yi tshe na mtha' la
NK091(ke)001:10759: mi gnas pa'i rig pa de nyid 'od gsal chos
NK091(ke)001:10760: kyi sku rang byung ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK091(ke)001:10762: der ma zad skad cig ma'i mi rtag pa bral
NK091(ke)001:10763: la rgyu rkyen med pas rang byung rang gsal bas
NK091(ke)001:10764: ye shes ngos bzung med pas nam mkha' lta bu
NK091(ke)001:10765: la che ba'i yon tan thams cad rdzogs pas rnam
NK091(ke)001:10766: pa ma 'dres la chos nyid du yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:10767: pa'i ngang nyid rgyu las mi skye rkyen gyis mi
NK091(ke)001:10768: 'gag par gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid ngo
NK091(ke)001:10769: bo bstan du med pas smra bsam las grol te
NK091(ke)001:10770: ngag gis brjod du med cing yid kyi rtog pa
NK091(ke)001:10771: las 'das pas ma bcos yongs grol chen po'i dgongs
NK091(ke)001:10773: rang byung zhi ba ma bkag chos //
NK091(ke)001:10774: ye nas ma bcos don gyis gsal //
NK091(ke)001:10775: ma skyes rnam dag byang chub sems //
NK091(ke)001:10776: mi gnas ye shes thugs dang mnyam //
NK091(ke)001:10778: de ltar de kho na nyid yul med pa'i yul
NK091(ke)001:10779: chen po ni so so rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:10780: kyi spyod yul rgyal ba'i dgongs pa dam pa yin
NK091(ke)001:10781: te / de la bshad pa bzhin bden pa'i dbus
NK091(ke)001:10782: dang mi bden pa'i mtha' yi tha snyad tsam yang
NK091(ke)001:10783: mi dmigas shing mtshan nyid gza' gtad med pas ji
NK091(ke)001:10784: bzhin pa nyid de thams cad kyi gzhi rtsar gyur
NK091(ke)001:10785: pas snying po byang chub dam pa 'dus ma byas
NK091(ke)001:10786: te / pa ni / rgyal ba kun gyi 'byung
NK091(ke)001:10787: gnas dang bskyed pa'i yum du gnas la de nyid
NK091(ke)001:10788: gang du'ang ma 'gag par gsal bas ma spros kun
NK091(ke)001:10789: la khyab pa'i thig le chen po de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:10790: las ma g.yos par dgongs pa lhan ne bar bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:10791: pa la spyod yul gyi tha snyad tsam yang med
NK091(ke)001:10792: te / pa ni / pa'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:10799: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10800: yang lang ka'i bdag pos dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:10802: byang chub kyi snying po de kho na nyid de
NK091(ke)001:10803: rang snang la dus dang tha dad med pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:10804: na yun ji tsam gyi tshad kyis na gdul bya'i
NK091(ke)001:10806: de'i mtshan nyid dang rang bzhin ci lta bu lags /
NK091(ke)001:10809: mtshan nyid dang rang bzhin bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10814: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10817: gnas pa'i yun gyi dus ni kun tu ma nges te /
NK091(ke)001:10818: lung chen pa'am dbugs chen pas /
NK091(ke)001:10821: zla ba phyed kyi bar du gnas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10823: yud tsam sum cu zhag gcig dang /
NK091(ke)001:10824: yud tsam bco lnga lta bu nyi ma gcig tu gnas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10826: chu tshod bcu lta bu thun dang /
NK091(ke)001:10827: de'i phyed dam yud tsam phyed gsum lta bu thun phyed du gnas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10829: se gol lam yungs kar bskor ba lta bu skad cig dang /
NK091(ke)001:10830: se gol gcig gi yun la drug cu 'da' bas
NK091(ke)001:10831: dus mtha'i skad cig ma brgya dang nyi shu de'i
NK091(ke)001:10832: skad cig /de drug cu thang ciga gcig dang /
NK091(ke)001:10833: de sum cu yud tsam gcig dang /
NK091(ke)001:10834: snga ma gang rung gi rjes thog de ma thag pa'i yun du gnas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10835: sangs rgyas rnams dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid dus gsum
