NK091(ke)001:10836: du 'gyur ba med pas de kho na nyid du
NK091(ke)001:10837: bzhugs pa dang / lung chen pa'am mthar lam dang po pas /
NK091(ke)001:10838: bskal phran brgyad cu gcig tu brtsis pas bskal pa chen por gnas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:10840: bskal pa 'bum dang drug khri sogs kyis tshad med
NK091(ke)001:10841: de bde ba chen por lhun gyis grub pas so
NK091(ke)001:10842: // zhes chos rje dam pa rin po che'i phyag mchan 'di dang bstun na /
NK091(ke)001:10843: mthar lam bar pa nas 'og ma lta bu'i mnyam rjes med cing /
NK091(ke)001:10844: tha ma nas mnyam par bzhag pa dang ma bzhag pa med pa'i dgongs pa thob nas /
NK091(ke)001:10845: de nyid kyis byang chub chen po la sbyor bas
NK091(ke)001:10846: bskal pa'i tshad kyis gzhal ba las 'das par bstan
NK091(ke)001:10848: de dag tu snang ba gnas pa ni gzhi dang lam dang 'bras bu thun mong ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:10856: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10857: ma 'gag pa'i cha yi mtshan nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:10858: ma skyes pa'i cha yi rang bzhin gnyis ye nas dbyer med pas 'di 'drar gzung du med pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10859: yul dang bral bas mi dmigs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10860: ye bdag dang mi phyed pa'i ngang la mnyam pas goms par byasa pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10861: ngo bo nyid grub zin te sgro skur med par gsal bas nges para brtagsa pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10862: ci spyad de'i ngang yin pas yongsa su spyad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10863: 'gro 'ong med kyang rang bzhin sa ma zin pas cir yang snang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:10864: 'khrul pa med cing mi 'gyur bas yin don ma nor bar nges pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10865: ngo bo cir yang shar bas byin rlabs kun nas 'byung ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:10866: ril de nyid las ma 'das pas 'khor 'das thams cad 'dus pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10867: chos thams cad bsnums pas yongs la khyab pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10868: sgo gang yang mi 'gog par rang bzhin kun tu snang bas yongs kyis skye ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:10869: dri ma'i sa bon ngang gis med par mtha' yis ma gos pas rnam par dag pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10870: mtshan nyid dang ngo bo thams cad pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:10871: phan tshun yangs pas snum par byed pas rang bzhin gar yang ma grub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:10872: bya ba med pas bgos pa can du khyab pa med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10873: thams cad de nyid yin pas ma khyab pa meda pa /
NK091(ke)001:10874: mtho dman nam spangs bral ba'i ngo bo la grangs
NK091(ke)001:10875: kyi rim pa ma dmigs pas mtho dman med pa
NK091(ke)001:10876: / snying po byang chub de kho na nyid la
NK091(ke)001:10877: zla med cing kun gyi bran du gyur pas che
NK091(ke)001:10878: / chung med pa / ye ji bzhin pa la
NK091(ke)001:10879: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' gnyis
NK091(ke)001:10880: ma spangs bral bas bzang ngan med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10881: rang byung rgya mtsho'i klong la gang yang ma spangs
NK091(ke)001:10882: shing log rtog gi ming yang ma grub pas yangs
NK091(ke)001:10883: dog med pa / ye nyid 'bras bur lhun gyis
NK091(ke)001:10884: grub pa la rtsol ba'i dus snga phyi bral bas
NK091(ke)001:10886: gnyis kar snang la ma grub pas pho mo med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10887: 'gro ba'i rnam pa'i rgyud du ma nges pas rigs rgyud med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10888: dbyibs dang kha dog thams cad pa la rnam pa ma dmigs pas gzugs med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10889: ci spyad ci mdzad la 'dzin chags ma dmigs pas las dang rnam smin med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10890: ril ye shes chen po'i khob 'og tu chub pas
NK091(ke)001:10891: ye nas yul gyi rnam pa ngang gis bral te
NK091(ke)001:10892: tha snyad ma grub pas phyi nang gi spyod yul
NK091(ke)001:10893: med pa / rkyen bzhi dang bral bas skye ba med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10894: bdag gzhan ma dmigs pas rang rig ma skyes pa la 'pho 'gyur med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10895: rig ma rig dbyer med chen po'i ye shes kyi
NK091(ke)001:10896: nyi ma ye shar la nub pa bral bas mun
NK091(ke)001:10897: snang med pa / rgyun du ma skyes te ril rang rig par gsal bas snga phyi med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10898: snang stong dbyer med gsum gyi tha snyad ye nas bral bas mtha' dbus med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10899: rnam pa med cing gcig dang du ma las grol bas bdag gzhan med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10900: ye grub zin pa la btsal bas mi rnyed par
NK091(ke)001:10901: 'bras bur lhun gyis grub pas rtsol sgrub med pa
NK091(ke)001:10902: / skyon yon dbyer med la bzang ngan med pas blang dora med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10903: rang bzhin gyi gtan tshigs kyis dbyer med kyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:10904: bo nyid la byed pa po dang bral bas ngang
NK091(ke)001:10906: sgrib byed med par 'char nub bral bas yong gis 'od gsal ba /
NK091(ke)001:10907: sel med pas ma bslad pa /
NK091(ke)001:10909: rkyen las ma skyes te tha snyad du grangs kyi
NK091(ke)001:10910: rnam pa sum cu rtsa brgyad dang ldan pa yin
NK091(ke)001:10911: na / ye nas rnam dbye med pa'i mtha' bral
NK091(ke)001:10912: 'od gsal chen po'o zhes dri ba tha ma gnyis
NK091(ke)001:10918: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10920: de lta bu la ci lta bu'i mtshan nyid can dang /
NK091(ke)001:10921: rang bzhin ci ltar yin zhes 'dri bar bya ba ci yod de /
NK091(ke)001:10922: byang chub snying po ni ma grub la mi 'gog
NK091(ke)001:10923: pa'i phyir snang ba dang mi snang ba'o zhes pa'i
NK091(ke)001:10924: tha snyad las 'das te mtshan nyid dang rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:10925: 'di 'drar med par mtha' gang du'ang ma dmigsa pas
NK091(ke)001:10926: so // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:10936: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10937: de ltar na lang ka'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:10938: gang skyes bu dam pa dag snying po byang chub
NK091(ke)001:10939: tu gnas te mi dmigs par lhun gyis grub zin
NK091(ke)001:10940: pa de dag la rdo rje sems dpa' stong pa
NK091(ke)001:10941: nyid de kho na nyid dam pa de las de
NK091(ke)001:10942: dag gis byang chub snying po'i don ci 'dra ba'i
NK091(ke)001:10943: lan thebs sam mi thebs lta zhing bgam pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:10944: / rtogs pa nyug pa'i dgos ched kyis dri ba 'di skad ces bka' stsal pa 'byung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:10945: kye skyes bu dam pa rigs lnga la sogs dag /ces bos nas /
NK091(ke)001:10946: gang snying po byang chub ji lta ba de mthong ngam /
NK091(ke)001:10949: snying po byang chub de kho na nyid du lhun
NK091(ke)001:10950: gyis grub pa de las 'di skad ces lan btab
NK091(ke)001:10951: pa 'byung ngo // kye rdo rje sems dpa' bshes gnyen dama pa lags /
NK091(ke)001:10952: byang chub kyi snying po ni yul du byar med
NK091(ke)001:10953: pa la dgongs nas bdag cag gis ngo bo ci
NK091(ke)001:10954: yang ma yin par bsam pa cir yang mi rtog
NK091(ke)001:10955: pa'i shes rab kyi spyan dam pas dngos mtha' gang
NK091(ke)001:10956: du'ang ma mthong bar dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med pa'i
NK091(ke)001:10959: ji ltar ma mthong bar mthong zhes de nyid kyi tshul dris pas /
NK091(ke)001:10961: dngos por grags so cog der skyas ye thebs pas
NK091(ke)001:10962: byang chub kyi snying po gud du ma mthong bar
NK091(ke)001:10963: chos thams cad 'di 'drar med pa'i ngo bo byang
NK091(ke)001:10964: chub kyi snying por ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su mthong
NK091(ke)001:10969: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:10971: byang chub kyi snying po zhes ngo bo gang la bya /
NK091(ke)001:10973: bshes gnyen dam pa byang chub kyi snying po ni /
NK091(ke)001:10974: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba dgongs pa dam pa la bgyi'o //
NK091(ke)001:10978: dgongs pa dam pa zhes gang la bgyi /
NK091(ke)001:10980: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin gang lagas pa ye
NK091(ke)001:10981: ji bzhin pa dngos po rnams kyi de kho na
NK091(ke)001:10982: nyid do // zhes lan btab bo //
NK091(ke)001:10984: ci'i phyir chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin la gsang
NK091(ke)001:10985: sngags zhes bya zhes gsang sngags kyi nges tshig dris
NK091(ke)001:10987: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin skye ba med pa'i chos nyid ganga lags pa de na /
NK091(ke)001:10988: gtan tshigs kyi chos dgu dang ldan pa'i phyir gsang sngags zhes bya ste /
NK091(ke)001:10991: blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur /
NK091(ke)001:10994: yid kyis bsam du med pa /
NK091(ke)001:10995: kun la khyab pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK091(ke)001:10996: blo yis brtag para dka' zhing /
NK091(ke)001:10997: tshig gis bstan par dka' ba'i phyir lags so zhes bshad zin pa rnams las shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:11003: ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi zhus lan /
NK091(ke)001:11004: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi zhus lan /
NK091(ke)001:11005: rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyi zhus lan no //
NK091(ke)001:11010: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11012: skyes bu dam pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor mthong ngama /
NK091(ke)001:11013: skyes bu dag gis gsol pa /
NK091(ke)001:11014: bshes gnyen dam pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin ni bdag cag gisa ma mthong lagsa so //
NK091(ke)001:11018: ngo bo gang du'ang mi dmigs pa'i slad du'o //
NK091(ke)001:11021: khyed rnams kyis thams cad kyi rang bzhin ma mthong ngam /
NK091(ke)001:11023: bshes gnyen dam pa bdag cag gis mthong lagsa so //
NK091(ke)001:11025: skyes bu dam pa ci lta bur mthong /
NK091(ke)001:11027: thams cad kyi rang bzhin gang lags pa de ni /
NK091(ke)001:11032: rnal ma la dbri bslad med pas ji bzhin pa /
NK091(ke)001:11033: ma nor bas de kho na nyid ye jii bzhin
NK091(ke)001:11034: pa'i dkyila 'khor spros pa dang bral ba'i ngang du
NK091(ke)001:11035: yongs su rdzogs par mthong lags so //
NK091(ke)001:11041: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11043: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ye sangs rgyas pa mthong ngama /
NK091(ke)001:11058: thams cad ma bcos par de bzhin nyid du sangs
NK091(ke)001:11059: rgyas te kun la khyab pa'i slad du rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:11060: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyila 'khor ye shes 'od gsal
NK091(ke)001:11061: gyi ngang du ma 'dres la mtha' dang bral bar
NK091(ke)001:11062: mthong lagsa so // gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:11067: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11069: rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du 'khrul pa'i sems can mthong ngama /
NK091(ke)001:11073: ci'ii phyira ma mthong gsol pa /
NK091(ke)001:11074: ye nas gnyis su mi dmigs pa'i slad du'o //
NK091(ke)001:11082: thams cad ye nas gnyis su med pa'i rtsa ba
NK091(ke)001:11083: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor sems nyid snang stong
NK091(ke)001:11084: dbyer med kyi ngang du rang snang mnyam pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:11086: 'di nyid a nu yo ga'i lta ba mthar thug pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11088: lta ba btsal thabs kyi dris lan /
NK091(ke)001:11089: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi dris lan no //
NK091(ke)001:11091: zhus lan tshan gcig gi 'og nas /
NK091(ke)001:11096: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11098: skyes bu dam pa lta bas gtan la dbab pa'i byang chub kyi snying po gang nas btsal /
NK091(ke)001:11100: gang nasa kyang mi tshol lo //
NK091(ke)001:11104: chos thams cad ye nas byang chub kyi snying po de kho na nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:11105: de las logs su gang na yang mi gansa te
NK091(ke)001:11106: btsal du med pa la 'di na gnas bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:11109: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin rtsol ba med pa'i dris lan /
NK091(ke)001:11110: snying rje chen po bsgom pa'i rtsol ba med pa'i dris lan /
NK091(ke)001:11111: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin rtsol ba med pa'i dris lan no //
NK091(ke)001:11119: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11121: skyes bu dam pa chos nyid mi g.yo ba la blo mi rtog pa nyid du gnas sama /
NK091(ke)001:11123: mi rtog pa la mi 'jug lagsa so //
NK091(ke)001:11126: bdag nyid kyi sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas mi rtog pa nyid pas /
NK091(ke)001:11127: da gdod mi rtog pa la 'jug tu mi 'tshal te yul dang yul can med pa'i slad du'o //
NK091(ke)001:11128: gal te bdag gi sems nyid ye nas rnam par mi rtog pa ma lags na ni /
NK091(ke)001:11129: gdod rnam par mi rtog pa la bdag 'jug pa zhig na /
NK091(ke)001:11130: thams cad ye nasa rnam par mi rtog par gnas pas 'jug mi 'jug las 'das pa'i slad du'o //
NK091(ke)001:11137: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11140: rnam gsum dbyer med pas snying rje chen po kun tu snang ste 'byung bar 'dod dam /
NK091(ke)001:11146: mnyam pa nyid las 'og ma ltar yul la kun tu mi g.yo lags so //
NK091(ke)001:11150: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa nyid kho na bas snying rje'i yul mi dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:11157: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11159: skyes bu dam pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis lha
NK091(ke)001:11160: bskyed nas phrin las bzhis sems can rnams kyi don
NK091(ke)001:11167: don bya ba'i yul med par thams cad ye nas de bzhin nyid kho na'i bslad du'o //
NK091(ke)001:11170: ltos pa'i chos sku mi 'dod pa'i dris lan /
NK091(ke)001:11171: ngo bo lhun gyis grub pa'i dris lan no //
NK091(ke)001:11176: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11179: sgyu 'phrul man chad kyi lugs ltar 'bras bu kun
NK091(ke)001:11180: tu 'od chos kyi sku ru lhun gyis grub par
NK091(ke)001:11186: ltos pa'i chos kyi sku de nyid lam pa'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:11187: du tshogs gnyis las grub pa'am dbyings dang ye shes
NK091(ke)001:11188: 'dus pa las byung ba'i slad du'o //
NK091(ke)001:11189: de'i phyir 'dir dang du mi len te /
NK091(ke)001:11191: rgyas par nges pa don gyi bka' dang dgongs 'grel ltar shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:11193: byang chub snying por lhun gyis grub pa'i dris lan /
NK091(ke)001:11194: zhing khams lhun gyis grub pa'i dris lan /
NK091(ke)001:11195: sangs rgyas kyi sa lhun gyis grub pa'i dris lan no //
NK091(ke)001:11202: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11204: skyes bu dam pa khyed rnams byang chub kyi snying por grub par 'dod dam /
NK091(ke)001:11206: bshes gnyen dam pa yongs su mi 'dod de smin zin to //
NK091(ke)001:11210: gang skyes bu dam pa zhes bgyi ba mya ngan las 'das pa nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:11211: gang sems can sems can zhes bgyi ba 'khor ba'i
NK091(ke)001:11212: srid pa nyid ye nas dbyer med pa'i byang chub
NK091(ke)001:11213: kyi snying po las ma g.yos pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11214: de'i phyir chos thams cad kyang chos nyid de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:11215: nyid ma bcos pa'i ngang las ma g.yos par yang
NK091(ke)001:11218: lta ba'i zhus lan gyi 'og nas /
NK091(ke)001:11222: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11224: skyes bu dam pa rnams sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams yongs su bgrod par 'dod dam /
NK091(ke)001:11226: yongs su bgrod par mi bgyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11228: ci'i phyir bgrod par mi byed /
NK091(ke)001:11230: gnas lugs ji bzhin par rtogs nas sems can gyi
NK091(ke)001:11231: ris mtha' dag ye nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams
NK091(ke)001:11232: rnam par dag pa nyid kyi slad du'o //
NK091(ke)001:11238: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11240: skyes bu dam pa sa bcu po rnams yongs su bgrod par 'dod dam /
NK091(ke)001:11242: yongs su bgrod par mi bgyid lags so //
NK091(ke)001:11246: thams cad sangs rgyas kyi sa la ma bgrod par ye nas phyin pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:11248: des na ma bcos rdzogs pa'i sa //
NK091(ke)001:11249: rang byung lhun rdzogs khyad par snang //
NK091(ke)001:11250: sa yi khyad par ci bstan kyang //
NK091(ke)001:11251: ma bcos rdzogs pa'i sa la 'dus //
NK091(ke)001:11257: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11260: snying po byang chub de dpe gang gisa bstan /
NK091(ke)001:11263: phyogs thams cad nas mthun pa'i dpe ni gang yang ma mchis te /
NK091(ke)001:11264: dpe rnams ni phyogs re ba yin la don ni phyogs med yin pas /
NK091(ke)001:11265: dpe gang gis kyang bskrun du ma mchis pa lags so //
NK091(ke)001:11267: dpes mtshon du ye med dam /
NK091(ke)001:11269: 'on kyang cung zad tsam du phyogs re nas mthun
NK091(ke)001:11270: pa'i dpe bzung na dpe'i rtsa ba bcu bzhi 'di
NK091(ke)001:11271: lta ste / mtha' dbus med par khyab la ma
NK091(ke)001:11272: 'gag pas dus thams cad par gyur pa nam mkha'
NK091(ke)001:11273: lta ste / lta bu dang / phyogs ris med
NK091(ke)001:11274: par kun la gsal zhing blang dor med pas nyi
NK091(ke)001:11276: rtog pa med par dgos 'dod 'byung la zad 'phel
NK091(ke)001:11277: med cing mun pa sel te chu dwangs pas yid
NK091(ke)001:11278: bzhin nor bu rin po che dbang gi rgyal po
NK091(ke)001:11279: klu'i go cha lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11280: thog mthar mi 'gyur zhing g.ya' 'am dri ma med pas rin po che gser lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11281: mun pa bsal nas dngos po ston zhing gsal bar mthong bas sgron ma lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11282: nyon mongs pa ye shes su bsgyur zhing sdug bsngal
NK091(ke)001:11283: bde ba chen por bsgyur bas dug 'gyur rtsi lta
NK091(ke)001:11284: bu dang / 'di la dug shes nas 'bros pa dang 'dra ba'i nyan thos /
NK091(ke)001:11285: mi reg pa dang 'dra ba'i rang rgyal /
NK091(ke)001:11286: bsrung ba 'chang bas mi gnod pa dang 'dra ba'i byang sems /
NK091(ke)001:11287: sngags kyis bcom pa dang 'dra bar sku gsung thugs lha'i cha lugs can phyi pa /
NK091(ke)001:11288: sman sngags kyis bdud rtsir bsgyur ba dang 'dra ba'i nang pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11289: zhes pa'i stong thun kyang chos rje'i phyag mchan na bzhugs so //
NK091(ke)001:11290: rtog pa ye shes kyi klong du bsgyur bas gser 'gyur gyi rtsi lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11291: rang bzhin gyis dri ma med cing mi 'gyur bas bee d+aur+ya lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11292: gting zab cing yon tan gyi rlabs la zad 'phel med pas rgya mtsho chena po lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11293: ngo bo mi 'gyur la sel med cing gnyen pa
NK091(ke)001:11294: dang bral te mi 'jig pas rdo rje'i snying po
NK091(ke)001:11295: lta bu dang / 'di la phyag dpe la lar /
NK091(ke)001:11296: sel med pa'am mi 'gyur bas rdo'i snying po zhes kyang bzhugs /
NK091(ke)001:11297: rnam rtog zil gyis gnon pas rtsal gyisa gnon pa seng ge lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11298: shes rab kyis 'jug tu med pa'i tshul gyis 'jug
NK091(ke)001:11299: ste rig cing gsal la bar chad med pas yul
NK091(ke)001:11300: la 'jug pa rnam shes lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11301: sel dang bral te thams cad chos nyid gcig tu
NK091(ke)001:11302: 'khyil bas gser rdo rin po che lta bu dang
NK091(ke)001:11303: / ma 'dres par gsal la stong pas mngon par
NK091(ke)001:11304: spro ba skyed pa ngo mtshar gyi rdzas 'ja' tshon
NK091(ke)001:11305: nam ri mo'i rnam pa lta bu lags so //
NK091(ke)001:11306: de dag chos ngu dang ldan pa'i dper gyur pas
NK091(ke)001:11307: phal cher 'chad par 'gyur yang kun gyi don la'ang
NK091(ke)001:11312: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11314: skyes bu dam pa snying po byang chub de mtshon pa'i ming ji ltar grags /
NK091(ke)001:11316: bshesa gnyen dam pa ming na tshig gi bla dwagsa te /
NK091(ke)001:11317: ming la nges pa gang yang ma mchis pas /
NK091(ke)001:11318: ming tshig rnams ni mtha' can yin phyir /
NK091(ke)001:11319: don ni mtha' dbus med pa la smra brjod dang bral ba lagsa so //
NK091(ke)001:11321: ye ming gisa mtshon du med dam /
NK091(ke)001:11323: gang yongs su mi dmigs pa las /
NK091(ke)001:11324: blo chung ba la phyogs re nas brjod pa'i dbang du mtshon na /
NK091(ke)001:11325: ming gi rnam grangs su btags pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:11326: tha dad pa ji ltar btags pa de ltar chagsa
NK091(ke)001:11327: pa lags pas mtshan gyi khyad par bcu drug tu'ang
NK091(ke)001:11328: grags te / mtha' dbus med pas snying po byang chub nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:11329: gzhan du med pas de nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:11330: ma nor bas de kho na nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:11331: ma bcos pas de bzhin nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:11332: rnal mar nges pas ji bzhin pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:11333: ma 'khrul bas ma nor ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11334: ye nas gnas pas ma bcos pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:11335: bya rtsol gyis mi rnyed pas gzhan ma yin pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:11336: spros pa bral bas chos nyid dang /
NK091(ke)001:11337: mu mtha' med pas chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK091(ke)001:11338: rtog ge bas mi rtogs pas bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:11339: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs yin pas yang dag pa'i mtha' dang /
NK091(ke)001:11340: zab cing rtogs par dka' ba'i yon tan dang ldan pas gsang sngags dang /
NK091(ke)001:11341: don dang mi 'bral ba'i yon tan dang ldan pas gzungs sngags dang /
NK091(ke)001:11342: don rig pa'i yon tan dang ldan pas rig sngags dang /
NK091(ke)001:11343: ma shong ba med pas theg pa chen po zhes yongs su grags pa lagas so //
NK091(ke)001:11344: 'o na bshad pa dang 'chad pa'i dri lan bzhi
NK091(ke)001:11345: bcu rtsa bzhi po 'di dag ston pa dang 'khor
NK091(ke)001:11346: gang gis gang la gsungs zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:11347: phyag na rdo rje skyes bus ni 'khor la sngar ston pa las thos pa'i don brjod la /
NK091(ke)001:11348: 'di nyid rdo rje sems dpa' chen po dang /
NK091(ke)001:11349: rigs lnga lta bur snang ba'ang stong pa nyid las
NK091(ke)001:11350: sgra dus gcig tu snang ba'i phyir rdo rje 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:11351: pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i ngo bos gnyi
NK091(ke)001:11353: de la skyes bu dang ston pa yang snying po
NK091(ke)001:11354: byang chub nyid kyis phyir gsang ba pos kyang ston
NK091(ke)001:11355: pa rdo rje 'chang gcig las thos par yang bsnyad
NK091(ke)001:11356: do // drug pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:11363: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11365: skyes bu dam pa snying po byang chub de ji ltar snang /
NK091(ke)001:11367: snying po byang chub ni ma skyes pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:11368: skad cig kyang dngos po dang mtha' gang du'ang snang
NK091(ke)001:11371: ci gang du'ang mi snang ngam /
NK091(ke)001:11373: 'on kyang chad pa lta bu min te thams cad
NK091(ke)001:11374: kyi dngos gzhi bas ji ltar bltas pa de ltar
NK091(ke)001:11375: snang lagsa so // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:11376: cir char 'jug pa lam gyi gzhir bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:11377: lam klong du gyur pa yon tan gyi gzhir bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11382: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11383: byang chub sems kyi mtshan nyid bdun cu rtsa gsum gyis sems snang ba'i chos grub par byed de /
NK091(ke)001:11384: snying po byang chub ni rgya chad phyogs lhung thams
NK091(ke)001:11385: cad dang bral te ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:11387: snying po byang chub de ji ltar yongs su snang /
NK091(ke)001:11390: snying po byang chub kyi sems ni bshad pa ltar
NK091(ke)001:11391: ril bsnums te kun la khyab pas rnam pa thams
NK091(ke)001:11392: cad pa'i phyir phyogs gcig pa'i rnam pa kun dang
NK091(ke)001:11393: bral bas snang ba med pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11394: de ni mi mthun pa dang mthun pa'i gtan tshigs gnyis las /
NK091(ke)001:11395: mi mthun pa'i gtan tshigs kyis bstan pa ste rjes su mthun pa dag kyang sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:11396: ye nas bdag nyid chen po ma bskungs par lkog
NK091(ke)001:11397: tu ma gyur pas gang du yang ma sbas la
NK091(ke)001:11398: / mig gis mig mi mthong ba ltar /
NK091(ke)001:11399: de nyid lhan skyes dang kun brtags gnyis kyis bsgribs
NK091(ke)001:11400: te ji bzhin du mthong ba med pa nyid do
NK091(ke)001:11401: // dus gsum du rang rig dang mi phyed pas
NK091(ke)001:11402: ye nas ma bral la rgyal bu dwa'u ltar bdag
NK091(ke)001:11403: zhal ma mthong bas ngo ma shes pa nyid do
NK091(ke)001:11404: // // so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis ngo
NK091(ke)001:11405: bo mi zin pas brtags na ma mthong la ji
NK091(ke)001:11406: ltar bsam pa ltar 'byung bas cir yang snang ba
NK091(ke)001:11407: // // nyid do // ngo bo mi mthun pa
NK091(ke)001:11408: tha dad du snang bas sna tshogs su snang yang
NK091(ke)001:11409: de nyid rang rig pa nyid du rdzogs te mtha'
NK091(ke)001:11410: grol bas dngosa po med pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11411: ji snyed 'khor ba'i kha brgyud de bskal par 'khyams
NK091(ke)001:11412: kyang gzhan ma yin pa'i phyir ma brlag ma phye
NK091(ke)001:11413: bas stor bral meda pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11414: mtshan rtog ji snyed pa las ma bkol bar sna
NK091(ke)001:11415: tshogs bsgo yang byang chub sems kyi ngo bo rnam
NK091(ke)001:11416: pa'i phyogs su ma g.yos pas 'gyur ba med pa
NK091(ke)001:11417: nyid do // dngos gzhi btsal na cha tsam mi
NK091(ke)001:11418: rnyed pas rdul cha med par snod bcud la son
NK091(ke)001:11419: bas snang srid khyab pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11420: ngo bo mtha' gsum dang bral bas stong pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:11421: las ji snyed du snang bas sna tshogs 'byung ba
NK091(ke)001:11422: nyid do // ngo bo'i rnam pa mi rnyed pas
NK091(ke)001:11423: dngos gzhi med par thang snyad ji snyed kyi ming
NK091(ke)001:11424: du grags pas cir btagsa chags pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11425: grub mtha'i phyogs kyis brtsal gnas med para theg pa
NK091(ke)001:11426: so so'i ji ltar gnyer ba'i 'bras bur snang bas
NK091(ke)001:11428: dbyibs dang kha dog gi rnam pa bral bas gzugs
NK091(ke)001:11429: mtshan med par dngos po bzang ngan ji ltar mnos
NK091(ke)001:11430: pa ltar snang bas cir bltas snang ba nyid do
NK091(ke)001:11431: // ngo bo med la yul dang bral bas ci
NK091(ke)001:11432: yang med par ril ma 'dres rdzogs par gsal bas
NK091(ke)001:11433: cir yang rig pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11434: mtha' ma dmigs la ma 'gags pas khyab gdal 'ub
NK091(ke)001:11435: chub chen por gcig dang du mas grol bas gcig
NK091(ke)001:11437: mtha' gang gis kyang ma reg la cha med nyid pas kun bral nyag gcig la /
NK091(ke)001:11438: ril ma bkol bar lhun gyis grub pas ci ma spangs pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11439: ril rang byung ye shes kyi klong du gsal bas
NK091(ke)001:11440: phyi dang nang med par de nyid ma spangs bral
NK091(ke)001:11441: bas kun tu nang nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11442: mdzad pa dang yon tan grangs las 'das par shar
NK091(ke)001:11443: bas mtha' yas byung yang rgyun chad pa dang 'phel
NK091(ke)001:11444: 'grib bral bas zad pa med pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11445: ngo bo blo dang ming gis ma brtags ma bsnyad
NK091(ke)001:11446: de bsam brjod med pas ma bzung ma btags kyang
NK091(ke)001:11447: blo dang sgra brjod ma bkol bas gang du chags
NK091(ke)001:11448: pa nyid do // dngos po dang ther zug las
NK091(ke)001:11449: grol bas gdos pa med par ngo bo nyid mi
NK091(ke)001:11450: 'gyur bas rtag par lhung ba nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11451: 'di ni ther zug dang rgyun gyi rtag pa gnyis
NK091(ke)001:11452: las 'das pas ji bzhin pa 'dus ma byas pa'i
NK091(ke)001:11454: la shan lta ba'i me long las /
NK091(ke)001:11455: gang gis don 'di mthong gyur na //
NK091(ke)001:11456: de bzhin gshegs pa kho na'i phyir //
NK091(ke)001:11457: ji bzhin pa yi dngos de bzhin //
NK091(ke)001:11458: rtag gnyis grol ba'i ye shes sku //
NK091(ke)001:11459: ngo bo nyid rtag brjod las 'das //
NK091(ke)001:11461: sus kyang ma btegs pas 'degs pa med par rang
NK091(ke)001:11462: bzhin gsal la ma bsgribs pas mkha' la 'gro ba
NK091(ke)001:11463: nyid do // bgrod pa'i thabs la ma brten pas
NK091(ke)001:11464: yan lag med par dbye ba med pa'i sa nyid
NK091(ke)001:11465: non pas sa rnams bgroda pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11466: chos nyid la 'gro 'ong med pas gar yang ma
NK091(ke)001:11467: g.yos la thams cad du son te ril gyi bdag
NK091(ke)001:11468: nyid du gyur pas kun tu phyin pa nyid do
NK091(ke)001:11469: // g.yo ba bral bas bskyod med par cir yang snang bas thogsa meda myur ba nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11470: ji snyed du snang bas tha dad spros kyang rang
NK091(ke)001:11471: byung rgya mtshor gcig pa'i phyir te 'gre ldog spyi
NK091(ke)001:11472: tshugs gar 'gros kyang snying po'i don las mi 'da'
NK091(ke)001:11473: bas gcig las ma g.yosa pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11474: ngo bo thig le chen por 'gro 'ong ye bral
NK091(ke)001:11475: bas gcig las ma g.yos par de nyid ril gyi
NK091(ke)001:11476: dngos gzhir gyur te ci ltar shar bas sna tshogs
NK091(ke)001:11479: chos thams cad kyi gzhir bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:11480: mya ngan las 'das pa'i gzhir bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:11481: de dang 'dra ba'i gzhir bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:11482: bsnyen bsgrub kyi gzhir bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11487: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11488: tshig gcig kyang gtan tshigs dang don phyed mar 'grel te /
NK091(ke)001:11493: snying po byang chub kyi don la lam pa thams
NK091(ke)001:11494: cad gnas te phyin pa med par phyin pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:11495: gyis 'jug pasa dus gsum gyi shul lam ma nor
NK091(ke)001:11496: ba nyid do // dngos po ngan pa gang yang
NK091(ke)001:11497: ma bkol ba'am ma spangs par de'i ngo bor snang
NK091(ke)001:11499: chos nyid ye nas ma bral yang ngo ma shes
NK091(ke)001:11500: par 'khrul te nor bar snang ba'ang de nyid yin
NK091(ke)001:11502: nang gi chu bo skye rga na 'chi bzhi las
NK091(ke)001:11503: sgrol ba po yang de nyid mthong ba yin pas
NK091(ke)001:11505: sa dang theg pa'i ngo bor shar te myang 'das la rnam par bskyod pasa bgroda pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11506: ngo bo bde chen nyid la gnyis su dmigs pa med pasa chos sku chen por byang chub bo //
NK091(ke)001:11507: dran rig ji snyed par rang shar te rnam pa sna tshogs su nges pas sems nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11508: ril ma 'dres par gsal te shes bya kun la mkhas pas shes rab bo //
NK091(ke)001:11509: thams cad kyi ngo bo gsal la ngang las mi g.yo bas ting nge 'dzin no //
NK091(ke)001:11510: ril ma bgrod par 'gro 'ong bral te ji bzhin par phyin pasa gansa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11511: 'gran gyi do zla med pasa rab nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11512: ya mtshan lnga'i bdag nyid ngo mtshar ba'i gnas su gyur pas mchog nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11513: che btsan gcig pur byung ste rnam par 'phagsa pas phul nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11514: snying po byang chub la dbang du byed pa'i rje
NK091(ke)001:11515: bo dang zil gyis gnon pa'i gnyen po med pas
NK091(ke)001:11516: bla na med pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11517: mu mtha' bral te gting mi rnyed pas zab pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11518: bsal blos ngo bor mi reg ste dapaga tu med pasa na gab pa'i phyir gsang ba nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11519: ngo bo gzung dka' zhing phra ste lta ba po
NK091(ke)001:11520: la phyogs su mi mngon pas mi gsal ba nyid
NK091(ke)001:11521: do // dngos po gnyis pa ril mi 'gog par thams cad 'byung bas chos so //
NK091(ke)001:11522: gzhi lam mthar thug pas ngo bo ma barjesa te mi 'gyur bas de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11523: bsgrub bya'i mchog tu gyur pa'i go 'phang gi sa nyid non pas byang chub sems dpa' 'o //
NK091(ke)001:11524: zhen pa gnyis kyi skad cig ma ma spangs bral
NK091(ke)001:11525: te rgyun sangs shing rnam kun mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:11526: shes bya'i chos so cog la khyab pas sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:11527: nyid do // thams cad gnas pa'i rten gzhir gyur pasa rtsa ba nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11532: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11533: ji bzhin pa'i de kho na nyid shes rab chen
NK091(ke)001:11534: po'i dbyings las 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad shar
NK091(ke)001:11535: zhing skyed pasa ma'am yum nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11536: gzhi de las thabs chen po'i ye shes rang byung zhing snang bas pha'am yab nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11537: rgyal ba'i gdung rgyud yin la byang chub chen po 'dzin pas sras nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11538: gzhan la rag ma las par ye nas rang byung
NK091(ke)001:11539: ba nyid pas dbang ril gyi sdong po'i bdag nyid
NK091(ke)001:11540: do // dus gsum du mi 'gyur zhing ma chad
NK091(ke)001:11541: par de bzhin nyid pas gdung chen po nyid do
NK091(ke)001:11542: do // // dal pos mchongs kyang khang thog ste
NK091(ke)001:11543: mgyogs pas bros kyang de las gzhan du mi phyin
NK091(ke)001:11544: par 'da' bar dka' basa thugsa dam chen po nyid
NK091(ke)001:11545: do // // do // rgyal ba dang lam la
NK091(ke)001:11546: gnas pa ril zhe'am dngos po ril des bzung ste
NK091(ke)001:11547: rnam para 'tsho bas srog nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11548: rgyal ba'i yon tan dang 'khor ba'i longs spyod ril
NK091(ke)001:11549: zad pa med par shar te zad mi shes pas
NK091(ke)001:11551: ril gyi re ba skongs te 'dod pa sgrubs pasa nor nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11552: dus gsum du rgyun gyis 'byung ba'i snying rjesa kun
NK091(ke)001:11553: gyi don mdzad cing bya ba byed pas bran nyid
NK091(ke)001:11554: do // de kho na nyid kyi rten gzhi mi
NK091(ke)001:11555: 'gyur bar rnam para brjid pa'i lhun por bzhugs pas
NK091(ke)001:11556: do // sku nyid do // brjod med kyi ngang
NK091(ke)001:11557: las smra brjod kun 'byung ste don 'jal bar byed
NK091(ke)001:11559: ril ma 'dres rdzogs par gsal la mi rtog par thams cad mkhyen pasa thugs nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11560: dngos grub dang 'bras bu'i gzhir gyur te 'dod rgu 'byung basa yon tan nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11561: thams cad kyi don rgyun chad med par mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:11562: chen po'i bya ba byed cing don mdzad pas phrin
NK091(ke)001:11563: las nyid do // gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:11567: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11568: 'dod pa sna tshogs pa'i yul ril la kun tu 'gro bas 'dod pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11569: 'khor 'das gnyis la yul dang bral bar rol te
NK091(ke)001:11570: de nyid la spyod pas longs spyod chen po nyid
NK091(ke)001:11571: do // ril gyi rgyur gyur pa spyad bya nyid du snang bas yo byad chen po'o //
NK091(ke)001:11572: 'dod pa'i rkyen ril dbyings la rdzogs te dgos pa tshang bas tshogs chen po'o //
NK091(ke)001:11573: bya ba ma spangs la bya ba brtsal med pa'i snying por gnas pas don thams cad grub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11574: dngos la cir yang shar te sna tshogs su 'phrul
NK091(ke)001:11575: yang mtshan nyid ma nges pas cho 'phrul nyid do
NK091(ke)001:11576: // sku phyag rgya la sogs par rkyen la rag
NK091(ke)001:11577: ma las par shar te mtshan mar byung bas phyag
NK091(ke)001:11578: // rgya nyid do // bzhi pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:11585: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11586: go 'phang logs nas mi gnyer bas gzhi'i phyir gzhan nas mi tshol bas bsnyen pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11587: de las thob bya rang rig pa nyid yin pas
NK091(ke)001:11588: don gzhan nas ma byung ba'i phyir rang las byung
NK091(ke)001:11589: bas nye ba'i bsnyen pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11590: rgyu 'bras gnyis su med par 'bras bu nyid lam yin pa'i phyir snying po nyid pasa bsgrub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11591: grub mtha' chen por rang nyid ye grub zin pa'i phyir 'bras bu nyid pas bsgrub pa chen po'o //
NK091(ke)001:11596: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11597: de lta bas na gzhi lam mtha' ril du snying
NK091(ke)001:11598: po byang chub 'gro 'ong med par snang bar la
NK091(ke)001:11600: skyes bu dam pa dag /byang chub kyi snying po de ji ltar bsgrub /
NK091(ke)001:11602: bsgrub tu ma mchis lagas so //
NK091(ke)001:11606: gnas lugs ye nas 'bras bu ye sangs rgyas par
NK091(ke)001:11607: grub pa gang de byang chub snying po nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:11611: ye grub zin pa'i gtan tshigs bzhi ste 'bras bu gzhan nas mi 'byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11612: rang rig pa las 'byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11613: rtsol ba'i bya brtsal med pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:11614: rgyu rkyen med par rang byung ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:11615: ye nas nyams su lon pa nyid du nges pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11616: zhes don de lta dpe de ltar stong pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:11617: chen po snying po byang chub kyi byin rlabs lasa
NK091(ke)001:11618: sgra byung bas / de kho na nyid de kho
NK091(ke)001:11619: na nyid du nges par don gyi ngo bo las
NK091(ke)001:11620: gzhan pa med pas thams cad nas thams cad du
NK091(ke)001:11621: snying po byang chub nyid las ma gtogs pa ganga
NK091(ke)001:11624: snying po byang chub tu nges pa dngos /
NK091(ke)001:11625: ru tra btul ba'i tshe sku lngar bzhengs par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:11626: sku lngar bzhengs pa'i tshul bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11631: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11633: de ltar skyes bu dam pa dngos po'i gnas lugs
NK091(ke)001:11634: snying po byang chub nyid du nges pa de dag
NK091(ke)001:11635: chos nyid bde ba chen po kun tu mi g.yo
NK091(ke)001:11636: ba'i ngang lasa rnam par mi rtog pa nyid du
NK091(ke)001:11637: zhi ba lhan ne bar gnas pa de'i tshe de'ii
NK091(ke)001:11638: dus na dgongs pa chos nyid kyi nam mkha' la
NK091(ke)001:11639: 'grel pa ye shes kyi nyi ma gdal te thams
NK091(ke)001:11640: cad de kho na nyid du ngees par gdengs su
NK091(ke)001:11641: gyur te ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:11647: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11648: snying po byang chub tu nges pa dang gdul bya'i skabs la bab pa dus gcig pa'i khungs te /
NK091(ke)001:11649: thub dka' gzhon nu dang skyes bu lnga dag ji
NK091(ke)001:11650: bzhin par son zhing nges pa rnyed pa de'i tshe
NK091(ke)001:11651: de'i dus ni dngos su na ru tra snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:11652: bskal pa'i dus nyid de snying po byang chub ni
NK091(ke)001:11653: dus gsum ma 'gags bral ba la tshe skabs med
NK091(ke)001:11654: kyang gdul bya'i ngo btsan no //
NK091(ke)001:11655: gdul bya la sngon gyi gleng gzhi smos pa'ang 'di'i phyir te /
NK091(ke)001:11656: gsang sngags 'byung ba'i rgyu khyad par du gyur pa thar pa nag po /
NK091(ke)001:11657: rkyen khyad par du gyur pa gsang sngags kyi spyod pa /
NK091(ke)001:11658: rten stobs khyad par du gyur pa thub dka' gzhon nu /
NK091(ke)001:11659: las khyad par du gyur pa sbyor sgrol rang ka ma /
NK091(ke)001:11660: 'bras bu khyad par du gyur pa ru tra nyid
NK091(ke)001:11661: gdul bar bya ba'i zhing khyad par du byung ba
NK091(ke)001:11662: / 'jig rten gyi khams gsum po sreg para byed pa /
NK091(ke)001:11663: khro bo'i tshul can gdul bya'i dus la nges par bab pa'i tshe /
NK091(ke)001:11664: 'di byung bas 'di 'byung pa'i phyogs dus kun gyi
NK091(ke)001:11665: sangs rgyas thams cad snying po byang chub gang na
NK091(ke)001:11666: bar 'dus nasa zhes pa gdul bya'i ngo ste ngo
NK091(ke)001:11667: bo nyid der ma 'dres rdzogs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11668: des na gdul bya'i ngor 'og min na bzhugs pa de dag gis /
NK091(ke)001:11669: ru tra 'dul ba'i phyir thub dka' gzhon nu byang
NK091(ke)001:11670: chub snying po na bzhugs pa sku lnga'i sgo nas
NK091(ke)001:11671: bskul ba dang / skyes bu tha dad la so
NK091(ke)001:11672: so nas bskul ba ni spyi dang khyad par gyi
NK091(ke)001:11673: dbang ste gnyis ka dang thun mong du 'gyur bas
NK091(ke)001:11674: skyes bu dam pa de dag /la la zhes bkar
NK091(ke)001:11675: ba ni skyes bu dang bskul byed thun mong du
NK091(ke)001:11676: sbyar te bla na med pa'i byang chub chen por
NK091(ke)001:11677: ngo bo nyid kyi skur 'tshang rgya ba las bzhengs
NK091(ke)001:11678: par rnam para bskul ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11679: la la ni gsang ba'i sku rol pa nyi shu
NK091(ke)001:11680: rtsa lnga bu la sogs pa'i cho 'phrul chen pora
NK091(ke)001:11681: mdzod cig par rnam par bskul ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11682: la la ni sprul pa'i sku rdzu 'phrul gyi bya
NK091(ke)001:11683: ba'am cho ga rdzogs par gyis shig par rnam par
NK091(ke)001:11684: bskul ba dang / la la ni longs spyod rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:11685: pa'i sku'i sgo nas ting nge 'dzin gyi dgongs pa
NK091(ke)001:11686: dang sku'i mdzad pa nyid kyis don mdzod cig par
NK091(ke)001:11688: la la ni chos sku mtha' dang bral ba'i ye
NK091(ke)001:11689: shes chen po'i sgo nas rnam grol rig pasa chos
NK091(ke)001:11690: nyid kyi skur bzhengs par rnam par bskul bar gyur
NK091(ke)001:11695: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11696: de ltar bskul ba desa gdul bya'i snang ngor gang
NK091(ke)001:11697: snying po byang chub stong pa nyid chen po gang
NK091(ke)001:11698: na ba rang don gyi dgongs pa mi g.yo ba
NK091(ke)001:11699: lasa langs te gzhan don du gzugs kyi sku rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:11701: rnam par sprul pa gnyis su rnam par bkod pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:11702: ji lta ji ltar rdo rje sems dpa'i de kho
NK091(ke)001:11703: na nyid nges pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:11704: so so'i gnas su sgron ma yongs su bkod de
NK091(ke)001:11705: chos ston pas byung tshul las bshad pa ltar kun
NK091(ke)001:11706: tu snang bas de'i don du'ang 'gyur te zhi khro
NK091(ke)001:11708: de dag gi don mdzad lugs ci zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:11709: 'di ltar yongs su dag pa ngo bo nyid chos kyi skur bzhugs pas gdul bya med na yang /
NK091(ke)001:11710: lhun gyis grub pa de nyid gdul bya la mtshan
NK091(ke)001:11711: tha dad par btags pa'i sangs rgyas brjod pa las
NK091(ke)001:11712: 'das par grags shing sku snang ba tha dad pa
NK091(ke)001:11713: mtha' dag /rgyal ba'i zhing khams bshad pa bzhin mtshan
NK091(ke)001:11714: tha dad par bkod pas 'jig rten gyi 'dzam bu
NK091(ke)001:11715: gling rnams na / sprul pa 'khor longs sgyur ba'i
NK091(ke)001:11716: rgyal po lta bu cha byad tha dad pa dag
NK091(ke)001:11717: gis theg pa de nyid don bcu ston pa dang
NK091(ke)001:11718: gling rnams na / / lha gnas gsum tha dad par /
NK091(ke)001:11719: gtsang ma'i rigs kyi 'og min chen po rdzogs longs spyod pa rigs lnga'i rgyal ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11721: sprul pa'i rgyal tshab chos kyi rgyal po dam pa tog dkar po dang /
NK091(ke)001:11722: sum cu rtsa gsum du sprul pa'i bargya byin lha'i
NK091(ke)001:11723: bla ma lta bu tha dad pa dag gis chos
NK091(ke)001:11725: srid pa tha ma'i dus tha dad para mi yul
NK091(ke)001:11726: la sogs pa la rgyal ba'i cho 'phrul las rgyun
NK091(ke)001:11727: gcod pa'i mdzad pa lnga tha dad para snang ba
NK091(ke)001:11728: dang / yum gyi b+ha ga dang gsang ba'i rdo
NK091(ke)001:11729: rje gnyis 'phrad pa'i dbu zhabs bde ba chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:11730: ros gang ba yan man du dbang bsgyur nas snang
NK091(ke)001:11731: ba'i gnas yum gtsug tor 'khor los sgyur ba'i lhums
NK091(ke)001:11733: gsang ba'i sku thig le gnyis su med pa'i bde
NK091(ke)001:11734: ba chen po 'dus pa'i sku las mdzad pa cir
NK091(ke)001:11735: yang mdzad de tha dad par snang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11736: mi'i gnas zhing khams tha dad pa na /
NK091(ke)001:11737: sprul pa'i mtshan sgron ma bkod pa lta bur tha dad par snang bas don mdzad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:11738: don thams cad grub pa lta bu'i thugs 'og min
NK091(ke)001:11739: du sangs rgyas pas dgongs pa snying po byang chub
NK091(ke)001:11740: chen po na bzhugs te mi g.yo ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11741: de'i sku tha dad pa 'dzam bu'i gling gi 'jig
NK091(ke)001:11742: rten tha dad pa na ne rany+dza nar dka' thub
NK091(ke)001:11743: kyi khog par bzhugs nas bsam gtan la snyoms par
NK091(ke)001:11745: he ru ka gal po las /
NK091(ke)001:11746: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku rnams la //
NK091(ke)001:11747: mi yi yul du 'dul mdzad pa //
NK091(ke)001:11748: bcom ldan sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK091(ke)001:11749: mdzad pa nyi shus byang chub bo //
NK091(ke)001:11750: zhes gsungs pa ltar rgya cher rol par gsungs pa la kha bskang ste /
NK091(ke)001:11751: dang por dga' ldan gnas nas gshegs //
NK091(ke)001:11753: yum gyi lhums su zhugs pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:11754: de bzhin lhums na gnas pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:11755: lhums nas bltams par gyur pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:11756: tshangs dang brgya byin gyis blangs dang //
NK091(ke)001:11757: ka shi'i ras kyis dkris pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:11758: klu yis sku khrus gsol ba dang //
NK091(ke)001:11759: mtshan mkhan rnams kyis mtshan brtags dang //
NK091(ke)001:11760: phyogs bzhir gom pa bdun bor dang //
NK091(ke)001:11761: gyad zla rnams dang gyad bkye dang //
NK091(ke)001:11762: yi ge 'phong dang bzo bslab dang //
NK091(ke)001:11763: khab dang rgyal srid bzhes pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:11764: rab byung 'khor rnams mi dga' dang //
NK091(ke)001:11765: 'khor rnams kun gyis bsrungs pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:11766: nee rany+dza nar dka' thub dang //
NK091(ke)001:11767: spre 'us sbrang rtsi phul ba dang //
NK091(ke)001:11768: shing drung rdo rje'i gdan stengs su //
NK091(ke)001:11769: mngon par byang ni chub pa ste //
NK091(ke)001:11771: rnam pa nyi shu tham par 'dod //
NK091(ke)001:11772: ces lo ts+aa bas galpo'i mtshan las 'byung ba sogs
NK091(ke)001:11773: mdzad pa nyi shu dang yongs grags ltar bcu gnyis
NK091(ke)001:11774: mthar phyin te rdzogs pa lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11775: so so'i rdo rje gdan tha dad pa la gshegs te 'tshang rgya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11776: grong khyer r+ts+wa mchog la sogs par tha dad pa'ii bdud btul te /
NK091(ke)001:11777: w+aa r+aa na s+ai la sogs par chos kyi 'khor lo yongs su bskor bar mdzad nas /
NK091(ke)001:11778: gdan nyid la mngon para rdzogsa para byang chub ste
NK091(ke)001:11779: sangs rgyas pa lta bu la sogs par sna tshogs
NK091(ke)001:11780: su snang ste / mdor na chos nges pa'i byin
NK091(ke)001:11781: rlabs kyis zhing khams tha dad par sku tha dad
NK091(ke)001:11782: pas mdzad pa tha dad pa mdzad nas tha dad
NK091(ke)001:11783: pa'i bdud btul te gsang sngags kyi chos 'khor lo
NK091(ke)001:11784: tha dad par bskor bas snying po byang chub nyid
NK091(ke)001:11785: du nges pa na yang gsang sngags nges par 'byung
NK091(ke)001:11791: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11792: de skad ces smras te bka' stsal pas /
NK091(ke)001:11793: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:11794: 'gro ba dman pa'i lus can gyi sems dpa' chen po rnams kyis /
NK091(ke)001:11795: snying po byang chub gsang ba dam pa de kho na nyid mngon du gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:11796: de ltar nges pa'i byin rlabs las de nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:11797: dus su mi yul du gsang ba snang bar yongs
NK091(ke)001:11800: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:11801: lnga dang bzhi dang thub dka' gzhon nu dang /
NK091(ke)001:11802: skyes bu bcu la sogs pa gsang ba dam pa
NK091(ke)001:11803: de kho na nyid du ngo bo nges par gyur
NK091(ke)001:11804: pa'i don bstan pa'i le'u ste bco lnga pa rnam
NK091(ke)001:11805: par bshad pa'o // de dag gi sgo nas theg pa chen po nges par 'byung ba'i tshul las /
NK091(ke)001:11806: snying po byang chub nyid du nges pa'i gtam rgyud
NK091(ke)001:11807: brjod pa'i gsung chos kyi phyag rgya'i ye shes rnam
NK091(ke)001:11808: para bgros pa ste byung tshul bstan pa bzhi pa
NK091(ke)001:11809: nyid legs par bshad de rgyas par bkrol ba'o ////bam
NK091(ke)001:11811: lnga pa dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba'i byung tshul la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:11813: bye brag tu rgyas par bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:11814: zhabs bsdu bas 'khor gyis go ba'i yon tan no //
NK091(ke)001:11818: zhabs bsdus te dgongs pa ngos gzung ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:11823: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11824: spyir byung tshul 'adi'ang dam pa'i sgron ma ji ltar bkod kyi lan te /
NK091(ke)001:11825: khyad par rtsal 'phangs las sgom lam gzhan don /
NK091(ke)001:11826: rgyud gnas lugs las dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba'i
NK091(ke)001:11827: byung tshul ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi lta ba rgya
NK091(ke)001:11828: mtsho'i gzugs brnyan lta bu nyid rgyas par ston to
NK091(ke)001:11829: // de nas yang lang ka'i bdag pos /
NK091(ke)001:11830: gsang ba pa'i bdag po la /
NK091(ke)001:11831: sngon du byung ba'i tshig bcu gnyis pa'i lnga pa
NK091(ke)001:11832: dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa na yang byung zhes
NK091(ke)001:11833: 'byung ba de nyid dri ba yongs su dris pa
NK091(ke)001:11834: / kye gasnga ba pa'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:11835: nyid kyisa theg pa chen po gsang ba dam pa
NK091(ke)001:11836: byung ba'i tshul ston pas lung bstan pa gtam du
NK091(ke)001:11838: dgongs pa nges par 'grel pa na yang 'byung zhes bkod pa de /
NK091(ke)001:11839: ji lta ba zhig tu dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba zhig grags pa lagsa /
NK091(ke)001:11840: lan smras te bka' stsal pa /
NK091(ke)001:11842: de'i dus nges pa ni byung tshul bzhi pa dang gcig pas /
NK091(ke)001:11843: gang skyes bu dam pa nyid du nges pa de
NK091(ke)001:11844: dag snying po byang chub la dgongs pa mnyam bzhag
NK091(ke)001:11845: dang rjes thob med par gyur ba de'i tshe de'i
NK091(ke)001:11851: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11852: de lta na'ang ngo bo ni so sor ma 'dres pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:11853: lang ka'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:11855: gang skyes bu dam pa tha ma'i dbugs phyin te
NK091(ke)001:11856: dam pa nyid du nges pa de dag snying po
NK091(ke)001:11857: byang chub la ji ltar dgongsa /
NK091(ke)001:11858: snying po byang chub la dgongs pa nges par 'grel
NK091(ke)001:11859: zhes pa'i ngo bo de nyid gang gi tshig bla
NK091(ke)001:11860: dwags lagas / zhes mtshan ci las btags pa dris pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:11863: snying po ni dngos po gnyis kyi gzhir gyur pas rtsa ba la bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:11864: byang chub ni gnyis med ji bzhin pas rang bzhin la bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:11865: dgongs pa ni rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo ngang gis ma g.yos pas chos nyid la bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:11866: de gsum ni zhi gnas su 'adu'o //
NK091(ke)001:11867: nges pa ni 'khrul pa med pa'i thog tu phebs pas ma nor ba nyid la bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:11868: de ni zhi gnas dang lhag mthong dbyer med pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:11869: 'grel pa ni ji lta bar mngon du byas pa'i don rang gsal bas ye shes la bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:11870: de ni lhag mthong nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:11871: de dag gi ngo bo ma bcos pas ji bzhin pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:11872: ma bslad pas de bzhin pa'i don te de nyid
NK091(ke)001:11873: nges par mtshon pas glo bur gyi tha snyad ni
NK091(ke)001:11877: lnga po des dgongs pa de ji ltar 'grel ba lagas /
NK091(ke)001:11881: rgya mtsho chen po'i gzugs brnyan ltar ma 'dres pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:11882: mtsho chen po de'i klong ltar yongsa su rdzogs para 'grel to //
NK091(ke)001:11887: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11890: de nyid ji ltar yongs su shes par bgyi /
NK091(ke)001:11893: de yi ngo bo bstan pa ni gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:11894: mi g.yo ba zhi gnas dang /
NK091(ke)001:11895: gsal ba lhag mthong nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:11896: gzhi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi gnas lugs dang /
NK091(ke)001:11897: lam mi g.yo zhing gsal ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11898: 'bras bu rnam par mi rtog cing dag gsal du
NK091(ke)001:11899: mkhyen pa'i ji lta ji snyed kyi ye shes rnams
NK091(ke)001:11900: las 'dir lam gyi dang mthar thug pa thun mong
NK091(ke)001:11901: du sbyar ro // slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyis /
NK091(ke)001:11902: cho 'phrul rtsa ba bzhi'i gzhi dang /
NK091(ke)001:11903: ngo bo snang ba gnyis la sbyar ba'ang mi 'thad pa ma yin no //
NK091(ke)001:11904: gang skyes bu lnga'i dgongs pa lta bu'i gzhi rtsa
NK091(ke)001:11905: las 'grel ba'i ngo bo snang ba'i phyir skye ba
NK091(ke)001:11906: ste thams cad ngo bo skye ba bzhir yongs rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:11907: su 'dus shing / skye ba bzhir shar ba ma 'dres par 'grel pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:11909: skye ba bzhi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi don du 'grel to //
NK091(ke)001:11910: 'o na skye ba bzhi sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin nam snyam pa la /
NK091(ke)001:11911: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams ni gdul bya'i don mdzad tshul gang ci yang rung /
NK091(ke)001:11914: sku'i mdzad pa thams cad gang la'nga dgongs pa can te /
NK091(ke)001:11915: de ni 'di ltar 'khor 'das kyi chos dngos po
NK091(ke)001:11916: gnyis pa thams cad cho 'phrul gyi snang ba bzhir
NK091(ke)001:11917: 'dus la / de nyid snying po byang chub la
NK091(ke)001:11918: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs par gsal ba la dgongs
NK091(ke)001:11927: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11931: chos gang yongs su rdzogs pa skye ba meda pa las /
NK091(ke)001:11932: skye ba'i cho 'phrul ma 'dres pa'i snang ba 'byung ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:11933: sems can gyi las kyi rdzu 'phrul las 'khrul pa'i snang ba skye ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK091(ke)001:11934: lam bsam gtan gyi rdzu 'phrul las gdul bya'i snang ba skye ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK091(ke)001:11935: gzhi chos nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul las rang bzhin gyi snang ba skye ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK091(ke)001:11936: 'bras bu thugs rje'i rdzu 'phrul las de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba skye ba'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK091(ke)001:11938: las kyi rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul /
NK091(ke)001:11939: bsam gtan gyi rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul /
NK091(ke)001:11940: chos nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul /
NK091(ke)001:11941: thugs rje'i rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK091(ke)001:11946: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11948: de la gang las gsum gyi bya ba byed nus pa'i rdzu 'phrul las ni /
NK091(ke)001:11949: khams gsum gyi 'gro ba tha dad cir yang snang
NK091(ke)001:11950: bas dngos po gnyis ma 'dres par srid par skye
NK091(ke)001:11951: ba'i cho 'phrul sna tshogs bkod pa ni 'di lta
NK091(ke)001:11952: ste / de nyid dngos su na mi la sogs pa mngal nas skye ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11953: grog sbur la sogs pa drod gsher dang /
NK091(ke)001:11954: sbrul dang 'dab chags la sogs pa sgo nga dang /
NK091(ke)001:11955: lha dang bar ma do dang dmyal ba la sogs
NK091(ke)001:11956: pa bardzusa nas skye ba ste gang skye ba rnam
NK091(ke)001:11957: bzhira snang ba thams cad de bzhi'i cha 'dzin par
NK091(ke)001:11958: smos pa ni tha ma 'dod pa'i khams nyid do
NK091(ke)001:11963: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11965: gang yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsam gtan gyi
NK091(ke)001:11966: nus pa'i rtsal cir yang 'byung ba'i rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK091(ke)001:11967: rgyu las lam snang gi skye ba'i cho 'phrul sna
NK091(ke)001:11968: tshogs su bkod pa nyid gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:11970: gang gsal la mi g.yo ba'i bsam gtan gyi mu
NK091(ke)001:11971: bzhi g.yo thob goms brtan las drod dang rtags dang
NK091(ke)001:11972: cho 'phrul dang mngon par shes pa skye ba thams
NK091(ke)001:11974: snang ba ma nges pa bzhi ni /
NK091(ke)001:11975: brtags pas shes rab skye ba dang //
NK091(ke)001:11976: brtsal bas goms pa skye ba dang //
NK091(ke)001:11977: bsgrubs pas 'bras bu skye ba dang //
NK091(ke)001:11978: bsgoms pas drod dang rtags rnams skye ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:11983: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:11985: gang chos nyid ji bzhin pa thams cad kyi bdag
NK091(ke)001:11986: nyid pa'i phyir de nyid cir yang snang du btub
NK091(ke)001:11987: pa'i bzhi'i rdzu 'phrul las skye ba'i cho 'phrul gang
NK091(ke)001:11989: gang gzhi ma nges pa'i rang bzhin gyi snang ba
NK091(ke)001:11990: cho 'phrul bzhir tha dad par snang zhing bkod pa
NK091(ke)001:11991: thams cad de / nam mkha'i ngang las 'byung ba'i cho 'phrul tha dad snang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11992: sems kyi ngang las sems las byung ba'i cho 'phrul skye ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11993: chos nyid kyi ngang las chos can gyi cho 'phrul skye ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:11994: zhi gnas ji bzhin pa'i ngang las lhag mthong gi
NK091(ke)001:11995: cho 'phrul shes rab rang 'char ba dang bzhi po
NK091(ke)001:12004: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12006: gang rang byung gi ye shes thugs rje'am snying rje
NK091(ke)001:12007: chen po'i thabs kyi mdzad pa lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK091(ke)001:12008: rdzu 'phrul gyi gzhi las skye ba'i cho 'phrul gdul
NK091(ke)001:12009: bya la gang gis 'dul ba bzhin cir yang snang
NK091(ke)001:12012: gang rgyal ba rnams kyi gzhan don gyi mdzad pa cho 'phrul bzhir snang ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:12013: zhi ba dang khro bo'i rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12014: yi ge'i sgo chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12015: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12016: dgongs pa 'grel pa rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul dang bzhir snang ba thams cad do //
NK091(ke)001:12017: de re re'ang rtag pa rgyun gyis skye ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:12018: rang bzhin shugs kyis skye ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:12019: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pas skye ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:12020: yul dang 'phrad pas skye ba ste skye ba'i dus dang ngo bo'i rgyur sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:12021: 'di dag kun 'dus le'u gsum pa las gsungs pa
NK091(ke)001:12022: 'dir le'u re res rgyas par ston pa'i phyir bshad
NK091(ke)001:12023: pa'i rgyud du yang khas len te /
NK091(ke)001:12024: de dang rjes du mthun par sku bzhi'i bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:12025: gsang chen lung gi skabs don 'chad pa dag la'ang
NK091(ke)001:12026: sbyar te sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pas
NK091(ke)001:12027: chos thams cad kyi me long du gyur pa'i mdo
NK091(ke)001:12028: chen po'i gzhung don ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:12030: byin rlabs sku bzhi'i bstan pa rin po che //
NK091(ke)001:12031: kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i spyi mdo 'di //
NK091(ke)001:12032: rnam 'dren bzhi pas lung bstan brgyud pa yi //
NK091(ke)001:12033: bstan pa'i gsang lung chen por bdag gis 'tshal //
NK091(ke)001:12034: zhes bya ba ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12039: rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK091(ke)001:12048: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12051: de la rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul ni /
NK091(ke)001:12053: gang sku ma 'gag pa'i ngang las zhi ba snang
NK091(ke)001:12054: bar mdzad pa'i cho 'phrul ci bzhin pas 'dul ba
NK091(ke)001:12055: dang / gzhi de las gang du rnam par bsgyur
NK091(ke)001:12056: ba'i cho 'phrul gdul bya la mi mthun par snang
NK091(ke)001:12057: bas 'dul ba khro ba'i tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:12069: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12071: ganga snang bar mdzad pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK091(ke)001:12073: de la lngar snang ba ni lha rgyud kyi rtog pa chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:12074: rtog 'joms spyod pa mthun pas 'gro 'dul zhing //
NK091(ke)001:12075: brda' can yang dag len pas don go la //
NK091(ke)001:12076: lha rgyud brjod pas dngos grub kun dang 'brel //
NK091(ke)001:12077: bka' don gtan tshigs rigs pas brjod par 'os //
NK091(ke)001:12079: dngos po gang yang rung ba 'byung ba dag ni brda'i don du 'chad de /
NK091(ke)001:12080: gang la mtshon pasa 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni sku mdog ste gzhi'i don dang /
NK091(ke)001:12081: gang gis mtshon pasa 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho
NK091(ke)001:12082: 'phrul ni phyag dang phyag mtshan te yan lag mtshon
NK091(ke)001:12083: pa'i don dang / gang gir gyur pas 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni bzhugs thabs te /
NK091(ke)001:12084: gnyis kyis 'dul bas gdul bya la dgongs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12085: thabs tshul tha dad pas 'dul ba'i don dang /
NK091(ke)001:12086: gang theg pasa 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul
NK091(ke)001:12087: ni gdan khri ste de nyid kyi las dang yon
NK091(ke)001:12089: gang ltar mdzes pasa 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni rgyan chas su 'jal te /
NK091(ke)001:12090: yid tshim zhing dga' bar byed pas 'dul ba la
NK091(ke)001:12091: dgongs pa'i phyir lnga po so so'i ming gi gtan
NK091(ke)001:12092: tshigs su yang 'gyur ba'i tshul lo //
NK091(ke)001:12106: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12108: de la ganga la mtshon pasa 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK091(ke)001:12110: gang zhi ba spyi'i rang bzhin gyi sku mdog ma bcos pasa 'dul ba la dgongs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12111: gdul bya la snang ba'i rigs tha dad kyi sku
NK091(ke)001:12112: mdog gang la mos pa ltar bsgyur bas 'dul ba
NK091(ke)001:12113: la dgongs pa'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:12114: rang bzhin gyi sku mdog /rigs kyi sku mdog go //
NK091(ke)001:12119: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12121: de la ma bcos pas 'dul ba la dgongs pa bzhi ni lha gcig la'ang ldan te /
NK091(ke)001:12122: nyon mongs pa med pa'i rtags su ye nas rang
NK091(ke)001:12123: bzhin gyis dag cing dri ma med pas dung lta
NK091(ke)001:12124: bu dang / gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i rtags su
NK091(ke)001:12125: snum la 'brel ba ku mu ta lta bu dang
NK091(ke)001:12126: bu dang / / kun la snang ba'i rtags su
NK091(ke)001:12127: dwangs shing rnyogs pa med pa zla ba lta bu
NK091(ke)001:12128: bu dang / / dang / rang bzhin gyis 'od
NK091(ke)001:12129: gsal ba'i rtags su shin tu gsal zhing 'tsher ba
NK091(ke)001:12131: bzhi po des ye nas lha kun gyi sku mdog
NK091(ke)001:12132: la khyab pa'i phyir ma bcos pas 'dul ba zhes
NK091(ke)001:12138: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12140: rigs gang la mos pa ltar snang bas so sor bsgyur basa 'dul ba la dgongs pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:12142: rdo rje'i rigs bee d+aur+ya lta bu rkyen gyis mi 'gyur bas mthing ga dang /
NK091(ke)001:12143: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kang ka ri lta bu dri mas ma bslad pas dkar po dang /
NK091(ke)001:12144: pad+ma'i rigs le brgan lta bu chags pa med pas dmar ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:12145: rin po che'i rigs gser sbyangs pa lta bu ye shes rgyas pas ser po dang /
NK091(ke)001:12146: las kyi rigs sna tshogs pa lta bu phrin las cir yang mdzad pas ljang gu'o //
NK091(ke)001:12147: de'ang rigs lnga dang ye shes lnga dang kha dog
NK091(ke)001:12148: lnga dang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga
NK091(ke)001:12149: la sbyar ba'i tshul ni rgyud kun na gsal la
NK091(ke)001:12150: / de ltar sku mdog la rang bzhin bzhi dang rigs lnga ste yan lag dgu bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12158: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12160: gang gis mtshon pas 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK091(ke)001:12163: gang snang ba phyag mtshan dang /
NK091(ke)001:12164: gang ltar 'gyur ba phyag rgya ste rang rang gi ngo bos ming yang 'grub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12173: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12175: de la gang byung ba na /
NK091(ke)001:12177: zhi ba lha rgyud chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:12178: zhal phyag 'dul bar dgongs pa la //
NK091(ke)001:12179: chos sku spros pa med pa'i phyir //
NK091(ke)001:12180: zhal ni gcig tu bstan pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:12181: dbyings dang ye shes 'brel ba'i phyir //
NK091(ke)001:12182: phyag ni gnyis su bstan pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:12183: thabs dang shes rab mnyam pas na //
NK091(ke)001:12184: zhabs kyang rdo rje'i skyil krung bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:12187: thabs dang shes rab gnyis mtshon pas phyag gi grangs gnyis sama /
NK091(ke)001:12189: bkri drang 'bras bu rnam thar gsum //
NK091(ke)001:12190: nges don 'bras bu sku gsum snang //
NK091(ke)001:12191: de phyir zhal yang gsum du bstan //
NK091(ke)001:12192: nges par chos nyid zhal las 'das //
NK091(ke)001:12193: pha rol phyin drug snang ba yang //
NK091(ke)001:12194: sbyin pa btang zhing tshul khrims srungs //
NK091(ke)001:12195: brtson 'grus brtsams shing bsam gtan bsgoms //
NK091(ke)001:12196: bzod pa bsgoms nas shes rab rtogs //
NK091(ke)001:12197: rgyu yi lam nas bgrod 'dul ba //
NK091(ke)001:12198: rdo rje'i phyag kyang drug tu byung //
NK091(ke)001:12200: pha rol du phyin pa drug gam /
NK091(ke)001:12201: ye shes drug mtshon pa la dgongs te phyag gi grangs kyang drug tu byung ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12207: de bzhin du gang snang ba phyag mtshan yang /
NK091(ke)001:12209: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang //
NK091(ke)001:12210: chos dbyings me long lta bu dang //
NK091(ke)001:12211: so sor rtog dang mnyam pa nyid //
NK091(ke)001:12212: bya ba grub par mthar phyin te //
NK091(ke)001:12213: 'bras bu'i sgo nas mthar phyin pas //
NK091(ke)001:12214: rdo rje'i phyag mtshan drug po rnams //
NK091(ke)001:12215: zhes gsungs pa ltar ye shes drug gi don mtshon
NK091(ke)001:12216: pa de la dgongs pas phyag dang rjes su mthun
NK091(ke)001:12217: te ye shes drug gi rol pas 'gro ba sgrol
NK091(ke)001:12218: ba'i phyir rdo rje la sogs pa drug bsnams pa'o
NK091(ke)001:12219: // 'o na ye shes drug gi don mtshon pa
NK091(ke)001:12220: la 'dra bas phyag dang phyag mtshan la khyad par
NK091(ke)001:12222: rgyal ba ye shes kyi sku can la /
NK091(ke)001:12223: phyag lhan skyes su yod cing phyag mtshan de'i byin
NK091(ke)001:12224: rlabs gzhan la snang nas don byed pa'i cha nas
NK091(ke)001:12225: dbye ba'o // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:12232: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12236: ma bcos pa ni sku phyag rgya chen po ste
NK091(ke)001:12237: gzhi ji bzhin pa las ma g.yos par bzhugs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:12239: dam tshig gi phyag rgya ste /
NK091(ke)001:12240: gang don las mi 'da' ba'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:12241: ma nges pa ni chos kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK091(ke)001:12242: 'dul dbang gis tha dad du ston pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:12243: 'brel ba ni las kyi phyag rgya ste bya ba
NK091(ke)001:12244: gang 'brel ba yod pa'i phyir phyag rgya bzhi po
NK091(ke)001:12245: dag go // gnyis pa la bzhi ste /
NK091(ke)001:12254: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12256: gang ma bcos pa phyag rgya chen po ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:12257: rgyu rkyen dang bral bas ma skyes pa chos kyi sku phyag rgya chen po dang /
NK091(ke)001:12258: de'i tshul gdul bya la ma 'aggas par snang ba
NK091(ke)001:12259: gzugs kyi sku phyag rgya chen po'i rnam pa ste
NK091(ke)001:12260: / rang gi mtshan nyid kyis ming yang grub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12261: de la ma 'gags pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12263: zhes gzugs sku la phye ba bzhi ste /
NK091(ke)001:12264: rang bzhin gzugs kyi sku 'og min na bzhugs pa
NK091(ke)001:12265: mtshon bya'i yul ma 'gags pa 'bras bu mthar phyin
NK091(ke)001:12267: yon tan rdzogs pa'i gzhir gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:12268: de nyid kyi sku gsung thugs kyi gzugs brnyan lder
NK091(ke)001:12269: so la sogs pa mtshon pa ma 'gags pa'i rnam
NK091(ke)001:12270: pa nyid de / de rmongs pa la bstan pa'i don du byas pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:12271: ring bsrel gyi sku la sogs pa mtshan ma ma 'gags pa'i gzugs brnyan gyi bkod pa rnams te /
NK091(ke)001:12272: grub pa'i rtags su gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:12273: yi dam gyi lha sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin las
NK091(ke)001:12274: nye bar brtags pa ma 'gags pa phyag rgya'i skur
NK091(ke)001:12276: rang gi bsam pas byas pa'i phyir de ltar phyag rgya chen po'i rnam pa bzhi'o //
NK091(ke)001:12281: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12283: gang don las mi 'da' ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:12284: zhes dam tshig gi phyag rgya'i rnam grangs ston te /
NK091(ke)001:12285: rang rtags kyis zin pa 'dzin pa dam tshig gi
NK091(ke)001:12286: phyag rgya thugs kyi rtags rdo rje rtse lnga la
NK091(ke)001:12288: thugs rje las mi 'da' bar 'gro don mdzad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:12289: rtags bca' ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya phyag gis
NK091(ke)001:12290: byed pa dang / dgongs pa rtse gcig las mi
NK091(ke)001:12291: bskyod pa bsam pa dam tshig gi phyag rgya gang
NK091(ke)001:12292: bsam pa las gzhan du mi 'gyur ba'i phyir so
NK091(ke)001:12298: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12300: ma nges pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12302: gsung chos kyi phyag rgya 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:12303: gi phyir gdul bya'i bsam pa mtha'a yas bsam gyis
NK091(ke)001:12304: mi khyab pa dang mthun pa'i sgo chos kyi phyag
NK091(ke)001:12305: rgya yi ge tha dad pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK091(ke)001:12306: par snang zhing ston pa'i phyir te /
NK091(ke)001:12309: bzlas pa'i 'phro 'du gsum las 'dir tha ma'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12314: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12318: chos thams cad zag pa med pa chos kyi dbyings
NK091(ke)001:12319: su 'brel bas dga' ba khyad par can du gyur
NK091(ke)001:12320: pa las kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK091(ke)001:12321: de'ang dam par 'brel bar dgongs pa bca' ba las dang dam tshig thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12322: yab kyi phyag g.yon yum dam tshig ma la brtan pa'i tshul dang yang sbyor bar bya la /
NK091(ke)001:12323: las su 'brel bar dgongs pa chos dang las 'brel
NK091(ke)001:12324: ba nyid du bstan pa'i phyir bde ba skyed par
NK091(ke)001:12325: byed pa'i thabs khyad par can te thabs dang shes
NK091(ke)001:12326: rab phyag rgya bzhis rol pa'i phrin las chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:12327: phyag rgya dang / yum gyi phyag g.yas yab la
NK091(ke)001:12328: las su 'khril ba'i tshul dang yang sbyar bar bya'o
NK091(ke)001:12329: phyag rgya dang / // de ltar gnyis pa la nying lag bcu bzhir bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12337: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12339: gang gir gyur pas 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK091(ke)001:12343: bzhugs gnas gzhal yas khang dang /
NK091(ke)001:12353: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12357: gral dang sku'i thabs gnyis las phyi ma ste /
NK091(ke)001:12358: 'grel chen mun pa'i go cha las /
NK091(ke)001:12359: 'dir sku'i thabs dgongs pa mi g.yo ba gzhi dang mthun pa'i phyir 'greng bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:12360: khyad par gang dag par snang bas skyil krung dang /
NK091(ke)001:12364: chos rje dam pa rin po che'i phyag mchan sogs las /
NK091(ke)001:12365: rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid la dgongs pa gtso bo rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung dang /
NK091(ke)001:12366: gtso 'khor gyi khyad par la dgongs pa 'khor phyed skyil la sogs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12369: bzhugs thabs 'dul bar dgongs pa la //
NK091(ke)001:12370: sangs rgyas rnams ni yab yin pas //
NK091(ke)001:12371: rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:12372: rig ma gzungs ma yum rnams ni //
NK091(ke)001:12373: pad+ma'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:12374: byang chub sems dpa' yab yum rnams //
NK091(ke)001:12375: sems dpa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:12376: thub pa 'gro ba'i don mdzad pas //
NK091(ke)001:12377: bzhengs nas gdul byar mthun par bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:12378: sgo ba gdug pa 'dul bas na //
NK091(ke)001:12379: yab yum brkyangs bskum dor thabs bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:12385: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12389: gzung rtog med pas phyi dang 'dzin pa bral bas
NK091(ke)001:12390: nang med par ye shes yul dang yul can las
NK091(ke)001:12391: grol bas kun tu'ang nang du gyur pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:12393: de bzhin nyid du kun chub phyir //
NK091(ke)001:12394: phyi dang nang dang dbye ba med //
NK091(ke)001:12395: rig pa'i ye shes brdal ba'i phyir //
NK091(ke)001:12396: kun tu nang du gyur pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:12398: gdul bya la snang ba'i gnas kyang sgra bzhin te /
NK091(ke)001:12400: gdos pa can las rab grol bas //
NK091(ke)001:12401: phyi nang med par gsal ba ni //
NK091(ke)001:12402: shel gyi phor par bcud bzhag 'dra //
NK091(ke)001:12403: khyad par zhing khams lngar yang snang //
NK091(ke)001:12409: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12414: rigs lnga chos sku'i ngang la bzhugs pa'i phyir bla phab nas mi g.yo bar bzhugs pa'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12415: sems dpa' yab yum de ltar bzhugs pa'i tshul lam /
NK091(ke)001:12416: yang na sku btegs te smon lam dang thugs rje'i gzugs skur bzhengs pa'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12417: 'di nyid 'grel chen gyi gong gi bzhugs thabs ltar na rigs lngar yang rung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:12418: thub pa dang sgo ba yab yum bzhud la ma
NK091(ke)001:12419: rag pa thugs rje'i dbang gis 'gro don la gshegs
NK091(ke)001:12420: pa'i tshul dang / rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyir spyan 'gyur bas gzigs pa'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12421: sku'i tshul dgu dang ldan te /
NK091(ke)001:12422: zhe sdang dag pas sku la gyor ba dang bral ba lta bu mnyen pa'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12423: nga rgyal dag pas sku cir yang drang du rung
NK091(ke)001:12424: ba lta bu'am phyag zhabs kyi sor mo sogs lcug
NK091(ke)001:12425: pa'i tshul dang / 'dod chags dag pas thabs dang
NK091(ke)001:12426: shes rab 'brel ba'i phyir yab yum 'khril ba'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:12427: pa'i tshul dang / dang / phrag dog dag pas
NK091(ke)001:12428: rked skabs phyed par phrab lta bu ldem pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:12429: pa'i tshul dang / dang / dang / gti mug
NK091(ke)001:12430: dag pas sku sha rgyas la 'jam pa lta bu
NK091(ke)001:12432: thugs la ma rig pa med pas gzi mdangs ldan pa gsal ba'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12433: ye shes shin tu gsal bas rigs lnga dang thabs
NK091(ke)001:12434: shes sogs sku mdog so so na 'tsher ba'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:12435: dang / dgongs pa mi g.yo bas brjid dang ldan pa lhun sdug pa'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12436: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i yon tan mnga' zhing gzhan zil
NK091(ke)001:12437: gyis gnon pas shin tu byin che ba gzi byin
NK091(ke)001:12439: dgu po yab la bzhi dang yum la lngar yang gsungs te /
NK091(ke)001:12441: zhi ba'i mdzad pas 'dul don du //
NK091(ke)001:12442: yab kyi sku yi tshul bzhi ni //
NK091(ke)001:12443: gsal 'tsher lhun stug gzi byin ldan //
NK091(ke)001:12444: yum gyi tshul lnga ldan pas na //
NK091(ke)001:12445: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK091(ke)001:12447: shes rab chen po mnga' bas phyag zhabs gang du'ang
NK091(ke)001:12448: thogs pa med pa lta bu'am smin ma 'khyugs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:12449: tshul dang / thugs mnyam pa'i ngang las mi g.yo
NK091(ke)001:12450: bas gtso bo dang sems dpa' spyan phye tsam du
NK091(ke)001:12451: shangs rtser dbab ste bzhugs pa dgongs pa'i tshul dang
NK091(ke)001:12452: tshul dang / / chos sku'i dgongs pa mtha' yis
NK091(ke)001:12453: mi g.yos bas sku mi 'gyur bar brtan pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:12454: tshul dang / / dang / byang sems la rten
NK091(ke)001:12455: pas phan tshun rgyab yol dang gdan la rten pa'i
NK091(ke)001:12456: tshul dang / / dang / tshul dang / thabs
NK091(ke)001:12457: dang shes rab 'brel ba'i phyir yab yum gyi dbu
NK091(ke)001:12459: yab kyi dbu 'abyo ba'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12460: mos shing gdung ba'i phyir gcig la gcig dbu btud
NK091(ke)001:12461: pa lta bu'am yum gyi dbu 'dud pa'i tshul dang
NK091(ke)001:12462: / longs spyod dang ldan pa'i phyir yab yum dang
NK091(ke)001:12463: mnga' thang rkyen longs spyod thams cad rdzogs pa lta
NK091(ke)001:12464: bu tsam me pa'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12465: nyon mongs pa dag pas thugs zhi ba ma le ba'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12466: yengs pa med pas dgongs pa las mi g.yo bas lhan ne ba'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:12467: sgrib pa med par thams cad mkhyen pas ma 'gags
NK091(ke)001:12468: par gsal ba'i mngon shes mnga' bas le ba'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:12469: lo // de ltar rtsa gsum dang thabs kyi gnyis
NK091(ke)001:12470: dang gnas kyi gcig ste gsum pa'i nying lag rtsa
NK091(ke)001:12471: lo // drug bshad pa'o // bzhi pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:12475: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12477: gang theg pasa 'dul ba dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:12479: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i phyir 'og gzhi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang ldan pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:12481: gdan khris 'dul bar dgongs pa la //
NK091(ke)001:12482: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan //
NK091(ke)001:12485: sa'i khyad par bzhin bgrod zin pa'i phyir them skas dang nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan te /
NK091(ke)001:12487: dgos 'dod re ba skong bas na //
NK091(ke)001:12488: yid bzhin rin chen khri rkang brtsegs //
NK091(ke)001:12490: sa yi khyad par bgrod pas na //
NK091(ke)001:12491: nyi ma zla ba pad+ma'i gdan //
NK091(ke)001:12494: yon tan thams cad kyi che ba dus gcig la
NK091(ke)001:12495: rdzogs te spyom pa'i phyir sems can gyi gdan du
NK091(ke)001:12496: snang ba ste / de nyid las /
NK091(ke)001:12497: yon tan che bas spyom pas na //
NK091(ke)001:12498: stobs bcu tshang ba glang po'i gdan //
NK091(ke)001:12499: mi 'jigs bzhis bcom seng ge nyid //
NK091(ke)001:12500: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi rta yi gdan //
NK091(ke)001:12501: dbang bcu mtshon pas rma bya la //
NK091(ke)001:12502: phrin las thogs med nam mkha' lding //
NK091(ke)001:12503: zhes gsungs pa ltar gdan khri rnams snang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:12505: byang chub kyi yan lag gi rgyan cha /
NK091(ke)001:12506: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rgyan cha /
NK091(ke)001:12507: mtshan dang dpe byad kyi rgyan cha /
NK091(ke)001:12508: lam gyi yan lag bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi rgyan cha'o //
NK091(ke)001:12513: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12515: gang ltar mdzes pas 'dul ba la dgongs pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK091(ke)001:12517: zhes rgyan chas kyi don te /
NK091(ke)001:12518: thun mong ma yin pa'i byang chub kyi yan lag bdun rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK091(ke)001:12519: chos rnam par 'byed pa byang chub kyi yan lag
NK091(ke)001:12520: dang chos mthun pa'i dbu rgyan lnga po ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:12521: pa'i rgyan dang / de bzhin du chos nyan pa la dga' ba snyan cha dang /
NK091(ke)001:12522: bsam pa shin tu sbyangs pa do shal dang /
NK091(ke)001:12523: zag med kyis ste ting nge 'dzin mgur chu dang /
NK091(ke)001:12524: de nyid mi brjed pa'i dran pa phreng ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:12525: 'dir se mo do ni do shal la btags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:12526: rin po che'i rgyan yin pas de med kyang do
NK091(ke)001:12527: shal mi mdzes par mi 'gro bas btang snyoms su
NK091(ke)001:12528: 'jug pa ltar / gang yang dang du mi len pa'i btang snyomsa se mo do dang /
NK091(ke)001:12529: bar mi chad pa'i brtson 'grus phyag zhabs kyi gdu
NK091(ke)001:12530: bu ste de rnams kyis mdzes pas so so'i rgyan
NK091(ke)001:12531: gyi las dang / dbyibs kyi don dang chos mthun zhing mtshon du btub pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:12532: thugs ye shes rang snang ba'i rgyan chen posa rnam para bkod par dgongs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12537: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12539: gzhan yang sku gsal la brjid pa chos gos dang /
NK091(ke)001:12540: gsung thugs rje chags pas smad dkris sam sham thabs dang /
NK091(ke)001:12541: thugs shes bya gsal bas cod pan nam zi ldir dang /
NK091(ke)001:12542: yon tan gzi 'bar gyi stod g.yogs dang /
NK091(ke)001:12543: phrin las gar gyi gsang gos sku reg dang phu
NK091(ke)001:12544: dung rnams kyis bsgyings pa'i phyir cha lugs chen posa
NK091(ke)001:12546: 'o na der nges pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12547: gdul bya phyogs gcig gi dbang las mtha' grol bas ther zug pa ni ma yin te /
NK091(ke)001:12549: cha lugs chen pos brjid pas na //
NK091(ke)001:12550: sku yi stod g.yogs rab mdzes shing //
NK091(ke)001:12551: gsung gi smad dkris lhub dang ldan //
NK091(ke)001:12552: thugs kyi ze'u ldir rnam par bgos //
NK091(ke)001:12553: yon tan chos gos bsnams nas ni //
NK091(ke)001:12554: mdzad pa las kyi phu dung ldan //
NK091(ke)001:12555: zhes sogs mang du bzhugs kyang /
NK091(ke)001:12556: 'dir sku gzhir gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:12558: thugs shin tu brjid pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:12559: yon tan mngon par mtho ba'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:12560: phrin las bya ba dang bcas pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:12565: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12568: sems dpa' yab yum bcu tshan gsum dang gnyis te
NK091(ke)001:12569: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan gyi me tog gisa
NK091(ke)001:12571: sems dpa' re re la'ang dbu rgyan rigs lnga lnga
NK091(ke)001:12572: ste bcu drug pa lnga yis dpe byad kyi ze'u
NK091(ke)001:12573: 'brus spras pa'i phyir sras kyi tshogs kyis kun nas
NK091(ke)001:12574: brgyan pa'o // sems ma ni grangs las 'das pa'i don te ma brjod do //
NK091(ke)001:12579: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12581: gzhan yang thun mong ma yin pa'i 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:12582: yang dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin la goms pa thugs
NK091(ke)001:12583: ka'i dpal be'u ste rgyu'i theg pas brang rus la
NK091(ke)001:12584: yod par 'dod kyang 'di bas thugs la rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:12585: dang gnyis ka yod par bzhed pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12586: bslab pa'i mtha' bcu'i don la rtsol ba mthar phyin pas phyag zhabs kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK091(ke)001:12587: bden pa dang chos dang bzlas pa'i gsung gi yang dag pa'i ngag mnga' bas ljags kyi pad+ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:12588: dam pa rnams kyi de kho na nyid la rtog cing dpyod pas sku'i rgyal mtshan brjid pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12589: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa las kyi mtha' las nges
NK091(ke)001:12590: par 'byung zhing nyi mas tshad pa sel ba ltar
NK091(ke)001:12591: nyon mongs kyis gdung ba bsil bas dbu skra gdugs
NK091(ke)001:12592: dang / ma nor ba'i lta ba rtogs pas mgur gyi bum pa zlum pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12593: dam pa'i yo byad lngas yun ring du 'tsho ba phyag zhabs bzhi nya dang /
NK091(ke)001:12594: dam pa'i chos sgra dran zhing 'chang bas snyan gnyis
NK091(ke)001:12595: dung ngam mgrin pa'am spyi gtsug g.yas su 'khyil ba
NK091(ke)001:12598: 'phags lam yan lag brgyad ldan pas //
NK091(ke)001:12599: bkra shis rtags brgyad lus la rdzogs //
NK091(ke)001:12600: zhes pa ltar las dang dbyibs kyi chos mthun sbyar te bkra shisa 'khyil basa 'bar bar dgongs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12601: de ltar bzhi pa'i gsum dang lnga pa'i rgyan nyi
NK091(ke)001:12602: shu ste nying lag rtsa gsum du phye bas bshad
NK091(ke)001:12607: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12609: spyir nying lag bdun cu rtsa gnyis kyis zhi ba'i rtog pa bshad pa de dag ni /
NK091(ke)001:12610: dngos po ganga gdul bya la snang na de dag
NK091(ke)001:12611: snang bas zhi ba'i sku yis gdul ba'i don snang
NK091(ke)001:12612: bar mdzad pa'i cho 'phrul zhes bya ste /
NK091(ke)001:12613: de dag gi de kho na nyid snying po byang
NK091(ke)001:12614: chub kyi ngang du mtshan nyid ma 'dres la yongs
NK091(ke)001:12617: gcig dang du ma las grol bar bstan pas snang
NK091(ke)001:12618: cha so sor ma 'dres par dbyings gcig tu yongs
NK091(ke)001:12619: su 'grel to // tshul de ni khro bo la'ang rjes su mthun no //
NK091(ke)001:12620: gsang ba pa'i bdag posa de skad ces smras pas /
NK091(ke)001:12621: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:12622: dman pa'i lus kyi sems dpa' chen po rnams /
NK091(ke)001:12623: chos thams cad thugs rje'i cho 'phrul gyi rnam par
NK091(ke)001:12624: snang ba tsam du mthong nas gcig dang du ma'i
NK091(ke)001:12625: mtha' las grol bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:12626: gnyis pa khro bo la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:12633: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12634: de nas yang gsang ba pa'i bdag posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:12636: gang du de nyid kyis mi 'dul ba'i gdul bya'i
NK091(ke)001:12637: ngo la snang ba'i phrin las snga ma zhi ba
NK091(ke)001:12638: las phyi ma khro bo'i rnam par bsgyur ba'i cho
NK091(ke)001:12640: lam pa'i dbang du 'dzin pa gzhil dka' la tshan
NK091(ke)001:12641: te zhing 'thug pa'i phyir rnam par rtog pa'i ri
NK091(ke)001:12642: bo bcu'o // bcu gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12644: yang dag pa'i sa la sbyor ba'i phyir sbyor ba'i rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12645: ngo bo mi phyed pa'i phyir zhen pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12646: phyi mo'i ngo bo tha mi dad par nges par zin pa'i phyir dngos gzhi'i rtog pa dang /
