NK091(ke)001:12647: sku phyag rgyar snang ba'i phyir skyed pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12648: bar du gcod pa bdud 'joms pa'i phyir rkyen gyi rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12649: gang rkyen du 'tshams pas 'dul ba'i phyir las kyi rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12650: yon tan mtshon par 'byung ba'i phyir mtshan ma'i rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12651: gdul bya la mngon par snang ba'i phyir mngon pa' rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12652: mdzad pa mi 'gog par mdzad pa'i phyir spyod pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12653: nang gi don phyi ru snang ba'i phyir rtags kyi
NK091(ke)001:12654: rtog pa ste gtan tshigs rnams kyis phyogs tsam du
NK091(ke)001:12655: bstan pa'o // lang ka'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:12656: rtsa ba'i rtog pa 'di bcu las /
NK091(ke)001:12657: re re la'ang 'og gi ming gi rtog pa sogs
NK091(ke)001:12658: dgu dgur phye bas rtog pa'i ri bo dgu bcu'am
NK091(ke)001:12659: / gsum pa yan chad la gsum gsum /
NK091(ke)001:12662: drug pa la drug /bdun pa la gsum /
NK091(ke)001:12663: brgyad pa la bcu drug /dgu pa la nyi shu /
NK091(ke)001:12664: bcu pa la bdun te brtags pa'i rtog pa gcig
NK091(ke)001:12665: dang nying lag brgyad cu rtsa gcig gis 'gyur bas
NK091(ke)001:12666: grangs phrag gnyis po la nges par 'dzin pa ni
NK091(ke)001:12667: / lam lnga la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor rnams kyi
NK091(ke)001:12668: gnyis pa man chad la sgrib ste shin tu cha
NK091(ke)001:12669: phra ba'i rim pas lam gong ma'i rtogs pa dam
NK091(ke)001:12670: pa rnam para bcad pasa mthar lam bgrod par dka'
NK091(ke)001:12671: / ba'i phyir / de ngo shes nas bsal ba'i
NK091(ke)001:12672: ched du bstan pas yongs su sbyar bar bya ba
NK091(ke)001:12676: rtog pa'i ri bo dgu bcu ngos gzung ba /
NK091(ke)001:12677: brgyad cu shin tu rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12682: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12684: de la grangs dang po'i dbang du dgu gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12686: gong gi sbyor ba la sogs pa bcu po re rer yang sbyor ba'i ming gi rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12687: de bzhin du mtshan ma'i rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12689: tha snyad kyi rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12692: the tshom gyi rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12693: nges par 'jog pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12694: dpyod pa'i rtog pa ste dgu yi ngo bo ni
NK091(ke)001:12695: sbyor ba lta bu'i ming la sogs pa'i mtshan ma
NK091(ke)001:12696: bsdus pa dgu yul du byed pa'i zhen rtog nges
NK091(ke)001:12698: des na dgu po 'di dag ni snga ma'i rnam
NK091(ke)001:12699: pa bcur re re'ang dgu rer 'gyur ba'i nges 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:12700: gyi rtog par gyur pas rtog pa'i ri bo bcu
NK091(ke)001:12701: phrag dgu ste dgu bcu tham par grangs nges pa'o
NK091(ke)001:12709: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12711: de la bcu phrag brgyad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12712: gcig gi grangs su nges pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12715: rtog pa gsum phrag dang po la gsum re nyid du brtsis pa spyi grangs gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:12716: sbyor zhen dngos gzhi yan lag dgu dang bcas pa /
NK091(ke)001:12717: rtsa ba'i dbang du byas pa'i yan lag mtshon pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12718: bskyed pa'i rtog pa lnga gsum bco lnga la gcig tu brtsis pas spyi grangs bzhi pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:12719: yan lag nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK091(ke)001:12720: rkyen gyi rtog pa bzhi gcig tu brtsis pas spyi
NK091(ke)001:12721: grangs lnga pa ste yan lag nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK091(ke)001:12722: de / las kyi rtog pa drug gcig tu bsdom
NK091(ke)001:12723: pa dang spyi grangs drug pa ste yan lag sum
NK091(ke)001:12724: de / cu rtsa bzhi'o // mtshan ma'i rtog pa
NK091(ke)001:12725: gsum gcig tu byas pas bdun pa ste yan lag
NK091(ke)001:12727: mngon pa'i rtog pa lnga gnyis dang drug ste bcu
NK091(ke)001:12728: drug gcig tu bsdom pas spyi grangs brgyad pa ste
NK091(ke)001:12729: yan lag lnga bcu rtsa gsum mo //
NK091(ke)001:12730: spyod pa'i rtog pa bcu phrag gnyis te nyi shu
NK091(ke)001:12731: gcig tu brtsis pa dang spyi grangs dagu ste yan
NK091(ke)001:12732: lag bdun cu rtsa gsum mo //
NK091(ke)001:12733: rtags kyi rtog pa bdun gcig tu bsdom pas spyi
NK091(ke)001:12734: grangs rtsa ba bcu pa ste yan lag brgyad cu
NK091(ke)001:12735: tham par nges pas de ltar na spyir bcu phrag
NK091(ke)001:12736: brgyad do // de ril la yang brtags pa'i rtog
NK091(ke)001:12737: pa nges par zhen pa yod pas de ni gcig
NK091(ke)001:12738: tu bgrangs pas brgyad cu rtsa gcig tu grangs nges
NK091(ke)001:12739: brgyad do // pa'o // 'o na grangs gnyis bstan pa ci dgos zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12740: rtog pa rtsa ba las phye ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:12741: yan lag las phye ba ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir bkod de /
NK091(ke)001:12742: spyir bsdom pas brgya dang bdun cu rtsa gcig go //
NK091(ke)001:12743: chos rje dam pa rin po ches /
NK091(ke)001:12744: rtog pa'i ri bo brgyad cu rtsa gcig dang /
NK091(ke)001:12746: don bsdus las lam gyi gol sa dang ngo bo gnyis kar bshad pas mtshon tshul 'dres zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12747: rtog pa'i ri bo 'di rnams mthar lam gyi gol
NK091(ke)001:12748: sgrib yin kyang zag bcas pa'i lam gyi ngo bor
NK091(ke)001:12749: 'gro la des na lam 'og ma'i ngo bo ni
NK091(ke)001:12750: gong ma'i gol sgrib tu mi 'gal lo //
NK091(ke)001:12751: lam gcig la mtshon tshul 'dres na skyon yin no //
NK091(ke)001:12752: zhes gsungs te 'dir gzhan du ldan chos bshad pa
NK091(ke)001:12753: sogs dang ma 'dres pa'i a nu'i rang lam gyi
NK091(ke)001:12754: khyad chos ngos zin par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:12770: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12771: de dag brgyad cu las nying lag gis brgya drug cu rtsa drug ngo shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:12773: da la sbyor ba'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12775: chos kyi dbyings mi rtog pa de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK091(ke)001:12776: ye shes ma rmongs pa kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK091(ke)001:12777: zung 'jug mi 'gog pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gsum
NK091(ke)001:12778: gyi las dang mtshan nyid de 'bras bu mthar phyin
NK091(ke)001:12779: te lhun gyis grub par mnga' ba la 'dzin pa'o
NK091(ke)001:12781: zhi gnas chen po mi rtog pa nam mkha' lta
NK091(ke)001:12782: bu dang lhag mthong chen po ma rmongs pa de
NK091(ke)001:12783: la gza' skar bkram pa lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:12784: zung du 'brel bar mi 'gog pa mkha' dang gza'
NK091(ke)001:12785: skar gyi gzugs brnyan rgya mtshor gsal ba lta bu
NK091(ke)001:12786: ste / khro bo lha rgyud kyi rtog pa chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:12787: zhi gnas mi rtog dngos po mkha' khyab 'dra //
NK091(ke)001:12788: lhag mthong ma rmongs mkha' la gza' skar bkram //
NK091(ke)001:12789: rdos bcas don dang bstun zhing 'tshams par bshad //
NK091(ke)001:12790: ting 'dzin shes rab bka' lung gsum du 'dus //
NK091(ke)001:12791: zhes gsungs pa'i lung gsum gyi don la rtog pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12796: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12798: zhen pa'i rtog pa ganga zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12800: khro bo dag gdul bya'i ngor bkod pa tsam las
NK091(ke)001:12801: ngo bo nyid spyod yul du ma grub pas mi
NK091(ke)001:12802: dmigs pa dang / sems kyi rnam par shar yang
NK091(ke)001:12803: ngo bo gang du'ang sa ma zin pas ma grub
NK091(ke)001:12804: dmigs pa dang / pa dang / mtshan ma dang
NK091(ke)001:12805: bral te dngos gzhi mi rnyed pas ma skyes pa'i
NK091(ke)001:12806: dmigs pa dang / pa dang / don te / snga ma las /
NK091(ke)001:12807: bdag tu mi rtog sprul pa mdzad nas 'thon //
NK091(ke)001:12808: yul du ma grub gzhan med mdzod du gshegs //
NK091(ke)001:12809: yul sems gnyis med ma skyes dbyings su gcig /nyan
NK091(ke)001:12810: thos rang rgyal sems tsam spong man ngag /ces man
NK091(ke)001:12811: ngag gsum la zhen pa'i rtog pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12816: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12818: dngos gzhi'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12820: khro bo kun snying po byang chub lhun gyis grub
NK091(ke)001:12821: pa'i ngang las thabs dang shes rab rang snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:12823: kun gyis mdzad pa drag po'i phrin las mdzad pa'i phyir spyod pa gcig pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12824: ril shes rab dang thugs rjes shin tu khros par bzhugs pas /
NK091(ke)001:12826: med rgyu btags chags bsgrub 'grub bltas par snang //
NK091(ke)001:12827: spyod mthun khro drag gdug pa dpa' bos 'dul //
NK091(ke)001:12828: rtog 'dzoms smad rdzas dang len dngos grub rgyu //
NK091(ke)001:12829: 'di ni khro bo spyi yi don du bshad //
NK091(ke)001:12830: ces spyi don gsum la rtog pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12838: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12840: skyed pa'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12843: gang zhig na rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid khro bor gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12844: gnas sam gdul bya gang la na dur khrod kyi bdag po las gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12845: dgos ched gang gi phyir na gdug pa 'dul ba'i phyir gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12846: thabs gang gisa na drag po'i 'dul thabs kyis khro bor gyur pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12851: gang gis gyur pa bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12856: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12858: gang gyur ba ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:12859: ye nyid rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir mnyam
NK091(ke)001:12860: pa nyid rtoogs pas mtshan rtog ngang gisa 'joms pa'i
NK091(ke)001:12862: thugs rje dang smon lam gyis gdul bya 'dul ba'i shugs kyis khro bor gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12863: thugs rje'i 'du 'phro khro bor gyur pa dang ldan pa khro bar bcas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12864: ru tra lta bu'i gnyen por gyur pa gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:12865: la sprul pa'i khro bo ltar snang bar bcos pa
NK091(ke)001:12866: dang bzhi'o // de'ang de bzhin nyid kyi khro bo ye ldan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12867: phyi ma gsum thugs rje'i dbang gis gdul bya la
NK091(ke)001:12868: snang ba ched du byas pa'i phyir ye shes kyi
NK091(ke)001:12869: khro bo dang / thugs rje'i khro bo gnyis su 'du ste /
NK091(ke)001:12870: khro bo lha rgyud chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:12871: ngang khro shugs khro khro bar bcas dang bcos //
NK091(ke)001:12872: rtogs pas thugs rje'i rang bzhin 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK091(ke)001:12878: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12882: khro bo de yang yul gdul bya ru tra lta
NK091(ke)001:12883: bu dur khrod kyi dregs pa can la snang bar
NK091(ke)001:12884: gyur pa dang / dur khrod kyi gnas bam ril
NK091(ke)001:12885: thod la mkhar lta bu la snang bar gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:12886: gyur pa dang / dang / snying rje chen pos
NK091(ke)001:12887: drag por gyur pa'i phrin las kyis sgrol bar mdzad
NK091(ke)001:12888: gyur pa dang / dang / pa dang / bsgral
NK091(ke)001:12889: bar gyur pa'i 'brasa bu phung po dur khrod kyi
NK091(ke)001:12890: gnas su byas te shes pa byang chub la bkod
NK091(ke)001:12891: de mi 'khor ba dang dam la btags pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12896: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12898: gang gi phyir gyur pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:12900: gdul bya drag po de lta ngan spyod cing nyon
NK091(ke)001:12901: mongs la zhen pas mtshams med pa byed pa'i rgyu'i
NK091(ke)001:12902: gdug pa 'dul ba'i dgos ched kyi phyir khro bor
NK091(ke)001:12903: gyur pa dang / shin tu drag por skyes pas /
NK091(ke)001:12904: bdag gzhan gyi sdug bsngal gyi sa bon 'debs par
NK091(ke)001:12905: smin zin pa 'bras bu'i gdug pa 'dul ba'i dgos
NK091(ke)001:12906: ched kyi phyira khro bor gyur pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:12911: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12915: ye shes chen pos rtog mtshan ril sgrol ba'i thugs
NK091(ke)001:12916: rje mnga' ba'i phyir bskyed pa'i snying po h'u ha
NK091(ke)001:12917: he phatahcesa sngags kyi rgyu yisa khro bor gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:12918: dang / b+h+r+aum las dur khrod kyi gzhal yas khang
NK091(ke)001:12919: rgyan dang ldan pa'i gnas kyis khro bor gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:12920: dang / dang / cho ga gsum gyi thugs rje'i
NK091(ke)001:12921: thabs kyis bsgral la ma thogs pa las khro bor
NK091(ke)001:12922: dang / dang / gyur pa dang / cir yang
NK091(ke)001:12923: snang ba mnga' bas drag po'i phrin las kyis mdzad
NK091(ke)001:12924: pas khro bor gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12925: gnas spar bas sdug bsngal tshar bcad nas bde ba'i
NK091(ke)001:12926: ye shes chen por sbyor ba'i byed pa 'brasa bus
NK091(ke)001:12927: dbang las khro bor gyur pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:12929: gang gi rgyu ni h'u dang ha he phatah gnas ni steng 'og mkha' ste ye shes sku //
NK091(ke)001:12930: bskyed thabs cho 'phrul gsum po khro bo'i sku //
NK091(ke)001:12931: 'bras bu dpal chen phra men 'khor gyis bskor //
NK091(ke)001:12932: phrin las drag pos 'gro ba cis 'dul mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:12933: ces gsungs pa ltar de dag gi don la rtog par shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:12938: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12940: de la rkyen gyi rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12942: lha'i bu'i bdud drag po dang lha brgyad btul nas gdan du mdzad de bardzisa pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12943: phung po'i bdud de ma dmigs pas rgas rgud med
NK091(ke)001:12944: par mdzad pas shes rab kyi mtshon gyis gdug pa
NK091(ke)001:12945: can gyi gdos bcas kyi lus bral te bshigsa pa
NK091(ke)001:12946: dang / nyon mongs pa'i bdud ma dmigs par bcom
NK091(ke)001:12947: pas sa bon med pa'i phyir dug gsum zad nas
NK091(ke)001:12948: sha rus khrag gsum zos 'chos 'thung ste za ba
NK091(ke)001:12949: dang / dang / skye shi mi mnga' bas na
NK091(ke)001:12950: 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom pas shes pa zag med
NK091(ke)001:12951: kyis la bkod de gnas su stobs pa rnams la
NK091(ke)001:12952: dang / dang / rtog pa ste / tsham rngams drag pos lha chen 'dar bsgyel bardzisa //
NK091(ke)001:12953: brtul zhugs rol pas gdos bcas phung po bshigs //
NK091(ke)001:12954: dug gsum mi spang sha rus khrag la za //
NK091(ke)001:12955: rnam shes 'chi med rgyal ba'i gnas su stobs //
NK091(ke)001:12961: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:12963: las kyi rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:12965: dbang phyug chen po'i yon tan brnyes pa'i phyir dug
NK091(ke)001:12966: lnga dbang du sdud par mdzad pa'i rtags las mnyes
NK091(ke)001:12967: pas thod khrag stobs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12968: 'jigs tshul sbrul gyi rgyan la sogs pas brjid pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12969: bdag gzhan gyi dpal mnga' ba'i phyir dpa' bas 'jigs
NK091(ke)001:12970: shing nyam nga med par bde ba mchog dang ldan
NK091(ke)001:12971: pa'i rtags las kha t+wam bsnams pa sogs kyis rngam
NK091(ke)001:12972: pa dang / mtshan dang dpe byad kyi sku mchog mnga' ba'i phyir mi thung byis pa /
NK091(ke)001:12975: 'dul dbang srin po'i tshul gyi sku mtha' yas pa
NK091(ke)001:12976: snang ba'i rtags las 'khor lo bsnams pa sogs kyis
NK091(ke)001:12977: 'jigs pa dang / ril du grags pa phun sum
NK091(ke)001:12978: tshogs pa mnga' ba'i phyir sku gsung thugs chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:12979: phung po grags pa mtha' yas pa'i rtags las rnge'u
NK091(ke)001:12980: chung bsnams pa la sogs pas mdzes pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12981: cis kyang ma gos pa'i ye shes mnga' ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:12982: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen cing nyon mongs kyi d+r+wa
NK091(ke)001:12983: ba gcod pa la thogsa pa med pa'i rtags las
NK091(ke)001:12984: ral gri bsnams pa sogs kyis 'phags pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:12985: dus gsum du rgyun ma chad par gdul bya chud
NK091(ke)001:12986: mi gson pa'i brtson 'grus chen po'i go cha mnga'
NK091(ke)001:12987: ba'i phyir phrin las dus gcig grub pa las slar
NK091(ke)001:12988: yang mi skyor ba'i nan tan mchog gi rtags las
NK091(ke)001:12989: rdo rje rgya gram bsnams pa sogs kyis gnon pa
NK091(ke)001:12990: ste / dbang dang rab tu ldan pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:12991: dpal dang gzugs dang grags pa dang //
NK091(ke)001:12992: ye shes dang ni nan tan dang //
NK091(ke)001:12993: drug dang yang dag ldan phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:12994: zhes de rnams la rtog pa rnams so //
NK091(ke)001:13002: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13004: mtshan ma'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13007: na bza' rgyan gyi lung rgyan rnams don gyi ngo bo las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:13008: yan lag rtags kyi lung 'gro ba'i don du rol pa mdzad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13009: che mchog yon tan gyi lung mchog tu 'phags pa'i che ba dang ldan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13013: che ba yon tan gyi lung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:13018: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13020: de la mi 'da' ba gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13022: thugs rje chen po gdul bya 'dul ba las mi
NK091(ke)001:13023: 'da' ba lhun gyis grub par don mdzad de dus
NK091(ke)001:13024: gsum du gdul bya mi dor ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:13027: glang chen 'dul stobs theg pa'i rgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13029: dpa' ba'i rang bzhin las mi 'da' ba khro bo'i
NK091(ke)001:13030: rang bzhin du dpa' ba'i phyir stag gi sham thabs
NK091(ke)001:13031: te / stag gi dpa' brtul za byed rgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13033: dbyings shes rab las mi 'da' ba thugs kyis gnyis
NK091(ke)001:13034: med du mkhyen pas mtha' ril 'joms pa'i phyir sbrul
NK091(ke)001:13035: gyi chun po'i chas brgyad de /
NK091(ke)001:13036: sbrul chun dpa' brjid mnyen lcug rgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13039: zab mo yum gyi rtags sbrul bzhi //
NK091(ke)001:13041: dug gsum sku gsum du dbang bsgyur ba'i thabsa las
NK091(ke)001:13042: mi 'da' ba thabs mchog dpag gis mi lang bas
NK091(ke)001:13043: 'khor ba'i dpyis phyung ba'i phyir thod phreng tshar gsum
NK091(ke)001:13044: ste / thod phreng dbang sgrol 'chad pa'i rgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13046: 'di gnyis ni gdags pa'i rgyan gnyis so //
NK091(ke)001:13047: thabs kyis gdug pa sgrol ba'i thugs dam las mi
NK091(ke)001:13048: 'da' ba sngon gyi go chas gdul bya mi dor
NK091(ke)001:13049: ba'i phyir zhing gi g.yang gzhi mnabs pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13050: g.yang gzhi tshul khrims gos kyi rgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13052: snga ma gnyis dang 'di gsum ni bgo ba'i rgyan gsum mo //
NK091(ke)001:13053: dmigs pa dag pa'i thugs rje las mi 'ad'a ba
NK091(ke)001:13054: shes rab dang thugs rje chen pos 'khor 'das la
NK091(ke)001:13055: chags pa mi phyed pa'i phyir rak+ta'i thig le ste
NK091(ke)001:13056: / rak+ta thugs rje chags pa'i rgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13058: dgongs bcud dam pa las mi 'da' ba chos mnyam
NK091(ke)001:13059: pa'i de kho na nyid dri ma'i zug rngu dang
NK091(ke)001:13060: bral bar mkhyen pa'i phyir zhag gi zo ris kyis
NK091(ke)001:13061: brgyan te / gzi chen don dam bcud kyi rgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13063: sku gsum gyis dug gsum 'joms pa'i phrin las las
NK091(ke)001:13064: mi 'ad'a ba mdzad pas 'gro ba sgrol ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:13065: thal chen gyi mtshan ma ste /
NK091(ke)001:13066: thal chen 'dul byed phrin las rgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13068: gsum ni byugs pa'i rgyan gsum mo //
NK091(ke)001:13069: de dag ni thun mong ye shes rang snang gi rgyan brgyad do //
NK091(ke)001:13070: mtshan ma bsregs pa'i ye shes las mi 'da' bas
NK091(ke)001:13071: mtha' dang bral ba'i me klong na bzhugs pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:13075: dgongs pa chos nyid kun tu khyab pa las mi
NK091(ke)001:13076: 'da' bar ma 'dres pa'i sprul pa 'phro ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:13077: ral pa gyen du gtibs pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13078: chos nyid dbang drag sprul pa 'phro //
NK091(ke)001:13080: don shin tu gsal ba'i dgongs pa las mi 'da'
NK091(ke)001:13081: bar de kho na nyid la 'gyur ba med par
NK091(ke)001:13082: bzhugs pa'i phyir sku mdog mthing nag 'bar ba ste
NK091(ke)001:13083: / sku mdog mthing nag nam mkha'i rgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13087: don la dgongs pa mtha' dbus med //
NK091(ke)001:13089: de ltar bcu gcig la rtog pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13097: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13101: rang gi don gyi ngo bo yongs su lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13102: de yis gzhan don so so'i phrin las mdzad par bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13104: grub pa rtags kyi phyag rgya /
NK091(ke)001:13105: mdzad pa las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK091(ke)001:13110: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13113: dngos gzhi yongs su ma zin par dug gsum ma
NK091(ke)001:13114: skyes par gsal ba'i ye shes ril gyi blar gyur
NK091(ke)001:13116: dbu gsum dug gsum sku gsum lhun gyis grub //
NK091(ke)001:13118: de'ang gti mug dag pas g.yas dkar sku /
NK091(ke)001:13119: 'dod chags dag pas g.yon dmar gsung /
NK091(ke)001:13120: zhe sdang dag pas dbus mthing thugs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13121: theg pa'i bye brag dgu po ma 'dres par gzigs
NK091(ke)001:13122: shing gzugs snang mtho dman thams cad yul med du
NK091(ke)001:13123: chu dang gza' skar ltar gsal bas kun nas ma
NK091(ke)001:13124: rmongas pas spyan du grub pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13125: spyan dgus sa gsum sku gsum ye shes gsum //
NK091(ke)001:13130: ting 'dzin gsum las mi yengs par thugs la 'gro
NK091(ke)001:13131: 'ong 'byung 'jug gi nges gsum bral te mi g.yo
NK091(ke)001:13132: bas shangs su grub pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13133: shangs gsum srog la mnga' mdzad ting 'dzin gsum //
NK091(ke)001:13134: de bzhin nyid rgyu kun snang zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:13136: de gsum ni gral dang las dang dbyibs kyi sgo nas bzhag pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13137: thams cad ma sgribs pas brjod pa ril ma gsan
NK091(ke)001:13138: par gsal te ma 'gagsa pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pas
NK091(ke)001:13140: sgra chen tha dad sgra ste chos sku ting 'dzin snyan //
NK091(ke)001:13142: rnam thar gsum gyis ci la rol yang zhen chags
NK091(ke)001:13143: mi mnga' bar ma chagsa pa dang ldan pas zhal
NK091(ke)001:13145: zhal gsum rnam thar sgo gsum lhun gyis grub //
NK091(ke)001:13147: de'ang sku stong pa nyid g.yas /
NK091(ke)001:13148: gsung mtshan ma med pa g.yon /
NK091(ke)001:13149: thugs smon pa med pa dbus zhal dang /
NK091(ke)001:13150: theg pa kun mkhyen pa'i ye shes nyid mi shes
NK091(ke)001:13151: pa'i mdud pas ma bcingsa pa'i brjod pa ljags su
NK091(ke)001:13152: grub ste / ljags gsum theg gsum mthar phyin shes rab rtags //
NK091(ke)001:13154: de'ang sku'i theg pa 'chad pas g.yas dkar /
NK091(ke)001:13155: gsung gi theg pa 'chad pas g.yon dmar /
NK091(ke)001:13156: thugs kyi theg pa 'chad pas dbus mthing ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:13157: las bzhi dus tshigs gcig la ched du grub par
NK091(ke)001:13158: mdzad de mi skyor ba'i rtags las mche ba bzhi
NK091(ke)001:13159: grub pa ste / mche bzhi phrin las mthar phyin bzhi yi tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13161: phrin las skad cig tsam la mdzad de ye shes
NK091(ke)001:13162: chen po gang la'ang mi thogs pas phyag tu grub
NK091(ke)001:13163: pa ste / ye shes drug ni mthar phyin phyag drug ste //
NK091(ke)001:13165: rigs drug gi don mdzad pa'i yon tan mang po
NK091(ke)001:13166: kun ma lus par rdzogs pas phyag mtshan du grub
NK091(ke)001:13167: pa ste / pha rol phyin drug mthar phyin phyag mtshan drug /ces gsungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:13168: thams cad chos dbyings su gsal bas bgrod pa med
NK091(ke)001:13169: par sa non te mi bgrod pas zhabs su grub
NK091(ke)001:13170: pa ste / zhabs bzhis lam bzhi bgrod pa med par thob //
NK091(ke)001:13171: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir de rnams la rtog pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13176: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13181: spyan dgus sa dgu 'dul ba'i bye brag gzigs //
NK091(ke)001:13182: spyan gsum srid gsum 'gro rgyud so sor mkhyen //
NK091(ke)001:13183: zhes gsungs pa ltar spyan gyi phrin las gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:13184: ched du ma bltas par gzigsa par mdzad pa dang
NK091(ke)001:13185: / shangs nas rlung byung sprul pas stong gsum 'gengs //
NK091(ke)001:13186: zhes pa ltar shangs kyi phrin las sprul pa'i 'byung
NK091(ke)001:13187: gnas su gyur pas sprul pa 'gyed par mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:13188: dang / snyan drug 'gro drug gnas nas ci gsol gsan //
NK091(ke)001:13189: zhes pa ltar snyan gyi phrin las thugs dam bskul
NK091(ke)001:13190: zhing ci gsol ba ril gsan nas dngos grub snang
NK091(ke)001:13192: dbu gsum srid gsum mgon mdzad sku gsung thugs //
NK091(ke)001:13193: zhes pa ltar dbu'i phrin las gdul bya'i 'gro ba rnams kyi mgon skyabs dam par mdzad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13194: zhal gsum dbyings su dug gsum zad par rngub //
NK091(ke)001:13195: zhes pa ltar zhal gyi phrin las sha rus khrag
NK091(ke)001:13196: la rol te dug chen gsum po zad par mdzad
NK091(ke)001:13197: pa dang / ljags gsum theg gsum bstan pa'i gdangs ngar sogs //
NK091(ke)001:13198: zhes pa ltar ljags kyi phrin las gsang sngags theg mchog rgyal po ston par mdzad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13199: mche bzhis skye bzhi rtsad nas gcod par byed //
NK091(ke)001:13200: zhes pa ltar mche ba bzhi'i phrin las mngal dang
NK091(ke)001:13201: drod gsher sgo nga bardzusa nas skye ba'i sa bon
NK091(ke)001:13202: 'joms pas skye ba rnam bzhi gcod par mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:13203: dang / phyag drug rgyud drug 'khor ba gnas nas 'don //
NK091(ke)001:13204: zhes pa ltar phyag gi phrin las 'gro drug gnas
NK091(ke)001:13205: nas sgrol bas rgyud drug gdon par mdzad pa dang
NK091(ke)001:13206: / phyag mtshan pha rol phyin drug 'gro don mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:13207: zhes pa ltar phyag mtshan rnams kyi phrin las ye
NK091(ke)001:13208: shes drug dang 'bras bu drug lhun gyis grub par
NK091(ke)001:13209: rtogs te yang dag pa'i mtha' drug rdzogs par mdzad
NK091(ke)001:13210: pa dang / zhabs bzhis phrin las rnam bzhis bgrod med sgrol //
NK091(ke)001:13211: zhes pa ltar zhabs kyi phrin las zhi rgyas dbang
NK091(ke)001:13212: drag gi phrin las rnam pa bzhis 'gro ba sgrol
NK091(ke)001:13213: bar mdzad pa dang bcu la rtog pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13218: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13222: thun mong ma yin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa bcu mnga' ba'i phyir te /
NK091(ke)001:13223: rdo rje ye shes pha rol phyin pa ni //
NK091(ke)001:13224: rang bzhin mi 'gyur las ni 'bigs shing 'joms //
NK091(ke)001:13225: zhes gnyis med kyi ye shes chen po mnga' ba'i
NK091(ke)001:13226: phyir gnyen po med pa'i che ba dang ldan pas
NK091(ke)001:13227: badz+ra he ru ka'i g.yas dang por rang rtags kyi
NK091(ke)001:13228: gnyen po dang bral ba'i rdo rje bsnams pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13229: b+han+d+ha bzod pa'i pha rol phyin pa ni //
NK091(ke)001:13230: chos dbyings spros med ye shes bzhi dang ldan //
NK091(ke)001:13231: zhes mnyam pa'i ngang la sdug bsngal ma spang bral
NK091(ke)001:13232: ba'i bzod pa chen po mnga' bas don byed pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13233: phyir 'gran zla med pa'i che ba dang ldan pas
NK091(ke)001:13234: g.yon dang por thugs rje ye shes kyis 'phags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13236: kha t+w+aam stobs kyi pha rol phyin pa ni //
NK091(ke)001:13237: dug gsum sgrol byed dregs pa'i lha bdud 'joms //
NK091(ke)001:13238: zhes stong gsum yongs sgrol gyi stobs mchog mnga' ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:13239: khyad par du 'phags pa'i che ba dang ldan pas
NK091(ke)001:13240: g.yon bar par dug gsum lha bdud 'joms pa'i kha
NK091(ke)001:13242: zhing chen smon lam pha rol phyin pa ni //
NK091(ke)001:13243: 'bod pa'i g.yab mos 'khor rnams dbang du sdud //
NK091(ke)001:13244: zhes yon tan bdag la rdzogs pas smon gnas mthar
NK091(ke)001:13245: phyin pa'i phyir gang la'ang rag ma las par che
NK091(ke)001:13246: btsan gcig pu'i che ba dang ldan pas g.yas bar
NK091(ke)001:13247: par dregs pa can bran du 'khol ba'i zhing chen
NK091(ke)001:13248: bsnams pa'o // thong gshol thabs kyi pha rol phyin pa ni //
NK091(ke)001:13249: nyon mongs thugs rjes tha ba sku gsum 'grub //
NK091(ke)001:13250: zhes thabs mchog dpag gis mi lang ba'i mdzad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13251: byin rlabs kyis nyon mongs pa'i tha ba 'dul ba'i
NK091(ke)001:13252: phyir tsham ngam rlabs kyi che ba dang ldan pas
NK091(ke)001:13253: g.yas tha mar gdug pa 'dul ba'i thong gshol bsnams
NK091(ke)001:13254: pa'o // rnga ni shes rab pha rol phyin bstan pa //
NK091(ke)001:13255: yul med chos sku rnam dag rnga logs la //
NK091(ke)001:13256: 'dzin pa bdag med rig pa'i dbyug gus brdungs //
NK091(ke)001:13257: gsung rab rnga sgras 'gro ba shes rab skyed //
NK091(ke)001:13258: zhes gsang sngags ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:13259: du 'dzin pa dang yang bral bas mi dmigs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13260: shes rab chen pos rmad du byung ba'i theg pa
NK091(ke)001:13261: gzhan la'ang sgrogs pa'i phyir rmad du byung ba'i che
NK091(ke)001:13262: ba dang ldan pas g.yon tha mar pha rol shes
NK091(ke)001:13263: rab skyed pa'i rnga chung bsnams pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13264: pad+ma 'dam skyes ma chags thugs rjes spyod //
NK091(ke)001:13265: tshul khrims pha rol phyin pa'i dbang du bstan //
NK091(ke)001:13266: zhes dus gsum du 'da' nyams bral bas pham ltung
NK091(ke)001:13267: gis mi gos pa'i tshul khrims chen po mnga' ba'i
NK091(ke)001:13268: phyir thams cad du ma pham pa'i che ba dang
NK091(ke)001:13269: ldan pas pad+ma he ru ka'i g.yas dang por 'khor
NK091(ke)001:13270: ba'i dpung gis mi 'jigs pa'i pad+ma bsnams pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13271: 'khor lo bsam gtan lhag pa gsum gyi mtshan //
NK091(ke)001:13272: tshul khrims ting 'dzin shes rab gsum dang ldan //
NK091(ke)001:13273: zhes snying po byang chub lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i ngang
NK091(ke)001:13274: las dus gsum du mi g.yo ba chen po'i bsam
NK091(ke)001:13275: gtan mnga' ba'i phyir mnga' dbang rdzogsa pa'i che ba
NK091(ke)001:13276: dang ldan pas bud+d+ha he ru ka'i g.yas dang por
NK091(ke)001:13277: dbang bcu thob pa'i 'khor lo bsnams pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13278: ral gri ye shes thugs rjes mtha' gnyis gcod //
NK091(ke)001:13279: rtse gcig ting 'dzin gnyis la brtson 'grus mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:13280: zhes bya byed bral bas yengs pa med pa'i brtson
NK091(ke)001:13281: 'grus kyi go mtshon chen pos le lo'i skyon gyi
NK091(ke)001:13282: dgra dpung gtan nas 'joms pa'i phyir kun las rgyal
NK091(ke)001:13283: ba'i che ba dang ldan pas karma he ru ka'i
NK091(ke)001:13284: g.yas dang por ye shes thugs rjes mtha' gnyis gcod
NK091(ke)001:13286: bdag med sems las rin chen dgos 'dod skong //
NK091(ke)001:13287: mi zad par ldan sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin //
NK091(ke)001:13288: zhes gang la'ang ma chags par thams cad khyab pas
NK091(ke)001:13289: sbyin pa'i yon tan chen po 'phel 'grib dang bral
NK091(ke)001:13290: ba mnga' ba'i phyir yongsa su mi nub pa'i che
NK091(ke)001:13291: ba dang ldan pas rat+na he ru ka'i g.yas dang
NK091(ke)001:13292: por mi zad pa ldan pa'i rin po che bsnams
NK091(ke)001:13293: pa ste de rnams kyi mtshan mar rtog pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:13301: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13303: mngon pa'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13305: sku'i rngama spyom bye ba sa yar mngon pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13306: gsung gi rngam spyom bstan pa rgya mtshor mngon pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13307: thugs kyi rngam spyom chos nyid nam mkhar mngon pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13308: mthu'i rngam spyom nam mkha'i dbyings ltar mngona pa ste
NK091(ke)001:13309: rtsa ba bzhi'i nges tshig yan lag gis 'grub pa'o
NK091(ke)001:13319: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13321: de dag kyang tshul bcu dang drug gisa rdzogs par 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:13324: sku mdog gi rngam rgyal ba'i sku gdul bya'i bsam
NK091(ke)001:13325: pa bzhin ji ltar yang snang ba dper na ri
NK091(ke)001:13326: rab lhun po phyogs bzhi kha dog so sor snang
NK091(ke)001:13328: nam mkha'i ri mo phyag rgya sku'i rngam mkha' dbyings
NK091(ke)001:13329: dwangs pa'i 'ja' sprin sna tshogs su snang yang slar
NK091(ke)001:13330: yang de ru zhi ba lta bu'i tshul du mtshon
NK091(ke)001:13331: pa'i mdog dang / bzhugs thabs kyi rngam mtshan nyid
NK091(ke)001:13332: ma nges pas cir yang 'gyur te gcig dang du
NK091(ke)001:13333: ma bral bar snang ba dpe gar thabs mkhan lta
NK091(ke)001:13334: pa'i mdog dang / bu'i tshul dang / gdan gyi
NK091(ke)001:13335: rngam thams cad las che btsan gcig pur gyur pas
NK091(ke)001:13336: srid pa'i 'khor lo zil gyis gnon pa lha chen
NK091(ke)001:13337: gtso bo dag mnan te khyad du byung ba'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:13338: pa'i mdog dang / bu'i tshul dang / dang /
NK091(ke)001:13339: khro bo'i stabs kyi rngam bdud dpung gis mi bardzi
NK091(ke)001:13340: zhing de nyid 'joms pas tsham ngam chen po'i stabs
NK091(ke)001:13341: su zhabs 'gying ba'i tshul dang bzhi ni sku'i rngam
NK091(ke)001:13342: pa'i mdog dang / bu'i tshul dang / dang /
NK091(ke)001:13343: du 'gyur te / de la sku yi rngam bzhi
NK091(ke)001:13344: pa'i mdog dang / bu'i tshul dang / dang /
NK091(ke)001:13345: du 'gyur te / ni / nam mkha'i ri mo
NK091(ke)001:13346: pa'i mdog dang / bu'i tshul dang / dang /
NK091(ke)001:13347: du 'gyur te / ni / phyag rgya rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13348: cir yang 'gyur ba'i bzhugs stabs rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13349: zil gyis gnon pa'i gdan yang rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13350: tsham ngam chen po'i stobs ldan rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13356: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13357: zhal gyi rngam hom lnga 'brel ba'i zhal gang du ril gsol zhing rngub pa zhal gyi tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:13358: ljags kyi rngam gsung sgras zur ma 'dres pa'i cir yang 'gyur ba ljagsa kyi tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:13359: tshems kyi rngam skye shi rtsa ba nas yongs su gcod pa tshems kyi tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:13360: gsung dbyangs kyi rngam gdul bya'i blo la don gsal
NK091(ke)001:13361: bar ston pa yan lag drug cu'i dbyangs dang ldan
NK091(ke)001:13362: par go bar sgrogsa pa 'brug sgra sgrogs pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:13363: dang bzhi ni gsung gi rngam ste /
NK091(ke)001:13364: de la gsung gi rngam bzhi la /
NK091(ke)001:13366: zla gam cir ston ljags kyang rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13367: skye shi rtsad gcod mche ba rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13368: 'brug ltar sgrogs pa'i gsung dbyangs rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13374: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13375: don mkhyen pa'i rngam ril ma 'dres la yongs su
NK091(ke)001:13376: rdzogs par gsal bas dgongs pa nam mkha'i skar tshogsa
NK091(ke)001:13377: lta bu'i lhag mthong gi rgyan ma g.yos par rang
NK091(ke)001:13379: dbyings mkhyen pa'i rngam dgongs pa mi g.yo ba'i ngang
NK091(ke)001:13380: las 'gro don mdzad pa mi 'gog pas phrin las
NK091(ke)001:13381: rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs lta bu'i zhi gnas kyi khyab
NK091(ke)001:13383: ye shes mkhyen pa'i rngam sku dang ye shes kyi
NK091(ke)001:13384: yon tan ril gyi 'byung gnas su snang bas yon
NK091(ke)001:13385: tan thams cad rdzogs pa dpe sa gzhi'i ngos la
NK091(ke)001:13386: rtsi shing 'khrungs pa lta bu'i lhag mthong gi rgyan
NK091(ke)001:13388: thabs mkhyen pa'i rngam ril zin pa'i thugs rje chen
NK091(ke)001:13389: po mnga' bas thugs rje la rgyun chad med pa
NK091(ke)001:13390: gar gyi phreng ba lta bu'i lhag mthong gis cir
NK091(ke)001:13391: yang dga' ba skyed pa'i tshul dang bzhi ni thugs
NK091(ke)001:13392: kyi rngam ste / thugs kyi rngam ni rnam bzhi la //
NK091(ke)001:13393: ting 'dzin nam mkha'i skar tshogs rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13394: phrin las rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13395: yon tan mi zad rtsi shing rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13396: mdzad pa'i rol mo gar thabs rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13402: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13403: ru dra bcom pa'i gnas kyi rngam dregs pa ru
NK091(ke)001:13404: dra bcom pa'i sprul pa'i gnas kyi khyad par du
NK091(ke)001:13405: byung zhing yon tan thams cad 'du zhing sdud pa
NK091(ke)001:13406: dur khrod kyi gnas lta bu'i tshul dang /
NK091(ke)001:13407: lha chen gnon pa'i gdan gyi rngam dregs pa lha
NK091(ke)001:13408: chen gdan du mdzad de gnon pa'i khyad para rgyal
NK091(ke)001:13409: po btson du bzung ba lta bur gzhan rnams spa
NK091(ke)001:13411: gdul dka' sgrol ba'i phrin las kyi rngam khams gsum
NK091(ke)001:13412: bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pas zhing gi khyad par
NK091(ke)001:13413: sangs rgyas kyi sa la bkod pas bla na med
NK091(ke)001:13414: pa'i tshul dang / cig char spyod pa'i brtul zhugs
NK091(ke)001:13415: kyi rngam mdzad spyod ci la'ang chig chod du grub
NK091(ke)001:13416: pas spyod pa'i khyad par cig char grub pa la
NK091(ke)001:13417: slar gnon bya mi dgos pas phyis mi skyor ba'i
NK091(ke)001:13418: tshul dang bzhi ni mthu'i rngam ste /
NK091(ke)001:13419: de la mthu yi rngam bzhi ni //
NK091(ke)001:13420: ru dra bcom pa'i gnas kyang rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13421: lha chen gnon pa'i gdan yang rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13422: khams gsum bsgral ba'i zhing rngam zhing //
NK091(ke)001:13423: rtog 'joms spyod pa'i brtul zhugs rngam //
NK091(ke)001:13424: zhes de ltar gdul bya la mngon par snang ba'i don la rtog pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13425: zhib par rngam tshul so gnyis su 'gyur bar lha rgyud na gsal lo //
NK091(ke)001:13433: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13435: spyod pa'i rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13437: sku'i gzi brjid zil gyis gnon pa seng ge 'bum gzugs lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:13438: gsung gi gzi brjid kun tu grags pa 'brug stong ldir ba lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:13439: thugs kyi gzi brjid khyab gdal du mkhyen pa nam mkha'i gtos chen lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:13440: yon tan gyi gzi brjid 'dod rgur 'byung ba nor bu rin po che lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:13441: phrin las kyi gzi brjid gang 'dul ltar ston pa
NK091(ke)001:13442: chen po'i dkyil 'khor 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:13443: bas bkod pa lta bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:13449: phrin las kyi gzi brjid do //
NK091(ke)001:13454: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13456: de dag ni gzi brjid bcu phrag gnyis kyis rdzogs pa yin te /
NK091(ke)001:13459: sku'i brjid sku yi bkod pa che chung tshad med
NK091(ke)001:13460: par spro yang chos sku dang mnyam par 'byung ba'i
NK091(ke)001:13461: sgo nas che la thugs rje dang mnyam par 'byung
NK091(ke)001:13462: ba'i sgo nas yan lag ragas pa'i gzi brjid dang
NK091(ke)001:13463: / sems can kun gyi 'du byed dang mthun par
NK091(ke)001:13464: sku ji snyed du snang bas grangs mang la smon
NK091(ke)001:13465: lam gyi sgo nas rigs mthun du ston pas gdul
NK091(ke)001:13466: bya 'dul ba'i rkyen dang 'tshams pa'i gzi brjid dang
NK091(ke)001:13467: / / spyod lam gyi sgo nas 'jig rten pas bkur bar 'os la /
NK091(ke)001:13468: rigs btsun pa'i sgo nas sa pa rnams kyis gtso
NK091(ke)001:13469: mchog tshogs kyi bdag pora mthong ba'i gzi brjid dang
NK091(ke)001:13470: / yon tan grub pa'i sgo nas 'gran zla med pas khyad zhugs la /
NK091(ke)001:13471: phrin las kyi sgo nas gdul bya'i bsam pa dang
NK091(ke)001:13472: mthun pas yida dang 'thad pa'i gzi brjid dang bzhi
NK091(ke)001:13473: ste / de la sku yi brjid bzhi la //
NK091(ke)001:13474: sku che yan lag rags pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13475: grangs mang rkyen dang 'tshams pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13476: bkur 'os gtso bor mthong bas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13477: khyad zhugs yid dang 'thad pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13478: chos sku mnyam byung sgo nas che //
NK091(ke)001:13479: thugs rje mnyam byung sgo sprul rags //
NK091(ke)001:13480: 'du byed mnyam byung sgo sprul mang //
NK091(ke)001:13481: smon lam sgo rigs mthun rkyen 'tshams //
NK091(ke)001:13482: spyod lam sgo nas bkur bar 'os //
NK091(ke)001:13483: rigs btsun pa yi gtso bor mthong //
NK091(ke)001:13484: rang bzhin grub sgo nas khyad zhugs //
NK091(ke)001:13485: phrin las sgo nas yid dang 'thad //
NK091(ke)001:13491: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13492: gsung gi brjid gdul bya'i gnas ril du chos skus khyab par gsal bas gdangsa chen po nyid la /
NK091(ke)001:13493: skad cig tsam la sgra tha dad par sgrogs pas stong gsum gang ba'i gzi brjid dang /
NK091(ke)001:13494: 'khor gyi bsam pa'i gegs ji snyed pa skad kyi
NK091(ke)001:13495: dbyangs kyis tshig myur bar res mos pa med par
NK091(ke)001:13496: nye bar sel bas the tshom gcod par mdzad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13497: gzi brjid dang / 'khor rnams gcig kyang byams pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13498: sgo nas bdag kho na la dgongs shing thugs rje'i
NK091(ke)001:13499: sgo nas chos nyi tsher ston no snyam du snang
NK091(ke)001:13501: shes pa'i bye brag gi rigs pas khyad par 'phags
NK091(ke)001:13502: la tshig gi yon tan gyi sgo nas gsang sgo
NK091(ke)001:13503: mthong ba'i gzi brjid dang bzhi ste /
NK091(ke)001:13504: de yang gsung gi brjid bzhi la //
NK091(ke)001:13505: gdangs che stong gsum gang bas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13506: tshig myur the tshom gcod pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13507: bdag la nyi tsher ston pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13508: khyad zhugs yon tan mthong bas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13509: chos skus khyab sgo nas gdangs che //
NK091(ke)001:13510: tha dad sgra sgrogs stong gsum 'gengs //
NK091(ke)001:13511: dbyangs kyi sgo nas go bar gyur //
NK091(ke)001:13512: nye bar gyur pas the tshom gcod //
NK091(ke)001:13513: byams pa'i sgo nas bdag la gzigs //
NK091(ke)001:13514: thugs rje'i sgo nas nyi tsher ston //
NK091(ke)001:13515: shes pa'i bye brag sgo khyad zhugs //
NK091(ke)001:13516: tshig gi yon tan sgo kun 'dul //
NK091(ke)001:13522: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13523: thugs kyi brjid 'khor 'das gnyis ka ma spangs par
NK091(ke)001:13524: gnyis su med pa'i mkhyen pa yangs pas blang dor
NK091(ke)001:13525: bral te re dogs med pa'i gzi brjid dang /
NK091(ke)001:13526: gnyis med la gang gis kyang ma sgrib par lhag
NK091(ke)001:13527: mthong gsal bas zhi gnas mi 'gyur bar mtha' gnyis
NK091(ke)001:13528: ngang gis spangs pa'i gzi brjid dang /
NK091(ke)001:13529: mi g.yo mi 'gog par rgyun mi 'chad pa'i thugs
NK091(ke)001:13530: rjes 'khor ba ma stongs bar du 'gro ba sgrol
NK091(ke)001:13531: ba'i don mdzad pas thugs dam rdzogs pa'i gzi brjid
NK091(ke)001:13532: dang / thabs kun ma 'dres par mkhyen pa'i shes
NK091(ke)001:13533: rab chen pos ma rmongs par ting 'dzin 'bum phrag
NK091(ke)001:13534: mang po'i thabs kyis 'dul ba'i gzi brjid dang bzhi
NK091(ke)001:13535: dang / ste / de yang thugs kyi brjid bzhi la //
NK091(ke)001:13536: yangs la re dogs med pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13537: gsal ba mtha' gnyis spangs pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13538: thugs rje thugs dam mthar phyin brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13539: ma rmongs thabs kyis 'dul bas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13540: gnyis su med pa'i sgo nas yangs //
NK091(ke)001:13541: spang blang med sgos re dogs med //
NK091(ke)001:13542: lhag mthong sgo nas dbu mar gsal //
NK091(ke)001:13543: zhi gnas mi 'gyur mtha' rnams spangs //
NK091(ke)001:13544: mdzad rgyun mi 'chad thugs rje che //
NK091(ke)001:13545: thugs dam mthar phyin ji srid bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:13546: shes rab sgo nas ma rmongs shing //
NK091(ke)001:13552: ma gos pa'i gzi brjid dang /
NK091(ke)001:13553: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13554: yon tan gyi brjid ngo bo 'di 'drar ma grub pas dag med la /
NK091(ke)001:13555: kun rdzob tu dngos grub 'grib pa med par 'byung bas zad mi shes pa'i gzi brjid dang /
NK091(ke)001:13556: ngo bo ye shes su gcig la lhun gyis grub
NK091(ke)001:13557: pa'i byin rlabs nor bu rin po che ltar sems
NK091(ke)001:13558: kyis bsam don 'dod rgur ston pa'i gzi brjid dang
NK091(ke)001:13559: / sems can gyi las kyi bsgral gnas la sogs
NK091(ke)001:13560: pas gnod sbyor mdzad pa yang grub 'bras kyi sgo
NK091(ke)001:13561: nas sman chen po nyid du gyur pas phan par
NK091(ke)001:13563: mdzad spyod gang la'ang shes bya'i sgo nas thabs la
NK091(ke)001:13564: mkhas pas sa bon du gyur pa med par spyod
NK091(ke)001:13565: pa'i sgo nas skyon gyis ma gos pa'i pad+ma lta
NK091(ke)001:13566: bu'i gzi brjid dang bzhi ste /
NK091(ke)001:13567: de yang yon tan brjid bzhi la //
NK091(ke)001:13568: med la zad mi shes pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13570: gnod sbyor phan par mdzad pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13571: thabs mkhas skyon gyis ma gos brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13572: bdag tu mi 'dzin sgo nas med //
NK091(ke)001:13573: med pa'i sgo nas zad mi shes //
NK091(ke)001:13574: ye shes dag gi sgo nas gcig /sems kyi bsam sgo 'dod rgur ston //
NK091(ke)001:13575: sems can sgo nas gnod par sbyor //
NK091(ke)001:13576: grub rgyu'i sgo nas phan par mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:13577: shes bya'i sgo nas thabs la mkhas //
NK091(ke)001:13578: spyod pa'i sgo nas skyon ma gos //
NK091(ke)001:13584: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13585: phrin las kyi brjid sgyu mar mkhyen pas bdud dpung
NK091(ke)001:13586: gis bag tsha ba med pas mi bsnyengs la rang
NK091(ke)001:13587: bzhin mnyam par mkhyen pa'i gdengs mnga' bas nyam bag
NK091(ke)001:13589: don mdzad pa'i sgo nas 'khor bar thog mtha' med
NK091(ke)001:13590: par bzhugs la ngal dub mi mnga' bar bya ba
NK091(ke)001:13591: med pa'i sgo nas yun ring mi bsnyel ba'i gzi
NK091(ke)001:13592: brjid dang / thugs rje'i mthu yis sgo nas 'gro
NK091(ke)001:13593: ba'i mgon skyabs mchog nyid dam bca' ba'i sgo nas
NK091(ke)001:13594: dus chad pa med par rgyun du mdzad pa'i gzi
NK091(ke)001:13595: brjid dang / brjid dang / ye shes rtse gcig
NK091(ke)001:13596: gi sgo nas 'gro ba bsgral ba'i dgongs don bya
NK091(ke)001:13597: ba mthar phyin pas lhun gyis grub pa'i gzi brjid
NK091(ke)001:13598: brjid dang / brjid dang / dang bzhi ste / de la phrin las brjid bzhi la //
NK091(ke)001:13599: mi dngas nyam bag che bas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13600: 'khor bar yun ring mi bsnyel brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13601: mgon skyabs rgyun du mdzad pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13602: dgongs pa'i don rnams bsgrubs pas brjid //
NK091(ke)001:13603: sgyu mar ston sgo nas mi dngas //
NK091(ke)001:13604: rang bzhin sgo nas nyam bag rol //
NK091(ke)001:13605: don mdzad 'khor bar yun ring bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:13606: bya med sgo nas mi bsnyel la //
NK091(ke)001:13607: mthu yi sgo nas mgon skyabs che //
NK091(ke)001:13608: dam bcas 'gro don myur du mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:13609: rtse gcig mtha' gnyis don la dgongs //
NK091(ke)001:13610: nan tan sgo nas bya ba grub //
NK091(ke)001:13611: de dag brjid ni nyi shu sgo //
NK091(ke)001:13612: bzhi bcu dang ni spyir drug cu //
NK091(ke)001:13613: zhes pa'i don rnams la rtog pa ste des kun
NK091(ke)001:13614: 'dus kyi le'u dang po bshad cing 'grel pa ni
NK091(ke)001:13615: rtog pa'i ri bo dang mtshungs pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:13623: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13625: rtags kyi rtog pa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13627: chos kyi mnga' bdag chen po dbang bcu brnyes pas
NK091(ke)001:13628: chos kyi 'khor lo bcu bskor ba la dbang bsgyur
NK091(ke)001:13629: ba'i chos kyi rgyal po the tshom gyis bsnyengs pa
NK091(ke)001:13630: mi mnga' ba'i mnga' dbang chen po brnyes pa'i yon
NK091(ke)001:13631: tan snang zhing mtshon pa'i rtags 'khor lo rin po
NK091(ke)001:13632: che zhes pa'i ming yang 'grub pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13633: yum bzhis mnyes pa phul te thabs dang shes rab
NK091(ke)001:13634: kyi bde ba dam pa'i nyam baga chen po phyag
NK091(ke)001:13635: rgya bzhi la rol pa'i yon tan rgyun chad med
NK091(ke)001:13636: par snang zhing mtshon pa'i rtags btsun mo rin po
NK091(ke)001:13637: che dang / gang gar dagu'am tshul dgu'i yon tan
NK091(ke)001:13638: rdzogs pa'i mthu dbang mnga' bas bdud bzhi'i sde tshogs
NK091(ke)001:13639: dag gi dpunga gis mi bsnyengs zhing mi thub par
NK091(ke)001:13640: kun nas 'joms par snang ba mtshon pa'i rtags dmag
NK091(ke)001:13642: 'khor ba'i dus thog mtha' med par thun mong min
NK091(ke)001:13643: pa'i tshad med bzhis don gnyis rdzogs pa'i chab srid
NK091(ke)001:13644: 'dzin pas yun gyi don srid chen po brnyes pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13645: rtagsa khyim bdag rin po che dang /
NK091(ke)001:13646: thun mong ma yin pa'i stobs mchog bcu mnga' bas
NK091(ke)001:13647: gzhan don spyod pa'i stobs kyis gzhan mi mthun pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13648: phyogs ganga yang mi ldang bar zil gyis gnon par
NK091(ke)001:13649: mdzad pa'i rtags glang po rin po che dang /
NK091(ke)001:13650: skad cig ma la'ang thabs khyad par can gyi rkang
NK091(ke)001:13651: pa bzhis bgrod nas mthar thug gi sa chen por
NK091(ke)001:13652: sleb cing non par byed pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis mi
NK091(ke)001:13653: gnas par bskyod pa mtshon pa'i rtags rta mchog rin
NK091(ke)001:13654: po che dang / rnam pa bzhi'i sgo nas re
NK091(ke)001:13655: 'dod skong bas mi zad pa'i mdzod dam pa yon
NK091(ke)001:13656: tan 'phel 'grib mi mnga' bar snang zhing mtshon pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13657: rtags nor bu rin po che mnga' ba rnams te
NK091(ke)001:13658: po che dang / / lha rgyud las /
NK091(ke)001:13659: rgyal rtags nang nas phyi rol la //
NK091(ke)001:13660: shar mtshon rin chen sna bdun ni //
NK091(ke)001:13661: 'khor lo dbang bcus skye bzhi bsgyur //
NK091(ke)001:13662: btsun mo yum bzhis rgyal mnyes 'bul //
NK091(ke)001:13663: dmag dpon tshul dgus dpung yang 'joms //
NK091(ke)001:13664: khyim bdag tshad med chab srid 'dzin //
NK091(ke)001:13665: glang po stobs bcus bdag gzhan don //
NK091(ke)001:13666: rta mchog rkang bzhis bgrod par sleb //
NK091(ke)001:13667: yid bzhin rnam bzhis re 'dod skong //
NK091(ke)001:13681: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13682: de dag yan lag gi dbang du rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:13685: de la mnga' dbang chen po brnyes pa'i rtags ni /
NK091(ke)001:13687: gang dbang bcu yongs su rdzogs te lhun gyis grub pa'i yon tan snang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:13688: de la dbang bcu po ganga zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13689: man ngag gi tshigs su na skye ba la dbang ba rigs kyi sprul skur ston pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13690: khro bo rtog pa lha rgyud las /
NK091(ke)001:13691: skye bzhi skur ston skye bzhi sgrol mdzad pa //
NK091(ke)001:13692: lha mi sdig sprul skye ba bzhi ru bstan //
NK091(ke)001:13694: yo byad la dbang ba 'dod pa lnga la rol pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13695: yo byad 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga dang ni //
NK091(ke)001:13696: rtog pa gzhom phyir sman lnga dang len rol //
NK091(ke)001:13698: mos pa la dbang ba bdag gzhan gyi mos pa bzhin snang ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:13699: ji ltar mos bzhin tshul dgu'i gzugs ston pa //
NK091(ke)001:13700: gar dbang thabs kyi tshul dgus rol pa mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:13702: rdzu 'phrul dbang ba 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul ston pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13703: rdzu 'phrul ba spu'i dbyings nas phra men 'phro //
NK091(ke)001:13704: lus ni cir rdzu sems ni cho 'phrul ston //
NK091(ke)001:13706: chos la dbang ba gsung gcig gis chos skad so sor sgrogs pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13707: gad rgyangs gdangs ngar sna tshogs phyogs bcur sgrogs //
NK091(ke)001:13708: mche bas zil gnon chos rnams tha dad ston //
NK091(ke)001:13710: ye shes la dbang ba ye shes kun la ma rmongs pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13711: shes rab thabs ldan spyan gyis dbu ma'i ngang //
NK091(ke)001:13712: dbyings las mi g.yo cir yang sa ler mkhyen //
NK091(ke)001:13714: sems la dbang ba ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag la rol pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13715: sems kyi bye brag ting 'dzin sa ya 'phro //
NK091(ke)001:13716: bsam gyis mi khyab bzhi la rol par mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:13718: tshe la dbang ba 'khor ba ji srid du bzhugs pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13719: rdo rje sder mo pags pa spu phreng brgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13720: 'khor ba ji srid bzhugs pa'i tshe la dbang //
NK091(ke)001:13722: las la dbang ba sbyor sgrol gyi phrin las mdzad pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13723: lta ba rnam bzhi'i spyan zur gyis bskul bas //
NK091(ke)001:13724: phra men bzhi 'phro phyogs bzhir las bzhi mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:13726: smon lam la dabnga ba rang dbang med par ston pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13727: smon lam dbang gis drag po'i skur ston zhing //
NK091(ke)001:13728: dus mtha'i bskal pa bzhin du bshol du med //
NK091(ke)001:13734: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13736: nyam bag chen para rol pa'i rtags gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13738: phyag rgya bzhi la rol pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13739: sku'i phyag rgya chen po gnyis su med pas mnyam pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:13740: ma chags rdo rje'i gzungs kyi yum gyis 'khyud //
NK091(ke)001:13742: thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya don gyi dbyings las mi 'da' bar brtan pa'i thigsa pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13743: zhi gnas ting 'dzin mi g.yo yum gyis sbyor //
NK091(ke)001:13745: gsung chos kyi phyag rgya bde mchog zung 'jug gi rol par 'grel ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:13746: lhag mthong ye shes yum gyis gnyis med 'bebs //
NK091(ke)001:13748: phrin las las kyi phyag rgya byang chub kyi sems gsal ba'i rba rlabsa la rol pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:13749: thogs med shugs 'chang dngos grub yum gyis bskyod //
NK091(ke)001:13755: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13757: gang gi dpung gisa mi bsnyengs pa'i rtags ni /
NK091(ke)001:13759: dur khrod kyi rgyan dang cha lugs dang ldan pas sgeg pa'i tshul te /
NK091(ke)001:13760: sgeg pas 'gro ba shes rab skyed pa'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13762: bdud bzhi'i dpung bcom ste bag tsha med par gdan du mdzad pas dpa' bo'i tshul te /
NK091(ke)001:13763: nyam nga med pa'i mdzad spyod dpa' bo'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13765: zhal dbus mthing la rngam brjid dang ldan zhing sku che yan lag rags pas 'jigs pa'i tshul te /
NK091(ke)001:13766: gdug rtsub rngam pas brgyan pas 'jigs pa'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13768: zhal g.yon dmar gdangs gdug pas gshe ba'i tshul te /
NK091(ke)001:13769: log par lta ba zhe gcod gshe ba'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13771: zhal g.yas dkar la dgod pas theg chen gsang ba sgrogs pas bzhad pa'i tshul te /
NK091(ke)001:13772: rmad du byung ba'i chos sgrogs bzhad pa'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13774: rgyud drug thugs rjes 'don cing 'dul dka' sgrol bas snying rje'i tshul te /
NK091(ke)001:13775: shin tu gdul dka' khro bos snying rje'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13777: dug gsum zhal du gsol bas bdud la rngam pa'i tshul te /
NK091(ke)001:13778: smon lam dbang gis mi bshol rngam pa'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13780: sku dang gsung gi las lnga rdzogs par mdzad pas ya mtshan che ba'am ngo mtshar ba'i tshul te /
NK091(ke)001:13781: nyon mongs grub pa'i rgyur mdzad ngo mtshar tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13783: dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong chen po chos sku
NK091(ke)001:13784: mtshan ma med par bzhugs pas shin tu zhi ba'i
NK091(ke)001:13785: tshul te / khro drag dbyings nas mi g.yo zhi ba'i tshul //
NK091(ke)001:13787: de la phyi tshul gar dgu ni /
NK091(ke)001:13788: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs pa'i sku //
NK091(ke)001:13789: dgod dang gshe dang rngam pa gsung //
NK091(ke)001:13790: ngo mtshar snying rje zhi ba'i thugs //
NK091(ke)001:13796: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13798: yun gyi don srid pa rnyes pa'i rtags ni /
NK091(ke)001:13800: byams pa'i blo drag pos rjes su 'dzin pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13801: snying rje'i gros phung po rdo rjes gtams pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13802: dga' ba'i thabs rnam shes gnas su stobs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13803: btang snyoms kyi mdo mnyam chen dbyings la sbyor ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:13804: khro gtum tshad med byams par snang //
NK091(ke)001:13805: gsod chen snying rje'i bdag nyid de //
NK091(ke)001:13806: bsgral zhing stobs pas dga' ba'i mchog /yal bar mi 'dor btang snyoms so //
NK091(ke)001:13812: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13814: stobs kyis gzhan gang gnon pa'i rtags ni /
NK091(ke)001:13816: dregs pa can gyi dug lnga sgrol bas snying rje'i stobs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13817: de la mtshan mar mi dmigs pas ma gos pa chos nyid kyi stobs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13818: de ltar mkhyen te spyod pas blang dor mi 'byed pa'i stobs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13819: de bas rnam pa bzhis dngos grub kyi rgyur grub pa'i stobs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13820: de nyid ril sku la brgyan cing zhal du gsol bas ma spangs pa'i stobs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13821: de yis skyon gyis mi gos par don las ma g.yos pa'i stobs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13822: de yis mdzad pa mthar phyin pa'i smon lam gyi stobs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13823: de ltar bkod pa dpag med ston pas sprul pa'i stobs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13824: de rnams slar yang mi 'khor bas mi gtong ba'i stobs dang /
NK091(ke)001:13825: de ltar 'phral dang yun du don mdzad pas chags pa'i stobs dang bcu ste /
NK091(ke)001:13826: snying rje chen po'i stobs kyis dregs pa sgrol //
NK091(ke)001:13827: chos nyid stobs ni mi dmigs nam mkha'i mdog /mi 'byed stobs kyis barlanga po'i rdzas la rol //
NK091(ke)001:13828: grub pa'i stobs kyis bdud rtsi dngos grub rgyu //
NK091(ke)001:13829: ma spangs stobs kyis gdos bcas sku la brgyan //
NK091(ke)001:13830: ma g.yos stobs ni don mthun grol ba'i rgyun //
NK091(ke)001:13831: smon lam stobs ni bskal pa yongs sgrol mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:13832: sprul pa'i stobs ni mgo brnyan phra men 'phro //
NK091(ke)001:13833: 'phrang dog 'khor bar log lta gcig mi gtong //
NK091(ke)001:13834: chags pa'i stobs ni yun chags spyan dmar bzlog /zhes bya ba rnams so //
NK091(ke)001:13839: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13841: rdzu 'phrul gyis mi gnas par bskyod pa'i rtagsa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13843: mi g.yo ba'i ngang la ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pas chos nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul te /
NK091(ke)001:13844: chos nyid rdzu 'phrul med bzhin cir snang ba //
NK091(ke)001:13845: mkha' la 'ja' tshon bzhin te rnam par bkra //
NK091(ke)001:13847: chos kyi dbyings rtogs nas mkhyen pa'i sgrib med du gsal bas ye shes kyi rdzu 'phrul te /
NK091(ke)001:13848: ye shes mtshan nyid ma sgrib dag pa'i phyir //
NK091(ke)001:13849: mkha' la nyi shar 'dra ste gsal la stong //
NK091(ke)001:13851: dper na sprin gyis gar khyab nam mkhas khyab pa
NK091(ke)001:13852: ltar bsod nams kyis gar khyab ye shes kyis khyab
NK091(ke)001:13853: la / ye shes kyis gar khyab thugs rje mi
NK091(ke)001:13854: g.yo bas khyab par gdal bas thugs rje'i rdzu 'phrul
NK091(ke)001:13855: la / te / tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i rdzu 'phrul bye brag ni //
NK091(ke)001:13856: mkha' dang mnyam pas sprin phung bzhin du gdal //
NK091(ke)001:13858: 'gro 'ong med par gang la gang 'tshams su 'dul bas sbrul pa'i rdzu 'phrul te /
NK091(ke)001:13859: sprul pa'i bye brag 'phro ba'i rdzu 'phrul ni //
NK091(ke)001:13860: ro gcig char 'bab snod kyi bye brag phye //
NK091(ke)001:13861: cir yang snang zhing ma nges snang la med //
NK091(ke)001:13862: des na ming gi don bzhi rdzogs par bshad //
NK091(ke)001:13868: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13870: mi zad pa'i mdzod mnga' ba'i rtagsa gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13872: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i khro bo'i thugs ye shes ni rin po che nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:13873: dpe nor bu mchog lta bu bas /
NK091(ke)001:13874: rnam par grol ba'i sgo gdul bya'i mos pa ltar snang nas 'dod pa skong ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:13875: 'gro rnams ji ltar 'dul bzhin re 'dod skong //
NK091(ke)001:13877: 'o na zad pa yod dam zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13878: dbyings dang mnyam pas ma zad para yon tan 'byung ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:13879: mi zad bdag med gter chen nam mkha'i mdzod //
NK091(ke)001:13881: 'o na dgos ched yod dam zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13882: khams gsum gyi rmongs pa'i mun pa thams cad sel bar byed pa can te /
NK091(ke)001:13883: srid gsum mun nag sel ba'i ye shes sgron //
NK091(ke)001:13885: 'o na rgyun du 'byung ngam zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13886: dus kun tu rtsol ba dang bral te 'gags pa med pas rgyun mi 'chad par snang ste /
NK091(ke)001:13887: dus gsum rgyun mi 'chad par rin chen phreng //
NK091(ke)001:13889: de lta bu'i yon tan rtsa ba dang yan lag
NK091(ke)001:13890: bdun dang nying lag zhe lnga'i bdag nyid du bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:13891: pa ni khro bo gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:13892: de la 'dzin pa ni ched du byas pa'i rtog pa ste spang bya nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:13893: gsum pa mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:13897: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13899: de dag gi don ni rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul zhes bya ste /
NK091(ke)001:13901: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyisa bsdusa pa'i rtog pa
NK091(ke)001:13902: mtha' yas ji snyed pa kun snang cha nas so
NK091(ke)001:13903: sora ma 'dres par ngo bo tha mi dad pa
NK091(ke)001:13904: gcig tu yongs su rdzogs par 'grel to //
NK091(ke)001:13905: de skad ces cho 'phrul dang po'i don smras pas /
NK091(ke)001:13906: lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa dman pa'i lus kyi sems dpa' rnams /
NK091(ke)001:13907: chos thams cad ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par
NK091(ke)001:13908: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul tsam du rig pa la
NK091(ke)001:13909: snang ba gsal bar mthong ngo //
NK091(ke)001:13911: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:13912: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu
NK091(ke)001:13913: drug pa gsal bar bkrol ba'o ////gnyis pa chos snang
NK091(ke)001:13915: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul gyi yon tan /
NK091(ke)001:13923: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:13924: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK091(ke)001:13925: de nas yang gsang ba pa'i bdag pos /
NK091(ke)001:13926: cho 'phrul gnyis pa bstan par dgongs nas /
NK091(ke)001:13927: lang ka'i bdag po la bos te /
NK091(ke)001:13930: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:13932: ston pa gang gisa gnas tha dad pa gang du /
NK091(ke)001:13933: gdul bya la chos snang bar nges pa'i cho 'phrul
NK091(ke)001:13934: bstan pasa 'gro ba'i rgyud la de ltar chos snang
NK091(ke)001:13936: snod bcud kyi gnas de dang der stong chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:13937: 'jig rten gyi khams de dag thams cad kun tu
NK091(ke)001:13938: de yi byin rlabs dang mthu yis phyi ltar na
NK091(ke)001:13939: sgra ji bzhin du dngos su tshab che chung dang
NK091(ke)001:13940: khyab par g.yos pa la sogs pa'i ltas chen por
NK091(ke)001:13943: chen por kun tu rab tu g.yos la /
NK091(ke)001:13944: 'das pa dag brdar gyur pas nang ltar na byang
NK091(ke)001:13945: chub kyi sems g.yos tshab che chung gsum thar lam
NK091(ke)001:13946: pa man chad la 'byung bas 'dun pa sems pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13947: rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin g.yo ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:13953: chen por kun tu rab tu 'gul te /
NK091(ke)001:13955: rigs chen 'byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin g.yo thob brtan gsum du gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13959: chen por kun tu rab tu ldeg te /
NK091(ke)001:13961: dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor gyi ting nge 'dzin g.yo thob brtan gsum du gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13965: chen por kun tu rab tu 'ur te /
NK091(ke)001:13967: lung chen thob pa'i ting nge 'dzin g.yo thob brtan gsum du gyur zhing /
NK091(ke)001:13971: chen por kun tu rab tu chem ste /
NK091(ke)001:13973: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin g.yo thob brtan
NK091(ke)001:13974: gsum du rtogs pa'i rtsal 'phar bar gyur pa dang
NK091(ke)001:13976: dngos su mtha' mtho na dbus dma' /
NK091(ke)001:13978: shar mtho na nub dma' ba sogs tshab che ba dang khyab par g.yos te /
NK091(ke)001:13980: byang chub kyi sems g.yo tshab che chung gsum byung
NK091(ke)001:13981: ba des rang rang gi sa la mi gnas par
NK091(ke)001:13982: don gong ma la 'jug pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:13983: zhugs pas rang rang gi zhen pa mi brtan par
NK091(ke)001:13984: gyur te las bzhi'i don rdzogs pas chos nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:13985: mtha' mtho na rtog pa'i dbus dma' la /
NK091(ke)001:13986: lhun gyis grub pa'i don rdzogs te ye shes kyi
NK091(ke)001:13987: dbus mtho na 'khor ba'i mtha' dma' bar gyur zhing
NK091(ke)001:13988: / zhi ba'i don rdzogs te ye shes shar ba'i
NK091(ke)001:13989: phyogs mtho na rtog pa'i nub dma' bar gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:13990: / dang / dbang gi don rdzogs te rtog pa
NK091(ke)001:13991: nub pa'i phyogs mtho na ye shes la zhen pa'i
NK091(ke)001:13993: rgyas pa'i don rdzogs te yon tan rgyas pa'i lho
NK091(ke)001:13994: yi phyogs mtho na sgrib pa'i byang dma' bar gyur
NK091(ke)001:13995: zhing / drag po'i don rdzogs te sgrib pa byang
NK091(ke)001:13996: ba'i phyogs mtho na yon tan la zhen pa'i lho
NK091(ke)001:13997: dma' bar gyur te chos ji bzhin pa rig pa
NK091(ke)001:13998: la 'jal ba ni brjod pa dang 'dra bar grags
NK091(ke)001:13999: zhing / pa'o // de ltar sa'i sgrib pa shin tu 'joms pa tshab che chung dang /
NK091(ke)001:14000: des snying po byang chub mtshan nyid cir yang snang
NK091(ke)001:14001: la ma nges pa nyid du son par mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:14002: ste / dngos su phyi nang gi mun pa gzung 'dzin rnam gnyis rgyud dang /
NK091(ke)001:14003: ched du byas pa phra rags thams cad sbyangs nas /
NK091(ke)001:14004: rgyud dag pa'i rim pa bzhin yid ches pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:14005: 'gro ba mtha' thug pa med pa dag 'jig rten
NK091(ke)001:14006: pa'i sa nas sems skyes te dga' zhing spro ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14007: ngo mtshar bskyed / de bzhin du sems dang po
NK091(ke)001:14008: pa rnams sems kyi dkyil 'khor rigs pa 'od gsal
NK091(ke)001:14009: bar byas te rmad du byung ba la 'jug cing
NK091(ke)001:14010: ngo mtshar bskyed / zhugs / theg pa chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:14011: sbyor lam la brten pas bden pa mthong nas chos
NK091(ke)001:14012: nyid kyi dga' ba'i ro tshor te sa nas sar
NK091(ke)001:14013: 'phar bas rtsal chen rdzogs pa snying po byang chub
NK091(ke)001:14014: ngo mtshar bskyed / zhugs / tu gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:14015: de ltar snang bas 'gro ba dang sa pa thams
NK091(ke)001:14016: cad 'bras bu gong ma la 'dod pa skye zhing
NK091(ke)001:14017: don snang ba la re zhing ngam pa'i gnas dam
NK091(ke)001:14018: pa chos nyid je gsal du gyur te shin tu
NK091(ke)001:14019: ya mtshan par snang bar byed pa'i chos dngos gzhi
NK091(ke)001:14029: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14030: de ltar 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yasa shing rdul
NK091(ke)001:14031: snyed kyi gnas de dag kun tu don mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:14032: po de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa yang mtha' yas
NK091(ke)001:14033: rdul snyed grangs las 'das par spros te snang nas
NK091(ke)001:14034: yi ge'i sgra'i chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul bstan pas
NK091(ke)001:14035: / yon tan ni bshad pa ltar /
NK091(ke)001:14036: rmongs pa'i mun pa bsal zhing gzung dang 'dzin pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14037: dngos po sgrib pa'i phung po ji snyed kun chos
NK091(ke)001:14038: nyid du sbyangs te 'bras bu chos thams cad snying
NK091(ke)001:14039: po byang chub ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid rang
NK091(ke)001:14040: bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings la rim par bkod
NK091(ke)001:14041: do // des na ma 'gags pa'i chos snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14042: sprul pa kun gyis gdul bar bya ba'i don mdzad
NK091(ke)001:14043: pa'i thabs ni rdul snyed dang mnyam pa rnams las
NK091(ke)001:14044: cho 'phrul gyi ngo bo chos nyid nges par snang
NK091(ke)001:14045: ba'i sgo yi ngo bo ni rtsa ba a h'u
NK091(ke)001:14046: gnyis sam dbyings dang ye shes gnyis kyi rgyu las
NK091(ke)001:14047: yi ge bcu tshan bzhir snang ba na sngags kyi
NK091(ke)001:14049: des mtshon pa'i lha dang don thams cad gsal bar snang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:14050: spyir pho brang lha yi yi ge /
NK091(ke)001:14051: lus gnas rtsa yi yi ge /
NK091(ke)001:14052: zhing khams cho 'phrul gyi ye ge thams cad do //
NK091(ke)001:14055: ma bcos pa'i chos snang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:14060: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mtshon pa /
NK091(ke)001:14063: cho ga'i rim pa mtshon pa /
NK091(ke)001:14066: dakyil 'khor gsum mtshon pa'i yi ge ma 'gag pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:14070: dran pa'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14071: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14073: pho brang lha yi ge ni 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:14075: a ni yig 'bru kun gyi mchog /don chen yi ge dam pa yin //
NK091(ke)001:14078: dbyings las a byung a las ni //
NK091(ke)001:14079: yi ge'i tshogs byung sna tshogs 'phros //
NK091(ke)001:14080: a ni rang bzhin yi ge ste //
NK091(ke)001:14081: rten dang bral bas rgyu rkyen med //
NK091(ke)001:14082: kun la khyab pas nam mkha' 'dra //
NK091(ke)001:14083: a ni chos nyid cho 'phrul te //
NK091(ke)001:14084: chos nyid zab mo'i ngang las ni //
NK091(ke)001:14085: cho 'phrul yi ge a byung bas //
NK091(ke)001:14086: as ni chos nyid mtshon par byed //
NK091(ke)001:14088: tshig tshogs bstan pa rgya mtshor grags //
NK091(ke)001:14089: yi ge'i sgra skad kun bzung ste //
NK091(ke)001:14090: sna tshogs yi ge'i skad du bsgyur //
NK091(ke)001:14091: yig 'bru yan lag mang po rnams //
NK091(ke)001:14092: rang bzhin a yi ngang du 'dus //
NK091(ke)001:14095: yi ge'i phreng ba tshogs byung ste //
NK091(ke)001:14096: yi ge'i yan lag ye shes la //
NK091(ke)001:14097: sangs rgyas sku yi sa bon byung //
NK091(ke)001:14099: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi ngo bo nyid kyang
NK091(ke)001:14100: yi ge sngags kyi sgra las snang ba'i phyir te
NK091(ke)001:14101: / a ni a b+ha dra sa man+ta zhes pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14102: sngags su gyur pas chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag
NK091(ke)001:14103: pa'i chos nyid kyi ngo bo ril gyi 'byung gnas
NK091(ke)001:14104: yum kun tu bzang mor gsal bar byung zhing snang
NK091(ke)001:14105: / ba'i sgo'o // de'ang sgra la khyab pa ni
NK091(ke)001:14106: yi ge dang sgra thams cad kyi khong na a
NK091(ke)001:14107: / ba'i sgo'o // yod cing / don la khyab
NK091(ke)001:14108: pa ni chos kyi dbyings kyis chos thams cad dang
NK091(ke)001:14109: ye shes thams cad la'ang khyab la /
NK091(ke)001:14110: lha la khyab pa ni kun tu bzang mos lha thams cad la khyab pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:14111: h'u ni h'u badz+ra tsit+ta'i sngags kyis rang byung ye
NK091(ke)001:14112: shes kyi ngo bo ma bcos pa kun tu bzang
NK091(ke)001:14113: po'i skur byung ba rang rig pa'i chos nyid rnam
NK091(ke)001:14114: para snang zhing gsal bar byed pa'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14115: de'ang snga ma la kun tu bzang mo chos kyi dbyings chos khams gsum sbyar zhing /
NK091(ke)001:14116: phyi ma la kun tu bzang po /
NK091(ke)001:14118: yid kyi shes pa gsum sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:14119: chos nyid thams cad la ma 'gag pa'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:14120: dang rang bzhin gyi chos nyid gnyis kun la sbyar
NK091(ke)001:14121: te ma 'gag pa ni lha dang ye shes gnyis
NK091(ke)001:14122: dang / rang bzhin ni chos kyi dbyings so //
NK091(ke)001:14123: h'u ni h'u badz+ra d+h+rika gi sngags las rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:14124: 'dzin pa mi bskyod pa'am mi g.yo ba'i sems kyi
NK091(ke)001:14125: chos nyid yongs su snang bar byed pa'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14127: chos dbyings ye shes sam mi g.yo ba'i sems kyi chos nyid /
NK091(ke)001:14128: rnam shes kyi phung po gsum sbyar te 'og ma rnams la'ang 'gre shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:14129: ni dzi na dzi ka ces pa'i don rang rig
NK091(ke)001:14130: cir yang snang zhing shar ba'i don gyi chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:14131: gang de rnam par snang mdzad du snang bar byed
NK091(ke)001:14132: pa'i sgo'o // de'ang rnam par snang ba rnams ni ma 'gag pa'am /
NK091(ke)001:14137: s+w+aa ni s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika ces pas yon tan sna
NK091(ke)001:14138: tshogs ji snyed pa 'byung ba'i rin chen 'byung ldan
NK091(ke)001:14139: te sems nyid la yon tan lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14140: chos nyid rnam par snang bar byed pa'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14141: +aa ni +aam a ro lika ces pa'i don snang
NK091(ke)001:14142: ba mtha' yas kyi bkod pa ston pa'ii chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:14143: gsal la ma g.yos pa ste 'khor ba'i 'gro ba
NK091(ke)001:14144: dang sa pa'i rig pa la ye grub pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:14145: rnam par snang zhing gsal bar byed pa'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14146: h+aa ni h+aa pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rika gi don gyis shes
NK091(ke)001:14147: rab kyi don dang ma bral bas bdag gzhan gyi
NK091(ke)001:14148: bya ba rdzogs pa don yod grub pa'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:14149: gang de rnam par snang zhing gsal bar byed pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14150: sgo'o // de la sngags ni lam pas bskyed pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:14151: sgra don dang ldan pas mtshon pa'i dbang ste 'chad par 'gyur ba rnams la'ang sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:14152: lha yi dbang du yab rnams ma 'gag pa'ang ye shes kyi rnam pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:14153: yum rnams rang bzhin nam dbyings kyi rnam pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:14154: m+aum ni m+aum d+h+aa t+w+ae sh+w+aa r+ai'i sngags don gyis
NK091(ke)001:14155: chos kyi dbyings ma skyes pa tshig gis brjod pa
NK091(ke)001:14156: las 'adsa shing grol bas gang yang mi 'gog par
NK091(ke)001:14157: khyab pa'i chos nyid rdo rje dbyings kyi dbyings phyug
NK091(ke)001:14158: mar rnam para snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14159: de'ang dbyings phyug ma chos dbyings ye shes kyi yul
NK091(ke)001:14160: don gyi kun gzhi'i dbyings nam mkha'i khams gsum sbyar
NK091(ke)001:14162: l+aam ni l+aam t+we sha ra ti'i sngags don gyis
NK091(ke)001:14163: sa nyid rang rig ma byung ma brlag ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:14164: mi 'gyur bar skye 'gag med pa'i chos nyid rang
NK091(ke)001:14165: gsal bar sangs rgyas spyan mar rnam par snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14166: sgo'o // zhes me long ye shes kyi dbyings so //
NK091(ke)001:14167: m+aam ni m+aam mo ha ra ti'i sngags don las
NK091(ke)001:14168: 'byung ba chu yi ngo bo de bzhin nyid yon
NK091(ke)001:14169: tan 'phel 'grib med par 'byung ba mi zad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14170: chos nyid ma m+aa kir rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o
NK091(ke)001:14171: // zhes mnyam nyid kyi dbyings so //
NK091(ke)001:14172: p+aam ni p+aam r+aa ga ra ti'i sngags don gyis
NK091(ke)001:14173: 'byung ba me rang rig pa mtha' ma sgrib dag
NK091(ke)001:14174: pas skyon med pa'i chos nyid gos dkar mor rnam
NK091(ke)001:14176: zhes so sor kun rtog gi dbyings so //
NK091(ke)001:14177: t+aam ni t+aam badz+ra ra ti'i sngags don gyis 'byung
NK091(ke)001:14178: ba rlung gi de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bo mtshan
NK091(ke)001:14179: nyid gang du'ang mi zin par skad cig la'ang 'gro
NK091(ke)001:14180: don mi 'gog par mdzad pas thogsa pa med pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14181: chos nyid dam tshig sgrol mar rnam par snang zhing
NK091(ke)001:14182: lhun gyis grub par byed pa'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14183: zhes bya grub ye shes kyi dbyings so //
NK091(ke)001:14184: hrihni h+r+ai ha h'u pad+ma p+aa da ma'i sngags las
NK091(ke)001:14185: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsunga
NK091(ke)001:14186: gi rig 'dzin pa'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14187: sgo'o // rtog pa'i dbang du rna bas gsung gi brjod pa 'dzin pas so //
NK091(ke)001:14188: t+r+aam ni t+r+aam +aa gar+b+ha ya'i sngags las nam mkha'i
NK091(ke)001:14189: snying po nam mkhas dngos po'i go 'byed pa ltar
NK091(ke)001:14190: yon tan ci'ang mi 'gog pa'i chos nyid rnam par
NK091(ke)001:14191: snang pa'i sgo'o // snas dri'i go 'byed pas so //
NK091(ke)001:14192: k+sh+aim ni k+sh+aim hi r+aa dza ya'i sngags las sa'i
NK091(ke)001:14193: snying po 'gro ba'i mig dag pa ste me long
NK091(ke)001:14194: lta bu'i ye shes kyi ngo bo ci'ang ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:14195: la mi rtog par mthong ba gsal ba'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:14197: sa mthong ba'i yul yin pa'am mig gis gzugs mthong bas so //
NK091(ke)001:14198: dz+aim ni dz+aim ku ru p+aa ni'i sngags las phyag
NK091(ke)001:14199: na rdo rje gsang ba'i mthu stobs kyi bdag nyid
NK091(ke)001:14200: pas gnod byed 'dul zhing 'jomsa pa'i chos nyid rnam
NK091(ke)001:14203: de dag ngo bo mi mthun pa bzhi'i char snang ba'i chos nyid yi ges snang bar byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:14204: h'u ni h'u l+aa s+ye sa ma ya'i sngags las
NK091(ke)001:14205: rang rig pa ril lhun gyis rdzogs te ma 'gag
NK091(ke)001:14206: la gsal bas rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi chos
NK091(ke)001:14207: nyid l+aa s+ye ste sgeg mo me long can du
NK091(ke)001:14209: t+r+aam ni t+r+aam m+aa le sa ma ya'i sngags las
NK091(ke)001:14210: rgyal ba'i yon tan sna tshogs rgyun chad med par
NK091(ke)001:14211: snang bas cir yang 'byung ba'i chos nyid m+aa le
NK091(ke)001:14212: phreng ba can du rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14213: h+r+aihni h+r+ai g+ai ta ra go'i sngags las chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:14214: sgra dbyangs ji ltar 'dul ba ltar ston cing sgrog
NK091(ke)001:14215: pa'i chos nyid g+airti glu dbyangs mar rnam par snang
NK091(ke)001:14216: ba'i sgo'o // a ni a nirti r+aa ga y+aa
NK091(ke)001:14217: mi'i sngags las phrin las sna tshogs kyis 'gro don
NK091(ke)001:14218: mdzad pas cir yang ma nges pa'i chos nyid n+airti
NK091(ke)001:14219: gar bsgyur mar rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14220: mee ni mee d+ha ra ni'i sngags las thams cad
NK091(ke)001:14221: gnyis su med par mkhyen pas 'byed pa'i phyogs ris
NK091(ke)001:14222: med par phan 'dogs pa byams pa chen po'i chos
NK091(ke)001:14223: nyid byams par rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14224: th+l+him ni th+l+him ni s+sa ram pa ya'i sngags las
NK091(ke)001:14225: thugs rje chen pos zin pas dngos su skyob pa'am
NK091(ke)001:14226: des sgrib pa sel bas snying rje chen po'i chos
NK091(ke)001:14227: nyid sgrib pa rnam sel du rnam par snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14228: sgo'o // h'u ni h'u swa r+aa dza ya'i sngags
NK091(ke)001:14229: las thugs rje chen pos spyod yul dag pas kun
NK091(ke)001:14230: tu bzang zhing don mdzad pa la 'gyod pa dang
NK091(ke)001:14231: bral bas dga' ba chen po'i chos nyid kun tu
NK091(ke)001:14232: bzang por rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14233: m+aum ni m+aum sh+r+ai a r+aa g+aa ya'i sngags las
NK091(ke)001:14234: ye shes chen po zug rngu dang bral te 'jam
NK091(ke)001:14235: pa'am mnyam pas 'dul ba btang snyomsa chen po'i chos
NK091(ke)001:14236: nyid 'jam dpal du rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14237: de ltar sngags kyi sgra don gyis tshad med bzhi dang sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:14238: d+h+au ni dzahd+h+au pe pra be sha'i sngags las ches
NK091(ke)001:14239: tshim par byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul
NK091(ke)001:14240: gyi chos nyid d+h+au p+pe mar rnam par snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14241: sgo'o // pu ni h'u push+pe a be sha'i sngags
NK091(ke)001:14242: las go bar byed pas dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul
NK091(ke)001:14243: gyi chos nyid push+pe mar rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o
NK091(ke)001:14244: sgo'o // // bam ni bam d+ai pa su gi
NK091(ke)001:14245: r+ai'i sngags las gzhan la snang bar byed pas byin
NK091(ke)001:14246: gyi rlabs kyi cho 'phrul gyi chos nyid +aa lo
NK091(ke)001:14247: ker rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14248: ho ni ho gan+d+he tsit+ta'i sngags las mnyes par byed
NK091(ke)001:14249: pas mchod pa'i cho 'phrul gyi chos nyid gan+d+he mar
NK091(ke)001:14252: 'gro ba lam la 'jug pa na dang po rnam
NK091(ke)001:14253: thar bzhi'i sgo nas the tshom dang sgro 'dogs thams
NK091(ke)001:14254: cad gcod cing / bar du de ltar sgoms nas /
NK091(ke)001:14255: mthar 'bras bu'i ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa yin la /
NK091(ke)001:14256: sangs rgyas rnams kyis gzhan don yang de'i sgo nas mdzad pas na sgo dang sbyar ro //
NK091(ke)001:14257: ya ni chos thams cad kyi ngo bo stong pa
NK091(ke)001:14258: nyid kyi rnam para thar pa'i chos nyid rnam par
NK091(ke)001:14260: khro bo ya man+ta kri ta gshin rje gshed po ste /
NK091(ke)001:14261: mtha' yi gshin rje 'joms pas stong nyid sgo la gnas //
NK091(ke)001:14263: th+aa ni snang stong gi mtshan ma med pa'i rnam
NK091(ke)001:14264: par thar pa'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo
NK091(ke)001:14265: ste / khro bo stobs chen stong 'dzin mtshan ma 'joms //
NK091(ke)001:14266: de phyir mtshan med rnam thar sgo la gnas //
NK091(ke)001:14268: h+r+aihni ye nas byang chub kyi sems la rdzogs pas
NK091(ke)001:14269: smon pa med pa'i rnam par thar pa'i chosa nyid
NK091(ke)001:14270: rnam par snang ba'i sgo ste /
NK091(ke)001:14271: rta mgrin re smon rtog pas rtsol ba bcom /
NK091(ke)001:14272: de phyir bdag rdzogs smon med sgo la gnas //
NK091(ke)001:14274: h+aum ni bya ba med par 'od gsal bas thabs
NK091(ke)001:14275: la mkhas pa'i rnam par thar pa'i chosa nyid rnam
NK091(ke)001:14277: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yang dag zhen bgegs 'joms //
NK091(ke)001:14278: de phyir bya med thabs chen rang bzhin 'od gsal sgo //
NK091(ke)001:14279: ye nas bdag la lhun rdzogs khro bo'i chos //
NK091(ke)001:14280: yi ge'i chos nyid mdzad pas rig la snang bar byed //
NK091(ke)001:14286: h'u pradz+ny+aa ta krita zhes pa'i sngags don du gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:14287: dzani sbyin pa'i thabs kyis 'gro ba don la 'dren pa'i chosa nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo ste /
NK091(ke)001:14288: lcags kyu'i chos nyid sbyin pas 'gro ba 'dren pa'i sgo //
NK091(ke)001:14290: h'u ni snyan par smra bas gsang don brjod pa'i chosa nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo ste /
NK091(ke)001:14291: zhags pa'i chos nyid snyan pa'i don brjod sgo mas las ngan 'ching //
NK091(ke)001:14293: bam ni gdul bya'i don yang dag par spyod pa'i chosa nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo ste /
NK091(ke)001:14294: lcags sgrog chos nyid 'gro ba'i don spyod log sdom sgo //
NK091(ke)001:14296: honi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi dona dang mthun pa'i chosa nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo ste /
NK091(ke)001:14297: dril bu'i chos nyid 'gro don mthun pas dga' byed sgo //
NK091(ke)001:14298: bsdu pa rnam thar sgo bzhir yab yum brgyad rnams bzhugs //
NK091(ke)001:14299: log skyon tshogs brgyad ye bcom bsrung ba'i ngo bor gnas //
NK091(ke)001:14301: krem ni thun mong ma yin pa'i byang chub yan
NK091(ke)001:14302: lag bdun gyi ngo bos rang bzhin zhi ba chen
NK091(ke)001:14303: po'i phyir lha'i thub pa'i chosa nyid rnam par snang
NK091(ke)001:14304: ba'i sgo'o // chos rje dam pa rin po che'i phyag mchan las /
NK091(ke)001:14305: lha'i thub pa rgyud zhi ba'am /
NK091(ke)001:14306: brgya byin gyis byang chub kyi lam ston la /
NK091(ke)001:14307: gsang ste gsang sngags kyang ston pas so gsungs /
NK091(ke)001:14308: drum ni stobs lnga'am bcu'i ngo bos rtsod pa lta
NK091(ke)001:14309: bur byed pa 'dul ba'i phyir lha min gyi thub
NK091(ke)001:14310: pa'i chosa nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14312: lha ma yin stobs che ba'am 'thab pa la dga' bas so //
NK091(ke)001:14314: srum ni dbang po lnga'i ngo bos 'dod pa rang
NK091(ke)001:14315: dga' ba dang dbang po'i sgo sdom pas 'dul ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14316: phyir mi'i thub pa'i chosa nyid rnam par snang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14318: mi dbang sh+aakya thub pa'am yang na mi dbang po lnga gsal la rig pa rno bas so //
NK091(ke)001:14320: bra ni rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi'i ngo bos
NK091(ke)001:14321: rkang bzhi la sogs pa ma rig pa las chos
NK091(ke)001:14322: nyid kyis bskyod par 'dul ba'i phyir byol song gi
NK091(ke)001:14323: thub pa'i chosa nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14324: k+sham ni yang dag par spong ba bzhi'i ngo bos
NK091(ke)001:14325: 'dod pa spong bas 'bras bu mi 'byung bar 'dul
NK091(ke)001:14326: ba'i phyir yi dwags kyi thub pa'i chosa nyid rnam
NK091(ke)001:14328: ye ni dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi'i ngo
NK091(ke)001:14329: bos snga ma'i las dran te log lta 'thibs po
NK091(ke)001:14330: bsal nas sdug bsngal gyis myos pa sgrol bar 'dul
