NK091(ke)001:14331: ba'i phyir dmyal ba'i thub pa'i chosa nyid rnam par
NK091(ke)001:14332: snang ba'i sgo'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:14340: chos 'byung ba'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14341: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14342: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag kun gang na bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:14343: na b+h+r+aum ni stong pa nyid bco brgyad dbyings kyi
NK091(ke)001:14344: ngo bor lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i gzhal yas khang gi
NK091(ke)001:14345: chos nyid mtshon cing de nyid la gnas par rnam
NK091(ke)001:14347: shwa ni shwa sa ni'i sgras gnas phyi nang sna
NK091(ke)001:14348: tshogs dang 'byung ba rim par brtsegs pa'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:14350: d+ha ni d+harma d+ha tu ste chos kyi 'byung gnas
NK091(ke)001:14351: gsang ba'i nam mkha' dbyings kyi b+ha ga'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:14353: phyi ma 'di gnyis mar btags nas ye shes lngar lcags 'grel gyis bshad de /
NK091(ke)001:14354: de ltar na ma dang ha ni khyad par gyi tshig tu sbyar la /
NK091(ke)001:14356: stong nyid ye shes dang me long lta bu la sogs par sngags kyi 'bru bsdeb nas bshad do //
NK091(ke)001:14361: sdud pa'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14362: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14363: e ni drag po khro bo'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14364: wam ni mtha' kun zhi ba' chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14365: ma ni mtha' bzhi rgyas pa'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14366: ya ni dbang du sdud pa'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14368: e ni drag po'i las te wam zhi ba //
NK091(ke)001:14369: ma ni rgyas pa'i phrin las ya dbang sdud //
NK091(ke)001:14370: yi ge bzhi dbyibs so sos las bzhi bstan //
NK091(ke)001:14371: de nyid ye nas gnas pa'i yi ger snang //
NK091(ke)001:14376: shes pa'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14377: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14378: ma ni ma nu ste dran zhing rig pa'i ting
NK091(ke)001:14379: nge 'dzin gyi chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o
NK091(ke)001:14380: // h+aa ni h+ya hi kye ste spyan drangs pa'am bod pa'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14381: pra ni pra pa ste 'od zer spro ba'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14382: k+sha ni k+sha ya ta na mtha' zad pa ste
NK091(ke)001:14383: dkyil 'khor bsdu ba'i las zin pa'am mtha' yi sgrib
NK091(ke)001:14384: pa zad pa'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o
NK091(ke)001:14385: // dz+ny+aa ni dz+ny+aa na ste shes pa'i tshogs brgyad kyi chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14389: rkyen gyi chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14390: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14391: he ni he tu na rgyu'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14392: s+w+aam ni s+w+aa b+h+aa ba na 'bras bu'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14393: tham ni tha ka na rkyen bzhi po rnams kyi chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14397: dkar po'i chos nyid rnam par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14398: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14399: ska ni skan+d+ha pany+tsa na phung po lnga'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14401: sh+ai la skan+d+hahtshula khrims kyi phung po /
NK091(ke)001:14402: sa m+aa ti skan+d+ha ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po /
NK091(ke)001:14403: pradz+ny+aa skan+d+hahshesa rab kyi phung po /
NK091(ke)001:14404: bi muk+ti skan+d+hahrnama par grol ba'i phung po /
NK091(ke)001:14405: bi muk+ti dz+ny+aa na d+har+sha skan+d+hahrnama grol ye shes mthong ba'i phung po'o //
NK091(ke)001:14406: kra ni karma na las kyi chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14407: bam ni bam k+aa la na nag po'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14408: tra ni tra ye na dkar po'i chos nyid rnama par snang ba'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14409: de dag ni sna tshogs snang ba'i chos nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:14410: zur 'dren pa ste tha ma gnyis kyis lha'i sku
NK091(ke)001:14411: mdog gi chos nyid kyi zur yang 'dren no //
NK091(ke)001:14416: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14417: +aa ni yon tan rdzogs pa'i phyir rang bzhin lhun
NK091(ke)001:14418: gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi chos nyid rnama par
NK091(ke)001:14419: snang ba'i sgo'o // h'u ni chos ril gyi 'byung
NK091(ke)001:14420: gnas rang gi byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor chos
NK091(ke)001:14421: nyid rnama par snang ba'i yi ge'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14422: m+aum ni chos nyid kyi phyi mo ma bslad ma
NK091(ke)001:14423: bcos te ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi chos
NK091(ke)001:14424: nyid rnama par snang ba'i yi ge'i sgo'o //
NK091(ke)001:14429: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14431: de ltar don bshad pa dag ni yi ge'i cho 'phrul las chos rnam par snang bar byas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:14432: de'i gtan tshigs de ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:14434: yi ge' sgo la brten pa'i sgras drangs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:14436: bsgyur bas mtshon nas chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:14437: mthong ste chos thams cad nam mkha'a dang 'dra bar
NK091(ke)001:14439: de bzhin du mi brjed pa'i gzungs thob pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:14440: gzhan la brjod pa'i sgra la mkhas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:14441: dran pa thob pas shes bya gsal ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:14442: mkhas par chub pas blo gros yangs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:14443: don thag chod pas rtogs pa gdeng dang ldan pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:14444: dgongs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba dang bdun thob par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:14445: de bzhin du der yang ma zad /
NK091(ke)001:14446: dpes mtshon tshig gi lde mig gis //
NK091(ke)001:14447: mnyam nyid rig pa'i sgo dbyer 'os //
NK091(ke)001:14448: zhes pa ltar yi gesa ni 'jig rten dang 'jig
NK091(ke)001:14449: rten las 'das pa'i chos thams cad kyi don gyi
NK091(ke)001:14450: sgo yang 'gyed cing brda ril yang gsal bar 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:14451: ro // ming tshig sgron mas don gyi gser mtshon ltar //
NK091(ke)001:14453: yi ge'i rjes su don dpags na //
NK091(ke)001:14454: yi ges don rnams ston par 'gyur //
NK091(ke)001:14455: zhes pa ltar don yang mtshon par byed do //
NK091(ke)001:14456: yi ge sgra btags ming tshogs la //
NK091(ke)001:14457: brten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK091(ke)001:14459: a ni ma skyes ye shes yin //
NK091(ke)001:14460: rang bzhin thams cad stong par ston //
NK091(ke)001:14461: ces a'i sgras skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin yang rtogs par byed do //
NK091(ke)001:14463: de ltar yi ges mtshon nas ji lta ba nyid mthong zhing shes par byed de /
NK091(ke)001:14464: de dag ni 'chad pa la ltos nas bcos pa'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK091(ke)001:14465: spyir lus gnas rtsa'i yi ge ni /
NK091(ke)001:14466: rang byung gi yi ge bzhi las cho 'phrul yi ger gnas pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:14468: rtsa gnas dkyil 'khor grub pa'i gzhan yas nas //
NK091(ke)001:14469: khams kyi bdud rtsi sangs rgyas skur bzhugs shing //
NK091(ke)001:14470: grub pa sngags kyi nus mthu ngag la 'char //
NK091(ke)001:14471: snying po rlung gi thugs kyis yongs la khyab //
NK091(ke)001:14472: zhes sogs lung rnams dang sbyor la /
NK091(ke)001:14473: zhing khams cho 'phrul gyi yi ge ni /
NK091(ke)001:14474: sprul pa'i yi ge 'jig rten tha dad du 'tshol
NK091(ke)001:14475: bar spros pas gdul bya spro ba skyed pa ste
NK091(ke)001:14477: gsung gis 'dul ba'i dus byung na //
NK091(ke)001:14478: dbyangs kyi yan lag drug cu la //
NK091(ke)001:14479: sogs pa'i sgra skad thams cad dang //
NK091(ke)001:14480: yi ge'i gzugs su bstan nas ni //
NK091(ke)001:14481: 'khor ba'i khams su snang bar byed //
NK091(ke)001:14484: de dag ni yi ge'i cho 'phrul gyi sgo nas
NK091(ke)001:14485: chos nyid du rnam para snang ba ste bcos pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14491: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14493: gang gzhi ji bzhin pa chos nyid ma bcos pa
NK091(ke)001:14494: las cir snang yang cir srid kyang mtshan nyid ma
NK091(ke)001:14495: nges par de kho na nyid kyi rang bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:14496: snang ba'i cho 'phrul bstan pa gang zhee na /
NK091(ke)001:14498: rang bzhin gyi chos snang lugs bcu po 'di sgra
NK091(ke)001:14499: ji bzhin par mi lta zhing chos bcu gcig bsal
NK091(ke)001:14500: nas don bcu gcig tu snang ba'ang ma yin par
NK091(ke)001:14501: phyogs ris med la ldog sa mi 'tshol pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:14503: chos dang ldan pas chos can rgya che ba ji
NK091(ke)001:14504: snyed par zhen blo'i ngo la 'khrul pa'i mtshan mar
NK091(ke)001:14506: dper na rgyal po'i phrug gu rgyal po las nor
NK091(ke)001:14507: yang ngo bo rgyal po las ma g.yos pa dang
NK091(ke)001:14508: 'dra ba tsam gyi phyir chos nyid zab mo mtshan
NK091(ke)001:14509: ma med pa'i ngang nyid du gsal bar snang ngo
NK091(ke)001:14510: // 'gro ba sems can lus ngag yid gsum dang
NK091(ke)001:14511: ldan pa'i dngos pora snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams kyang
NK091(ke)001:14512: // / snang ba nyid na nyi ma'i zer bzhin
NK091(ke)001:14513: pas rang rig pa mtha' dang bral ba nyid brda
NK091(ke)001:14514: dang tha snyad mang por btags pa la snang ba
NK091(ke)001:14515: de dag cir snang yang snang ba mi 'gog la
NK091(ke)001:14516: snang ba med de sems nyid dngos po med pa
NK091(ke)001:14517: ye ma bcos pa'i ngang du snang ba nyid do
NK091(ke)001:14518: // / // tha snyad sna tshogs ji snyed par rnam para snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams kyang /
NK091(ke)001:14519: don la dbyer med pas chos nyid ji bzhin pa
NK091(ke)001:14520: de bzhin nyid kyi nganga du mnyam par snang ngo
NK091(ke)001:14521: // 'gro ba lnga'i sdug bsngal gyi rgyu 'du byed
NK091(ke)001:14522: lnga 'khrul pa la nyon mongs pa dug lngar snang
NK091(ke)001:14523: ba'i rang bzhin rnams kyang spu ma barjesa mdog ma
NK091(ke)001:14524: bsgyur bzos ma byas par rnam grol ye shes lnga
NK091(ke)001:14526: gti mug stong pa'i ye shes /
NK091(ke)001:14527: zhe sdang me long ye shes /
NK091(ke)001:14528: nga rgyal mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK091(ke)001:14530: phrag dog bya grub ye shes so //
NK091(ke)001:14531: nyon mongs pa dug gsum nyid khams gsum gyi gazhi'am
NK091(ke)001:14532: rtsa bar snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams kyang ye nas
NK091(ke)001:14533: ngo bo snang la med pas sku gsum lhun gyis
NK091(ke)001:14534: grub pa'ii ngang du snang ste /
NK091(ke)001:14538: 'gro ba'i yul sems la gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa
NK091(ke)001:14539: gnyis su 'khrul par snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams kyang
NK091(ke)001:14540: / ye nas dbyings dang ye shesa gnyis su meda pa'i ngang du brdal bar snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:14541: skye 'gro'i bya ba yul dang byed pa shes par cir yang snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams kyang /
NK091(ke)001:14542: ther zug dang rgyun med par thabs dang shes rab
NK091(ke)001:14543: bdag nyid chen por 'brel te dbyer med pa'i ngang
NK091(ke)001:14545: mtshan nyid mi rtag pas 'jig pa'i tshogs can phung
NK091(ke)001:14546: po lnga'i dngos por snang ba'i rang bzhin rnams kyang
NK091(ke)001:14547: ma spangs par 'khor ba las rnam par grol ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14548: zag pa med pa tshul khrims ting 'dzin shes rab
NK091(ke)001:14550: rnam grol ye shes mthong ba'i phung po'i ngang du
NK091(ke)001:14551: sangs rgyas te rigs kyi rgyal ba lngar snang ba
NK091(ke)001:14552: nyid do // kun nasa nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i
NK091(ke)001:14553: rang bzhin du snang ba rnams kyang 'khor ba rang
NK091(ke)001:14554: rgyud ka nas bral bas de nyid rnam par byang
NK091(ke)001:14555: ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i ngang du yang dag
NK091(ke)001:14556: nyid do // par snang ngo // 'jig pa'i rten
NK091(ke)001:14557: du gyur pa'i nang bcud g.yo ba'i rdul dang phyi
NK091(ke)001:14558: snod mi g.yo ba'i rdul du snang ba'i rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:14559: rnams kyang rang rig rang snang bas rgyal ba bzhi
NK091(ke)001:14560: bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor gcig dang du ma
NK091(ke)001:14561: las grol ba'i ngang nyid du rnam par snang ngo
NK091(ke)001:14562: nyid do // par snang ngo // // mya ngan
NK091(ke)001:14563: las 'das pa dang 'khor ba'i rang bzhin gyi dngos
NK091(ke)001:14564: po gnyis pa ril du gyur pa rnams ye nas
NK091(ke)001:14565: lhun gyis grub pas brtsal ba med par ma bslad
NK091(ke)001:14566: pas ma bcos shing ji bzhin pa de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:14567: kyi ngang du bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rnam par
NK091(ke)001:14569: zhes de dag thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs
NK091(ke)001:14570: rje'i cho 'phrul gyi sgrar sngon byung du yongs su
NK091(ke)001:14571: grags shing da ltar yang grags par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:14572: de dag ni byed pa med par rang snang la
NK091(ke)001:14573: ma nges pas ji bzhin pa nyid kyi phyir ming
NK091(ke)001:14575: snang ba'ang snang ba yod pa'i phyogs las btags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14576: tha snyad de ngo bo ni snang mi snang las
NK091(ke)001:14577: grol ba'o // de 'khor gyi rig pa la brjod
NK091(ke)001:14578: pa dang 'dra bar grags shing 'jal ba'ang zhing ril
NK091(ke)001:14579: grol ba'o // du'o // gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:14583: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14584: lang ka'i bdag po de dag ni chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul te /
NK091(ke)001:14585: de dag kyang so sor ma 'dres par dbyings kyi
NK091(ke)001:14586: chos nyid gcig tu yongs su rdzogs par 'grel to
NK091(ke)001:14587: // des kyang byung tshul gyi don gsal bar bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:14588: de ltar chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul gyi don 'di
NK091(ke)001:14589: nyid a nu yo ga'i rang lugs ji lta ba
NK091(ke)001:14590: bzhin du mdo chen po'i dgongs don thun mong min
NK091(ke)001:14591: par rgyud las 'byung ba dang man ngag dang 'grel
NK091(ke)001:14592: pa kun gyis ji ltar bkral ba bzhin ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:14593: 'dus gsal du bkod par byas pas spyir khro bo
NK091(ke)001:14594: lha rgyud chen po las gsungs pa ltar theg pa
NK091(ke)001:14595: rim pa dgu dang bye brag tu /
NK091(ke)001:14596: rnal 'byor chen po nang pa ni //
NK091(ke)001:14597: rang byung 'od gsal chos kyi sku //
NK091(ke)001:14599: thun mong drug khyad khro phyir sprul //
NK091(ke)001:14600: rdzogs pa rjes su rnal 'byor ni //
NK091(ke)001:14604: rdzogs chen theg pa'i yang rtse ni //
NK091(ke)001:14605: ye ji bzhin smra bsam 'das chos //
NK091(ke)001:14606: thun mong lhun grub longs spyod rdzogs //
NK091(ke)001:14607: cir yang snang ba de kho na //
NK091(ke)001:14608: sku gsum khyad che sems bskyed tshul //
NK091(ke)001:14610: ma h+aa las 'phags shing a ti yo ga'i khyad
NK091(ke)001:14611: chos rnams kyi gegs bsal ba'i tshul gyis sku gsum
NK091(ke)001:14612: gyi chos snang ba dang sbyor te spyi rgya legs
NK091(ke)001:14613: par gcod cing skabs kyi dgongs gnad nor 'khrul dang
NK091(ke)001:14614: bral ba rnyed par bya ste 'dir yi ges 'jigs
NK091(ke)001:14616: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdoo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:14617: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul gyi don bstan pa zhes
NK091(ke)001:14618: bya ba'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa rnam par bshad
NK091(ke)001:14619: pa'o ////gsum pa kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul la gsum
NK091(ke)001:14627: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14630: chos kun gyi don brjod pa'i cho 'phrul zhes nges
NK091(ke)001:14631: tshig gis nye bar brjod pa de nyid gang zhe
NK091(ke)001:14633: rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa'i chos kun gyi spyi
NK091(ke)001:14634: dang rang gi mtshan nyid gnyis byang chub kyi sems
NK091(ke)001:14635: sum 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:14636: chos nyid de kho na nyid du nges par gnas
NK091(ke)001:14637: pa'i gzhi'i bzhugs tshul ji ltar yin pa'i don de
NK091(ke)001:14638: nyid ji lta ba bzhin du sgro skur med par
NK091(ke)001:14639: phyin ci ma log pa nyid du nges don gyi
NK091(ke)001:14640: tshig tu phyung nas brjod pa des na nges pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14641: tshig kyang 'grub ste de nyid mtha'i spros pa ma
NK091(ke)001:14642: spangs rnam par dag pa'i lam chen po ma nor
NK091(ke)001:14643: ba yang dag pa nyid yin par nges par bzhag
NK091(ke)001:14644: go // de bas na mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14645: 'bras bu mthar thug pa sku dang gsung dang thugs
NK091(ke)001:14646: kyi rang bzhin de yang don de las gzhan ganga
NK091(ke)001:14647: na'ang med de ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi byang chub
NK091(ke)001:14648: kyi sems de kho na nyid mngon du gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:14649: go // yin la / des na sgron ma bkod
NK091(ke)001:14650: pa lta bu 'khor ba'i dpung bcom pas dpag tu
NK091(ke)001:14651: med pa'i rgyal ba mtha' yasa pa rnams kyang gzhan
NK091(ke)001:14652: go // yin la / na med de / rang
NK091(ke)001:14653: gi sems kyi chos nyid de kho na nyid yin
NK091(ke)001:14654: pas gcig dang du ma las grol bar bstan pa'o
NK091(ke)001:14655: go // yin la / na med de / // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:14657: gang gi spyod yul yin pa /
NK091(ke)001:14658: rtogs ma rtogs kyi skyon yon no //
NK091(ke)001:14660: 'khor ba ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:14661: mya ngan las 'das pa ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:14662: 'khor 'das thams cad ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:14664: nyon mongs pa lnga ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14665: phung po lnga ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14672: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad lngas bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14673: dngos po 'khrul pa dang lam dang 'bras bu ji
NK091(ke)001:14674: snyed brjod pa'i dang po bstan pa gang snyam pa
NK091(ke)001:14675: la / gzhal bya'i ngo ti ma rig pa'am gti
NK091(ke)001:14676: mug rang gi mtshan nyid chos gzhan dang ma 'dresa
NK091(ke)001:14678: dus dang skabs ril du don mi shes te kun nas rmongs pas 'byed pa med pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:14679: de nyid ye nas rig pa byang chub kyi sems
NK091(ke)001:14680: nyid du yongs su rdzogs pasa ye shes rang gsal
NK091(ke)001:14681: ba'i ngo bo la ma rig pa ma spangs la
NK091(ke)001:14682: ma grub pas stong ste brtags pa'i bdag bral te
NK091(ke)001:14683: meda pa ni spyi'i mtshan nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:14684: de ltar spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid gnyis po
NK091(ke)001:14685: de nyid so sor snang ba ma 'gags bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:14686: ngo bo bstan du yang med pas mtha' gnyis las
NK091(ke)001:14687: grol ba'i phyir ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo gnyis
NK091(ke)001:14689: de nyid gnas lugs min pa la yin par ma
NK091(ke)001:14690: byas par gti mug nyid chos thams cad kyi ji
NK091(ke)001:14691: bzhin pa yin par sangs rgyas pas na ye nas
NK091(ke)001:14692: ma bcosa pa'i de bzhin nyid de ma nor ba
NK091(ke)001:14693: de kho na nyid du gsal bas gti mug nyid
NK091(ke)001:14694: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK091(ke)001:14695: de bzhin du zhe sdang gi rang mtshan gzhan dang
NK091(ke)001:14696: ma 'dres par pha rol la kun nas mnar sems
NK091(ke)001:14697: pa de nyid rig pa byang chub kyi sems la
NK091(ke)001:14698: yongs su rdzogs pas zhe sdang ma spangs la ma
NK091(ke)001:14699: grub pas stong zhing brtags pa'i bdag meda pa ni
NK091(ke)001:14701: de ltar rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid gnyis po de
NK091(ke)001:14702: nyid mtha' gnyis las grol te ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:14703: ngo bo dbyer med du rang gsal la yul dang
NK091(ke)001:14704: bral ba na / ye nas ma bcos par chos
NK091(ke)001:14705: nyid de bzhin nyid de kho na nyid de zhe
NK091(ke)001:14706: sdang nyid me long ye shes su gsal lo //
NK091(ke)001:14707: nga rgyal gyi rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par
NK091(ke)001:14708: myong zhing khengs pas ri bo gzhan zil gyis gnon
NK091(ke)001:14709: pas che bar rlom pa de nyid rig pa byang
NK091(ke)001:14710: chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs pas nga rgyal
NK091(ke)001:14711: ma spangs la ma grub pas stong zhing brtags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14712: bdag med pa ni spyi'i mtshan nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:14713: de ltar mtshan nyid gnyis po de nyid mtha' dang
NK091(ke)001:14714: bral te ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo gnyis med
NK091(ke)001:14715: du mnyam par gyur na ye nas ma bcos par
NK091(ke)001:14716: chos nyid de bzhin nyid mi bslu bas de kho
NK091(ke)001:14717: na nyid de nga rgyal nyid mnyam nyid ye shes
NK091(ke)001:14718: su rgyas so // nyon mongs pa 'dod chagsa kyi
NK091(ke)001:14719: rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par 'dod pa'i yul
NK091(ke)001:14720: la kun tu zhen te mi gtong ba de nyid
NK091(ke)001:14721: rig pa byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:14722: pasa 'dod chags ma spangs la ma grub pas stong
NK091(ke)001:14723: zhing brtags pa'i bdag med pa ni spyi'i mtshan nyid
NK091(ke)001:14724: su rgyas so // de / de ltar mtshan nyid
NK091(ke)001:14725: gnyis nyid mtha' dang bral te ma 'dresa yongs rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:14726: ngo bo dbyer med du gyur te kun mkhyen pa
NK091(ke)001:14727: na ye nas ma bcos par chos nyid de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:14728: nyid de kho na nyid de 'dod chags nyid kun
NK091(ke)001:14730: phrag dog gi rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par
NK091(ke)001:14731: gzhan gyi phun tshogs la mi bzod par kun nasa
NK091(ke)001:14732: 'khrug ste mi shong ba de nyid rig pa byang
NK091(ke)001:14733: chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs pasa phrag dog
NK091(ke)001:14734: ma spangs la ma grub pas stong zhing brtags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14735: bdag med pa ni spyi mtshan te /
NK091(ke)001:14736: gnyis po de nyid mtha' dang bral te ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:14737: yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du bya rtsol bral
NK091(ke)001:14738: bar lhun gyis grub na ye nas ma bcos par
NK091(ke)001:14739: chos nyid de bzhin nyid de kho na nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14740: phrag dog nyid bya grub ye shes su shar ro
NK091(ke)001:14745: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad drug gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14746: gzugs kyi phung po'i rang mtshan ni gzhan dang ma
NK091(ke)001:14747: 'dres par rkyen gyis 'jig cing gzhom du rung ba
NK091(ke)001:14748: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:14749: pasa spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14750: / de gnyis nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du snang na /
NK091(ke)001:14751: ye nas ma bcos par rang snang de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:14752: de kho na nyid de gzugs phung nyid rnam par
NK091(ke)001:14753: snang mdzad du phyi nang med pa snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:14754: de bzhin du tshor ba'i phung po'i rang mtshan snang
NK091(ke)001:14755: ba gzhan dang 'dres par gnyis med kyi rnam par
NK091(ke)001:14756: nyams su myong ba nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:14757: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:14758: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14759: / de gnyis nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du mnyam na /
NK091(ke)001:14760: ye nas ma bcos par rang snang de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:14761: de kho na nyid de tshor phung nyid phyogs ris
NK091(ke)001:14762: med par rin chen 'byung ldan du gdal lo //
NK091(ke)001:14763: 'du shes kyi rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par
NK091(ke)001:14764: mtshan mar 'dzin pa de nyid byang chub kyi sems
NK091(ke)001:14765: la yongs su rdzogs pasa spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag
NK091(ke)001:14767: de gnyis nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du gsal na /
NK091(ke)001:14768: ye nas ma bcos par rang snang de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:14769: de kho na nyid de 'du shes kyi phung po
NK091(ke)001:14770: nyid gzung 'dzin med par snang ba mtha' yas su
NK091(ke)001:14771: shar ro // 'du byed kyi phung po'i rang mtshan
NK091(ke)001:14772: gzhan dang ma 'dres par sems pas yul mngon du
NK091(ke)001:14773: 'du bar byed de rang dbang med par rjes su
NK091(ke)001:14774: 'brang ba nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su
NK091(ke)001:14775: rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:14776: shar ro // de / de gnyis nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du grol na /
NK091(ke)001:14777: ye nas ma bcos par rang snang de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:14778: de kho na nyid de 'du byed kyi phung po
NK091(ke)001:14779: don yod grub par 'gro 'ong med par dag go
NK091(ke)001:14780: // rnam shes rig pa'i rang mtshan gzhan dang ma
NK091(ke)001:14781: 'dres par yul dus rnam pa tha dad du shes
NK091(ke)001:14782: pa nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:14783: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14784: // / de gnyis nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du rig na /
NK091(ke)001:14785: ye nas ma bcos par rang snang de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:14786: de kho na nyid de rnam shes kyi phung po
NK091(ke)001:14787: nyid mtha' dbus med par rdo rje mi bskyod par
NK091(ke)001:14788: gsal lo // tshor ba'i bye brag sdug bsngal gyi
NK091(ke)001:14789: rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par sgo gsum kun
NK091(ke)001:14790: nas gdung ba nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs
NK091(ke)001:14791: su rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa
NK091(ke)001:14792: gsal lo // nyid de / de gnyis nyid ma
NK091(ke)001:14793: 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du mnyam na
NK091(ke)001:14794: gsal lo // nyid de / / ye nas ma
NK091(ke)001:14795: bcos par rang snang de bzhin nyid de kho na
NK091(ke)001:14801: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14802: khams bco brgyad kyi rang gi mtshan nyid ni gzhan
NK091(ke)001:14803: dang ma 'dresa par byed pa med par rang gi
NK091(ke)001:14804: rigs 'dzin pa'am skyed par byed pa'i nus pa can
NK091(ke)001:14806: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogsa
NK091(ke)001:14807: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14808: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du chub na /
NK091(ke)001:14809: ye nas ma bcos par chos dbyings de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:14810: de kho na nyid mu mtha' med par khyab pa'o
NK091(ke)001:14815: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14816: skye mcheda bcu gnyis kyi rang mtshan gzhan dang ma
NK091(ke)001:14817: 'dres par shes pa yul la skye zhing mched pa'i
NK091(ke)001:14818: sgo nyid de / de nyid rang rig pa byang
NK091(ke)001:14819: chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs pas spyi mtshan
NK091(ke)001:14820: stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:14821: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du gnas na /
NK091(ke)001:14822: ye nas ma bcos par rang gsal de bzhin nyid de kho na nyid kyi bdag nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:14827: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14828: dang po brgyad pa dgu pa gsum rgyu dang /
NK091(ke)001:14829: gnyis dang bcu pa rkyen te /
NK091(ke)001:14830: lhag ma bdun 'bras bu'i tshul du rten cing 'brel
NK091(ke)001:14831: bar 'byung ba'i rang mtshan kun nas ma 'dres par
NK091(ke)001:14832: 'du zhing 'phrad pas rten cing 'byung ba nyid la
NK091(ke)001:14833: / de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su
NK091(ke)001:14834: rdzogsa pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa de
NK091(ke)001:14835: nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med 'dus
NK091(ke)001:14836: ma byas pa'i ngang klong du grol na /
NK091(ke)001:14837: ye nas ma bcos par gnas lugs de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:14838: bslu med de kho na nyid de 'gyur ba med
NK091(ke)001:14839: pa'o // ji skad bshad pa'i chos de dag gi
NK091(ke)001:14840: 'khor ba nyid mya ngan las 'das par gnas kyi
NK091(ke)001:14841: pa'o // / de dag spangs pa'i pha rol na mya ngan las 'das pa med par ston no //
NK091(ke)001:14846: pha rol phyin drug ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14847: tshad med snyoms 'jug ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14848: rnam thar gyi sgo ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14849: rnam thar brgyad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs so //
NK091(ke)001:14854: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad drug gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14855: zas nor sogs la ma chags pa sbyin pa'i pha
NK091(ke)001:14856: rol tu phyin pa'i rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:14857: par kun nas gtong ba nyid la /
NK091(ke)001:14858: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogsa
NK091(ke)001:14859: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14860: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du rtogs na /
NK091(ke)001:14861: ye ma bcos par de bzhin nyid du mthar phyin pa'i lam gyi de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:14862: sgo gsum dag pa tshul khrims kyi pha rol tu
NK091(ke)001:14863: phyin pa'i rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par 'chal
NK091(ke)001:14864: ba'am nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14865: / de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su
NK091(ke)001:14866: rdzogsa pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:14867: / de / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du rtogs na /
NK091(ke)001:14868: ye ma bcos par de bzhin nyid du mthar phyin pa'i lam gyi de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:14869: mi mthun pas mi g.yo ba bzod pa'i pha rol
NK091(ke)001:14870: tu phyin pa'i rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par
NK091(ke)001:14872: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogsa
NK091(ke)001:14873: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14874: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du rtogs na /
NK091(ke)001:14875: ye ma bcos par de bzhin nyid du mthar phyin pa'i lam gyi de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:14876: don dang ldan pa'i yon tan sgrub pas brtson 'grus
NK091(ke)001:14877: kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i rang mtshan gzhan dang
NK091(ke)001:14878: ma 'dres par bar chad kyis thub pa med pa'am
NK091(ke)001:14879: don du 'gyur ba'i las la ngal zhing dub pa
NK091(ke)001:14881: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogsa
NK091(ke)001:14882: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14883: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du rtogs na /
NK091(ke)001:14884: ye ma bcos par de bzhin nyid du mthar phyin pa'i lam gyi de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:14885: bsam bya de kho na nyid kyi don la brtan
NK091(ke)001:14886: pa thob pa bsam gtan gyi pha rol tu phyin
NK091(ke)001:14887: pa'i rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par sems yul
NK091(ke)001:14888: la mi 'phro bar sdud pa nyid yin la /
NK091(ke)001:14889: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogsa
NK091(ke)001:14890: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14891: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du rtogs na /
NK091(ke)001:14892: ye ma bcos par de bzhin nyid du mthar phyin pa'i lam gyi de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:14893: zab pa dang rgya che ba'i chos rnams kyi mtshan
NK091(ke)001:14894: nyid rnam par 'byed cing lhag par gcod pa shes
NK091(ke)001:14895: rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i rang mtshan gzhan
NK091(ke)001:14896: dang ma 'dres par chagsa pa dang thogs pa med
NK091(ke)001:14897: pa nyid la / de nyid byang chub kyi sems
NK091(ke)001:14898: la yongs su rdzogsa pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag
NK091(ke)001:14900: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du rtogs na /
NK091(ke)001:14901: ye nas ma bcos par de bzhin nyid kyi ngang
NK091(ke)001:14902: du mthar phyin pa'i lam gyi de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:14907: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14908: gzugs kyi sa pa bsam gtan rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK091(ke)001:14910: gzugs med pa'i snyoms 'jug bzhi ste bcu gnyis kyi
NK091(ke)001:14911: rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par de dag g.yo
NK091(ke)001:14912: ba med pas mi 'khruga pa nyid la /
NK091(ke)001:14913: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogsa
NK091(ke)001:14914: pas spyi mtshan stong pa dang bdag med pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:14915: de / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi chos
NK091(ke)001:14916: nyid ngo bo dbyer med mnyam pa nyid du gyur
NK091(ke)001:14917: pa de nges par mthong na ye nas ma bcos
NK091(ke)001:14918: par de bzhin nyid kyi ngang de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:14922: sgo gsum bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:14927: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14928: spyir rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi po kun kyang
NK091(ke)001:14929: rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par 'khor 'das dang
NK091(ke)001:14930: mtshan nyid kyi mtha' kun las nges par 'byung ba
NK091(ke)001:14931: nyid la / de nyid ji bzhin pa'i byang chub
NK091(ke)001:14932: sems la yongs su rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing
NK091(ke)001:14934: de ltar mtshan nyid gnyis po nyid ma 'dres yongs
NK091(ke)001:14935: rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med ye rdzogs kyi bdag nyid
NK091(ke)001:14937: ye ma bcos par chos nyid de bzhin nyid rang byung gi ye shes de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:14938: 'di nyid 'grel chen las khams gnyis kyi nyon mongs pa kun las 'byung ba'i don du bshad cing /
NK091(ke)001:14939: phyag mchan la lar don dang tshig dang sngags dang
NK091(ke)001:14940: yi ge'i sgo bzhi kun tu 'byung ba la'ang gsungs
NK091(ke)001:14945: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig dang rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14946: stong pa nyid kyi rnam par thar pa'i sgo yi
NK091(ke)001:14947: rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par ngo bos dben
NK091(ke)001:14949: mtshan ma med pa'i rnam par thar pa'i sgo'i rang
NK091(ke)001:14950: mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par dmigs mtshan zhi ba
NK091(ke)001:14951: nyid yin la / smon pa med pa'i rnam par
NK091(ke)001:14952: thar pa'i sgo'i rang mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par
NK091(ke)001:14953: sdug bsngal bral ba'am sel ba'i rang rang gi rnam
NK091(ke)001:14954: nyid yin la / cha can nyid / rtsa ba
NK091(ke)001:14955: byang chub kyi sems la yongsa su rdzogs pas spyi
NK091(ke)001:14956: mtshan de dang de'i mtha'i rnam pas stong zhing bdag
NK091(ke)001:14958: de dag nyid kyang ma 'dres yongsa rdzogs ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:14959: dbyer med kun grol chen por gsal bar rtogs na
NK091(ke)001:14960: / ye nas ma bcos par gnyug ma don gyi
NK091(ke)001:14961: de bzhin nyid sems kyi rang bzhin de kho na
NK091(ke)001:14966: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14967: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rang gi mtshan nyid
NK091(ke)001:14968: ma 'dres par rang sa'i sgrib pa las grol te
NK091(ke)001:14969: sa lam gong nas gong du 'phags pas rnam par
NK091(ke)001:14971: de rnams byang chub kyi sems la yongsa su rdzogsa
NK091(ke)001:14972: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing badga med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:14973: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer
NK091(ke)001:14974: med ji bzhin par rtogs na ye nas ma bcos
NK091(ke)001:14975: par chos dbyings de bzhin nyid de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:14976: / du grol ba'o // gnyis pa la bcu ste /
NK091(ke)001:14979: 'bras bu'i tshad med bzhi ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14980: gzungs kyi sgo ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14981: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14982: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14983: mngon shes drug ma 'dres yongs rdzogs /
NK091(ke)001:14986: sku gsum ma 'dres yongs rdzogs so //
NK091(ke)001:14991: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:14992: rgyal ba rnams kyi stobs bcu po rnams kyi rang
NK091(ke)001:14993: mtshan ni kun nas ma 'dres par gdona mi za
NK091(ke)001:14994: bar zil gyis gnon pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:14995: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:14996: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid la
NK091(ke)001:14997: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med mkhyen pa mthar phyin pas na /
NK091(ke)001:14998: ye nas ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid gdal khyab
NK091(ke)001:14999: chen po'i de kho na nyid mngon du gyur pa'o
NK091(ke)001:15004: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15005: mi 'jigsa pa bzhi'i rang mtshan kun nas ma 'dres par ye shes shin tu brtan pa nyid la /
NK091(ke)001:15006: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15007: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid pas
NK091(ke)001:15008: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer
NK091(ke)001:15009: med du gzigs pa dag cing don gnyis mthar phyin
NK091(ke)001:15010: / pas na / ye nas ma bcos pa'i de
NK091(ke)001:15011: bzhin nyid sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba'i de
NK091(ke)001:15012: kho na nyid mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15017: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad bzhis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15018: snying rje chen po'i rang mtshan kun nas ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:15019: par 'gro ba kun sdug bsngal las skyob pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:15020: yin la / de nyid byang chub kyi sems la
NK091(ke)001:15021: yongs su rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med
NK091(ke)001:15022: yin la / pa nyid de / de nyid ma
NK091(ke)001:15023: 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du mkhyen pa
NK091(ke)001:15025: ye nas ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid dag pa gnyis ldan gyi de khoo na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:15026: byams pa chen po'i rang mtshan kun nas ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:15027: par gzhan la dngos su phan 'dogs pa yin la
NK091(ke)001:15028: / de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su
NK091(ke)001:15029: rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:15030: / de / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo

NK091(ke)001:15032: / de / / ye nas ma bcos pa'i de
NK091(ke)001:15033: bzhin nyid dag pa gnyis ldan gyi de kho na
NK091(ke)001:15034: / de / / nyid do // dga' ba chen
NK091(ke)001:15035: po'i rang mtshan kun nas ma 'dres par sngar gyi
NK091(ke)001:15036: don la phyis 'gyod pa med par gsal ba yin
NK091(ke)001:15038: nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs pas
NK091(ke)001:15039: spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15040: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du mkhyen pa mthar phyin pas na /
NK091(ke)001:15041: ye nas ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid dag pa gnyis ldan gyi de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:15042: btang snyoms chen po'i rang mtshan kun nas ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:15043: par dog pa med par yangs pas mnyam pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:15044: yin la / de nyid byang chub kyi sems la
NK091(ke)001:15045: yongs su rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med
NK091(ke)001:15046: yin la / pa nyid de / de gnyis nyid
NK091(ke)001:15047: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du mkhyen
NK091(ke)001:15049: ye nas ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid dag pa gnyis ldan gyi de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:15054: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15055: gzung sa kyi sgo lnga brgya rnams kyi rang mtshan
NK091(ke)001:15056: ni kun nas ma 'dres par don dang 'brel ba
NK091(ke)001:15057: nyid yin la / de rnams byang chub kyi sems
NK091(ke)001:15058: la yongs su rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag
NK091(ke)001:15059: med pa nyid pas de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15060: ngo bo dbyer med du mkhyen pa mthar phyin te
NK091(ke)001:15061: bsnyel ba mi mnga' bas na /
NK091(ke)001:15062: ye nas ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid nges pa don gyi de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:15067: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15068: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag rnams kyi rang
NK091(ke)001:15069: mtshan kun nas ma 'dres par don las gzhan du
NK091(ke)001:15070: mi g.yeng bas yul gyis mi 'phrog pa yin la
NK091(ke)001:15071: / de rnams byang chub kyi sems la yongs su
NK091(ke)001:15072: rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:15073: / pas / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo
NK091(ke)001:15074: bo dbyer med du mkhyen te ngang las mi g.yo
NK091(ke)001:15075: / pas / bas na / ye nas ma bcos
NK091(ke)001:15076: pa'i de bzhin nyid dgongs pa tshad du phyin pa'i
NK091(ke)001:15082: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15083: sangs rgyas kyi chos ma 'dres pa bco brgyad kyi
NK091(ke)001:15084: rang mtshan nyid gang dang yang ma 'dres par gzhan
NK091(ke)001:15085: gyis mi 'phrog pa khyad par dang ldan pa yin
NK091(ke)001:15086: la / de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs
NK091(ke)001:15087: su rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa
NK091(ke)001:15088: la / nyid pas / de nyid ma 'dres yongs
NK091(ke)001:15089: rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du mnga' dbang thob pas
NK091(ke)001:15090: la / nyid pas / na / ye nas ma
NK091(ke)001:15091: bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid dgongs pa'i mkhyen spyod mthar
NK091(ke)001:15092: phyin pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:15097: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /

NK091(ke)001:15099: chen po drug gi rang mtshan rnam kun ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:15100: par mngona sum du gsal ba yin la /
NK091(ke)001:15101: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15102: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid pas
NK091(ke)001:15103: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du gsal bas na /
NK091(ke)001:15104: ye nas ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid gsal zhing dag pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:15105: mngon par shes pa rnams kyi yul chos can ji
NK091(ke)001:15106: snyed pa thams cad kyi rang mtshan kun nas ma
NK091(ke)001:15107: 'dres par rnam pa sna tshogs pa yin la /
NK091(ke)001:15108: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15109: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid pas
NK091(ke)001:15110: / de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer
NK091(ke)001:15111: med du gsal 'grib med par mkhyen pa mthar phyin
NK091(ke)001:15112: / pas na / ye nas ma bcos pa'i de
NK091(ke)001:15113: bzhin nyid rang snang ba'i de kho na nyid do
NK091(ke)001:15114: / pas na / // 'di gnyis mdo sgyu la
NK091(ke)001:15115: grags pa ltar ka dag chen po dang lhun grub
NK091(ke)001:15116: chen po la bzhed pa'ang yod par mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:15121: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15122: shes bya'i rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:15123: kyi rang mtshan kun nas ma 'dres par ji ltar
NK091(ke)001:15124: ji snyed kyi rnam pa kun skad cig gis mkhyen
NK091(ke)001:15125: la ngo bo la skad cig gi skye 'gag med
NK091(ke)001:15127: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15128: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid pas
NK091(ke)001:15129: / de ltar rang spyi gnyis po nyid ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:15130: yongs rdzogs rang bzhin gnyis su med par mkhyen pa
NK091(ke)001:15131: sgrib med du gsal bas na /
NK091(ke)001:15132: ye nas ma bcos pa'i chos nyid de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:15133: rang gsal rig pa'i de kho na nyid mthar phyin
NK091(ke)001:15134: pa'o // snga ma'i tshigs bcad phyi ma dang 'di
NK091(ke)001:15135: gnyis chos can de'i chos nyid gzigs pas ji lta
NK091(ke)001:15136: ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis la sbyar ba'ang
NK091(ke)001:15137: pa'o // bzhugs so // dgu pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:15141: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15142: chos kyi dbyings nyid kyi rang mtshan dngos po med
NK091(ke)001:15143: la ji ltar bltas pa ltar mi zad par 'byung
NK091(ke)001:15144: ba yin la / de nyid byang chub kyi sems
NK091(ke)001:15145: la yongs su rdzogs pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag
NK091(ke)001:15147: de ltar mtshan nyid gnyis po ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15148: ngo bo dbyer med du klong chen po gcig gi
NK091(ke)001:15149: dbyings su mnyam par gyur pas na /
NK091(ke)001:15150: ye nas ma bcos pa'i chos nyid dbyings kyi de
NK091(ke)001:15151: bzhin nyid mi bslu ba'i de kho na nyid mngon
NK091(ke)001:15152: du gyur pa'o // bcu pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:15156: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gsum gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15157: 'bras bu mthar thug sprul pa yi sku'i rang mtshan
NK091(ke)001:15158: kun nas ma 'dres par dngos po med par 'gro
NK091(ke)001:15159: ba'i don du gang 'dul ltar 'byung zhing rgyun mi
NK091(ke)001:15161: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15162: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:15163: / de ltar rang spyi gnyis nyid ma 'dres yongs
NK091(ke)001:15164: rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med pa'i thugs rje chen por
NK091(ke)001:15165: / gsal bas na / ye nas ma bcos pa'i
NK091(ke)001:15166: de bzhin nyid rang rig pa de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:15167: kyi rol pa 'gag pa med pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15168: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi rang mtshan kun nas
NK091(ke)001:15169: ma 'dres par zhing dang longs spyod kyi yon tan
NK091(ke)001:15170: phun sum tshogs pa nyid yin la /
NK091(ke)001:15171: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15172: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:15173: / de ltar rang spyi'i mtshan nyid gnyis po ma
NK091(ke)001:15174: 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med du mtha' bral
NK091(ke)001:15175: gsal dag tu rdzogs pas na /
NK091(ke)001:15176: ye nas ma bcos pa'i rang snang de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:15177: rang rig bde ba chen po'i de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:15178: mthar phyin pa'o // rnam grol chos kyi sku yi
NK091(ke)001:15179: rang mtshan kun nas ma 'dres par spros pa thams
NK091(ke)001:15180: cad dang bral te dbyings dang ye shes su 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:15181: pa tsam yang rnam par dag pa rang byung gi
NK091(ke)001:15183: de nyid byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15184: pas spyi mtshan stong zhing bdag med pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:15185: / de ltar mtshan nyid gnyis po mtha' dang bral
NK091(ke)001:15186: te ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med thig
NK091(ke)001:15187: le nyag gcig tu gsal bas na /
NK091(ke)001:15188: ye nas ma bcos pa'i dri med dag pa'i de
NK091(ke)001:15189: bzhin nyid rang byung rig pa'i dee kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:15190: ji lta ba bzhin du mngon du gyur pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15195: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15196: mdor na lam dang rgyal ba'i yon tan thams cad dang /
NK091(ke)001:15197: 'gro ba rigs drug gis bsdus pa'i 'khor ba dang
NK091(ke)001:15198: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad kyi rang
NK091(ke)001:15199: mtshan gzhan dang ma 'dres par so sor bya ba
NK091(ke)001:15200: byed pas tha dad pa nyid yin la /
NK091(ke)001:15201: de dag kun kyang ye nas dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer
NK091(ke)001:15202: med pa'i byang chub kyi sems la yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15203: pasa spyi mtshan 'khor 'das ma spangs la ma grub
NK091(ke)001:15204: pas stong zhing brtags pa'i bdag med pa nyid du
NK091(ke)001:15205: gnas te / de ltar rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid
NK091(ke)001:15206: gnyis po ma 'dres yongs rdzogs ngo bo dbyer med
NK091(ke)001:15207: chen por lhun gyis grub par gyur pa na /
NK091(ke)001:15208: ye nas ma bcos par chos nyid gdod ma'i gshis
NK091(ke)001:15209: lugs gnyug ma don gyi de bzhin nyid dbyings dang
NK091(ke)001:15210: ye shes gnyis su med pa'i de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:15211: ye ji bzhin pa'i gsang ba dam pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15216: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15217: de ltar chos kun gyi don brjod pa'i cho 'phrul gyi thabs las /
NK091(ke)001:15218: skabs 'dir 'khor 'das lam gsum gyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK091(ke)001:15219: thams cad ye nas ma bcos par chos nyid de
NK091(ke)001:15220: bzhin nyid du rang snang zhing rang rig de kho
NK091(ke)001:15221: na nyid du gsal ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:15222: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs gnyis su med pa'i thabs byung don gyi gnas lugs so //
NK091(ke)001:15223: 'o na gnyis su med par 'dod dam zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15224: mtha' gnyis las grol ba'i don la dbu mar yang
NK091(ke)001:15225: mi dmigs pas mu bzhi mtha' drug gi spros pa
NK091(ke)001:15226: kun dang bral ba'i 'od gsal bsam gyis mi khyab
NK091(ke)001:15227: pa snying po don gyi gsang ba mthar thug pa
NK091(ke)001:15228: nyid de / rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK091(ke)001:15229: rgyal tshab skyes bu dam pa'i yul du gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:15230: dbang po yang rab mchog dang ldan pa dag gis
NK091(ke)001:15231: spyod yul kho na yin te /
NK091(ke)001:15232: slob dpon chen po rdo rje bzhad pas /
NK091(ke)001:15233: rnal 'byor rig pa'i nyi ma las /
NK091(ke)001:15234: 'o na byang chub kyi sems snang ba 'ba' zhig tu lta'o zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15235: de ni rtog ge ba rnams tshig gang ltar brjod
NK091(ke)001:15236: pa ltar blo skye ba ste mtha' dang bral zhes
NK091(ke)001:15237: brjod na yang mtha' dang bral ba zhig tu blo
NK091(ke)001:15238: la skye bar byed de mtha' ma spangs pa ma
NK091(ke)001:15239: mthong / thams cad mkhyen pa zhes brjod na yang
NK091(ke)001:15240: snang ba gsal gsal po zhig tu lta bar byed
NK091(ke)001:15241: mthong / de / de'i ngo bo dmigs su med pa mthong /
NK091(ke)001:15242: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa zhes brjod na yang /
NK091(ke)001:15244: yongs su rdzogs pas du ma bsal te /
NK091(ke)001:15245: gcig dang du ma dang bral bar lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:15246: de nyid ni gcig du ma kun dngos nyag gcig
NK091(ke)001:15247: ji ma spangs pa yan lag med par rtsis las
NK091(ke)001:15248: 'das pas smra bsam las 'das pa ma mthong ngo
NK091(ke)001:15250: skyes bu yang rab rnams ni gang brjod pa thams
NK091(ke)001:15251: cad de dang mi mthun pa dgrol ba'i dgos ched
NK091(ke)001:15253: phyogs re'i don mtshon par chud pas /
NK091(ke)001:15254: de dag ltar phyogs la blo mi gtod de /
NK091(ke)001:15255: de bas na lta ba la gza' gtad med de /
NK091(ke)001:15256: gang gza' ba ni rtsol ba byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15257: gtad pa ni dmigs pa ste 'di la rgyu 'bras
NK091(ke)001:15258: gnyis su med pa'i phyir thob par rtsol ba dang
NK091(ke)001:15259: / dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i phyir dmigs gtad dang bral ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:15260: 'on kyang gza' gtad dmigs pa'i lta ba grol bar bya ba'i phyir brjod kyi /
NK091(ke)001:15261: nges par gza' gtad dang bral bar 'dod pa yang med do //
NK091(ke)001:15263: gza' gtad dang bral bar 'dod pa nyid gza' gtad yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:15265: 'di'i don mthar thug pa a nu'i a ti'i dgongs par shes dgos te /
NK091(ke)001:15266: de ltar na a ti'i a nu dang gnad gcig pas /
NK091(ke)001:15267: gsang bdag dga' rab dpa' bos /
NK091(ke)001:15269: byang sems kun mkhyen ye shes des //
NK091(ke)001:15270: kun mkhyen yul med rang gsal ba //
NK091(ke)001:15271: dgos pa cir brtags der mi rtog /ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rang grol ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:15272: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen por la bzla bar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:15273: de bas na theg pa'i rgyal po gsang sngags rdo
NK091(ke)001:15274: rje'i theg pa lung chen po 'di yi lugs kyis
NK091(ke)001:15275: / chos thams cad ye nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK091(ke)001:15276: nyid du ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su mtha' dang bral
NK091(ke)001:15277: te rang gsal bar bstan no //
NK091(ke)001:15278: de'i gtan tshigs de ci yi phyir zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15279: rdo rje ltar mi phyed pas gsang sngagsa don gyi gnas lugs dang /
NK091(ke)001:15280: sems can rnams kyi sems nyid dang rgyal ba rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15281: pa'i sangs rgyas rnams dngos po la tha dad min
NK091(ke)001:15282: par dbyer med thig le nyag gcig tu nges pa'i
NK091(ke)001:15287: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15288: des na gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i gsang lung
NK091(ke)001:15289: chen po 'di'i don la spyod pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK091(ke)001:15290: blo dang ldan pa dag kyang mthong lam thob nas
NK091(ke)001:15291: bzung lta ba ji bzhin du rtogs nas skyes bu
NK091(ke)001:15292: dam pa bya ba med pa'i thabs kyi pha rol
NK091(ke)001:15293: du phyina pas ched du ma bgrod par yang sa
NK091(ke)001:15294: mchog dbye ba med pa nyid non par 'gyur te
NK091(ke)001:15295: / gal te rdo rje gsang ba'i don rmad du
NK091(ke)001:15296: byung ba 'di nyid ji bzhin du ma rig pas
NK091(ke)001:15297: rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor dang mi ldan par tshig tsam
NK091(ke)001:15299: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi de nyid mthong ba'i thabs
NK091(ke)001:15300: kyi rgyal po ting nge 'dzin dang shes rab kyi
NK091(ke)001:15301: snying po lta ba'i nges gsang dang bral bas 'khrul
NK091(ke)001:15302: 'khor gyi d+r+wa ba la gnas shing kun nas 'ching
NK091(ke)001:15303: bar 'gyur te / kun mkhyen dam pa rin po ches //
NK091(ke)001:15304: ji lta'i don nyid mi shes par //
NK091(ke)001:15305: ji snyed snang ba'i rtsad bcad pas //
NK091(ke)001:15307: ri dwags smig rgyu snyogs pa 'dra //
NK091(ke)001:15308: ma 'dres chos rnams mi shes par //
NK091(ke)001:15309: yongs su rdzogs la blo gtod pa //
NK091(ke)001:15310: rnal 'byor stong pa'i lam du zhugs //
NK091(ke)001:15311: rtsal med mkha' la mchong ba 'dra //
NK091(ke)001:15312: zhes gsungs pa sogs shin tu mang bas don la mkhas par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:15313: rgyu mtshan de bas na skal ba dang ldan zhing
NK091(ke)001:15314: blo gros yang rab tu gyur bas rnal 'byor chen
NK091(ke)001:15315: po skyes bu dam par nges pa yis /
NK091(ke)001:15316: rdo rje theg pa'i gsang sngags gsang ba'i yang bcud
NK091(ke)001:15317: rgyud lung man ngag kun gyi dgongs pa'i mthil dam
NK091(ke)001:15318: pa 'di yi lugs la tshul bzhin du spyod pa
NK091(ke)001:15319: dag gis bshad pa dang 'chad pa'i cho 'phrul chen
NK091(ke)001:15320: po bzhi yi chos nyid don gyi rang bzhin las
NK091(ke)001:15321: nam yang 'ad'a bar bya ba min no zhes bka'
NK091(ke)001:15322: stsal pa ni lta ba ma 'dres la yongs su
NK091(ke)001:15323: rdzogs pa las gzhan gol bar mi lta ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:15325: ma 'dres pa dang yongs su rdzogs pa'i chos nyid ji bzhin par rtogs pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:15326: chos thams cad dgag sgrub med par kun tu bzang
NK091(ke)001:15327: po nyag gcig thig le'i klong du spyod yul yongs
NK091(ke)001:15328: su dag ste don gdeng du gyur pa nyid do
NK091(ke)001:15329: // zhes sngar byin rlabs 'byung ba'i bstan par yongsa
NK091(ke)001:15330: su grags shing da ltar lung bstan brgyud pa'i bstan
NK091(ke)001:15331: par yang grags par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:15336: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15338: de dag ni kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul te /
NK091(ke)001:15339: de dag kyang chos rnams kyi gnas lugs so sora
NK091(ke)001:15340: ma 'dres para chos nyid de kho na nyid gcig
NK091(ke)001:15341: tu yongs su rdzogs par 'grel to //
NK091(ke)001:15343: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:15344: ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pa'i kun brjod pa'i
NK091(ke)001:15345: cho 'phrul bstan pa zhes bya ba'i le'u ste bco
NK091(ke)001:15346: brgyad pa gsal bar bshad pa'o ////bzhi pa rjes su
NK091(ke)001:15347: bstan pa'i cho 'phrul la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:15354: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15357: de la chos nyid kyi rjes su tha snyad thams
NK091(ke)001:15358: cad gsal bar bstan pa'i cho 'phrul gang zhe na
NK091(ke)001:15359: / de kho na nyid mi g.yo ba'i zhi gansa
NK091(ke)001:15360: kyi rjes su tha snyad ril yongs su rdzogs par
NK091(ke)001:15361: gsal bar 'grel ba'i phyir de nyid nye bar bstan
NK091(ke)001:15363: 'khor 'das kyi chos 'chad par 'gyur ba'i tha snyad
NK091(ke)001:15364: ji snyed pa thams cad rang rig pa'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:15365: ji bzhin pa ye ma bcos pa'i ngo bo nyid
NK091(ke)001:15366: du ma brtsal bar yongs su rdzogs te byung thebs
NK091(ke)001:15367: pa la sel med par bstan pa 'aba'a zhig go
NK091(ke)001:15368: // de' tshul ji lta bu zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15370: dbyings de bzhin nyid kyi ngo bo gang du'ang mi
NK091(ke)001:15371: g.yo ba'i rang gi sems nyid kyi nam mkha' yangs
NK091(ke)001:15372: pa la / g.yo ba bcud kyi 'gro ba dang
NK091(ke)001:15373: brtan pa rdul las snod du grub pa'i dngos po
NK091(ke)001:15374: mi 'dra zhing tha dad pa sna tshogs ji snyed
NK091(ke)001:15375: du snang ba rnams kyang ngo bo med pas gtod
NK091(ke)001:15376: 'dzin dang bral ba'i rnam par mi rtog pa'i rang
NK091(ke)001:15377: byung gi ye shes g.yo ba med la zab cing
NK091(ke)001:15378: gting dpags dka' ba dper na rgya mtsho chen po
NK091(ke)001:15379: la gza' skar bkra ba ltar ngang gi thig le
NK091(ke)001:15380: bkrag po che bdag nyid chen po gcig la rnam
NK091(ke)001:15381: pa thams cad rang gsal du rdzogs pa las tha
NK091(ke)001:15382: snyad gzhan pa yongs kyis med par rang bzhin gyi
NK091(ke)001:15383: gtan tshigs kyis 'grub pas ye ji bzhin pa'i ngang
NK091(ke)001:15384: las rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i rnam pa mi
NK091(ke)001:15385: 'gyur bar bstan pa nyid kyang rtsa ba gnyis su
NK091(ke)001:15386: med pa'i byang chub kyi sems la rdzogs te dkyil
NK091(ke)001:15387: 'khor gsum dbyer med pa'i gnas lugs yid bzhin gyi
NK091(ke)001:15388: nor bu rin po che lta bu la lhun gyis
NK091(ke)001:15389: pa la / rdzogs pa'o // des na rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:15390: gyi dkyil 'khor ye nas gnas pa'i gzhi de'i ngang
NK091(ke)001:15391: rang gsal ba'i nyag gcig gi rgyu la tha snyad
NK091(ke)001:15392: sna tshogs pa ngo bo nyid du dag pas rgyud
NK091(ke)001:15393: tha dad pa'i gang zag skal ba med pas mi
NK091(ke)001:15394: pa la / rdzogs pa'o // mthong bas / mnyam
NK091(ke)001:15395: pa nyid kyi klong chen po de na dman pa
NK091(ke)001:15396: nyan rang sogs dang dbu sems kyi semsa dpa' rnams
NK091(ke)001:15397: pa la / rdzogs pa'o // mthong bas / dang
NK091(ke)001:15398: / spyod pa'i rnal 'byor kri yog gsum gyi ming
NK091(ke)001:15399: pa la / rdzogs pa'o // mthong bas / dang
NK091(ke)001:15400: / yang med de / spyod yul de dag la
NK091(ke)001:15401: gnas pa rnams gsang sngags ji bzhin pa 'di'i yul
NK091(ke)001:15402: du ma gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:15403: de bas na gsang sngags la sangs rgyas dang sems
NK091(ke)001:15404: can lam gyi tha snyad so so ba med par
NK091(ke)001:15405: ye nas lhun gyis gnas par mnyam pa'i 'bras bu
NK091(ke)001:15406: byang chub kyi snying po dang rang bzhin bdag nyid
NK091(ke)001:15407: chen po gsum dbyer med pa'i klong las sna tshogs
NK091(ke)001:15408: su snang yang byang chub kyi sems las g.yos pa
NK091(ke)001:15409: med de / ye shes gsang ba las /
NK091(ke)001:15410: ngang ni rig pa gsal ba ste //
NK091(ke)001:15411: rang bzhin rig pa cir yang snang //
NK091(ke)001:15412: bdag nyid snang stong tha dad med //
NK091(ke)001:15413: bsgrub bya dag gi rang bzhin ni //
NK091(ke)001:15414: 'khrul pa byang chub sems su shes //
NK091(ke)001:15416: de ltar gsang sngags ma nor ba ngesa pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:15417: gyi dgongs pa dam pa de nyid yul du ma
NK091(ke)001:15418: grub pas rtogs par byar yang med pa'i don mchog
NK091(ke)001:15419: phul du byung ba ji bzhin pa'i ngang du cir
NK091(ke)001:15420: yang ma rnyed par rig pas nyams kyi gdeng chen
NK091(ke)001:15421: po rnyed nas gzhan don du gsang sngags sems kyi
NK091(ke)001:15422: dkyil 'khor 'od gsal ba ye ma bslad pas ji
NK091(ke)001:15423: bzhin pa rgyu rkyen gyis ma byas pas ma bcos
NK091(ke)001:15424: pa mi bslu zhing ma nor bas de kho na
NK091(ke)001:15425: nyid rtogs par dka' la gting dpags dka' bas zab
NK091(ke)001:15426: mo dam pa mtha' dang bral bas ngesa pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:15427: sku lnga dang ye shes lnga la sogs pa ngo
NK091(ke)001:15428: mtshar che zhing ya mtshan rmad du byung bas gnas
NK091(ke)001:15429: dam pa rnams ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i ngang
NK091(ke)001:15430: ngam byin rlabs kyi shugs chen po yis byang chub
NK091(ke)001:15431: snying por lhun gyis mnyam pa'i phyir ston pa dang
NK091(ke)001:15432: 'khor snang la mi phyed pas rdo rje snying pa
NK091(ke)001:15433: ston 'khor gnyis su med par nyid la nyid kyis
NK091(ke)001:15434: bka' stsal te dgongs pa'i don la 'di skad 'grel
NK091(ke)001:15435: te nye bar gsal bar ston no //
NK091(ke)001:15436: zhes pa'i tshig gsang ba pas bka' stsal to //
NK091(ke)001:15439: thig le drug tu bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:15442: gsang ba'i rgyud drug tu bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:15443: theg pa rim dgur bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:15444: bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhir bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15450: de dag de nyid ngang grol na //
NK091(ke)001:15453: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15454: tha snyad ji snyed par snang ba'i dngos po de
NK091(ke)001:15455: dag kun kyang chos dbyings de bzhin nyid kyi ngang
NK091(ke)001:15456: du byas pa med par rang grol bas na /
NK091(ke)001:15457: ngo bo ma dmigs pa nyid dngos po kun gyi
NK091(ke)001:15458: de kho na nyid du rtog par med par rang
NK091(ke)001:15459: gsal ba'i gsang sngags kyi zab don ji lta ba
NK091(ke)001:15460: de ltar me long gi gzugs brnyan ltar rig cing
NK091(ke)001:15461: mthong ba de ni sangs rgyas nyid yin te /
NK091(ke)001:15462: de la spyod yul kun kyang phyogs ris dang rtsol
NK091(ke)001:15463: ba med par bde ba chen po byang chub kyi
NK091(ke)001:15464: sems su mnyam par gyur pas /
NK091(ke)001:15465: klong de la snying po de kho na nyid du
NK091(ke)001:15466: 'dzin pa'am ched du byas pa'i rtog pa nyid kyang
NK091(ke)001:15467: bral te mtha' yi dri ma med cing so sor
NK091(ke)001:15468: ma 'dres par gsal la gzung 'dzin rnam par dag
NK091(ke)001:15469: ste rang rig pa bde ba chen po nyid la
NK091(ke)001:15470: rang bzhin bde ba chen po ma bsdus par rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15471: te rang bzhin gyi bya ba kun lhun gyis grub
NK091(ke)001:15472: pas rang byung gi rig pa ye shes lngar nyi
NK091(ke)001:15473: ma'i snying po ltar dus phyed par gsal 'grib med
NK091(ke)001:15474: par shar ro // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:15479: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15480: 'grel lugs khas blangs pa gang snyam pa la /
NK091(ke)001:15481: gsang sngags kyi dgongs 'grel sum cu rtsa bdun gyis ston te /
NK091(ke)001:15482: 'di dag thams cad gnyis su med pa mtha' rnams
NK091(ke)001:15483: ma spangs bral bas mtshan nyid gzung bar dka' zhing
NK091(ke)001:15485: tshigs bcad re re zhing gong ma gnyis kyis gsang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:15486: 'og ma gnyis kyis sngags kyi don ston te /
NK091(ke)001:15487: de'ang gsang ba la dgongs pa dang sngags la 'grel
NK091(ke)001:15488: pa zhes bya bas don du dgongs 'grel zhes bya'o
NK091(ke)001:15489: // de la dang po stong pa nyid kyi ye shes ston te /
NK091(ke)001:15490: skyes pa dang ma skyes pa gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK091(ke)001:15491: e ma'o zhes shin tu ngam zhing ya mtshan che la ngo mtshar mchog gi gnas dam pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:15492: de ltar gnyis med kyi don de ni lhun gyis
NK091(ke)001:15493: rdzogs pa nyid yin pas rmad du byung ba gnas
NK091(ke)001:15494: lugs don gyi chos nyid ji bzhin pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:15495: / de nyid theg pa gzhan las khyad par du 'phags shing /
NK091(ke)001:15496: kun gyi spyod yul ma yin par rgyal ba rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15497: pa'i sangs rgyas ma lus pa tshogs gnyis kyi mnga'
NK091(ke)001:15498: bdag kun gyi yang thugs kyi brnag par bya ba
NK091(ke)001:15499: mthar thug pa shin tu gsang ba'i dgongs pa blos
NK091(ke)001:15500: reg cing ngo bo gzung bar bka' ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:15501: 'chad pa ril yang rang rang gi skabs kyi don dang sbyar zhing rjes su mthun par 'grel to //
NK091(ke)001:15503: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi ngo ti ni /
NK091(ke)001:15504: ye gang du'ang snang ba med pas skye ba med
NK091(ke)001:15505: la de nyid ril gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:15506: las chos thams cad cir yang snang zhing 'byung pas
NK091(ke)001:15507: skyes pa ste 'gog rgyu yang med la /
NK091(ke)001:15508: de ltar skyes pa nyid tsam na ngo bo rnam
NK091(ke)001:15509: pa thams cad pa'i phyir 'di 'drar mi zin pas
NK091(ke)001:15510: skye ba med de mtha' grol ba ni gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:15512: de bas na 'chad par 'gyur ba'i shwa lo ka
NK091(ke)001:15513: sum cu rtsa bdun yang gsang sngags kyi don la
NK091(ke)001:15514: skabs skabs su phyed mar 'grel te /
NK091(ke)001:15515: gcig ni dgongs pa gsang ba las brgyud pa'i thabs
NK091(ke)001:15516: su shar ba ste de yang don la bkol ba
NK091(ke)001:15517: med do // des na dgongs 'grel kun la rjod byed kyi tshig dang /
NK091(ke)001:15519: ji bzhin pa sems kyi chos nyid dang gsum gsum du sbyar la /
NK091(ke)001:15520: ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba thams cad so so'i don
NK091(ke)001:15521: mtshon pas tshig dang don gyi yin tshul gnyis la'o
NK091(ke)001:15523: e ma'o zhes shin tu ngam pas dbu drang ste
NK091(ke)001:15524: so so'i tshig la ngo mtshar zhing don la rmad
NK091(ke)001:15525: kyi chos su shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:15526: gnyis pa me long ye shes ni /
NK091(ke)001:15527: 'gag pa dang ma 'gag pa gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo la /
NK091(ke)001:15528: e ma'o zhes shin tu ngam zhing ngo mtshar che ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:15529: don de ni lhun gyis rdzogs pas rmad du byung
NK091(ke)001:15530: ba ma bcos yul med du gsal ba'i don gyi
NK091(ke)001:15531: chos nyid ji bzhin pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15532: 'gal ba thams cad mi 'gal bar ston pas kun
NK091(ke)001:15533: gyi spyod yul ma yin par rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:15534: sangsa rgyas sku gsum gyi bdag nyid kun gyi thugs
NK091(ke)001:15536: de'i ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15537: ye ji bzhin pa ni skad cig ma min pas
NK091(ke)001:15538: rang bzhin 'gag pa med la skye shi'i rgyun las
NK091(ke)001:15539: grol ba'i bdag nyid de lhun gyis rdzogs shing chos
NK091(ke)001:15540: thams cad kyi gzhi yin pas 'byung khungs lta bu
NK091(ke)001:15541: ste zhen blo la 'gag pa'i chos su yang snang
NK091(ke)001:15542: la / de ltar 'gag pa ltar snang ba nyid
NK091(ke)001:15543: na'nga ngo bo cir yang mi zin pas 'gag bdo
NK091(ke)001:15544: ba la 'gag pa ma grub pas dbyer med pa
NK091(ke)001:15545: ni nam mkha'i ri bong can lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:15546: gsum pa mnyam nyid ye shes ni /
NK091(ke)001:15547: dmigs pa dang mi dmigs pa gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo la /
NK091(ke)001:15548: e ma'o zhes ngam zhing ngo mtshar che ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:15549: don de ni ye nas lhun gyis rdzogs pa rmad
NK091(ke)001:15550: du byung ba'i dbyings mnyam pa nyid kyi chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:15551: de kun gyi spyod yul ma yin par rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:15552: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi bdag nyid kun
NK091(ke)001:15553: gyi thugs kyi gsang ba dam pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15554: de'i ngo ti gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15555: snying po byang chub yul dang bral te dmigsa pa
NK091(ke)001:15556: med pa las zhen pa gnyis la gnas pa'i sa
NK091(ke)001:15557: pa dang 'gro ba thams cad ni rol par snang
NK091(ke)001:15558: ba la yul du dmigs shing 'dzin pa'i rnam par
NK091(ke)001:15559: snang la / de ltar sna tshogs su dmigs bdo
NK091(ke)001:15560: ba tsam nyid na'ang ngo bo spyod pa dang yul
NK091(ke)001:15561: snang dbyer med pas gtod 'dzin dang ngang gis bral
NK091(ke)001:15562: te dmigs pa med par ngang du gcig pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15563: bzhi pa sor rtog ye shes ni /
NK091(ke)001:15564: gnas pa dang mi gnas pa gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo la /
NK091(ke)001:15565: e ma'o zhes shin tu ngam zhing ngo mtshar che
NK091(ke)001:15566: ba ste don de ni ye nas lhun gyis rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15567: te rmad du byung bar ma 'dres la spros med
NK091(ke)001:15568: du gsal ba'i don gyi chos nyid de kun gyi
NK091(ke)001:15569: spyod yul ma yin par rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK091(ke)001:15570: rgyas sku gsum gyi bdag nyid kun gyi thugs kyi
NK091(ke)001:15572: de'i ngo bo ji lta bu zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15573: de kho na nyid snang ba dam pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:15574: rten dang rten can gyi ngo bo ma grub pas phyogs dang ris su mi gansa pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15575: de nyid 'byung khungs lta bu lasa zhen pa dag
NK091(ke)001:15576: la thams cad phyogs ris su gnas te yod pa
NK091(ke)001:15577: ltar snang la / de ltar gnas pa ltar snang ba nyid kyi dus na /
NK091(ke)001:15578: ngo bo 'di 'dra bar med pas gnas pa med
NK091(ke)001:15579: par kun gsal rang grol du mkhyen pa ni rma
NK091(ke)001:15581: lnga pa bya grub ye shes ni /
NK091(ke)001:15582: 'gro 'ong dang 'gro 'ong bral ba gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo la /
NK091(ke)001:15583: e ma'o zhes shin tu ngam zhing ngo matshara ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:15584: don de ni ye nas lhun gyis rdzogs pa rmad du byung ba'i kun grol gyi chos nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15585: kun gyi spyod yul ma yin par rgyal ba rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15586: pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi bdag nyid kun gyi
NK091(ke)001:15587: thugs kyi gsang ba dam pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15588: de'i ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15589: gsang sngags 'od gsal gyi rang bzhin byang chub sems
NK091(ke)001:15590: kyi rnam pa ni ril la bsnums pas phan tshun
NK091(ke)001:15591: yan man bral bas 'gro ba dang 'onga ba med
NK091(ke)001:15592: pa'i ngang 'byung khungs lta bu las brtags pa'i rtog
NK091(ke)001:15593: pa can dag la sems kyi cho 'phrul 'gro ba
NK091(ke)001:15595: de ltar 'gro 'ong ltar ma 'gags par snang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:15596: pa nyid na'ang don la 'gro 'ong dang bral te
NK091(ke)001:15597: dbyer med par thugs rje bya rtsol dang bral bar
NK091(ke)001:15598: grub pa'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:15603: ma lus mtha' dag /ces pa nas /
NK091(ke)001:15605: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15606: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos ma
NK091(ke)001:15607: lus pa kun la mu mtha' rnam par dag pa'i
NK091(ke)001:15608: dbyings byang chub kyi sems nyag gcig spros pa dang
NK091(ke)001:15609: bral ba'i thig le' rgya yis ye nas thebs te
NK091(ke)001:15610: lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir sngar ma grub pa slar
NK091(ke)001:15611: yang grub par bya zhing gzhan nas btsal du med
NK091(ke)001:15612: la / brtsal yang mi dgos te rgyu dang 'bras
NK091(ke)001:15613: bu la snga phyi dang bral bar dbyer med pa
NK091(ke)001:15614: de ni chos nyid de kho na nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:15615: de bas rang gi blo ji bzhin pa'i rjes su'ang
NK091(ke)001:15616: mi 'brang ste mi g.yo nges par mi 'dzin te
NK091(ke)001:15617: mi rtog pa ni yul las 'adsa pa'i dbyings te
NK091(ke)001:15618: bdag gi de kho na nyid la gzhan du dmigs
NK091(ke)001:15620: de ltar kun tu bzang po ji bzhin pa'i ngang
NK091(ke)001:15621: las gol te rgyu dang 'bras bur snga phyir bzung
NK091(ke)001:15622: nas rgyu yis grub par rtog cing 'bras bu la
NK091(ke)001:15623: nges par 'dzin pas mun sprul gyi blo can rnams
NK091(ke)001:15624: kyis chos thams cad rang gi rtog pa med bzhin
NK091(ke)001:15625: du snang ba'i sgyu ma lta bu /
NK091(ke)001:15626: rgyu 'bras dbyer med pa'i don la so sor mthong
NK091(ke)001:15627: nas lam pa de dag nor zhing 'khrul pa'i rtog
NK091(ke)001:15628: pas rang bcings te grol bar ma gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:15629: de bas na gang la'ang rag ma las pa'i rang
NK091(ke)001:15630: byung gi ye shesa nyi ma lta bur ye nas
NK091(ke)001:15631: gsal ba nyid dus gsum du gdal khyab chen por
NK091(ke)001:15632: rang shar ba kho na bas ye ma byas pas
NK091(ke)001:15633: ma bcos la ma bslad pas ji bzhin pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:15634: kyi ngo bo dgag tu med par rang snang ba
NK091(ke)001:15635: na thams cad thig le las mi 'da' bar snying
NK091(ke)001:15636: po nyid du nges pas de la gol sa med
NK091(ke)001:15642: byang chub nyid de log rgyun chad //
NK091(ke)001:15643: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15644: 'di nyid kun mkhyen dam pa rin po ches /
NK091(ke)001:15645: res gcig la 'khrugs mdzad de gsungs /
NK091(ke)001:15646: gzhan du 'khrugs mi mdzad par bka' stsal pa'ang yod par gsungs pa las /
NK091(ke)001:15648: phyag mchan gzhan kun dang yang mthun par /
NK091(ke)001:15649: dang po dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le ston te /
NK091(ke)001:15650: ye ji bzhin pa'i ngo bo phyogs ris mtha' dag
NK091(ke)001:15651: las grol ba la shin tu ngam pas e ma'o
NK091(ke)001:15652: ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos dbyings kyi bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:15653: tshul dam pa rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangas rgyas kun
NK091(ke)001:15654: gyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid de
NK091(ke)001:15655: / ye ji bzhin pas ma bcos la sems nyid
NK091(ke)001:15656: gdod nas dag pas ma bslad cing byas pa med
NK091(ke)001:15657: par ye sangs rgyas pa nyid gang du'ang ma g.yos
NK091(ke)001:15658: par ji bzhin pa'i ngang las cir snang cir srid
NK091(ke)001:15659: kyang mtha' ma spangs bral ba'i phyir dri ma dang
NK091(ke)001:15660: rdul ye nas med par rang bzhin rnam par dag
NK091(ke)001:15661: pa'i gshis kyi yin lugs so //
NK091(ke)001:15662: gnyis pa lhun gyis grub pa'i thig le ni /
NK091(ke)001:15663: ye nas rgyan dang rnam pa ma brtsal bar lhun gyis rdzogs pa la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15664: e ma'o ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos lhun mnyam gdal khyab chen po /
NK091(ke)001:15665: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15666: brtags pa'i rang bzhin ye nas ngang gis bral te
NK091(ke)001:15667: med pa'i ngo bo nyid kyi rang bzhin las sdug
NK091(ke)001:15668: bsngal ka nas dag pas rtsol ba med par bde
NK091(ke)001:15669: ba chen po gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor lhun
NK091(ke)001:15670: gyis grub par bzhugs pa'i gshis kyi gnas lugs yon
NK091(ke)001:15672: gsum pa dbyings kyi thig le ni /
NK091(ke)001:15673: gnyis su med pa'i ngang las rol pa 'gag med
NK091(ke)001:15674: du 'char ba'i ngo bo la shin tu ngam pas
NK091(ke)001:15675: / e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos dbyings kyi rang snang zad pa med pa /
NK091(ke)001:15676: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15677: rang rig pa skyed pa'i gzhi dang rten gnas kyi
NK091(ke)001:15678: rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid 'gag pa med pa
NK091(ke)001:15679: ni / ril mi 'gog par ji ltar bsam pa
NK091(ke)001:15680: ltar 'char ba'i phyir chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba
NK091(ke)001:15681: 'khor 'das 'byung ba'i gnas gzhi yin pas dbyings kyi
NK091(ke)001:15682: rnam pa tshad dang bral ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:15683: bzhi pa ye shes chen po'i thig le ni /
NK091(ke)001:15684: rang byung 'od gsal gyi ngo bo gsal rkyen dang bral ba la shin tu ngam zhing /
NK091(ke)001:15685: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos ji bzhin par ye nas gsal ba'i mkhyen pa /
NK091(ke)001:15686: rgyal ba rdzogsa pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15687: de kho na nyid ni ngo bo gsal bas nyi
NK091(ke)001:15688: tshe ba'i stong pa ma yin la 'bras bur bzhag
NK091(ke)001:15689: kyang mtshan nyid mi rnyed pas mi stong pa'ang min
NK091(ke)001:15690: par mtha' thams cad grol ba la dbus kyi tha
NK091(ke)001:15691: snyad gdags pa'i gzhi yang bral bas dbu ma tsam
NK091(ke)001:15692: du 'ang dmigs su yod pa ma yin te sems
NK091(ke)001:15693: nyid don gyi me long 'od gsal 'dus ma byas
NK091(ke)001:15694: pa'o // lnga pa chos nyid kyi thig le ni /
NK091(ke)001:15695: ma bcos byang chub sems kyi ngo bo ye nas gnas pa la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15696: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos g.yo med dbyings kyi ngang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:15697: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15698: ye shes chen po rgyud du mi skye bas don
NK091(ke)001:15699: de la ngesa par brtag ste dpyad pas dpyad na
NK091(ke)001:15700: ngo bo mi 'gyur bas rtag pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15701: ther zug dang rgyun las grol bas stong pa'i rang
NK091(ke)001:15702: bzhin rtag pa chena po de nyid zil gyis gnon
NK091(ke)001:15703: cing 'joms par byed pa'i gnyen po gang yang med
NK091(ke)001:15704: pa'i phyir gshis kyi ngo ti 'pho 'gyur dang bral
NK091(ke)001:15705: ba'o // drug pa kun tu bzang po'i thig le ni /
NK091(ke)001:15706: rnam grol kun nas dag pa'i dgongs pa la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15707: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i gzigs pa /
NK091(ke)001:15708: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15709: don mi 'gyur ba'i ngo bo gang du'ang ma grub
NK091(ke)001:15710: pa la nges par chad na ye nas chad pa
NK091(ke)001:15711: nyid de bkol ba'ang med pas byang chub chen po
NK091(ke)001:15712: kun nas dag pa'i ngang nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15713: yod pa las med par gyur na chad pa'i mtha'
NK091(ke)001:15714: yin kyang kun bzang bde ba chen po la log
NK091(ke)001:15715: rtog ye nas mi gnas pas rgyun las grol te
NK091(ke)001:15716: log lta'i chad pa ngang gis dag pa ngo bo'i
NK091(ke)001:15717: yon tan sgrib pa kun dang bral ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:15720: rig pa'i ye shes thig le drug /lta spyod dgongs pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:15722: mi g.yo sems nyid ma 'phros pa //
NK091(ke)001:15723: chos nyid spros bral ye sangs rgyas //
NK091(ke)001:15724: byang chub sems kyi khyad par che //
NK091(ke)001:15725: zhes gsungs pa ltar la bzla bar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:15734: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15735: chos thams cad ril chos nyid la bya rgyu med
NK091(ke)001:15736: pas byang chub snying pa de nyid mngon du byed
NK091(ke)001:15737: pa'i 'du shes kyang bral te mngon sum du gsal
NK091(ke)001:15739: de ltar yul med pas na kun kyang sems las
NK091(ke)001:15740: gzhan du ma brtsal bar ye gnas pa'i bdag nyid
NK091(ke)001:15741: chen po la bde bar mnos shig ces gdams te
NK091(ke)001:15744: ji ga snang srid 'khor ba'i kha brgyud de ji
NK091(ke)001:15745: snyed du btsal kyang don snying po byang chub sems
NK091(ke)001:15746: kyi dbyings de nyid las gzhan du 'das te gar
NK091(ke)001:15747: yang ma phyin pa'i phyir dang /
NK091(ke)001:15748: mtha' la thug pa med pa'i rgyal ba'i zhing khams
NK091(ke)001:15749: rnams bgrod kyang don gyi snying po de las ma
NK091(ke)001:15750: 'phags pas gzhan du g.yos pa med par de nyid
NK091(ke)001:15751: yin pas sems tsam dang dbu ma las 'phags la
NK091(ke)001:15752: / dpag tu med pa'i rgyal ba ril gyi sku
NK091(ke)001:15753: gsung thugs kun bskrun te grub par gyur cing mthong
NK091(ke)001:15754: / na yang / snying po de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:15755: las yongs su 'phel te mang zhing rags par gyur
NK091(ke)001:15756: pa med de chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pas skye
NK091(ke)001:15757: bo dang mu stegs las 'phags te /
NK091(ke)001:15758: sdug bsngal can gyi sems can mtha' la thug pa
NK091(ke)001:15759: med pa'i 'gro ba ji snyed du byung zhing shar
NK091(ke)001:15760: yang / sems kyi de kho na nyid de las
NK091(ke)001:15761: 'grib ste nyung ba dang phra bar gyur pa med
NK091(ke)001:15762: de sems nyid rang byung gi ye shes las gzhan
NK091(ke)001:15763: du sangs rgyas zhes brtsal du med pa'i che ba
NK091(ke)001:15764: dang ldan pas ma h+aa dang a nu'i rgyud lung
NK091(ke)001:15765: yang / las 'phags pa'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:15769: ma gtogs gang yang yod ma yin //
NK091(ke)001:15770: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15771: de la dang po spangs gar yang ma spangs par mngon sum par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:15772: snang grags srid pa'i chos thams cad byang chub sems
NK091(ke)001:15773: kyi ngo bor ye sangs rgyas par rdzogs pa la
NK091(ke)001:15775: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos
NK091(ke)001:15776: bde ba chen po'i klong la gzhan gyis sel med
NK091(ke)001:15777: pa / rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK091(ke)001:15778: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gsang ba
NK091(ke)001:15779: pa / zab mo ste / phyi nang du snang
NK091(ke)001:15780: zhing grags pa'i chos so cog gi rang bzhin ni
NK091(ke)001:15781: ye nyid nas sems nyid 'od gsal ba'i ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:15782: yin pa'i phyir sangs rgyas nyid lasa gzhan ma yin
NK091(ke)001:15783: par rgyal ba'i go 'phang dam pa nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:15784: 'o na de nyid yin pa ci'i phyir te su yi spyod yul du nges pa yin zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15785: rgyal ba'i spyod yul gsang ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15786: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos rin po che gser gling dang 'dra ba'i dgongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:15787: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas kun gyi sku gsung
NK091(ke)001:15788: thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gsang ba zab mo
NK091(ke)001:15789: ste / sangs rgyas nyid lasa dngos po gzhan du
NK091(ke)001:15790: gyur ba'i chos gzhan pa zhig rgyal ba sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:15791: nyid kyisa kyang mi brnyes te spyod yul yongs su
NK091(ke)001:15792: dag par mngon du gsal bas so //
NK091(ke)001:15793: de bas na ngo bo btsal du med par la gcad do //
NK091(ke)001:15794: gnyis pa rag gang du'ang ma las par bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pa'i che ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:15795: gzhan las mi 'byung bar rang byung bya rtsol bral ba shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15796: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos ye rdzogs thog mtha' med pa'i klong /
NK091(ke)001:15797: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung
NK091(ke)001:15798: thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gsang ba zab mo
NK091(ke)001:15799: ste / 'jig rten gyi khams rab 'byams mthar thug
NK091(ke)001:15800: pa med cing mtha' yas pa gang nas kyang rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:15801: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang dam pa de nyid
NK091(ke)001:15802: yong ye mi tshol zhing don du mi gnyer bar
NK091(ke)001:15805: sems nyid ye nas byang chub snying por rdzogs pa la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15806: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos rang rig phyogs med du gsal ba'i dgongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:15807: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung
NK091(ke)001:15808: thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gsang ba zab mo
NK091(ke)001:15809: ste / sems kyi chos nyid bshad pa lta bu'i
NK091(ke)001:15810: mtshan nyid gsang ba chen po de nyid ji bzhin
NK091(ke)001:15811: du go zhing rtogs pa nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:15812: kyi go 'phang mchog tu nges te /
NK091(ke)001:15813: de las gzhan du bla na med pa'i byang chub dam pa yod pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:15814: gsum pa ltos gang la yang mi ltos par de nyid yin par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:15815: ye nas blang dor dang phyogs cha bral te ji bzhin par gsal ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15816: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:15817: thams cad byang chub sems su gsal pa'i dgongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:15818: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung
NK091(ke)001:15819: thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gsang ba zab mo
NK091(ke)001:15820: ste / 'di phyi bar do gsum dang /
NK091(ke)001:15823: gzugs med de srid pa khams gsum gyi ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:15824: ye phyi mo nas byang chub snying po rang snang
NK091(ke)001:15825: ba nyid yin pa la 'khrul pa'i log skyon ngang
NK091(ke)001:15826: gis ma dmigs te shes bya dang bsgrub bya'i de
NK091(ke)001:15827: kho na nyid ma nor ba gdod nas ma bcos
NK091(ke)001:15828: par lhun gyi grub pas rdzogs pa chen po nyid
NK091(ke)001:15829: do // bzhi pa gnas gang la'ang mi gnas par
