NK091(ke)001:15830: chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba ni
NK091(ke)001:15831: do // / chos nyid kun mnyam gyi dbyings rang
NK091(ke)001:15832: bzhin rnam dag chen po la shin tu ngam pas
NK091(ke)001:15833: do // / / e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:15834: ye mnyam kun grol gyi klong chen /
NK091(ke)001:15835: rgyal ba rdzogsa pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung
NK091(ke)001:15836: thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gsang ba zab mo
NK091(ke)001:15837: ste / sems kyi rang bzhin mnyam chen yangs pa
NK091(ke)001:15838: la 'bras bu ye rdzogs su lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK091(ke)001:15839: dbyings kyi yon tan zad pa med pa'i cha nas
NK091(ke)001:15840: bzhag pa las 'phral du 'bad cing brtsal ba med
NK091(ke)001:15841: par tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas spangs rtogs mthar
NK091(ke)001:15842: phyin pa'i ngo bor ye nas bzhugs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:15843: lnga pa gzhi lam 'bras bu'i tha snyad las 'das pas sangs rgyas med pa'i che ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:15844: bya byed dang bral bas mtha' bral 'od gsal chen po la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15845: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmada kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:15846: sangs rgyas pa dang ma rgyas pa'i tha snyad las grol ba'i dgongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:15847: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung
NK091(ke)001:15848: thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gsang ba zab mo
NK091(ke)001:15849: ste / snga ma'i dus kun nas phyis kyi dus
NK091(ke)001:15850: kun tu rig pa'i klong nyid kyis ma khyab pa
NK091(ke)001:15851: med pas ngang bzang po nyid la bzang ngan dang
NK091(ke)001:15852: blang dor gyi chos dang bral te /
NK091(ke)001:15853: ngo bo med pa la skyon gyi rnam pa rang
NK091(ke)001:15854: grol bas thams cad ye thog ma nas gsang sngags
NK091(ke)001:15855: ji bzhin par rab tu 'byams shing rmad du byung
NK091(ke)001:15856: bar grags pa'i chos ma yin pa gzhan med pas
NK091(ke)001:15857: sems can spong la sangs rgyas len pa'i tha snyad
NK091(ke)001:15858: dang bral ba'o // 'o na blang dor med na gnyis 'dzin ji ltar dag snyam na /
NK091(ke)001:15859: gang cir snang yang gdod nas snying po byang chub tu rang byung ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15860: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:15861: kun bral nyag gcig ci ma spangs pa'i ngo bo /
NK091(ke)001:15862: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung
NK091(ke)001:15863: thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gsang ba zab mo
NK091(ke)001:15864: / chos thams cad snying po byang chub kyi ngang
NK091(ke)001:15865: du ye nas sangs rgyas pa de nyid kho na
NK091(ke)001:15866: / las / de la ma gtogs pa'i mtha'i skyon
NK091(ke)001:15867: gang yang yod par ma yin par gser sa le
NK091(ke)001:15869: la shan lta ba'i sgron ma las /
NK091(ke)001:15870: rang byung ye shes mngon byas pa'i //
NK091(ke)001:15871: nyi ma bye ba'i 'od brdal yang //
NK091(ke)001:15872: dus dang rnam pa thams cad du //
NK091(ke)001:15873: sangs ma rgyas par bya byed pa'i //
NK091(ke)001:15874: chos ni rdul tsam yod min pas //
NK091(ke)001:15875: sangs rgyas med pa'i che bar gsungs //
NK091(ke)001:15877: de ltar che ba lnga po 'di'i rang ngo ni /
NK091(ke)001:15878: byang chub kyi sems yid skyob las /
NK091(ke)001:15879: ma spangs mi gnas mi ltos rag ma las //
NK091(ke)001:15880: tha snyad kun dang bral ba'i 'bras bu ste //
NK091(ke)001:15881: rang byung lhun grub 'dus ma byas pas na //
NK091(ke)001:15882: 'bras bu'i rgyal po khyad par 'phags te che //
NK091(ke)001:15883: zhes gsungs pa ltar la bzla bar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:15884: 'di ltar thig le drug dang che ba lnga nyid
NK091(ke)001:15885: mdo chen po 'di'i rang lugs ji lta ba bzhin
NK091(ke)001:15886: du rgyud lung man ngag dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa
NK091(ke)001:15887: kun gyi dgongs pa mthar thug dang mthun par nyung
NK091(ke)001:15888: gsal gnad dril du bshad pas /
NK091(ke)001:15889: ji bzhin du mthong ba'i blo gros dang ldan na /
NK091(ke)001:15890: sems phyogs rgya mtsho'i skabs don thun mong ma yin
NK091(ke)001:15891: pa la'ang gzhan dring mi 'jog pa'i nges pa rnyed
NK091(ke)001:15892: par 'gyur ro // bzhi pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:15900: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15901: de yang skye ba bzhi dang lam rgyud lngar gang
NK091(ke)001:15902: snang ba de nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:15903: las gzhan du mi tshol bas bsnyen pa yin la
NK091(ke)001:15904: / de nyid rang rig pa'i ye shes chos sku
NK091(ke)001:15905: chen por grub pa ni nye bar bsnyen pa dang
NK091(ke)001:15907: gnyis su med pa'i de kho na nyid kyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:15908: bo der ro gcig tu gnas pas dngos po gnyis
NK091(ke)001:15909: pa'i rnam pa med par ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK091(ke)001:15910: bde ba chen po nyid kyi lhun la bzhugs te
NK091(ke)001:15911: skye 'gag dang 'pho 'gyur med pa'i snying po yin
NK091(ke)001:15912: pas 'phel 'grib dang bral ba ni sgrub pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:15913: / / yin la / yi ge h'u m+aum +amo
NK091(ke)001:15914: gsum gyi don bya ba med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum
NK091(ke)001:15916: 'phral du lam pas ma byas par ye nas 'bras
NK091(ke)001:15917: bur thob ste bsgrubs zin pa'i phyir lhun gyis grub
NK091(ke)001:15918: pa ni bsgrub pa chen po'o //
NK091(ke)001:15923: thob par bya ba ga la yod //
NK091(ke)001:15924: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:15925: 'o na 'khrul pa'i sems can 'byung ba'i snyad ci yod ce na /
NK091(ke)001:15926: dang po bsnyen pa nyid ston te /
NK091(ke)001:15927: kun nas sgrib med du gsal yang rang gsang thabs kyis chod pa la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15928: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:15929: 'khrul par brtags kyang ngo bo ye nas dag pa /
NK091(ke)001:15930: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku bzhi'i bdag nyid kun gyi gsang ba dam pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15931: skye bzhi rgyud lngar snang ba thams cad ye nas
NK091(ke)001:15932: gar yang ma sbas par sangs rgyas pa nyid yin
NK091(ke)001:15933: pa la thag pa la sbrul du mthong ba ltar
NK091(ke)001:15934: rtog pas bsgribsa pas rang gi de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:15935: ngo ma shesa pa'am ma mthong ba'i don gyis yul
NK091(ke)001:15936: du ma gyur pas brtag tu mi btub pa ni
NK091(ke)001:15937: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:15938: dper mtshon rnon po rang gis rang mi chod pa lta bu'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:15939: 'o na de dag snying po byang chub las 'das sam zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15940: gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa ston te /
NK091(ke)001:15941: de nyid spang du med par rang snang ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15942: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:15943: sangs rgyas gzhan nas mi 'byung bar rang du shes pa /
NK091(ke)001:15944: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku bzhi'i bdag nyid kun gyi gsang ba dam pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15945: de ltar rtog pa nyid 'khrul zhing 'dzin pa'i ngo
NK091(ke)001:15946: bo nyid du snang ba na yang bshad pa bzhin
NK091(ke)001:15947: glo bur gyi mtshan nyid pas rtog pa ther zug
NK091(ke)001:15948: dang bral te snang la med pa'i phyir dpe gser
NK091(ke)001:15949: las byas pa'i rdzas bzhin bde bar gshegsa pa'i snying
NK091(ke)001:15950: po byang chub mchog nyid yin gyi gzhan gang nas
NK091(ke)001:15952: des na bla ma'i gdams ngag gis de kho na
NK091(ke)001:15953: nyid kyi don rtogs na rtog pa nyid chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:15954: yin pas na / gsum pa bsgrub pa ston te /
NK091(ke)001:15955: byang chub ye rdzogs chen po la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15956: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:15957: chos sku rang bab kyi ngo bo /
NK091(ke)001:15958: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku bzhi'i bdag nyid kun gyi gsang ba dam pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15959: dngos po grags so cog kun gyi rtsa ba snying po byang chub chos kyi sku chen po la /
NK091(ke)001:15960: ye gdod ma nas rgyal ba'i dgongs pa 'bras bu'i
NK091(ke)001:15961: bdag nyid rang rdzogs su lhun gyis grub pas rgyu
NK091(ke)001:15964: bya byed las 'das pa'i don gyis bzhi pa bsgrub pa chen po ston te /
NK091(ke)001:15965: dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med pa'i ngo bo la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15966: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:15967: gdal khyab gnyis med kyi dgongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:15968: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku bzhi'i bdag nyid kun gyi gsang ba dam pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15973: 'joms par byed pa'i ngo bo'i phyir rdo rje ni
NK091(ke)001:15974: ye shes chen po phra zhing zab pa ril gyi
NK091(ke)001:15975: 'bras bu gsang ba'i snying po nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15976: de la ni sngar ma grub pa zhig don du
NK091(ke)001:15977: gnyer te sgrub par byed pa dang thob cing bsgrub
NK091(ke)001:15978: par bya ba gnyis kyi ming yang ye nas med
NK091(ke)001:15979: pa la de nyid kyi tha snyad dang yang bral
NK091(ke)001:15980: ba'o // 'o na de ci'i phyir te bsgrub tu med na 'bras bu ji ltar 'byung zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:15981: de nyid kyi 'thad pa ston te /
NK091(ke)001:15982: ye grol don gyi gnas lugs la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:15983: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:15984: ye gsal phyogs grol gyi dgongs klong /
NK091(ke)001:15985: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku bzhi'i bdag nyid kun gyi gsang ba dam pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:15986: gnas lugs snying po byang chub ni tshogs las byas
NK091(ke)001:15987: pa ma yin par ye thog ma nyid nas 'bras
NK091(ke)001:15988: bu dam pa de nyid kyi ngo bor bzhugs pa
NK091(ke)001:15989: la ltos pa'i rgyu 'bras kyi ming gi bla dwags
NK091(ke)001:15990: tsam yang bral bas rgyu rkyen gyis gsar du thob
NK091(ke)001:15991: cing rnyed par bya ba ga la yod de 'dus
NK091(ke)001:15992: byas kyi chos gang yang ma dmigs par rang gsal
NK091(ke)001:16002: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16003: thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyud rdo rje gsang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:16004: snying po rgyud lnga po kun gyi dngos gzhir nges
NK091(ke)001:16005: pa gang gis logs nas bsgrub tu med par shes
NK091(ke)001:16006: pa'i ngo bo nyid dam pa 'di nyid la gang
NK091(ke)001:16007: yang don du mi gnyer bar bsgrub pa chen po
NK091(ke)001:16008: la gnas pa yi rnal 'byor dbang phyug de nyid
NK091(ke)001:16009: ni skal ba shin tu bzang po ste /
NK091(ke)001:16010: snying po'i ngo bo la sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK091(ke)001:16011: phrin las lnga'i yon tan rdzogs te thabs chen lam
NK091(ke)001:16012: gyi mchog nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:16014: gzhi gsang ba'i snying por bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:16015: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i rgyud lngar bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16020: sangs rgyas sems can kun gyi gsang //
NK091(ke)001:16025: sangs rgyas kun gyi nges pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16026: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16027: dang po dag mnyam dbyer med spyod yul dang bral
NK091(ke)001:16028: ba'i dbyings ye lhun rdzogs chen po 'khor 'das kun
NK091(ke)001:16029: gyi gzhi'i gnas lugs la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16030: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16031: rgyud sde chen po drug gi yang gzhi dang rtsa ba /
NK091(ke)001:16032: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa don gyi gsang pa mthar thug pa /
NK091(ke)001:16033: byang chub kyi sems gsang sngags gsang ba'i snying po
NK091(ke)001:16034: de kho na nyid shin tu mthong dka' ba 'bras
NK091(ke)001:16036: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang 'gro ba sems
NK091(ke)001:16037: can kun gyi ngo bo der gcig pa'i gzhi dbyings
NK091(ke)001:16038: gnyug ma'i chos nyid kun gyi spyod yul ma yin
NK091(ke)001:16040: 'di la gzhi dbyings don gyi snying po 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:16041: 'khor 'das kun gyi gsang ba rtogs par bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:16042: dam pa yin kyang log pa'i srad bu bcu yis
NK091(ke)001:16043: bla ma'i zhabs la reg pa'i yul min pas gsang
NK091(ke)001:16045: de'i phyir lam gyi bstan pa ril gyi ngo bo yang /
NK091(ke)001:16046: 'di'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs snang bas yon tan cha re mtshon pa las btags te /
NK091(ke)001:16048: rgyud sde chen po drug tu bstan pa las /
NK091(ke)001:16049: gnyis pa gzhi dbyings de nyid ji bzhin du ston
NK091(ke)001:16050: pa'i gzhi'i rgyud dam spyi'i rgyud kyi ngo bo yin
NK091(ke)001:16051: par ston te / bstan pa kun gyi yang bcud
NK091(ke)001:16052: gsang chen don gyi ngo bo la shin tu ngam
NK091(ke)001:16053: par ston te / pas / e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16054: ye nas lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i spyod yul ston pa'i /
NK091(ke)001:16055: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'bras chos lnga'i mnga' bdag kun gyi dgongs pa gsang ba dam pa /
NK091(ke)001:16056: shin tu dpags par dka' ba bstan pa thams cad
NK091(ke)001:16057: kyi gsang ba dam pa'i snying po 'di nyid ni
NK091(ke)001:16058: / mi bstan par bya'o cog gi mchog tu gyur pa yin te /
NK091(ke)001:16059: chos thams cad kyi srog snying shin tu ma nor
NK091(ke)001:16060: ba'i don gyi gnas lugs rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK091(ke)001:16061: rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i zhe phugs mthar thug tu
NK091(ke)001:16062: nges pa yin pas gsang ba'i snying po de kho
NK091(ke)001:16063: na nyid nges pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:16068: rdo rje snying po 'dus pa nyid //
NK091(ke)001:16074: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16075: dang po rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i thugs kyi gsang ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16076: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16077: mtha' bral kun gsal gyi dgongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:16078: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thugs lnga'i mnga' bdag
NK091(ke)001:16079: kun gyi thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab
NK091(ke)001:16080: pa / gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK091(ke)001:16081: su bshad pa ltar ril ma 'dres la yongs su
NK091(ke)001:16082: rdzogs par 'dusa pa ngo bo zab cing phra ba'i
NK091(ke)001:16083: don mchog gsang ba rmad du byung ba /
NK091(ke)001:16084: de kho na nyid rdo rje rnam pa gsum gyi
NK091(ke)001:16085: snying po sems nyid gnyis med la 'dus pas grub
NK091(ke)001:16086: mtha'i bcud du gyur pa nyid du nges pas /
NK091(ke)001:16087: gsang ba 'dus pa yang yin te /
NK091(ke)001:16089: gsang ba zhes su bstan pa ni //
NK091(ke)001:16090: sku gsung thugs ni rnam pa gsum //
NK091(ke)001:16093: gnyis pa rgyal ba kun gyi bstan pa 'byung ba'i gsung gi gsang ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16094: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16095: nye ring med par rang skad dang 'tshams par grags kyang ngos bzung mi gnas pa /
NK091(ke)001:16096: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gsung lnga'i mnga' bdag
NK091(ke)001:16097: kun gyi gsung gi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab
NK091(ke)001:16098: pa / rang rig pa ni mtha'i dri ma dwangs
NK091(ke)001:16099: pas zla ba ltar ngo bo ma bsgrib par gsal
NK091(ke)001:16100: yang bsam dka' bas gsang ba dam pa de nyid
NK091(ke)001:16101: las byung ba' ma 'gags la ma 'dres par rang
NK091(ke)001:16102: shar ba'i gsung gi thig le spros kun bral zhing
NK091(ke)001:16103: mu mtha' mi rnyed pas zab mo tshangs dbyangs kyi
NK091(ke)001:16105: zla gsang thig le'ang yin no //
NK091(ke)001:16106: gsum pa rgyal ba kun gyi bkod pa ston pa'i sku'i gsang ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16107: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16108: gang la gang 'dul du snang yang ngo bo mi rnyed pa /
NK091(ke)001:16109: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku lnga'i mnga' bdag
NK091(ke)001:16110: kun gyi sku'i gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK091(ke)001:16112: rgyud dag pa'i rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ma
NK091(ke)001:16113: lus pa kun dang ngo bo mi phyed par mnyam
NK091(ke)001:16114: par sbyor bas / rgyal ba'i gzugs skur snang ba
NK091(ke)001:16115: ji snyed pa dper na mkha' la 'aja'a tshon shar
NK091(ke)001:16116: ba ltar snang la rang bzhin med de ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:16117: la yongs su rdzogs par gcig dang du ma bral
NK091(ke)001:16118: bar gsal ba'i phyir sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor yang yin
NK091(ke)001:16119: par sbyor bas / no // bzhi pa rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:16120: kun gyi che ba'i khyad par yon tan gyi gsang
NK091(ke)001:16121: ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16122: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16123: 'bras bu'i chos kyi mnga' thang kun la rang dbang bsgyur te zad pa med pa /
NK091(ke)001:16124: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yon tan lnga'i mnga'
NK091(ke)001:16125: bdag kun gyi yon tan gyi gsang ba bsam gyis
NK091(ke)001:16126: mi khyab pa / snang srid snod bcud kyi chos
NK091(ke)001:16127: thams cad sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid ltar snang yang grub
NK091(ke)001:16128: pa med pa ye shes chen po'i ngo bor lhun
NK091(ke)001:16129: gyis grub pa las 'gro 'ong med par ji snyed
NK091(ke)001:16130: pa'i chos su rnam par 'phrul te gnyis su med
NK091(ke)001:16131: pa'i d+r+wa ba tshad dang bral bas sprin gyi phung
NK091(ke)001:16132: mi khyab pa / poor byung yang / don la
NK091(ke)001:16133: dbyer med pa'i phyir sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'ang yin no
NK091(ke)001:16134: mi khyab pa / poor byung yang / // 'di
NK091(ke)001:16135: nyid yon tan gyi cha nas bzhag pas rnam snang
NK091(ke)001:16136: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yin par gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:16137: lnga pa rgyal ba kun gyi mdzad pa'i rnam rol
NK091(ke)001:16138: phrin las kyi gsang ba la shin tu ngam pas
NK091(ke)001:16139: / e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16140: mdzad pa dus las mi yol bar gang yang thabs kyi rol mor 'char ba /
NK091(ke)001:16141: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas phrin las lnga'i mnga'
NK091(ke)001:16142: bdag kun gyi phrin las kyi gsang ba bsam gyis
NK091(ke)001:16143: mi khyab pa / rang rig pa cir yang snang
NK091(ke)001:16144: ba'i sprul pa'i mdzad pa thabs kyi d+r+wa ba chen
NK091(ke)001:16145: po'i rol pa las 'khor 'das dang yod med la
NK091(ke)001:16146: sogs pa'i mtha' gnyis su snang ba ril ma spang
NK091(ke)001:16147: par de nyid du 'dzin par mdzad pa'i zhags pa
NK091(ke)001:16148: dang 'dra bar byung ba'i phyir thabs kyi zhags pa
NK091(ke)001:16149: mi khyab pa / yang yin no // de yan
NK091(ke)001:16150: chad ni thob par bya ba'i don gyi rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:16151: mi khyab pa / yang yin no // no // drug pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:16158: don gyi mchog /ces pa'i bar rkang pa gnyis kyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16159: de ltar gzhan nas bsgrub tu med par shes pa
NK091(ke)001:16160: de ni thabs dang las khyad par can yin pas
NK091(ke)001:16161: / de nyid ji lta ba bzhin du thag chod
NK091(ke)001:16162: pa ltar gnas te theg pa'i rim pa dgu'i rtsol
NK091(ke)001:16163: ba'i mtha' yi sgom pa dang sgrub pa'i las kyi
NK091(ke)001:16164: rim pa gang cir yang mi 'gog par spyad kyang
NK091(ke)001:16165: / / byas pa la byas 'dzin med pas sems
NK091(ke)001:16166: kyi de kho na nyid der mthar thug pa yin
NK091(ke)001:16167: / / te / don chen po gtan la phebs
NK091(ke)001:16168: pa'i lam gyi mchog dam pa las ma nyams pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16169: / / te / phyir ro // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:16170: theg pa dgu'i ngo bo bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:16171: des na bstan pa'i 'byung gnas dang lung gi spyi 'grel du bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16176: dag pa'i mtha' gnyis nges par 'byung //
NK091(ke)001:16177: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16178: dam pa'i mdzod gsum dang thabs kyi gsang ba chen por shar ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16179: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16180: nges pa don gyi dgongs pa'i thabs kyi gsang mdzod /
NK091(ke)001:16181: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lhun rdzogs chos sku'i
NK091(ke)001:16182: ngo bor bzhugs shing mtshan dpe gsal rdzogs kyi longs
NK091(ke)001:16183: skur bkod pa kun gyi dgongs pa gsang ba dam
NK091(ke)001:16184: pa / ye nas lhun gyis grub pas bya rtsol
NK091(ke)001:16185: dang bral ba'i phyir bya bral rdzogs pa'i rgyud a
NK091(ke)001:16187: dbyings dang ye shes kyi ngo bo 'ching ba dang
NK091(ke)001:16188: bral ba'i phyir rnam grol rig pa'i rgyud a nu
NK091(ke)001:16189: yo ga dang / chags sdang can la spyod pa
NK091(ke)001:16190: mthun mjug tu snang ba'i phyir mthun 'jug spyod pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16191: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga ste bskyed rdzogs gsum du
NK091(ke)001:16192: yo ga dang / yang shar ro // dka' thub
NK091(ke)001:16193: rig byed kyi gsang ba gsum du shar ba yang
NK091(ke)001:16194: yo ga dang / yang shar ro // / ngang
NK091(ke)001:16195: gis mi g.yo zhing zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin du
NK091(ke)001:16196: zhugs pa'i phyir zhi gnas sbyor ba'i rgyud dang /
NK091(ke)001:16197: lta spyod gong 'og gi thabs la brten pa'i phyir mthar phyin thabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK091(ke)001:16198: sgo gsum sa la 'gong pa'i thabs kyi bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:16199: las gtso bor byed pa'i phyir bya ba las kyi
NK091(ke)001:16203: de bas na rgyud kyi yan lag drug kyang yin no //
NK091(ke)001:16204: der yang ma zad nges par 'byung ba'i gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:16205: la blo dang 'tshams par brgyud pa'i thabs su shar
NK091(ke)001:16206: ba la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16207: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16208: thugs rje dang thabs la mkhas pa'i gdul thabs /
NK091(ke)001:16209: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas thub pa sprul pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16210: sku mchog kun gyis brgyud nas 'dren pa'i thabs kyi
NK091(ke)001:16211: gsang ba mthar thug nges pa'i don la gzhol pa
NK091(ke)001:16213: don dam pa'i ngo bo gnyis ma 'gags par shar bas /
NK091(ke)001:16214: skye bo dang mu stegs las 'phags te bden bzhi'i chos nyid lhag par mthong ba nyan thos dang /
NK091(ke)001:16215: de nyid ji lta ba la gzung rtog dang bral
NK091(ke)001:16216: bas bying rgod la sogs pa med de mi bsgul
NK091(ke)001:16217: bas zhi bar gnas pa rang rgyal dang /
NK091(ke)001:16218: mtha' bzhi dang spros pa'i mtha' brgyad stong gzhi yod pa'am med pa'i tshul gyis ye dag pas /
NK091(ke)001:16219: don dam par ma skyes par rtogs pa'i dbu ma'i
NK091(ke)001:16220: lam gyis mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung ba'i theg
NK091(ke)001:16221: pa sems tsam dang dbu ma ste /
NK091(ke)001:16222: de bas na sde snod gsum du'ang shar ro //
NK091(ke)001:16227: zhes pa'i bar tshigs bcad gcig gis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16228: de ltar yongs rdzogs kyi ngo bo las theg pa
NK091(ke)001:16229: kun tu ma 'dres par shar ba la shin tu
NK091(ke)001:16230: ngam pas / e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16231: gdul bya'i blo rim ltar snang ba'i thabs kyi gsang sgo /
NK091(ke)001:16232: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangsa rgyas sku gsum gyi bdag nyid kun gyi dgongs pa gsang ba dam pa /
NK091(ke)001:16233: sprul sku'i chos mdzod sde snod rin po che gsum dang /
NK091(ke)001:16234: longs sku'i gsang mdzod sngags rgyud phyi pa gsum dang /
NK091(ke)001:16235: chos sku'i dgongs pa dam pa'i mdzod chen gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:16236: mdo sngags kyi bka' lung ji snyed pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pas /
NK091(ke)001:16237: de rnams kyi don rdzogs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16238: phyogs cha mtshon pa'i bka'i tshig dang /
NK091(ke)001:16239: yi ger yang byin rlabs kyis shar bas kun gyi 'byung gansa kyi gzhi yang yin la /
NK091(ke)001:16240: de dag gis de kho na nyid kyi don mngon sum dang rjes dpags /
NK091(ke)001:16243: brda thabs kyi brgyud pas yang dag par gtan la nges par 'bebsa te /
NK091(ke)001:16244: mdor bstan pa kun 'dis nor du rung bar byed pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16245: de bas na bka' thams cad snying po byang chub 'di nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:16254: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16255: gang bdud kyi dpung las rgyal te che bar gyur
NK091(ke)001:16256: pa kun gyi snying po 'bras bu dam pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:16257: ye nas lhun gyis grub par mnga' ba'i byin rlabs
NK091(ke)001:16259: mdo sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga ste /
NK091(ke)001:16260: ya mtshan che zhing ngo mtshar rgya cher 'byung ba
NK091(ke)001:16261: de dag ji bzhin pa las byung ba med par
NK091(ke)001:16262: 'char ro // de'i phyir rgyal ba rgya mtsho ma
NK091(ke)001:16263: lus pa rnams kyi skyed par byed pa'i yum du
NK091(ke)001:16269: sangs rgyas 'byung ba'i snying po yum //
NK091(ke)001:16270: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16271: 'o na bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi dang ji ltar ldan snyam na /
NK091(ke)001:16272: dang po don dang mi 'gal bar ston te /
NK091(ke)001:16273: rgyal ba sku gsum gyi bka' ji snyed du shar
NK091(ke)001:16274: yang don gyi ngo bor rgya chad phyogs lhung med
NK091(ke)001:16275: par gyur pa la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16276: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi de nyid /
NK091(ke)001:16277: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi mnga'
NK091(ke)001:16278: bdag kun gyi dgongs pa gsang ba dam pa phul
NK091(ke)001:16280: gdula bya'i yul gyi khams dbang bsam pa'i khyad par
NK091(ke)001:16281: sna tshogs pa ni rab 'bring tha ma bye brag
NK091(ke)001:16282: dang bcas par 'byung ba ji snyed pa kun gyi
NK091(ke)001:16283: don du rang rang gi rgyud dang 'tshams pa'i gdul
NK091(ke)001:16284: ba'i thabs kyi gsung gi 'jug sgo bstan pa rin
NK091(ke)001:16285: po che yang de snyed du snang zhing grags par
NK091(ke)001:16286: 'byung ste / de ltar lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir don dang mi 'gal bar snang du btub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16287: de bas na rgyud 'di lta bu nyid kyang ji ltar snang yang /
NK091(ke)001:16288: ngo bo'i dbang du ston pa nyag gcig gi byin rlabs snang ba yin no //
NK091(ke)001:16289: gnyis pa bka' lung la snang bar ston te /
NK091(ke)001:16290: bka' yi dam pa don gyi snying po nyid /
NK091(ke)001:16291: ji bzhin du ma nor bar 'grel ba'i gsang ba
NK091(ke)001:16292: mchog gi sgor shar ba la shin tu ngam pas
NK091(ke)001:16293: / e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16294: bstan pa'i yang rtse nges pa don gyi dgongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:16295: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi mnga'
NK091(ke)001:16296: bdag kun gyi bka' lung gsang ba dam pa rgyud
NK091(ke)001:16298: che ba bdun dang ldan pa'i rgyud lung man ngag
NK091(ke)001:16299: gi spyi mdzod rab 'byams rmad du byung bar grags
NK091(ke)001:16300: pa don dang tshig khyad par can du gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:16301: la snang ba'i dgongs pa 'dus pa chos kyi me
NK091(ke)001:16302: long du nye bar gzung ba 'di nyid mdo sngags
NK091(ke)001:16303: kyi bka' lung theg pa'i sgo yi rim pa de
NK091(ke)001:16304: snyed du bsgrang ba'i rab rgyud dam pa mchog tu
NK091(ke)001:16306: snying po byang chub nyid ji lta bar mtshon pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16307: sgro skur med par tshig tu snang ba 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:16308: kho na'o // 'o na dam par brjod pa'i gtan tshigs gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:16309: gsum pa rigs pas 'thad par ston te /
NK091(ke)001:16310: bstan pa rgya mtsho 'byung ba'i gzhi rtsa ye rdzogs snying po'i tshad mal shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16311: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16312: theg pa kun gyi dgongs bcud /
NK091(ke)001:16313: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi mnga'
NK091(ke)001:16314: bdag kun gyi dgongs pa gsang ba 'khrul med du
NK091(ke)001:16315: ston pa / snying po byang chub kyi ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:16316: chos nyid ji bzhin pa yi de kho na nyid
NK091(ke)001:16317: du nges pa'i phyir rgyud kyi rgyal po 'di las
NK091(ke)001:16318: bka' de snyed kyi bstan pa 'byung ba'i rgyu yi
NK091(ke)001:16319: snying po mchog tu 'phags pa nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:16320: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas yin pa'i che ba dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:16322: bzhi pa gtan tshigs kyis rgyas par ston te /
NK091(ke)001:16323: rgyud lung man ngag gi don gnas thams cad 'dus pa'i tshad ma la shin tu ngam pas /
NK091(ke)001:16324: e ma'o zhes ngo mtshar che zhing rmad kyi chos /
NK091(ke)001:16325: shes sgrub kun gyi yang bcud /
NK091(ke)001:16326: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi mnga'
NK091(ke)001:16327: bdag kun gyi rtogs bya don gyi gasnga ba mthar
NK091(ke)001:16328: thug pa / don tshig gting dpags dka' ba zab mo mtha' dag kun 'dus pa'i ngang dang /
NK091(ke)001:16329: rang bzhin la sogs pa'i gtan tshigs thams cad kyi
NK091(ke)001:16330: gsang bcud ston pa'i rgyud lung chen po 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:16332: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun 'byung ba'i snying po don gyi phyi mor nges pas /
NK091(ke)001:16333: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi yum du gyur pa'i khyad par dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:16334: de rnams kyis thob byed thabs kyi khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16335: gsum pa thugs rje'i cho 'phrul gyi zhabs bsdu ba la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:16339: le'u bcu drug pa'i bsdu ba /
NK091(ke)001:16347: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16348: rgyal ba'i sku yi bkod pa yon tan rnam pa
NK091(ke)001:16349: sna tshogs ji snyed pa thams cad mi 'gog par
NK091(ke)001:16350: snang bar mdzad pas na rnam par snang mdzad de
NK091(ke)001:16352: sku yi sprul pa thams cad ni //
NK091(ke)001:16353: de bzhin rigs kyi gdung rgyud 'dzin //
NK091(ke)001:16355: ngo bo mi 'gyur zhing gnyen po dang bral bas
NK091(ke)001:16356: mi shigs pa'i thugs la g.yo ba med pas rdo
NK091(ke)001:16359: thugs las sprul pa'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK091(ke)001:16360: rdo rje rigs kyi gdung rgyud 'dzin //
NK091(ke)001:16362: grags mtha' dpag tu med pa ji snyed par gsal
NK091(ke)001:16363: bas rgyal ba'i gsung du shar bar snang ba mtha'
NK091(ke)001:16364: yasa te / gsung las sprul pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK091(ke)001:16367: mtshan dang dpe byad dang dngos grub ji snyed pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16368: yon tan kun gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas dpe
NK091(ke)001:16369: nor bu rin chen dbang gi rgyal po ltar sangs
NK091(ke)001:16370: rgyas rnams kyi che ba'i yon tan sna tshogs pa
NK091(ke)001:16371: kun 'byung bas rin chen 'byung ldan te /
NK091(ke)001:16372: yon tan yul gyi sangs rgyas rnams //
NK091(ke)001:16373: rin chen rigs kyi gdung rgyud 'dzin //
NK091(ke)001:16375: gdul bya mtha' dag gi don thams cad ma brtsal
NK091(ke)001:16376: bar lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang nas rdzogs par mdzad
NK091(ke)001:16377: pas gdona mi za ba'am don yod grub pa ste
NK091(ke)001:16378: / mdzad pa sprul pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK091(ke)001:16379: phrin las rigs kyi gdung rgyud 'dzin //
NK091(ke)001:16381: des na lnga zhes nges par bshad //
NK091(ke)001:16382: ci phyir zhe na sangs rgyas kun //
NK091(ke)001:16383: lnga po de las ma gtogs pa /
NK091(ke)001:16384: gzhan las byung zhing gzhan na med //
NK091(ke)001:16386: 'o na sangs rgyas lngar snang bas gcig par mi 'gyur te tha dad do ce na /
NK091(ke)001:16387: chos nyid kyi ngang la ston 'khor tha mi dad
NK091(ke)001:16388: par rdo rje snying po nyid la nyid 'char zhing
NK091(ke)001:16389: snang ba'i tshul gyis dper na nyi ma 'od du
NK091(ke)001:16390: shar ba bzhin ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor chos
NK091(ke)001:16391: sku skye med don gyi gsung rig pa rang gsal
NK091(ke)001:16393: des na rang byung gi ye shes las dang ngo
NK091(ke)001:16394: bos rdo rje ste ye shes ril gyi rtsa ba
NK091(ke)001:16395: nyid de / de nyid kyi byin rlabs ye shes
NK091(ke)001:16396: lnga'i ngo bo rigs lngar shar bas rang byung ye
NK091(ke)001:16397: shes nyid dang drug gi phyir rigs kyang rjes su
NK091(ke)001:16398: nyid de / mthun te / lha rgyud chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:16399: sku lnga'ang kun bzang dbyer med pas /
NK091(ke)001:16400: rgyal ba drug pa zhes bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:16401: rigs lnga kun bzang dbyer med pas //
NK091(ke)001:16402: rigs drug pa zhes bya ba yin //
NK091(ke)001:16404: de bas na rgyal ba ma lus pa'i yum du'ang mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:16409: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16410: le'u'i stod ma 'gags par snang ba'i sgo bsdu ste /
NK091(ke)001:16411: snying po byang chub ngo bo bsam du med cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ngang las /
NK091(ke)001:16412: chos kyi sgo mo dpag tu med la grangs las 'das par snang ba'ang /
NK091(ke)001:16413: mdor nyon mongs pa 'dul dbang gis stong phrag brgyad
NK091(ke)001:16414: cu'am brgyad khri dang bzhi stong du gdul bya rnams
NK091(ke)001:16415: 'jug pa'i sgo ru bstan zhing gragsa par gyur pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16416: rnam grangs bsam yas par bzhugs kyanga /
NK091(ke)001:16417: le'u'i smad ma skyes par snang ba sdud de /
NK091(ke)001:16418: sems kyi de kho na nyid ji bzhin par ma
NK091(ke)001:16419: nor bar ngesa pa'i gsang ba mchog gi theg pa
NK091(ke)001:16421: dngos su sems kyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal bar ston
NK091(ke)001:16422: pa'i rgyud chen po chos kyi me long 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:16423: do // 'o na don gcig la tha dad du bstan pa ji ltar 'byung zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:16424: gsang ba mchog gi theg pa 'di nyid du rigs
NK091(ke)001:16425: ma nges te don ma rtogs par sha thang bas
NK091(ke)001:16426: rtsol ba dang bcas te 'jug pa'i bar du lam
NK091(ke)001:16427: stegs kyi theg pa'i sgo yang blo rim ltar bsam
NK091(ke)001:16428: gyis mi khyab par shin tu mang la /
NK091(ke)001:16430: gsang don zab mo nyid nges par snang nas rtogs ma thaga tu /
NK091(ke)001:16431: theg pa'i 'jug sgo yang mdo gcig po de las
NK091(ke)001:16432: lhag pa med pa'i phyir sgo kun nas bsdur ba'i
NK091(ke)001:16433: bslab pa'ang shin tu gces so //
NK091(ke)001:16434: de bas na theg pa thams cad kyi yum du'ang mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:16439: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16440: des na kun brjod pa dang bstan pa'i rnam grangs
NK091(ke)001:16441: ji snyed du grags pa kun kyang 'gro ba brgyud
NK091(ke)001:16442: nas drang zhing bkri ba'i don du brdas mtshon pa
NK091(ke)001:16444: tshig nyid nges pa don gyi de kho na nyid min pas so //
NK091(ke)001:16449: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16450: de ltar mtshon byed tshig gi brda' thabs brjod pa
NK091(ke)001:16451: la brten pas yun gyi don srid chen po de
NK091(ke)001:16452: kho na nyid rnyed cing rtogs par byed pa ni
NK091(ke)001:16453: / dper na gsal byed sgron mas mun pa bsal
NK091(ke)001:16454: nas khang pa'i nang gi gser tshol na rnyed pa
NK091(ke)001:16455: / ltar du / ji bzhin du mtshon pa'i thabs kyi sgo la brten nas /
NK091(ke)001:16456: don dbyings rig bde ba chen po gsang ba'i snying po'i klong mdzod brdol bar byas te /
NK091(ke)001:16457: dam pa rnams kyi spyod yul byang chub sems kyi
NK091(ke)001:16458: gteer chen po yul med rang gsal du 'byin pa
NK091(ke)001:16460: rang rig pa ngang gi thig le chos nyid byang chub kyi sems /
NK091(ke)001:16461: bdag nyid chen po gcig gis dngos po kun la khyab pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:16462: chos thams cad gsang sngags don gyi gnas lugs ye
NK091(ke)001:16463: ji bzhin pa nyid du lung chen po nges par
NK091(ke)001:16465: shes bya kun gyi de kho na nyid mthar thug tu nges pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:16467: lung chen por bstan pa kun gyi yum du'ang mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:16472: kun tu bzang po nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:16473: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16474: bcu drug pa'i bsdu ba rnam pa sna tshogs zhes pa sdud de /
NK091(ke)001:16475: de bas sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs pa dang sprul
NK091(ke)001:16476: pa'i sku ril ngang gi thig le bde ba chen
NK091(ke)001:16477: po de las 'byung ste snang ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:16478: bcu bdun pa'i bsdu ba bsam med ces pa sdud de /
NK091(ke)001:16479: rtsa ba chen po 'khor 'das ma lus pa kun
NK091(ke)001:16480: gyi snying po de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes 'di
NK091(ke)001:16481: nyid ye nas mtha' thams cad dang bral ba'i ngo
NK091(ke)001:16482: bo spros pa med pa'i thig lera gnas shing bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:16483: pa las / bco brgyad pa'i bsdu ba brjod dang zhes pa sdud de /
NK091(ke)001:16484: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob pa'i rgyal sras semsa can chen
NK091(ke)001:16485: po kun gyi don rtogs par bya ba'i phyir du
NK091(ke)001:16486: ston pa nyid la 'chad cing nyid la nges par
NK091(ke)001:16488: bcu dgu pa'i bsdu ba tshig brda' zhes pa sdud de /
NK091(ke)001:16489: rang bzhin gyi zhi gnas gang du'ang g.yo ba dang
NK091(ke)001:16490: 'dzin pa med par mi rtog pa'i ngang dam pa
NK091(ke)001:16491: ji bzhin pa'i nam mkha' khyab pa'i dbyings la ngo
NK091(ke)001:16492: bo nyid kyi lhag mthong rang rig pa'i mngon sum
NK091(ke)001:16493: kun nas ma rmongsa par 'ja' tshon ltar ye gsal
NK091(ke)001:16494: ba chen po bshad pa bzhin ma 'dresa la yongs
NK091(ke)001:16495: su rdzogsa te ngo bo gcig dang du ma yod
NK091(ke)001:16496: med rtag chad la sogs pa ma spangs par grol
NK091(ke)001:16497: ba'i don gyi gsang ba mthar thug pa zhi gnas
NK091(ke)001:16498: dang lhag mthong zung du 'brel ba'i rang bzhin ma
NK091(ke)001:16499: nor ba la dgongs pa nges par 'grel te legs
NK091(ke)001:16500: par bshad do zhes tha snyad du bsnyad par mdzad
NK091(ke)001:16502: stong pa nyid las de skad du tshig gi sgra brnyan byung bas /
NK091(ke)001:16503: don grub pa'i ngo bo thams cad ma 'dres pa
NK091(ke)001:16504: dang yongs su rdzogs par 'grel bar bstan pa ni
NK091(ke)001:16505: / spyod yul yongs su dag pas kun tu bzang po nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:16506: gsum pa zhabs bsdu bas 'khor gyi go ba'i yon tan ni /
NK091(ke)001:16510: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16512: de ltar na bshad pa la snyegs pa'i don gyis
NK091(ke)001:16513: rjes su mthun par gang gis dgongs pa nges par
NK091(ke)001:16514: 'grel pa rgyas par bstan pa de dag kyang /
NK091(ke)001:16515: las kyi rdzu 'phrul gzhi rang bzhin ji bzhin pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16516: bsam gtan gyi rdzu 'phrul lam pa'i 'jug pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16517: chos nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul 'bras bu la sbyor ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:16518: thugs rje'i rdzu 'phrul nges don sel med pa'i rtsa
NK091(ke)001:16519: ba dang cho 'phrul bzhi'i don 'khrul pa dang lam
NK091(ke)001:16520: dang rang bzhin dang 'bras bu'i snang ba bzhir bstan
NK091(ke)001:16521: pa las / phyi ma la gzhi lhun gyis grub pa las /
NK091(ke)001:16522: ji bzhin par nges pa zhi ba'i bkod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16523: de 'ba' zhig las gyur ba khro bor snang ba rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK091(ke)001:16524: gdul bya don la 'jug pa'i phyir chos snang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:16525: don dang sbyor bas kun brjod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16526: ji bzhin la rtsa ba'i rjes su bstan pa dang
NK091(ke)001:16527: bzhir nges par ji lta ba bzhin du rig par
NK091(ke)001:16528: bya'o // de skad ces gdams ngag gi mdo smras te bka' stsal pas /
NK091(ke)001:16529: 'khor lang ka'i bdag po la sogs pa dman pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16530: lus kyi sems dpa' rnams kyis de'i don rtogs pas
NK091(ke)001:16531: yi rangsa te / thams cad ma 'dres pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16532: yongsa su rdzogs par thugs su chud nas /
NK091(ke)001:16533: mtha' dbus med par grol te dbugs chen po phyin par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16535: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:16536: gang 'khor 'das kyi chos kun byang chub kyi sems
NK091(ke)001:16537: la yongs su rdzogs par 'grel pa'i le'u ste bcu
NK091(ke)001:16538: dgu pa gsal bar bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16539: de dag gi sgo nas theg pa chen po nges par 'byung ba'i tshul las /
NK091(ke)001:16540: snying po byang chub kyi ngo bo kun tu bzang pos /
NK091(ke)001:16541: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa dam pa nyid la
NK091(ke)001:16542: nyid kyis nges par 'grel ba'i tshul zab mo rnams
NK091(ke)001:16543: dus 'dir gsang ba pas gtam rgyud du thos pa
NK091(ke)001:16544: brjod pa'i phyir gsung chos kyi phyag rgya'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:16545: sgrib pa med par rnam par bgros pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:16546: byung tshul bstan pa lnga pa nyid shin tu gsal
NK091(ke)001:16547: bar bkrol ba'o ////drug pa gdul bya skabs la bab
NK091(ke)001:16548: pa'i byung tshul la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:16555: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16556: spyir byung tshul 'di nyid dam pa'i gsang lung ji ltar byung gi lan te /
NK091(ke)001:16557: khyad par rtsal 'phangs las mthar lam /
NK091(ke)001:16558: rgyud gnas lugs las gdul bya skabs la bab pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16559: byung tshul mtshan ma rang zhi'i lta ba dpa' bos
NK091(ke)001:16560: dgra thul ba lta bu nyid rgyas par ston no
NK091(ke)001:16561: // de nas yang sdud pa po /
NK091(ke)001:16562: lang ka'i mang'a bdag byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po des /
NK091(ke)001:16563: ston pa gsang ba pa'i bdag po la sngon du byung ba'i tshig bcu gnyis pa'i drug pa /
NK091(ke)001:16564: gdul bya skabs la bab pa'i ched na'ang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:16565: zhes 'byung ba'i dri ba yongs su dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:16566: kye gasnga ba pa'i bdag po /
NK091(ke)001:16567: nyid kyi theg pa chen po gsang ba dam pa
NK091(ke)001:16568: 'byung ba'i tshul ston pas lung bstan pa gtan du
NK091(ke)001:16570: gdul bya'i skabs la bab pa'i tshe na yang 'byung /
NK091(ke)001:16572: 'jig rten pa gang zhig gdul bya'i skabs la bab pa nas /
NK091(ke)001:16573: yongs su btul bar grags pa lagas /
NK091(ke)001:16577: gsang sngags 'byung ba'i rgyu phyi pas mi 'dul ba'i
NK091(ke)001:16578: gdul bya las dang rtsal shin tu drag pas khyad
NK091(ke)001:16579: para can khams gsum gyi byang chub sems kyi sa
NK091(ke)001:16580: bon rlag par byed pas 'jig rten gsum sreg par
NK091(ke)001:16581: byed pa / khro bo chen po dang cha lugs tshul mthun par /
NK091(ke)001:16582: las kyi khro bo'i ngo bo dang las dang cha
NK091(ke)001:16583: lugs kyi tshul gtum zhing rngam pa de nyid 'dul
NK091(ke)001:16584: ba'i gdul bya'i dus la nges par bab nas thugs
NK091(ke)001:16585: rje 'byung ba'i dus su phyin te smin pa'i tshe
NK091(ke)001:16586: yongs su btul bar mdzad pa na /
NK091(ke)001:16587: de'i phyir phyogs dus kun gyi sangs rgyas bdud bzhi'i
NK091(ke)001:16588: g.yul las rgyal ba thamsa cad gnas chen po snying
NK091(ke)001:16589: po byang chub nyid ga la ba dera 'dus nas
NK091(ke)001:16590: / skyes bu dam pa thu ba dka' dang dan
NK091(ke)001:16591: phag dag 'chad pa bzhin du gyur pa la rnam
NK091(ke)001:16593: spyir cha 'dra bas gcig dang du ma las grol gyis kyang /
NK091(ke)001:16594: dang po 'dul ba'i dpon du gyur pa dang g.yog
NK091(ke)001:16595: yin pas khyad par gyi thugs rje 'byung ba'i yul
NK091(ke)001:16596: dang gnyen por gyur pas so //
NK091(ke)001:16597: de yang dpe ji ltara ji ltar rdo rje semsa
NK091(ke)001:16598: dpa'i sprul pa'i sgron ma zhi ba'i zhing khams yongs
NK091(ke)001:16599: su bkod pa lta bu'i grangs dang mnyam pa shin
NK091(ke)001:16600: tu phra ba rkang dang sri la gnas pa'i bdud
NK091(ke)001:16601: bzhi po kun 'joms pas khro bo'i sprin rnam par
NK091(ke)001:16602: 'jigs pa rnams kyi phrin las kyi mdzad pa gnyen
NK091(ke)001:16603: po rdul snyed kyisa btul bar gyur pa de kho
NK091(ke)001:16604: na'i tshe / de kho na'i dus nyid du theg pa chen po 'di yang byung zhing grags so //
NK091(ke)001:16606: gdul bya ru tra bshad pa /
NK091(ke)001:16607: gnyen pos bdud btul tshul bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16615: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16616: yang lang ka'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:16618: gdul bya de gol gzhi'i rgyu gang las byung /
NK091(ke)001:16619: de'i rkyen las ji zhig spyad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16620: skye ba brgyud de ji ltar blangs pa lagas zhes ngo bo dang /
NK091(ke)001:16621: de nyid gsang sngags 'byung ba'i rgyur ji ltar gyur zhes ru tra'i rgyu rkyen dang /
NK091(ke)001:16623: gsang ba'i rgyu ru ji ltar byung ba dang dri ba gsum po de skad ces gsol pa las /
NK091(ke)001:16625: gol gzhi gang las byung ba /
NK091(ke)001:16627: skye ba ji ltar blang ba /
NK091(ke)001:16628: sngags kyi rgyur ji ltar 'gyur ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:16633: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16635: de nas gsang ba pa'i bdag posa lan smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:16636: de la lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu drag po nyid gsogs pa'i dus gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:16639: de yang rgyu gsogs pa'i dus dang ngo bo gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:16640: dran pa bskal pa dpag tu med pa 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:16641: bskal pa dang bstan pa'i sgo nas slob dpon gyi yon tan bstan pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:16642: ston pa sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa zhes bya ba /
NK091(ke)001:16643: bskal pa kun dga' zhes bya ba la /
NK091(ke)001:16644: zhing khams mngon par dga' ba zhes bya bar byung ba'i bstan pa la /
NK091(ke)001:16645: cha lugs rab tu byung ba'i dge slong thugs gsang
NK091(ke)001:16646: sngags kyi don dang ldan pa thub dka' gzhon nu
NK091(ke)001:16647: zhes bya ba / gang gdul bya'i blo'i mos pa
NK091(ke)001:16648: ji lta ba bzhin du chos nyid ji bzhin pa
NK091(ke)001:16649: ma nor bar gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i chos
NK091(ke)001:16651: dus thams cad nas gnas skabs thams cad du /
NK091(ke)001:16652: sems kyi chos nyid ma bcos ma bslad par lta sgom spyod pa'i rnal 'byor du gnas pa /
NK091(ke)001:16653: skyes bu dam par nges te dgongs pa sangs rgyas kyi sar chud pa zhig byung ba des /
NK091(ke)001:16654: sems can thams cad rgyal ba'i sras su mthong zhing /
NK091(ke)001:16655: de dag thar pa la yongs su bskul te smin pa la brtson pa 'ba' zhig byed do //
NK091(ke)001:16657: 'khor ba thog ma dang tha ma med par skye
NK091(ke)001:16658: ba thoga ma dang tha ma med pa'i las dang
NK091(ke)001:16659: skye ba dpag tu med pa ni brjod kyi mi
NK091(ke)001:16660: lang zhing ngo bo mi rdzogs te /
NK091(ke)001:16661: 'dir las dang po'i dus na bla ma gang la
NK091(ke)001:16662: sems ji ltar bskyed cing bstan pa la log par
NK091(ke)001:16663: zhugs pas las skabs gcig gis drag po'i las gsogs
NK091(ke)001:16664: pa'i skye ba cha gcig la bzung na /
NK091(ke)001:16666: thub daka'i nye 'khor du blon po'i rigs kyi khyim bdag ke'u ka ya zhes bya ba zhig la /
NK091(ke)001:16667: bu thar pa nag po zhes bya ba zhig yod de /
NK091(ke)001:16668: bu de la g.yog dan phag zhes bya ba zhig yod do //
NK091(ke)001:16670: mi gang dag dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu la rnal 'byor dam pa sngags kyi lam bslabsa te /
NK091(ke)001:16671: kun kyang rnal ma la blo 'byor ba'i don gyi
NK091(ke)001:16672: lam la gnas shing rnal 'byor la spyod par gyur
NK091(ke)001:16673: to // de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK091(ke)001:16674: thar pa nag po de 'di ltar rtog go //
NK091(ke)001:16675: dge slong thub daka'a gzhon nu 'dis /
NK091(ke)001:16676: gdul bya thams cad rang rang gang la mos pa ji lta ba bzhin ston par thos nas /
NK091(ke)001:16677: thar pa nag po lta ba gol ba'i gzhi'i dang por /
NK091(ke)001:16678: thams cad ci dga' bar spyod pa bzhin du lam yod pa'i chos dag 'byung ngam zhes rtog la /
NK091(ke)001:16679: gzhan gang dag la yang dris pa las /
NK091(ke)001:16680: thams cad kyis lta ba rtogs pa la bsam nas de ltar 'byung bar smras so //
NK091(ke)001:16681: de nasa g.yog dang bcas pa dge slong ga la ba der zhugs te /
NK091(ke)001:16682: gnas su phyin te 'dun pa legs par 'dun nas gsol pa /
NK091(ke)001:16683: dge slong chen po thams cad ji lta bar spyod
NK091(ke)001:16684: pa de bzhin du lam ston pa'i thabs la mkhas
NK091(ke)001:16685: par thos na / de de lta nyid du nges sam /
NK091(ke)001:16686: de skad ces gsol pa las /
NK091(ke)001:16688: rigs kyi bu lta ba rtogs nas spyod pa yangs
NK091(ke)001:16689: pa la dgongs nas de de lta nyid du nges
NK091(ke)001:16690: par 'byung ba dag yong bar runga ngo //
NK091(ke)001:16692: thar pa nag po g.yog dang bcas pa dga' mgu yi rangs te /
NK091(ke)001:16693: bdag g.yoga dang bcas pa 'di khyod nyid kyi bka' la gnas par gzung du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:16694: bdag kyang khyed la thams cad mi 'gog pa'i lam blangs te rnal 'byor du gnas par 'tshal bas /
NK091(ke)001:16695: dam pa nyid du nges par gzung du gsol zhes zhus te 'dun pa las /
NK091(ke)001:16696: dge slong des gnang ste smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:16697: khyod nyid bka' pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:16698: rnal 'byor du gnas pa legs so //
NK091(ke)001:16699: de bas na de ltar bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:16701: thar pa nag po rab tu byung nas dge slong dam para byas te slob dpon du bzung /
NK091(ke)001:16702: dan phag ni de'i dus 'dzin du dge bsnyen gyi
NK091(ke)001:16703: khrims la bcug ste dge slong thar pa'i g.yog tu
NK091(ke)001:16704: byas so // de nas thar pa nag po dge slong gis gsol pa /
NK091(ke)001:16705: dge slong thub dka' chen po /
NK091(ke)001:16706: thams cad ji lta ba'i lam dam pa de gang lags /
NK091(ke)001:16708: gzhi chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor rang gi
NK091(ke)001:16709: sems nyid 'od gsal ba de nyid rtogs te ma
NK091(ke)001:16715: 'dod yon lnga ste bzhi po rnams la gnas te
NK091(ke)001:16716: spyod kyang don chos nyid ji bzhin pa yin pas
NK091(ke)001:16717: dper na nam mkha' la ni sprin gyi tshogs rang
NK091(ke)001:16718: byung zhing zhi ba bzhin te /
NK091(ke)001:16719: 'di ltar goms pa ni rnal 'byor dam pa'i lam mchog gsang ba chen po'o //
NK091(ke)001:16721: thar pas log pa'i spyod pa rang gar go //
NK091(ke)001:16722: dan phag gis don gyi gzhi la go nas /
NK091(ke)001:16723: thar pa g.yog dang bcas pa gnyis ka yid rangas te /
NK091(ke)001:16725: 'khor ba'i chos la spyad kyang 'bras bu thob pas thabsa la mkhas so //
NK091(ke)001:16729: bdag cag gnyis thams cad du de la yongs su gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:16732: sgra ji lta ba de bzhin /
NK091(ke)001:16735: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16736: de nas dpon g.yog gnyis sgra ji lta ba de
NK091(ke)001:16737: bzhin du lta ba gol ma gol gyis phyin ci
NK091(ke)001:16738: log pa dang ma log pa'i tshul du spyad pa
NK091(ke)001:16739: las / thar pa dge slong ni blo gros kyi
NK091(ke)001:16740: nges pa ma rnyed de bla med mi spangs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16741: dam las nyams nas sgra 'ba' zhig la phyogs pas
NK091(ke)001:16742: las / / rgyu nye bar bzung ba 'dir lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK091(ke)001:16743: rkyen thun mong du gyur pa ste sbyor sgrol dang /
NK091(ke)001:16746: tshig rtsub mo ste spyad par bya ba lnga dang /
NK091(ke)001:16748: dam rdzas lnga ste dang du blang ba lnga dang /
NK091(ke)001:16750: 'dod yon lnga ste lnga phrag gi dngos po bzhi
NK091(ke)001:16751: kho na la spyod de zhen nas don ma go
NK091(ke)001:16752: bar tshig gi rjes su 'brangs te lus dge slong
NK091(ke)001:16753: dam pa'i cha byad du bcug nas /
NK091(ke)001:16754: sems log pa ngan 'gro'i lam du zhugs so //
NK091(ke)001:16755: g.yog dan phag ni sgra'i gzhi don gyi nges pa
NK091(ke)001:16756: rnyed nas spyod kyang mi 'dzin pas blo gros dam
NK091(ke)001:16757: par 'brel te / lta ba gnyis su med pa
NK091(ke)001:16758: rtogs pa'i don 'ba' zhig la phyogs pas ji bzhin
NK091(ke)001:16759: pa snang la zhen pa med pa kho nara spyad
NK091(ke)001:16760: par 'brel te / de / goms pa la zhen
NK091(ke)001:16761: nas yongs su gnas pas lta spyod 'dres te rnal
NK091(ke)001:16762: ma la blo 'byor pas lus dge bsnyen gyi tshul
NK091(ke)001:16763: ma rabsa kyi cha byad du bcug nas /
NK091(ke)001:16764: sems dam par nges pa'i lam du zhugs so //
NK091(ke)001:16765: de nas thar pa g.yog dang lta ba ma mthun te /
NK091(ke)001:16767: bdag cag gnyis ni dpon gcig la /
NK091(ke)001:16768: sgra gcig tu byung ba 'di la /
NK091(ke)001:16769: so sor ma mthun pa 'di ji lta bu zhig /dan phag gisa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:16771: da ltar lta ba'i ngang la nges par 'jog pa 'di kho na las gzhan ma thos lags so //
NK091(ke)001:16773: don rtogs pa med pa'i tshig tu song nas bdag
NK091(ke)001:16774: gisa kyang de ltar nges pa rnyed de spyod pa
NK091(ke)001:16775: 'di kho na las gzhan ma thos so //
NK091(ke)001:16777: de lasa rtsod pa chen pora gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16778: de ltar lta ba ma mthun pas rtsod pa ni
NK091(ke)001:16779: mtshams med gsog pa'i rgyu ste g.yog dang so sor
NK091(ke)001:16780: bskal te ma mthong ma phrad par dam bcas nas
NK091(ke)001:16781: g.yog nyid khams ring por spyugs te spangsa pas yang
NK091(ke)001:16782: dag lam du zhugs pa la byams pa'i dam nyams
NK091(ke)001:16783: so // de nas thar pa dge slong de /
NK091(ke)001:16784: mngon pa'i nga rgyal log pa'i ri bo skyes te /
NK091(ke)001:16785: dpon la rang dang g.yog po'i lta bas mthun te so so'i nges pa rnyed pa gsol ba las /
NK091(ke)001:16786: dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu ma bcos ma bslad
NK091(ke)001:16787: pa'i rnal mar spyod pasa kha gsag med de rang
NK091(ke)001:16788: bzhin gsonga por smra bas na /
NK091(ke)001:16789: dan phag ltar nges so zhes bsgo ste ltangs bcad pas /
NK091(ke)001:16791: slob dpon la khros te spong nas smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:16793: gnyis ka ltar ro zhes kyang ma bsnyamsa pas /
NK091(ke)001:16794: nges para bdag bkar ba bcag pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16796: dpon 'di yang khams 'dir ma chags par byas la /
NK091(ke)001:16797: 'di dag bdag gi khams su bya'o zhes dam bcas nas /
NK091(ke)001:16798: che ba'i nga rgyal skyes te /
NK091(ke)001:16799: dpon yang khams ring pora spyugs te yongs su spangs pas bla ma bkur ba'i dam nyams so //
NK091(ke)001:16800: de ltar mtshams med pa'i rgyu dang rtsa ba nyams
NK091(ke)001:16801: pa de yang lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu dang rkyen
NK091(ke)001:16802: no // de nas thara pa nag po mtshungs par
NK091(ke)001:16803: ldan pa'i rgyu lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas
NK091(ke)001:16804: bsgribs pas de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gi sgo grangs
NK091(ke)001:16805: mang zhing rgya che bar gyur pas /
NK091(ke)001:16806: thams cad du ston pa dapagas par dka' ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:16807: gsang ba'i don ma go ba ste yongs su ma
NK091(ke)001:16808: chud de gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par /
NK091(ke)001:16809: gtan tshigs kyis gzhal bar bya ba lung dang man
NK091(ke)001:16810: ngag gi tshad ma zab mo gnyis kyisa gzhal te
NK091(ke)001:16811: gtan la dbab pa ma byas par /
NK091(ke)001:16812: thar pa rang gi log zhen gyis 'thad par nges
NK091(ke)001:16813: pa'i tshad ma yin par gzung ba la zhen phyogs
NK091(ke)001:16814: su drangs nas ras chod dang gzu lum byas te
NK091(ke)001:16815: sbas pa'i gsang ba la 'chel bas gsang don mi
NK091(ke)001:16816: smra ba'i dam nyams te gsang ba gzhan la spel
NK091(ke)001:16817: nas gdul zhing thams cad kyang log par bsgyur zhing
NK091(ke)001:16818: / rang nyid kyang log pa'i rgya mtshor zhugs te /
NK091(ke)001:16819: phyin ci log gi lam la ma nor ba yin
NK091(ke)001:16820: par rdzun du smras pas byang sdom las nyams la
NK091(ke)001:16821: / sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcad pa las nyams te log pa'i dka' thub drag po dang /
NK091(ke)001:16822: log pa'i brtul zhugs chen po la zhugs pa ni
NK091(ke)001:16823: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen te dur khrod kyi mi
NK091(ke)001:16824: ro dag blangs te kha zas su byed cing /
NK091(ke)001:16825: pagsa pa dag bshus te g.yang gzhir gyon te longs spyod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16826: gzhan srog gcod pa'i ce spyang nag po dang /
NK091(ke)001:16831: za byed dur phag la sogs pa'i gson ma mang po bsten te /
NK091(ke)001:16832: thams cad kyi srog gcod cing /
NK091(ke)001:16833: sha khrag la longs spyod par byed pa /
NK091(ke)001:16834: smad 'tshong ma'i tshogs mang po bsdus te chagsa pa chen por spyod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16835: thun mong gi dngos po bzhi rdzun /
NK091(ke)001:16837: 'dod log /srog gcod pa rnams las mi 'da' bar
NK091(ke)001:16838: dngos po bzhi'i rang bzhin chos nyid ji bzhin pa
NK091(ke)001:16839: de kho na nyid rtogs pa las yongs su 'das
NK091(ke)001:16840: par gyur to // gsum pa la bzhi ste /
NK091(ke)001:16842: dmyal ba'i skye ba blang ba /
NK091(ke)001:16843: de las thar nas skye ba blangs pa /
NK091(ke)001:16844: tha ma srin po'i skye ba blangs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16848: de la byed par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16849: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16850: de nasa thar pa nag po'i skye ba de 'phos par gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:16851: de skye ba de'i phyi ma thar pa 'phos ma
NK091(ke)001:16852: thag pa'i skye ba dang po la spyod pa rgyu
NK091(ke)001:16853: mthun las ce spyang nag po'i lus su skye ba
NK091(ke)001:16855: srog chagsa 'ba' zhig gsod pa'i las spyod cing /
NK091(ke)001:16856: sha dang khrag drona mo za bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16857: skye ba de'i phyi ma gnyis pa la dmyal ba'i
NK091(ke)001:16858: khyi lu 'de la sogs pa gdug pasa gsod pa'i
NK091(ke)001:16859: las can sha khrag zas su byed pa /
NK091(ke)001:16860: tha dad pa'i lus su skye ba lnga brgya blangs shing /
NK091(ke)001:16861: myong ba rgyu mthun gzhan gyis bsad cing skye ba 'phos pa sha stag tu gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16862: skye ba de'i phyi ma gsum pa la bya ne le sha zana dang /
NK091(ke)001:16865: ru rtse rkang ldag zhes phyi ma 'di gnyis bod na med gsungs /
NK091(ke)001:16866: de la sogs pa tha dada pa'i lus blangs shing /
NK091(ke)001:16867: gzhan gyis bsad cing skye ba 'pho ba sha stag tu gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16868: skye ba de dag gi phyi ma bzhi pa dag la sbrang bu tre ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:16870: ro za rkang 'jibs la sogs pa 'bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:16871: sbrul lta bu 'bu shin tu chen po tha dad pa'i lus su skye ba blangs shing /
NK091(ke)001:16872: de dag kyang gnyen posa bsad cing skye ba 'pho ba sha stag tu gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16873: skye ba de'i phyi ma lnga pa dag la /
NK091(ke)001:16874: ngan skyugs kyi 'dam na gnas pa'i skye bor skyes pa skye ba lnga brgya blangs te /
NK091(ke)001:16875: myong ba rgyu mthun gnyen posa bsad cing skye ba 'pho ba sha stag tu gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16876: skye ba de dag gi phyi ma drug pa la /
NK091(ke)001:16877: srog chags dag gi lus la gnas shing /
NK091(ke)001:16878: zas kyang de dag la byed pa'i skye bora skye ba lnga brgya blangs te /
NK091(ke)001:16879: gnyen pos bsad cing skye ba 'pho ba sha stag tu gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16880: yang skye ba de'i phyi ma bdun pa dag la /
NK091(ke)001:16884: lung pa tha dad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16887: shing 'bu lta bu sdong chen la sogs pa'i nang du gnas pa'i skye bor gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:16888: de dag la gnas shing zas kyang desa 'tsho ba /
NK091(ke)001:16889: gnyen posa bsad cing skye ba 'pho ba 'ab'a zhig tu gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16890: skye ba de'i phyi ma brgyad pa dag la /
NK091(ke)001:16891: mngal gyi grong khyer na gnas pa'i skye bor skye ba lnga brgyar gnas te /
NK091(ke)001:16892: gnas dang 'tsho ba yang de la byed par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16893: de yan chad du spyod pa rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu ste /
NK091(ke)001:16894: rnam grangs ni skye ba brgyad pa yan chad la skye ba bzhi stong du don gyis brtsis pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16898: bdun pa la grangs nges pa ma smos kyang /
NK091(ke)001:16899: tha dad pa'i lus blangs zhes pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16900: gong 'og gi sgra nges pas bartsi'o //
NK091(ke)001:16904: dmyal ba rnams su de ltar 'phen no //
NK091(ke)001:16905: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16906: yang skye ba de'i phyi ma dgu pa la /
NK091(ke)001:16907: mnar med pa'i gnas rdo rje dmyal ba zhes bya bar /
NK091(ke)001:16908: de nyid kyi tshe'i tshad brgyad khri'i bar du gnas te /
NK091(ke)001:16909: dmyal ba de'i sdug bsngal gyi tshad ni brjod du mi rung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:16911: gang gi mdun du sdug bsngal gyi tshad de brjod
NK091(ke)001:16912: na ganga gis thos pa de brgyal bar 'gyur ro
NK091(ke)001:16915: e ma'o 'di ci nyes zhes smras pa'i lan gsungs pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' 'byon pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:16916: dmyal ba pa de tshe 'pho ba'i yun gnyis skad cig gcig gis phyin par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16917: de'ang dge slong thub dka' gnas gyur te rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:16918: sems dpa' thub pa'i dbang po nyid du sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:16919: nas dmyal ba pa de'i ngo la chos kyi rgyal
NK091(ke)001:16920: po gshin rjer snang bas de 'dul bar mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:16921: des / kho na nyid kyi las yin no zhes chos bstan pas /
NK091(ke)001:16922: las de yid la byas pas yongs su shes te /
NK091(ke)001:16923: sngar byas la 'gyod para gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16924: 'gyod pa tsam gyisa gnas de nas shi 'phos nas /
NK091(ke)001:16925: bcu pa rab tu tsha ba'i dmyal ba'i gnas su
NK091(ke)001:16926: yang de nyid kyi tshe'i tshad bskal pa brgyad khrir
NK091(ke)001:16927: gnas te / mnar med pa ji lta ba bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:16928: der yang sdug bsngal dris pas thub pas lan btab ste de nas yang 'phos nas /
NK091(ke)001:16929: bcu gcig pa tsha ba chung ngu dang /
NK091(ke)001:16930: bcu gnyis pa ngu 'bod chen po dang /
NK091(ke)001:16933: bco lnga pa thig nag dang /
NK091(ke)001:16935: bcu bdun pa yang sos dang la sogs pa zhes pas grang dmyal brgyad kyang gsang snying ltar te /
NK091(ke)001:16936: thub pas lung bstan nas 'gyod pa'i rgyus gyen du
NK091(ke)001:16937: 'byung ste dmyal ba'i gnas rnams su yang de dag
NK091(ke)001:16938: gi tshe tshad brgyad khrira gnas te /
NK091(ke)001:16939: mnar med pa dang rab tu tsha ba ji lta ba bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:16940: dmyal ba tshe ring bas 'jig rten zhig par 'gyur zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:16941: de nama zhig pa na yang /
NK091(ke)001:16942: 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan gyi dmyal ba rnams su de ltar 'phen no //
NK091(ke)001:16943: 'di dag gi las ni ma rdzogs pa rdzogs par
NK091(ke)001:16944: byed pa'i phyir skye ba brgyad yan chad kyi las
NK091(ke)001:16945: las gyur te yongs su rdzogs par byed pa'i rkyen
NK091(ke)001:16946: dang 'phen pa'i las zhes bya ste rgyu dang thun
NK091(ke)001:16947: mong ngo // dmyal ba rnams ni 'bras bu gsum las rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:16948: de ltar skye ba phrag brgyad dang dgur 'bum phrag brgyad du brgyud pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:16952: gtogs 'dod can zhes bya bar skye ba blangs so //
NK091(ke)001:16953: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16954: de dag las 'phos nas kyang thar pa nag po
NK091(ke)001:16955: las brtsis pas skye ba bcu dgu pa dag la
NK091(ke)001:16956: bskal pa'i snyigs ma gsum du sdug bsngal myong ba
NK091(ke)001:16957: ni / gang 'jig pa'i bskal pa mu ge dang
NK091(ke)001:16958: nad dang mtshon gang dang gang du 'byung ba de
NK091(ke)001:16959: dang der skye bar byed do //
NK091(ke)001:16961: 'jig pa de dag gisa de dag gang stongs na yang /
NK091(ke)001:16962: gzhan dag gang 'jig pa'i dus su yang las kyi dbang gis dera skye ba len par 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:16963: de dag ni myong ba rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:16964: de dag las thar nas kyang nyi shu pa sha
NK091(ke)001:16965: dang rus pa za ba'i ched du 'dod pas gsoda
NK091(ke)001:16966: pa'i skye ba'i rigsa su bskal pa brgyad khrir skye
NK091(ke)001:16967: ba len cing 'pho bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16968: de dag ni spyod pa rgyu mthun du rtogs te las ngan der yang gsog go //
NK091(ke)001:16969: de las thar nas nyer gcig pa gshin rje'i 'jig
NK091(ke)001:16970: rtena gyi khams yi dwags bzhi'i rigs su skye ba
NK091(ke)001:16971: lnga brgyara gdung bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:16972: 'di ni dbang gi 'bras bur yang 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:16973: de las 'phos nas nyer gnyis pa lus srul po'i rigs su skye ba blangs so //
NK091(ke)001:16974: skye ba de'i phyi ma nyer gsum pa la dri
NK091(ke)001:16975: dang sha rjen za bas sha za'i rigs su skye
NK091(ke)001:16976: ba blangs so // skye ba de'i phyi ma nyer
NK091(ke)001:16977: bzhi pa la lus srul po'i rigsa su skye ba
NK091(ke)001:16978: ba blangs so // blangs te / srul po gnya' drag can zhes bya ba'i bu /
NK091(ke)001:16979: srul po gtogs 'dod can zhes bya bar skye ba blangs so //
NK091(ke)001:16980: skye ba 'di gsum la tshe tshad bstan pa med la dbang gi 'bras bur yang 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:16981: mdor na gong 'og gi skye ba bzhi stong lnga
NK091(ke)001:16982: brgya dang gsum ste dmyal bar brgyud pa'i skye ba
NK091(ke)001:16983: bcu gcig brgyad khrir mtshungs pa la /
NK091(ke)001:16984: tshe tshad bskal pa 'bum phrag dgu dang drug khri
NK091(ke)001:16985: snyed du brgyud nas lang ka'i yul du skyes so
NK091(ke)001:16987: ma zan ma tang kar grags pa /
NK091(ke)001:16988: lus dang mthu'i mtshan nyid do //
NK091(ke)001:16990: skye ba de'i phyi ma la yul lang ka /zhes pa nas /
NK091(ke)001:16992: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:16993: skye ba de'i phyi ma nyer lnga pa la rgyu
NK091(ke)001:16994: mthun gyi spyod pa rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu ru tra
NK091(ke)001:16996: yul lang ka pu ra zhes bya ba'i smad 'tshong
NK091(ke)001:16997: ma zhig gi mngal du chags te skye ba smin
NK091(ke)001:16998: to // de der skye ba blangas te skyes nas
NK091(ke)001:16999: zla ba dgu na ma shi bar gyur pa dang
NK091(ke)001:17000: to // / mi gang de dag gis dwa bu
NK091(ke)001:17001: rkog bu 'di gso bar byar mi rung ste yul
NK091(ke)001:17002: gang sme bar 'gyur bas ma'i mchan du bzhag par
NK091(ke)001:17003: to // / rigs so // zhes gleng nas /
NK091(ke)001:17004: dug shing nala byi zhes bya ba'i rtsa na /
NK091(ke)001:17005: dur phag gti mug gi tshang chags pa'i bar na dug sbrul zhe sdang gi 'khra sar byed pa /
NK091(ke)001:17006: kha la 'doda chags dur bya'i tshang bacasa pa'i rtsar /
NK091(ke)001:17007: 'di nyid mi ma yin gyi gnas te chags sdang skye ba'i sa yin la /
NK091(ke)001:17008: shing 'di w+aa r+aa na s+ai'i yul gra gcig na'ang
NK091(ke)001:17009: yod gsung ste rlangs pa dang dri mas mi la
NK091(ke)001:17011: nang ltar na bdag 'dzin gyi ru trar smin pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:17012: bde gshegs snying po las gol nas bdag gi lus
NK091(ke)001:17013: kyi phung po'i dug shing la dug gsum chags pa'o
NK091(ke)001:17014: // ma ro dur khang dang bcas pa kun gzhi la /
NK091(ke)001:17015: bu ro mchan du bzhag pa nyon yid de /
NK091(ke)001:17016: kun gzhi la bdag tu bzung ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:17017: de nas srin po kun gyis ma'i ro khang brtsigsa te /
NK091(ke)001:17018: ro khyogs la blangs te der bcug nas bu yang ma'i ro mchan du bzhag go //
NK091(ke)001:17019: dwa bu des ma'i ro la 'jus nas 'tsho ba'i
NK091(ke)001:17020: tshul nu ma la 'jibsa nas chu ser drangs te
NK091(ke)001:17021: zhags bdun gyi 'tsho ba byas so //
NK091(ke)001:17022: de nasa khrag tu gzhibas pas zhag bdun gyi 'tsho bas 'tsho'o //
NK091(ke)001:17023: de nas nu ma gnyis zos pas zhag bcu'i 'tsho bas 'tsho'o //
NK091(ke)001:17024: de nas ma'i nang khrol zad par zos pas 'tsho ba'i bya bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:17025: de nas sha zad para zos pasa zla ba bdun gyi 'tsho ba'i bya ba byas so //
NK091(ke)001:17026: dee nas gzhon nu de rtas par gyur nas /
NK091(ke)001:17027: dur khrod kyi ro rnams kyisa 'tsho ba'i bya ba byas so //
NK091(ke)001:17028: spyir sngon gyi las phal cher zad kyang lhag ma yod la /
NK091(ke)001:17029: sngon lha sgom zhing sngags bzlas te spyod pa rlabs
NK091(ke)001:17030: che ba brten stobs kyis 'dir nus pa che bar
NK091(ke)001:17031: gyur te / de nas shin tu brtas para gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:17032: ro rnams zas su za zhing /
NK091(ke)001:17035: dur khrod kyi ma mo dang /
NK091(ke)001:17038: mi dang mi ma lags pa'i ma yam gyi tshogs mang po yang /
NK091(ke)001:17039: mi ro rnams kyi sha rjena zos pa'i rang bzhin gyi mthus dbang du 'dus te /
NK091(ke)001:17040: myong ba rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu gzhan la gnod pas /
NK091(ke)001:17041: dur khrod kyi gdug pa can kun gyi bdag pora gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:17042: gzhan gyi gzi byin 'phrog pa'i nus pa can mi
NK091(ke)001:17043: gang dang gang dag gson pora za zhing mdangs 'phrog
NK091(ke)001:17044: par byed pa / shin tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs can ma rungsa par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:17045: ma'i sha rjena zos pas na /
NK091(ke)001:17046: ma zan ma tang ka zhes /
NK091(ke)001:17047: mi gang dag gisa ru tra'i ming du 'bod de yongs su grags so //
NK091(ke)001:17052: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17053: las kyi spyod tshul dang mthu'i khyad par sngon drag
NK091(ke)001:17054: sngags bzlas pa'i rgyu mthun gyi yi dwags chen po
NK091(ke)001:17055: de'i kha rlangs las na tsha ba'i nad byung bas
NK091(ke)001:17056: gang la phog pa nad kyi 'byung bas khyab ste
NK091(ke)001:17057: / 'gro ba gang lus can rnams zug rngu drag pos gzir ba /
NK091(ke)001:17058: sna nas ni grang ba'i nad dbyung bas gang la
NK091(ke)001:17059: phog par de'i 'byung bas khyab ste kun tu gdung
NK091(ke)001:17060: bar byed do // mig 'bri tshugs su gtad na
NK091(ke)001:17061: mig bug gis phog pasa nad du song nas 'chi
NK091(ke)001:17062: bar byed do // bar nges pa / gang la
NK091(ke)001:17063: dmigs te drag po'i sngags zer bzlas par byas pas
NK091(ke)001:17064: bar byed do // bar nges pa / / thamsa
NK091(ke)001:17065: cad rang dbang med par dbang du 'dus para gyur
NK091(ke)001:17066: bar byed do // bar nges pa / / pa
NK091(ke)001:17067: / lus chen po la mdog thal ka sngo skyar
NK091(ke)001:17068: bar byed do // bar nges pa / / pa
NK091(ke)001:17069: / 'dug pa / khrag dang zhag gisa thig les
NK091(ke)001:17070: bar byed do // bar nges pa / / pa
NK091(ke)001:17071: / 'dug pa / brgyan pa / thod pa'i phreng
NK091(ke)001:17072: ba se ral du thogsa pa /
NK091(ke)001:17073: dmar po khrag gisa bskus pa'i pagas pa bgos pa /
NK091(ke)001:17074: thod pa ma drangs par bcag pa'i 'phro can thod skyogs khrag gisa bkang ba rtag par 'thung ba /
NK091(ke)001:17075: skra ral pa kham nag bungs che bar 'ban cing mang la 'dzing bar gnyigs pa /
NK091(ke)001:17076: khrag dang dbang po lnga bsres pa dang klad pa
NK091(ke)001:17077: dang tshil dang rkang ste 'bru mar thod rus zas
NK091(ke)001:17078: su za ba / thal ba dang mi tshil nang
NK091(ke)001:17079: du dri chen blugs pa sro tsa ana 'dza' nas
NK091(ke)001:17080: su za ba / lus brgyan pa / la lar sbrul dang ba su ta yang gsungs /
NK091(ke)001:17081: bya'i gshog pa lus las byung bas nama mkha' la bya bzhin bya ba byed pa /
NK091(ke)001:17082: gcer bu pa thags med thogs pa med pas chu la nya bzhin bya ba byed pa /
NK091(ke)001:17083: gang gisa mthong ba mig rtsa rig rig sngangs zhing brgyal bar byed ba /
NK091(ke)001:17084: lus phag gi spu can rtsub la yan lag sbrul du byung zhing sbrul gyisa brgyan pa /
NK091(ke)001:17085: sen mo kang ka'i mchu sder du byung bas gang
NK091(ke)001:17086: zin pa'i lusa can sha rus myogs par byed pa
NK091(ke)001:17087: / sngon skye ba snga ma rnams la thar pa'i
NK091(ke)001:17088: dus kyi sgrol ba sogs gomsa pa'i mthus lus can
NK091(ke)001:17089: tha dad gsad par dmigs pa /
NK091(ke)001:17090: gang mthong bas thar pa'i dus sbyor ba la sogs pas mo'i dbang po sdud par chags pa /
NK091(ke)001:17091: lus can mtha' dag hag sngangs te zil gyis mnan nas 'dar yed yed 'jog pa /
NK091(ke)001:17094: gnod sbyin mthu can rnams kyis phyag byas te gtso bor mthong ba /
NK091(ke)001:17096: gdug pa can mtha' dag mangga pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:17102: dang por khro bor bsgom pa shes rab kyis ma zin pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:17103: bka' bsgo log pa'i rgyu dngos su snang ba'i phyir te /
NK091(ke)001:17104: 'jig rten gyi bdag po dbang can gdul dka' bar
NK091(ke)001:17105: byung ste khams gsum kun la dbang bsgyur ba'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:17107: nang ltar na nyon yid kyis kun gzhi la bdag
NK091(ke)001:17108: tu bzung bas zag pa rgyas te nyon mongs dug
NK091(ke)001:17109: lnga stobs 'phel bas reg pa la sogs pa sems
NK091(ke)001:17110: las byung ba kun kyang de dang mtshungs par ldan
NK091(ke)001:17112: sangsa rgyas kun gyi dgongs la 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:17113: gang thar pa nag po nas ru tra'i bar yongs
NK091(ke)001:17114: su ma dag pa'i skye brgyud bstan pa'i le'u ste
NK091(ke)001:17115: nyi shu pa rnam par bshad pa'o ////bzhi pa sngags
NK091(ke)001:17116: 'byung ba'i rgyur ji ltar 'gyur ba la gnyis te
NK091(ke)001:17117: / 'khor dang spyod yul log par bsgyur bas sngags 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur pa /
NK091(ke)001:17118: srid gsum dbang du bsdu lugs kyis sngags 'byung ba'i rgyur bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17120: nga rgyal gyi tshig sgrog pa /
NK091(ke)001:17121: ji ltar log par bsgyur ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:17126: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17128: der skyes pa'i ngo bo dang rang skal gyi las kyi nus mthu gang zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:17129: de nas yang ngo bo srin por gyur pa'i yi dwags kyi sde dpon drag po de yis /
NK091(ke)001:17130: nga rgyal can gyi rang gi mthu yi che ba rnyed pas gtum skad 'byin te /
NK091(ke)001:17131: e ma'o thams cad kyi dbang phyug chen po ni bdag yin na /
NK091(ke)001:17132: bdag las gzhan pa'i dbang phyug dang /
NK091(ke)001:17133: mnga' 'bangs kyi phru ma yod na de yang bdag gir 'gyur te dbang du sdud na /
NK091(ke)001:17134: bdag ni 'gran gyi zla med che btsan gcig pur
NK091(ke)001:17135: byung ngo zhes nga rgyal gyi gdangs ngar sgrogs so
NK091(ke)001:17137: ru tra ni nang gi mu stegs te /
NK091(ke)001:17138: de'i bstan pa log pa la khams gsum bkod la'o //
NK091(ke)001:17146: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17147: de'i las dang nus mthu log lta can du gyur pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:17148: ru tra 'jig rten du byung ba de'i tshe 'gro ba rnams kyi tshul 'di ltar byung ste /
NK091(ke)001:17149: ru tras bslad pas shes blo thams cad rmugs shing
NK091(ke)001:17150: bdud kyis byin gyis brlabs pas rtags su 'gro ba'i
NK091(ke)001:17151: spyod pa dang blo thams cad kyang log par lta
NK091(ke)001:17153: des dbang byas pas ltung ba'i 'bras bu dang bcas par gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:17154: skye ba snga phyi dang las rgyu 'bras kyi chos
NK091(ke)001:17155: kyis shin tu stong par lta bas byang chub kyi
NK091(ke)001:17156: bsam pa rgyun chad pa can du gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:17157: mtha' zad pa stong pa nyi tshe bar gol ba sha stag go //
NK091(ke)001:17158: gang zag gi bdag tu zhen para gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:17159: ther zug pa rtag lta la gol ba sha stag go //
NK091(ke)001:17160: yang dag pa'i bsam pa dang tshogs drug 'gog para
NK091(ke)001:17161: 'jug para gyur te tshogs drug gi shes rgyun 'gagsa
NK091(ke)001:17162: shing don las 'das te mun par zhugs pa sha
NK091(ke)001:17163: stag go // zhe sdang gis sems gdug cing lus gtum par gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:17164: 'o dod 'bod pa dmyal bar ltung ba sha stag go //
NK091(ke)001:17165: mchog gsum med ces log par lta bar gyur te
NK091(ke)001:17166: 'bras bu mnar med par lhung ba sha stag go
NK091(ke)001:17167: // ser sna'i dbang gis 'dod pa la brkam zhing 'jungs par gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:17168: gshin rje'i 'jig rten du ltung ba sha stag go //
NK091(ke)001:17169: le lo'i dbang gis shin tu g.yenga ba chen por gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:17170: mi khom pa'i ris brgyad kyi gnas su ltung ba sha stag go //
NK091(ke)001:17171: shin tu gti mug gi rmongs par gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:17172: byol song gi gnas su ltung ba sha stag go //
NK091(ke)001:17173: 'khrig pa la shin tu chags pas myos par gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:17174: mngal gyi khams su 'gro ba sha stag go //
NK091(ke)001:17175: de ltar log par lta ba rnams kyis byang chub
NK091(ke)001:17176: kyi shing skams pas sems kyi rtsa ba tshig pa
NK091(ke)001:17177: sha stag go // lang ka'i bdag po de yang
NK091(ke)001:17178: ru tra rjes 'brang dang bcas pa 'di ltar log
NK091(ke)001:17180: da ltar yang grags par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:17182: stong pa rgyun chad du bsgyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:17183: bdag tu zhen par bsgyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:17185: gdug cing gtum par bsgyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:17186: log par lta bar bsgyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:17188: shin tu g.yengs par bsgyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:17189: gti mug rmongs par bsgyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:17190: chags pas myos par bsgyur ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:17195: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17196: gol ba'i dus bskal pa grangs med mang po 'das
NK091(ke)001:17197: pa'i dus na sngon du byung ba'i bskal pa mngon
NK091(ke)001:17199: zhing khams kun dga' zhes bya ba la /
NK091(ke)001:17200: sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa'i bstan pa la thar pa nag po zhes bya bar byung ba des /
NK091(ke)001:17201: gol ba'i gzhi rigs kyi bdag po chen po ngo
NK091(ke)001:17202: bo mi 'gyur ba'i bka' gsang rang byung 'dus ma
NK091(ke)001:17203: byas pa'i bdag nyid zag pa med pa'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:17204: chen po ni sangs rgyas kun gyi ngo bo nyid
NK091(ke)001:17205: de / de las sprul pa rgyun du 'byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:17206: longs spyod chen por bar ma chad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:17207: chos kyi sku la skye 'gag med pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:17209: bde ba chen po rtag tu rtag /ces dang /
NK091(ke)001:17210: bde ba chen po dag la rtag bzhugs pa //
NK091(ke)001:17211: zhes gsungs pa ltar chos nyid 'pho 'gyur dang bral
NK091(ke)001:17212: bas rtag pa dam pa yi gnas lugs ji bzhin
NK091(ke)001:17213: pa ma bcos ma bslad par ston pa'i de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:17214: gshegs pas bstan pa'i gsung rab gsang sngags theg pa
NK091(ke)001:17215: chen po ji lta ba'i don mgo ba las gol
NK091(ke)001:17217: 'gro ba'i sde dpon srin po'i tshul du ma tram ka dregs pa chen por sngon byung ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:17218: spyir 'khor ba thog ma dang tha ma med par 'byung bas na /
NK091(ke)001:17219: skabs kyi cha gcig tu brtsi na gsang ba'i theg
NK091(ke)001:17220: pa ma byung gi gong du bskal pa 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:17222: 'on kyang le'u rtsa bzhi pa las /
NK091(ke)001:17223: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ltar //
NK091(ke)001:17224: da lta dus 'di nyid du byung //
NK091(ke)001:17225: zhes 'byung bas 'di ni sngon gyi lo rgyus brjod pa'i dbang du'o //
NK091(ke)001:17226: de'i rtsal gyis log par drangs te ru tra byung
NK091(ke)001:17227: ba de yi tshe 'gro ba sems can thams cad
NK091(ke)001:17228: ni blo dregs pas brlabs nas tshe snga phyi dang
NK091(ke)001:17229: las dang 'bras bus shin tu stong pa nyi tshe
NK091(ke)001:17230: ba chad pa'i lta ba nyid la brtson te log
NK091(ke)001:17231: par gnas so // 'di ni zhing khams mngon dag'i
NK091(ke)001:17232: dus thar pas gdul bya rnams de ltar btsud pa
NK091(ke)001:17233: par gnas so // dang / ru tra'i dus su
NK091(ke)001:17234: sems can rnams de ltar gyur pa gnyis ka la
NK091(ke)001:17235: go bar bya ste 'og ma rnams la'ang 'agre'o //
NK091(ke)001:17236: de'i nyes pa de ltar nyi tshe'i stong pa chad pa nyid du mu bcad pas /
NK091(ke)001:17237: lta ngan gyi rgyu des 'bras bu rigs chad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:17238: khamsa chen rdo rje dmyal ba nyid du skye bar
NK091(ke)001:17239: gyur to // gal te gnas ngan de nas slar
NK091(ke)001:17240: yang 'phos te mir skyes pa na'ang lta ngan de
NK091(ke)001:17241: la dga' ste long 'dogs pa yisa rgyu mthun las
NK091(ke)001:17242: grol ba dang thar pa'i lam ni chad par 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:17244: mdor na dang po gol ba'i dus dang /
NK091(ke)001:17246: gol ba dngos por byung ba'i dus dang /
NK091(ke)001:17247: de'i rtsal gyis dge ba'i myu gu chad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:17248: ril log pa'i lam du drangs pas gnas ngan du ltung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:17249: de las thar kyang lta ba ngan pa'i long 'dogs
NK091(ke)001:17250: pa dang drug po 'di 'chad pa rnams la'ang sbyar
NK091(ke)001:17255: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17256: de'ang chos drug po kun la sbyar te gol ba'i
NK091(ke)001:17257: dus 'das pa'i dus na sngon du byung ba bskal
NK091(ke)001:17259: thar pa nag po zhes bya ba /
NK091(ke)001:17260: gol ba'i gzhi rig pa bdag nyid chen po kun
NK091(ke)001:17261: bral nyag gcig ci ma spang ba ngo bo mi
NK091(ke)001:17262: 'gyur bas rtag pa 'dus ma byas pa yi rang
NK091(ke)001:17263: bzhin gsang ba dam pa nyid ston pa'i de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:17264: gshegs pa'i gsung rab gsang chen nang gi rgyud kyi
NK091(ke)001:17265: don zab mo ma go ba las gol ba'i dngos
NK091(ke)001:17266: po 'gro ba'i sde dpon srin po'i tshul du sngon
NK091(ke)001:17267: ru tra nyid du byung ba /
NK091(ke)001:17268: de'i tshe na sems can thams cad kyang log pa'i
NK091(ke)001:17269: rtsal gyi bsgyur ba ni lhan skyes kyi lcags sgrog
NK091(ke)001:17270: la kun btags kyi gzer btab nas shin tu gang
NK091(ke)001:17271: zag la bdag tu lta zhing sgro 'dogs pa la
NK091(ke)001:17272: brtson no // de'i nyes pas brtags pa ltar ther
NK091(ke)001:17273: zug rtag pa'i bdag chen gyis zhen pas rgyud 'ching
NK091(ke)001:17274: ste thams cad kyang 'khor ba'i dngos po gnas ngan
NK091(ke)001:17275: las thar pa med par rtag pa nyid du 'khor
NK091(ke)001:17276: brtson no // bar gyur to // de nas skye
NK091(ke)001:17277: ba 'phos kyang bdag rtog de nyid slar byung nas
NK091(ke)001:17278: long btags pas yang dag pa'i lam dam pa bdag
NK091(ke)001:17279: med kyi don ston pa dag la rmongs te lhag
NK091(ke)001:17280: mthong gi snang ba dang bral bar 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:17285: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17286: gol ba'i dus 'das pa'i dus na sngon gyi bskal
NK091(ke)001:17287: pa kun dga' la dge slong thar par byung ba
NK091(ke)001:17288: nyid / gol gzhi rang rig bdag nyid chen po
NK091(ke)001:17289: snang med rnam pa thams cad pa ngo bo 'dus
NK091(ke)001:17290: ma byas pas rtag pa dam pa yi rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:17291: gsang ba chen po nyid gsal bar ston pa'i de
NK091(ke)001:17292: bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab gsang sngags nang gi rgyud
NK091(ke)001:17293: kyi don mchog gsang ba ji bzhin du ma go
NK091(ke)001:17294: ba las gol ba'i dngos po 'gro ba'i dbang phyug
NK091(ke)001:17295: srin po'i tshul du ru trar smin te sngon gyi
NK091(ke)001:17297: de'i tshe log pa'i rtsal rgyas pas sems can thams
NK091(ke)001:17298: cad ni byang chub kyi bsam pa dang bral te
NK091(ke)001:17299: tshogs drug shin tu 'gog pa'i 'du shes med pa
NK091(ke)001:17301: de ltar shina tu 'gog pa'i sbyor ba la goms
NK091(ke)001:17302: pa yis 'bras bu tshogs drug 'gag pa'i gnas ngan
NK091(ke)001:17303: du 'khyams shing byang chub mchog gi lam 'bras kyi
NK091(ke)001:17304: don las yongs su 'das par 'gyur zhing slar yang
NK091(ke)001:17305: lta ba de nyid la dga' ste long 'dogs pas
NK091(ke)001:17311: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17312: 'das pa'i dus na sngon gyi bskal pa kun dga' la byung ba'i thar pa nag po des /
NK091(ke)001:17313: rang rig pa bdag nyid chen po phyogs med ji
NK091(ke)001:17314: bzhin pa'i gnas lugs ngo bo 'pho 'gyur bral bas
NK091(ke)001:17315: rtag pa dam pa yi bka' gsang de bzhin gshegs
NK091(ke)001:17316: pa'i gsung rab nang rgyud rin po che'i nges pa
NK091(ke)001:17317: las gol te 'gro ba'i sde dpon dregs pa chen
