NK091(ke)001:17318: po'i tshul du sngon tshe ma tram kar byung ba
NK091(ke)001:17319: de yi tshe na sems can thams cad ni /
NK091(ke)001:17320: shin tu ma rungs pa lus khro zhing ngag gtum la sems gdug par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:17321: de ltar shin tu khro gtuma gdug pa la goms
NK091(ke)001:17322: pa'i las de yisa ru tra'i skye rgyud lta bu
NK091(ke)001:17323: ngan song gsum du brgyud cing lhag par yang dmyal
NK091(ke)001:17324: ba'i gnas su 'o dod 'bod par ltung bar 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:17325: ro // brgya lam na de nas 'phos te mir
NK091(ke)001:17326: skyes pa'i semsa can des kyang sngon gyi bag chags
NK091(ke)001:17327: ngan pa'i las kyisa 'tshams sbyar bas ru tra lta
NK091(ke)001:17328: bu shin tu gdug pa chen por 'gyur la /
NK091(ke)001:17329: blo yang nag phyogs bdud rigs kyis byin gyis brlabs
NK091(ke)001:17330: nas dug nad dang rims dang phra men ma sogs
NK091(ke)001:17331: gzhan la gnod pa'i zug rngu sna tshogs kyi zer
NK091(ke)001:17332: mda' 'phro zhing kun la bdud dang log 'dren gyi
NK091(ke)001:17333: tshul du rnam par 'tshe ste shin tu gtum rngam
NK091(ke)001:17334: ma rungs par gyur pas sa bla man chad kyi
NK091(ke)001:17335: 'jig rten gsum dag 'jig par byed cing /
NK091(ke)001:17336: dam ldan la sdang zhing dam la mi gnas par byed pas dam tshig dag la za ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:17337: dge ba'i lam gyi dam pa'i chu bo rka nas bzlog ste /
NK091(ke)001:17338: lha mi'i 'jig rten 'pho zhing nyams par byed do //
NK091(ke)001:17339: yang na ru tra lta bu thams cad bsad cing sdud par sems pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17340: 'di nyid ru tra yin na sems can thams cad ces pa dang 'gal la /
NK091(ke)001:17341: sems can yin na lha mi'i 'jig rten 'pho bar
NK091(ke)001:17342: byed pa dang 'gal lo zhes bkod kyang sems can
NK091(ke)001:17343: gyi ris la ru tra lta bu gzhan yang 'byung
NK091(ke)001:17344: bar nges pas shin tu 'thad par mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:17349: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17350: 'das pa'i dus na sngon gyi bskal pa kun dga' la byung ba dge slong thar pas /
NK091(ke)001:17351: rig pa bdag nyid chen po kun mnyam yangs pa
NK091(ke)001:17352: ngo bo 'gyur med rtag pa dam pa yi bka'
NK091(ke)001:17353: gsang de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab nang rgyud rin
NK091(ke)001:17354: po che'i nges pa las gol te 'gro ba'i che
NK091(ke)001:17355: btsan srin po'i tshul du sngon tshe byung nas ru
NK091(ke)001:17356: trar smin pa de yi tshe na sems can thams
NK091(ke)001:17357: cad ni / spyir na kun log 'ba' zhig la
NK091(ke)001:17358: 'dir khyad par du brjod de ma log pa'i bstan
NK091(ke)001:17359: pa la zhugs pa'ang log par lta ba la gnas
NK091(ke)001:17360: cad ni / par gyur to // de ltar lta
NK091(ke)001:17361: ba shin tu log pa la goms pa yis mnar
NK091(ke)001:17362: meda pa'i sems can dmyal ba chen pora ltung ngo
NK091(ke)001:17363: cad ni / par gyur to // // de nas
NK091(ke)001:17364: gal te brgya lam na slar byung ste mir skyes
NK091(ke)001:17365: cad ni / par gyur to // // na yang
NK091(ke)001:17366: / thar pa byang chub dam pa'i lam gyi snang
NK091(ke)001:17372: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17373: 'das pa'i dus na sngon gyi zhing khams mngon dga' la byung ba thar pa nag pos /
NK091(ke)001:17374: rang rig bdag nyid chen po rang bzhin kun tu
NK091(ke)001:17375: snang ba'i dbyings ngo bo 'gyur med rtag chen 'dus
NK091(ke)001:17376: ma byas pa yi bka' gsang de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:17377: gsung rab nang rgyud rin po che'i nges pa las
NK091(ke)001:17378: gol te 'gro ba'i dbang phyug srin po'i tshul du
NK091(ke)001:17379: sngon tshe ru trar byung ba de yi tshe na
NK091(ke)001:17380: sems can thams cad ni 'dod pa la shin tu
NK091(ke)001:17381: gdung ba'i ser snas rang gi yo byad la brkams
NK091(ke)001:17382: shing gzhan nor la 'jungs par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:17383: de ltar shin tu 'dod pa gdungsa nas rang bzhin gyi yo byad la 'jungs shing brkamsa pa yis /
NK091(ke)001:17384: yi dwags kyi 'jig rten gshin rje'ii khams su ltung ngo //
NK091(ke)001:17385: de nasa de nyid slar byung bas mi ru gyur
NK091(ke)001:17386: kyang shin tu skem pa phongs shing dbul por 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:17387: zhing / bkres dang skom pas shin tu gdung ba
NK091(ke)001:17388: yis zas nor gyi phyir phan tshun gsod cing 'joms
NK091(ke)001:17389: par 'gyur bas thar pa dang bral lo //
NK091(ke)001:17394: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17395: 'das pa'i dus na sngon gyi zhing khams mngon dga' la byung ba dge slong thar pas /
NK091(ke)001:17396: rig pa bdag nyid chen po brtsal med lhun gyis
NK091(ke)001:17397: grub pas rtag chen 'pho 'gyur bral ba yi bka'
NK091(ke)001:17398: gsang de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab nang rgyud rin
NK091(ke)001:17399: po che'i nges pa las gol te 'gro ba'i dregs
NK091(ke)001:17400: pa srin po'i tshul du sngon chad ru trar byung
NK091(ke)001:17401: ba de yi tshe na sems can thams cad ni
NK091(ke)001:17402: / rgyu dman pa la sbyor ba dang snyoms las
NK091(ke)001:17403: 'dzin pa gnyis kyis shin tu le losa g.yengs par
NK091(ke)001:17404: / gyur to // de ltar shin tu g.yeng ba'i
NK091(ke)001:17405: le lo yis rnam smin mi khomsa pa'i gnas brgyad
NK091(ke)001:17406: rnams su ltung bar gyur la /
NK091(ke)001:17407: de nas de nyid las thon nas slar byung bas
NK091(ke)001:17408: mi ru skyes kyang bskal pa grangs med pa gsum
NK091(ke)001:17409: gyis yang dag pa'i lam las bskal te 'gyang bar
NK091(ke)001:17410: 'gyur ro // yang na yul dus rang bzhin gsum
NK091(ke)001:17411: gyis gsang ba'i don las bskal pa la'ang gsungs so
NK091(ke)001:17416: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17417: 'das pa'i dus na sngon gyi zhing khams mngon dga' la byung ba dge slong thar pas /
NK091(ke)001:17418: rang rig bdag nyid chen po mnyam nyid bsal bzhag
NK091(ke)001:17419: med pa'i rang byung rtag pa'i chos nyid 'dus ma
NK091(ke)001:17420: byas pa yi bka' gsang de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung
NK091(ke)001:17421: rab nang rgyud rin po che'i nges pa las gol
NK091(ke)001:17422: te 'gro ba'i sde dpon drag po'i tshul du sngon
NK091(ke)001:17423: tshe ma zan ma tang kar byung ba de yi
NK091(ke)001:17424: tshe na sems can thams cad ni lam legs nyes
NK091(ke)001:17425: 'bras bu dang bcas pa la shin tu gti mug
NK091(ke)001:17427: de ltar shin tu gti mug dang rmongs pa de yis /
NK091(ke)001:17428: gti mug mun pa'i skye mched byol song nyid du lhung bar gyur la /
NK091(ke)001:17429: de nasa de nyid slar byung bas mtho ris su skye yang /
NK091(ke)001:17430: dkon mchog gsum gyi mthong snang dang yang dag pa'i lam yang chad par 'gyur ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:17434: zhes thams cad tu grags so //
NK091(ke)001:17435: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17436: chos drug gi gol ba'i skabs 'adsa pa'i dus na
NK091(ke)001:17437: sngon gyi bskal pa kun dga' zhes bya bar byung
NK091(ke)001:17438: ba dge slong thar par gyur pa'i dus su /
NK091(ke)001:17439: gol ba'i gzhi rig pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK091(ke)001:17440: bdag nyid chen po bde chen don gyi 'od gsal
NK091(ke)001:17441: zag med 'dus ma byas pas ngo bo mi 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:17442: pa'i rtag pa dam pa yi bka' gsang rmad du
NK091(ke)001:17443: byung ba de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab nang rgyud
NK091(ke)001:17444: rin po che'i nges don gsang ba zab mo ji
NK091(ke)001:17445: lta ba bzhin ma go ba las /
NK091(ke)001:17446: gol ba'i dngos po 'gro ba'i rje dpon yi dwags
NK091(ke)001:17447: srin po chen po'i tshul du ru trar smin te
NK091(ke)001:17448: sngon gyi dus su byung ba na /
NK091(ke)001:17449: gol ba'i rtsal gyis de tshe 'byung ba'i semsa can thams cad ni /
NK091(ke)001:17450: gnyis kyis gnyis sprod pa'i 'khrig pa la shin tu chags pas myos para gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:17451: de ltar gol ba'i rtsal gyi nyes pa shin tu
NK091(ke)001:17452: chags pas myos pa yis rnam par smin pa mngal
NK091(ke)001:17453: gyi grong khyer nyid du ltung bar gyur la /
NK091(ke)001:17454: log par gol ba'i rgyu mthun long 'dogs pa de
NK091(ke)001:17455: nas de nyid las slar byung bas rjes su yang
NK091(ke)001:17456: sngar goms pa'i byed pas 'dod pa'i me yis kun
NK091(ke)001:17457: tu gdung bar 'gyur bas grol ba'i skabs dang bral
NK091(ke)001:17458: ba'o // zhes zhing khams thams cad kun tu de ltar gyur par yongs su grags so //
NK091(ke)001:17459: bsdus pa'i skabs su bstan pa'i sems kyi rtsa ba tshig ces pa /
NK091(ke)001:17460: rgyas pa'i skabs su spyi la khyab pas logs su
NK091(ke)001:17461: smras na tha dad du 'gyur bas ma smras so
NK091(ke)001:17462: // mdor na ru tra ni rang bzhin dang bcas pa'i ltung ba gnyis kar gyur la /
NK091(ke)001:17463: 'gro ba rnams ni rang bzhin gyi ltung bar gyur pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17465: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:17466: ru tra'i dus kyi lo rgyus bstan pas 'das pa
NK091(ke)001:17467: sngon byung ba'i le'u zhes bya ste nyi shu rtsa
NK091(ke)001:17468: gcig pa rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17469: spyir rang rgyud pa'i gol sa dgag cing bdud bzhi
NK091(ke)001:17470: 'dul ba'i ched du dgos dgongs kyis rgyal ba nyid
NK091(ke)001:17472: le'u 'dis rgyas bshad kyi gnas las de ltar yang
NK091(ke)001:17473: 'chad du rung ngo ////gnyis pa srid pa gsum dbang
NK091(ke)001:17474: du bsdu lugs kyis sngags 'byung ba'i rgyur bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:17475: la lnga ste / srin po dbang du bsdus pas sngags 'byung ba'i rgyur bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:17476: lha yi tshogs dbang du bsdus pas sngags 'byung ba'i rgyur bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:17477: lha mi g.yo 'gul thams cad dbang du bsdus pas sngags 'byung ba'i rgyur bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:17478: nyan thos kyi mchog dang rta mgrin gyis ma thul bar bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:17479: dgos dgongs kyi thar pa dpon g.yog smin pa'i dus mtshungs par bstan pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17481: srin po'i gnas su bab pa /
NK091(ke)001:17482: srin pos gzhom par sad pas slar zil gyis gnon pa /
NK091(ke)001:17483: srin po'i gtso bos 'khor la 'dun par gyis shig par bsgos pas dbang du byas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17488: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17490: de nas gsang ba pa'i bdag posa smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:17492: de ltar yi dwags drag po des /
NK091(ke)001:17493: mi yi 'jig rten gang ji snyed pa dbang du
NK091(ke)001:17494: gyur pa'i che ba la nga rgyal gyis spyom zhing
NK091(ke)001:17497: 'jig rten na dbang phyug bdag las su dag che /
NK091(ke)001:17498: su dag yod ces rang nyid la ngam pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:17499: che ba gzhan 'jig rten na su yod pa nyan
NK091(ke)001:17500: cing phrag dog gang che ba dbang du bsdus la
NK091(ke)001:17501: bdag gir bya'o snyam pas skabs su 'di nyid 'dzam
NK091(ke)001:17502: gling la gling phran sum brgya yod zer ba'i gcig
NK091(ke)001:17503: yin gsung ste / lang ka yul gyi grong rdal mtsho ko ka thang dmar gyi gling /
NK091(ke)001:17504: byan lag gnam du mchongsa pa'i dbyibs kyi ri bo
NK091(ke)001:17505: ma la ya rtsa ba gser rtse mo gnam lcags
NK091(ke)001:17506: 'phangs su dpag tshad brgyad cu yod pa'i rtse zhes
NK091(ke)001:17507: bya ba nas / lang ka'i mnga' bdag srin po'i rgyal po blo gros thabs ldan zhes bya ba /
NK091(ke)001:17508: sangs rgyas sprul sku thub pa'i dbang po zhes bya ba'i slob mar gyur pa /
NK091(ke)001:17509: mthu dang rtsal rmad du byung zhing ngo mtshar du che ba /
NK091(ke)001:17510: blo gros yongs su chub pa /
NK091(ke)001:17511: spyir sa brgyad pa yan chad yin la da res kyi 'di ni 'jam dpal yin gsung /
NK091(ke)001:17512: dge ba bcu'i thabas rgya mtsho'i d+r+wa ba sprin dpung
NK091(ke)001:17513: lta bu 'byung ba zhig 'jig rten na che'o zhes
NK091(ke)001:17514: grags pa las / yi dwags bya'i gshog pa can
NK091(ke)001:17515: des zhe sdang dang nga rgyal gyis rab tu 'khrugs
NK091(ke)001:17516: shing khams nas nyon mongs pa drag po'i ru tra'i
NK091(ke)001:17517: me dpung du 'bar ba dang dngos su'ang lus la
NK091(ke)001:17518: grags pa las / me 'bar nas / rang gi rdzu 'phrul dang 'phur rtsal gyis /
NK091(ke)001:17519: byan lag mchongsa pa'i rii'i rtse mo la babs nas /
NK091(ke)001:17520: nga rgyal gyi gtum skad du /
NK091(ke)001:17521: ru tra ma tra ma ra tra zhesa bsgrags pas
NK091(ke)001:17522: srin po'i ljongs lang ka yul gyi grong rdal shig
NK091(ke)001:17523: shig /rab tu shig shig /yama yoma du gyur pas
NK091(ke)001:17524: / lang ka'i srin po kun dang srin mo kun kyang skrag cing sngangs nas /
NK091(ke)001:17525: e ma'o 'di ni ji lta ba zhig ces mig rtsa rig rig sngangs yed yed gnas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:17526: gnod sbyin bya'i gshog pa gtum rngam 'khrugs pa zhig
NK091(ke)001:17527: srin po bdag cag gi 'khra sa na gnas pa
NK091(ke)001:17528: la las mthong zhing ma mthong bas kyang sgra sgrogs
NK091(ke)001:17529: pa thos pa skrag cing 'jigs par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:17534: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17535: de nas lang ka'i mnga' bdag chen po la sogs pa srin poo'i tshogs rnams kyis /
NK091(ke)001:17536: dmag gi tshogs kyis bsdu ba byas te gzhom par sad cing 'bad pa las /
NK091(ke)001:17537: yang srin po bya'i gshog pa can des /
NK091(ke)001:17538: srin poo'i tshogs bag 'khumsa pa zhes bya ba'i rdzu
NK091(ke)001:17539: 'phrul gyi bya ba 'gying gar dang gtum po'i sngags
NK091(ke)001:17542: nga ni dbang phyug chen po ste /
NK091(ke)001:17543: rgyal chen rigsa bzhi nga yi g.yog /mi'am ci sogs lha srin sde brgyad nga yi bran /
NK091(ke)001:17544: tshig lo ma can gyi ngan sngags dang /
NK091(ke)001:17545: log sde'i gsang sngags sum brgya drug cu la sogs
NK091(ke)001:17546: pa gasnga ba mchog gi bdag po chen po yin
NK091(ke)001:17547: pas su zhig nga la 'gran zla yod /
NK091(ke)001:17548: ru tra ma tra ma ra tra /
NK091(ke)001:17549: zhes nga rgyal gyi gtum skad bsgrags pa las /
NK091(ke)001:17550: srin po thams cad zil gyis gnona cing bag 'khums nas /
NK091(ke)001:17551: la la ni 'di ni srin po'i khams rgyal bar byed pa zhig ste /
NK091(ke)001:17552: bdag cag gi gtso bo'i 'osa so //
NK091(ke)001:17554: la la ni 'di ni 'jig rten 'jig par byed pa zhig ste /
NK091(ke)001:17555: bdag cag gi gnyen por gyur pa zhig go zhes sgrogs /
NK091(ke)001:17556: la la dag 'di ni 'jig rten pa'i dbang phyug chen po zhig go //
NK091(ke)001:17558: la la dag 'di ni mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyi tshogs bdag zhig go //
NK091(ke)001:17564: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17565: srin po'i rgyal po lang ka'i mnga' bdag blo gros thabs ldan ni /
NK091(ke)001:17566: ru tra'i lo rgyus dang dgos pa gsum gyi phyir 'dun na legs par lung ston te /
NK091(ke)001:17567: 'di ni 'byung po'i bu gtogs 'dod can zhes bya ba yin te /
NK091(ke)001:17568: 'jig rten gsum sgrag pa de kho na nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes sam /
NK091(ke)001:17570: sangs rgyas ma gtogs pa thams cad brlag cing dbang du byed pa /
NK091(ke)001:17572: gdul bya khyad par can 'ad nyid gzhan gyis mi thula te /
NK091(ke)001:17573: 'di'i gnyen po sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams kyis mdzad de /
NK091(ke)001:17574: sprul pa gsang bdag rdo rje can gyis btul nas /
NK091(ke)001:17575: nges pa dam para bkod de /
NK091(ke)001:17576: yang dag par lung ston pa zhig pas /
NK091(ke)001:17577: 'di'i rgyus gsang sngags dam pa'i nges pa theg pa
NK091(ke)001:17578: chen po rmad du byung ba'i chos 'jig rten du
NK091(ke)001:17580: bdag cag kyang 'di'i g.yog tu byas na /
NK091(ke)001:17581: sangs rgyas rdo rje snying po'i zhal mthong zhing /
NK091(ke)001:17582: gsang sngags dam pa'i nges pa rnyed par 'gyur bas /
NK091(ke)001:17583: 'di la nges par 'dun pa 'dun zhig /ces bsgo nas /
NK091(ke)001:17584: srin po'i tshogs rnams yid rangsa te rang gi sde
NK091(ke)001:17585: dpon ci smra ba mi 'dor bar de ltar 'dun
NK091(ke)001:17586: pas na / srin po kun srin po bya'i gshog pa can de'i g.yog tu dong ste /
NK091(ke)001:17588: bdag cag kyang dbang phyug chen po kha na nyid ltara 'dun no //
NK091(ke)001:17591: de dag 'khor du 'dzina par byas so //
NK091(ke)001:17594: des tshogs lam yang dbang du byas pas /
NK091(ke)001:17595: tshogs lam gyi shes rab 'khor dang bcas pas de
NK091(ke)001:17596: las 'da' ma nus par rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK091(ke)001:17597: ye shes la dmigs kyang mos pa dang yid la
NK091(ke)001:17598: byed pa dang ngo tsha shes pa dang khrel yod
NK091(ke)001:17599: pa la sogs pa kun bdag 'dzin gyis 'khor du
NK091(ke)001:17600: song ba'o // gnyis pa gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:17601: gtso bo dbang du bsdus pa /
NK091(ke)001:17603: gtso 'khor gnyis ka dbang du bsdus pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17608: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17609: de nas yang srin po bya'i gshog pa can de la /
NK091(ke)001:17610: dus der srin po de'i deda dpon ma tang ka ru tra zhes bya bar grags pa de nyid /
NK091(ke)001:17611: nga rgyal gyi che ba spyom ste /
NK091(ke)001:17612: bdag las che ba ganga zhig yod /
NK091(ke)001:17614: ru tra ma tra ma ra tra /
NK091(ke)001:17616: lha yi deda dpon ma tang ka ru na zhes
NK091(ke)001:17617: bya ba mthu dang rdzu 'phrul thabs dang che ba
NK091(ke)001:17618: khyad par du byung ba de nyid 'phags so //
NK091(ke)001:17620: bdun ru tra nag po de shin tu khams 'khrugs nas /
NK091(ke)001:17621: nga rgyal gyi gtum skad bsgrags te rang gi rdzu
NK091(ke)001:17622: 'phrul dang 'phur rtsal gyis gzhan 'phrul dbang byed ma
NK091(ke)001:17623: tang ka ru na'i gnas su babs te yongs su
NK091(ke)001:17625: zhes pa bru sha'i skad de /
NK091(ke)001:17626: dbang du bya bar brtsams pa na /
NK091(ke)001:17627: ja zha mara zhes pa'ang bru sha'i skad de bod
NK091(ke)001:17628: skad du rnal mar 'gyur bas rnal mar soda pa
NK091(ke)001:17630: ru tras lha yi ded dpon dbang du bsdu bar
NK091(ke)001:17631: nyams sad pas rnal mar thub pa mi 'dra nas
NK091(ke)001:17632: / kho lus can yin pasa ru tra'i sna 'ung
NK091(ke)001:17633: nas byung ba'i dbugs dang kha rlangs kyi dbugs gnyis
NK091(ke)001:17634: tsha grang dang 'thabs thabs su byung ba'i ngada la
NK091(ke)001:17635: tsha grang gi dbugs ham pa'am gtor nas nad kyi
NK091(ke)001:17636: mtshon cha bzhi bzhir spros pas lha'i rgyal po kho
NK091(ke)001:17637: na de'i lus la khyab ste lus me dbal nag
NK091(ke)001:17638: po'i 'brum pas gang nas mi bzod pa'i zug rngus
NK091(ke)001:17639: / gdungs te / lha'i ded dpon kho na ngo
NK091(ke)001:17640: bo de 'ung thabs sam 'ur thabs su glo bur
NK091(ke)001:17641: du btsan thabs su basda do //
NK091(ke)001:17642: kho na de'i bam ro 'dzam bu'i gling du han zhes bor ba'ang bzhag pa lasa /
NK091(ke)001:17643: dge gnas kyi yul o rgyan /
NK091(ke)001:17645: bal po'i yul la sogs par mchod rten brgyad dngos
NK091(ke)001:17646: grub brgyad dang ldan par ma mo brgyad kyis srung
NK091(ke)001:17647: ba nyid du rnam par snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:17653: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17654: de nas ru tra'i gdug pa'i zug rngu me dang 'dra bar 'bar bas /
NK091(ke)001:17655: 'khor kun kyang ri rab kyi phyogs bzhi'i sde dpon
NK091(ke)001:17656: rgyal po chen po bzhi la skyabs su dong la
NK091(ke)001:17657: / de dag kyang spu zings bcas rab tu 'jigsa par /
NK091(ke)001:17658: lha'i dbang po brgya byin dag la skyabs su dong zhing /
NK091(ke)001:17659: de nas dbang pora bcas pa'i lha yang /
NK091(ke)001:17660: tshangs pa'i skyabs su nye bar dong la /
NK091(ke)001:17661: de nas tshangs pa lha dang dbang pora dbang po
NK091(ke)001:17662: bcas pa yang lha gtogs 'dod zhes khyab 'jug nag
NK091(ke)001:17663: po la ni skyabs su dong zhing /
NK091(ke)001:17664: tshangsa pa dang gtogs 'dod dang dbang por bcas pa yang /
NK091(ke)001:17665: lha ma h+aa de ba drag po'i skyabs su nye bar dong la /
NK091(ke)001:17666: tshangs pa dang gtogs 'dod dang dbang poo dang drag
NK091(ke)001:17667: po kun kyang shin tu skrag cing 'jigsa par gyur
NK091(ke)001:17668: te / gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje can la skyabs su dong ngo //
NK091(ke)001:17669: de bzhin du gang na skyabs yod par nye bar
NK091(ke)001:17670: brgyug kyang ma thar bar 'bras bu che ba man
NK091(ke)001:17671: chad 'jigs byed de yi bran du jena nas dbang
NK091(ke)001:17672: du bsdus so // zhes thams cad du grags par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:17678: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17679: 'ung zhes pa bru sha'i skad de bod skad du
NK091(ke)001:17680: byas zhes par 'gyur bas de ltar byas nas kho
NK091(ke)001:17681: na nyid bsad pa'i khyo mo chung ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:17682: bu 'khor rnams ni gnod sbyin bya'i gshog pa can
NK091(ke)001:17683: de'i 'khor du jen zhes pa'ang bru sha'i skad de
NK091(ke)001:17684: byas so // lha ma yin dang /
NK091(ke)001:17686: ro langs ril yang bdud de'i sar jena zhes 'dus so //
NK091(ke)001:17687: rgyal po bzhi yang ganga gi skyabs su brgyugs kyang
NK091(ke)001:17688: yongs su ma thar bar de'i bran du jena zhes
NK091(ke)001:17692: drag po la sogs pa kun kyang gang gi skyabs
NK091(ke)001:17693: su brgyugs kyang ma thar bar de'i bran du jena
NK091(ke)001:17694: zhes song ngo // de dag gi khyo mo ril yang phrogs nas /
NK091(ke)001:17695: la la ni khyo mo byas /
NK091(ke)001:17696: la la ni slas su byas /
NK091(ke)001:17697: la la ni byi mor byas /
NK091(ke)001:17698: la la ni mdza' mor byas /
NK091(ke)001:17699: la la ni bran mor byas /
NK091(ke)001:17700: la la ni pho nya dang mngag par byas /
NK091(ke)001:17701: lha mi yongs kyi dge ba dang thar pa bsgrub
NK091(ke)001:17702: pa'i srid brlag nas thams cad nag po bkrag med
NK091(ke)001:17704: de yang 'di ltar dus gsum mam yang na khams
NK091(ke)001:17705: gsum la grags shing grags te grags par gyur to
NK091(ke)001:17706: // kha dog dang las gnyis ka nag pas nag
NK091(ke)001:17707: po khyung gshog 'phur rtsal can la lus gtum zhing
NK091(ke)001:17708: ngag rngam la yid shin tu ma rung par gyur
NK091(ke)001:17709: pa lus kyi bzhin mi sdug pa'i gdong la mi
NK091(ke)001:17710: sdug pa'i gzugs sna tshogs dang mi snyan pa'i sgra
NK091(ke)001:17711: yi tsham ngam sgrogs pa can sha sna tshogs spungs
NK091(ke)001:17712: shing rus pa phyogs su spungsa nas 'bu dang rnag
NK091(ke)001:17713: dang khrag dang gashanga gci dang khu ba rnams la
NK091(ke)001:17714: longs spyod par byed cing rtag tu 'tsho bar gnas
NK091(ke)001:17715: // so // de ltar log pa'i sde dpon drag po des /
NK091(ke)001:17716: 'jig rten 'di na lha dang mi'ii dge ba'i srid
NK091(ke)001:17717: brlag nas lha yi ded dpon chen po ka ru
NK091(ke)001:17718: na zhes bya ba kho na ngo bo nyid bsad
NK091(ke)001:17719: cing bsgral nas 'khor ma lus pa yang rang gi
NK091(ke)001:17720: phru mar zhes pa bru sha'i skad de 'khor du
NK091(ke)001:17721: byas nas dbang du bsdus so //
NK091(ke)001:17722: nang ltar na bdag 'dzin des sbyor lam gyi dbang
NK091(ke)001:17723: po lnga dang stobs lnga yang dbang du byas te
NK091(ke)001:17724: tshogs lam las 'phags kyang drod rtse bzod mchog bzhi
NK091(ke)001:17725: po 'jig rten pa'i lam las ma 'das pas bdag
NK091(ke)001:17726: 'dzin bgas kyis bshams te chags sdang rags pa'i yul
NK091(ke)001:17727: las grol yang zag bcas kyi dge rtsa tshad med
NK091(ke)001:17728: bzhi / mi g.yo ba'i bsam gtan bzhi /
NK091(ke)001:17729: snyoms 'jug bzhi po thams cad bdag tu 'dzin pas dbang du byas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17735: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17736: yang 'ung zhes song nas bdud ru tra nag po
NK091(ke)001:17737: lta zhig gis lha mi g.yo 'gul thams cad dbang
NK091(ke)001:17738: du mdzad de / lang ka yul gyi grong rdal /
NK091(ke)001:17739: mtsho ko ka thang dmar byan lag mchongs kyi ri
NK091(ke)001:17740: bor bam ri thod pa mkhar zhes bya bar 'khras
NK091(ke)001:17741: te bdud kyi rgyal mtshan kha t+w+aam rtse gsum la
NK091(ke)001:17742: mi ro btags pa ni phugs su btsugs /
NK091(ke)001:17743: bdud kyi ru mtshon ni sgor phyar te /
NK091(ke)001:17744: rang gi 'khor ram phru mas yongs su bskor nas gnas la /
NK091(ke)001:17745: log pa'i sde dpon drag po rang gi rdzu 'phrul bskyed nas /
NK091(ke)001:17746: rdzu 'phrul gyis ri rab mdzub mo'i rtse la bzhag ste /
NK091(ke)001:17747: spyi bo la 'gying bag tu bskor nas /
NK091(ke)001:17748: nga rgyal gyi gtum skad sgrogs pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:17750: ru tra ma tra ma ra tra /
NK091(ke)001:17751: sa khams na bdag las su zhig che /
NK091(ke)001:17758: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17759: e ma' sngon dpal sh+aakya thub pa zhes bya bas /
NK091(ke)001:17760: 'chi bdag gi bdud btul ba'i tshe /
NK091(ke)001:17761: de'i bstan pa la rab tu byung ba'i mchog chen
NK091(ke)001:17762: po nyan thos rnams kyisa thams cad zhi ba lham
NK091(ke)001:17763: me ba'am zhi bar lhan pa'i smra bas smras te
NK091(ke)001:17764: / nga'i bka' nyon cig ces zer ba las kyang /
NK091(ke)001:17765: sngon bskal pa kun dag'i dus su bdag thar pa nag por gyur pas /
NK091(ke)001:17766: bu chung go zu phrag pa la khol la /
NK091(ke)001:17767: rang gi dka' thub la bde bar mnos shig /cesa byas nas /
NK091(ke)001:17768: ma nyan nas desa kyang bdag dbang du byed ma nus so //
NK091(ke)001:17769: zhes smras pa 'di ni ru tra'i kha pho yin
NK091(ke)001:17770: te sprul sku ris la sh+aakya thub pa zer ba
NK091(ke)001:17771: yin skad / des na thar pa nag po'i dus kyi lo rgyus brjod pa yin gsungs /
NK091(ke)001:17772: lar da ltar gyi dus su ston pa sh+aaka thub byon pas de nyid yin min dpyad na /
NK091(ke)001:17773: ru tra sprul pa pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:17774: byung tshul gyi skabs don las gzhal na 'chad pa'i sgo shin tu yangs par mngon yang /
NK091(ke)001:17775: dkyus 'dir rang rgyud pa ltar bshad pa'i dbang du na /
NK091(ke)001:17776: sngon thar pa'i dus kyi sprul sku la brjod pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:17777: la lar sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa chen po yin par yang gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:17778: yang na ru tra rang gi dus su byas kyang gzhung dang mthun no //
NK091(ke)001:17779: ston pa sh+aakya thub pa de'i drung na dpal rdo
NK091(ke)001:17780: rje snying po byang chub ngag gi dbang phyug spyan
NK091(ke)001:17781: ras gzigs kyi sprul pa lta zhig mi'i lus la
NK091(ke)001:17782: rta'i mgo can du sna tshogs kyi gzugs su sprul
NK091(ke)001:17783: nas dbang gi snying po h+r+aizhes sgrogs te dbang gi
NK091(ke)001:17784: rgyun du nyan na nyon cig /ces zer ba la
NK091(ke)001:17785: / slar ru tra kho na nyid kyis tha'i kha
NK091(ke)001:17786: brdabs pa zhes thal mo rdeb cing skan sgra gtogs
NK091(ke)001:17787: par byas nas mgrin bu khyod kyang bde bar mnosa
NK091(ke)001:17788: shig ces bsgo bas rta mgrin de yang thaga khos
NK091(ke)001:17789: zhes pa bru sha'i skad de /
NK091(ke)001:17790: bod skad du yid ches par 'gyur bas dbang gis mi thul bar yid ches te slar jen no //
NK091(ke)001:17791: zhes pa'ang bru sha'i skad de slar song ngo //
NK091(ke)001:17793: don la sngon rta mgrin h+r+ai'i sgra sgrogs shing dbang
NK091(ke)001:17794: gis 'dul du 'ong ba la nga yis khyod kyis
NK091(ke)001:17795: mi thul ba'i ngag smras pas rang gi gnas su
NK091(ke)001:17797: gnam rim pa bcu bzhi zhes pa lung gis nyi shu rtsa gcig gam nyer gnyis las /
NK091(ke)001:17798: 'jig rten pa'i sa dgu la gcig tu byas nas /
NK091(ke)001:17799: 'das pa'i sa bcu dang sku gsum gyi sa gsum
NK091(ke)001:17800: ste bcu bzhi pa na bzhugs pa'i dpal rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:17801: snying po'am rdo rje sems dpa' lta zhig 'grana gyi
NK091(ke)001:17803: de man chad yang bdag gi dbang du byas la
NK091(ke)001:17804: thamsa cad 'ub la zhes pa dbang du bsdus la
NK091(ke)001:17805: jen rban / zhes pa 'khor du bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:17808: de ltar sgrogs shing 'gran gyi zla med che btsan gcig pu nyid du lta'o //
NK091(ke)001:17813: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17814: ji lta ji ltar thar pa nag po gang yin pa /
NK091(ke)001:17815: ru tra nag por smin par gyur pa de'i tshe de'i dus na /
NK091(ke)001:17816: gang dang po bskal pa kun dag'i dus kyi slob
NK091(ke)001:17817: dpon thub dka' gzhon nu de ni sa mchog bcu
NK091(ke)001:17818: bzhi pa brnyes te byang chub snying po gang na
NK091(ke)001:17819: bar dpal rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin nyid du
NK091(ke)001:17820: gyur to // gang bskal pa kun dag'i dus kyi
NK091(ke)001:17821: g.yog dan phag de ni de'i tshe de'i dus na
NK091(ke)001:17822: gyur to // / rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rgyal tshab
NK091(ke)001:17823: skyes bu dam pa rdo rje 'dzin pa zhes bya
NK091(ke)001:17825: ru tra dpon g.yog smin pa'i dus gcig par bshad
NK091(ke)001:17826: pa 'di nyid las dang thugs rje'i 'brel ba brtsi
NK091(ke)001:17827: ba'i dgos pa las spyir smin pa'i dus mi gcig
NK091(ke)001:17828: go // 'on kyang rgyu la gnas pa'i dus su
NK091(ke)001:17829: snga phyi'i tha snyad yod kyang 'bras bu thob nas
NK091(ke)001:17832: bshad pa'i bskul ba dag khyad par 'di gnyis su brjod pa'ang don 'di'i dbang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:17834: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:17835: gdul zhing ru tra nag poo'i spyod yul la che
NK091(ke)001:17836: ba spyom pa'i tshul bstan pa'i le'u ste nyi shu
NK091(ke)001:17837: rtsa gnyis pa legs par bshad pa'o ///bam po bzhi
NK091(ke)001:17838: par zug pa / gnyis pa gnyen pos bdud btul ba la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:17839: bdud btul ba'i sngon du bya ba'i sbyor ba /
NK091(ke)001:17841: sngags kyi sgor zhugs nas dbang thob pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17853: de skad du grags pa las /
NK091(ke)001:17854: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17855: le'u 'dis drang don dang nges don gnyis ka ston no //
NK091(ke)001:17856: de la gdul bya ru tra de las dang thugs
NK091(ke)001:17857: rjer 'brel ba'i rgyal ba rnams kyis gzigs nas 'dul
NK091(ke)001:17858: bar rtsom pa'i tshul ston te /
NK091(ke)001:17859: 'dul ba'i gnyen po 'byung ba'i rgyu rkyen gyis snang bar byed pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:17860: de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:17861: gshegs pa thams cad ngo bo de nyid du gcig
NK091(ke)001:17862: pa'i phyir gnas snying po byang chub gang na bar
NK091(ke)001:17863: ro gcig gi dgongs pas 'dus nas /
NK091(ke)001:17864: thub dka' gzhon nu snying po byang chub na bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:17865: pa dang dan phag rdo rje 'dzin pa chen por
NK091(ke)001:17866: rtsal rdzogs pa la cha mthun gyis bskul ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:17867: / so so'i sku mi snang bar stong pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:17868: du bshigs nas de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos par
NK091(ke)001:17869: / / de nyid skyes bu dam pa thub dka'
NK091(ke)001:17870: gzhon nu snying po byang chub dang dan phag rtsal
NK091(ke)001:17871: chen rdzogs pa'i snying por stong pa nyid du bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:17872: pa la snang bar mdzad de /
NK091(ke)001:17873: don gyi gsung gis stong pa de nyid kyi sgra
NK091(ke)001:17874: stong pa de nyid la grags pa zhes rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:17875: ril dang thub dka' gzhon nu dang rdo rje 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:17876: pa ngo bo tha mi dad pas nyid la nyid
NK091(ke)001:17877: bskul ba'o // ji ltar bskul ba dngos ni skyes
NK091(ke)001:17878: bu dam pa dge slong thub dka' rdo rje snying
NK091(ke)001:17879: po'am dan phag rdo rje 'dzin pa khyed kyis gdul
NK091(ke)001:17880: byar 'brel ba'i mtha' ru trar gyur pa ma btul
NK091(ke)001:17881: ba'am 'gro ba'i rgyud dag par ma byas te zhing
NK091(ke)001:17882: khams kyi bya ba yongs su ma rdzogs para /
NK091(ke)001:17883: ci'i phyir mngon para rdzogs par byang chub par bya
NK091(ke)001:17884: snyam ste chos sku las gzugs skur ma bzhengs pas
NK091(ke)001:17885: so // rgyal ba'i phrin las drag po'i las kyi
NK091(ke)001:17886: yan lag kun gyis sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa ma
NK091(ke)001:17887: rdzogs par ci'i phyir mngon par rdzogs par byang chub
NK091(ke)001:17888: par bya snyam ste gzugs sku las rigs lngar ma
NK091(ke)001:17889: so // bzhengs pas so // khro bo'i sku la
NK091(ke)001:17890: sogs pa sprul pa mang po tha dad du da
NK091(ke)001:17891: dung rnam para snang bar ma mdzad par /
NK091(ke)001:17892: ci'i phyir mngon par rdzogs para byanga chub par bya
NK091(ke)001:17893: snyam ste rigs lngas sems can gyi don ma mdzad
NK091(ke)001:17894: pas so // des na mngon par sangs rgya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:17895: dus ma yin pas de gsum gyis shig pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:17896: bskul bar mdzad pa dee skad ces grags pa las
NK091(ke)001:17897: pas so // / bskul ba gsan nas snying po
NK091(ke)001:17898: byang chub dang rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i stong pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:17899: de las 'di skad du grag go //
NK091(ke)001:17900: kye de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad don gyi dgongs
NK091(ke)001:17901: pa dang dgos pa gang gi dbang gis zhing khams
NK091(ke)001:17902: kyi bya ba yongs rdzogs par 'gyur /
NK091(ke)001:17903: de bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa gang gis dang /
NK091(ke)001:17904: tha dad du rnam par snang bar mdzad par ji
NK091(ke)001:17905: ltar 'gyur zhes de skad du gragsa te bskul ba
NK091(ke)001:17906: de gsum ji ltar bya bar zhus pa las /
NK091(ke)001:17908: chos sku las gzugs bzhengs par bskul bas bzhengs pa /
NK091(ke)001:17909: gzugs sku las rigs lngar bzhengs par bskul bas bzhengs pa /
NK091(ke)001:17910: rigs lngas sems can gyi don mdzad cig par bskul bas don mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17912: bskul bas de bzhin du mdzad pa /
NK091(ke)001:17915: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nges snang ba'i gzhir bskul bas de ltar mdzad pa lan dang bcas pa /
NK091(ke)001:17916: snying rje'i ting nges rgyal ba'i yum mdzod cig par bskul bas mdzad pa lan dang bcas pa /
NK091(ke)001:17917: rgyu'i ting nges sku bskyed cig par bskul bas mdzad pa lan dang bcas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:17923: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17924: yang rgyal ba thams cad snying po byang chub kyi
NK091(ke)001:17925: de kho na nyid la bzhugs pa las bskul ba
NK091(ke)001:17926: mchog gi thabs tshul gsum gyis bskul bar brjod pa'i
NK091(ke)001:17927: thog ma la'ang de bzhin nyid kyi sgo nas bskul
NK091(ke)001:17928: ba la sogs pa lnga brjod pa'i yang dang po
NK091(ke)001:17929: de bzhin nyid du bzhugs pa las bzhengs par bskul
NK091(ke)001:17930: te / rdo rje snying po la de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:17931: kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas bskul ba 'di
NK091(ke)001:17933: le'u 'di'i bskul ba'i mkhan po phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad yin la /
NK091(ke)001:17934: lan 'debs pa po ni thub dka' gzhon nu rdo rje sems dpar gyur pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:17935: dan phag phyag na rdo rjer gyur pa yin te kun la shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:17936: de yang stong pa nyid chen po 'byung 'jug dang
NK091(ke)001:17937: bral te mi g.yo bar rang gsal ba'i ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:17938: nam mkha'a lta bu la rtog pas yongs su mi
NK091(ke)001:17939: bskyod par bde ba chen po'i ngang du chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:17940: skur yang dag par gshegs pa'i rang don gyi mdzad
NK091(ke)001:17941: pa mthar phyin par brnyes pas skyes bu chen po
NK091(ke)001:17942: don grub pa khyed nyid gzhan don gyi mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:17943: yul du mi dmigsa shing ngo bo sems su mi
NK091(ke)001:17944: rtog pa'i chos dbyings de bzhin nyid cir yang gtod
NK091(ke)001:17945: 'dzin med de ma bcos pa chen po'i ngang las
NK091(ke)001:17946: thugs rje'i dbang gis yang dag pa'i rtoga pa brgyad
NK091(ke)001:17947: cu rtsa gcig la sogs par sna tshogs su snang
NK091(ke)001:17948: nas gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs kyi rgyur bskyed para
NK091(ke)001:17949: mdzod cig /ces bzhengs par bskul ba'i sgra grag go
NK091(ke)001:17950: // de la lan yang skyes bu dam pa snying
NK091(ke)001:17951: po byang chub kyi chos nyid la bzhugs pa de
NK091(ke)001:17952: nyid las 'di skad du grag go //
NK091(ke)001:17953: bsgom pa dmigs su med pa'i mi rtog pa chen
NK091(ke)001:17954: po'i ngang las dus rtag par thams cad du 'da'
NK091(ke)001:17955: ba med pa nyid du gsal ba la /
NK091(ke)001:17956: zhen pas bzung bas brtags pas rtog pa'am stong pa
NK091(ke)001:17957: nyid du gang byung ba de nyid ther zug gi
NK091(ke)001:17958: rtog pa chen po gzhil bar dka' ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:17959: des na gang bla dwags dang bral ba'i de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:17960: nyid rnam par mi rtog pa chen po dmigs pa
NK091(ke)001:17961: kun dang bral bar lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang ni
NK091(ke)001:17962: yang dag pa'i rtog pa brgyad cu rtsa gcig la
NK091(ke)001:17963: sogs pa'i rgyu yi ngo bo ril ma 'dres yongs
NK091(ke)001:17964: su rdzogs pa nyid pas rtog pa bskyed ci dgos
NK091(ke)001:17966: zhes de bzhin nyid las bzhengs pa'i zhal bzhes nyid grag go //
NK091(ke)001:17967: de ltar bskul ba'ang rgyal ba ril gyi chos nyid las byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:17968: lan yang skyes bu'i chos nyid las byung nas zhal
NK091(ke)001:17969: gyis bzhes par 'chad pa ril yang rjes su sbyar
NK091(ke)001:17975: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:17976: yang rgyal ba thams cad kyi de kho na nyid las 'di skad du grag go //
NK091(ke)001:17977: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin las thugs rjer bskyed cig par bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:17978: ye shes ma sgrib par 'od gsal bas nam mkha'
NK091(ke)001:17979: dbyings kyi snying po mu mtha' med pa las ye
NK091(ke)001:17980: gsal gyi ngo bor brdal ba ni chos kun gyi
NK091(ke)001:17982: sems kyi rang bzhin gyis ril zin pa'i kun tu snang ba'i rang 'od thugs rje chen po ste /
NK091(ke)001:17983: sems can thams cad kyi don mdzad cing yongsa la
NK091(ke)001:17984: khyab pa 'byung ba'i snying rje'i yum yin pas 'gro
NK091(ke)001:17985: ba mtha' yas ji snyed pa las rgyal ba'i rigs
NK091(ke)001:17986: 'dzin pa dag rgyal sras su skyed de thugs rjes
NK091(ke)001:17987: smin par mdzod cig ces kun tu snang ba'i ting
NK091(ke)001:17988: nge 'dzin gyis bskul bar grag go //
NK091(ke)001:17989: yang de'i lan skyes bu dam pa de nyid las 'di skad du grag go //
NK091(ke)001:17990: rdo rje snying po la ched du ma byas par
NK091(ke)001:17991: kun snang gi snying rje chen po rdzogs pa las
NK091(ke)001:17992: bzhengs par zhal gyis bzhes te /
NK091(ke)001:17993: dngos po bzang ngan 'khor 'das kyi chos kun 'byung
NK091(ke)001:17994: zhing snang la kun gyi rten gzhi chos thams cad
NK091(ke)001:17995: kyi de bzhin nyid ma bcos pa'i chos nyid mnyam
NK091(ke)001:17996: pa chen po'i dbyings ngo bo ma skyes shing mi
NK091(ke)001:17997: 'gag pas 'dus byas kyi mtshan nyid dang bral te
NK091(ke)001:17998: ldan pa med pa ni ye shes chen po nyid
NK091(ke)001:17999: de thams cad kun tu snang ste snums shing gsal
NK091(ke)001:18000: ba la / tshig dang blos 'di 'drar smra bsam
NK091(ke)001:18001: brjod pa dang bral te dmigs pa med cing yul
NK091(ke)001:18002: las 'das pa yin kyang rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK091(ke)001:18003: rgyas mtha'a yas pa kun dang sems can mtha' yas
NK091(ke)001:18004: pa ril thugs chen po de las 'char zhing bskyed
NK091(ke)001:18005: pa'i yum chen por ye nas bzhugs pa la ched
NK091(ke)001:18006: du bskyed ci dgos zhes lan btab par grag go
NK091(ke)001:18007: ba la / // gsum pa la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:18008: gsung yig 'brur bzhengs par bskul bas bzhengs pa lan dang bcas pa /
NK091(ke)001:18009: thugs phyag rgyar bzhengs par bskul bas bzhengs pa lan dang bcas pa /
NK091(ke)001:18010: sku rdzogs par bzhengs par bskul bas bzhengs pa lan dang bcas pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:18016: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18017: yang rgyal ba thams cad kyi de kho na nyid las 'di skad du grag go //
NK091(ke)001:18018: rgyu'i yi ge las bzhengs shig par bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:18019: rgyal ba'i sku mi mthun pa tha dad mang po
NK091(ke)001:18020: 'gro ba la rnam par snang bar mdzad pa na
NK091(ke)001:18021: / de'i gzhi yi ge yin pa'i phyir rang snang
NK091(ke)001:18022: gsung gi phyag rgya'i rnam grol yi ge'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:18024: rgyal ba rnams ni gsung yi gera ngo bo tha
NK091(ke)001:18025: mi dad par snang bas rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin yi
NK091(ke)001:18026: ge'i ye shes dang gsung gi cho ga'i ngo bor
NK091(ke)001:18027: gsal zhing bskyed par mdzod cig ces rgyu dang gsung
NK091(ke)001:18028: gi cho ga thun mong gis bskul bar grag go
NK091(ke)001:18029: // lan du yang skyes bu dam pa de nyid las 'di skad du grag go //
NK091(ke)001:18030: yi ge'ang rang rig la yin pas thams cad kyi rgyu yin par bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18031: chos rnams kyi de bzhin nyid rang rig pa ni
NK091(ke)001:18032: yi ge'i rang bzhin du lhun gyis grub par rang
NK091(ke)001:18033: gsal ba'i ngo bo nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:18034: des na chos rnams kyi rang bzhin ma skyes pa
NK091(ke)001:18035: nyid rang byung yi ge m+aum gyi ngo bo nyid
NK091(ke)001:18036: du dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal bar shar la
NK091(ke)001:18037: / sems nyid rang rig pa nyid bshad pa bzhin
NK091(ke)001:18038: du yi ge'i rang bzhin dang tha mi dad pa
NK091(ke)001:18039: nyid du nges te gnyis su med pas ye shes
NK091(ke)001:18040: sna tshogs ji snyed pa kun gyi ngo bo yi
NK091(ke)001:18041: ge h'u nyid rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK091(ke)001:18043: rgyal ba bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:18044: nyid yon tan ril gyi bdag nyid kyang yi ge'i
NK091(ke)001:18046: de'i phyir phyag rgya gsung gi yi gee'i +amo la
NK091(ke)001:18047: sogs pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su ye nas gsal
NK091(ke)001:18048: bar rdzogs pas rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil
NK091(ke)001:18049: 'khor ro // der ma zad chos so cog thams
NK091(ke)001:18050: cad kun kyang yi ge'i rang bzhin dang ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:18051: tha mi dad pa 'phral la tha dad du skyes
NK091(ke)001:18052: 'khor ro // pa min te / ril ma skyes
NK091(ke)001:18053: pa'i phyir gsang ba'i yi ge a yi ngo bor
NK091(ke)001:18054: shar ba la 'phral du rgyu'i yi ge bskyed mi
NK091(ke)001:18062: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18063: yang rgyal ba thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid las 'di skad du grag go //
NK091(ke)001:18064: snying po byang chub las thugs kyi cho gas yi
NK091(ke)001:18065: ge las phyag mtshan gyii phyag rgyar bzhengs shig par
NK091(ke)001:18066: bskul te / rgyal ba'i thugs snying po byang chub
NK091(ke)001:18067: la ye shes ril ma 'dres la pha rol tu
NK091(ke)001:18068: phyin par yongs su rdzogs shing 'dus pas /
NK091(ke)001:18069: de'i don rnal 'byor pa lam pa rnams kyis rnam
NK091(ke)001:18070: grol gyi ngo bor rig cing rtogs par bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:18071: sgo mtshon pa'i thabs dam pa thugs ye shes lnga
NK091(ke)001:18072: la sogs kyi rang rtags rdo rje dang 'khor lo
NK091(ke)001:18073: la sogs pa rnams su gsal bar rgyal ba rnams
NK091(ke)001:18074: kyis snang bar mdzad pa ltar du /
NK091(ke)001:18075: skyes bus kyang thugs rnam grol ye shes mtshon pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18076: thugs mtshan dam tshig gi phyag rgya bskyed par mdzod
NK091(ke)001:18077: cig ces thugs kyi cho gas bskul bar grag go
NK091(ke)001:18078: // lan yang skyes bu dam pa de nyid las 'di skad du graga go //
NK091(ke)001:18079: rdo rje snying po thugs mi g.yo bar snang ba'i phyag rgya 'byung bar zhal gyis bzhes te /
NK091(ke)001:18080: zhen pa gnyis mthar spangs pas thams cad ma bkol
NK091(ke)001:18081: ba'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs
NK091(ke)001:18083: dus gsum kun tu mi 'gyur bar rtag tu mtshan
NK091(ke)001:18084: ma'i rnam par rtog pa gzhi med du grol ba'i
NK091(ke)001:18085: go 'phang dam pa brnyes pa las 'byung ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:18086: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo
NK091(ke)001:18087: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog gi mdud pa rang sar zhig
NK091(ke)001:18088: cing rnam par grol ba'i ye shes chen po rang
NK091(ke)001:18090: de bas na 'dul bya rtog pa can la phyag
NK091(ke)001:18091: mtshan sna tshogs kyi phyag rgya'i mtshan mar snang yang
NK091(ke)001:18092: thugs ye grol ba la mtshon pa'i phyag rgya bskyed
NK091(ke)001:18093: mi dgos par lan btab bo //
NK091(ke)001:18094: zhes rtog pa can la yi ge las phyag mtshan 'byung bar ston pa'i zhal bzhes grag go //
NK091(ke)001:18100: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18101: yang rgyal ba thams cad kyi de bazhana nyid las 'di skad du grag go //
NK091(ke)001:18102: sku yongs su rdzogs par bzhengs shig par bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:18103: ye ji bzhin pa'i stong pa chen po de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:18104: nyid ngo bo mi rtog par me long lta bur
NK091(ke)001:18105: rang gsal las rang bzhin ma skyes kyang rnam pa
NK091(ke)001:18106: mi 'agga par longs spyod rdzogs pa dang sprul pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18107: sku'i gzugs su 'char zhing snang bar mdzad pa yang
NK091(ke)001:18108: dpe nam mkha' la 'ja' tshon snang ba ji lta
NK091(ke)001:18109: ba bzhin du mi g.yo ba'i chos sku chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:18110: dbyings las phyag mtshan 'od du zhu nas khro bo'i
NK091(ke)001:18111: phyag rgyar bzhengs su gsol zhes sku yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:18112: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis bskul ba nyid grag go
NK091(ke)001:18113: // de'i lan yang skyes bu dam pa de nyid las 'di skad du graga go //
NK091(ke)001:18114: thugs mi g.yo ba las skur bzhengs par zhal gyis bzhes te /
NK091(ke)001:18115: ye nas ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid kyi ngang
NK091(ke)001:18116: du gzugs sku'i rnam pa mi dmigs par chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:18117: skur rnam par grol ba yin kyang rol ba'i rang
NK091(ke)001:18118: bzhin kun tu snang ba la gzugs kyi sku mi
NK091(ke)001:18119: mthun pa sna tshogs su 'char ba'ang mi 'gog par
NK091(ke)001:18120: mu mtha' med pa'i dbyings las mi g.yo bar bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:18121: so // de bas na ma 'dres la yongs su
NK091(ke)001:18122: rdzogs pas ngang chen po la gcig dang du ma
NK091(ke)001:18123: bral ba'i tshul gyis lhun gyis grub pa'i gtan tshigs
NK091(ke)001:18124: de'i phyir na zhi ba dang khro bo'i skur ma
NK091(ke)001:18125: 'dres par phyag rgya'i gzugs mchog rnam para snang zhing
NK091(ke)001:18126: gsal ba la skur bzhengs ci dgos zhes lan btab
NK091(ke)001:18132: zhes pa'i bar gyi bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18133: de ltar bskul ba dang po lnga po des sku
NK091(ke)001:18134: yongs su rdzogs par gyis shig par bskul bas skyes
NK091(ke)001:18135: bu dam pa de kho na nyid de yis don
NK091(ke)001:18136: gyis zhal gyis bzhes nas bskul ba gsan pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:18137: stong pa nyid kyi dbyings de las 'byung 'jug med
NK091(ke)001:18138: par stong pa nyid kyi sku rnam par snang ba
NK091(ke)001:18139: ni don ji ltar dpe ji ltar chu zla'i dkyil
NK091(ke)001:18140: 'khor snang ba'am / nam mkha'a la 'ja' tshon snang
NK091(ke)001:18141: ba'i tshul du byung nas sku de snang yang bskul
NK091(ke)001:18142: ba'i sa la gzhes pa'i phyir rigs dang longs spyod
NK091(ke)001:18144: zhi ba dang khro bo gang du yang ma nges
NK091(ke)001:18145: par cir yang 'gyur du rung ba'i ye shes kyi
NK091(ke)001:18146: skur gsal bar shar te dbyings las bzhengs par gnas
NK091(ke)001:18147: pas gzugs kyi skur gnas shing bzhugs pa la zhes
NK091(ke)001:18148: de ltar sku snang bas zhing khams kyi gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:18149: sbyong ba'i phyir lan dang po bstan to //
NK091(ke)001:18154: yab yum gyi skur bzhengs par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:18155: rigs lnga'i skur bzhengs par bskul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:18160: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18161: lan gnyis pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:18162: de nas rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:18163: gshegas pa thams cad kyisa skyes bu dam pa dbyings
NK091(ke)001:18164: dang ye shes kyi skur bzhengs pa la bskul ba
NK091(ke)001:18165: gnyis pa 'dis longs spyod rdzogs pa dang sprul pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18166: skur bzhengs la sgrol ba'i don mdzod cig par nges
NK091(ke)001:18169: ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgo nas bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:18170: chos rnams kyi rang bzhin rgyu rkyen med par rang
NK091(ke)001:18171: byung ba'i chos nyid ma bcos pa'i de bzhin nyid
NK091(ke)001:18172: ye ji bzhin pa de nyid ji lta bar mngon
NK091(ke)001:18173: du gyur nas mtha' gang du'ang snang ba med pas
NK091(ke)001:18174: mi g.yo ba ngo bo nyid kyi sku bde ba
NK091(ke)001:18175: chen po'i ngang nyid ched du brtsal zhing 'gro 'ong
NK091(ke)001:18176: gis g.yo ba gang yang dag pa gnyis ldan 'di
NK091(ke)001:18177: la ci yang med de ma dmigs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:18178: des bas na thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang
NK091(ke)001:18179: chos kyi dbyings gnyis su med pa'i chos kyi sku
NK091(ke)001:18180: la de nyid du btags pa'ang tshig gi tha snyad
NK091(ke)001:18181: tsam las don la med par ma bcos par mthar
NK091(ke)001:18182: phyin pa'i de kho na nyid rang gsal chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:18184: de nyid yul lam 'khor ba dngos po dang sems
NK091(ke)001:18185: sam mya ngan las 'das pa dngos po min pa
NK091(ke)001:18186: ril gyi 'byung gansa nyid yin pas ji ltar bsam
NK091(ke)001:18188: de nyid la skye 'jig med pas cis kyang mi
NK091(ke)001:18189: tshugs shing gnyen po dang bral bas mi choda mi
NK091(ke)001:18190: shigsa pa'i ngo bo mi 'gyur rdo rje'i sku ste
NK091(ke)001:18191: rtag pa chen po bzhugs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:18192: de kho na nyid ye gdod ma nyid nas ma
NK091(ke)001:18193: bslad pas lhan skyes ji bzhin par rol pas bde
NK091(ke)001:18194: ba mchog gi dgyes pa chen po'i thugs kyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:18195: bo dus gsum du mi g.yo zhing ma 'gags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18196: bcud chen por bzhugs pa ni gsang ba'i sku yang
NK091(ke)001:18197: yin no // rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgo nas bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:18198: de ltar sku bzhi dbyer med kyi ngang nyid rdo
NK091(ke)001:18199: rje sems mchog nam mkha'i snying po dbyings nyid 'od
NK091(ke)001:18200: gsal ba la che ba'i yon tan yongs su rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:18201: pa'i chos kyi rgyal po dus gsum gyi bde bar
NK091(ke)001:18202: gshegs pa'i rgyal ba ma lus pa kun gyi dge
NK091(ke)001:18203: ba'i bshes gnyena chen po mnga' dbang rdzogs pa'i ston
NK091(ke)001:18204: pa dam par byung ba la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18205: sku zhes bya'o // rgyal ba ril gyi btsan po
NK091(ke)001:18206: nyid thugs rje chen po'i ngang las thams cad du
NK091(ke)001:18207: 'dul ba bzhin 'phags pa'i tshogs kyi rje btsun sprul
NK091(ke)001:18208: pa mang po 'byung zhing snang ba'i gnas ni sprul
NK091(ke)001:18210: de lta bu sku lnga po ma lus pa kun
NK091(ke)001:18211: gyi rang bzhin gsal rdzogs kyi ngo bor bzhugs la
NK091(ke)001:18212: mi rtog ma 'gags pa chen po'i me long 'od
NK091(ke)001:18213: po che khyod nyid khro ba'i sprin gyi rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:18214: mtha' yas pa ji snyed du rol pa'i bkod pa
NK091(ke)001:18215: 'byung zhing bskyed pa'i khro bo chen po yab yum
NK091(ke)001:18216: du bzhengs par mdzod cig ces gong du bzhengs nas
NK091(ke)001:18217: sku ma nges pa la nges par bskul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:18225: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18226: rigs drug la so sor bskul ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:18227: skyes bu nyid la rigs drug gi don mdzad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18228: tshul gyis bskul ba ni spyi dang khyad par gyi
NK091(ke)001:18229: dbang ste / de thun mong du bstan pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:18230: rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyi sgo nas bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:18231: de yang thog mar rigs kyi bdag po la bskul
NK091(ke)001:18232: ba dang de'i tshul nas skyes bu la bskul ba
NK091(ke)001:18233: ste / de bzhin gshegs pa gang dag ji snyed
NK091(ke)001:18234: pa rnams byang chub snying por tha mi dad par
NK091(ke)001:18235: mtshungs pa yi rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i dbyings
NK091(ke)001:18236: las ma g.yos par bskyed pa med pa'i byang chub
NK091(ke)001:18237: kyi sems nyid du bzhugs kyang gnas tha dad pa
NK091(ke)001:18238: gang du dus thog ma'i dang por rgyal ba ril
NK091(ke)001:18239: gyi grong khyer gsum ma spangs bral nas rgyud rnam
NK091(ke)001:18240: par dag pa'i 'bras bu chen po brnyes pas sangs
NK091(ke)001:18241: rgyas kun gyi mdzad pa ltar skyes bu dam pa
NK091(ke)001:18242: khams gsum gyi zhen pa las grol nas 'dus ma
NK091(ke)001:18243: byas par rang byung ba'i skye 'jig mi mnga' ba'i
NK091(ke)001:18244: rdo rje snying po'i lus sam sku mchog gi ngang
NK091(ke)001:18245: las gdul bya'i 'gro ba mang po mtha' yas pa
NK091(ke)001:18246: rtog pa can dag gi ngo la gsung yi ge
NK091(ke)001:18247: tha dad pa sna tshogs su rnam par sprul zhing
NK091(ke)001:18248: snang bar mdzad de don mdzad cing yi ge de
NK091(ke)001:18249: las kyang sku'i dkyil 'khor byung ste thugs ye shes
NK091(ke)001:18250: rang snang ba'i sras kyi tshogs kyis 'khor mang pos
NK091(ke)001:18251: mdzes par bskor ba'i dkyil lam sprul pa ji snyed
NK091(ke)001:18252: pa'i dbus na gtso bo'i gzugs kyi skur khro bo'i
NK091(ke)001:18253: phyag rgyar bstan nas dpyangs thag chad pa'i gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:18254: drag po'i gdung ba'i sa bon nyon mongs pa'i rtog
NK091(ke)001:18255: pa thams cad sbyang zhing dag par mdzad du gsol
NK091(ke)001:18257: spyi dbang du rgyal ba ril la bskul bar yang 'chad do //
NK091(ke)001:18258: khyad par gyi dbang du lan 'debs pa'i tshul gyis
NK091(ke)001:18259: rigs kyi bdag po dang rgyal ba ji snyed pas
NK091(ke)001:18260: de ltar mdzad pa ltar skyes bu khyod khro bo'i
NK091(ke)001:18261: sprul pa'i 'khor tshogs dang bcas par byung nas gdug
NK091(ke)001:18262: pa can gyi las sbyang du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:18263: zhes bskul bar sbyar te 'chad pa dag kyang rjes su bsnyad do //
NK091(ke)001:18265: rdo rje'i rigs su bzhengs par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:18266: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs su bzhengs par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:18267: rin po che'i rigs su bzhengs par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:18268: pad+ma'i rigs su bzhengs par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:18269: las kyi rigs su bzhengs par bskul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:18271: gang du dang por rdo rje /
NK091(ke)001:18274: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18275: rigs lnga'i tshul du bzhengs la ru tra thul zhig
NK091(ke)001:18276: par bskul ba las rdo rje sems dpar bskul te
NK091(ke)001:18277: / gnas gang du dus dang por rdo rje snying
NK091(ke)001:18278: po'am rdo rje sems dpa' ni khams gsum gyi sa
NK091(ke)001:18279: bon zad par bton nas rang byung bde ba chen
NK091(ke)001:18280: por lhun gyis grub ste mngon par rdzogs par sangs
NK091(ke)001:18281: rgyas pa'i 'bras bu rdo rje'i rigs kyi go 'phang
NK091(ke)001:18282: dam pa brnyes nas gdul bya lus gtum zhing ngag
NK091(ke)001:18283: drag la thung ba sems shin tu gdug par gyur
NK091(ke)001:18284: pa zhe sdang can gang de rang mthun 'dul thabs
NK091(ke)001:18285: kyis grol bar mdzad pa'i phyir dgongs pa rtog pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18286: dri ma med pa me long lta bu'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:18287: yul med par sna tshogs su gsal ba'i blos ni
NK091(ke)001:18288: yi ge h'u du sprul nas de las rdo rje'i
NK091(ke)001:18289: rigs kyi gtso 'khor 'od zera gyi tshul gyi phreng
NK091(ke)001:18290: bas mdzes par thugs rigs kyi 'khor gyis bskor ba'i
NK091(ke)001:18291: dkyil na sprul pa'i gtso bor mdzad nas bzhugs pa
NK091(ke)001:18292: khyod nyid dang po byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed
NK091(ke)001:18293: pa'i sngon gyi thugs dam dang smon lam gyi dbang
NK091(ke)001:18294: gisa na da lta'i thugs dam cis kyang mi bskyod
NK091(ke)001:18295: pa'i rdo rje'i rigs kyi badz+ra he ru ka'i gzugs
NK091(ke)001:18296: skur bzhengs nas mdzad pa bstan du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:18299: gang du dang por rnam par /
NK091(ke)001:18302: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18303: rnam par snang mdzad la bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:18304: yul gang du dus dang por rnam par snang mdzad
NK091(ke)001:18305: ni khamsa gsum gyi sa bon zad par bton nas
NK091(ke)001:18306: rang byung 'gag med cir yang snang ba'i 'bras bu
NK091(ke)001:18307: mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas te de bzhin gshegs
NK091(ke)001:18308: pa'i rigs kyi go 'phang dam pa brnyes par mdzad
NK091(ke)001:18309: nas gdul bya 'jig rten gsum rmongs par byed pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18310: mun pa gti mug can gang de rang mthun gyi
NK091(ke)001:18311: thabs kyisa grol bar mdzad pa'i phyir dgongs pa stong
NK091(ke)001:18312: pa nyid kyi ye shes rnam dag byang chub kyi
NK091(ke)001:18313: blos ni yi ge du sprul nas de las bde
NK091(ke)001:18314: gshegs rigs kyi gtso 'khor gzugs mang po'i tshul gyis
NK091(ke)001:18315: phreng bas mdzes par sku'i rigs kyi 'khor gyis bskor
NK091(ke)001:18316: ba'i dkyil na sprul pa'i gtso bor mdzad nas bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:18317: pa khyod nyid sngona gyi byang chub mchog tu sems
NK091(ke)001:18318: bskyed pa'i thugs dam dang smon lam gyi dbang gis
NK091(ke)001:18319: na da lta'i thugs dam cir yang snang ba'i bud+d+ha
NK091(ke)001:18320: he ru ka'i gzugs skur bzhengs nas mdzad pa bstan
NK091(ke)001:18323: gang du dang por yon tan /
NK091(ke)001:18326: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18327: rin chen 'byung ldan la bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:18328: yul gang du dus dang pora yon tan rin po
NK091(ke)001:18329: che'i 'byung gansa ni khams gsum gyi sa bon zad
NK091(ke)001:18330: par bton nas rang byung yid bzhin rin po che
NK091(ke)001:18331: yon tan kun rdzogs kyi 'bras bur mngon par rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:18332: par sangs rgyas te rin chen rigs kyi go 'phang
NK091(ke)001:18333: dam pa brnyes nas gdul bya 'dod pa la zhen
NK091(ke)001:18334: te nga rgyal gyis rmongs pa rnams rang mthun gyi
NK091(ke)001:18335: thabsa kyis grol bar mdzad pa'i phyir dgongs pa mnyam
NK091(ke)001:18336: nyid ye shes rnam dag 'byung gnas kyi blos ni
NK091(ke)001:18337: yi ge s+w+aa ru sprul nas de las yon tan
NK091(ke)001:18338: rigs kyi gtso 'khor rin chen phreng bas mdzesa par
NK091(ke)001:18339: rang rigs kyi 'khor gyis bskor ba'i dkyil na sprul
NK091(ke)001:18340: pa'i gtso bo mdzad nas bzhugs pa khyod nyid sngona
NK091(ke)001:18341: gyi byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed pa'i thugs dam
NK091(ke)001:18342: dang smon lam gyi dbang gis na da lta'i thugs
NK091(ke)001:18343: dam 'dod pa kun 'byung rat+na he ru ka'i gzugs
NK091(ke)001:18344: skur bzhengs nas mdzad pa bstan du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:18347: gang du dang por 'od dpag /ces pa nas /
NK091(ke)001:18349: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18351: yul gang du dus dang pora 'od dpag tu med
NK091(ke)001:18352: pa ni khams gsuma gyi sa bon zad par bton
NK091(ke)001:18353: nas rang byung gsung rab kun bdag snang ba mtha'
NK091(ke)001:18354: yas su mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas te 'bras
NK091(ke)001:18355: bu byang chub chen po pad+ma rigs kyi go 'phang
NK091(ke)001:18356: dam pa brnyes na gdul bya 'dod pa la chags
NK091(ke)001:18357: pas rmongs pa rnams rang mthun gyi thabs kyis grol
NK091(ke)001:18358: bar mdzad pa'i phyir du dgongs pa sor rtog ye
NK091(ke)001:18359: shes rnam dag dri med kyi blos ni yi ge
NK091(ke)001:18360: am du sprul nas de las pad+ma'i rigs kyi gtso
NK091(ke)001:18361: 'khor gsung snyan yi ge'i phreng bas mdzes par gsung
NK091(ke)001:18362: gi rigs kyi 'khor gyis bskor ba'i dkyil na sprul
NK091(ke)001:18363: pa'i gtso bo mdzad nas bzhugs pa khyod nyid sngon
NK091(ke)001:18364: gyi byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i smon lam
NK091(ke)001:18365: dang thugs dam gyi dbang gisa na da ltar thugs
NK091(ke)001:18366: dam sna tshogs ston pa'i pad+ma he ru ka'i gzugs
NK091(ke)001:18367: skur bzhengs nas mdzad pa bstan du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:18370: gang du dang por gdon mi /
NK091(ke)001:18373: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18374: gdon mi za ba la bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:18375: yul gang du dus dang pora gdon mi za ba'am
NK091(ke)001:18376: don yod grub pa ni khams gsum gyi sa bon
NK091(ke)001:18377: zad par bton nas rang byung phrin las sna tshogs
NK091(ke)001:18378: cir yang mdzad pa'i 'bras bur mngon par rdzogs par
NK091(ke)001:18379: sangs rgyas te las kyi rigs kyi go 'phang dam
NK091(ke)001:18380: pa brnyes nas gdul bya bdag gzhan gyi bya ba
NK091(ke)001:18381: la rmongs pa phrag dog can rang mthun gyi thabs
NK091(ke)001:18382: kyis grol bar mdzad pa'i phyir dgongs pa bya grub
NK091(ke)001:18383: ye shes rnam dag nan tan gyi blos ni yi
NK091(ke)001:18384: ge ham du sprul nas de las las kyi rigs
NK091(ke)001:18385: kyi gtso 'khor mdzad pa gar gyi phreng bas mdzes
NK091(ke)001:18386: par phrin las kyi rigs kyi 'khor gyis bskor ba'i
NK091(ke)001:18387: dkyil na sprul pa'i gtso bo mdzad nas bzhugs pa
NK091(ke)001:18388: khyod nyid sngon gyi byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed
NK091(ke)001:18389: pa'i smon lam dang thugs dam gyi dbang gisa na
NK091(ke)001:18390: / da lta'i thugs dam thams cad mdzad pa'i karma
NK091(ke)001:18391: he ru ka'i gzugs skur bzhengs nas mdzad pa bstan
NK091(ke)001:18393: 'di rnams kyi gang du dang po'i tshig ni skyes bu la bskul ba'i gtan tshigs su 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:18394: sngon gyi thugs dam dang smon lam ni rang rang la bskul ba'i gnyer te /
NK091(ke)001:18395: de'i phyir thun mong du bstan to //
NK091(ke)001:18400: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18401: zhes bskul ba gnyis pa des yongs su rdzogs par
NK091(ke)001:18402: bskul bas de'i yon tan gyis de ltar gsan nas
NK091(ke)001:18403: cir yang 'byung du rung ba'i rigs ma nges pa
NK091(ke)001:18404: chos nyid sgyu ma lta bu'i sku las rigs nges
NK091(ke)001:18405: pa ye shes lnga'i ngang las so so'i rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:18406: sgyu ma'i sku snang ba ni dpe ji lta don
NK091(ke)001:18407: ji ltar me long gi dbyings su bzhin gyi dkyil
NK091(ke)001:18408: 'khor snang zhing gsal ba bzhin du res 'jog med
NK091(ke)001:18409: par ye shes sgyu ma'i skur rang snang bar gnas
NK091(ke)001:18410: pa las zhes de ltar ye shes kyi sku snang
NK091(ke)001:18411: bas rgyal ba kun gyi mdzad pa'i phrin las skyes
NK091(ke)001:18412: bus kyang mdzad par 'gyur bas na lan gnyis par
NK091(ke)001:18413: 'gyur ro // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:18417: sku snang bar mdzod cig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:18418: khams gsum gyi nad sol cig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:18419: mun pa bsal bar mdzod cig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:18420: 'dul ba'i dus la bab par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:18421: rgyal ba kun gyi thugs dam bskul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:18426: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18427: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bskul ba gsum pa 'dis /
NK091(ke)001:18428: gsang ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur bzhengs pa'am /
NK091(ke)001:18429: 'on te ye shes kyi skur mngon du rdzogs par
NK091(ke)001:18430: bkod de khro bo'i lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po
NK091(ke)001:18431: rigs nges pa'i longs spyod rdzogs par bzhengs par bskul
NK091(ke)001:18433: snying po byang chub de bzhin nyid du gshegs te
NK091(ke)001:18434: mthar son pa'i skyes bu dam pa khyod ces nges
NK091(ke)001:18435: par gzung ba'i phyir thub dka' rdo rje snying por
NK091(ke)001:18438: 'chad pa'i kye ma la sogs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:18439: rtsa lnga pa las thub dka' rdo rje snying po las sprul pa 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:18440: 'on kyang skabs mthun pa nges par gzung ba las
NK091(ke)001:18441: rgyal ba gzhan dang tha dad par mi lta ste
NK091(ke)001:18442: gdul bya'i snang ba tsam mo //
NK091(ke)001:18443: de lta bu khyod ni 'jig rten gyi 'og min
NK091(ke)001:18444: chen po'i zhing khams su mnga' dbang rdzogs pa'i bdag
NK091(ke)001:18445: nyid du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i bya
NK091(ke)001:18446: ba mdzod la / snying po byang chub ji bzhin pa de nyid las /
NK091(ke)001:18447: 'gro ba sems can kun gyi don du sku gsung
NK091(ke)001:18448: thugs kyi bkod pa snang zhing shar bar mdzod cig
NK091(ke)001:18449: /sngon byung du yang 'jig rten gyi khams kyi zhing
NK091(ke)001:18450: khams ni dpag tu med pa mang po nyid du
NK091(ke)001:18451: / ji snyed cig bde bar gshegs pa yi rgyal
NK091(ke)001:18452: ba ma lus pa sprul pa mang pos 'gro don
NK091(ke)001:18453: mdzad pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyisa kyang gdul bya mtha'
NK091(ke)001:18454: dag gi dona du sku gsung thugs rnam par snang
NK091(ke)001:18455: ste bkod pa mdzad pa ltar skyes bus kyang don
NK091(ke)001:18461: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18462: khams gsum 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i sems can dug drag
NK091(ke)001:18463: po lngas nad kyis gdung bar gyur pa la gzhan
NK091(ke)001:18464: gyis sos shing phan par 'gyur ba'i sman ma mchis
NK091(ke)001:18465: pas ma nor mi bslu ba'i don gyis yang dag
NK091(ke)001:18466: bdud rtsi'i sman dam pa sbyar bas 'khor ba'i gcong
NK091(ke)001:18467: rnying ma rig pa'i mun pa gzhi rtsa dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:18468: pa sbyang bar mdzad pa dang sdug bsngal zug rngu'i
NK091(ke)001:18469: nad thams cad sel bar mdzad pa'i sman pa che
NK091(ke)001:18470: mchog gi gtso bor skyes bu khyed nyid gshegsa par
NK091(ke)001:18471: mdzad nas 'khrul pa'i nad do cog gi dgrara gyur
NK091(ke)001:18472: pa 'tsho byed dam pa bdud rtsi sman gyi rgya
NK091(ke)001:18473: mtsho byang chub sems kyi chu yis dug lnga la
NK091(ke)001:18474: sogs pa log pa'ii nad kyi dgras gzir ba yi
NK091(ke)001:18475: ru tra la sogs pa grong khyer gsum gyi nad
NK091(ke)001:18476: pa'i tshogs kun bslang bar mdzod cig ces bskul lo
NK091(ke)001:18481: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18482: dan phag rdo rje 'dzin par gnas gyur pa la bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:18483: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skyes bu 'bras bu lhun gyis
NK091(ke)001:18484: grub pa khyod nyid thugs snying po byang chub kyi
NK091(ke)001:18485: ngang la dgongs pa mi g.yo bar gnas pa las
NK091(ke)001:18486: 'gro ba'i don la sprul pa'i 'od zer gyi snang
NK091(ke)001:18487: ba rgyas par bkye ste ma rig pa'i muna pa
NK091(ke)001:18488: bsal ba'i dgongs pa mdzod cig ces bskul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:18493: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18494: 'bras bu chen po brnyes pa la ngo mtshar ba dang ldan pas /
NK091(ke)001:18495: kye ma skyes bu zhes bos nas rdo rje snying
NK091(ke)001:18496: po mngon du byas pas bsgrub bya ril chub ste
NK091(ke)001:18497: mthar thug gi don grub pa bdag don gyi bya
NK091(ke)001:18498: ba byas shing gzhan don gyi byed pa byas pa
NK091(ke)001:18499: srid lam gyi rtsol bas khur bora te gdung ba
NK091(ke)001:18500: dang bral ba sngon gyi rgyal ba bzhin du bdag
NK091(ke)001:18501: gi don srid chen po rjes su thob cing brnyes
NK091(ke)001:18502: pa khyed kyis gang 'dir dregs pa 'dul ba'i dus
NK091(ke)001:18503: la nges par baba pas dgongs par mdzod cig ces
NK091(ke)001:18508: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18509: gtsang ma'i gnas kyi 'og min las mchog tu 'phags
NK091(ke)001:18510: pa'i khyad par gyi sgras 'jig rten gyi 'og min
NK091(ke)001:18511: las khyad par du gyur pas 'og min gyi zhing
NK091(ke)001:18512: khams de nyid rnam par mdzes pa chen por 'bras
NK091(ke)001:18513: bus chos kyisa mtho ba'i gzhal yas su rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:18514: bdag po rdzogs longs spyod pa'i skur gshegs par mdzad
NK091(ke)001:18515: de snying po byang chub na bzhugs pa'i rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:18516: ril la bskul ba'i bya ba yang khyod kyis mdzod
NK091(ke)001:18518: dper na 'o ma mar gyi rang bzhin yang der
NK091(ke)001:18519: ma bzhag par bskul ba'i bya bas mar du 'gro
NK091(ke)001:18520: ba bzhin du sems can thams cad ye shes kyi
NK091(ke)001:18521: snying po can yin kyang der ma bzhag par snying
NK091(ke)001:18522: po bskul ba'i bya ba mdzod cig ces bskul ba'ang
NK091(ke)001:18528: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18529: ces de skad ces rnam par bskul bas /
NK091(ke)001:18530: dpe ji lta don ji ltar sprin gyi mthongsa nas
NK091(ke)001:18531: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor shar ba ltar mi g.yo ba
NK091(ke)001:18532: yid dbyings kyi ngang nyid las gzugs sku'i nyi ma
NK091(ke)001:18533: shar ba ste chos kyis mtho ba zhes bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:18534: gzhal yasa su 'gro 'ong dang 'char nub med par
NK091(ke)001:18535: smon lam dang thugs rje'i dbang gis rdo rje snying
NK091(ke)001:18536: po skyes bu de longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku chen
NK091(ke)001:18537: por rnam par snang bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:18538: zhes bskul ba'i rkyen gyis thugs dam gyi dbang gis dngos su bzhengs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:18539: 'dis sku tha dad 'dul ba bzhin snang bar byas
NK091(ke)001:18540: nas lam zhing khams sbyong ba rdzogs par 'gyur bas
NK091(ke)001:18541: lan tha ma'o // le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK091(ke)001:18542: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:18543: skyes bu rdo rje snying po gang gi thugs rje'i
NK091(ke)001:18544: cho 'phrul gyis shig par bskul ba'i lee'u zhes bya
NK091(ke)001:18545: ba ste nyi shu rtsa gsum pa gsal bar bkrol
NK091(ke)001:18546: ba'o ////gnyis pa bka' bgros mdzad pa la gnyis te
NK091(ke)001:18547: / rdo rje go 'byed kyis mtshan mas sangs rgyas thams cad bsdus pa /
NK091(ke)001:18548: 'dus pa de rnams kyis bka' bgros mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:18553: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18555: de nas rmad du byung bas ston pa mchog ril
NK091(ke)001:18556: gyi bdag po chos kyi rgyal po tshogs gnyis yongs
NK091(ke)001:18557: su rdzogs shing dngos po gnyis la dmigs pa med
NK091(ke)001:18558: par longs spyod pa chen po de yis /
NK091(ke)001:18559: nyid kyi slob ma ru tra de thabs gang gis 'dul bar bgro ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:18560: rdo rje go 'byed yongs su bsdu ba'i brda mdzad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:18561: bka' bgros la spyan drangs pa'i phyir te /
NK091(ke)001:18562: sa ma dzah'i sgras thugs dam bskul zhing phyag g.yas
NK091(ke)001:18563: g.yon bkyed pa dang bsnol ba'i se gol ni 'byed
NK091(ke)001:18564: sdud kyi mtshan ma ste phyag rgya de mdzad pas
NK091(ke)001:18565: mtha' thug pa med pa'i zhing khamsa rnam dag stug
NK091(ke)001:18566: po bkod pa nas dpag tu med pa'i rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:18567: thams cad byon te gdul ba'i bka' bgros mdzad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18568: phyir kun nas yongs su 'dus par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:18571: snying po bskul ba'i bya ba mdzod //
NK091(ke)001:18574: bder gshegs rigs kyi bka' bgro ba /
NK091(ke)001:18575: rdo rje'i rigs kyi bka' bgro ba /
NK091(ke)001:18576: rin chen rigs kyi bka' bgro ba /
NK091(ke)001:18577: pad+ma'i rigs kyi bka' bgro ba /
NK091(ke)001:18578: las kyi rigs kyi bka' bgro ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:18584: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18585: spyan drangs nas byon pa de'i tshe bka' bgros pa de'i dus na /
NK091(ke)001:18586: zhing khams so so'i rgyal bas bka' bgros gsungs pa
NK091(ke)001:18587: so sor bstan pa'i phyir 'jig rten gyi khams gdung
NK091(ke)001:18588: ba sel ba zhes bya ba na bzhugs pa'i de
NK091(ke)001:18589: bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi sangs rgyas snying rje yongs
NK091(ke)001:18590: su rol pa'i tshogs kyi rgyal ba rnams kyis gti
NK091(ke)001:18591: mug can tshar gcod pa'i don du dgongs pa gcig
NK091(ke)001:18592: tu mthun par bka' bgros pa /
NK091(ke)001:18593: kye kye zhes rgyal ba rnams la bod nas bka'
NK091(ke)001:18594: bgros la 'dus pa'i sangs rgyas rnam pa mang po'i
NK091(ke)001:18595: tshogs rnams gdul byar snang ba'i ngo bo kun tu
NK091(ke)001:18596: rmongs shing rab tu gtum pa dus 'dir byung ba
NK091(ke)001:18597: srid pa gsum po log par bsgyur ba'i gdug pa
NK091(ke)001:18598: can mtshan nyid ci 'dra ba'i rgyu 'bras 'khor ba'i
NK091(ke)001:18599: sa bon bdag 'dzin rtsub mosa 'phangs te kun nas
NK091(ke)001:18600: 'khrugs pa'i sdug bsngal chen po'i mnar bas yi dwags
NK091(ke)001:18601: kyi sde dpon srid pa rnams dbang du sdud pa
NK091(ke)001:18602: nyid las kyis dbang gis 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir
NK091(ke)001:18603: byung ba gang gsang sngags kyi brtul zhugs drag po
NK091(ke)001:18604: log par spyad pa'i dka' thub kyis mthus srid pa
NK091(ke)001:18605: gsum gyi bdag por smin pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:18606: de'i spyod yul gzhan la gnod pas dregs pa ru
NK091(ke)001:18607: tra'i gdug pa'i dbal gyis 'gro ba rnams rtag chad
NK091(ke)001:18608: la sogs pa'i mthar lhung nas rgyud rlog cing 'jomsa
NK091(ke)001:18609: par byed pa 'di nyid btul ba'i dgos pa thabs
NK091(ke)001:18610: kyis gdul ba'i zhing mchog rmad du byung ste /
NK091(ke)001:18611: des na snying rje'i bdag po rgyal ba kun 'dus nas bka' bgros kyis btul te /
NK091(ke)001:18612: lasa ngan las kyi rgyun bcad de /
NK091(ke)001:18613: bde ba chen po'i sa la bzhag par rigsa so //
NK091(ke)001:18620: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18621: sangs rgyas rdo rje'i rigs kyi gtso bo gdung dang
NK091(ke)001:18622: 'khor sde'i tshogs kyi rgyal ba rnams kyis zhe sdang
NK091(ke)001:18623: can tshar gcod pa'i don du dgongs pa gcig tu
NK091(ke)001:18625: kye ma'o zhes bos nas bka' bgros la 'dus pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18626: sangs rgyas rnams gdul bya'i ngo bo 'adsa pa'i dus
NK091(ke)001:18627: na sngon byung ba ltar da lta dus 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:18628: du yang byung la mtshan nyid ci 'dra ba'i rgyu
NK091(ke)001:18629: 'bras gsang sngags ji bzhin pa'i lunga don log par
NK091(ke)001:18630: go ba'i brtul zhugs dang mngon pa'i nga rgyal gyi
NK091(ke)001:18631: ri bora brtsegs pa'i dbang gis zhe sdang gis rang
NK091(ke)001:18632: rgyud bsregs cing gzhan la gnod pa'i blo yis bslad
NK091(ke)001:18633: pa can de'i spyod yul bdud kyis byin gyis brlab
NK091(ke)001:18634: pa yi mthus glang chen myos pa dang 'dra ba'i
NK091(ke)001:18635: drag po gtum rngam che ba nyid 'dul ba'i dgos
NK091(ke)001:18636: pa gal te ma bsgral na shin tu mi bzad
NK091(ke)001:18637: pa'i dug chen gyis kun nas bslang ba'i las ngan
NK091(ke)001:18638: gyis 'o dod 'bod pa'i dmyal bar sems can mang
NK091(ke)001:18639: po basda cing brlag par byed pas na bka' bgros
NK091(ke)001:18640: kyis gdul bar bskul ba ro gling gi dur khrod
NK091(ke)001:18641: kyi mthar zhen cing gnas pa la ji lta'i mthun
NK091(ke)001:18642: 'jug gi thabs kyis bsgral bas phan bde'i gnas bla
NK091(ke)001:18650: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18651: sangs rgyas nor bu'i rigs sam rin chen rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:18652: gtso bo gdung dang 'khor sde'i tshogs kyi rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:18653: rnams kyis nga rgyal can tshar gcod pa'i ched du
NK091(ke)001:18654: dgongs pa gcig tu mthun par bgros pa /
NK091(ke)001:18655: don gyi drug ka tshang yang ngo gsal ba gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:18656: gdul bya'i ngo bo lus nag po sems gdug pa smyon pa'i spyod pa can 'di /
NK091(ke)001:18657: spyod yul gzhan la gnod pa ji ltar kho rang
NK091(ke)001:18658: de gar bzhag par gyur na mi bzad pa'i dug
NK091(ke)001:18659: gi rgya mtsho'i chu rlabs kyis srid gsum nag po'i
NK091(ke)001:18660: khams su rgyas par 'gyur bas rnam 'dren dam pa
NK091(ke)001:18661: rnams kyi rgyun gcod cing ye shes snang bar byed
NK091(ke)001:18662: pa'i dam pa'i chos kyi nyi ma'i sgron ma 'jig
NK091(ke)001:18663: par 'gyur ro // de 'dul ba'i dgos pa ma
NK091(ke)001:18664: btul ba de yi tshe sdig pa'i las kyi mun
NK091(ke)001:18665: pa yis thams cad mun nag gi smag rum du
NK091(ke)001:18666: 'khyams par 'gyur bas bka' bgros kyis gdul bar rigs
NK091(ke)001:18667: par 'gyur ro // so // zhes bgros so //
NK091(ke)001:18673: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18674: sangsa rgyas pad+mo'i rigs kyi gtso bo gdung dang 'khor
NK091(ke)001:18675: sde'i tshogs kyi rgyal ba rnams kyis 'dod chags can
NK091(ke)001:18676: tshar gcod pa'i ched du dgongs pa dang mgrin gcig
NK091(ke)001:18677: tu mthun par bka' bgros pa /
NK091(ke)001:18679: mtshan nyid ci 'dra ba'i rgyu 'bras ganga 'das pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18680: dus na sngon byung ba yi las kyi 'khor losa
NK091(ke)001:18681: 'phangs pa yi blo gros phyin ci log pa'i ru
NK091(ke)001:18682: tra de nyid dpe ltar byung ba'i gdul bya'i ngo
NK091(ke)001:18683: bo sngon byung du snying po byang chub kyi gnas
NK091(ke)001:18685: sangs rgyas pa'i dbyings nas byung ba'i rgyal ba gang
NK091(ke)001:18686: dag ni skyes bu dam pas bdud btul ba'i sbyor
NK091(ke)001:18687: ba yis / bdud chen po'i tshul gyis bdud kyi
NK091(ke)001:18688: sde tshogs btul nas rig 'dzin gyi sa la nyer
NK091(ke)001:18689: zhes nye bar bkod pa ltar da ltar dus 'di
NK091(ke)001:18690: yi tsher yang byung ba yi rtsa ba dang nye
NK091(ke)001:18691: ba'i nyon mongs pa'am dug gsum dug lngas 'gyur bag
NK091(ke)001:18692: brtsegs pa'i ri bo 'di nyid bka' bgros kyis 'dul
NK091(ke)001:18693: bar bskul te rdo rje khros pa'i tho ba chen
NK091(ke)001:18694: po nyid kyis brlag cing gzhom pa'i dus la nges
NK091(ke)001:18695: ba yis / par baba bo // zhes bgros so //
NK091(ke)001:18700: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18701: sangs rgyas las kyi rigs sam gzhon nu'i rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:18702: gtso bo gdung dang 'khor sde'i tshogs kyi rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:18703: rnams kyis phrag dog can tshar gcod pa'i ched du
NK091(ke)001:18704: dgongs pa gcig tu mthun par bka' bgros pa /
NK091(ke)001:18705: 'dir yang ngo gsal ba lnga ste /
NK091(ke)001:18706: mtshan nyid ci 'dra ba'i rgyu 'bras bdag rtog gi
NK091(ke)001:18707: khong sran nang nas 'khyil ba'i dug chen po 'phel
NK091(ke)001:18708: bas thar pa med pa'i mi bzad pa'i nad kyis
NK091(ke)001:18709: zin pas rtag pa dang chad pa'i khams su shi
NK091(ke)001:18710: nas mtha'i g.yang sar lhung ba'i ro ru gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:18711: / gdul bya'i ngo bo lam phyin ci log tu
NK091(ke)001:18712: 'phyan nas yang dag pa'i lam stor ba'i dmus long
NK091(ke)001:18713: / 'di nyid / 'dul ba'i dgos pa ye shes
NK091(ke)001:18714: khros pa'i cho 'phrul las byung ba'i 'bar 'phro 'khrug
NK091(ke)001:18715: pa'i 'od zer chen po'i rtsal gyis 'khor ba'i smag
NK091(ke)001:18716: chen gyi mun nag drag po gtibs pa gzhom par
NK091(ke)001:18717: mdzad pa'i phyir bka' bgros kyis gdul bar bskul te
NK091(ke)001:18718: / 'di nyid / / kun mkhyen ye shes can
NK091(ke)001:18719: gyi spyod yul 'og min chos kyi dbyings nas rgyal
NK091(ke)001:18720: ba rgya mtsho kun 'dus te ye shes chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:18721: rdo rje khros pa yi ngang las khro bo'i cho
NK091(ke)001:18722: 'phrul sprin phung ltar 'thibsa pa yis ru tra rang
NK091(ke)001:18723: dang mthuna 'jug gi rol pa byis pa'i cha byad
NK091(ke)001:18724: dang 'dra ba'i tshul gyis drag po rnam par rol
NK091(ke)001:18725: pa'i mngona spyod kyis thabs las dug chen nyon mongs
NK091(ke)001:18726: 'khyil ba'i rgya mtsho ma bskams na /
NK091(ke)001:18727: 'dir ni snying rje byed pa rkyen dang 'tsham mama
NK091(ke)001:18728: ste mi 'tshams pas na chos nyid thugs rjer bzhengs
NK091(ke)001:18729: pa'i snying rje chen po yi gang gi dus 'dir
NK091(ke)001:18730: rkyen dang 'tshams pa'i snying rje'i dam tshig dam pa
NK091(ke)001:18731: mdzad pa'i phyir 'khor ba'i dngos po bzhi po bshad
NK091(ke)001:18732: pa dag 'dir spang du med de spyad pa las
NK091(ke)001:18733: rang grol du bzlog pa yi bstan pa mchog gi
NK091(ke)001:18734: 'od snang gsang ba dam pa spro bar mdzod cig
NK091(ke)001:18735: ces bgros so // de ltar bka' bgros 'di rnams
NK091(ke)001:18736: la bod nas gdul bya'i ngo bo dang mtshan nyid
NK091(ke)001:18738: de'i spyod yul gzhan la gnod pa /
NK091(ke)001:18740: bka' bgros kyis gdul ba drug tu don gyis 'grel
NK091(ke)001:18741: zhing ngo gsal ci rigs su bshad pa ltar shes
NK091(ke)001:18742: par bya'o // de bzhin du nyon mongs pa lngar
NK091(ke)001:18743: 'chad pa rnams kyang bshad pa ltar rjes su mthun
NK091(ke)001:18744: par bya'o // no // de ltar tshul lnga'i bgro bar mdzad pa'i rgyu mtshan yang /
NK091(ke)001:18746: mtha' thug med pa'i rgyal ba rnams //
NK091(ke)001:18747: re re'ang lnga lngar snang ba'i phyir //
NK091(ke)001:18748: rigs dang ye shes sku la sogs //
NK091(ke)001:18749: lnga lngas 'gro ba dgrol mdzad de //
NK091(ke)001:18750: gcig dang du mar mi dmigs kyang //
NK091(ke)001:18751: mos dang thugs rje smon lam mthus //
NK091(ke)001:18752: dpag tu med pa'i skye bo la //
NK091(ke)001:18753: bu gcig pa ltar rtag dgongs pa //
NK091(ke)001:18754: skyo dub bsnyel ba mi mnga' bar //
NK091(ke)001:18755: nam mkha'i mtha' ltar rtag bzhugs pa //
NK091(ke)001:18757: zhes gsungs pa la sogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:18759: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:18760: chos kyis mtho ba'i 'og min gyi gnas su byon
NK091(ke)001:18761: pa'i rgyal ba ril 'dus pa chen pos ru tra
NK091(ke)001:18762: gdul bar rnam par bka' bgros pa zhes bya ba'i
NK091(ke)001:18763: le'u ste nyi shu rtsa bzhi pa rnam par bshad
NK091(ke)001:18764: pa'o ////gsum pa bka' bgros bcad pa la gsum ste
NK091(ke)001:18765: / zhi rgyas kyis mi 'dul bar bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:18766: dbang drag gis 'dul bar rig pa /
NK091(ke)001:18767: rig nas bka' bgros bcad pa dngos po /
NK091(ke)001:18772: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18774: de ltar 'dus pa chen po'i bka' bgros pa yongs
NK091(ke)001:18775: su chad de gros thag chod nas gdul ba'i phrin
NK091(ke)001:18776: las la 'jug pa'i phyir las rnam pa bzhi gang
NK091(ke)001:18777: gisa 'dul ba'i skabs la bab par dgongs pa yis
NK091(ke)001:18778: gang de rnam par brtags pa'i dgos ched kyi phyir
NK091(ke)001:18779: dge slong thub dka' gzhon nu des snying po byang
NK091(ke)001:18780: chub tu son te mtshan rdo rje sems dpa' 'am
NK091(ke)001:18781: rdo rje snying pora gnas gyur pa nyid 'dir thugs
NK091(ke)001:18782: dam gyi dbang gis khyad par gyi gnyen por gyur
NK091(ke)001:18783: pa'i phyir de'i 'od zer gyi byin rlabs las sprul
NK091(ke)001:18784: pa thub pa'i dbang po'am sh+aakya thub pa snang bar
NK091(ke)001:18785: gyur nas de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyis sprul pa
NK091(ke)001:18786: de la yongs su bsgo ba /
NK091(ke)001:18787: thub pa'i dbang po ru tra 'dul ba'i phrin las la brtags pa'i dus 'di lags te /
NK091(ke)001:18788: zhi ba'i las kyis chos nyid ji bzhin du bden
NK091(ke)001:18789: pa'i byin rlabsa kyis ru tra'i 'khor ba'i dngos po
NK091(ke)001:18790: lnga tshan bzhi me dpung gis rgyud bsregs pa de
NK091(ke)001:18791: bden tshig gis bzlog la byang chub snying po yang
NK091(ke)001:18792: dag la bskul bar mdzod cig ces bka' stsal te
NK091(ke)001:18793: yongs su bskul nas sprul pa thub pa'i dbang po
NK091(ke)001:18794: des dur khrod kyi bdag po dregs pa de yi
NK091(ke)001:18795: phru mara zhes gnas kyi 'khor du snang bar mdzad
NK091(ke)001:18796: nas las rgyu 'bras kyi chos mi dge ba'i las
NK091(ke)001:18797: ma byed cig par bden tshig 'jam pas thams cada
NK091(ke)001:18798: zhi ba'i smra bar smras pa las dur khrod kyi
NK091(ke)001:18799: bdag po des tha'i kha brdabs pa zhes thal mo
NK091(ke)001:18800: rdeb cing skan sgra gtogs nas mi thul ba'i gtam
NK091(ke)001:18802: bu chung khyod kyis bdag thul ba ma yin te /
NK091(ke)001:18803: sngona nga gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon gzhan la gnod
