NK091(ke)001:18804: pa sbyin par byed pa dngos su ru tra rang
NK091(ke)001:18805: gi lus te ma tang ka ru tra drag po
NK091(ke)001:18806: zhes bya bar grags par gyur pa na khyod kho
NK091(ke)001:18807: na nyid lta bu mang po byung nas nga'i bstan
NK091(ke)001:18808: pa la zhugs shig /nga'i bka' nyon cig zer ba
NK091(ke)001:18810: da khyod kyi dbang du bdag ga la jen nam 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:18811: go zu se mo der gzod la rang gi dka'
NK091(ke)001:18812: thub la bde bar mnos shig ces bsgo nas bdud
NK091(ke)001:18813: kyi dngos po spyi'i dbang du 'dam gyi 'obs /
NK091(ke)001:18816: bslu byed kyi bu mo bzhis yongs su zhams zhes
NK091(ke)001:18817: pa bru sha'i skad de bod skad du btang zhes
NK091(ke)001:18819: 'dir dngos po bzhi kun gyis spang bya nyid yin
NK091(ke)001:18820: pas de dag gi spyod pa sh+aakya thub pa la
NK091(ke)001:18821: btang bas rgyal ba dri ma med pa gtsang ma
NK091(ke)001:18822: rigsa kyi 'phags pa nyid dngos po ngan par thugs
NK091(ke)001:18823: rtog pa la zhugs pa lta bur mdzad nas phyir
NK091(ke)001:18824: log go zhes slar bzhud pa ltar ru tra'i ngo
NK091(ke)001:18825: la snang ngo // des kyang zhi rgyas kyis mi 'dul bar mkhyen te 'chad do //
NK091(ke)001:18830: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18831: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rgyal ba thams cad
NK091(ke)001:18832: kyis yang sangs rgyas kun gyi pad+ma'i gdung dang sde'i
NK091(ke)001:18833: sprul pa kun tu thugs rje'i mnga' bdag 'phags pa
NK091(ke)001:18834: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la yongs su bskul te
NK091(ke)001:18835: bsgo ba / rgyal ba dbang gi bdag po kun
NK091(ke)001:18836: gyi chos nyid don gyi sku gsung pad+ma'i rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:18837: gdung 'tshob cing 'dzin pa chos kyi rgyal po'am rje
NK091(ke)001:18838: bo gsung gi don ji snyed pa mnga' bas 'od
NK091(ke)001:18839: dpag med pa rdo rje chos gdul bya thams cad
NK091(ke)001:18840: la thugs rje'i spyan ras kyis so dang bya ra
NK091(ke)001:18841: mdzad cing gzigs pa khyod kyis dbang gi sa bon
NK091(ke)001:18842: h+r+aiyig las shin tu rngam par byung ba'i khro bo
NK091(ke)001:18843: chen po'i tshul ston pas ngag gi dbang phyug rta
NK091(ke)001:18844: yi gdong ngam mgrin pa'i zhal gyis dregs pa ru
NK091(ke)001:18845: tra non zhing thul cig ces pa'am yang na rta
NK091(ke)001:18846: gdong zhal gyis non zhes dbu'i steng na rta mgo
NK091(ke)001:18847: yod pas rta gdong gi zhal gyis non pa khyod
NK091(ke)001:18848: kyis ru tra gnon cig cesa yongs su bskul bas
NK091(ke)001:18849: bsgo ba / / don gyis gsan te sprul pa
NK091(ke)001:18850: rdo rje rta yi gdong can sku mi bzad pa
NK091(ke)001:18851: chen poosa dur khrod kyi bdag po'i gnas su snang
NK091(ke)001:18852: bar mdzad nas rngam pa'i gad mo ha ha dgyes
NK091(ke)001:18853: pa'i gad mo hi hi dbang gi sa non h+r+aisku
NK091(ke)001:18854: gsung thugs kyis dbang du sdud pa hu lu hu
NK091(ke)001:18855: lu hu lu h'u zhes lhang lhang tser tser rta
NK091(ke)001:18856: skad drag po'i sgra dbyangs phyung ba las /
NK091(ke)001:18857: srin po'i 'khor tshogs phru ma rnams yongs su spa
NK091(ke)001:18858: zhum zhing bag 'khums pa tsam du gyur na yang
NK091(ke)001:18859: / dur khrod kyi bdag po ru tra kho na
NK091(ke)001:18860: ngo bo de rang gi che ba'i nga rgyal gyi
NK091(ke)001:18861: / gtum skad du / ru tra ma tra ma ra tra /
NK091(ke)001:18863: lus rnam par brjid phyung ste 'gyings pa las zil gyis ma non te /
NK091(ke)001:18864: slar yang ru tra kho na ngo bo des rta mgrin la bsgo ba /
NK091(ke)001:18865: mgrin bu sngon yang khyod lta bus bdag ma non pas /
NK091(ke)001:18866: khyod kyis bdag jen zhes thul ba ma yina te
NK091(ke)001:18867: rang nyid kyi gansa gang yin par bde bar mnosa
NK091(ke)001:18868: shig ces brjod nas tha'i kha brdab pa byas te
NK091(ke)001:18869: yang bdud kyi dngos po bzhis yongs su zhams pas
NK091(ke)001:18870: ru tras sngam bzhin mi gtsang bas gtsang ma rigsa
NK091(ke)001:18872: rtog pa skyes nas phyir log par 'gyur snyam pa las /
NK091(ke)001:18873: de bzhin gshegs pa dbang gis dbang du sdud pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18874: tshul ston pa nam mkha' lta bu la gtsang sme
NK091(ke)001:18875: mi mnga' nas khro bos 'dul phyir phyir ma log
NK091(ke)001:18876: par slar hen zhes pa bru sha'i skad de gam
NK091(ke)001:18878: ru tra kho na ngo bo des thim par dzamsa
NK091(ke)001:18879: zhes pa'ang bru sha'i skad de khong du mid nas
NK091(ke)001:18880: kha zas su mdzad pa na de bzhin gshegs pa
NK091(ke)001:18881: dag gi dbang phyug des de dang mthun 'jug tu
NK091(ke)001:18882: kho dga' ba ltar thim du han no zhes khong
NK091(ke)001:18884: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rta mgrin des dbu
NK091(ke)001:18885: yi rta mgo ru tra kho na'i spyi gtsug tu
NK091(ke)001:18886: phyung zhabs kho na'i rkang mthil du phyung nas rdo
NK091(ke)001:18887: rje h'u zhes brgyangs pas rta mgrin gyi sku lus
NK091(ke)001:18888: kun tu rgyas pas ru tra'i lus kyang kun tu
NK091(ke)001:18889: rgyas te / kho na des ma bzod pa'i nga ro 'o dod kyis sgra mthar bton pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:18891: ci mdzad myur bar mdzod la sgrol zhig ces gdung ba bton no //
NK091(ke)001:18892: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa des kho na de
NK091(ke)001:18893: yi las kyi sgrib pa sbyang bas tshogs lam dang
NK091(ke)001:18894: skal ba mnyam par mdzad nas /
NK091(ke)001:18895: sdug bsngal med par bde ba kho nar ru tra
NK091(ke)001:18896: kho na'i spyi gtsug tu phyungs te nam mkha' la
NK091(ke)001:18898: ru tra dang srin po'i tshogs rnams 'ur mer thor
NK091(ke)001:18899: shig tu gyur te zil gyis gnon cing bag 'khums
NK091(ke)001:18901: dpa' bo chen po khyed kyi 'bangs su mchi yis
NK091(ke)001:18902: ji ltar bgyi ba bka' stsol zhig /ces zhus te
NK091(ke)001:18903: btud pas de bzhin gshegs pa des gnyen po phyis
NK091(ke)001:18904: 'byung zhing drag pos 'dul ba'i lung bstan gsungs pa
NK091(ke)001:18905: / ngas ni khyod ma btul gyis khyod kyi gnyen
NK091(ke)001:18906: po rdo rje h'u ngam gnod sbyin zhes bya ba
NK091(ke)001:18907: / / de bzhiin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dbang gis dbang bskur ba /
NK091(ke)001:18908: shin tu sku gtum la gsung rngam zhing thugs 'khrugsa pa ma rungsa shing mi bzad pa /
NK091(ke)001:18909: bdud thams cad kyi yang bdud chen po /
NK091(ke)001:18911: de la skyabs su dong zhig /ces gsungs te 'og
NK091(ke)001:18912: min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du mi dmigs
NK091(ke)001:18913: par gshegs so // de ltar las gang gis 'dul
NK091(ke)001:18914: brtags pa las dngos su btul ba ma yin la
NK091(ke)001:18915: par gshegs so // / de la ma bzod pas
NK091(ke)001:18916: zhi rgyas kyis mi thul bar dbang drag gis 'dul
NK091(ke)001:18917: par gshegs so // / bar mkhyen no // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:18924: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18925: de nas gsang ba 'dus pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK091(ke)001:18926: de ltar 'dus pa chen po rnam par bgros nas
NK091(ke)001:18927: phrin las bzhi'i sgo gang gis 'dul ba'i skabs la
NK091(ke)001:18929: gang zhi rgyas kyis 'dula ba mi 'dra bar mkhyen nas /
NK091(ke)001:18930: dbang drag gis 'dul bar bka' bgros dam par mdzad
NK091(ke)001:18931: de mthun pa'am gnyen pos 'dul bar gros kyis nges
NK091(ke)001:18933: yongs su gsungs pa nii 'di lta ste /
NK091(ke)001:18934: zhes le'u gong ma dang 'di gnyis bka' bgros ldab pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:18935: gong ma spyir 'dul ba tsam dang /
NK091(ke)001:18936: 'di ni khyad par gyi las gang gis 'dul ba'i phyir mi 'gal lo //
NK091(ke)001:18939: ngo bo nyid kyi skus 'dul bar bcad pa /
NK091(ke)001:18941: sprul pa dang gsang ba'i skus 'dul bar bcad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:18946: ces nges pa dam par bcad do //
NK091(ke)001:18947: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:18948: de nasa de bzhin gshegs pa chos kyis sku rnam
NK091(ke)001:18949: grol spyod pa'i tshogs kyi mtshan de nyid du nges
NK091(ke)001:18950: pa ji snyed pa rnams kyis bka' bcad mdzad de
NK091(ke)001:18951: ru tra gdul thabs dang rjes 'jug gis gzhan don
NK091(ke)001:18952: spyod tshul ston pa'i mdo gsungs pa /
NK091(ke)001:18953: le'u nyer gcig pa ltar zhing khams 'dir dregs pa dang 'gro ba'i tshul 'di ltar du gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:18955: shina tu yang dag pa'i sems 'gog pas re zhig
NK091(ke)001:18956: gsal cha bral te mun pa'i zhi bar gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:18957: chud pa la / gdul thabs mi mthun pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:18958: gyis khrosa pas btul yang chad lta de las gtan
NK091(ke)001:18959: du mi ldog pas na phan par mi 'gyur te
NK091(ke)001:18960: chud pa la / / des na rgyal ba rnams kyi cha mthun gyi mdzad pa /
NK091(ke)001:18961: rnal 'byor ma bcos pa'i mnyam pa chen po'i ngang
NK091(ke)001:18962: de nyid las mthun pas 'dul bas zhi ba chen
NK091(ke)001:18963: po'i rnam par de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyis mdzod
NK091(ke)001:18965: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyi
NK091(ke)001:18966: tshul can nyan thos rnams kyis chos kyi bdag med
NK091(ke)001:18967: ma rtogs par 'gog pa zhi ba phyogs gcig pas
NK091(ke)001:18968: kyang srid pa'i rtse mo man chad kyi sa bon
NK091(ke)001:18969: spangs te 'khor ba'i myu gu 'gog par nus na
NK091(ke)001:18970: gsang ba'i rnal 'byor yod med kyi mtha' gnyis po
NK091(ke)001:18971: zhi bas stong pa'i chos nyid chen po rtogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18972: mthus yang dag pa'i sems 'gog ste mun par zhi
NK091(ke)001:18973: ba de las bslang bar mdzad pas don grub pa
NK091(ke)001:18975: de bas ru tra lta bu gdul bya shin tu
NK091(ke)001:18976: ma rungs pa byang chub sems kyi myu gu sngo
NK091(ke)001:18977: skams su gyur pa de thugs rje'i chu bos rlan
NK091(ke)001:18978: par mdzad pa la mun pa'i khams gang du re
NK091(ke)001:18979: zhig tshogs drug 'gog pa rnams bslang bar byed pa'i
NK091(ke)001:18980: dgos ched kyi phyir gnyen pos 'dul ba gang yang
NK091(ke)001:18981: 'gog pa med par stong pa'i chos nyid ma 'dres
NK091(ke)001:18982: yongs rdzogs kyi ngang las mdzad pa sna tshogs cir
NK091(ke)001:18983: yang mi 'gog par snang bas mthun pa'i yon tan
NK091(ke)001:18984: gyis gdul bya'i don ji lta ba bzhin du mdzod
NK091(ke)001:18985: cig ces rgyal ba rnams la bka' bgros te nges
NK091(ke)001:18989: cha mthun du mdzod cig par bskul ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:18990: mdzad pas don grub par the tshom mi za ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:18991: dgos ched dang mthun pa'i yon tan snang bas don
NK091(ke)001:18992: mdzod cig par bskur bar 'chad pa dag kyang rjes
NK091(ke)001:18993: su 'grel to // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:18994: ngo bo nyid med pas 'dul bar bcad pa /
NK091(ke)001:18995: ngo bo nyid mi 'gyur bas gdul bar bcad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:19000: ces nges pa dam par bcad do //
NK091(ke)001:19001: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19002: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa ngo bo nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:19003: sku spros pa med pa'i tshogs kyis chad lta bzlog
NK091(ke)001:19004: cig par bka' bcad mdzad pa'i mdo gsungs pa /
NK091(ke)001:19005: gdul bya las dang 'bras bus shin tu stong par
NK091(ke)001:19006: lta ba byang chub kyi bsam pa rgyun chad pa
NK091(ke)001:19007: can la gdul thabs mi mthun pa'i tshul gyis dngos
NK091(ke)001:19008: posa btul yang lta ngan de las gtan du mi
NK091(ke)001:19009: ldog pas na phan par mi 'gyur te sngar bshad
NK091(ke)001:19010: pa ltar rgyun gyi byang chub chen po mtha' bral
NK091(ke)001:19011: stong pa nyid las mthun pas 'dul ba med rgyur
NK091(ke)001:19012: btags chags kyi rnam par de bzhin gshegs pa kun
NK091(ke)001:19013: gyis mdzod cig / 'dul ba'i tshad byang chub sems
NK091(ke)001:19014: dpa'i mdo sde don dam par spros pa kun dang
NK091(ke)001:19015: bral ba'i stong pa nyid kyi tshul can de yis
NK091(ke)001:19016: sngags kyi stong pa chen po ma mthong yang cha
NK091(ke)001:19017: 'dra bar mthong ba'i stong pa gang gi nus pas
NK091(ke)001:19018: kyang dngos snang ci yang med par gnas par 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:19019: gyis mdzod cig / na / skye ba med pa
NK091(ke)001:19020: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings las rang byung
NK091(ke)001:19021: ba'i rnal 'byor mthar thug stong pa chen po'i mathus
NK091(ke)001:19022: mthar zad chad par lta ba'i mu la gnas pa
NK091(ke)001:19023: las bzlog par nus pa smos ci dgos te /
NK091(ke)001:19024: de bas na dgos pa shin tu stong pa rgyun
NK091(ke)001:19025: chad du lta ba bzlog pa dang gang du med
NK091(ke)001:19026: pa'i rgyu las btags par chags shing sgrubs pa grub
NK091(ke)001:19027: par bskyed pa'i phyir gnyen pos 'dul ba mthun pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19028: yon tan rgyun dang bcas pa'i stong pa nyid chen
NK091(ke)001:19029: po las che ba'i yon tan rgyun mi chad par
NK091(ke)001:19030: 'gyur bas gdul bya'i don mdzod cig /ces nges pa
NK091(ke)001:19036: ces nges pa dam par bcad do //
NK091(ke)001:19037: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19038: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa ngo bo nyid sku
NK091(ke)001:19039: rang bzhin mi 'gyur ba'i tshogs kyi mtshan dang rigs
NK091(ke)001:19040: de nyid du nges pa'i rgyal ba rnams kyis bka'
NK091(ke)001:19041: bcad mdzad de rtag lta las bzlog pa'i mdo gsungs
NK091(ke)001:19042: pa / gdul bya gang zag gi bdag shin tu
NK091(ke)001:19043: ther zug tu zhen cing rtag par lta ba la
NK091(ke)001:19044: pa / / gdul thabs mi mthun pa'i tshul gyis
NK091(ke)001:19045: med pa'i stong pa bstan pas lta ngan gtan du
NK091(ke)001:19046: mi ldog pas na phan para mi 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:19047: cha mthun gyi tshul du snying po byang chub de
NK091(ke)001:19048: nyid kyi ngang las gnyis med bdag nyid chen por
NK091(ke)001:19049: thams cad du mthun pas 'dul bar mdzod cig /
NK091(ke)001:19050: 'dul ba'i tshad 'gro ba rnams kyis zhen pa rdzas
NK091(ke)001:19051: can du lta ba mthu brtas pas mi 'gyur ba'i
NK091(ke)001:19052: tshul can rtag pas kyang dngos po brtan g.yor snang
NK091(ke)001:19054: ye nas 'pho 'gyur med par bdag nyid chen por
NK091(ke)001:19055: lhun gyis grub pa mngon du byas pa'i mthusa rtag
NK091(ke)001:19056: pa ther zug tu log par lta ba de las
NK091(ke)001:19057: bzlog par nus pa smos ci dgos te /
NK091(ke)001:19058: de bas bdag tu zhen pa bzlog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:19059: dngos por 'dzin pa'i rka mgo bsgyur ba'i dgos pa'i phyira /
NK091(ke)001:19060: gnyen pos 'dul ba mthun pa'i yon tan lhun grub
NK091(ke)001:19061: bdag med chen po 'gyur med rtag pa'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:19062: las bya ba dang byed pa med par rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:19063: ngang du phebs pas snying po byang chub nyid du
NK091(ke)001:19064: mthar phyin pa'i don mdzod cig /ces gdul ba'i thabs
NK091(ke)001:19065: mchog tu nges pa dam par bcad do //
NK091(ke)001:19067: rdo rje'i rigs kyis bka' 'gros bcad pa /
NK091(ke)001:19068: rigs kyi bdag pos bka' bgros bcad pa /
NK091(ke)001:19069: rin chen rigs kyis bka' bgros bcad pa /
NK091(ke)001:19070: las kyi rigs kyis bka' bgros bcad pa /
NK091(ke)001:19071: de bzhin rigs kyis bka' bgros bcad pa /
NK091(ke)001:19072: pad+ma'i rigs kyis bka' bgros bcad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:19077: ces nges pa dam par bcad do //
NK091(ke)001:19078: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19079: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje'i rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:19080: gdung dang sde'i tshogs kyis gnas ngan gyi rgyu zhe
NK091(ke)001:19081: sdang las bzlog cig par bka' bcad pa'i mdo gsungs
NK091(ke)001:19082: pa / gdul bya shin tu gdug cing gtum pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19083: las kyi ngu 'bod kyi na rag tu ltung ba
NK091(ke)001:19084: la gdul thabs mi mthun pa'i tshul gyis zhi bas
NK091(ke)001:19085: btul yang phan par mi 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:19086: cha dang mthun pa stong pa shes rab dang snang
NK091(ke)001:19087: ba thabs kyi ngo bo khro bo 'jigs pa'i rnam
NK091(ke)001:19088: par de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyis mdzod cig /de
NK091(ke)001:19090: las kyi dbang gis khro bo'i tshul can ye shes chen pos snang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:19091: thugs rje chen por bzhengs pa dang cha 'dra ba ru tra lta bu khros pasa mthus kyang /
NK091(ke)001:19092: 'jig rten srid pa gsum gyi 'gro ba mtha' daga sgrag par byed nus na /
NK091(ke)001:19093: yang dag pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi ye shes dang thugs rje chen po khros pa yis /
NK091(ke)001:19094: khams gsum ma lus pa bsgral bar mdzad pas don grub pa smos ci dgos pas so //
NK091(ke)001:19095: de bas na dgos ched gdul dka' ma lus pa
NK091(ke)001:19096: 'dul ba dang dam tshig can la sdang ba rnams
NK091(ke)001:19097: sgrib pa rnam par sbyang ba'i phyir mthun pa dang
NK091(ke)001:19098: gnyen po gnyis kas 'bar ba chen po khro bo'i
NK091(ke)001:19099: gar dgu las / dur khrod gar gyi phyag rgyar
NK091(ke)001:19100: bzhengs par mdzod cig /ces ngesa pa dam par bcad
NK091(ke)001:19101: gar dgu las / do // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:19102: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rdo rje snying po /
NK091(ke)001:19105: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19106: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa rigs kyi bdag po
NK091(ke)001:19107: rdo rje snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK091(ke)001:19108: zhes bya ba'i tshogs kyi mtshan dang rigs de nyid
NK091(ke)001:19109: kyi bdag po rdo rje sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun
NK091(ke)001:19110: gyi dge ba'i bshes gnyen nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:19111: de rnams kyis lam log par 'phyan pa mthun 'jug
NK091(ke)001:19112: gi thabs kyis 'dul bar bka'a bcad pa'i mdo gsungs
NK091(ke)001:19113: pa / gdul bya ma log pa'i bstan pa la
NK091(ke)001:19114: zhugs kyang shin tu log par zhen nas rang 'thad
NK091(ke)001:19115: la spyad pas mnar med pa'i dmyal bar lhung nges
NK091(ke)001:19116: pa la gnyen po mi mthun pa bdena tshig 'jam
NK091(ke)001:19117: pos bkrol bas phan par mi 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:19118: cha mthun gyi mdzad pa de kho na nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:19119: theg pa gsang ba chen po bstan zhing brtags par
NK091(ke)001:19120: dka' ba de la sbyor ba'i brda sna tshogs dang
NK091(ke)001:19121: ldem po bzhi dang dgongs pa bzhi yi thabs mang
NK091(ke)001:19122: po las 'dir ni thams cad mthun 'jug gis 'dul
NK091(ke)001:19123: thabs kyis yang dag pa nyid du nges par mdzoda
NK091(ke)001:19124: cig / 'dul ba'i tshad theg pa chen po gsang
NK091(ke)001:19125: sngags kyi phrin las dang mtshungs pa'i mdzad spyod kyi
NK091(ke)001:19126: tshul can dngos po bzhi la rang 'thad du spyad
NK091(ke)001:19127: pas kyang 'gro ba thams cad bka' yi don ji
NK091(ke)001:19128: bzhin pa las bzlog nas log par bskyur bar byed
NK091(ke)001:19129: nus pa ru tra'i spyod pa lta bur yang srid
NK091(ke)001:19130: cig / na / rgyal ba rnams kyi yang dag
NK091(ke)001:19131: pa'i thugs rje dang thabs la mkhas pas mthun 'jug
NK091(ke)001:19132: gi mdzad spyod kyis lam log pa rnams drang por
NK091(ke)001:19133: srong nus pa smos ci dgos te /
NK091(ke)001:19134: de bas na dper chang gis chang nad bsal ba
NK091(ke)001:19135: lta bur dngos posa dngos po grol bar mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:19136: dang / de nyid kyis de nyid 'joms pa lta
NK091(ke)001:19137: bur dug gisa dug nad lnga po bsal ba'i dgos
NK091(ke)001:19138: ched kyi phyir mthun pa dang gnyen po gnyis kas
NK091(ke)001:19139: rmad du byung ba'i thabs mchog dpag gisa mi lang
NK091(ke)001:19140: ba'i sgo nas mdzad pa gar gyi phyag rgyar bzhengs
NK091(ke)001:19141: la gdul bar mdzod cig /ces nges pa dam par
NK091(ke)001:19142: dang / bcad do // gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:19143: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa nor bu'i /
NK091(ke)001:19146: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19147: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa nora bu'i rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:19148: gdung dang sde'i tshogs kyis brkam chags can gshin rje'i
NK091(ke)001:19149: 'jig rten las dgrol bar bka' bcad pa'i mdo gsungs
NK091(ke)001:19150: pa / gdul bya zas nor la shin tu 'jungs
NK091(ke)001:19151: shing brkam pa'i las kyis yi dwags gshin rjer ltung
NK091(ke)001:19152: bar nges pa la sbyin pa btang bas phan par
NK091(ke)001:19153: pa / mi 'gyur te / mthun pas don la
NK091(ke)001:19154: sbyor ba dngos po med la yon tan mi zad
NK091(ke)001:19155: par phyogs kun nas 'byung ba las chos thams cad
NK091(ke)001:19156: la dbang bsgyur te mi zad pa nor bu lta
NK091(ke)001:19157: bura mdzod cig /de ci'i phyir na /
NK091(ke)001:19158: dka' thub can gyi sdom pa'i cha dang mtshungs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19159: tshul can ser sna mchog tu che bas nor rdzas
NK091(ke)001:19160: sdom ste gzhan la gtong ba'i sgo 'gagsa pas kyang
NK091(ke)001:19161: / nor ma btang ba de'i stobs kyis rang nyid
NK091(ke)001:19162: tshe gcig gi bar du 'tsho zhing gnas par byed
NK091(ke)001:19163: / nus na / rgyal ba nam mkha'i mdzod mnga'
NK091(ke)001:19164: med la 'dod rgur 'byung ba la dbang bsgyur ba
NK091(ke)001:19165: yisa khams gsum gyi gdung ba bsal nus pa smos
NK091(ke)001:19167: de bas na mthun pas 'dul ba ser snas 'jungs pa tshim par bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:19168: gnyen pos 'dul ba 'dod pas yongs su gdung ba
NK091(ke)001:19169: bsal ba'i phyir 'dul thabs gnyis kas theg chen gsang
NK091(ke)001:19170: ba dam pa'i thabs la mkhas pa'i longs spyod las
NK091(ke)001:19171: / mi zad nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgyar bzhengs
NK091(ke)001:19172: la 'dul bar mdzod cig /ces rkam chags can thul
NK091(ke)001:19173: zhig par nges pa dam par bacada do //
NK091(ke)001:19175: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa gzhon nu'i /
NK091(ke)001:19178: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19179: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa gzhon nu'i rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:19180: gdung dang sde'i tshogs kyis snyoms las can thul zhig
NK091(ke)001:19181: par bka' bcad pa'i mdo gsungs pa /
NK091(ke)001:19182: gdul bya shin tu le lo dang rnam g.yeng che
NK091(ke)001:19183: bas mi khom pa brgyad du 'khyams par 'gyur ba
NK091(ke)001:19184: la / thar pa la bskul bas brtson par mi 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:19185: mthun pas 'dul ba bya brtsal med pa'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:19186: kyi ngang las thams cad du bya ba med pa
NK091(ke)001:19187: ngang gi thabs kyis gdul bar mdzod cig /
NK091(ke)001:19188: 'dul ba'i tshad mi g.yo ba'i bsam gtan bya rtsol
NK091(ke)001:19189: dang bral ba'i tshul dang mtshungs pa can snyoms las
NK091(ke)001:19190: 'dzin pa'i le lo la gnas te lam la bya
NK091(ke)001:19192: thar pa dam pa'i las lam gcod de brlag par byed nus na /
NK091(ke)001:19193: bya ba dang bral bar yang dag pa'i don las
NK091(ke)001:19194: mi g.yo ba'i 'pho med bde ba chen posa 'jig
NK091(ke)001:19195: rten gyi le los g.yenga ba bzlog nus pa smos
NK091(ke)001:19196: ci dgos te / de bas na dgos ched 'bras
NK091(ke)001:19197: bu bcom pa mthun pa'i cha mi khom pa'i las
NK091(ke)001:19199: rgyu gzhom pa gnyen po'i cha le lo g.yeng ba'i dgra dpung gzhom pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:19200: gnyen pos 'dul ba mthun pa'i yon tan /
NK091(ke)001:19201: phyogs ris med pa'i btang snyoms kyi rnal 'byor chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:19202: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa bya ba med pa'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:19203: la gnas par nges pa'i phyag rgyar bzhengs te mdzad
NK091(ke)001:19204: pa dam pa mdzod cig /ces nges pa dam par
NK091(ke)001:19206: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa glang po'i /
NK091(ke)001:19209: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19210: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa glang po'i rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:19211: gdung dang sde'i tshogs kyis gti mug can 'dul bar
NK091(ke)001:19212: bka' bcad pa'i mdo gsungs pa /
NK091(ke)001:19213: gdul bya shin tu gti mug che zhing rmongs par gyur pa byol song du ltung ba'i rigs la /
NK091(ke)001:19214: gnyen po'i chos bstan pas shes shing go bar mi 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:19215: mthun pas 'dul ba khyad par cir yang 'byed pa
NK091(ke)001:19216: med par mtshungs pa las thams cad chos nyid la
NK091(ke)001:19217: dbye bsal med pa'i gti mug chen pora mdzod cig
NK091(ke)001:19218: / 'dul ba'i tshad yang dag pa'i gti mug dang
NK091(ke)001:19219: mtshungs pa'i tshul can rmongs pa ma rig pa chen
NK091(ke)001:19221: dus gsum thams cad du yang dag pa'i don mi mthong ba'i mun par 'phyan par byed nus na /
NK091(ke)001:19222: mi dmigs 'byed pa med pa mnyam nyid chen po
NK091(ke)001:19223: blang dor med pa yis dgongs pa dam pas khams
NK091(ke)001:19224: gsum gyi rmongs pa thams cad bsal bar nus pa
NK091(ke)001:19226: de bas na gnyen po'i chas mun pa'i skye mched gzhom pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:19227: mthun pas 'dul ba rmongsa pa rang dag nam mkhar
NK091(ke)001:19228: bya ba'i dgos pa'i phyir thabs kyi gnyen po gti
NK091(ke)001:19229: mug rnam par dag pa'i ye shes las /
NK091(ke)001:19230: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi phyag rgyar bzhengs te gdul
NK091(ke)001:19231: bar mdzod cig /ces nges pa dam par bcad do
NK091(ke)001:19233: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa pad+mo'i /
NK091(ke)001:19236: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19237: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa pad+mo'i rigs kyi gdung
NK091(ke)001:19238: dang sde'i tshogs kyis 'dod chags can thul zhig par
NK091(ke)001:19239: bka' bcad pa'i mdo gsungs pa /
NK091(ke)001:19240: gdul bya shin tu chags shing zhen pa mngal gyi srin bur ltung bar 'gyur ba'i rigs la /
NK091(ke)001:19241: chags pa spong ba'i thabs kyi gnyen pos phan bar mi 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:19242: mthun pas 'dul ba chags med chags pa'i shes rab chen po'i ye shes las /
NK091(ke)001:19243: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad yab yum rol pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19244: chags pa chen por snang bar mdzod cig /de ci'i
NK091(ke)001:19245: phyir na / chags med chags pa'i tshul can yang
NK091(ke)001:19246: dag pa'i sbyor ba dang cha 'dra ba log pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19247: 'dod chags su la yod pa des chags pa spyod
NK091(ke)001:19248: pasa stobs kyis kyang khams gsum gyi grong khyer thams
NK091(ke)001:19249: cad shin tu zhen pas mi 'bral bar 'dod chags
NK091(ke)001:19250: khrag tu 'khyil ba'i rgya mtshor byed nus na /
NK091(ke)001:19251: rgyal ba rnams kyis 'dod chags rnam par dag pa'i ngang las chagsa pa'i tshul du spyad pas /
NK091(ke)001:19252: khams gsum gyi zhen chags thams cad bsal bar nus pa smos ci dgos pas so //
NK091(ke)001:19253: de bas na dgos ched gnyen po'i cha 'doda chags khrag mtsho bskam pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:19254: mthun pa'i chas chags pas chags pa gcod pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:19255: mthun pa dang gnyen po gnyis kas 'dul ba 'dod
NK091(ke)001:19256: chags rnam par dag pa'i ye shes chen po'i ngang
NK091(ke)001:19257: las / 'doda chagsa gar gyi phyag rgyar bzhengs te
NK091(ke)001:19258: mdzad pa'i rol mo mdzoda cig /ces nges pa dam
NK091(ke)001:19259: las / par bcad do // de ltar bka' bgros
NK091(ke)001:19260: bcad pa dgu po le'u nyer gcig pa dang bsdeb
NK091(ke)001:19261: las / par bcad do // la bshad do // bzhi pa la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:19263: mdzad pa thabs kyi spyod pa mtha' yas pas 'dul ba /
NK091(ke)001:19264: skabs 'dir ni gnyen pos btul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:19269: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19270: de nas de bzhin gshegsa pa sprul pa'i sku dang
NK091(ke)001:19271: gsang ba'i sku thams cad kyis mthun 'jug gi mdzad
NK091(ke)001:19272: pa mtha' yas pa'i tshul gyis skabs kyi gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:19273: drag pos 'dul bar bka' bacada pa'i mdo gsungs pa
NK091(ke)001:19274: / gdul bya shin tu gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i dngos por zhen cing 'thas pa la /
NK091(ke)001:19275: 'dul thabs de dang mi mthun par gnyen pos bkag
NK091(ke)001:19276: pasa gtan du ldog mi nus pas phan par mi
NK091(ke)001:19277: 'gyur te / ji lta bas 'dul na spyod pa
NK091(ke)001:19278: rjes 'jug dang mthun par dbyings shes raba dang ye
NK091(ke)001:19279: shes thabs kyi ngo bo las snang bar mdzad nas
NK091(ke)001:19280: 'gyur te / / phrin las thams cad gdul bya
NK091(ke)001:19281: dang mthun 'jug tu sbyor ba'i spyod par mdzod cig
NK091(ke)001:19283: spyod pa rang kha ma log par 'tsho bas gang
NK091(ke)001:19284: dga' dga' la spyod pa lta bu ni /
NK091(ke)001:19285: yang dag pa'i mthun 'jug gi thabs kyi spyod pa
NK091(ke)001:19286: dang tshul 'dra ba can du cha mthun par log
NK091(ke)001:19287: lta rang rgyud can la zhen te rang 'thad du
NK091(ke)001:19288: spyad pas kyang khams gsum gyi grong khyer na gnas
NK091(ke)001:19289: pa'i 'gro ba thams cad lam log para byed nus
NK091(ke)001:19290: na / yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs
NK091(ke)001:19291: rje sprul pa'i gar gyi mdzad spyod kyis 'jig rten
NK091(ke)001:19292: pa blo log pa rnams drang bar mdzad pas don
NK091(ke)001:19293: grub pa smos ci dgos te the tshom gyi gnas
NK091(ke)001:19294: na / ma mchis pas / dgos ched dang mthun
NK091(ke)001:19295: par yon tan snang bar mdzod cig ces bskul ba'o
NK091(ke)001:19296: na / ma mchis pas / // gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:19297: thabs sna tshogs kyis don la drang bar bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:19298: de 'gro ba'i rig pa la lhun gyis grub pa /
NK091(ke)001:19299: ji ltar mos pa ltar don mdzod cig pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:19304: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19305: de la sogs pa zhes snga ma rnams la snyegs pas dngos po gzhan bsdu ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:19306: thabs kyi spyod pa snga ma dang phyi mar bstan
NK091(ke)001:19307: pa'i 'dul byed mtha' yas pa snyed kyis gdul bya'i
NK091(ke)001:19308: 'jig rten ji snyed pa khams dbang bsam pa mtha'
NK091(ke)001:19309: yas pa'i rigs can kun 'dul ba'i thabs ni mngal
NK091(ke)001:19310: yangs pa sna tshogsa kyis gdul zhing lam du drangs
NK091(ke)001:19311: te yang dag pa'i gnas lugs gsang sngags ji bzhin
NK091(ke)001:19312: pa'i don la sbyor bar byos shig /ces mdor bstan
NK091(ke)001:19313: nas / de'i tshul rgyas par gsungs pa /
NK091(ke)001:19314: de'ang gdul bya khro ba can la shas chung na gnyen po byams pas 'dul ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:19315: drag por gyur nas mthun pas gdul ba khro bo'i
NK091(ke)001:19316: tshul du mdzoda cig /de bzhin du zhi ba'i rigs
NK091(ke)001:19317: la zhi ba'i gdams pas bkrol te lhag mthong gi
NK091(ke)001:19318: rtsal slong nas don la sbyor ba nyid kyis 'dul
NK091(ke)001:19319: la / gdul bya drag shul can la byams pa'am
NK091(ke)001:19320: yang na drag po 'ba' zhig nyid kyis gdul lo
NK091(ke)001:19321: la / // g.yem pa can la shas chung na
NK091(ke)001:19322: mthun par g.yem pa nyid dang shas che na mi
NK091(ke)001:19323: tshangs spyod kyi gnyen pora gyur pa'i thabs kyis gdul
NK091(ke)001:19324: bar mdzod cig /srid pa'i dngos por chagas pa can
NK091(ke)001:19325: la mthun pa chagas pa rang dang mi mthun pa
NK091(ke)001:19326: gnyen pos rnam par spong ba nyid kyis 'dul la
NK091(ke)001:19327: la / // / gdul bya rnam g.yeng can la
NK091(ke)001:19328: gnyen po semsa sdud pa dang mthun pa g.yeng ba
NK091(ke)001:19330: gti mug gis rmongs pa la gnyen po'i khyad par
NK091(ke)001:19331: gyis 'dul ba rnam par 'byed pa'i shes rab skyed
NK091(ke)001:19332: pa dang mthun pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang gis
NK091(ke)001:19333: thul zhig /nga rgyal gyi ri bo can la gnyen
NK091(ke)001:19334: pos zhi ba ting nge 'dzin dang mthun pas 'dul
NK091(ke)001:19335: ba ri bo nyid kyi tshul gyis dgrol lo //
NK091(ke)001:19336: gdul bya phrag dog can la mthun pa phrag doga
NK091(ke)001:19337: gi tshul gyis mnyam pa'i dbyings la sbyor te gdul
NK091(ke)001:19338: bar bya'o // de ltar rgyud las /
NK091(ke)001:19339: ji ltar rna bar chu song ba //
NK091(ke)001:19340: slar yang chu gzhan dag gis dbyung //
NK091(ke)001:19341: zhes pa la sogsa pa ltar thabs mu mtha'a yas par 'dren pa ji snyed kyis thul zhig pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:19346: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19347: ye don gyi kun gzhi snying po byang chub kyi
NK091(ke)001:19348: dbyings mnyam pa bde bar gshegs pa dang mi mnyam
NK091(ke)001:19349: pa 'khor ba'i dngos po ril la khyab pas bdag
NK091(ke)001:19350: nyid mu mtha' med pa'i nam mkha' dbyings kyi mtha'
NK091(ke)001:19351: klas par ngang gis rang shar ba'i tshul gyis gang
NK091(ke)001:19352: nas gang du bsnums par rang rang gi khyad par
NK091(ke)001:19353: gyi snang ba zhen pa dang ma bral ba'i ting
NK091(ke)001:19354: nge 'dzin dang khams gsum gyi 'doda pa dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:19355: pa'i yid dang 'byung ba'i phung po dang ldan pas
NK091(ke)001:19356: lus can gyi 'gro ba rnams kyis snang sems kun
NK091(ke)001:19357: gyi gzhi tha snyad gnyis kyi chos kuna gyi ngo
NK091(ke)001:19358: bo rang bzhin gyi dbyings na rang rig par gsal
NK091(ke)001:19359: te / gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi dpal /
NK091(ke)001:19361: thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal gsum gyi bdag nyid chen
NK091(ke)001:19362: por rdo rje snying po byang chub kyi sems thabs
NK091(ke)001:19363: dang mdzad pa thams cad lhun gyis grub par ye
NK091(ke)001:19365: 'di yis ngo bo nyid kyis don byed par gsal te /
NK091(ke)001:19366: rgyas par ye shes gsang ba las /
NK091(ke)001:19367: chos sku 'bras bu rang gsal la //
NK091(ke)001:19368: rin chen 'bar ba lhun grub ltar //
NK091(ke)001:19370: skal ldan rang rkyen nyi ma bzhin //
NK091(ke)001:19371: sems can dus na skabs kyis mthun //
NK091(ke)001:19372: lhun grub dus na phyogs ris med //
NK091(ke)001:19373: ces gsungs pa sogs sems phyogs kyi rgyud dang man ngag rnams las shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:19378: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19379: gong du bstan ma thag pa de'i phyir sems can
NK091(ke)001:19380: rnams kyi sems nyid sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin dang
NK091(ke)001:19381: gnyis su med pas chos kun gyi dbyings rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:19382: sems dpa' snying po byang chub spros pa dang bral
NK091(ke)001:19383: ba'i de bzhin nyid du ye nasa ma bcos par
NK091(ke)001:19384: gnas pa'i de kho na nyid yin par nges pa
NK091(ke)001:19385: de bas na bsgrang ba las 'das pas mtha' thug
NK091(ke)001:19386: pa med pa'i semsa can rnams bsam pa rang rang
NK091(ke)001:19387: gi mos pa ltar ji ltar dga' ba dang 'doda
NK091(ke)001:19388: pa bzhin du thabs kyi mdzad pa gang yang ma
NK091(ke)001:19389: bkag par ji ltar snang ba dang mthun par spyad
NK091(ke)001:19390: de don la drangs pas ye nas ma bcos pas
NK091(ke)001:19391: chos nyid ji bzhin pa yang dag par nges pa
NK091(ke)001:19392: de kho na nyid du son par 'gyur ba yin
NK091(ke)001:19393: no // gtan tshigs de'i phyir na rgyal ba rnams
NK091(ke)001:19394: kyis gdul bya gdul ba'i thabs mchog khyad par can
NK091(ke)001:19395: gdul bya so so'i snang tshul gyis phye bas dpag
NK091(ke)001:19396: gis mi lang zhing grangs las 'das pa'i mdzad spyod
NK091(ke)001:19397: kyi gar thabs gcig las ma g.yos par cir yang
NK091(ke)001:19398: snang ba sprin gyi phung po mang zhing rgya che
NK091(ke)001:19399: ba ji snyed pa dag gis gdul bya'i bsam pa
NK091(ke)001:19400: dang mthun par ji ltar spyad kyang mnyam pa'i dbyings
NK091(ke)001:19401: de kho na nyida las ma g.yos shing bskyod pa
NK091(ke)001:19402: med pas ji ltar spyad kyang mi gos te 'khrul
NK091(ke)001:19403: nor med pas legs par gyur te chos kyi dbyings
NK091(ke)001:19404: na rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal du rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:19405: pa'i mdzad pa yang dag pa nyid du nges pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19406: ngo bo nyid kyi rang bzhin las mdzad spyod mu
NK091(ke)001:19407: mtha' yas shing dpag tu med pa yi tshul dam
NK091(ke)001:19408: pa blos mi 'khyud pa'i sgo gang nas nges par
NK091(ke)001:19409: drangs kyang gdul thabs thams cad gang yang ma bkag
NK091(ke)001:19410: cing bsdam pa med par phye bas rang nyid ci
NK091(ke)001:19411: la dga' ba de nyid dang mthun pa'i tshul du
NK091(ke)001:19412: ji ltar 'tshams pas btul nas bde bar drangs te
NK091(ke)001:19413: mdzad pa thams cad dam pa rnams kyi yang dag
NK091(ke)001:19414: pa'i spyod par gyur te gdul bya rnams sangs rgyas
NK091(ke)001:19415: kyi sa la nges par 'god pa'i thabs kyi gar
NK091(ke)001:19416: thabs dam pa mdzod la yal bar ma bzhag cig
NK091(ke)001:19417: no // ces bskul lo // gsum pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:19421: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19422: dus dang gnas skabs nye bar bzung ba 'dir ni
NK091(ke)001:19423: gdul bya ru tra nyid shin tu drag pas bshad
NK091(ke)001:19424: pa ltar zhi rgyas kyis mi 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:19425: dbang drag gi mdzad pa rdo rje 'dzin pa nyid
NK091(ke)001:19426: kyis shin tu nan tan nges pa'i draga shul gyis
NK091(ke)001:19427: de dag gi ngo bo ye nyid nas rang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:19428: gyi khros pa'i rol pa'i dkyil 'khor 'jigs byed chen
NK091(ke)001:19429: po khro ba'i sku mi bzad pa'i me dpung 'abra
NK091(ke)001:19430: ba'i rang byung ye shes kyi ngang las /
NK091(ke)001:19431: las kyi khro bo 'jig rten gyi sde dpon dur
NK091(ke)001:19432: khrod kyi bdag po ru tra 'khor bcas 'dul ba'i
NK091(ke)001:19433: gnyen por rab tu 'jigsa shing rngam pa'i che mchog
NK091(ke)001:19434: he ru ka'i rnam par 'bar ba'i phyag rgya chen
NK091(ke)001:19435: po'i skur snang bar mdzod cig ces bskul bas ngesa
NK091(ke)001:19436: pa dam par bka' gros thag bcad do //
NK091(ke)001:19437: 'o na rgyal ba'i tshogs rel ther zug rtag par
NK091(ke)001:19438: lta ba dang shin tu stong par lta ba sogs
NK091(ke)001:19439: gdul bya mi mthun par snang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:19440: khro la byams dang sogs rgyal ba ril gyi bgros
NK091(ke)001:19441: pa la thabs mtha' yas par bstan pa ji lta
NK091(ke)001:19442: bu zhe na / bde bar gshegs pa la ngo
NK091(ke)001:19443: bo tha dad par mi bzhugs te chos nyid kyi
NK091(ke)001:19444: nam mkha' la ye shes kyi nyi ma brdal bas
NK091(ke)001:19445: dgongs pa dkyil 'khor gsum dbyer med pa'i klong du
NK091(ke)001:19446: mnyam par gyur mod kyis kyang rigs dang mthun pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19447: thabs ni gdul bya'i snang ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:19448: de dag gi longs sku la sogs pa tshogs re
NK091(ke)001:19449: re'i phyir thabs kyi grangs kyang rjes su mthun la
NK091(ke)001:19450: / rgyal ba ji snyed pa'i thabs kyang de snyed kyi phyir smos so //
NK091(ke)001:19452: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:19453: drag pos 'dul bar bka' bgrosa dam pa nges par
NK091(ke)001:19454: bcad pa'i le'u ste nyi shu lnga pa gsal bar
NK091(ke)001:19455: bkrol ba'o ////bzhi pa las kyi skos gdab pa la
NK091(ke)001:19456: gnyis te / nye bar bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:19462: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19465: ru tra 'byung ba'i dus dang bka' bgros bcad pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19466: dus gnyis ngo bo gcig par gyur pa de'i tshe
NK091(ke)001:19467: de'i dus na / gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na
NK091(ke)001:19468: rdo rje khro bo rgyal ba de dag gi 'khor
NK091(ke)001:19469: de nyid du 'dus bar gyur te gsang ba 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:19470: pa'i sdud pa po byed pa zhig gis /
NK091(ke)001:19471: ru tra'i mtshan nyid thugs la mnga' zhing shes bzhin
NK091(ke)001:19472: du gang yongs su sad cing shes pa nyug pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19473: phyir / yang dus de tsam na 'khor der 'dusa
NK091(ke)001:19474: par gyur pa'i byang chub sems dpa' chen po don
NK091(ke)001:19475: du 'jam dpal dang gnyis su med par bskul ba'i
NK091(ke)001:19476: go cha ldan pa lang ka mgrin bcu blo gros
NK091(ke)001:19477: thabs ldan zhes bya ba zhig la /
NK091(ke)001:19478: de yis shes sam mi shes nyams su blang ste
NK091(ke)001:19479: brtags pa'i dgos ched kyi phyir yongs su dris pa
NK091(ke)001:19486: las skal gyi spyod pa ni ci byed /
NK091(ke)001:19488: btul na ci zhig gi dgos pa yod /
NK091(ke)001:19489: de skad ces dri ba bdun dris pa las /
NK091(ke)001:19490: gsang bdag gis bskul ba'i brtson 'grus kyis go cha chen po can des smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:19491: sems dapa'a chen po gsang ba'i bdag po zhes gsang ba'i bka'i sdud pa po la bos te /
NK091(ke)001:19493: gang legs pa'i rgyu rkyen las ni ma byung bar /
NK091(ke)001:19494: nyes pa 'ba' zhig gi rgyu rkyen las byung ste /
NK091(ke)001:19495: rgyu ni lhan skyes dang kun brtags kyi ma rig
NK091(ke)001:19496: pa'i dbang gis de kho na nyid dang las rgyu
NK091(ke)001:19497: 'bras la rmongs pas muna pa'i ri bo las byung
NK091(ke)001:19498: ngo // rkyen ni gsang sngags kyi bka' bsgo la
NK091(ke)001:19499: go ba log par gyur pa'i sngags kyi dka' thub
NK091(ke)001:19500: drag po dang mi dge ba spyod pa'i brtul zhugs
NK091(ke)001:19501: ngo // las byung ngo // 'bras bu ni dang
NK091(ke)001:19502: por ngan song kha brgyud de mthar ru trar smin
NK091(ke)001:19503: pas sdug bsngal gyi ri bora smin no //
NK091(ke)001:19504: rigsa ni mtho ris dang thar lam chad pas dman
NK091(ke)001:19505: rigs 'khor ba pa las ngan byed pas gdol pa
NK091(ke)001:19506: gzhan la gnod pas 'byung po 'dod pa yid la
NK091(ke)001:19507: btags pas yi dwags su gtogs so //
NK091(ke)001:19508: las skal gyi spyod pa ni 'khor ba'i dngos po
NK091(ke)001:19509: lnga tshan bzhi'am rtsa ba bzhi la nyin mtshan 'jol
NK091(ke)001:19512: khos log lam spel bas las can rnams kyi byang
NK091(ke)001:19513: chub kyi snying po yun ring du nub pa'i skyon
NK091(ke)001:19514: du 'gyur ro // nang ltar na bdag 'dzin gyis
NK091(ke)001:19515: thar pa dang byang chub la bar du gcod par
NK091(ke)001:19516: du 'gyur ro // yang sbyar ro // btul na
NK091(ke)001:19517: ni gsang sngags dar bas kun gyi snying po ye
NK091(ke)001:19518: shes 'od gsal gyi dkyil 'khor mngon du gyur te
NK091(ke)001:19521: kho bosa de la 'di skad ces smras so //
NK091(ke)001:19522: ru tra'i rgyu 'bras sogs la ngam nas /
NK091(ke)001:19523: e ma'o zhes pas drangs te sems dpa' chen po zhes lang ka la bos nas /
NK091(ke)001:19524: 'o na de ltar yin na dregs pa can 'dul
NK091(ke)001:19525: ba'i dus la tshad mar phyin pas da lta'i dus
NK091(ke)001:19526: 'di ni btul ba'i dus la bab pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:19527: de la drag po'i las mdzad pa 'di ni rmad du byung ba'i phrin las kyi mchog go //
NK091(ke)001:19528: de'i dus su 'byung ba'i gsang ba sngags kyi don
NK091(ke)001:19529: 'di ni phyi pa las shin tu gsang ba'i bstan
NK091(ke)001:19530: pa rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i yang zhe phugs su gyur
NK091(ke)001:19532: de bas na gtso bo thul la 'khor rnams kun tu raba tu thul zhig ces bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:19533: da ltar dus la bab pa'i skabs chen po 'dir /
NK091(ke)001:19534: drag po'i lasa kyis gdul skal la bab pa'i sems can ru tra 'di nyid /
NK091(ke)001:19535: khro la phan chen mdzad pa'i stongs la bab pas
NK091(ke)001:19536: 'phags mchog rgyal ba'i thugs rje chen po yis sgrol
NK091(ke)001:19537: ba'i thabs kyis phyin ci log gi 'du shes bsgyur
NK091(ke)001:19538: te zag med la bkod pa ni thugs rje'i mchog
NK091(ke)001:19539: tu nges pas stong gsum gyi 'gro ba ma lus
NK091(ke)001:19540: pas srog bton pa bas kyang bsod nams 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:19541: 'bum gyi char yang mi phod do //
NK091(ke)001:19543: de ltar sems dpa' chen po blo gros thabs ldan
NK091(ke)001:19544: dang chos kyis mtho ba'i gnas na 'dus pa'i rgyal
NK091(ke)001:19545: ba ma lus pa la bskul zhing /
NK091(ke)001:19546: drag po'i las kyi bsod nams kyi tshad dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:19547: pas bskul ba ni don gyis der 'dus pa'i 'khor
NK091(ke)001:19548: gyis shes par bya ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:19549: gsang ba 'byung ba'i sgo dbye ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:19550: gdul bya dpyang thag chad pa'i ru tra nyid yal bar mi 'dor ba'i phyir ro //
NK091(ke)001:19551: don 'dis na 'khor ba thog ma tha ma med
NK091(ke)001:19552: par gsang ba 'byung ba'i skabs su gsang bdag nyid
NK091(ke)001:19553: dang / bskul ba'i go cha blo gros thabs ldan
NK091(ke)001:19554: zhes pa'i mtshan 'ba' zhig tu grags pa la 'gal
NK091(ke)001:19556: 'dir ni gsang bdag gis 'das pa'i dus kyi lo rgyus brjod par zad do //
NK091(ke)001:19557: de bas na phyis kyang gsang bdag dang lang kas gsang sngags 'byung ba la the tshom med do //
NK091(ke)001:19558: de ltar yin na gsang bdag gis gsang sngags kyi
NK091(ke)001:19559: bstan pa ma la ya'i rtser 'dus pa'i 'khor la
NK091(ke)001:19560: bshad pa dang srin po ma la yar bab pa
NK091(ke)001:19561: gnyis gal te dus gcig na ni byung tshul yang
NK091(ke)001:19563: bstan pa gcig la dus gnyis smos pa la'ang dgos pa med par 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:19564: de ste min te tha dad yin na dus gcig la gsang sngags lan gnyis 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:19565: de ma yin na gnyis ka bskal pa 'di la ma la yar 'byung ba'ang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK091(ke)001:19566: de dag ni thog ma dang tha ma med par
NK091(ke)001:19567: smos pa las 'dir 'das pa'i dus ru tra btul
NK091(ke)001:19568: ba dang / gsang ba 'byung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:19569: ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul rnams lo rgyus su smos pas dus 'dir yang 'byung ste /
NK091(ke)001:19570: gong du bshad pa de dag dus gcig par 'og nas 'chad par 'gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:19571: dgos pa re re'i phyir byung tshul bcu gnyis tha
NK091(ke)001:19572: dad du bstan kyang gsang ba mchog gi bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:19573: ni bskyar zhing ma gsungs te 'gal ba med par
NK091(ke)001:19576: sprul pa rdo rje 'dzin rgyal po //
NK091(ke)001:19577: sngar byung rgyal tshab skyes bu yis //
NK091(ke)001:19578: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK091(ke)001:19579: gsang mdzod chen po dam pa'i lung //
NK091(ke)001:19580: gsang ba 'dzin pa'i bdag po mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:19581: ces pa la sogs pas the tshom gyi kho thag
NK091(ke)001:19582: chod de lung chen che ba bdun ldan la gzhan
NK091(ke)001:19583: dring mi 'jog pas nges shes rnyed do //
NK091(ke)001:19585: las kyi skos rgyal ba rnams la bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:19586: bskul ba bzhin du mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:19588: rgyal ba rnams kyis rdo rje 'dzin pa la thul zhig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:19589: thugs rje skyes nas zhal gyis bzhes pa /
NK091(ke)001:19590: rdo rje 'dzin pas so pa la bskul pa /
NK091(ke)001:19591: rdo rje sems dpa' rta mgrin bskul zhig par zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:19592: rgyal ba kun la khams gsum yongs sgrol gyi dgongs ba mdzod cig par bskul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:19597: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19598: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis thar
NK091(ke)001:19599: pa'i g.yog dan phag dus 'dzin du bcug pa de
NK091(ke)001:19600: nyid kyis nges pa rnyed de gnas gyur pa rgyal
NK091(ke)001:19601: tshab skyes bu dam pa gsang ba'i bdag po phyag
NK091(ke)001:19602: na rdo rje 'am rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po
NK091(ke)001:19603: nyid du snang bar gyur pa de nyid la ru
NK091(ke)001:19604: tra thul zhig par bka'i las gnyer gtad de yongs
NK091(ke)001:19606: rgyal ba kun gyi gsang ba'i mdzod gsum mtha' dag
NK091(ke)001:19607: la dbang bsgyur te 'dzin par mdzad pa spyir gdul
NK091(ke)001:19608: bya yongs la thugs rje mchog gi bdag po khyad
NK091(ke)001:19609: par du gnyis med don gyi ye shes mi phyed
NK091(ke)001:19610: par 'chang zhing gsang ba'i mdzod kun 'dzin pa dang
NK091(ke)001:19611: thugs rje 'char ba'i rtags su phyag na rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:19612: 'dzin pa drag po rngam pa'i cha byad kyis gdug
NK091(ke)001:19613: pa thams cad 'dul ba'i brtul zhugs chen po can
NK091(ke)001:19614: phyi nang gi 'dzin pa mtha' dag 'joms pa'i dpa'
NK091(ke)001:19615: bo 'jig rten gsum lasa rnam par rgyal ba'i blar
NK091(ke)001:19616: gyur pa khyod kyis sngona gyii smon lam dang thugs
NK091(ke)001:19617: rje'i stobs kyi go cha chen po'i mthus /
NK091(ke)001:19618: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas kun dang da ltar gyi sangs
NK091(ke)001:19619: rgyas thams cad kyi rngam brjid 'bar ba'i phrin las
NK091(ke)001:19620: kyi mnga' bdag gdul dka' drag po thams cad 'dul
NK091(ke)001:19621: bar mdzad pa bdud kyi tshogs rnams 'jigs par byed
NK091(ke)001:19622: pas bdud kyi rje bo ste bdud rnams 'joms par
NK091(ke)001:19623: mdzad pa'i sems dpa' chen po dgongs pa dbyings las
NK091(ke)001:19624: mi 'gyur ba'i rtags su kha dog sngon po bee
NK091(ke)001:19625: d+aur+ya'i ri bo la nyin byed 'bum gyis 'khyud pa
NK091(ke)001:19626: ltar gzi byin che zhing ye shes kyi me dpung
NK091(ke)001:19627: 'bar ba'i thugs rje chen po'i ngang las khro bor
NK091(ke)001:19628: bzhengs pa'i sku che la yan lag rags pas 'jigs
NK091(ke)001:19629: su rung ba'i dpa' byad can sku gtum zhing gsung
NK091(ke)001:19630: rngam la thugs 'khrug pa'i rnam pa ngo bo chos
NK091(ke)001:19631: nyid dbyings kyi snang ba yis dur khrod kyi bdag
NK091(ke)001:19632: po 'khor bcas rab tu chomsa shig /ces yongsa su
NK091(ke)001:19633: bskul bas na don 'di nyid kyis gsang bdag tu
NK091(ke)001:19634: mngon no // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:19636: gdul bar zhal gyis bzhes pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:19641: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19642: de ltar bskul ba gsan nas sngon gyi go cha'i dbang gis /
NK091(ke)001:19643: skyes bu rdo rje 'dzin pa de yis zhal gyis bzhes te gzigs par mdzad pa na /
NK091(ke)001:19644: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten 'di rnams 'byung po'i
NK091(ke)001:19645: rgyal pos dbang du byas nas sgo gsum shin tu
NK091(ke)001:19646: yang gtum rngam 'khrug pa des lha mi'i 'jiga rten
NK091(ke)001:19647: gyi dge ba'i srid brlag la khyad du gyur te
NK091(ke)001:19648: / lus kyi bzhin gyi mdangs kyang mi gsal bar sems kun tu mog mog por gyur nas /
NK091(ke)001:19649: sprin sogs kyi dbang gis dus ma yin pa'i mun
NK091(ke)001:19650: par yang muna nag smag tu gyur pas 'thibs shing
NK091(ke)001:19651: tsha ba dang grang ba'i nad dang rimsa drag po
NK091(ke)001:19652: sogs nges par srog 'phrogs pa'i mi ngas pa'i nad
NK091(ke)001:19653: rigs sna tshogs kun tu rgyas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:19654: rlung dmar dang 'brug gi sgra dang char dang ser ba drag po 'bab pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:19655: rnag khrag rdol ba'i sdug bsngal skyed pas rdo dang
NK091(ke)001:19656: mtshon cha'i char la sogs pa dus ma yin para
NK091(ke)001:19658: dregs pa'i mthus phyi nang gi skye ba log cing
NK091(ke)001:19659: lo nyes pa la sogs pa 'byung bas 'bras bu
NK091(ke)001:19660: dus su skye ba'am dang por skye ba dang smin
NK091(ke)001:19661: pa logs pas de'i dbang gis 'tsho ba'ang log par
NK091(ke)001:19663: de ltar gdug pa sna tshogs kyis mnar ba'i sems
NK091(ke)001:19664: can rnams dregs pa'i stobs kyis shin tu nyam thag
NK091(ke)001:19665: cing gdung bar 'gyur bas spyir khams gsum po ru
NK091(ke)001:19666: tra'i dbang du song ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:19667: sgos su ru tra rang lam log par 'phyan pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19668: mgon med pa yi 'jig rten de nyid sdug bsngal
NK091(ke)001:19669: gyis nyam thag par mkhyen te thugs su chud pas
NK091(ke)001:19670: mi g.yo ba'i ngang las mi 'gog pa'i thugs rjes
NK091(ke)001:19671: gdung bar mdzad pa'i khyad par shin tu 'brel ba'i
NK091(ke)001:19672: brtse ba ste drag po'i gnas skabs su nges pas
NK091(ke)001:19673: shin tu khros pa'i tshul gyis dgongs pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:19676: shes rab kyis gzigs pa na lhar bcas 'jig rten
NK091(ke)001:19677: thams cad rtog bdag tu 'dzin pas dbang du byas
NK091(ke)001:19678: te / sgo gsum po zag bcas su gyur nas
NK091(ke)001:19679: rang gi snying po ma bral bzhin du mi mngon
NK091(ke)001:19680: par brlag la khad du song bas sems kyi chos
NK091(ke)001:19681: nyid mi gsal zhing lhan skyes kyis ma rig pas
NK091(ke)001:19682: te / rmongs nas / dad brtson dang shes rab
NK091(ke)001:19683: chen pos legs par brtags na gzung 'dzin don la
NK091(ke)001:19684: med pas dus ma yin par kun brtags kyi mun
NK091(ke)001:19685: pa sna tshogs par 'thibs nas zhe sdang dang 'dod
NK091(ke)001:19686: chags kyi tsha grang gi nad dang rtsa ba dang
NK091(ke)001:19687: nye ba'i nyon mongs kyi rims drag po 'tshig pa
NK091(ke)001:19688: dang 'khon 'dzin sogs gong du 'phel bas rgyas shing
NK091(ke)001:19689: g.yo sgyu dang 'chab pa sogs kyis ngag gi bzhi
NK091(ke)001:19690: sogs las sna tshogs bslang ste char ltar bab pas
NK091(ke)001:19691: rnam par smin pa skye ba dang gnas pa dang
NK091(ke)001:19692: te / rmongs nas / / tshe tshad log par
NK091(ke)001:19693: gyur te srid par nyam thag pa de yang dag
NK091(ke)001:19694: par mkhyen nas thabs kyis bsgral te byang chub don
NK091(ke)001:19695: te / rmongs nas / / du gnyer ba'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:19700: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19701: dngos por med la kun 'byung ba'i stong nyid chen
NK091(ke)001:19702: po ngo bo nyid sku'i ngang las ye ja bzhin
NK091(ke)001:19703: pa'i rang snang mngon du byas pa yi rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:19705: lhun rdzogs stug po bkoda pa'i zhing khams na rgyud
NK091(ke)001:19706: rnam par dag pa'i lam du gshegs pas longs sku
NK091(ke)001:19707: las srid pa gsum gyi khams sbyong bar mdzad pas
NK091(ke)001:19708: rgyal ba sprul pa'i sku'i sangs rgyas rnams zhes rang
NK091(ke)001:19709: bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas dang stug po
NK091(ke)001:19710: bkod pa'i rgyud dag pa'i rgyal ba rnams la bos
NK091(ke)001:19711: nas / gsang ba'i bdag po rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK091(ke)001:19712: bdag ni gdug pa 'dul ba dang gsang ba ston
NK091(ke)001:19713: pa la sogs pa rgyal ba'i phrin las ril gyi
NK091(ke)001:19714: byed pa po yin pas bka' yi las mkhan mchog
NK091(ke)001:19715: nas / tu nges te / des na bka' yi
NK091(ke)001:19716: las kyi dus skabs la skabs la bab pa da
NK091(ke)001:19718: bdag gis deng 'dir bagyi'o zhes zhal gyis 'ches pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19719: don gyis chos sku dang gzugs sku'i sangs rgyas rnam
NK091(ke)001:19720: gnyis la yongs su rdzogs par bskul te /
NK091(ke)001:19721: sangs rgyas kun gyi gdul bya gdul bar dka' ba
NK091(ke)001:19722: de dag la drag po'i stobs kyis don mdzad par
NK091(ke)001:19723: bskul ba ltar gdul bya ma lus thams cad badga
NK091(ke)001:19724: gis gdul la / srid pa las ma grol ba
NK091(ke)001:19725: yang bdag gis dgrol zhing gang bag chags kyis las
NK091(ke)001:19726: ma bsgral ba yang bdag gisa rnam par mi rtog
NK091(ke)001:19727: pa'i ye shes chen pos bsgral nas ngan 'gro'i gnas
NK091(ke)001:19728: las dbugs ma phyung ba yang dbugs phyung ste yang
NK091(ke)001:19729: dag pa'i 'bras bu nyid la dgod par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:19735: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19736: de nas phyag na rdo rje rab tu rngam pa'i brtul zhugs can gyis /
NK091(ke)001:19737: gsung rdo rje chos kyi sprul pa dpal ldan rta
NK091(ke)001:19738: yi gdong ngam rta mgrin la gdug pa can gzhom
NK091(ke)001:19739: pa'i bka' lung dbang dang drag po gnyis las dbang
NK091(ke)001:19740: gis 'dul ba'i phyir dus tshod gzung bar gyis shig
NK091(ke)001:19741: par rdo rje'i tshig tu 'di skad du bskul lo
NK091(ke)001:19742: // khro bo rta mgrin rgyal ba thams cad kyi
NK091(ke)001:19743: gsung gi bdag nyid ngag gi dbang phyug yin pas
NK091(ke)001:19744: rta'i 'dur glu dang bcas pas dregs pa 'joms pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19745: zhal lam rdo rje'i gdong can khyod kyis lang ka'i
NK091(ke)001:19746: yul gyi grong rdal gyi dbus kyi ri bo ma
NK091(ke)001:19747: la ya zhes bya ba ko ka thang dmar rgya
NK091(ke)001:19748: mtsho'i ngo yi do la chen po drag shul yod
NK091(ke)001:19749: pa'i rtse mo la dong nas /
NK091(ke)001:19750: chos nyid ma 'gag pa'i rdo rje thabs kyis bya
NK091(ke)001:19751: ra mdzad cing lta ba'i yul ni dur khrod kyi
NK091(ke)001:19752: bdag po dregs pa 'khor tshogsa dang bcas pa mi
NK091(ke)001:19753: la sha khrag yod pas gsod cing dud 'gro dang
NK091(ke)001:19754: lha min yang de dang 'dra bas srog chags mang
NK091(ke)001:19755: po'i srog 'phrogs pas mi ngas skyama ling chen po
NK091(ke)001:19756: rngon byed pa la song nas skabs la bab pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19757: dus su rgyal ba thugs rje chen po khams gsum
NK091(ke)001:19758: gyi grong khyer gyi mgon po gdug pa 'joms pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19759: rdo rje'i dgongs pa mnga' ba rnams la bya btang
NK091(ke)001:19760: ba dang sbron pa thong la dus la bab pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19766: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19767: mtha' yi rtog pa cis kyang mi bskyod pas mi
NK091(ke)001:19768: 'khrugs pa zhes bya ba'i rdo rje sems dpa' ye
NK091(ke)001:19769: ji bzhin pa dang rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas kun
NK091(ke)001:19770: gyi rang bzhin dngos su na rdo rje sems dpa'
NK091(ke)001:19771: de bzhin nyid rdo rje snying po zhes bya ba
NK091(ke)001:19772: srid pa gsum gyi mgon po khyed kyis chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:19773: sku stong pa chen po'i nam mkha' la longs spyod
NK091(ke)001:19774: rdzogs sku zhi ba las khro bor bzhengs te 'bar
NK091(ke)001:19775: ba chen po'i gar dgur mdzod la mthu yis bstangs
NK091(ke)001:19776: nas rta mgrin so la bskul zhig thugs rje sprul
NK091(ke)001:19777: sku ma la ya'am gdul bya'i zhing gi sa la
NK091(ke)001:19779: gdul bya dang mthun 'jug gi mdzad pa dpal rdo
NK091(ke)001:19780: rje gzhon nu'i rol gar byis pa'i spyod pa dang
NK091(ke)001:19781: 'dra bar ston pa la gnyis su med pa'i dgongs
NK091(ke)001:19787: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19788: sangs rgyas ma lus pa ril gyi dgongs pa gsang
NK091(ke)001:19789: ba kun yongs su 'dus pa gsang sngags lung gi
NK091(ke)001:19790: rgyud chen po 'di nyid ston pa'i rmad du byung
NK091(ke)001:19791: ba gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi rgyal ba thun mong
NK091(ke)001:19792: ma yin pa thams cad kyis mtha' thug pa med
NK091(ke)001:19793: pa'i sems can rnams yang gsang nges don dam pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19794: don gyi gter shes rab chen pos rtogs su chug
NK091(ke)001:19795: la snying po byang chub la bskul te dbyings dang
NK091(ke)001:19796: ye shes dbyer med kyi sa la 'god pa'i thabs
NK091(ke)001:19797: kyi byin rlabs snang bar nges pa'i gsang ba zab
NK091(ke)001:19798: mo ston pa'i dgongs pa mdzod cig ces rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:19799: 'dzin pa des drag tu bskul ba las /
NK091(ke)001:19801: rdo rje sems dpas rta'i tshogs la bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:19802: rta mgrin so la gshegs pa /
NK091(ke)001:19803: rgyal ba rnams kyis khams gsum yongs sgrol gyi dgongs pa mdzad pa /
NK091(ke)001:19804: bdud btul ba'i sbyor ba mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:19809: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19810: de nas bsnyul bar mkhyen nas 'og min chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:19811: dbyings kyi pho brang nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK091(ke)001:19812: cad kyi bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpas 'gro 'ong
NK091(ke)001:19813: med par rang byung gi ye shes chen po'i me
NK091(ke)001:19814: dpung mtha' dang gdug pa sreg pas dus mtha'i bskal
NK091(ke)001:19815: pa'i me klong ltar 'bar ba'i thugs rje'i sprin dpung
NK091(ke)001:19816: nam mkha'i mtha' klas par gtibs nas /
NK091(ke)001:19817: zhes pa'i tshig 'dis he ru ka'i sku thams cad skabs 'dir snang bar byas pa yin no //
NK091(ke)001:19818: de ltar 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu'i mngon spyod du snang bar mdzad nas /
NK091(ke)001:19819: rdo rje rta'i tshogs la bkas bsgo ba /
NK091(ke)001:19820: so mtha' la song zhig 'jig rten kun tu rab
NK091(ke)001:19821: tu nges par song zhig /de'i tshul ni sgeg po
NK091(ke)001:19822: dpa' bo la sogs pa le'u nyer bdun pa las
NK091(ke)001:19823: 'chad pa ltar khams gsum sa dgu las bsgral ba'i
NK091(ke)001:19824: phyir rta yi rdo rje'i stabs dgu yis gdul bya'i
NK091(ke)001:19825: 'jiga rtena shes rab kyi blo gros rab 'bring tha
NK091(ke)001:19826: ma dgu'i rang rang gi 'dod pa ltar theg pa
NK091(ke)001:19828: 'jig rten gyi ru tra nag poo gtum pa'i tshogs
NK091(ke)001:19829: rnams dur khrod du srog chags gsod pa'i skyam ling
NK091(ke)001:19830: gi rngon pa'i spyod pa la song ba'i tshe na
NK091(ke)001:19831: rdo rje rtog pa'i bya ra gyis la dus su
NK091(ke)001:19832: sgron par gyis shig /thugs dam gnad nas bskul te
NK091(ke)001:19833: / spyan ras kyis 'khor ba mtha' dag ma bsgral
NK091(ke)001:19834: ba'i bar du 'di ltar gzigs nas don bya bar
NK091(ke)001:19835: dam bcas pa'i go cha chen po gyon pa yi
NK091(ke)001:19836: thugs rje'am snying rje chen po'i rgyus rtog cing 'jug
NK091(ke)001:19837: pa'i tshul dag gis spyir 'khor ba'i 'gro ba rnams
NK091(ke)001:19838: la bya ra mdzad de rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa
NK091(ke)001:19839: gang ltar spyod pa'i skal ba ltar ston cing 'gro
NK091(ke)001:19840: ba bde bar gyis shig /khyad par du skabs kyi
NK091(ke)001:19841: dregs pa ci byed pa'i so mtha' thag chod par
NK091(ke)001:19842: gyis shig /ces drag tu bsgo bas /
NK091(ke)001:19847: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19848: de ltar bskul bas spyan ras gzigs rdo rje chos
NK091(ke)001:19849: rta'i gdong can de nyid rab tu dgyes nas rgyal
NK091(ke)001:19850: ba rnams kyi bka' bzhin chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK091(ke)001:19851: bar dgongs shing gdul bya la rtag tu spyan ras
NK091(ke)001:19852: gzigs shing 'tsho ba ni dbang gi rigs te rdo
NK091(ke)001:19853: rje thugs kyi spyan mchog de yis rab tu gzigs
NK091(ke)001:19854: te rdo rje gsum gyi sgo nas gsung gi gsang
NK091(ke)001:19855: ba chags med skyon bral pad+mo dam pa'i chos kyi
NK091(ke)001:19856: 'khor lo bskor bar rab tu dga' zhing dgyes pa
NK091(ke)001:19857: yis sku mngon du snang bar mdzad de ngag gi
NK091(ke)001:19858: dbang phyug sprul pa'i tshogs de lta bu mang pos
NK091(ke)001:19859: skabs dang mthun par gang la gang 'dul du chos
NK091(ke)001:19860: ston pa'i phyir byang chub chen po skad cig gis
NK091(ke)001:19861: non zhing myur bar bgrod pa'i cang shes kyi gtso
NK091(ke)001:19862: bo'i rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pas shes bya gang la
NK091(ke)001:19863: yang ma rmongs par byol song gi rgyal po rta
NK091(ke)001:19864: yi stabs chen po dgu yi rdzu 'phrul gyis skal
NK091(ke)001:19865: ba dang 'tshams par don mdzad cing /
NK091(ke)001:19866: ru tra dbang du sdud pa'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:19867: rdo rje rta yi gdong can dpal rta mgrin gyi
NK091(ke)001:19868: sprul pa'i tshogs kyis nam mkha'i khams kun yongs su
NK091(ke)001:19869: bkang bar mdzad pa ni dregs pa'i snang ba ste
NK091(ke)001:19870: de nas sprul pa de rnams kyis srin po'i gnas
NK091(ke)001:19871: ma la ya yi ri'i rtse la so bya bar
NK091(ke)001:19872: lhagsa te skad cig gis byon nas yun 'khor ba
NK091(ke)001:19873: ma stongs kyi bar du ni thugs rje chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:19874: dbang gis mi rtog bzhin du spyan ras kyis gzigs
NK091(ke)001:19875: shing bya ra mdzad de spyi dang bye brag la
NK091(ke)001:19880: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19881: de'i dus su 'og min stug po bkod pa'ii zhing
NK091(ke)001:19882: gi rdul gcig gi steng na rdul snyed kyi rgyal
NK091(ke)001:19883: ba ji snyed pa yang rta'i tshogs dang dgongs pa
NK091(ke)001:19884: mi gnyis par ngo bo chos nyid mi 'gag pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19885: gsang ba gcig tu 'dus pas bdud btul ba dang
NK091(ke)001:19886: khams kyi grong khyer gsum po kun gnyis med kyi
NK091(ke)001:19887: ngang du ye sgrol te ye shes chen po gzung
NK091(ke)001:19888: 'dzin nga bdag gi rang bzhin gzhi med ye dag
NK091(ke)001:19889: tu grol bas byang chub snying por yang dag par
NK091(ke)001:19890: dgod pa'i dgongsa pa mdzad de /
NK091(ke)001:19891: chags sdang gti mug gi dug gsum po sa bon
NK091(ke)001:19892: rtsa ba nas zad cing gtan sprugs su gcod pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19893: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs par mdzad nas
NK091(ke)001:19894: / gnas gcig tu yang yang 'khor ba'i 'gro ba
NK091(ke)001:19895: rnams kyi sdug bsngal thams cad chos nyid mnyam pa
NK091(ke)001:19896: chen po'i ngang du rnam par mi rtog pa'i spyan
NK091(ke)001:19898: gang sgo gsum gdung ba'i ngo bo nyid kyang nam
NK091(ke)001:19899: mkha'i 'ja' rlan dang 'dra zhing lam gzhan du ma
NK091(ke)001:19900: dmigs pa de nyid kyi don la rtogs pa gdeng
NK091(ke)001:19901: chud pas mthar phyin pa'i phyir sdug bsngal thams cad
NK091(ke)001:19902: byang chub kyi lam du rang grol bar mdzad cing
NK091(ke)001:19903: / dge sdig gam smad par bya ba'i las nyid
NK091(ke)001:19904: kyang ril byang chub sems kyi mdzad pa las thal
NK091(ke)001:19905: ba med pas chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes
NK091(ke)001:19906: chen po rang gsal bar 'grel ba'i phyir /
NK091(ke)001:19907: des bskyed pa'i rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu log
NK091(ke)001:19908: pa'i sgo gsum po'ang ye ma dmigs pas sun phyung
NK091(ke)001:19909: ste rdo rje gsum gyi ngo bo nyid du bya
NK091(ke)001:19910: byed med par gsal ba ni /
NK091(ke)001:19911: glo bur du lam pas byas pa min te /
NK091(ke)001:19912: ye nas ji bzhin pa'i gnas lugs ma bcos ma
NK091(ke)001:19913: byas te rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i ngo bo rang
NK091(ke)001:19914: byung don gyi dkyil 'khor chen pora lhun gyis rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:19915: pa'i ngang du dgongs pa dam pa mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:19916: de lta bu'i don ni ngo bo gnyis med la
NK091(ke)001:19917: dgongs pas gdul bya'i snang ba la rta'i tshogs la
NK091(ke)001:19918: rgyal ba rnams kyis mthu btang ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:19919: de nyid kyi mdzad pa mi dor ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:19923: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19924: rta'i tshogs ma la ya'i rtser so mdzad pa'i tshe
NK091(ke)001:19925: 'og min gyi zhing du dan phag phyag na rdo
NK091(ke)001:19926: rjer gyur pa'i gsang bdag rdo rje 'dzin pa chen
NK091(ke)001:19927: po yang thugs dam gyi dbang gis sku dang gsunga
NK091(ke)001:19928: dang thugs kyi rdo rje gsum mi phyed pa las
NK091(ke)001:19929: sprul pa'i sras mchog rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bkod pa
NK091(ke)001:19930: la dpal chen po rdo rje gzhon nu byis pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19931: gzugs can grangs las 'das pa bye ba sa yar
NK091(ke)001:19932: snang bar mdzad pa ji snyed pa thamsa cad kyang
NK091(ke)001:19933: dbyar gyi sprin dpung gtibs pa bzhin du nam mkha'i
NK091(ke)001:19934: dbyings kyi mtha' klas par khyab cing gang bar mdzad
NK091(ke)001:19935: pa yang / gnas ma la ya yi rtse de
NK091(ke)001:19936: la lhagsa te srin po'i spyod pa dang mthuna 'jug
NK091(ke)001:19937: gi thabs kyi cha byad can du bstan te gang
NK091(ke)001:19938: 'dir cir yang mi 'gog par mdzad pa'i phyir byis
NK091(ke)001:19939: pa'i spyod pa dang mthun pa'i gdul thabs kyi mdzad
NK091(ke)001:19940: pa yis bdud kyi spyod yul kun kyang cha mthun
NK091(ke)001:19941: du mdzad de 'jig rten gyi khams su byis pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19942: spyod par snang ba'i 'phrul gyi bkod pa bstan par
NK091(ke)001:19943: pa yang / mdzad do // le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK091(ke)001:19944: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:19945: spyi'i dbang du las bzhi la dgongs kyang 'dir gtso
NK091(ke)001:19946: che ba'i ngos nas dbang dang drag po'i las gnyis
NK091(ke)001:19947: kho na mdzad pa'i phyir gcig la gcig bsgo ba
NK091(ke)001:19948: dang / rta'i tshogs bskul te so mdzad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:19949: stug po bkod pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis dgongs pa mdzad pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:19950: rdo rje 'dzin pas rdo rje snying po nyid la
NK091(ke)001:19951: bskul zhing nyid kyi las so sor bskos pa'i don
NK091(ke)001:19952: ston pas gang gis 'dul ba'i las bzhi rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:19953: skos kyi le'u ste nyi shu rtsa drug pa rnam
NK091(ke)001:19954: par bshad pa'o ////gnyis pa la bdud btul ba dngos
NK091(ke)001:19955: la brgyad de / ru tra'i 'khor dang spyod yul bstan pa /
NK091(ke)001:19956: 'khor dang spyod yul gzhan du bsgyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:19957: de las ma rangs pa'i rtog pa srin mos bsal ba /
NK091(ke)001:19958: las kyi srin mo la rdo rje srin po'i sku 'khrungs pa /
NK091(ke)001:19959: de la ru tras dmag bsags pa /
NK091(ke)001:19960: bdud btul ba rang gi ngo bo /
NK091(ke)001:19961: smre sngags bton cing lus dang 'khor phul pa /
NK091(ke)001:19962: rang rtags srog gi snying po phul bas byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:19966: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:19968: de nasa zhes ma la ya'i rtser byon pa la
NK091(ke)001:19969: snyegs pa dang 'og nas 'byung ba'i don 'dren pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19971: rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po ru tra dang mthun
NK091(ke)001:19972: 'jug gi tshul du shin tu khros pas he ru
NK091(ke)001:19973: kar byung ba'i rgyal tshabs skyes bu sprul pa gzhon
NK091(ke)001:19975: mthun 'jug byis pa'i spyod pa mdzad pa'i spyan gyis
NK091(ke)001:19976: gang dur khrod bdag po'i dngos po rnams tshul ji
NK091(ke)001:19978: las kyi dbang gis skyes pa'i yi dwags drag poo de nyid /
NK091(ke)001:19979: 'khor ba'i dngos po 'dam mtshan la sogs pa bzhisa
NK091(ke)001:19980: ni rtag par dbang du byas pa kho nar gyur
NK091(ke)001:19981: la / gdug pas rnam par smin pa'i dngos po ru tra gang gi gnas tshul na /
NK091(ke)001:19982: ro rus brtsegs pas bam ri thod pa mkhar gyi
NK091(ke)001:19983: rtsa bar 'obs chen po khrag dang gcig bshang ba
NK091(ke)001:19984: dang gnyis gci ba dang gsum sha chen dang bzhi
NK091(ke)001:19985: / rkang dang lnga klad pa dang de'i sri klad
NK091(ke)001:19986: rgyas dang drug rnag dang bdun chu ser dang brgyad
NK091(ke)001:19987: de la sogs zhes pas dug dang me dang mtshon
NK091(ke)001:19988: dang bcas pa'i 'dam rnams kyis yongs su gang pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19989: 'obs kyi phru mas grong rdal gyi tshul du yongs
NK091(ke)001:19990: / su bskor zhing / de'i nang na sa la
NK091(ke)001:19991: gnas pa'i 'bu dang sbrul lta bu shin tu 'bu
NK091(ke)001:19992: / su bskor zhing / chen po dang / mkha'
NK091(ke)001:19993: la gnas pa'i sbrang ma dang sbrang rgod dang bung
NK091(ke)001:19995: gzhan yang sbrul dang sdig pa dang sdom la sogs pa mang po dang /
NK091(ke)001:19996: 'dab chags kyi rigs kang ka dang khwa ngang ri skegs dang 'ug pa'i tshogs dang /
NK091(ke)001:19998: ce spyang dang stag dang seng ge la sogs pa'i
NK091(ke)001:19999: gdug pa can gyi tshogs rnams kyis bskor bar gyur
NK091(ke)001:20000: la / lha yi sde dpon ka ru na'i bu
NK091(ke)001:20001: mo dang chung ma dang ma dang sring mo rnams
NK091(ke)001:20002: la / dang / 'jig rten gyi dbang phyug lha
NK091(ke)001:20003: chen po rnams kyi ma dang sring mo chung ma
NK091(ke)001:20004: dang bu mo rnams phrogs nas dbang du byas pa
NK091(ke)001:20005: yi slas dang byi mo dang bran mo'i tshogs kyi
NK091(ke)001:20006: dbang phyug ma bcu phrag gnyis dang ni brgyad la
NK091(ke)001:20007: sogs pa'i ma mo dang phra men ma gnod sbyin
NK091(ke)001:20008: mo dang srin mo sha za ma dang khrag 'phrog
NK091(ke)001:20009: la / dang / ma rnams dang / gzhan yang bdud kyi ming 'dzin pas barla rkun ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:20010: de bzhin du blon gyi tshul byed pas blon moo
NK091(ke)001:20011: dang damga dpon byed ma dang phyogs bzhi lta bu'i
NK091(ke)001:20012: sde dpon ma dang dmag nyung ngu'i dpon lta bu
NK091(ke)001:20013: ru dpon ma dang mangga gzhug byed pa mo dang
NK091(ke)001:20014: pho nyar 'gyed pa'i ma tshogs bcas rang rang gi
NK091(ke)001:20015: zhing la sogs pa'i stan dang mtshon cha sogs lag
NK091(ke)001:20016: char bcas te ru tra la ci bgyi zhes bka'
NK091(ke)001:20017: la nyan pa dang bka' bzhin sdod pa'i 'khor gyi
NK091(ke)001:20018: tshogs rnams za za rngam rngam lta bur spod gtod
NK091(ke)001:20019: rngam pa'i tshul du 'khod cing gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:20020: srid pa'i dbang phyug srin po'i bu mo dri za
NK091(ke)001:20021: chen mo sha za zhing khrag 'thung ba'i phra men
NK091(ke)001:20022: ma brgyad seng ge dang stag dang wa dang spyang
NK091(ke)001:20023: ki dang bzhad gdong ma'i tshogs dang /
NK091(ke)001:20024: dur bya dang bya rog dang 'ug pa'i gdong can
NK091(ke)001:20025: gyi tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams las rtod cing
NK091(ke)001:20027: srin po'i nye gnas ma mo chen mo brgyad de
NK091(ke)001:20028: koo ri ma dang tsoo ri ma dang pra mo
NK091(ke)001:20029: ha dang be ta li dang puk+ka si dang g+hasma
NK091(ke)001:20030: ri dang sma sha ni dang tsan+da li la sogs
NK091(ke)001:20031: pa ya so so'i 'khor dang bcas te ma zhing
NK091(ke)001:20032: rngam pa'i ma tshogsa ma rnams cha lugs rgyan dang
NK091(ke)001:20033: kha dog bcas shin tu 'jigs pa'i gzugs su 'khod
NK091(ke)001:20034: do // dur khrod kyi sa yi sgo srung ma bzhi btson mo rta gdong ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:20035: gdong mo phag gdong ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:20036: gar log mo dred gdong ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:20037: 'di pa mchan la lar seng gdong mar yang gsungs /
NK091(ke)001:20038: de bzhin du 'jug mo spyang gdong ma chen po
NK091(ke)001:20039: bzhi po rnams log sde'i gsang sgo 'dzin cing ru
NK091(ke)001:20040: tra'i bka' sgo srung nas gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:20041: dur khrod kyi bdag mo bzhi ni rgyal po bzhi'i
NK091(ke)001:20042: chung ma ste ri rab phyogs kyi gru nas 'degsa
NK091(ke)001:20043: pa'i tshul can ma gsang ba'i yum bzhi shar du
NK091(ke)001:20044: brkam ma / lhor shin tu brkam ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:20045: nub tu ra ro ma dang /
NK091(ke)001:20046: byang du khrag 'thung ma dang bzhi po chags pas myos pa'i mdangs kyisa 'khod nas gnas so //
NK091(ke)001:20047: chung ma ji ltar gnas na ro spungs pas bam
NK091(ke)001:20048: ri thod pa brtsegs pa'i mkhar gyi dbus na gnam
NK091(ke)001:20049: lcags 'bar ba'i thog gis gzer chen gyis shin tu
NK091(ke)001:20050: brtan par btab pa'i nang na /
NK091(ke)001:20051: bdag mo nye gnas kyi gtso mo kro ti shwa ri ma zhes bya ba /
NK091(ke)001:20052: thod skyogs khrag gisa bka' ba dang klad pa sogs
NK091(ke)001:20053: 'abru mar rdzas lnga chang dang sbyar ba rtag par
NK091(ke)001:20054: rang gis longs spyod cing 'dzin te gnas la /
NK091(ke)001:20055: de nyid chags pasa myos shing grogs la brkam pasa na /
NK091(ke)001:20056: 'dod pa'i dbang mo brkam mar yongs su grags so //
NK091(ke)001:20057: nang ltar na bam ri thod mkhar ni rang gi
NK091(ke)001:20058: lus yin la khrag la sogs pa de la yod
NK091(ke)001:20059: pa'i chos dang kang ka sogs ni nang rol dang
NK091(ke)001:20060: slas sogs bdag 'dzin dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i sems
NK091(ke)001:20061: dang sems byung yin zhing phra men ma brgyad yul
NK091(ke)001:20062: brgyad dang / nye gnas brgyad ni rnam shes tshogs brgyad /
NK091(ke)001:20063: sgo srung bzhi ni phyin ci log bzhi /
NK091(ke)001:20064: gru 'degs ma bzhi ni bdag tu rmongs pa chags
NK091(ke)001:20065: pa nga rgyal ba bdag tu lta ba bzhi ste
NK091(ke)001:20066: de rnams thabs kyi ye shes chen pos grol bar
NK091(ke)001:20067: mdzad pa'o // gnyis pa la bzhi ste /
NK091(ke)001:20068: sme brtsegs bton te 'obs lnga bsgyur ba /
NK091(ke)001:20069: 'khor mo la ye shes kyi sprul pa bzhag pa /
NK091(ke)001:20070: srin mo'i lhums su rdo rje srin po bzhag pa /
NK091(ke)001:20071: bsgyur nas snying po byang chub la bzhugs shing sdud pa po mdzad pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:20076: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20077: de nas btul bar dgongs te /
NK091(ke)001:20078: ru tra'i mnga' 'bang gi tshogs kyi phru ma grong
NK091(ke)001:20079: rdal de nyid 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgu yis
NK091(ke)001:20080: bcom nas dbang du mdzad pa'i phyir du lha'i sde
NK091(ke)001:20081: dpon btul ba'i 'khor rnams ru tra'i 'khor du 'dus
NK091(ke)001:20082: pa yi 'jig rten pa'i dbang phyug mthu chen ldan
NK091(ke)001:20083: pa rnams dbang du bsdus pas dregs pa 'khor bcas
NK091(ke)001:20084: kyi phal cher rang rang gi las la gram ste
NK091(ke)001:20085: pho rnams phyogs gcig tu skyam ling la song ba
NK091(ke)001:20086: skyes bus gzigs te rang gi gnas nas dong ba'i
NK091(ke)001:20087: skabs su mo la sbyor bas sras kyis 'dul ba'i
NK091(ke)001:20088: ched du dpal chen po rdo rje 'dzin pa he
NK091(ke)001:20089: ru ka de'i gsang ba bdag de nyid yang dag
NK091(ke)001:20090: pa'i sku dngosa min par sprul pa'i rnam rol du
NK091(ke)001:20091: rdo rje gzhon nu de nyid yum med pa'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:20092: snam nas bton pa'i sras lta bur chos nyid las
NK091(ke)001:20094: khro chen rdo rje gzhon nu de la snam nas
NK091(ke)001:20095: bton pa dang mi gtsang ba'i 'obs rnams zhal du
NK091(ke)001:20096: gsol bas / mtshan sme ba brtsegs pa zhes bya
NK091(ke)001:20097: ba sku mdog mthing nag khro gnyer chen pos brjid
NK091(ke)001:20098: cing ral pa gyen du bardzesa pa can sku 'bar
NK091(ke)001:20099: ba chen po'i gar dgura mdzad de yang dur khrod
NK091(ke)001:20100: kyi bdag po dregs pa ji 'dra ba de bzhin
NK091(ke)001:20101: du mdzad pa ni srin mo la snang bar byed
NK091(ke)001:20102: pa'i ched du ste sme ba brtsegs pa'i dbu dang
NK091(ke)001:20103: phyag zhabs kyang dera mthun du mdzad de /
NK091(ke)001:20104: bdud rtsi lnga yi sngags kyi sbyor ba +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihtha /
NK091(ke)001:20105: zhes pa'i cho 'phrul de yis ru tras mi gtsang
NK091(ke)001:20106: ba'i tshogs kyis 'obs bkang ba'i bshung ba dam rdzas
NK091(ke)001:20107: lnga ni ye shes rang snang gi bdud rtsir bsgyur
NK091(ke)001:20108: bar mdzad de zhal du gsol nas mi gtsang ba'i
NK091(ke)001:20109: 'obs la sogs pa thams cad stong pa'i chos nyid
NK091(ke)001:20110: skye ba med pa'i rdo rjera sbyangs nas mi snang
NK091(ke)001:20111: bar byas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:20115: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20116: de nas nye gnas las kyi koo ri ma brgyad
NK091(ke)001:20117: dang la sogs pas bsdus pa bu mo phra men
NK091(ke)001:20118: brgyad dang dur khrod kyi sgo srung bzhi sogs 'khor
NK091(ke)001:20119: mo bud med kyi tshogs rnams la 'dod pa spyod
NK091(ke)001:20120: pa ltar snang la ma chags pa'i ye shes dang
NK091(ke)001:20121: / sbyor ba byas la sgrib pa mi gsogs pa'i phrin las kyis /
NK091(ke)001:20122: 'dod chags kyi mthuna 'jug gis don la khrid pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20123: sbyor ba'i thabs kyis cha mthun du mdzad nas 'khor
NK091(ke)001:20124: mo rnams dbang du bsdus shing nyon mongs pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:20125: ngang gis sbyangs te de dag gi lhums su thugs
NK091(ke)001:20126: ye shes rang snang ba'i sprul pa bzhag pa ni
NK091(ke)001:20127: / zhi ba'i skabs kyi sems dpa' yab yum sgo
NK091(ke)001:20128: ma bzhi sogs dpal sme ba brtsegs pa'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:20129: las khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du sprul pa'i tshogs rnams
NK091(ke)001:20130: de dag las sras su thon pa na ye shes
NK091(ke)001:20131: kyi ke'u ri tse'u ri la sogsa pa ma tshogs
NK091(ke)001:20132: / rnams dang / seng stag gi gdong can la sogs ye shes kyi phra men rnams dang /
NK091(ke)001:20133: ye shes kyi sgo ma bzhi la sogs par mthong
NK091(ke)001:20134: yul du snang ste mthun pas mthun pa 'dul ba'i
NK091(ke)001:20135: phyir ro // de bas na lam pas zhi ba
NK091(ke)001:20136: las khro bor bsgom pa'ang tshul 'di dag gi phyir
NK091(ke)001:20137: phyir ro // ro // slas la sogs pa rnams kyang thabs chen pos shes rab la rol te /
NK091(ke)001:20138: nyer brgyad ni ye shes kyi dbang phyug mar bkod
NK091(ke)001:20139: nas rdo rje rtse gsum gyi prog zhu can du
NK091(ke)001:20140: byas te thams cad cha byad bsgyur bar mdzad do
NK091(ke)001:20145: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20146: de nas 'dod pa'i dbang mo brkam ma des sprul
NK091(ke)001:20147: pa rdo rje srin po'i sku de la rang gis
NK091(ke)001:20148: chags pa'i dbang gisa gang ltar du mthong ba ni
NK091(ke)001:20149: / spyir ni rang gi khyo badga ru tra lta
NK091(ke)001:20150: bu la de bas kyang lhag par gzi brjid chen
NK091(ke)001:20151: po 'bar bar mthong ngo snyam ste rtog pa'i dbang
NK091(ke)001:20153: gzi brjid la ngo mtshar bas /
NK091(ke)001:20154: e ma'o zhes bdag gi bdag po bas kyang /
NK091(ke)001:20155: shin tu 'od 'bar zhing gzi byin che ba 'di
NK091(ke)001:20156: ni ji lta ba'i sprul pa zhig yin ang snyam
NK091(ke)001:20157: du yid gnyis byung nas brtags pa las /
NK091(ke)001:20158: thabs mchog rdo rje gzhon nu desa mkhyen te ru
NK091(ke)001:20159: tra ma tra ma ra tra zhes srin skad thang
NK091(ke)001:20160: gsum phyung ba las the tshom gyi rtog pa chad
NK091(ke)001:20161: par gyur to // de nas dbang mo chags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20162: dbang gis rtog pa ma byung bar sangs rgyas kyi
NK091(ke)001:20163: sku la nges par 'khril ba na /
NK091(ke)001:20164: dper na tsan dan sbrul gyi snying po'i sdong po la /
NK091(ke)001:20165: tshad pas bdas pa'i sbrul 'khril bas sdong pos mi
NK091(ke)001:20166: rtog bzhin du sbrul gyi tshad pa'i gdung ba sel
NK091(ke)001:20167: ba ltar du / khro mchog sangs rgyas gang la
NK091(ke)001:20168: chags pa mi mang'a bar srin mo gang gi gdung
NK091(ke)001:20169: ba rnam par sel bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:20170: de nas sgrol byed kyi gnyen po khro chen sme
NK091(ke)001:20171: ba brtsegs pa des gdul bya thams cad dang 'tshams
NK091(ke)001:20173: yon tan gyi dpe yid bzhin nor bu lta bu'i
NK091(ke)001:20174: snying po de nyid dus nye bar 'byung ba'i rig
NK091(ke)001:20175: pa sngags 'di brjod par mdzad pas gdug pa 'dul
NK091(ke)001:20176: ba'i phrin las kyi bya ba thams cad byed cing
NK091(ke)001:20177: sgrub pa'i snying po mchog tu gsang ba ste /
NK091(ke)001:20178: gyis dbu drang ste b+hur kur zhes bsnyen pas /
NK091(ke)001:20181: u ts+au sma kro ta bsgrub chen /
NK091(ke)001:20184: de ltar he ru ka la chags pa mi mnga'
NK091(ke)001:20185: bas srin mo'i chags pa la ma chags thabs kyi
NK091(ke)001:20186: sbyor ba mdzad pas sel ba'i dus su rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:20187: 'dzin pa khro bo he ru ka nyid yang dag
NK091(ke)001:20188: dngos min par sprul pa'i sgyu 'phrul sme ba brtsegs
NK091(ke)001:20189: pa'i cho 'phrul 'disa de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi
NK091(ke)001:20190: sku'i tshogs rnam par snang mdzad chen po'i gsung gi
NK091(ke)001:20192: gang du dang poor rnam par snang mdzad nyid las sprul pa ltar /
NK091(ke)001:20193: 'dir yang sa bon thams cad pa'i phyir lhag pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20194: khu ba de yi rnam pa nyid sku ji snyed
NK091(ke)001:20195: pa mngon du 'byung bar byed pa'i mthu can yi
NK091(ke)001:20196: ge gyi gzugs ltar 'od zer las mngon par phaba
NK091(ke)001:20197: nas 'dod pa'i dbang mo brkam ma'i lhums su bzhag
NK091(ke)001:20198: par mdzad la / de bas gsang sngags kyi snying
NK091(ke)001:20199: po yi ge ni sku thams cad mngona par snang
NK091(ke)001:20200: ba'i mthu cana yin pas kho na bzhag pa 'dis
NK091(ke)001:20201: par mdzad la / / srin po'i cha lugs ci 'dra bar /
NK091(ke)001:20202: yi ge de yang khro chen rdo rje srin po'i sku der bsgyur te /
NK091(ke)001:20203: gang de nyid mngon sum du srin mo kro ti ma'i mngal gyi lhums su bzhag par mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:20204: de nas rdo rje ljags kyi 'od zer las sa bon de brtan pa'i sngags bka' stsal te /
NK091(ke)001:20205: bskyed sngags rak+sh+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK091(ke)001:20206: 'joms sngags ru tra ma tra ha ha ham /
NK091(ke)001:20207: zhes sku mngon du bskyed pas rdzogs shing gdug pa
NK091(ke)001:20208: 'joms par byed pa'i phyir yi ge phatahbarjoda pa yi
NK091(ke)001:20209: mthu yis byin gyis brlab pas shin tu drag po
NK091(ke)001:20210: mthu dang ldan par rab tu nges shing brtan par
NK091(ke)001:20215: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20216: sprul pa yin pas rang snang gi sku dngos mina
NK091(ke)001:20217: pa'am phyag dpe la lar dngos med ces bzhugs pas
NK091(ke)001:20218: / ngo bo mi zin par thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20219: ye shes kyi ngo bor bzhugs pa'i rig pa'ii skyes
