NK091(ke)001:20220: bu sme ba brtsegs pa de nyid rdo rje 'dzin
NK091(ke)001:20221: pa chen po he ru ka yab kyi sku la
NK091(ke)001:20223: de ltar phyag na rdo rje shin tu drag shul
NK091(ke)001:20224: che zhing gtum rngam 'bar bas log sde 'joms pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20225: stobs dang ldan pa'i skyes bu rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK091(ke)001:20226: he ru kar byung ba'i ngo bo rdo rje gzhon
NK091(ke)001:20227: nu gzhon nu rnams kyi yab nyid de /
NK091(ke)001:20228: gang de yis dpe sgyu ma ltar ye shes gsang
NK091(ke)001:20229: ba mchog gi sprul pa rdo rje gzhon nu bye
NK091(ke)001:20230: ba sa ya mang por 'gyed pa'i cho 'phrul gyis
NK091(ke)001:20231: / sangs rgyas kun gyi gdul bar dka' ba rnams
NK091(ke)001:20232: btul ba'i sbyor ba mdzad de bya ba rdzogs nas
NK091(ke)001:20233: bdud dang srin po 'jig rten na log pa'i sde
NK091(ke)001:20234: yi cha byad 'dzin pa thams cad 'dul ba'i mdzad
NK091(ke)001:20235: spyod mthun 'jug byis pa'i spyod pa de nyid bor
NK091(ke)001:20236: / nas / tsha bo srin mo'i lhums su bzhag
NK091(ke)001:20237: cing phyogs bcu'i gdug pa btul bas thugs khral bskyungs
NK091(ke)001:20238: pa'i phyir thugs ni snying po byang chub kyi ngang
NK091(ke)001:20239: la dgongs pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs lhun grub rang
NK091(ke)001:20240: gsal nyid du ngesa par 'grel te bzhugs so //
NK091(ke)001:20241: de nyid gdul bya'i snang ba la sprul pa gsang
NK091(ke)001:20242: ba'i bdag po rdo rje 'dzin rgyal chen po phyag
NK091(ke)001:20243: na rdo rje sngar byung gi ston pa'i rgyal tshabs
NK091(ke)001:20244: mdzad pa'i 'chad pa'i skyes bu de yis /
NK091(ke)001:20245: sum cu rtsa gsum dang dga' ldan dang 'og min dbang bsgyur gyi khang bzang ste /
NK091(ke)001:20246: lha gansa gsum du grags pa yi gsang sngags gsang
NK091(ke)001:20247: ba'i mdzod chen po che ba bdun dang ldan pas
NK091(ke)001:20248: dam pa'i lung gi gsang ba chos kyi me long
NK091(ke)001:20249: 'di nyid 'dzin cing ston pa'i mnga' bdag sdud pa
NK091(ke)001:20250: po mdzad de / de bas na he ru ka
NK091(ke)001:20251: nyid gsang bdag drag shul can dan phag tu gyur
NK091(ke)001:20252: ba la the tshom med do //
NK091(ke)001:20253: 'on kyang de ni gcig dang du ma las grol
NK091(ke)001:20254: bas gsang bdag gnyis su thal ba'ang med de bskal
NK091(ke)001:20255: pa gcig gi cha bzung ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:20256: tshul 'dis rdo rje sems dpa'i sgron ma'i zhing gi
NK091(ke)001:20257: rgyal ba rnams kyi gsang chen lung gi bstan pa
NK091(ke)001:20258: rin po che thog ma dang tha ma med par
NK091(ke)001:20259: 'byung ba'i tshul la nges pa rnyed par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:20264: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20265: dee nasa srin po'i sde dpon yi dwags drag po
NK091(ke)001:20266: de nyid srog chags kyi skyams lings las slar log
NK091(ke)001:20267: nas rang gi gnas su 'un zhes pa bru sha'i
NK091(ke)001:20269: rang gi yul khams kyi thod mkhar dang 'obs la sogs pa gnas dang longs spyod dang /
NK091(ke)001:20270: 'khor rnams phal cher mi snang zhing snang ba kun kyang snga ma dang mi 'dra ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:20271: sngon ma mthong ba yi cho 'phrul can du 'khor mo phal chera snang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:20272: de la ru tra kho na shin tu ma rangs
NK091(ke)001:20273: shing yid ma ches te ma dga' bar 'khrugs pas
NK091(ke)001:20274: ngam ste / e ma'o bdag gi phru ma mnga'
NK091(ke)001:20275: 'bang du gnas pa 'di rnams ji ltar gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:20276: yin zhes rnam par rtog cing smra'o //
NK091(ke)001:20277: de tshe nye gnas dbang mo de yis rang gi
NK091(ke)001:20278: khyo bdag lon 'una zhes pa bru sha'i skad de
NK091(ke)001:20279: bod skad du yang 'ong zhes par 'gyur bas yang
NK091(ke)001:20280: 'ong ngo snyam nas sngon bsus te /
NK091(ke)001:20281: ru tra la dga' bas ngam nas /
NK091(ke)001:20282: e ma'o dur khrod kyi rgyan gyis sgeg pa chen
NK091(ke)001:20283: po khams gsum dpa' bo gcig pu khyod gang 'dir
NK091(ke)001:20284: ngan du rtog pa'i tshig 'khor gyi nang du gsung
NK091(ke)001:20285: ngam ci ste / dpa' bo khyod kyi dgongs pa gang /
NK091(ke)001:20286: denga hun han phana nyo ba ti //
NK091(ke)001:20287: kho na'am tsa sma ra tsa //
NK091(ke)001:20288: dpa' bo sgeg po zhe'am nyid //
NK091(ke)001:20289: ku lana tra tsa bu th+ra tha //
NK091(ke)001:20290: zhes pa'i rkang pa bzhi po bru sha'i skad de bod skad du /
NK091(ke)001:20291: de ring phan chad bdag gis sgrubs //
NK091(ke)001:20292: bdag gi lhums ni mi bde ste //
NK091(ke)001:20293: dpa' bo sgeg po khyod nyid kyi //
NK091(ke)001:20294: gdung rgyud 'tshob pa bdag lags na //
NK091(ke)001:20296: srin po ma rangs pa'i sems rtog skyes pa las
NK091(ke)001:20297: srin mos dpa' bo khyod kyi thugs kyi dgongs pa
NK091(ke)001:20298: gang lags pa de nyid de ring phan chad bdag
NK091(ke)001:20299: gis sgrubs te bdag gi mngal ni mi bde ste
NK091(ke)001:20300: / de bas na dpa' bo sgeg po chen po
NK091(ke)001:20301: khyod nyid kyi gdung rgyud legs par 'tshob pa yi
NK091(ke)001:20302: sras gzhon nu bdag la nges par 'byung lags na
NK091(ke)001:20303: gnas gang du rgyu ji zhig gis thugs ji ltar
NK091(ke)001:20304: 'khrul zhes de ltar tshig tu hon zhes pa bru
NK091(ke)001:20305: sha'i skad de smras pa las srin po yid ches
NK091(ke)001:20307: de nas ru tras nye gnas mo dpal dang sbyor
NK091(ke)001:20308: bas lhag par gzi mdangs che ba la chags te
NK091(ke)001:20309: dga' bas 'dun pa dang srin rje kho na'i rigs
NK091(ke)001:20310: nyid nges par 'dzin pa'i sras 'byung ngo snyam nas
NK091(ke)001:20311: dga' ba'i thabs su bzung bar byas so //
NK091(ke)001:20316: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20317: de nas dbang mo brkam ma las pu tra gzhon
NK091(ke)001:20318: nu myu gura thon te rdo rje srin po sku
NK091(ke)001:20319: 'khrungs nas snang ba 'byung ba'i tshe na /
NK091(ke)001:20320: zhal nas khro bo'i gdangs skad thang gsum grags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20321: sgra byung bar mdzad pas dpal gyi rngam skad drag
NK091(ke)001:20322: po h'u gi sgra yis drag po srin po'i tshogs
NK091(ke)001:20323: dang drag mo srin mo'i tshogs la sogs pa ma
NK091(ke)001:20324: lus pa thams cad brgyal bar gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:20325: de nas slar brgyal ba nyid lon zhes pa'ang bru
NK091(ke)001:20326: sha'i skad de sangs nas bltas pas mthong ba'i snang
NK091(ke)001:20327: ba la / rdo rje srin po he ru ka
NK091(ke)001:20328: 'jigs byed chen po rngam brjid rab tu 'bar ba
NK091(ke)001:20329: la sku mdog sngo nag shin tu rngam pa'i tshul
NK091(ke)001:20330: gyis ral pa gyen du bardzesa shing khro bo'i cha
NK091(ke)001:20331: lugs can dbu dgu dang phyag ni bco brgyad pa
NK091(ke)001:20332: rdo rje gshog pasa bar snang khebs pa sogs khro
NK091(ke)001:20334: chos rje dam pa rin po che'i phyag mchan na /
NK091(ke)001:20335: khyab mdzad re skong rdo rje gshog pa'i chas //
NK091(ke)001:20336: gnod gdug bzlog byed rgya bye'u lcags kyi chas //
NK091(ke)001:20337: ting 'dzin dpa' bo rab brjid stag gi chas //
NK091(ke)001:20338: dbang gi bse khrab gzi 'bar gad mo'i chas //
NK091(ke)001:20339: spa brjid mnyen lcugs sbrul nag 'khril ba'i chas //
NK091(ke)001:20340: rdo rje rtse lnga'i slag pa rig pa ting 'dzin chas //
NK091(ke)001:20341: mdangs gsal ku shun chu srin sprul pa'i chas //
NK091(ke)001:20342: ye shes sreg byed rdo rje me yi chas //
NK091(ke)001:20343: zhes pa'i lung drangs par mdzad la /
NK091(ke)001:20344: rgyas par rdo rje srin po'i lha rgyud sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK091(ke)001:20345: de bzhin du sku'i ba spu thams cad lcags kyu
NK091(ke)001:20346: bsregs pa dang 'dra bar 'bar ba'i me stag 'phro
NK091(ke)001:20347: ba / ye shes kyi sprul pa sdom dang sdig
NK091(ke)001:20348: pa dang smyigs bu dang sbrul la sogs pa mi
NK091(ke)001:20349: bzad 'jigs pa'i gzugs kyis sa gzhi thams cad khebsa
NK091(ke)001:20350: ba / par gyur to // phyag bco brgyad na /
NK091(ke)001:20351: dang po gnyis kyi g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon thod skyogs bsnams pa /
NK091(ke)001:20352: gnyis pa gnyis na sti ra dang /
NK091(ke)001:20353: gsum pa gnyis na rgyu zhags bsdogs pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20354: bzhi pas g.yas nyi ma g.yon zla ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:20355: lnga pas g.yas na khyung dang g.yon na 'ug pa
NK091(ke)001:20356: bsnams pa drug pa gnyis na khra dang rdo rje
NK091(ke)001:20357: / bdun pa gnyis na mdung rtse gsum pa dang za ma tog dang /
NK091(ke)001:20358: brgyad pa gnyis na rdul yab dang rnga bsnams shing /
NK091(ke)001:20359: dgu pa gnyis na g.yas ri rab spyi nas bskor zhing g.yon nas stong gsum rgyangs mar 'phen pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:20360: yang na phyag dang po gnyis na rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK091(ke)001:20361: gnyis pa gnyis kyis thod skyogs zhal du gsol ba /
NK091(ke)001:20362: gsum pa gnyis na sti ra dang rgyu zhags /
NK091(ke)001:20363: bzhi pa man chad gong ltar gsungs so //
NK091(ke)001:20364: sku la klu dbang rgyal rigs dkar po'i sbrul sogs
NK091(ke)001:20365: 'bum gyisa brgyan cing klubs pa ste ru tra 'dul
NK091(ke)001:20366: ba'i phyir de'i ngo la snang bas klu mang po
NK091(ke)001:20367: tshad med pa'o // me dpung chen po dusa mtha'
NK091(ke)001:20368: bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar zhing khro gnyer 'jigs pas
NK091(ke)001:20369: tshad med pa'o // brjid la / sdang mig 'bar
NK091(ke)001:20370: ba yi nyi shu rtsa bdun gyi spyan ras zlum
NK091(ke)001:20371: tshad med pa'o // brjid la / pos gzigs te
NK091(ke)001:20372: / zhabs brgyad kyis 'bar ba'i lha chen brgyad gdan
NK091(ke)001:20373: du gnon pas rdo rje srin po khro bo 'jigs
NK091(ke)001:20376: rdo rje srin po khro bo che //
NK091(ke)001:20377: dbu dgu sum brtsegs ral pa 'bar //
NK091(ke)001:20378: rdo rje'i gshog gdengs bar snang khebs //
NK091(ke)001:20379: nyi shu rtsa bdun spyan ras gzigs //
NK091(ke)001:20380: zhabs brgyad lha chen brgyad la gnon //
NK091(ke)001:20381: bco brgyad dang po g.yas g.yon gyis //
NK091(ke)001:20382: rdo rje thod khrag dkrug cing gsol //
NK091(ke)001:20383: de 'og sti ra ril mid mdzad //
NK091(ke)001:20384: de 'og gnyis ni rgyu zhags ldog /bzhi pa g.yas g.yon nyi zla 'dzin //
NK091(ke)001:20385: lnga pa gnyis na 'ug pa khra //
NK091(ke)001:20386: drug pa rdo rje mdung rtse gsum //
NK091(ke)001:20387: bdun pa za ma tog rdul yab //
NK091(ke)001:20388: brgyad pa rnga dang ri rab bskor //
NK091(ke)001:20389: dgu pa stong gsum rgyangs mar 'phen //
NK091(ke)001:20390: klu dbang 'bum gyis sku la brgyan //
NK091(ke)001:20391: dur khrod rgyan rtags bco brgyad 'bar //
NK091(ke)001:20392: dus mtha'i me ltar sku la 'bar //
NK091(ke)001:20393: sdom sdig smrigs sbrul sku las 'phro //
NK091(ke)001:20394: zhes gsungs te rdo rje srin po'i cha lugs bshad pa ltar ro //
NK091(ke)001:20395: de ltar lha dang bdud la sogs pa khams gsum
NK091(ke)001:20396: gyi dregs byed kun gyis mthong zhing thos pa las
NK091(ke)001:20397: khyad par gyi gnyen por rnam par grags shing 'khor
NK091(ke)001:20398: ba'i g.yul las rgyal bar mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:20399: skabs 'dir phyag mtshan la cung zad 'dra min du
NK091(ke)001:20400: byung ba rnams lung las 'byung bas gang ltar yang
NK091(ke)001:20402: khro bo lha rgyud chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:20403: spyi dang bye brag snang ba yang //
NK091(ke)001:20404: spyir na dpal chen he ru ka'i //
NK091(ke)001:20405: sku mdog phyag mtshan ma nges te //
NK091(ke)001:20408: nang ltar na nyon mongs dang bdag 'dzin thabs kyis
NK091(ke)001:20409: spangs pa yin kyang 'das pa 'gags shing ma 'ongs
NK091(ke)001:20410: pa ma skyes pas spang du med la /
NK091(ke)001:20411: da ltar lhan cig skyes pas spang du mi btub bo //
NK091(ke)001:20412: des na mngon du mi spong sa bon spangs pa ste /
NK091(ke)001:20413: me dang du ba lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:20414: de'i phyir 'dir yang rdo rje gzhon nu'i bkod pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:20415: kun gzhi la chos nyid kyi khams sam sa bon
NK091(ke)001:20416: yod pas na thos bsam sgom gsum gyis mthong lam
NK091(ke)001:20417: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes skyed pa dang
NK091(ke)001:20419: kun gzhi la rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:20420: rang byung du skyes te nga bdag dang sgrib pa
NK091(ke)001:20421: bag chags bdud bzhi shin tu phra ba dang bcas
NK091(ke)001:20422: pa rtsad nas gcod pa mthar lam rtsal chen rdzogs
NK091(ke)001:20423: pa skyed pa'o // lnga pa la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:20424: ru tras 'khor gyi dbang phyug rnams la bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:20425: dpa' bskyed cing gnad nas phabs te bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:20431: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20432: de nas yi dwags drag po de nyid kho na'i sems kyi rtog pa cung zhig brtas nas kyang /
NK091(ke)001:20433: nga rgyal drag po'i gtum skad kyis rang gi 'khor
NK091(ke)001:20434: gyi dbang phyug mthu che ba rnams 'di ltar rnam
NK091(ke)001:20435: par bskul te / ru tra ma tra ma ra tra /
NK091(ke)001:20436: zhes dmag la bskul ba'i gtum sngags brjod nas /
NK091(ke)001:20437: 'du zhing 'du bar lha dang srin po dbang phyug
NK091(ke)001:20438: chen po'i tshogs rnams bsdu yis myur bar kun tu
NK091(ke)001:20439: shin tu myur bar rab tu bdag cag gi dam
NK091(ke)001:20440: la 'du bar gyis shig /gram gram du 'gyed pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20441: las la dbang phyug chen po'i tshogs rnams gtong gis
NK091(ke)001:20442: / kun tu rab tu las la gram pa'am 'gyed
NK091(ke)001:20443: par gyis shig /thud thud bcol ba'i las la dbang
NK091(ke)001:20444: phyug chen po'i tshogs rnams 'gyed kyis /
NK091(ke)001:20445: kun tu rab tu bcol ba 'di la nges par
NK091(ke)001:20446: thud de bskul ba bzhin mdzod cig /gnyis pa ni
NK091(ke)001:20450: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20451: dbang phyug chen po'i tshogs rnams ru tra nga yi
NK091(ke)001:20452: phru ma la gang 'dir gdug pa chen po rdo
NK091(ke)001:20453: rje srina po 'di 'joms byed du byung bas 'khor
NK091(ke)001:20454: khyed rnams kyis nges par brlag pa'i dus la baba
NK091(ke)001:20455: kyis / 'di la gang 'dir phyir rgol bar bya
NK091(ke)001:20456: 'am mi bya zhes rtog par byed na khyed rnams
NK091(ke)001:20457: ni 'dis tshur la shin tu brlag ma'am brlag la
NK091(ke)001:20459: bshes sam mdza' bo gang la grogs bya ba dang
NK091(ke)001:20460: mi bya ba'i khyad par yongs su rtog pa can
NK091(ke)001:20461: de dag med kyang bla ste /
NK091(ke)001:20462: de 'dra'i mdza' bo slu byed sgyu ma yina pas na /
NK091(ke)001:20463: de la mdza' bo yin zhes su zhig gis zera te ming tsam yang med do //
NK091(ke)001:20464: rgol ba gang la rtsod par bya ba'am mi bya
NK091(ke)001:20465: ba'i khyad par yongs su rtog pa de 'dra'i 'khor
NK091(ke)001:20466: de dag med kyang bla ste /
NK091(ke)001:20467: de 'dra'i phyir rgola ba de bslu byed sgyu ma
NK091(ke)001:20468: yin pas na de la dpa' bo yin zhes su
NK091(ke)001:20469: zhig zer te ming yang med do //
NK091(ke)001:20470: dam tshig gang la bsrung ba dang mi bsrung ba'i
NK091(ke)001:20471: bye brag yongs su rtog pa de dag med kyang
NK091(ke)001:20472: bla ste / de 'dra'i dam tshig slu byed sgyu
NK091(ke)001:20473: ma yin pas na de la dam tshig ldan par
NK091(ke)001:20474: su zhig 'dogsa te ming yang med do //
NK091(ke)001:20475: lar bya ba thams cad gang la spyod kyang bya
NK091(ke)001:20476: ba'am mi bya ba yi khyad par yongs su rtog
NK091(ke)001:20477: pa de dag meda kyang bla ste /
NK091(ke)001:20478: de 'dra'i spyod pa slu byed sgyu ma yin pas na /
NK091(ke)001:20479: de la bya ba byed ces su zhig zer te
NK091(ke)001:20480: ming yang med pas rdo rje srin po gang la
NK091(ke)001:20481: dus gang 'dir bdag cag gang gi drag po'i las
NK091(ke)001:20487: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20488: zhes ru tra 'jigs pa'i gtum skad kyis dbang phyug chen po rnams la bskul bas /
NK091(ke)001:20489: bdud kyi sde dpon gang gi gzi byin ma bzod de /
NK091(ke)001:20490: bdud kyi cha 'dzin pa'i lha'i bu bye ba dung phyur gyi dmag tshogs dang /
NK091(ke)001:20491: dbang phyug chen po rnams dmag la drangs pas shin tu sngangs pa dang 'khrugs te /
NK091(ke)001:20492: dran pa stor ba tsam du rngam nas skrag pas rod rod por gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:20493: dpe'i dbang du shing mya ngan can gyi lo ma
NK091(ke)001:20494: phyogs gcig tu 'dus nas 'tshub pa'am khong du dug
NK091(ke)001:20495: song na lo ma gdong la 'tshub pa ltar /
NK091(ke)001:20496: don gyi dbang du'ang ngam gnag la sdug bsngal skyes
NK091(ke)001:20497: pas mya ngana gyi duga lo 'tshub pa bzhin du
NK091(ke)001:20498: lang ka'i rtse la bdud kyi phru mara 'dus te
NK091(ke)001:20499: / tri shul la ro btags pas bdud kyi ru mtshon phyar /
NK091(ke)001:20500: mtshon cha'i rigs sna tshogs kyi sprin gtibs /
NK091(ke)001:20501: bdud kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi d+r+wa ba cho 'phrul yod tshad bkram ste /
NK091(ke)001:20502: bso dang cha'i sgra bsgrags nas grong rdal las ma
NK091(ke)001:20503: la ya'i rtse mo'i 'khra sar rgol ba la spags
NK091(ke)001:20504: pa las / drug pa la gsum ste /
NK091(ke)001:20505: rta'i 'dur glus khro bo rnams la thul zhig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:20506: thugs rjes the tshom med par btul ba /
NK091(ke)001:20507: ji ltar btul ba dngos so //
NK091(ke)001:20511: dbang mo drongs shig rab drongs shig /ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20512: de nas srin po rnams spa bkong ba'i phyir gong
NK091(ke)001:20513: du ma la yar so mdzad pa'i rdo rje rta'i
NK091(ke)001:20514: tshogs kyis rdo rje stam pa na'i gom stabs kyis
NK091(ke)001:20515: rdzu 'phrul shin tu myur zhing mgyogs pa'i 'dur shugs
NK091(ke)001:20516: drag pos khro bo gzhan gyi bzhon pa theg chen
NK091(ke)001:20517: ldan pas rta la sogs pa kun kyang rang dbang
NK091(ke)001:20518: med par bdud kyi ngo la 'dur thag gcod pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20519: rta'i 'dur glu khas blangs pa 'dis rnam par bskul
NK091(ke)001:20522: h+r+aizhes dbang du sdud pa'i snying pos drangs te 'bar
NK091(ke)001:20523: ba'i gar dgu ldan pas dpal gyi rgyan chas kyis
NK091(ke)001:20526: sku che la yan lag rags pas 'jigsa su rung ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:20527: zhal g.yas dkar ba dgod pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20528: g.yon dmar ba gshe ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:20529: dbus mthing nag 'jigs par byed pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20530: rgyud drug sgrol bas snying rje dang /
NK091(ke)001:20531: gdug pa can zhal du gsol bas rngam pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20532: chos sku mtshan ma med pas zhi ba la sogs
NK091(ke)001:20533: pa'i sku yi dngos po shina tu khro zhing rngam
NK091(ke)001:20534: par bsgyur ba yi gar gyi phyag rgya dgu dang
NK091(ke)001:20535: ldan pa'i sku chen po cir yang snang la me
NK091(ke)001:20536: dpung 'bar bas dbang phyug chen po ma h+aa de
NK091(ke)001:20538: h+r+aizhes rtsa ba'i yi ge ni snying po ste dbang
NK091(ke)001:20539: du bsdu ba'i phyir mi gtong bar brjod pas mgo
NK091(ke)001:20541: 'dod chags kyis dran pa myos par byed pa ma
NK091(ke)001:20542: h+aa de ba brgya phrag bcu ste stong bas kyang
NK091(ke)001:20543: lhag par gyur pa'i 'dod cing chags pa'i sku gzugs
NK091(ke)001:20544: su ston par mdzod la mthun pas 'dul bar gyis
NK091(ke)001:20545: shig / 'gro ba drag po 'dul ba'i dbang gis
NK091(ke)001:20546: gshin rje stong bas lhag par 'jigs pa'i khro bo'i
NK091(ke)001:20547: gzugs skur ston la gnyen pos 'dul bar gyis shig
NK091(ke)001:20548: shig / pa'o // zhi bas 'dul ba la de
NK091(ke)001:20549: dang mthun par mtshan dpe ldan pa zhi ba'i skur
NK091(ke)001:20550: yang tshangs pa chen po stong bas lhag par rab
NK091(ke)001:20551: tu ston la thul zhig /gdul bya thams cad sngar
NK091(ke)001:20552: bshad pa'i dkyil 'khor rnam gsum gyi ngo bo nyid
NK091(ke)001:20553: du sangs rgyas par kun tu snang bar mdzoda cig
NK091(ke)001:20554: /h+r+aigdul bya rnam par 'dul ba'i stobs kyi ngo mthon
NK091(ke)001:20555: drag pos mngon sum du lha chen po dang dregs
NK091(ke)001:20556: pa can thabs kyis zil gyis gnon par zhabs 'og
NK091(ke)001:20557: tu chug la gdan du non cig pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:20558: rdo rje'i gad mo bzhi ni /
NK091(ke)001:20559: ma rungs khros pa'i gad mo ho ho dang /
NK091(ke)001:20560: tshams ngam rngam pa'i gad mo ha ha dang /
NK091(ke)001:20561: mi bsnyengs rol pa'i gad mo he he dang /
NK091(ke)001:20562: dgyes shing tshim pa'i gad mo hi hi zhes yi ge zung bzhi'i rim pa bzhin no //
NK091(ke)001:20563: de ltar dgyes pa'i bzhad mosa rngam sgras khong la
NK091(ke)001:20564: dbang phyug 'khor bcas thams cad rab tu shig par
NK091(ke)001:20565: thul la kun tu rab tu shiga par thul zhig
NK091(ke)001:20566: /rab kyi rtsal gyi stobs kyis ngo mthon drag pos
NK091(ke)001:20567: dbang phyug ma h+aa de ba'i tshogs choms la dpung
NK091(ke)001:20568: bshigs te zhabs kyi gdan du non zhig /h+r+airtsal chen
NK091(ke)001:20569: ma h+aa de ba de'i chung ma sgyu rtsal chen
NK091(ke)001:20570: pos dbang byed hu lu hu lu mig gsum pa
NK091(ke)001:20571: las gsum grub u ma de b+ai de yang sems
NK091(ke)001:20572: bsgyur bas drongs la dbang du gyis shig /h+r+aikhro bo
NK091(ke)001:20573: drag po'i rab kyi rtsal gyis stobs kyis ngo mthona
NK091(ke)001:20574: du 'jig rten na mthu chen ldan pa khyab 'jug
NK091(ke)001:20575: nag po gdan du gnon par gyis shig /ru tra
NK091(ke)001:20576: ma tra'i bsam pa snying lasa yang dag par chags
NK091(ke)001:20577: pas lha mi dga' bas khyab 'jug gi chung ma
NK091(ke)001:20578: dpal mo de yang drongs shig rab tu drongs la
NK091(ke)001:20579: dbang du gyis shig /h+r+airab tu rtsal gyi stobs kyis
NK091(ke)001:20580: ngo mthon drag pos lha chen tshangs pa de nyid
NK091(ke)001:20581: gdan du non zhig /tshangs pa'i chung ma tshangs las
NK091(ke)001:20582: sgrol ma drongs shig sma ra tha zhes pa bru
NK091(ke)001:20583: sha'i skad de rab drongs shig ces rab tu drongs
NK091(ke)001:20584: la dbang du gyis shig /h+r+airab kyi rtsal gyi stobs
NK091(ke)001:20585: kyis ngo mthon chen pos dga' byed dbang phyug gdan
NK091(ke)001:20586: du non / bdud dpung 'dul ba'i sbyor chen kun
NK091(ke)001:20587: gyi bdag nyid la dga' byed chung ma de yang
NK091(ke)001:20588: drongs la dbang du gyis shig /h+r+airab kyi rtsal gyi
NK091(ke)001:20589: stobs kyisa ngo mthon du dur khrod kyi bdag po
NK091(ke)001:20590: ru tra dpung tshogs choms la zhabs kyi gdan du
NK091(ke)001:20591: non par gyis shig /dpal gyi sbyor chen ru tra'i
NK091(ke)001:20592: chung ma kro ti shwa ri dbang mo de nyid
NK091(ke)001:20593: drongs shig rab tu drongs la dprog nas dbang du
NK091(ke)001:20598: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20599: bshad pa'i dregs pa'i ngag dang mthun pa nyid du gcig pa'i yang phyir te /
NK091(ke)001:20600: gdug pa 'dul ba'i thugs rje'am snying rje mchog gis
NK091(ke)001:20601: sgrol ba de gdul bya gang la bya ba'am mi
NK091(ke)001:20602: bya ba yi yongs su rtog pa de dag med
NK091(ke)001:20603: kyang snying rje chen po bla na med cing mchog
NK091(ke)001:20606: de 'dra' snying rje de nyid snang la ma grub
NK091(ke)001:20607: pas sgyu ma lta bu yin pas na de la
NK091(ke)001:20608: su zhig gis snying rje chen po zer te tha
NK091(ke)001:20609: snyad kyis gdags pa med do //
NK091(ke)001:20610: de bzhin du gdul bya gang la gdul bar bya
NK091(ke)001:20611: ba'am mi bya ba yi khyad par dbye zhing 'dul
NK091(ke)001:20612: mi 'dul gyi the tshom dang yongs su rtog pa
NK091(ke)001:20613: de dag med kyang mchog dang bla na med pa
NK091(ke)001:20615: de 'dra'i gdul bya drag po de nyid snang bzhin
NK091(ke)001:20616: du ma grub par sgyu ma lta bu yin pas
NK091(ke)001:20617: na de la ched du dmigs te gdul bar bya
NK091(ke)001:20618: zhes su zhig zer te thul mi thul med pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20619: phyir ro // gsum pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:20623: dug gsum la zhen pa kun btul ba /
NK091(ke)001:20624: thul nas gsang chen bstan pa'i dbu zug pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:20629: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20631: ha ha tshams ngam rngam pa'i gad mo /
NK091(ke)001:20632: ho ho ma rungs khros pa'i gad mo ste gong dang rjes su mthun la /
NK091(ke)001:20633: khro bo'i gtso bo sprul la 'khor rab tu sprul
NK091(ke)001:20634: te kun tu rab tu sprul pa gdul bya la
NK091(ke)001:20635: snang zhing gsal bar mdzod la /
NK091(ke)001:20636: shin tu sku gtum zhing gsung drag cing thung la
NK091(ke)001:20637: thugs rngam pas 'khrugs te me dpung 'bar ba'i rnam
NK091(ke)001:20638: par kun tu snang bar mdzod cig /gdul bya'i bye
NK091(ke)001:20639: brag rnam pa mang po so sor ma 'dres par
NK091(ke)001:20640: sna tshogs ji snyed pa yi las kyi khro bo
NK091(ke)001:20641: srin por snang ba'i log par lta ba can de
NK091(ke)001:20642: yi rigs kyi zhe sdang can gang cha byad khro
NK091(ke)001:20643: bora snang ba'i 'gro ba rnam pa mang po bsam
NK091(ke)001:20644: yas pa de dag /shin tu zhe sdang drag po'i
NK091(ke)001:20645: tshul gyis khro bo chen por bzhengs pa'i badz+ra he
NK091(ke)001:20646: ru ka yi rigs dang rgyud kyisa gdul bya spyi
NK091(ke)001:20647: dang khyad par ma lus shing lus pa med par
NK091(ke)001:20648: 'dul bar mdzad pa'i thabs tshul mang zhing che ba
NK091(ke)001:20649: dang ldan pa mkhyen pas thabs la mkhas pa mnga'
NK091(ke)001:20650: ba'i phyir / rgyal ba kun gyi thabs mchog ma
NK091(ke)001:20651: grub bzhin du snang bas sgyu ma lta bur mthun
NK091(ke)001:20652: par rab tu sprul zhing gnyen por rnam par sprul
NK091(ke)001:20653: te cir snang ltar du 'dod pa'i phrin las mchog
NK091(ke)001:20654: ba'i phyir / mdzod la / gdul thabs khro bor
NK091(ke)001:20655: snang la ngo bo 'gro 'ong med pa'i dbyings las
NK091(ke)001:20656: ma g.yosa par rang byung gi ye shes chen po
NK091(ke)001:20657: la ye shes bzhi yang lhun gyis rdzogs par snang
NK091(ke)001:20658: ba'i khro bo mchog gis dug gsum zhal du gsol
NK091(ke)001:20659: kun tu bzhes shiga bsgral ba'i pags pa sku la
NK091(ke)001:20660: mnabs par mdzod cig ces bskul lo //
NK091(ke)001:20661: de bzhin du gdul bya rnam pa mang po sna
NK091(ke)001:20662: tshogsa kun tu 'dod par snang ba'i 'gro ba 'dod
NK091(ke)001:20663: chags can rnams / bkod pa rnam pa mang po'i
NK091(ke)001:20664: 'dod chags 'bar ba'i tshul gyis pad+ma he ru ka'i
NK091(ke)001:20665: rigs dang rgyud kyis gdul bya ma lus lus pa
NK091(ke)001:20666: med par 'dul ba'i mang la che ba'i thabs la
NK091(ke)001:20667: mkhas pa mnga' ba'i rgyal ba kun gyi thabsa mchog
NK091(ke)001:20668: snang la grub pa med pa sgyu ma lta bur
NK091(ke)001:20669: rab tu sprul te rnam para sprul zhing 'dod pa
NK091(ke)001:20670: la spyod pa ltar snang la ngo bo ma chags
NK091(ke)001:20671: pa'i ye shes chen pos bde mchog sgyu ma'i ro
NK091(ke)001:20672: nyid kun tu myong bar mdzad nas bzhes shing rol
NK091(ke)001:20673: pa'i gar thabs mdzod cig /de dang mtshungs par gdul
NK091(ke)001:20674: bya rnam pa mang po sna tshogs pa kun tu
NK091(ke)001:20675: rmongs par snang ba'i 'gro ba gti mug can rnams
NK091(ke)001:20676: chags can rnams / / mkhyen rtsal rnam pa mang
NK091(ke)001:20677: po mi 'byed gti mug chen po'i tshul gyis bud+d+ha
NK091(ke)001:20678: he ru ka'i rigs dang rgyud kyisa gdul bya ma
NK091(ke)001:20679: lus shing lus pa med par 'dul ba'i mang la
NK091(ke)001:20680: che ba'i thabs la mkhas pa mnga' ba'i rgyal ba
NK091(ke)001:20681: kun gyi thabs mchog snang la stong pas sgyu mas
NK091(ke)001:20682: rab tu sprul zhing rnam par sprul te /
NK091(ke)001:20683: chos kun 'bras bur mnyam pas 'byed pa med par
NK091(ke)001:20684: rnam pa kun la ma rmongs par rang gsal bsal
NK091(ke)001:20685: bzhag bral bar mkhyen pa'i ye shes ma 'dres yongs
NK091(ke)001:20686: rdzogs chen por bzhengs shing dgongs par mdzod cig ces
NK091(ke)001:20692: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20693: zhes ye shes kyi khro bo chen po ru tra
NK091(ke)001:20694: la sogs pa'i spyod log la ma rangs te dgyes
NK091(ke)001:20695: pa med kyang des mi bsnyengs te bag tsha ba
NK091(ke)001:20696: med pa'i phyir drag po dgyes pa'i gsung sgra 'brug
NK091(ke)001:20697: stong dus gcig tu ldir ba lta bu'i gdangs skad
NK091(ke)001:20698: byung ba bdud tshogs kyi ngo la snang bas bdud
NK091(ke)001:20699: kyi cha 'dzin pa'i bdud dmag bye ba dung phyur
NK091(ke)001:20700: rnams / bag bzhi 'khums te zil gyis gnon par
NK091(ke)001:20701: gyur pas rgol bar ma nus te ru mtshon la
NK091(ke)001:20702: sogs pa'i mtshon cha'i sprin dpung ni byed pa mi
NK091(ke)001:20703: dmigs pas stong pa nyid du sangs par gyur cing
NK091(ke)001:20704: rnams / / bdud kyi sgra dang ag tshar gyi
NK091(ke)001:20705: mi snyan pa'i ngag rnams ni chos kyi tshig don
NK091(ke)001:20706: du shar nas las dang skye ba dang mtshan nyid
NK091(ke)001:20707: thams cad mngon du gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:20708: theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi sgra nii di ri ri sgrogs par gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:20709: de bas na gsang ba mchog gi bstan pa 'byung ba'i 'go tshugs so //
NK091(ke)001:20711: kun gzhi la chos nyid kyi gsal snang 'phel te
NK091(ke)001:20712: dug gsum sa bon gyii cha dang bcas pa'i sgrib
NK091(ke)001:20713: pa thams cad dag pa'i sgom lam gyi ye shes
NK091(ke)001:20714: bskyed pa'o // gnyis pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:20715: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul tshar bcad pa /
NK091(ke)001:20716: bsgral te dngos su btul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:20721: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20722: de nas dur khrod kyi bdag poo ru tra nag
NK091(ke)001:20723: po gcig pu lta zhig rang gi 'khor gyisa yongs
NK091(ke)001:20724: su bor te 'khor thams cad 'jigs byed chen po
NK091(ke)001:20725: rje btsan dam pa de la skyabs su dngos nas
NK091(ke)001:20726: ru tra gcig pu las mi snang ste /
NK091(ke)001:20727: bdud kyi blo dang gros kun gyi yul 'khor thams
NK091(ke)001:20728: cad dang bral bar ma byas pa ni rta'i 'dur
NK091(ke)001:20729: glu'i mathu'o // de nas ru tra nag po rang
NK091(ke)001:20730: gi 'khor la yi khos bsam pa chad pa'am yi
NK091(ke)001:20731: chad de re ba med cing brgal ba'i thabs thams
NK091(ke)001:20733: shin tu zhe sdang drag pos kun nas 'khrugs te
NK091(ke)001:20734: de'i dbang gis dran pa med par rnam par 'khums
NK091(ke)001:20735: nas rtsal yod tshad bton pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:20736: rang gi ru tra lnga'i sa bon mngon du phyungs /
NK091(ke)001:20737: zhes pa'i don 'grel chen gyi lugs kyi nyon mongs pa dug lnga la bshad cing /
NK091(ke)001:20738: lung bstan dang ru tra lam srong gi lugs kyi 'di ltar bshad de /
NK091(ke)001:20739: brtags pa rang rgyud kyi ru tra mos pa rjes
NK091(ke)001:20740: su bzhag pa'i shes pa skyes bu yul gyi 'dod
NK091(ke)001:20741: pas gdung ba lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:20742: sprul pa 'dod pa skongs pa'i ru tra bsam pa
NK091(ke)001:20743: yid dang mthun pa'i shes pa sna tshogs me tog
NK091(ke)001:20744: gi gling la phyin pa lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:20745: ting nge 'dzin ye shes su langs pa'i ru tra
NK091(ke)001:20746: sna tshogs nyams dang ldan pa'i shes pa rgya mtshor
NK091(ke)001:20747: rin po che'i gling la phyin pa lta bu dang
NK091(ke)001:20748: / rig pa rnal du 'jog pa'i ru tra rang
NK091(ke)001:20749: gsal phyogs dang bral ba'i shes pa skyes bu rang
NK091(ke)001:20750: gi mtshan dpe la lta ba lta bu dang /
NK091(ke)001:20751: ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i ru tra klong yangs
NK091(ke)001:20752: snying por chub pa'i shes pa thams cad nam mkha'i
NK091(ke)001:20753: ngang du gnas shing 'byung 'jug med pa lta bu'o
NK091(ke)001:20754: // de la dang po brtags pa rang rgyud kyi ru tra ni /
NK091(ke)001:20757: brtags pas ci bzhin don la sgribs //
NK091(ke)001:20759: log pa'i dbang gis nyon mongs pa lngar brtags pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20760: rtog pa'i dbang gis gzung 'dzin du brtags pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20761: zhen pa'i dbang gis 'dod yon lngar brtags pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:20762: de ni grol thar ba la dad cing mos pa'i shes pa tsam yod de /
NK091(ke)001:20763: dper na skyes bu snying du sdug pa la chags shing zhen pa lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:20764: de nyid le'u nyi shu pa nyer gnyis pa gsum gyis ston no //
NK091(ke)001:20765: gnyis pa sprul pa 'dod pa skongs pa'i ru tra ni /
NK091(ke)001:20767: byin rlabs nyams ldan bla ma yis //
NK091(ke)001:20768: rigs nges ngad ldan shes rab spyod //
NK091(ke)001:20769: las dang thugs rjer 'phrad rung la //
NK091(ke)001:20770: rang bzhin dka' ba'i las dbang gis //
NK091(ke)001:20771: dug gis dug nad bsal ba ltar //
NK091(ke)001:20773: smon lam gyi dbang gis gang sprul pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20774: gdul bya'i dbang gis gang la sprul pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20775: 'dul byed las kyi dbang gis ji ltar sprul pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:20776: de ni gdul bya'i bsam pa yid dang mthun pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20777: shes pa ste me tog sna tshogs kyi gling la
NK091(ke)001:20778: phyin tsam na / mdzes shing yid dang mthun pa lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:20779: de nyid le'u nyer gsum pa nas nyer drug pa'i bar gyis ston no //
NK091(ke)001:20780: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin ye shes su langs pa'i ru tra ni /
NK091(ke)001:20782: sngon nas zhen pa'i bag chags dag /
NK091(ke)001:20783: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ltar //
NK091(ke)001:20784: bla mas gsal byas sel 'gyur bas //
NK091(ke)001:20785: nor bas yid ches 'gyod pa nyid //
NK091(ke)001:20786: gdul bya'i zhen pa sngon bsal nas //
NK091(ke)001:20787: rang sems snying po mthong ba'i rgyu //
NK091(ke)001:20788: da lta nyid du mngon par snang //
NK091(ke)001:20789: bla ma dbang po thams cad la //
NK091(ke)001:20790: mnyes shing tshogs kyis gus mchod cing //
NK091(ke)001:20792: gdul byed drag po'i stobs kyis sngon gyi las dran
NK091(ke)001:20793: te ting nge 'dzin ye shes su langs pa dang
NK091(ke)001:20794: / smre sngags drag po'i shugs kyis gdung ba chad
NK091(ke)001:20795: de ting nge 'dzin ye shes su langs pa dang
NK091(ke)001:20796: / / dbang dang gdams ngag drag po'i byin rlabs
NK091(ke)001:20797: kyis rig pa'i nyams 'phel te ting nge 'dzin ye
NK091(ke)001:20799: de ni ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams 'phel bas rgya
NK091(ke)001:20800: mtsho'i gling du phyin tsam na gang la bltas pa
NK091(ke)001:20801: thams cad nor bu rin po cher 'dug pa lta
NK091(ke)001:20802: bu'o // de nyid nyer bdun pa nas sum cu pa'i bar gyis ston no //
NK091(ke)001:20803: bzhi pa rig pa rnal du 'jog pa'i ru tra ni /
NK091(ke)001:20804: rtogs na ma bcos rang bzhin te //
NK091(ke)001:20805: chu yi rlabs ltar tha dad med //
NK091(ke)001:20806: cir snang rang sems skye med cing //
NK091(ke)001:20807: ngo bo mi 'gyur bcos su med //
NK091(ke)001:20808: mthun dang mi mthun byung tshor ni //
NK091(ke)001:20809: rgyu rkyen gnyis po dang bral bar //
NK091(ke)001:20810: ngo bo mthong ba ye shes gsal //
NK091(ke)001:20811: snga phyi med de de bzhin nyid //
NK091(ke)001:20813: rang bzhin ma bcos par rnal du 'jog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20814: gnas skabs mi 'gyur bar rnal du 'jog pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20815: mtshan nyid ma ltos par rnal du 'jog pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:20816: de ni rig pa ye shes gsal ba'i ye shes
NK091(ke)001:20817: su shar bas skyes bu rang gi mtshan dpe rang
NK091(ke)001:20818: la yod pa ngo ma shes pa me long du
NK091(ke)001:20819: shar nas gsal bar mthong ba lta bu'o //
NK091(ke)001:20820: de nyid nyer dgu pa nas so gcig pa'i bar gyis 'thor bur ston no //
NK091(ke)001:20821: lnga pa ma bcos lhun gyis grub pa'i ru tra ni /
NK091(ke)001:20823: rig pa ji ltar gang gsal kyang //
NK091(ke)001:20824: rang byung rang snang de bzhin nyid //
NK091(ke)001:20825: mthong rtogs goms pa'i skyes bu la //
NK091(ke)001:20826: sgo gsum mdzad pa phyogs ris med //
NK091(ke)001:20827: des na lung thob byin rlabs ldan //
NK091(ke)001:20829: gnas tshul ma bcos par lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20830: snang tshul ma bcos par lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20831: 'bras bu ma bcos par lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:20832: de ni snying po byang chub kyi sems mngon du
NK091(ke)001:20833: gyur pas chos thams cad dbyings kyi nam mkha' la
NK091(ke)001:20834: gsal ba'o // de nyid le'u so gcig pas ston no //
NK091(ke)001:20835: 'dis ni ru tra dang po gol ba nas mthar
NK091(ke)001:20836: 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa'i bar gyi byung tshul
NK091(ke)001:20837: 'di yi skabs don yongs rdzogs la sbyar nas 'chad
NK091(ke)001:20838: do // de ltar 'chad tshul gnyis po gang ltar
NK091(ke)001:20839: yang rang bzhin ye shes su gnas kyang snang cha
NK091(ke)001:20840: bdag tu rtog pa'i mthus nyon mongs pa dug lngar
NK091(ke)001:20841: shar ba la gnyis kar gtogs pa'i khams kyi chas
NK091(ke)001:20842: las kyi khro bor skye ba'i sku yi sa bon
NK091(ke)001:20843: srog sngags brjod nas stobs rtsal mngon du phyung ba
NK091(ke)001:20844: do // ste / dang po ru lu ru lu b+h+yo zhes mngon du brjod pas /
NK091(ke)001:20845: ru tra kho nyid sngar las mgo gsum la lag pa drug can rkang pa bzhi pa /
NK091(ke)001:20846: shin tu khros pa'i tshul du gyur nas che ba bton pa las /
NK091(ke)001:20847: dpal chen po rje btsan rdo rje srin po des
NK091(ke)001:20848: kho na nyid ci 'dra ba bzhin du dbu gsum
NK091(ke)001:20849: phyag drug zhabs bzhi pa der mdzad de /
NK091(ke)001:20850: lus kyi mthu 'phrog cing thugs ye shes kyi byin
NK091(ke)001:20851: rlabs snang ba'i rnam pa yi ge h'u la ngo
NK091(ke)001:20852: bo rdo rje mi phyed pa'i ye shes chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:20853: dbang du kho yi ngag byas te 'khor ba'i sa
NK091(ke)001:20854: bon lnga po ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yoh zhes
NK091(ke)001:20855: su byas nas gsungs pas ngag gi sprul pa de
NK091(ke)001:20856: nyid 'phrogs te ru tra kho na de yi ngag
NK091(ke)001:20857: gi dbang po nyams par mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:20858: de nas yang dur khrod kyi bdag po des /
NK091(ke)001:20859: gnyis pa ra la ra la b+h+yo zhes brjod pas /
NK091(ke)001:20860: de'i stobs kyis mgo dgu la bco brgyad lag tu gyur pa na /
NK091(ke)001:20861: gang der yang dpa' bo rje btsan dam pa des /
NK091(ke)001:20862: dbu dgu bco brgyad phyag tu mdzad nas /
NK091(ke)001:20863: ru tra gang gi sprul pa de nyid nges par bcad do //
NK091(ke)001:20864: yang der yang dur khrod bdag po des /
NK091(ke)001:20865: gsum pa hu lu hu lu b+h+yo zhes brjod pas /
NK091(ke)001:20866: mgo bo lnga la bcu drug lag tu gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:20867: dpal chen rje btsan srin po des kyang ru tra
NK091(ke)001:20868: kho na ci 'dra bar dbu lnga bcu drug phyag
NK091(ke)001:20869: dera mdzad de / der yang kho yi ngag gi brjod pa bacada de nyams par byas so //
NK091(ke)001:20870: 'di la dpe la lar mgo brgyad kyang 'byung la
NK091(ke)001:20871: don la 'di dang lnga mgo rim barje bar gsungs
NK091(ke)001:20872: so // gang der yang dur khrod bdag po des /
NK091(ke)001:20873: bzhi pa ha la ha la b+h+yo zhes brjod pas /
NK091(ke)001:20874: nyi shu rtsa gcig gi mgo bo la /
NK091(ke)001:20875: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi lag pa can du gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:20876: yang du rdo rje srin po des kyang ru tra
NK091(ke)001:20877: de ci 'dra ba kho na ltar dbu nyer gcig
NK091(ke)001:20878: la phyag zhe gnyis can der mdzad nas /
NK091(ke)001:20879: gang 'dir sa bon de slar smra ba'i ngag gi dbang po bcad par mdzad do //
NK091(ke)001:20880: yang der ru tra kho na de nyid kyis /
NK091(ke)001:20881: lnga pa ra li ra li b+h+yo zhes brjod pas /
NK091(ke)001:20882: lus ni tshad med pa'i chen po dbu phyag grangs
NK091(ke)001:20883: med pa la nad kyi bskal pa 'tshub mar gtong
NK091(ke)001:20884: zhing gdug pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs lus las 'gyed
NK091(ke)001:20885: par byed do // rje btsan rdo rje srin po
NK091(ke)001:20886: des kyang ru tra kho na de 'drara dbu phyag
NK091(ke)001:20887: mtha' yas pa nyid mdzad de /
NK091(ke)001:20888: kho yi ngag 'phrogsa par mdzad pas ngag gi sprul pa chad par gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:20889: dper na skyes bu gang la la zhig lce bcad
NK091(ke)001:20890: de khrag gis bor ba bzhin du shin tu myos
NK091(ke)001:20892: de dag gis sbyor lam dang skal ba mnyam par mdzad par mngon no //
NK091(ke)001:20894: kun gyi mnga' bdag /ces pa nas /
NK091(ke)001:20896: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20897: de nas 'khor 'das kun gyi mnga' bdag 'jigs byed
NK091(ke)001:20898: chen po dpal rdo rje srin po desa sa ma
NK091(ke)001:20899: ya ho zhes dam tshig bdar ba'i sngags gsungs te
NK091(ke)001:20900: dam bsgrags par mdzad pas ru tra sngon byung gi
NK091(ke)001:20901: dus bskal pa kun dga' la thar pa nag por
NK091(ke)001:20902: gyur tsam na gsang sgor lhan du zhugs nas mos
NK091(ke)001:20903: pas dam tshig mnos pa'i las dang thugs rjes 'brel
NK091(ke)001:20904: ba yi dbang gis srog gi dbang posa ma bzod
NK091(ke)001:20905: de lam log par phyogs ma phod par gang der
NK091(ke)001:20906: khro bo chen po la mdun gyi phyogs te yid
NK091(ke)001:20907: 'dun zhing mos pa byas pa dang /
NK091(ke)001:20908: rtse gsum kha t+w+aam 'bar ba yis dngos su brgyabs
NK091(ke)001:20909: te bsgral bar byas nas ru tra'i ngo bo bcom
NK091(ke)001:20910: zhing dbang du bsdu ba'i thabs mchog gang gis mdzad
NK091(ke)001:20911: pa gar gyi phyag rgyas rol stabs mdzad de /
NK091(ke)001:20912: sha zos khrag 'thung rus pa 'chos nas dug gsum mchod par bzhes /
NK091(ke)001:20913: yan lag bcad cing gtub ste snying dang dbang po kun phyungs /
NK091(ke)001:20914: nang khrol kun drangs te zhal du mid nas sku'i lto ba'i phyal du sbyangs par mdzad la /
NK091(ke)001:20915: pags pa ni sku la mkhas te gsol /
NK091(ke)001:20917: kho'i dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyang rgyal byed dpa'
NK091(ke)001:20918: rtags kyi rgyan du mdzad de nyon mongs pa rnams
NK091(ke)001:20921: sha khrag rus gsum zos pa ni dug gsum zad pa'i brda dang /
NK091(ke)001:20922: nang khrol kun zos pa gzung 'dzin zad pa'i brda dang /
NK091(ke)001:20923: dbang po rnams zos pa chags pa dang bral ba'i brda dang /
NK091(ke)001:20924: pags pa gyon zhing thod skyogs dung khrag mdzad de
NK091(ke)001:20925: rgyan rnams mnabs shing brgyan te phyag cha kun 'phrogs
NK091(ke)001:20926: pa ni nyon mongs pa thams cad kun nas bsgral
NK091(ke)001:20928: bar skabs der ru tras mthong lam don gyi ye
NK091(ke)001:20929: shes mngon du byas te snang ba rnam 'byed kyi
NK091(ke)001:20930: rtogs pa thob nas zhen pa yongs su dag go
NK091(ke)001:20940: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20941: sngon bskal pa kun dga' la gsang sngags la mos
NK091(ke)001:20942: pa'i las kyi bag chags kyi rgyu dang nye gnas
NK091(ke)001:20943: dam pa rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i skyes bur gyur te
NK091(ke)001:20944: thugs rjes 'brel ba'i rkyen gyi dbang gisa mtshamsa sbyar
NK091(ke)001:20945: te bsgral bar mdzad pa'i byin rlabs kyis thub dka'
NK091(ke)001:20946: rdo rje sems dpar gnas gyur pa'i rang gi bshes
NK091(ke)001:20947: gnyen dam pa la sogsa pa'i mtha' la thug med
NK091(ke)001:20948: pa'i sangs rgyas mang po dang /
NK091(ke)001:20949: blo bral dpag tu med pa'i byang chub kyi semsa
NK091(ke)001:20950: ji bzhin par mngon du byas te 'khor ba'i sel
NK091(ke)001:20951: med pas mi phyed stug po bkod pa'i zhing khams
NK091(ke)001:20952: dam pa gsal bar mthong ba'i mathus /
NK091(ke)001:20953: thog ma med pa'i dus kyi mtha'a nas lhan cig
NK091(ke)001:20954: skyes te zhen cing bag chags pa'i ma rig pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20955: muna nag dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa thams cad
NK091(ke)001:20956: sangs par gyur te rnam par dag nas sngon gyi
NK091(ke)001:20957: gnas rjes su dran pa thob pas skye ba mang
NK091(ke)001:20958: po thog ma'i dus mtha' med pa snyed du lus
NK091(ke)001:20959: blangs pa dang las sna tshogs pa ni gang dang
NK091(ke)001:20960: ci ltar spyad pa'i nyes pa thams cad dran par
NK091(ke)001:20961: gyur to // de nas dpal chen khro bos phyi
NK091(ke)001:20962: sa'i tshul du snam du bton te tha mal pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20963: lus su rgyur nas zhabs drung du 'khod pa nas
NK091(ke)001:20964: gyur to // / dbugs chen po phyin pa rab
NK091(ke)001:20965: tu dag'a bas gus par btud nas sngar gyi las
NK091(ke)001:20966: dang skye ba la shin tu gnong ba'i tshul duga
NK091(ke)001:20967: nga der shin tu ngus nas smre ngas pas ngam
NK091(ke)001:20969: snga ma'i las log mang po dang /
NK091(ke)001:20970: rgyal ba'i zhal ma mthong ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:20971: 'bras bu bde ba ma thob ba la ngam zhing 'gyod pa'am /
NK091(ke)001:20972: yang na mar la ngam pa gnyis dang yar la ngam pa gcig ste /
NK091(ke)001:20973: sngon gyi las la ngam pas e ma zhes dang /
NK091(ke)001:20974: bar du bsgral ba la ngam pas e ma'o zhes dang /
NK091(ke)001:20975: tha ma snam du bton pa la ngam pas e ma yang /
NK091(ke)001:20976: dpa' bo lha rje thugs rje chung /
NK091(ke)001:20977: dpal gyi lto ba shin tu bde ba'i gnas gcig nas snam du btona pa thugs rje chung /
NK091(ke)001:20978: da yang mdzad pa ci mdzad myur du mdzod cig
NK091(ke)001:20979: /myur du bsgral bar mdzad na sgrib pa sregs pas
NK091(ke)001:20980: yun du bde ba mchog gi dbang phyug dang ldan
NK091(ke)001:20986: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:20987: de nas gus pas lus phul te 'bangs su mchi
NK091(ke)001:20988: 'o bdag gi lus dbul gyis 'bangs su mdzad pa
NK091(ke)001:20989: la nan tan ma chung zhig /dus deng nas slan
NK091(ke)001:20990: chad kun tu dpal rdo rje srin pos bka' bstsal
NK091(ke)001:20991: pa bzhin du gsang rgyud las ji ltar grags pa'i
NK091(ke)001:20992: bka' yi lung bzhin rjes su bsgrubs par bagyi'o //
NK091(ke)001:20993: gal te dpal chen dngos kyi bka' bzhin du ma bgyis sama /
NK091(ke)001:20994: sgrub pa po dang gsang ba dam pa'i lung las 'gal bar gyur na /
NK091(ke)001:20995: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo lus snying rnams rim pa
NK091(ke)001:20996: bzhin du mgo rul nas lus myagsa shing snying skam
NK091(ke)001:20997: nasa nges par tshiga para 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:21002: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21003: 'khor gyi ma dang sring mo dang bu mo dang
NK091(ke)001:21004: chung ma rnams kyang 'bangs su 'bul lo 'bangs la
NK091(ke)001:21005: nan tan so tshis ma chung zhig /las las byung
NK091(ke)001:21006: bas dbus su mchi ba'i skal ba mi ldan gyis
NK091(ke)001:21007: / khro bo 'bar ba'i zhal mthong ba dang bsgral
NK091(ke)001:21008: zhing dam la btags pas dkyil 'khor gyi khyams phyi
NK091(ke)001:21009: ma'i mtha' la zhog cig /dman mo yin pas phud
NK091(ke)001:21010: la 'tshal ba'i skal ba mi ldan gyis /
NK091(ke)001:21011: dpal gyi lhag ma la dam tshig yin pas zhal
NK091(ke)001:21012: cha ba bron la rtsol bar mdzod cig /nang ltar
NK091(ke)001:21013: na / bdag med mngon sum du rtogs te mthong
NK091(ke)001:21014: lam rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes skyes pa
NK091(ke)001:21015: na lus kyi zag pa dang bral nas reg pa
NK091(ke)001:21016: dang yid la byed pa la sogs pa thams cad
NK091(ke)001:21017: ye shes su grol bar gyur pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:21019: rgyal ba'i bka' las mi nyams par gyis shig par gdams pa /
NK091(ke)001:21020: rnal 'byor pa la brtse gdung gyis shig par gdams pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:21025: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21026: de nas ru tras 'khor rnams la gdams ngag tu
NK091(ke)001:21027: bstan pa srungs shig pa dang las gyis shig par
NK091(ke)001:21028: gdams te / nye gnas su gyur pa'i gdung zhing
NK091(ke)001:21029: 'dud pa'i ma sring la sogs pa rnams dus deng
NK091(ke)001:21031: de bas na khyed rnams ni bka' lung ci bzhin
NK091(ke)001:21032: du sgrubs par bgyi ba'i bka' yi las mkhan yin
NK091(ke)001:21033: te / bka' yi las gang dang gang byung yang
NK091(ke)001:21034: rtag par myur du sgrubs shig /ru tra bdag kyang
NK091(ke)001:21035: de sngon phan chad lam log cing las nyes par
NK091(ke)001:21036: spyad pas dpag tu meda pa'i 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK091(ke)001:21037: te / kha brgyud kyang / da ni de yis
NK091(ke)001:21038: sun phyung bas lam dam pa la nges par 'jug
NK091(ke)001:21039: /dpal gyi thugs rje dang rang gi las 'phro gnyis
NK091(ke)001:21040: te / kha brgyud kyang / 'phrad pas / longs
NK091(ke)001:21041: spyod rdzogs sku bde ba can gyi zhing du myur
NK091(ke)001:21042: te / kha brgyud kyang / 'phrad pas / bar
NK091(ke)001:21043: 'gro yis / rgyal ba'i rjes su bstan pa'i bka'
NK091(ke)001:21044: lung nas byung ba rnams las nam yang nyams sa
NK091(ke)001:21045: te / kha brgyud kyang / 'phrad pas / bar 'gro yis / re / zhes khas blangs so //
NK091(ke)001:21050: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21051: ji ltar ma byams mas bu la gdung la gdung ba bzhin du /
NK091(ke)001:21052: spyi dang khyad par du sgrub pa po dam tshig
NK091(ke)001:21053: can la dung dung du gdung bar gyis shig /gang
NK091(ke)001:21054: du sring mo byams mas ming po la brtse ba
NK091(ke)001:21055: bzhin du / spyi dang lhag par du sgrub pa
NK091(ke)001:21056: po yal gama can la lhang lhang brtse bar gyis
NK091(ke)001:21057: shig /mdza' mo dga' ba'i grogsa la ji ltar gdung
NK091(ke)001:21058: zhing chags pa'i tshul bzhina du /
NK091(ke)001:21059: gsang ba'i rnal 'byor can la kril kril du chags
NK091(ke)001:21060: pa'i tshul gyis brtse bar gyis shig /ji ltar 'khor
NK091(ke)001:21061: g.yog byams pas rang gi dpon la snying brtse ba
NK091(ke)001:21062: bzhin du / rnal 'byor dam pa rnams la nges
NK091(ke)001:21063: par nye bar gyis shig /zhes 'khor gyi nye gnas
NK091(ke)001:21064: rnams la gdams ngag bor nas thams cad 'jigs byed
NK091(ke)001:21065: dpa' bo chen po la skyabs su dongs te gnas
NK091(ke)001:21066: bzhin du / so // brgyad pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:21070: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21071: bka'i lung gi che ba dbyung ste gsang sngags dang
NK091(ke)001:21072: sgrub pa po yongs su bsrung zhing bskyang ba'i phyir
NK091(ke)001:21073: rang rtags srog gi snying po phul te mna' bor
NK091(ke)001:21074: ro // mna' de'ang 'khor ba'i snying po ru lu
NK091(ke)001:21075: ru lu b+h+yo zhes rang gi srog la tshad du
NK091(ke)001:21076: ro // bzhag go // de nas bcom ldan 'das
NK091(ke)001:21077: dpal chen po nyid kyis rang gi srog la tshad
NK091(ke)001:21078: bzhag pa'i srog snying 'khor ba'i sa bon de nyid
NK091(ke)001:21079: +amo dang h'u gnyis te gsang sngags ru lu 'bru
NK091(ke)001:21080: brgyad du bsgyur te yongs su gnang ba ni 'di
NK091(ke)001:21081: ro // bzhag go // lta ste / +amo ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK091(ke)001:21082: zhes ye shes kyi sa bon du byin gyisa brlabs te /
NK091(ke)001:21083: 'jig rten 'bru lnga la 'das pa'i 'bru gsum bsnan
NK091(ke)001:21084: pas 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos
NK091(ke)001:21085: grub thams cad 'di yis mi 'grub pa gang yang
NK091(ke)001:21086: med la / dregs pa'i sgo gsum gyi sa bon
NK091(ke)001:21087: dang dngos po ngan pa rnams bsregsa shing sbyangs pas
NK091(ke)001:21088: btul nas dag par mdzad de /
NK091(ke)001:21089: sgom lam dag pa'i sa la bkod nas rigs nges pa'i sras su mdzad pas /
NK091(ke)001:21090: thugs kyi dgongs khral chung bar bskyungs te lhun rdzogs bde ba chen por bzhugs so //
NK091(ke)001:21092: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:21093: bdud yongs su btul ba'i le'u ste nyi shu rtsa
NK091(ke)001:21094: bdun pa gsal bar bkrol ba'o ////gsum pa sngags kyi
NK091(ke)001:21095: sgor zhugs nas dbang thob pa la gnyis te /
NK091(ke)001:21096: rgyud sbyangs nas dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa /
NK091(ke)001:21097: zhugs nas dbang thob pa'i yon tan no //
NK091(ke)001:21099: ru tra rgyud sbyangs shing dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa /
NK091(ke)001:21100: 'khor phal pa rgyud sbyangs shing dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:21108: thabs kyi phrin las kyis sbyangs pa'o //
NK091(ke)001:21116: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21118: de nas bdud btul te gdan du byas pa de'i
NK091(ke)001:21119: tshe de'i dus na ru tra'i 'khor gyi ma h+aa
NK091(ke)001:21120: de ba la sogs pa'i dbang phyug chen po'i dpung
NK091(ke)001:21121: tshogs ji snyed pa rnams 'di ltar sems rtog skyes
NK091(ke)001:21122: te / e ma'o zhes ngam nas bdag cag gi
NK091(ke)001:21123: gtso mchog ru tra drag po chen po 'di nyid
NK091(ke)001:21124: te / / 'ad ltar nus pa'i mthu che ba /
NK091(ke)001:21125: 'di ltar phrag dog gis dregsa pa /
NK091(ke)001:21126: 'di ltar gti mug gis ldongs pa /
NK091(ke)001:21128: 'di ltar nga rgyal gyis khengs pa /
NK091(ke)001:21129: 'di ltar zhe sdang gis gdug cing gtum pa 'di
NK091(ke)001:21130: yang dpa' bo chen po rdo rje srin po 'jigs
NK091(ke)001:21131: byed rngam pa'i he ru ka 'dis dngos su bsgral
NK091(ke)001:21132: te lus ni khro bo chen po'i zhabs 'og tu
NK091(ke)001:21133: rnam par bardzisa te gnon zhing /
NK091(ke)001:21134: nges para tshabs che bar sems ni yang dag par phyir mi ldog par legs par non nas /
NK091(ke)001:21135: dus dang rnam pa kun tu 'khor dang sde dpung
NK091(ke)001:21136: du bcas pa thams cad zil gyis rab tu non
NK091(ke)001:21137: to snyam du rnam par rtog go //
NK091(ke)001:21139: 'khor de dag gi sems kyi rtog pa bden pa
NK091(ke)001:21140: mthong ba'i mthus drag po ru tra de'i sems kyis
NK091(ke)001:21142: de nyid bsal ba'i phyir smras pa /
NK091(ke)001:21143: kye nye gnas dam pa rnams /
NK091(ke)001:21144: gang de ltar ma rtog cig /sngon gsang sngags la
NK091(ke)001:21145: zhugs te he ru ka sgoms pas kho bo'i las
NK091(ke)001:21146: kyi 'phro dang 'brel ba de'i dus kyi nye gnas
NK091(ke)001:21147: dam pa da lta kun gyi bshes gnyen de dang
NK091(ke)001:21148: 'phrad pas / dregs pa rang gis dang po bka' bsgo log pa'i las rnams shes so //
NK091(ke)001:21149: de'i dbang gis skye ba du blangs pa shes so //
NK091(ke)001:21152: tha ma da lta zhen pa dag pas dbang po'i mngon sum du lasa mngon du gyur to //
NK091(ke)001:21153: skye ba mngon du gyur nas shes pas rang gi
NK091(ke)001:21154: las la rang thag khos pa'am yi chad par gyur
NK091(ke)001:21155: la / sgrib pa dag pas skad cig mara rdo
NK091(ke)001:21156: rje srin po'i lto bar bde ba chen po'i g.yung
NK091(ke)001:21157: drung gi bkod pa rgyal ba longs spyod rdzogs sku'i
NK091(ke)001:21160: gang 'di ltar bud med dag sbrum pa'i sdug bsngal gyis nyen par gyur pa na /
NK091(ke)001:21162: sdug bsngal 'di ni sngona du skyes pa bsten cing
NK091(ke)001:21163: mang du spyad pa'i las 'ba' zhig kho na 'o
NK091(ke)001:21164: // snyam du yin la yid la byed pa bzhin du /
NK091(ke)001:21165: kho bo yang las 'ba' zhig la kho thag chad nas /
NK091(ke)001:21166: ji ltara ri gzar gyi rtse nas rbab 'dril ba gang gis kyang mi bzlog pa bzhin /
NK091(ke)001:21167: 'gyod pas gdung ba chen po'i shugs kyis las dang
NK091(ke)001:21168: dpal chen po dang rdo rje sems dpa' mthong bar
NK091(ke)001:21169: gyur pas shin tu gdung ba yin te /
NK091(ke)001:21170: nye gnas khyed rnams kyang rang gi las yid la gyis shig dang /
NK091(ke)001:21171: sgrib pa dag pas las dran /
NK091(ke)001:21173: de'i dbang gis dpal chen po la gdung ba'i shugs rbaba ltar 'dril bar 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:21182: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21184: dbang po 'gags pa tsam du rma ga chad par ngus nas /
NK091(ke)001:21185: shin tu smengs te yongs su gdung ba'i don smre sngags su bton pa ni /
NK091(ke)001:21188: dpang po la dgongs su gsol ba /
NK091(ke)001:21189: lam log cing las ngan spyad pas 'khor de 'gyod pa /
NK091(ke)001:21190: nyon mongs pa dang sdug bsngal myong bas 'gyod de thugs rje bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:21191: las ngan las thar pa ston pa'i drin yin pas sngar gang na bzhugs dris pa /
NK091(ke)001:21192: las ngan gyi 'bras bus 'jigs pas mngon spyod mdzod cig par bskul ba /
NK091(ke)001:21193: sngar gyi las la don med pas las kyi rlung bzlog cig par zhus pa /
NK091(ke)001:21194: rgyu rkyen ngan pas nyam thag pas thugs rje bskul te lus phul ba'o //
NK091(ke)001:21199: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21200: ston pa'i mtshan thugs rje chen po mnga' ba'i bcom
NK091(ke)001:21201: ldan 'das thub dka' gzhon nu rgyud dag pa'i dpal
NK091(ke)001:21202: rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ba /
NK091(ke)001:21203: sku'i cha lugs dri ma med pa'i dung mdog lta
NK091(ke)001:21204: bu mtshan dpes spras pas mchog tu gzugs bzang ba
NK091(ke)001:21205: rnam par dag pa'i 'od mdangs gsal ba ni dpe
NK091(ke)001:21206: nyi zla 'bum phrag gdal ba bzhin du phyi nang
NK091(ke)001:21207: gi dgra dpung 'joms pas dpa' bo chen po 'od
NK091(ke)001:21208: zer stong khams khyab par rab tu 'bar ba'i bsnyengs
NK091(ke)001:21209: pa mi mnga' bar mchog tu lham me bar 'phags
NK091(ke)001:21211: gzhan don gyi mdzad pa 'jig rten gsum la rnam
NK091(ke)001:21212: grol gyi lam gsal bar byed pas sa mkhan mchog
NK091(ke)001:21213: gi ston par grags shing khams gsum gyi 'gro ba
NK091(ke)001:21214: kun gyi mgon dang dpung gnyena gcig pur gyur pa
NK091(ke)001:21215: byams mgon thugs rje'i mnga' bdag lhag pa'i lha mchog
NK091(ke)001:21216: khyod kyis bdag la gsan zhing dgongs te rten gyi
NK091(ke)001:21217: stobs su bzhugs par mdzad du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:21222: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21223: bdag ni snga ma'i las la 'gyod de /
NK091(ke)001:21224: srid pa thoga ma med pa'i dus kyi mtha' nas lam log par 'phyan te /
NK091(ke)001:21225: yang dag pa'i lam stor pas srida pa'i grong khyer
NK091(ke)001:21226: gsum gyi 'khor ba'i 'khor lora kun tu 'khyams pas
NK091(ke)001:21227: spyir nongs shing / bye brag tu sngon tshe thar
NK091(ke)001:21228: pa nag por gyur tsa na thog mar lam gyi
NK091(ke)001:21229: bka' bsgo loga nas 'khor ba'i dngos po bzhi la
NK091(ke)001:21230: sogs pa'i sdig pa'i las sna tshogs pa spyad pas
NK091(ke)001:21232: sdig pa'i las rnams gang ci ltar spyad pas rnam
NK091(ke)001:21233: par smin pa gsal bar dran pas rab tu gnong
NK091(ke)001:21234: zhing 'gyod de gdung ba 'don bzhin rnam par sun
NK091(ke)001:21240: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21241: las dang nyon mongs pas 'khor bar ji ltar ltung ba'i sgo nas smrengs te /
NK091(ke)001:21242: shin tu drag la bdo bas dar zhing dragsa te
NK091(ke)001:21243: bzlog dka' ba'i las kyi dbang du song ba de
NK091(ke)001:21244: stobs btsan par gyur nas grong khyer gsum gyi 'khor
NK091(ke)001:21245: ba'i sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho chen por bying bar
NK091(ke)001:21246: gyur te / zhe sdang 'bar ba'i mes ni rang rgyud bsregs shing /
NK091(ke)001:21247: gti mug mun nag ltar rmongs par 'thibs pas shes rab ldongs nas /
NK091(ke)001:21248: srid par nub pa dang zhen pas rlan pa gnyis
NK091(ke)001:21249: kyis 'dod chags kyi rgya mtsho'i 'dam du rnama shes
NK091(ke)001:21250: bying ste / nga rgyal drag po'i ri bosa ngan 'gror mnan bzhin /
NK091(ke)001:21251: phrag dog gi rlung dmar 'tshubs mas 'khor bar srid
NK091(ke)001:21252: pa'i rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs la g.yeng bar gyur pa'i
NK091(ke)001:21253: bdag tu lta ba'i mdud pa dam pos rtag par
NK091(ke)001:21254: bcings te / 'dod pa dung dung pas gdung ba
NK091(ke)001:21255: me mdag gi dong dang 'dra'i zhes 'dra ba'i 'obs
NK091(ke)001:21256: su ltung bas rtsa ba dang yan lag gi sdug
NK091(ke)001:21257: bsngal mi bzad pa drag po char ltar du bab
NK091(ke)001:21258: bcings te / par gyur la / 'di 'dra' sdug bsngal sna tshogs shin tu bzod par dka' zhing /
NK091(ke)001:21259: sdig pa'i las dbang drag po me ltar 'bar bas /
NK091(ke)001:21260: rnam par shes pa dang dbang po rnams kyi ming gzugs kyi myu gu gdung bar gyur te /
NK091(ke)001:21261: 'byung bzhis bsdus pa'i phung poo sgyu ma'i lus kyis
NK091(ke)001:21262: mi bzod par gdung bas 'bod na byams mgon thugs
NK091(ke)001:21263: rje can gyisa thugs kyis bzod lags sam /
NK091(ke)001:21264: zhes dregs pa nyid kyis smrengs te /
NK091(ke)001:21265: dug lnga'i dbang du song bas nyam thag pa la mgon mdzod cig par bskul ba dang /
NK091(ke)001:21266: lha chen po'i tshogs kyis smrengs pa thun mong du 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:21271: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21272: bdag ni blun zhing rmongs pa'i dbang gis las ngan bsags pa'i sdig po che ste /
NK091(ke)001:21273: las kyi dbang gis 'dod pa'i khams 'dir ru trar skyes shing /
NK091(ke)001:21274: skyes pas rnam smin la gnong zhing 'gyod do de'i
NK091(ke)001:21275: rgyu las la yi re chad de yi chad 'gyod
NK091(ke)001:21276: kyang las dbang drag po bcos su med pas las
NK091(ke)001:21277: kyi shugs na dper na chu bo chen po'i gzhung
NK091(ke)001:21278: dang 'dra la / lasa dbang chu klung drag po
NK091(ke)001:21279: de nyid 'phral du ga la zlog ste bzlog mi
NK091(ke)001:21280: dang 'dra la / nus shing / 'khor ba'i rnam
NK091(ke)001:21281: par smin pa thams cad ni rang gi las sna
NK091(ke)001:21283: de ltar las kyi rlung dmar drag po des bdas
NK091(ke)001:21284: pas na bdag ni deng sngon phan chad bskal pa
NK091(ke)001:21285: grangs med nyid du 'khor ba'i btson ra mun pa'i
NK091(ke)001:21287: sngon gyi nye gnas dam pa khyod kyi thugs rje'i
NK091(ke)001:21288: byin rlabsa kyis las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa
NK091(ke)001:21289: kun gtan nas sbyangs shing bcad par mdzad nas /
NK091(ke)001:21290: thar pa la bkod pas ma ltar byams pa'ii zhabs drung du da ltar 'khod de zhal mthong ngo //
NK091(ke)001:21291: ye shes kyi sku nyi ma ltar 'od 'bar zhing
NK091(ke)001:21292: zla ba ltar mdangsa gsal ba'i thugs rje chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:21293: zhal gyi dkyil 'khor nyid lta bas chog mi shes
NK091(ke)001:21294: shing mi ngoms pa'i lhun po'i rgyal po lta bu
NK091(ke)001:21295: gang de / thog ma med pa'i dus nas ma
NK091(ke)001:21296: rig pa'i ling tog gis ldongs pa'i chu bur gyi
NK091(ke)001:21297: mig gis ma mthong bar sgrib par gyur na 'gro
NK091(ke)001:21298: ba'i mgon po dam pa khyed nyid deng gi dus
NK091(ke)001:21299: kyi sngon nam de snga phan chad gang na bzhugs
NK091(ke)001:21300: zhes ye nas ma bral yang phyin ci log gis
NK091(ke)001:21301: sgrib ste ngo ma shes shing ma mthong ba la
NK091(ke)001:21303: ngo bo ru tras smras pa yin kyang /
NK091(ke)001:21304: klu chen po rnams dang gzi byin rgyal po'i mnga'
NK091(ke)001:21305: bdag gis gsol ba dang yang thun mong du 'gyur
NK091(ke)001:21310: ces pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21311: 'di ltar las dbang drag po shin tu mi bzad
NK091(ke)001:21312: pa'i tshul 'di mthong bas shin tu skrag cing skyi
NK091(ke)001:21313: g.ya' la rab tu 'jigs par gyur nas yid dung
NK091(ke)001:21314: dung gdung ba'i ngang gis smre sngags 'di ltar 'don
NK091(ke)001:21315: zhing nyam thag cing phongs pa'i nga ro 'o dod
NK091(ke)001:21316: 'bod pa'i tshig tu gdon zhing bskul lagsa na /
NK091(ke)001:21317: byams mgona mchog gi thugs rjesa dus 'dir myur bar ma dgos na /
NK091(ke)001:21318: nam zhig 'chi zhing 'pho ba'i dus la bab nas lus dang semsa bral ba'i tshe na /
NK091(ke)001:21319: dge ba'i bshes kyi grogs dang bral nas gsod byed
NK091(ke)001:21320: las kyi gshin rjesa zhags pas khrid pa de yi
NK091(ke)001:21321: tshe na 'jig rten gyi nye dus phan pa med
NK091(ke)001:21322: pas mi stongs shing skyobs par mi nus te las
NK091(ke)001:21323: kyi dbang gi bdag 'dra gcig pu kho na mar
NK091(ke)001:21324: las spu nyag bton pa ltar khrid pa'i dus der
NK091(ke)001:21325: bdag la mgon dang skyabs gnas yong ye ma mchis
NK091(ke)001:21326: par ngan 'gro la ltung bar 'gyur gyis /
NK091(ke)001:21327: de bas na dpa' bo thugs rje'i mnga' bdag gang
NK091(ke)001:21328: gi phyi bshol gyi dus la ma gzhes par da
NK091(ke)001:21329: lta nyid du bstun te drag shul mngon spyod mchog
NK091(ke)001:21330: gi phrin las kyis sgrol bar mdzod cig /de ltar
NK091(ke)001:21331: dregs pas smrengs te srin po'i tshogs gzhan dang yang
NK091(ke)001:21337: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21338: de bzhin du las sna tshogs kyis mnar ba'i skye
NK091(ke)001:21339: bo rmongs pa bdag 'dra ba ni thog ma med
NK091(ke)001:21340: pa'i dus nas kun tu rtogs pas phyin ci log
NK091(ke)001:21341: tu brtags te bdag tu bzung bas khams gsum 'khor
NK091(ke)001:21342: ba'i gnas ris drug nas mthar bar gcig nas gcig
NK091(ke)001:21343: tu zo chun brgyud pa ltar 'khor te bskal pa
NK091(ke)001:21344: grangs med mang po brjod pa las 'das par skye
NK091(ke)001:21345: ba ci snyed zhig tu gdos bcas kyi lus de
NK091(ke)001:21346: snyed blangs nas grangs med mang po zhig par gyur
NK091(ke)001:21347: te / sha dang rus pa phyogs gcig tu bsags na 'jig rten khams kyi gtos dang mnyam zhing /
NK091(ke)001:21348: rnag khrag bsags na mtha' yas rgya mtsho chena po
NK091(ke)001:21349: tsam du mang la las 'phro bsags na bsam las
NK091(ke)001:21350: 'das shing brjod du ma lang ba snyed du khams
NK091(ke)001:21351: gsum 'khor ba'i gnas su lan mang por yang nas
NK091(ke)001:21352: yang du bgrangs shing skye ba dang shi ba kho
NK091(ke)001:21353: nar kha brgyud par gyur kyang byas pa'i las rnams
NK091(ke)001:21354: ni don med cing chud re zosa te 'bras med
NK091(ke)001:21355: du song ba kho nar zad do //
NK091(ke)001:21356: des na skye ba grangs meda mang po ci snyed
NK091(ke)001:21357: pa de tsam gyi nang la skye ba gcig cig
NK091(ke)001:21358: kho na tsam gyi las bsags pa de bla na
NK091(ke)001:21359: med pa'i byang chub chen po'i don du yang dag
NK091(ke)001:21360: par rab tu spyad na de tsam byas pa'i las
NK091(ke)001:21361: la 'bras bu 'byung ba'i don bzang po yod par
NK091(ke)001:21362: nges pas don gyi yong ye mya ngan las 'das
NK091(ke)001:21363: te rnam par grol ba thob zin par nges na
NK091(ke)001:21364: yang de lta bu 'i don yang med par las
NK091(ke)001:21365: kyi dbang btsan zhing nyon mongs pa stobs che ba
NK091(ke)001:21366: gang gi mthus sha khrag gi d+r+wa ba'i lus yang
NK091(ke)001:21367: yang blangs shing myong rig sdug bsngal gyi lus dang
NK091(ke)001:21368: 'gyu byed yid kyi lus dang stong pa ltar snang
NK091(ke)001:21369: gi lus sna tshogs su brgyud nas 'khor bar 'khyams
NK091(ke)001:21370: pas sdug bsngal bzod par dka' ba'i srid pa'i khri
NK091(ke)001:21371: mun gyi btson rar chud de mi bzad pa'i sdug
NK091(ke)001:21372: bsngal drag po myong ba 'di lta bu nyes par
NK091(ke)001:21373: byas pa thams cad byed po gzhan med par rang
NK091(ke)001:21374: gi las kho na las byung bas na /
NK091(ke)001:21375: 'dren mchog thugs rje chen posa las ngan las rgyun
NK091(ke)001:21376: bcad de nyon mongs rnams dang las kyi rlung dmar
NK091(ke)001:21377: drag po 'di nyid bzlog par mdzad du gsol /
NK091(ke)001:21378: 'di ni log rtog can rnams kyis gsol ba dang thun mong du 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:21383: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan te /
NK091(ke)001:21384: da lta don mi mdzad na thugs rje mi manga'o zhes gnad la bor ba'i tshul gyis smrengs te /
NK091(ke)001:21385: ma rig pa dang phyin ci log pa las kyi dbang 'di stobs btsan pas /
NK091(ke)001:21386: rang byung rig pa'i don mi shes par rmongs pa
NK091(ke)001:21387: ma rig pa'i muna pa'i nang du gtan du 'khyams
NK091(ke)001:21388: pa lags na / ye shes gsal ba'i sgron ma'i
NK091(ke)001:21389: 'od zer gyis mun pa bsal ba'i thabs kyis phan
NK091(ke)001:21390: gdags te mi stongs sama ci /
NK091(ke)001:21391: nyes par byas pa'i las kyi 'bras bu sdug bsngal drag po mi bzod par gyur na /
NK091(ke)001:21392: thugs rje chen pos sgrol ba'i gar gyi phrin las mi mdzad dam /
NK091(ke)001:21393: mthar 'dzin lta bas phyin ci loga gi g.yang sar ltung ba lags na /
NK091(ke)001:21394: thugs rje myur mgyogs ldan pa'i yang dag lta bas phyag gis mi 'dzin nam /
NK091(ke)001:21395: don dang mi mthun par nyon mongs pa dug gsum bzod par dka' ba'i nad kyis gdung lags na /
NK091(ke)001:21396: gnyen po thabs la mkhas pa'i thugs rje'i bdud rtsi'i sman gyisa mi gso'am /
NK091(ke)001:21397: las kyi rnam par smin pa bzod par dka' ba'i sdug bsngal gyi me klong 'bar na /
NK091(ke)001:21398: thugs rjee bsil ba'i char rgyun bzang po mi 'bebs sam /
NK091(ke)001:21399: sdug bsngal 'byung ba'i 'khor ba'i 'dam du bying zhing nub par gyur na /
NK091(ke)001:21400: thabs la mkhas pas thugs rje'i lcags kyus thar par mi 'dren nam ci /
NK091(ke)001:21401: des na khams gsum 'khor ba'i gnas su sdug bsngal
NK091(ke)001:21402: sna tshogs pas gdung ste sbyangs shing sbyangs nas nam
NK091(ke)001:21403: zhig gi dus na rang gisa rig pa'i 'bras bu
NK091(ke)001:21404: thob pa'i tshe 'phags pa'i thugs rje chen po'i dgos
NK091(ke)001:21405: pa ci zhig 'tshal te don ma mchis pas /
NK091(ke)001:21406: bdag nyid las kyi 'phro gang dbang btsan par bzhag
NK091(ke)001:21407: nas skyob par mi mdzad na ston mchog khyod lta
NK091(ke)001:21408: bu la thugs rje mnga' yang de la skyob pa'i
NK091(ke)001:21409: thugs rje zhes ni 'gro ba su la ltas nas
NK091(ke)001:21410: rgyu mtshan ci zhig gis gdags par bya ste /
NK091(ke)001:21411: de bas dpa' bo khyod la thugs rje chen po'i
NK091(ke)001:21412: stobs mang'a zhing sngon byung gi dus nas 'brel ba'i
NK091(ke)001:21413: las kyi 'phro yang dbang btsan par gyur na /
NK091(ke)001:21414: yal yol dang btang snyoms kyi le lo ma mdzad
NK091(ke)001:21415: par dgongs pa byang chub snying po'i ngang nas da
NK091(ke)001:21416: lta nyid du gzigs shig /thugs rje che mnga' rgyal
NK091(ke)001:21417: ba'i phrin las kun rdzogs pa'i lha yi yang lha
NK091(ke)001:21418: kye / 'di ltar dregs pas smrengs te gsol ba
NK091(ke)001:21419: la 'khor gyi mi dang mi ma yin pa kun
NK091(ke)001:21420: dang yang thun mong du 'gyur ro //
NK091(ke)001:21421: de dag kun tu spyod pa'i stobs te sor chud pa'ang don gyis tshang ngo //
NK091(ke)001:21422: zhes rang gi nga rgyal gyi ri bo bcag nas
NK091(ke)001:21423: lus seng gera mngon par sprul nas skyabs dam par
NK091(ke)001:21425: shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyang ba'i phyir zhabs kyi gdan khrir phul lo //
NK091(ke)001:21427: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dusa pa'i mdo chen po las /
NK091(ke)001:21428: bdud btul bas tha mar dman pa'i gdung ba bton
